[{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":1,"month_string":"January","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My daughter and sister, thank you for welcoming me into your heart. My daughter, in these times you have seen despair, death and backbiting all around you, perhaps you thought you had been abandoned by Me? You are constantly ready to complain, yet I have consoled you many times and you have never noticed this and not only have I given you important teachings, but you have not paid attention to this either. My children and brothers, God is waiting for you in love and joy, I have divided you to help you reflect, I have tested you every holy day and you have not always reflected. How much peace and joy I would like to give to these often hardened hearts.  I would like you to reflect, but how many times have I asked for your hands to lead you towards calm waters and instead you have preferred the storm believing that you are capable of solving everything without My help, but remember that I alone am the Way, the Truth and the Life and I alone can help you, if only you would really entrust yourselves to Me. It is only I who can hold your hands when you ask Me for help with all your heart and it is still I who can give you the consolation you deserve when you feel alone. My children, My time is near, enter the Ark of the Covenant, of peace, of love and brotherhood, only in this way will you be able to overcome the storm that is coming. I have taught you many things in this period and perhaps by calmly rereading my words you will be able to understand My Will, I want to see you all enter My Kingdom. I want to see you all enter into My Kingdom. Now I bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, always be ready to fight together with Me, My Angels, My Archangels and My Blessed Mother and we will succeed in defeating absolute evil and opening the doors to the infinite good. Your dear Jesus.","text_de":"Meine Tochter und meine Schwester, danke, dass Sie mich in Ihr Herz begr\u00fc\u00dfen. Meine Tochter, in diesen Zeiten haben Sie in diesen Zeiten Verzweiflung, Tod und Backbiting um Sie herum gesehen, vielleicht dachten Sie, Sie h\u00e4tten von mir aufgegeben worden worden? Sie sind st\u00e4ndig bereit, sich zu beschweren, aber ich habe Sie oft getr\u00f6stet, und Sie haben dies nie bemerkt, und habe nicht nur ich Ihnen wichtige Lehren gegeben, aber Sie haben auch nicht darauf geachtet. Meine Kinder und Br\u00fcder, Gott wartet auf Sie in Liebe und Freude, ich habe Sie geteilt, um Ihnen zu helfen, Sie zu reflektieren, ich habe Sie jeden heiligen Tag getestet und Sie haben sich nicht immer reflektiert. Wie viel Frieden und Freude m\u00f6chte ich diesen oft geh\u00e4rteten Herzen geben? Ich m\u00f6chte, dass Sie nachdenken, aber wie oft ich nach Ihren H\u00e4nden gefragt habe, um Sie in Richtung ruhiges Wasser zu f\u00fchren, und Sie haben den Sturm, glauben, dass Sie glauben, dass Sie alles ohne meine Hilfe l\u00f6sen k\u00f6nnen, aber denken Sie daran, dass ich allein bin Die Wahrheit und das Leben und ich allein k\u00f6nnen Ihnen helfen, wenn Sie sich nur wirklich anvertrauen w\u00fcrden. Es ist nur ich, der Ihre H\u00e4nde halten kann, wenn Sie mich um Hilfe von ganzem Herzen fragen, und es ist immer noch ich, der Ihnen den Trost geben kann, den Sie verdienen, wenn Sie sich allein f\u00fchlen. Meine Kinder, meine Zeit ist in der N\u00e4he, betreten die Arche des Bundes, des Friedens, der Liebe und der Bruderschaft, nur auf diese Weise werden Sie den Sturm \u00fcberwinden k\u00f6nnen, der kommt. Ich habe Ihnen in dieser Zeit viele Dinge beigebracht, und vielleicht, wenn Sie meine Worte ruhig erneut lesen k\u00f6nnen, k\u00f6nnen Sie meinen Willen verstehen, ich m\u00f6chte, dass Sie alle mein K\u00f6nigreich betreten. Ich m\u00f6chte, dass ich dich alle in mein K\u00f6nigreich betreten.Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen der heiligsten Trinity, sei immer bereit, mit mir zusammenzuk\u00e4mpfen, meine Engel, meinen Erzenzeln und meiner gesegten Mutter und wir werden es gelingen, absolutes B\u00f6se zu besiegen und die T\u00fcren zum unendlichen Guten zu \u00f6ffnen. Dein lieber Jesus.","text_es":"Hija y mi hermana Mina, gracias por darle la bienvenida en su coraz\u00f3n. Mi hija, en estos momentos, \u00bfhas visto a tu alrededor desesperado, muerte y calumnia, tal vez pensabas que me abandonaron? Usted est\u00e1 continuamente listo para quejarse, sin embargo, nunca las he notado muchas veces y nunca lo has notado y no solo te he dado cuenta de las ense\u00f1anzas importantes, sino tambi\u00e9n en esto, no has cargado. Hijos y hermanos, Dios te espera enamorado y alegr\u00eda, te divid\u00ed para que te ayudes a pensar, te puse cada buen d\u00eda y no te has reflejado. \u00bfCu\u00e1nta paz y alegr\u00eda les gustar\u00eda darles a estos corazones endurecidos? Me gustar\u00eda que reflexionaras, pero \u00bfcu\u00e1ntas veces me pido a tus manos para llevar a las aguas de Cheta y, en lugar de eso, prefer\u00edan que la tormenta cre\u00eda que puedes resolver todo sin mi ayuda, pero recuerda que solo yo soy el camino, la verdad? Y la vida y solo puedo ayudarte, aunque solo te conf\u00edes realmente. Solo soy yo que pueda apretar las manos cuando me pides ayuda con todo mi coraz\u00f3n y sigo siendo que puedo darle la consolaci\u00f3n que merece cuando se sienta solo. Mis hijos, mi tiempo est\u00e1 cerca, entr\u00f3 en el Arca de Alianza, Paz, Amor y Hermandad, solo para que puedas superar la tormenta que viene. Te ense\u00f1\u00e9 tantas cosas en este per\u00edodo y tal vez volv\u00ed a leer mis palabras con calma, podr\u00e1s entender mi voluntad, quiero verlos a todos en mi reino.Ahora te bendigo en el nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, siempre est\u00e1 listo para luchar conmigo, mis \u00e1ngeles, mis arc\u00e1ngeles y mi madre m\u00e1s santa y podremos derrotar al mal absoluto, abrir las puertas al infinito. activo. Tu querido Jes\u00fas.","text_fr":"Ma fille et ma soeur, merci de m'avoir accueillir dans votre c\u0153ur. Ma fille, dans ces moments o\u00f9 vous avez vu d\u00e9sespoir, mort et backbiter tout autour de vous, peut-\u00eatre que vous pensiez avoir \u00e9t\u00e9 abandonn\u00e9e par moi? Vous \u00eates constamment pr\u00eat \u00e0 vous plaindre, mais je vous ai consol\u00e9 de plusieurs reprises et vous n'avez jamais remarqu\u00e9 cela et non seulement je vous ai donn\u00e9 d'importants enseignements, mais vous n'avez pas fait attention \u00e0 cela non plus. Mes enfants et mes fr\u00e8res, Dieu vous attend dans l'amour et la joie, je vous ai divis\u00e9 pour vous aider \u00e0 r\u00e9fl\u00e9chir, je vous ai test\u00e9 tous les jours saints et que vous n'avez pas toujours refl\u00e9t\u00e9. Combien de paix et de joie j'aimerais donner \u00e0 ces c\u0153urs souvent durcis. J'aimerais que vous r\u00e9fl\u00e9chissiez, mais combien de fois ai-je demand\u00e9 vos mains de vous conduire vers des eaux calmes et que vous avez pr\u00e9f\u00e9r\u00e9 que vous avez pr\u00e9f\u00e9r\u00e9 que vous croyez que vous \u00eates capable de tout r\u00e9soudre sans mon aide, mais souvenez-vous que je suis seul? , la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 et la vie et moi seuls peuvent vous aider, si seulement vous ne voudriez vraiment me confier \u00e0 moi. Ce n'est que moi qui peut tenir vos mains lorsque vous me demandez de l'aide de tout votre c\u0153ur et c'est toujours moi qui peut vous donner la consolation que vous m\u00e9ritez lorsque vous vous sentez seul. Mes enfants, mon temps est proche, entrent dans l'arche de l'alliance, de la paix, de l'amour et de la fraternit\u00e9, seulement de cette fa\u00e7on pourrez-vous surmonter la temp\u00eate qui arrive. Je vous ai appris beaucoup de choses dans cette p\u00e9riode et peut-\u00eatre en relisant calmement mes paroles, vous pourrez comprendre ma volont\u00e9, je veux vous voir tous entrer mon royaume. Je veux vous voir tous entrer dans mon royaume.Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9, soyez toujours pr\u00eat \u00e0 vous battre avec moi, mes anges, mes archanges et ma m\u00e8re b\u00e9nie et nous r\u00e9ussirons \u00e0 vaincre le mal absolu et \u00e0 ouvrir les portes au bien infini. Ton cher J\u00e9sus.","text_it":"Figlia e sorella mia, grazie per avermi accolto nel tuo cuore. Figlia mia, in questi tempi avete visto intorno a voi disperazione, morte e maldicenza, forse avete pensato di essere stati abbandonati da me? Siete continuamente pronti a lamentarvi, eppure Io molte volte vi ho consolato e di questo non vi siete mai accorti e non solo vi ho dato degli insegnamenti importanti, ma anche su questo non avete fatto caso. Figli e fratelli, Dio vi aspetta nell\u2019amore e nella gioia, vi ho divisi per aiutarvi a riflettere, vi ho messi alla prova ogni Santo giorno e non sempre avete riflettuto. Quanta pace e gioia vorrei dare a questi cuori spesso induriti.  Vorrei che voi riflettiate, ma quante volte ho chiesto le vostre mani per condurvi verso le acque chete e invece avete preferito la tempesta credendo di essere capaci di risolvere tutto senza il mio aiuto, ma ricordate che solo Io sono la Via, la Verit\u00e0 e la Vita e solo Io posso aiutarvi, se solo vi affidaste davvero a me. Sono solo Io che posso stringere le vostre mani, quando mi chiedete aiuto con tutto il cuore e sono ancora Io che posso darvi la consolazione che meritate quando vi sentite soli. Figli miei, il mio tempo \u00e8 vicino, entrate nell\u2019Arca dell\u2019alleanza, della pace, dell\u2019amore e della fratellanza, solo cos\u00ec potrete superare la tempesta che \u00e8 in arrivo. Vi ho insegnato tante cose in questo periodo e forse rileggendo con calma le mie parole riuscirete a comprendere la mia volont\u00e0, Io voglio vedervi entrare tutti nel mio Regno. Ora vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, siate sempre pronti alla lotta insieme a Me, ai miei Angeli, i miei Arcangeli e la mia Santissima Madre e riusciremo a sconfiggere il male assoluto, ed aprire le porte al bene infinito. Il vostro caro Ges\u00f9.","text_pl":"Moja c\u00f3rko i siostro, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce przyj\u0119\u0142a\u015b mnie do swojego serca. C\u00f3rko Moja, w tych czasach widzia\u0142a\u015b wok\u00f3\u0142 siebie rozpacz, \u015bmier\u0107 i oszczerstwa; mo\u017ce my\u015bla\u0142a\u015b, \u017ce zosta\u0142a\u015b opuszczona przeze Mnie? Ci\u0105gle jeste\u015bcie gotowi narzeka\u0107, a ja wielokrotnie was pociesza\u0142em, jednak wy nigdy tego nie zauwa\u017cyli\u015bcie. Udziela\u0142em wam wa\u017cnych nauk, lecz wy r\u00f3wnie\u017c nie zwracali\u015bcie na to uwagi. Moje dzieci i bracia, B\u00f3g czeka na was z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 i rado\u015bci\u0105, podzieli\u0142em was, aby pom\u00f3c wam w refleksji, wystawi\u0142em was na pr\u00f3b\u0119 w ka\u017cdy dzie\u0144 \u015bwi\u0119ty, a wy nie zawsze to rozwa\u017cali\u015bcie. Ile\u017c pokoju i rado\u015bci chcia\u0142abym da\u0107 tym cz\u0119sto zatwardzia\u0142ym sercom. Chcia\u0142bym, aby\u015bcie si\u0119 zastanowili, ile razy prosi\u0142em wasze r\u0119ce, aby poprowadzi\u0142y was ku spokojnym wodom, a wy zamiast tego woleli\u015bcie burz\u0119, wierz\u0105c, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie w stanie rozwi\u0105za\u0107 wszystko bez mojej pomocy, lecz pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce tylko Ja jestem Drog\u0105, Prawd\u0105 i \u017byciem i tylko Ja mog\u0119 wam pom\u00f3c, je\u015bli tylko prawdziwie powierzycie si\u0119 Mnie. Tylko ja mog\u0119 trzyma\u0107 was za r\u0119ce, gdy z ca\u0142ego serca prosicie mnie o pomoc i tylko ja mog\u0119 da\u0107 wam pocieszenie, na kt\u00f3re zas\u0142ugujecie, gdy czujecie si\u0119 samotni. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3j czas jest bliski, wejd\u017acie do Arki Przymierza, pokoju, mi\u0142o\u015bci i braterstwa, tylko w ten spos\u00f3b b\u0119dziecie mogli pokona\u0107 burz\u0119, kt\u00f3ra nadchodzi. Nauczy\u0142em was wielu rzeczy w tym czasie i by\u0107 mo\u017ce poprzez spokojne ponowne przeczytanie moich s\u0142\u00f3w b\u0119dziecie mogli zrozumie\u0107 moj\u0105 wol\u0119, chc\u0119 zobaczy\u0107 was wszystkich wchodz\u0105cych do mojego Kr\u00f3lestwa. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, b\u0105d\u017acie zawsze gotowi walczy\u0107 razem ze Mn\u0105, Moimi Anio\u0142ami, Moimi Archanio\u0142ami i Moj\u0105 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105 Matk\u0105, a uda nam si\u0119 pokona\u0107 z\u0142o absolutne i otworzy\u0107 drzwi do niesko\u0144czonego dobra. Wasz kochany Jezus.","text_pt":"Minha filha e irm\u00e3, obrigado por me receber em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Minha filha, nestes tempos voc\u00ea viu desespero, morte e backbiting ao seu redor, talvez voc\u00ea pensasse que tinha sido abandonado por mim? Voc\u00ea est\u00e1 constantemente pronto para reclamar, mas eu consolei voc\u00ea muitas vezes e voc\u00ea nunca notou isso e n\u00e3o s\u00f3 te dei importantes ensinamentos, mas voc\u00ea n\u00e3o prestou aten\u00e7\u00e3o a isso tamb\u00e9m. Meus filhos e irm\u00e3os, Deus est\u00e1 esperando por voc\u00ea em amor e alegria, dividi-lo para ajud\u00e1-lo a refletir, eu te testei todo dia sagrado e voc\u00ea nem sempre refletiu. Quanta paz e alegria gostaria de dar a esses cora\u00e7\u00f5es muitas vezes endurecidos. Eu gostaria que voc\u00ea refletisse, mas quantas vezes eu pedi suas m\u00e3os para lev\u00e1-lo a \u00e1guas calmas e em vez disso voc\u00ea preferiu a tempestade acreditando que voc\u00ea \u00e9 capaz de resolver tudo sem a minha ajuda, mas lembre-se que eu sou sozinho , a verdade e a vida e eu sozinhos podem ajud\u00e1-lo, se voc\u00ea realmente se confiam a mim. \u00c9 s\u00f3 que eu que posso segurar as m\u00e3os quando voc\u00ea me pedir ajuda com todo o seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o e ainda \u00e9 eu que posso lhe dar o consolo que voc\u00ea merece quando voc\u00ea se sente sozinho. Meus filhos, meu tempo est\u00e1 perto, entre na arca da alian\u00e7a, da paz, do amor e da fraternidade, apenas desta maneira voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 capaz de superar a tempestade que est\u00e1 chegando. Eu te ensinei muitas coisas nesse per\u00edodo e, talvez, lateralmente as minhas palavras, voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 capaz de entender minha vontade, quero ver todos voc\u00eas entrarem no meu reino. Eu quero ver todos voc\u00eas entrar no meu reino.Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, sempre estar pronto para lutar junto comigo, meus anjos, meus arcanjos e minha m\u00e3e aben\u00e7oada e n\u00f3s teremos sucesso em derrotar o mal absoluto e abrir as portas para o bem infinito. Seu querido Jesus.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\u548c\u59b9\u59b9\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u6b22\u8fce\u6211\u8fdb\u5165\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u5728\u8fd9\u4e9b\u65f6\u4ee3\uff0c\u4f60\u5df2\u7ecf\u770b\u5230\u4e86\u7edd\u671b\uff0c\u6b7b\u4ea1\u548c\u80cc\u90e8\u5468\u56f4\uff0c\u4e5f\u8bb8\u4f60\u4ee5\u4e3a\u4f60\u88ab\u6211\u629b\u5f03\u4e86\uff1f\u4f60\u4e0d\u65ad\u51c6\u5907\u62b1\u6028\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\u5df2\u7ecf\u5f88\u591a\u6b21\u5b89\u6170\u4e86\u4f60\uff0c\u4f60\u4ece\u672a\u6ce8\u610f\u5230\u8fd9\u4e00\u70b9\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u6211\u4e0d\u4ec5\u7ed9\u4e86\u4f60\u91cd\u8981\u7684\u6559\u5bfc\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u4f60\u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u6ce8\u610f\u5230\u8fd9\u4e00\u70b9\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u548c\u5144\u5f1f\uff0c\u4e0a\u5e1d\u6b63\u5728\u7b49\u7740\u4f60\u7684\u7231\u60c5\u548c\u559c\u60a6\uff0c\u6211\u5212\u5206\u4f60\u5e2e\u52a9\u4f60\u53cd\u601d\uff0c\u6211\u5df2\u7ecf\u6d4b\u8bd5\u8fc7\u4f60\u7684\u6bcf\u4e00\u5929\uff0c\u4f60\u5e76\u4e0d\u603b\u662f\u53cd\u6620\u3002\u6211\u60f3\u5411\u8fd9\u4e9b\u7ecf\u5e38\u52aa\u529b\u878d\u5316\u7684\u5fc3\u7075\u548c\u9ad8\u5174\u3002\u6211\u5e0c\u671b\u4f60\u53cd\u601d\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\u6709\u591a\u5c11\u6b21\u8981\u6c42\u4f60\u7684\u624b\u5f15\u5bfc\u4f60\u8d70\u5411\u5e73\u9759\u7684\u6c34\u57df\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u5e0c\u671b\u4f60\u80fd\u591f\u5728\u6ca1\u6709\u6211\u7684\u5e2e\u52a9\u4e0b\u89e3\u51b3\u4e00\u5207\u7684\u98ce\u66b4\uff0c\u4f46\u8bf7\u8bb0\u4f4f\uff0c\u6211\u72ec\u81ea\u4e00\u4eba\u7684\u65b9\u5f0f\uff0c\u771f\u76f8\u548c\u751f\u6d3b\u548c\u6211\u72ec\u5904\u53ef\u4ee5\u5e2e\u52a9\u4f60\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u53ea\u6709\u4f60\u771f\u7684\u59d4\u6258\u7ed9\u6211\u3002\u53ea\u6709\u6211\u5f53\u4f60\u95ee\u6211\u5168\u5fc3\u5168\u610f\u7684\u65f6\u5019\u63e1\u4f4f\u4f60\u7684\u624b\uff0c\u6211\u4ecd\u7136\u53ef\u4ee5\u7ed9\u4f60\u4e00\u4e2a\u5b64\u72ec\u7684\u65f6\u5019\uff0c\u4f60\u5e94\u8be5\u5f97\u5230\u4f60\u5e94\u5f97\u7684\u5b89\u6170\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\u9760\u8fd1\uff0c\u8fdb\u5165\u201c\u548c\u5e73\uff0c\u7231\u60c5\u548c\u5144\u5f1f\u60c5\u8c0a\u7684\u76df\u7ea6\u201d\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u8fd9\u6837\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u8fd9\u6837\uff0c\u4f60\u80fd\u591f\u514b\u670d\u5373\u5c06\u5230\u6765\u7684\u98ce\u66b4\u3002\u6211\u5728\u8fd9\u4e2a\u65f6\u671f\u6559\u8fc7\u5f88\u591a\u4e8b\u60c5\uff0c\u4e5f\u8bb8\u901a\u8fc7\u51b7\u9759\u5730\u91cd\u8bfb\u6211\u7684\u8bdd\uff0c\u4f60\u80fd\u591f\u7406\u89e3\u6211\u7684\u610f\u5fd7\uff0c\u6211\u60f3\u770b\u5230\u4f60\u4eec\u6240\u6709\u4eba\u8fdb\u5165\u6211\u7684\u738b\u56fd\u3002\u6211\u60f3\u770b\u5230\u4f60\u4eec\u90fd\u8fdb\u5165\u6211\u7684\u738b\u56fd\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u6700\u795e\u5723\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u603b\u662f\u51c6\u5907\u548c\u6211\u4e00\u8d77\u6253\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5929\u4f7f\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5929\u4f7f\u548c\u6211\u5e78\u798f\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\uff0c\u6211\u4eec\u5c06\u6210\u529f\u5730\u51fb\u8d25\u7edd\u5bf9\u7684\u90aa\u6076\uff0c\u5e76\u5c06\u95e8\u6253\u5f00\u5230\u65e0\u9650\u7684\u5584\u826f\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u8036\u7a23\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":3,"month_string":"January","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for having responded to my call in your hearts. My children, it is a joy to see you united in one voice, in one heart, always be a united family, be mothers, fathers and brothers, with each other. My children, how costly will be what you will see in these times to come, but entrust everything to Jesus, He will not abandon you and will continue to console your heart and soul. Children, if you knew how much beauty there is in the Kingdom of God, already ready for you, look to the future with joy because after the purification of the earth there will be nothing but love, peace and joy. Many, in this year will be healed even from horrible evils, so trust and offer all your sufferings. Beware of the antichrist who is already working in silence, that is why I ask you to increase your faith, otherwise you will not even be able to overcome the Warning that is near. Children, today many graces will descend upon you, witness and have the courage of true faith. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen. Today my angels are among you and are praying with you.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, es ist eine Freude, Sie in einer Stimme in einem Herzen vereint zu sehen, in einem Herzen, immer eine vereinte Familie, Sei M\u00fctter, V\u00e4ter und Br\u00fcder miteinander. Meine Kinder, wie teuer sein wird, was Sie in diesen Zeiten sehen werden, aber alles in Jesus anvertrauen, er wird Sie nicht aufgeben, er wird Sie nicht aufgeben und wird Ihr Herz und Ihre Seele weiter darstellen. Kinder, wenn Sie wussten, wie viel Sch\u00f6nheit in dem Reich Gottes gibt, ist bereits bereit f\u00fcr Sie bereit, schauen Sie mit Freude in die Zukunft, denn nach der Reinigung der Erde gibt es nichts anderes als Liebe, Frieden und Freude. Viele, in diesem Jahr werden selbst von schrecklichen \u00dcbeln geheilt, so Vertrauen und bieten alle Ihre Leiden an. H\u00fcten Sie sich vor dem Antichristen, der bereits in der Stille arbeitet, deshalb bittet Sie, dass ich Sie bittet, Ihren Glauben zu steigern, andernfalls k\u00f6nnen Sie nicht einmal die Warnung \u00fcberwinden, die in der N\u00e4he ist. Kinder, heute werden viele Gnaden auf Sie steigen, Zeuge und den Mut des wahren Glaubens haben. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen. Heute geh\u00f6ren meine Engel unter euch und beten mit dir zusammen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder a mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Hijos, es una alegr\u00eda verte unido en una sola voz, en un solo coraz\u00f3n, siempre ser una familia unida, ser madres, padres y hermanos, entre ellos. Mis hijos, lo caro ser\u00e1 lo que ver\u00e1 en estos tiempos que llegar\u00e1, pero confiar\u00e1 todo a Jes\u00fas, no lo abandonar\u00e1 y continuar\u00e1 consolando su coraz\u00f3n y su alma. Los ni\u00f1os, si supieras cu\u00e1nta belleza est\u00e1 en el reino de Dios, listo para ti, mira al futuro con alegr\u00eda porque despu\u00e9s de la purificaci\u00f3n de la tierra no habr\u00e1 nada m\u00e1s que amor, paz y alegr\u00eda. Muchos, en este a\u00f1o tambi\u00e9n ser\u00e1n curados por malos males, as\u00ed que se confiar\u00e1n y ofrecer\u00e1 todo su sufrimiento. Atenci\u00f3n al anticristo que ya est\u00e1 trabajando en silencio, por eso les pido que aumente su fe, de lo contrario, ni siquiera podr\u00e1 superar la advertencia que es la siguiente. Los ni\u00f1os, hoy en d\u00eda, muchas gracias descender\u00e1n sobre usted, testificaron y tendr\u00e1n el coraje de la verdadera fe. Ahora te bendigo en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Amen. Hoy mis \u00e1ngeles est\u00e1n entre vosotros y rezan contigo.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, c'est une joie de vous voir uni d'une seule voix, dans un c\u0153ur, toujours une famille unie, des m\u00e8res, des p\u00e8res et des fr\u00e8res, les uns avec les autres. Mes enfants, \u00e0 quel point vous serez co\u00fbteux, vous verrez dans ces temps \u00e0 venir, mais de tout confier \u00e0 J\u00e9sus, il ne vous abandonnera pas et continuera de consoler votre c\u0153ur et votre \u00e2me. Enfants, si vous saviez combien de beaut\u00e9 il y a dans le Royaume de Dieu, d\u00e9j\u00e0 pr\u00eat pour vous, regardez-vous vers l'avenir avec joie, car apr\u00e8s la purification de la terre, il n'y aura que de l'amour, de la paix et de la joie. Beaucoup, dans cette ann\u00e9e, seront gu\u00e9ries, m\u00eame de mauvaises maux, alors faites confiance \u00e0 toutes vos souffrances. M\u00e9fiez-vous de l'Ant\u00e9christ qui travaille d\u00e9j\u00e0 en silence, c'est pourquoi je vous demande d'augmenter votre foi, sinon vous ne serez m\u00eame pas en mesure de surmonter l'avertissement proche. Les enfants, aujourd'hui, de nombreuses gr\u00e2ces se descendront sur vous, t\u00e9moignent et auront le courage de la vraie foi. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen. Aujourd'hui, mes anges sont parmi vous et prient avec vous.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, \u00e8 una gioia vedervi uniti in un\u2019unica voce, in un unico  cuore, siate sempre una famiglia unita, siate madri, padri e fratelli, l\u2019uno con l\u2019altro. Figli miei, quanto sar\u00e0 costoso ci\u00f2 che vedrete in questi tempi che arriveranno, ma affidate tutto a Ges\u00f9, Lui non vi abbandoner\u00e0 e continuer\u00e0 a consolare il vostro cuore e la vostra anima. Figli, se sapeste quanta bellezza c\u2019\u00e8 nel Regno di Dio, gi\u00e0 pronto per voi, guardate al futuro con gioia perch\u00e9 dopo la purificazione della terra non ci sar\u00e0 altro che amore, pace e gioia. Molti, in questo anno verranno guariti anche da mali orribili, quindi abbiate fiducia e offrite tutte le vostre sofferenze. Attenzione all\u2019anticristo che sta gi\u00e0 lavorando nel silenzio, ecco perch\u00e9 vi chiedo di aumentare la vostra fede, altrimenti non sarete neanche in grado di superare l\u2019avvertimento che \u00e8 prossimo. Figli, oggi molte grazie scenderanno su di voi, testimoniate e abbiate il coraggio della vera fede. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, Amen. Oggi i miei angeli sono tra voi e pregano con voi.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, to rado\u015b\u0107 widzie\u0107 was zjednoczonych w jednym g\u0142osie, w jednym sercu, b\u0105d\u017acie zawsze zjednoczon\u0105 rodzin\u0105, b\u0105d\u017acie matkami, ojcami i bra\u0107mi, jedni dla drugich. Moje dzieci, ile\u017c kosztowa\u0107 was b\u0119dzie to, co zobaczycie w tych czasach, kt\u00f3re maj\u0105 nadej\u015b\u0107, ale powierzcie wszystko Jezusowi, On was nie opu\u015bci i nadal b\u0119dzie pociesza\u0142 wasze serce i dusz\u0119. Moje dzieci, gdyby\u015bcie wiedzieli, ile pi\u0119kna jest w Kr\u00f3lestwie Bo\u017cym, kt\u00f3re jest ju\u017c dla was gotowe, patrzcie w przysz\u0142o\u015b\u0107 z rado\u015bci\u0105, bo po oczyszczeniu ziemi b\u0119dzie tylko mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, pok\u00f3j i rado\u015b\u0107. Wielu w tym roku zostanie uzdrowionych nawet z okropnych z\u0142ych rzeczy, wi\u0119c miejcie wiar\u0119 i ofiarujcie wszystkie swoje cierpienia. Strze\u017ccie si\u0119 antychrysta, kt\u00f3ry ju\u017c dzia\u0142a w ciszy, dlatego prosz\u0119 was, aby\u015bcie zwi\u0119kszyli swoj\u0105 wiar\u0119, w przeciwnym razie nie b\u0119dziecie w stanie nawet sprosta\u0107 Ostrze\u017ceniu, kt\u00f3re jest blisko. Dzieci moje, dzisiaj zst\u0105pi na was wiele \u0142ask, dajcie \u015bwiadectwo i miejcie odwag\u0119 prawdziwej wiary. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen. Dzi\u015b moi anio\u0142owie s\u0105 w\u015br\u00f3d was i modl\u0105 si\u0119 z wami.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por ter respondido \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, \u00e9 uma alegria v\u00ea-lo unido em uma s\u00f3 voz, em um cora\u00e7\u00e3o, ser sempre uma fam\u00edlia unida, ser m\u00e3es, pais e irm\u00e3os, uns com os outros. Meus filhos, qu\u00e3o caro ser\u00e1 o que voc\u00ea vai ver nestes tempos por vir, mas confiar tudo a Jesus, ele n\u00e3o vai abandonar voc\u00ea e continuar\u00e1 a consolar seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o e alma. Crian\u00e7as, se voc\u00ea soubesse quanta beleza existe no reino de Deus, j\u00e1 est\u00e1 pronto para voc\u00ea, olhe para o futuro com alegria, porque ap\u00f3s a purifica\u00e7\u00e3o da terra n\u00e3o haver\u00e1 nada al\u00e9m de amor, paz e alegria. Muitos, neste ano ser\u00e3o curados mesmo de males horr\u00edveis, ent\u00e3o confiam e oferecem todos os seus sofrimentos. Cuidado com o Anticristo que j\u00e1 est\u00e1 trabalhando em sil\u00eancio, \u00e9 por isso que pe\u00e7o para voc\u00ea aumentar sua f\u00e9, caso contr\u00e1rio, voc\u00ea nem ser\u00e1 capaz de superar o aviso que est\u00e1 pr\u00f3ximo. As crian\u00e7as, hoje muitas gra\u00e7as v\u00e3o descer sobre voc\u00ea, testemunhar e ter a coragem da verdadeira f\u00e9. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m. Hoje meus anjos est\u00e3o entre voc\u00ea e est\u00e3o orando com voc\u00ea.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5728\u4e00\u9897\u5fc3\u4e0a\u770b\u5230\u4f60\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u5feb\u4e50\uff0c\u4e00\u9897\u5fc3\uff0c\u6c38\u8fdc\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u56e2\u7ed3\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\uff0c\u662f\u5f7c\u6b64\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\uff0c\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u5144\u5f1f\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5728\u8fd9\u4e9b\u65f6\u4ee3\u5230\u6765\u7684\u65f6\u5019\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u7684\u6210\u672c\u5982\u4f55\uff0c\u4f46\u59d4\u6258\u4e00\u5207\u5230\u8036\u7a23\uff0c\u4ed6\u4e0d\u4f1a\u629b\u5f03\u4f60\uff0c\u5e76\u5c06\u7ee7\u7eed\u63a7\u5236\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u7075\u548c\u7075\u9b42\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u77e5\u9053\u4e0a\u5e1d\u738b\u56fd\u6709\u591a\u5c11\u7f8e\u5973\uff0c\u5df2\u7ecf\u4e3a\u4f60\u51c6\u5907\u4e86\uff0c\u4ee5\u5feb\u4e50\u4e3a\u672a\u6765\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5728\u5730\u7403\u7684\u51c0\u5316\u4e4b\u540e\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u7231\uff0c\u548c\u5e73\u548c\u559c\u60a6\u90fd\u6ca1\u6709\u3002\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\uff0c\u5373\u4f7f\u662f\u53ef\u6015\u7684\u90aa\u6076\uff0c\u4eca\u5e74\u5c06\u88ab\u6cbb\u6108\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u4fe1\u4efb\u5e76\u63d0\u4f9b\u4f60\u6240\u6709\u7684\u75db\u82e6\u3002\u5c0f\u5fc3\u5df2\u7ecf\u9ed8\u9ed8\u5730\u5de5\u4f5c\u7684\u654c\u57fa\u7763\u8005\uff0c\u8fd9\u5c31\u662f\u4e3a\u4ec0\u4e48\u6211\u8981\u6c42\u4f60\u589e\u52a0\u4f60\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\uff0c\u5426\u5219\u4f60\u751a\u81f3\u65e0\u6cd5\u514b\u670d\u8fd1\u4e4e\u4e34\u8fd1\u7684\u8b66\u544a\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4eca\u5929\u6709\u8bb8\u591a\u683c\u96f7\u65af\u5c06\u4e0b\u964d\u5230\u4f60\uff0c\u89c1\u8bc1\u5e76\u6709\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u7684\u52c7\u6c14\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002\u4eca\u5929\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5929\u4f7f\u662f\u4f60\u4e4b\u4e2d\uff0c\u6b63\u5728\u548c\u4f60\u7948\u7977\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":4,"month_string":"January","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: As prince of the armies of heaven and sent by the most Holy Trinity, I bless you. I convey to you the Divine Will for this people who continue to rebel, not believing in what is approaching for everyone and refusing to work and act according to the divine requests. You are continuously quarrelling, living without peace, each person being their brother\u2019s torment. Humanity is in permanent chaos. Attention, children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ! The churches will increasingly be plundered due to man\u2019s rebellion against what reminds him of law, obedience, love, peace, faith and morality. Pay attention! Communism is advancing: it has not retreated but advances at this time with greater freedom, which humanity itself has granted to it. You are acting like senseless, unreasoning creatures, who later will need one another. Woe to those who, because of the coming famine, because of sickness, in order to maintain the appearance of security, will reject the Divine Seal and replace it with the seal and distinctive mark of the antichrist! Pray, people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: the church will suffer due to changes that will suddenly arise. Pray, people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: pray for the institution of the church, plunged into confusion - the sceptre will pass from one side to the other. Pray, people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: a new disease will be announced. Do not panic, Divine Protection remains over its people. Pray, people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: Central America will suffer, Costa Rica will be shaken. As prince of the heavenly legions, I am the bearer of the Divine Will: you must change into creatures of good, of prudence, of firm and strong faith, convinced of the protection of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. How many, being aware of the approaching darkness, increase their errors, evoking the rebels and persecutors! You need to grow spiritually, to unite with the most Holy Trinity, with our Queen and Mother of the End Times, being sheltered by my heavenly legions. Receive our King and Lord Jesus Christ in the Eucharist, nourish yourselves with the Eucharistic meal. Be love, give love, live in divine love, transmit divine love so that the peace coming from love might bear witness on the part of each one of you. This is the moment for you to reflect: Evil wants to snatch the Ark of the New Covenant from you and leave you orphans in this world of iniquity. Be wise, lest your tongue be a fire that sets everything aflame, lest it be a poison that kills your brother. Keep in mind that it is with the same tongue that kills your brother or sister, that you pray to, bless and venerate the triune god or our Queen and Mother of the End Times. I bless you; we protect you: you have been entrusted to our custody. Remain unafraid: my legions are watching over each of you with constant attention. I bless you. Without fear, walk in faith. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 wojsk niebieskich i pos\u0142aniec Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Przekazuj\u0119 wam Wol\u0119 Bo\u017c\u0105 dla tego ludu, kt\u00f3ry nadal si\u0119 buntuje, nie wierz\u0105c w to, co zbli\u017ca si\u0119 dla wszystkich i odmawiaj\u0105c pracy i dzia\u0142ania zgodnie z boskimi pro\u015bbami. Ci\u0105gle si\u0119 k\u0142\u00f3cicie, \u017cyjecie bez pokoju, ka\u017cdy cz\u0142owiek jest udr\u0119k\u0105 swojego brata. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest w permanentnym chaosie. Uwa\u017cajcie, dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa! Ko\u015bcio\u0142y b\u0119d\u0105 coraz mocniej pl\u0105drowane z powodu buntu cz\u0142owieka przeciwko temu, co przypomina mu o prawie, pos\u0142usze\u0144stwie, mi\u0142o\u015bci, pokoju, wierze i moralno\u015bci. Uwa\u017cajcie! Komunizm posuwa si\u0119 naprz\u00f3d: nie cofn\u0105\u0142 si\u0119, lecz posuwa si\u0119 w tej chwili naprz\u00f3d z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 wolno\u015bci\u0105, kt\u00f3r\u0105 przyzna\u0142a mu sama ludzko\u015b\u0107. Zachowujecie si\u0119 jak bezsensowne, nierozumne istoty, kt\u00f3re p\u00f3\u017aniej b\u0119d\u0105 potrzebowa\u0142y siebie nawzajem. Biada tym, kt\u00f3rzy z powodu nadchodz\u0105cego g\u0142odu, z powodu choroby, aby zachowa\u0107 pozory bezpiecze\u0144stwa, odrzuc\u0105 Bosk\u0105 Piecz\u0119\u0107 i zast\u0105pi\u0105 j\u0105 piecz\u0119ci\u0105 i znakiem rozpoznawczym antychrysta! M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 b\u0119dzie cierpia\u0142 z powodu zmian, kt\u00f3re nagle si\u0119 pojawi\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za instytucj\u0119 ko\u015bcio\u0142a, pogr\u0105\u017con\u0105 w zam\u0119cie - ber\u0142o b\u0119dzie przechodzi\u0107 z jednej strony na drug\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: zostanie og\u0142oszona nowa choroba. Nie wpadajcie w panik\u0119, Boska Ochrona pozostaje nad jego ludem. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Ameryka \u015arodkowa b\u0119dzie cierpie\u0107, Kostaryka b\u0119dzie wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119ta. Jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 niebia\u0144skich legion\u00f3w przekazuj\u0119 wam Bosk\u0105 Wol\u0119: musicie zmieni\u0107 si\u0119 w istoty dobre, roztropne, o mocnej i zdecydowanej wierze, przekonane o ochronie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Jak\u017ce wielu, b\u0119d\u0105c \u015bwiadomym zbli\u017caj\u0105cych si\u0119 ciemno\u015bci, powi\u0119ksza swoje b\u0142\u0119dy, przywo\u0142uj\u0105c buntownik\u00f3w i prze\u015bladowc\u00f3w! Trzeba wzrasta\u0107 duchowo, jednoczy\u0107 si\u0119 z Tr\u00f3jc\u0105 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105, z nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0105 czas\u00f3w ostatecznych, b\u0119d\u0105c chronionym przez moje niebia\u0144skie legiony. Przyjmujcie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa w Eucharystii, karmcie si\u0119 posi\u0142kiem eucharystycznym . B\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, dawajcie mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, \u017cyjcie w Bo\u017cej mi\u0142o\u015bci, przekazujcie Bo\u017c\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, aby pok\u00f3j pochodz\u0105cy z mi\u0142o\u015bci \u015bwiadczy\u0142 o ka\u017cdym z was. To jest moment dla was na refleksj\u0119: Z\u0142o chce wam wyrwa\u0107 Ark\u0119 Nowego Przymierza i zostawi\u0107 was sierotami na tym \u015bwiecie nieprawo\u015bci. B\u0105d\u017acie m\u0105drzy, aby wasz j\u0119zyk nie by\u0142 ogniem, kt\u00f3ry wszystko podpala, aby nie by\u0142 trucizn\u0105, kt\u00f3ra zabija waszego brata. Pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce tym samym j\u0119zykiem, kt\u00f3ry zabija waszego brata lub siostr\u0119, modlicie si\u0119 do Tr\u00f3jjedynego Boga, b\u0142ogos\u0142awicie i czcicie nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119 Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych. Ja was b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119; my was chronimy: zostali\u015bcie powierzeni naszej opiece. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, moje legiony czuwaj\u0105 nad ka\u017cdym z was z nieustann\u0105 uwag\u0105. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Bez l\u0119ku kroczcie w wierze. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.  ","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":7,"month_string":"January","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"To my beloved people: My blessing is with my children so that they would be creatures of good. My people, as you begin, apply what you have forgotten and what is indispensable within every institution: respect for one another. This is not the time for you to live subject to a worldly way of thinking that dominates you, because this would lead you to fall under the dominion of a power that is not mine. You are experiencing hard times, although some feel that it is a respite, without looking beyond what their eyes can see or perceiving how much is approaching again for all humanity, provoking constant expressions of dissatisfaction in various countries, causing serious rebellions with great repression by the rulers. Freedom is being withheld: the rulers dominate the institutions and are making my children live in captivity. You are in transition between what you as humanity have been and what you will be as part of a so-called 'order' which is not my Will. The announced persecution of my mother's children is at an apex; the tentacles of the antichrist, traffickers of my sheep, are ceaselessly poisoning the hearts of my people so that they would rebel against me. That is why my children do not know how to adore me, they forget that I am in you, they seek me only when they feel threatened or afraid, they are stubborn, they mock me, I speak to them and they forget, yet I do not forget my words. They have forgotten me, they have ceased to love my Will, they do not wish to receive me in my body and blood. Loving and imitating my mother is a thing of the past; inviting me to stay is an obstacle to you; you do not desire healthy thoughts or a meek heart. The desire to do good is not even thought about. The technological advancements used to do evil to human beings are causing you to be among the workers of the antichrist. You have become a darkened humanity among whom loyalty does not exist; betrayal goes ahead without reflection, and from this is born institutional schism; from this will be born the schism of my church. I have called you to conversion - it is urgent... Among my people there are so many people who are not authentic: they act in contempt of the divine law, they do not fulfil the sacraments, they live with their own 'god' fabricated at their convenience. They choose their ego in order to please themselves with all that is contrary to me, because if they would serve me, they would not be able to do so much evil. You will see a new liberal religion, innovations within society, innovations within institutions. These innovations will be welcomed by a great number of my children, who will fall into them. My children, the great innovation is what you know already - there is no other\u2026 it is living in my Will. The consequences of wrongful human works and actions continue... Great nations and small nations will go from living in heat to cold, from drought to floods, from passive volcanoes to abrupt eruptions, from peace to death, from abundance to lack of food and medicines and of everything that humanity uses for its well-being. Therefore, plagues that seemed to have been eradicated will appear again as new ones in places that have not been spoken about, but now will be, and war, unthinkable some time ago and avoided on various occasions, will occur. The purification of this generation, which is immersed in its human self, will lead it to live in the cruellest loneliness if it does not renounce its 'ego'. I am present and watch you continually. I love you; I protect you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Do mojego ukochanego ludu: Moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo jest z moimi dzie\u0107mi, aby by\u0142y stworzeniami dobra. M\u00f3j ludu, gdy zaczynacie, stosujcie to, o czym zapomnieli\u015bcie, a co jest niezb\u0119dne w ka\u017cdej instytucji: szacunek do siebie nawzajem. Nie jest to czas, aby\u015bcie \u017cyli poddani \u015bwiatowemu sposobowi my\u015blenia, kt\u00f3ry was zdominowa\u0142, poniewa\u017c doprowadzi\u0142oby to do tego, \u017ce dostaliby\u015bcie si\u0119 pod panowanie w\u0142adzy, kt\u00f3ra nie jest moja. Prze\u017cywacie ci\u0119\u017ckie czasy, cho\u0107 niekt\u00f3rzy uwa\u017caj\u0105, \u017ce jest to wytchnienie, nie patrz\u0105c poza to, co widz\u0105 ich oczy, ani nie dostrzegaj\u0105c, jak wiele zbli\u017ca si\u0119 ponownie dla ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci, wywo\u0142uj\u0105c ci\u0105g\u0142e wyrazy niezadowolenia w r\u00f3\u017cnych krajach, powoduj\u0105c powa\u017cne bunty z wielkimi represjami ze strony rz\u0105dz\u0105cych. Wolno\u015b\u0107 jest wstrzymywana: w\u0142adcy dominuj\u0105 w instytucjach i sprawiaj\u0105, \u017ce moje dzieci \u017cyj\u0105 w niewoli. Jeste\u015bcie w okresie przej\u015bciowym mi\u0119dzy tym, czym jako ludzko\u015b\u0107 byli\u015bcie, a tym, czym b\u0119dziecie jako cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 tak zwanego \"porz\u0105dku\", kt\u00f3ry nie jest moj\u0105 Wol\u0105. Zapowiadane prze\u015bladowania dzieci mojej Matki znajduj\u0105 si\u0119 w punkcie kulminacyjnym; macki antychrysta, handlarze moich owiec, bezustannie zatruwaj\u0105 serca mojego ludu, aby si\u0119 zbuntowa\u0142 przeciwko mnie. Dlatego moje dzieci nie umiej\u0105 mnie uwielbia\u0107, zapominaj\u0105, \u017ce jestem w was, szukaj\u0105 mnie tylko wtedy, gdy czuj\u0105 si\u0119 zagro\u017ceni lub boj\u0105 si\u0119, s\u0105 uparci, wy\u015bmiewaj\u0105 mnie, m\u00f3wi\u0119 do nich, a oni zapominaj\u0105, jednak ja nie zapominam moich s\u0142\u00f3w. Zapomnieli o mnie, przestali kocha\u0107 moj\u0105 wol\u0119, nie chc\u0105 mnie przyj\u0105\u0107 w moim ciele i krwi. Kochanie i na\u015bladowanie mojej Matki nale\u017cy do przesz\u0142o\u015bci; zapraszanie mnie do przebywania jest dla was przeszkod\u0105; nie pragniecie zdrowych my\u015bli ani cichego serca. O pragnieniu czynienia dobra nawet si\u0119 nie my\u015bli.  Post\u0119p technologiczny wykorzystywany do czynienia z\u0142a ludziom powoduje, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie w\u015br\u00f3d pracownik\u00f3w antychrysta. Stali\u015bcie si\u0119 ciemn\u0105 ludzko\u015bci\u0105, w\u015br\u00f3d kt\u00f3rej nie istnieje lojalno\u015b\u0107; zdrada idzie naprz\u00f3d bez refleksji, a z tego rodzi si\u0119 schizma instytucjonalna; z tego zrodzi si\u0119 schizma mojego Ko\u015bcio\u0142a. Wezwa\u0142em was do nawr\u00f3cenia - jest ono pilne... W\u015br\u00f3d mojego ludu jest tak wielu ludzi, kt\u00f3rzy nie s\u0105 autentyczni: post\u0119puj\u0105 wbrew prawu Bo\u017cemu, nie wype\u0142niaj\u0105 sakrament\u00f3w, \u017cyj\u0105 z w\u0142asnym \"bogiem\", sfabrykowanym wed\u0142ug ich wygody. Wybieraj\u0105 swoje ego, aby zadowoli\u0107 si\u0119 tym wszystkim, co jest sprzeczne ze Mn\u0105, bo gdyby Mi s\u0142u\u017cyli, nie mogliby czyni\u0107 tyle z\u0142a. Zobaczycie now\u0105 liberaln\u0105 religi\u0119, innowacje w spo\u0142ecze\u0144stwie, innowacje w instytucjach.  Te innowacje zostan\u0105 przyj\u0119te przez wielk\u0105 liczb\u0119 moich dzieci, kt\u00f3re w nie wpadn\u0105. Moje dzieci, wielk\u0105 innowacj\u0105 jest to, co ju\u017c wiecie - nie ma innej... jest to \u017cycie w mojej woli. Skutki z\u0142ych dzie\u0142 i dzia\u0142a\u0144 ludzkich trwaj\u0105... Wielkie narody i ma\u0142e narody przejd\u0105 od \u017cycia w upale do zimna, od suszy do powodzi, od biernych wulkan\u00f3w do gwa\u0142townych erupcji, od pokoju do \u015bmierci, od obfito\u015bci do braku \u017cywno\u015bci i lekarstw oraz wszystkiego, czego ludzko\u015b\u0107 u\u017cywa dla swego dobrobytu.  Dlatego te\u017c plagi, kt\u00f3re wydawa\u0142y si\u0119 wyeliminowane, pojawi\u0105 si\u0119 ponownie jako nowe w miejscach, o kt\u00f3rych nie m\u00f3wiono, ale teraz b\u0119d\u0105, a wojna, nie do pomy\u015blenia jaki\u015b czas temu i unikana przy r\u00f3\u017cnych okazjach, b\u0119dzie mia\u0142a miejsce. Oczyszczenie tego pokolenia, kt\u00f3re jest zanurzone w swoim ludzkim \"ja\", doprowadzi je do \u017cycia w najokrutniejszej samotno\u015bci, je\u015bli nie wyrzeknie si\u0119 swojego \"ego\". Jestem obecny i obserwuj\u0119 was nieustannie. Kocham was; chroni\u0119 was. Wasz Jezus Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":8,"month_string":"January","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My dear children, thank you for having listened and responded to my call in your hearts. My children, my children, I ask you for urgent conversion, do you not notice that even the days have quickened? I know that you would like everything to end soon, but everything that is in writing must be fulfilled. My children, in this spiritual battle you must be ready and in the forefront of the fight, you who are soldiers of light. My children, soon another lethal virus will appear, be ready to fight for the demands of Jesus, there will be continuous natural catastrophes. My children, the war is ready, when I ask you to stock up, it will not be only for you, but also to help your brothers, because everything is about to collapse, including the economy that will bring famine in a short time. My children. listen to my words and treasure them. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, I am with you, I love you and I will never abandon you. Your Mother.","text_de":"Meine lieben Kinder, danke, dass Sie zugeh\u00f6rt haben, und reagierte auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen. Meine Kinder, meine Kinder, ich bitte Sie um dringende Umwandlung, bemerken Sie nicht, dass sich auch die Tage beschleunigt haben? Ich wei\u00df, dass Sie m\u00f6chten, dass alles bald enden w\u00fcrde, aber alles, was schriftlich ist, muss erf\u00fcllt sein. Meine Kinder, in dieser spirituellen Schlacht m\u00fcssen Sie bereit sein und in der Spitze des Kampfes, Sie, die Soldaten von Licht sind. Meine Kinder, bald ein weiteres t\u00f6dliches Virus wird erscheinen, ist bereit, f\u00fcr die Anforderungen Jesu zu k\u00e4mpfen, es wird kontinuierliche nat\u00fcrliche Katastrophen geben. Meine Kinder, der Krieg ist fertig, wenn ich Sie bittet, um aufzufordern, dass es sich nicht nur f\u00fcr Sie handelt, sondern auch f\u00fcr Sie, sondern auch, um Ihren Br\u00fcdern zu helfen, da alles kurz davor kommt, einschlie\u00dflich der Wirtschaft, die in kurzer Zeit Hungersnot einbringt. Meine Kinder. H\u00f6ren Sie auf meine Worte und sch\u00e4tzen Sie sie. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, ich bin bei dir, ich liebe dich und ich werde dich niemals aufgeben. Ihre Mutter.","text_es":"Estimados hijos, gracias por escuchar y respondieron mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Los ni\u00f1os, mis hijos, les hago la conversi\u00f3n urgente, \u00bfno te das cuenta de que incluso los d\u00edas se han acelerado? Pero gracias a sus oraciones, todo se convierte en una gran velocidad, s\u00e9 que le gustar\u00eda que terminara pronto, pero todo lo que est\u00e1 por escrito tendr\u00e1 que haber cumplido. Los ni\u00f1os, en esta batalla espiritual tendr\u00e1s que estar listos y a la vanguardia en combate, t\u00fa que son soldados ligeros. Mis hijos, pronto aparecer\u00e1 otro virus letal, estar\u00e1 listo para luchar por las solicitudes de Jes\u00fas, habr\u00e1 cat\u00e1strofes naturales continuas. Los ni\u00f1os, la guerra est\u00e1 lista, cuando le pido que te abastiques, no ser\u00e1 solo para usted, sino tambi\u00e9n para ayudar a sus hermanos, porque todo est\u00e1 a punto de colapsar, incluida la econom\u00eda que tomar\u00e1 la hambruna r\u00e1pidamente. Mis hijos. Escucha mis palabras y tesoros. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del Padre, del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, estoy contigo, te amo y nunca te dejar\u00e9. Tu madre.","text_fr":"Mes chers enfants, merci d'avoir \u00e9cout\u00e9 et avons r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, mes enfants, je vous demande une conversion urgente, ne remarquez-vous pas que m\u00eame les jours ont acc\u00e9l\u00e9r\u00e9? Je sais que vous voudriez que tout se termine bient\u00f4t, mais tout ce qui est \u00e9crit doit \u00eatre rempli. Mes enfants, dans cette bataille spirituelle, vous devez \u00eatre pr\u00eat et \u00e0 la pointe du combat, vous qui \u00eates des soldats de lumi\u00e8re. Mes enfants, bient\u00f4t un autre virus mortel appara\u00eetront, \u00eatre pr\u00eat \u00e0 se battre pour les demandes de J\u00e9sus, il y aura des catastrophes naturelles continues. Mes enfants, la guerre est pr\u00eate, lorsque je vous demande de stocker, ce n'est pas seulement pour vous, mais aussi pour aider vos fr\u00e8res, car tout est sur le point de s'effondrer, y compris de l'\u00e9conomie qui apportera la famine en peu de temps. Mes enfants. \u00c9coutez mes mots et ch\u00e9rissez-les. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, je suis avec toi, je t'aime et je ne t'abandonnerai jamais. Ta m\u00e8re.","text_it":"Cari figli miei, grazie per avere ascoltato e risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, bambini miei, vi chiedo l\u2019urgente conversione, non vi accorgete che anche le giornate si sono velocizzate? Ma grazie alle vostre preghiere tutto volge in grande velocit\u00e0, so che vorreste che tutto finisse presto, ma tutto ci\u00f2 che \u00e8 nella scrittura dovr\u00e0 avere compimento. Figli, in questa battaglia spirituale dovrete essere pronti e in prima linea nel combattimento, voi che siete soldati di luce. Figli miei, presto un\u2019 altro virus letale si affaccer\u00e0, siate pronti a lottare per le richieste di Ges\u00f9, ci saranno continue catastrofi naturali. Figli, la guerra \u00e8 pronta, quando vi chiedo di fare scorte, non sar\u00e0 solo per voi, ma anche per aiutare i vostri fratelli, perch\u00e9 tutto sta per crollare, compresa l\u2019economia che porter\u00e0 la carestia in tempi brevi. Figli miei. ascoltate le mie parole e fatene tesoro. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, sono con voi, vi amo e non vi abbandoner\u00f2 mai. Vostra Madre.","text_pl":"Moje drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam za to, \u017ce wys\u0142uchali\u015bcie i odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, moje dzieci, prosz\u0119 was o pilne nawr\u00f3cenie, czy nie zauwa\u017cyli\u015bcie, \u017ce nawet dni przyspieszy\u0142y? Wiem, \u017ce chcia\u0142aby\u015b, aby wszystko szybko si\u0119 sko\u0144czy\u0142o, ale wszystko, co jest napisane, musi si\u0119 wype\u0142ni\u0107. Dzieci moje, w tym duchowym boju musicie by\u0107 gotowi i sta\u0107 w pierwszej linii walki, wy, kt\u00f3rzy jeste\u015bcie \u017co\u0142nierzami \u015bwiat\u0142o\u015bci. Moje dzieci, wkr\u00f3tce pojawi si\u0119 kolejny \u015bmiertelny wirus, b\u0105d\u017acie gotowi do walki o spe\u0142nienie wymaga\u0144 Jezusa, b\u0119d\u0105 ci\u0105g\u0142e katastrofy naturalne. Moje dzieci, wojna jest gotowa, kiedy poprosz\u0119 was o zapasy, nie b\u0119dzie to tylko dla was, ale tak\u017ce, aby pom\u00f3c waszym braciom, poniewa\u017c wszystko ma si\u0119 zawali\u0107, w tym gospodarka, kt\u00f3ra przyniesie g\u0142\u00f3d w kr\u00f3tkim czasie. Moje dzieci, s\u0142uchajcie moich s\u0142\u00f3w i cencie je. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego; jestem z wami, kocham was i nigdy was nie opuszcz\u0119. Wasza Mama.","text_pt":"Meus queridos filhos, obrigado por ter escutado e respondido \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, meus filhos, pe\u00e7o uma convers\u00e3o urgente, voc\u00ea n\u00e3o percebe que mesmo os dias se aceleraram? Eu sei que voc\u00ea gostaria de terminar em breve, mas tudo o que est\u00e1 por escrito deve ser cumprido. Meus filhos, nesta batalha espiritual voc\u00ea deve estar pronto e na vanguarda da luta, voc\u00ea que s\u00e3o soldados de luz. Meus filhos, logo outro v\u00edrus letal aparecer\u00e3o, estar\u00e3o prontos para lutar pelas demandas de Jesus, haver\u00e1 cat\u00e1strofes naturais cont\u00ednuas. Meus filhos, a guerra est\u00e1 pronta, quando pe\u00e7o-lhe para estocar, n\u00e3o ser\u00e1 apenas para voc\u00ea, mas tamb\u00e9m para ajudar seus irm\u00e3os, porque tudo est\u00e1 prestes a entrar em colapso, incluindo a economia que trar\u00e1 fome em pouco tempo. Minhas crian\u00e7as. Ou\u00e7a minhas palavras e valorize-as. Agora eu deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o maternal em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, estou com voc\u00ea, eu te amo e nunca te abandonarei. Sua m\u00e3e.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u542c\u53d6\u5e76\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u8981\u6c42\u4f60\u8fdb\u884c\u7d27\u6025\u8f6c\u6362\uff0c\u4f60\u4e0d\u6ce8\u610f\u5230\u5373\u4f7f\u662f\u65e5\u5b50\u4e5f\u52a0\u5feb\u4e86\u5417\uff1f\u6211\u77e5\u9053\u4f60\u5e0c\u671b\u5c3d\u5feb\u7ed3\u675f\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u4f46\u5fc5\u987b\u6ee1\u8db3\u4e66\u9762\u5f62\u5f0f\u7684\u4e00\u5207\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5728\u8fd9\u79cd\u7cbe\u795e\u6218\u6597\u4e2d\uff0c\u4f60\u5fc5\u987b\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u5e76\u5728\u6218\u6597\u7684\u6700\u524d\u6cbf\uff0c\u4f60\u662f\u5149\u7684\u58eb\u5175\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5f88\u5feb\u5c31\u4f1a\u51fa\u73b0\u81f4\u547d\u75c5\u6bd2\uff0c\u51c6\u5907\u4e89\u53d6\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u9700\u6c42\uff0c\u4f1a\u6709\u6301\u7eed\u7684\u81ea\u7136\u707e\u96be\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6218\u4e89\u5df2\u7ecf\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u4e86\uff0c\u5f53\u6211\u8981\u6c42\u4f60\u5b58\u8d27\u65f6\uff0c\u5b83\u4e0d\u4f1a\u9002\u5408\u4f60\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u8fd8\u8981\u5e2e\u52a9\u4f60\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u5373\u5c06\u5d29\u6e83\uff0c\u5305\u62ec\u5c06\u5728\u77ed\u65f6\u95f4\u5185\u5e26\u6765\u9965\u8352\u7684\u7ecf\u6d4e\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u3002\u542c\u542c\u6211\u7684\u8a00\u8bed\u548c\u73cd\u60dc\u4ed6\u4eec\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u6211\u548c\u4f60\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\uff0c\u6211\u7231\u4f60\uff0c\u6211\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u4f1a\u629b\u5f03\u4f60\u3002\u4f60\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":11,"month_string":"January","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: In the name of the Holy Trinity, I bless you. As the captain of the armies of heaven I bless you. I call you to lift up your hearts, thought and reason so that with greater awareness you would remain certain that relationship with our King and Lord Jesus Christ is fruitful, depending on humanity\u2019s need to be close to the divine will and to fulfil it in life. Faith calls you to come out of personal selfishness, personal loneliness and foolishness so that you would go towards the encounter with our King and Lord Jesus Christ. A personal relationship with our King and Lord Jesus Christ is necessary in order for a person to put interior giving towards one\u2019s brother and sister into action in fraternity and respect. Humanity, you will not overcome by yourselves! You will be prey to the wolves who look to assuage their thirst for vengeance towards the children of 'the woman clothed with the sun, with the moon under her feet'. Examine yourselves! You are walking along the path with the cross on your shoulders. Each person is tested and everyone must commit themselves to obeying our King and Lord Jesus Christ. All must deny themselves, so that in its nothingness, the human being, convinced and converted, would be faithful to our King and Lord Jesus Christ. This generation is either heading towards the abyss or towards the encounter with the Divine Will. This is why it is so important that you know and recognize the beloved in order not to be deceived. The children of darkness have leapt out, have united and structured everything they need in order to go against the gift of life. The results have been satisfactory for them as a result of the surrender of human free will to the devil and to those who represent him on earth. At this time, they are attacking life behind masks of good intentions, and humanity continues like sheep to the slaughter. Humanity is living in the things of the world; they do not wish to work for our King and Lord Jesus Christ, 'and because of the increase of iniquity, the love of many will grow cold'. They do not believe, do not hope and do not love... You are being led to live in subjection, without air or sunlight, without the moon or the stars. Memories will be the sustenance for human beings who have become pale at the proximity of death. You are forgetting the warning at a time when it is near and when rumours of war cease to be rumours. Plagues continue to be present in great cities and small towns. Disease continues to make news, borders close and the fall of the world economy will quicken the pace of the antichrist, who dwells on earth beside his subjects. Pray for France: this nation is plunged into tragedy. Beloved of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, onward, without stopping, without faltering! Continue working on the spiritual path, love our Queen and Mother: keep in mind that you are protected. We protect you: we go before, behind, beside each one of you. Do not be afraid, do not be afraid, this is a time of great miracles. With my sword held high I bless you. St. Michael the archangel Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 Ci\u0119. Jako kapitan wojsk niebieskich b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Wzywam was do podniesienia serc, my\u015bli i rozumu, aby\u015bcie z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 \u015bwiadomo\u015bci\u0105 zachowali pewno\u015b\u0107, \u017ce relacja z naszym Kr\u00f3lem i Panem Jezusem Chrystusem jest owocna, zale\u017cna od ludzkiej potrzeby blisko\u015bci Woli Bo\u017cej i jej wype\u0142nienia w \u017cyciu. Wiara wzywa ci\u0119 do wyj\u015bcia z osobistego egoizmu, osobistej samotno\u015bci i g\u0142upoty, aby\u015b szed\u0142 w kierunku spotkania z naszym Kr\u00f3lem i Panem Jezusem Chrystusem. Osobista relacja z naszym Kr\u00f3lem i Panem Jezusem Chrystusem jest konieczna, aby cz\u0142owiek wprowadzi\u0142 w czyn w braterstwie i szacunku wewn\u0119trzne oddanie wobec brata i siostry. Ludzko\u015bci, sami nie zwyci\u0119\u017cycie! B\u0119dziecie ofiar\u0105 wilk\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re szukaj\u0105 zaspokojenia swojego pragnienia zemsty na dzieciach \"niewiasty obleczonej w s\u0142o\u0144ce i z ksi\u0119\u017cycem pod jej stopami\". Badajcie si\u0119! Idziecie drog\u0105 z krzy\u017cem na ramionach.  Ka\u017cda osoba jest testowana i ka\u017cdy musi zobowi\u0105za\u0107 si\u0119 do pos\u0142usze\u0144stwa naszemu Kr\u00f3lowi i Panu Jezusowi Chrystusowi. Wszyscy musz\u0105 zaprze\u0107 si\u0119 samych siebie, aby w swojej nico\u015bci cz\u0142owiek, przekonany i nawr\u00f3cony, by\u0142 wierny naszemu Kr\u00f3lowi i Panu Jezusowi Chrystusowi. To pokolenie zmierza albo ku przepa\u015bci, albo ku spotkaniu z Wol\u0105 Bo\u017c\u0105. Dlatego tak wa\u017cne jest poznanie i rozpoznanie umi\u0142owanego, aby nie da\u0107 si\u0119 zwie\u015b\u0107. Dzieci ciemno\u015bci wyskoczy\u0142y, zjednoczy\u0142y si\u0119 i zorganizowa\u0142y wszystko, co by\u0142o im potrzebne, aby przeciwstawi\u0107 si\u0119 darowi \u017cycia. Rezultaty by\u0142y dla nich zadowalaj\u0105ce w wyniku oddania wolnej woli cz\u0142owieka diab\u0142u i tym, kt\u00f3rzy go reprezentuj\u0105 na ziemi. W tym czasie atakuj\u0105 oni \u017cycie za maskami dobrych intencji, a ludzko\u015b\u0107 trwa jak owce na rze\u017a. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 \u017cyje w rzeczach tego \u015bwiata; nie chc\u0105 pracowa\u0107 dla naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, \"a z powodu wzrostu nieprawo\u015bci mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 wielu ozi\u0119bnie\".  Nie wierz\u0105, nie maj\u0105 nadziei i nie kochaj\u0105... Prowadzi si\u0119 was do \u017cycia w podda\u0144stwie, bez powietrza i \u015bwiat\u0142a s\u0142onecznego, bez ksi\u0119\u017cyca i gwiazd. Wspomnienia b\u0119d\u0105 straw\u0105 dla istot ludzkich, kt\u00f3re zblad\u0142y wobec blisko\u015bci \u015bmierci. Zapominacie o Ostrze\u017ceniu, teraz gdy jest ono bliskie i gdy pog\u0142oski o wojnie przestaj\u0105 by\u0107 pog\u0142oskami. Plagi nadal s\u0105 obecne w wielkich miastach i ma\u0142ych miasteczkach. Choroby nadal dostarczaj\u0105 wiadomo\u015bci, granice si\u0119 zamykaj\u0105, a upadek gospodarki \u015bwiatowej przyspieszy tempo dzia\u0142ania antychrysta, kt\u00f3ry mieszka na ziemi obok swoich poddanych. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Francj\u0119: ten nar\u00f3d jest pogr\u0105\u017cony w tragedii. Umi\u0142owani naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Naprz\u00f3d, bez zatrzymania, bez wahania! Kontynuujcie prac\u0119 na duchowej drodze, kochajcie nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119: pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie chronieni. My was chronimy, idziemy przed, za, obok ka\u017cdego z was.  Nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, to czas wielkich cud\u00f3w. Z moim mieczem trzymanym wysoko b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":15,"month_string":"January","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for having listened and responded to my call in your hearts.  My children, pray for the priests who are lost and for my Church where the devil is wandering. Dear children, pray for the rulers so that they do not carry out their project.  My children, humanity is now without return towards the abyss, pray and put everything into the wounds of my Son Jesus. My children, you will see many things that your eyes have never seen, sing praises to the Lord, your only salvation. It saddens me very much to see the filth on this earth, which my Father has blessed with so much love, yet now you no longer believe in God, everyone has created their own idols, enough my children with wickedness, confess and be ready every day. Soon my angels will come down to comfort my poor afflicted children, strengthen your faith and open your hearts to grace in order to be transformed, this is the time.  Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie zugeh\u00f6rt haben, und reagierte auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen. Meine Kinder, bete f\u00fcr die Priester, die verloren gehen und f\u00fcr meine Kirche, wo der Teufel wandert. Liebe Kinder, bete f\u00fcr die Herrscher, damit sie ihr Projekt nicht ausf\u00fchren. Meine Kinder, die Menschheit ist jetzt ohne R\u00fcckkehr in Richtung des Abgrunds, beten und legte alles in die Wunden meines Sohnes Jesus. Meine Kinder, du wirst viele Dinge sehen, die deine Augen noch nie gesehen haben, singe dem Herrn, dein einziger Errettung, lobt. Es s\u00e4ttigte mich sehr, den Schmutz auf dieser Erde zu sehen, den mein Vater mit so viel Liebe gesegnet hat, aber jetzt glaubst du nicht mehr an Gott, jeder hat ihre eigenen Idole geschaffen, genug, genug meine Kinder mit Bosheit, gestehen und sei bereit Tag. Bald werden meine Engel runterkommen, um meine armen betroffenen Kinder zu tr\u00f6sten, Ihren Glauben zu st\u00e4rken und Ihre Herzen zu \u00f6ffnen, um umgewandelt zu werden, ist dies die Zeit. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Estimados hijos, gracias por escuchar y respondi\u00f3 a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, oren por los sacerdotes que estaban perdidos y para mi iglesia donde la serpiente del diablo. Estimados hijos, oren por los gobernantes para que no traigan su proyecto hacia adelante. Mis hijos, la humanidad ahora no tiene regreso al abismo, ora y puso todo en las heridas de mi hijo Jes\u00fas. Ni\u00f1os, ver\u00e1s tantas cosas que tus ojos nunca han visto, cantaron alabanza al Se\u00f1or, \u00fanico su salvaci\u00f3n. Me entristec\u00e9 a ver el dricking en esta tierra, que mi padre ha bendecido con tanto amor, pero ahora no crees en Dios, todos han creado sus \u00eddolos, solo mis hijos con malicia, confesaron y est\u00e1n listos todos los d\u00edas. . Pronto dejar\u00e1s a mis \u00e1ngeles para consolar a mis hijos pobres afligidos, fortalecer\u00e1n su fe y abra los corazones a Grace para poder transformarlo, esto es el momento. Ahora te bendigo en nombre del padre del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir \u00e9cout\u00e9 et r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, prient pour les pr\u00eatres qui sont perdus et pour mon \u00e9glise o\u00f9 le diable errant. Chers enfants, priez pour les dirigeants afin qu'ils n'effectuent pas leur projet. Mes enfants, l'humanit\u00e9 est maintenant sans retour vers l'ab\u00eeme, prie et met tout dans les plaies de mon fils J\u00e9sus. Mes enfants, vous verrez beaucoup de choses que vos yeux n'ont jamais vu, chanter des louanges au Seigneur, votre seul salut. Il me sais beaucoup de voir la crasse de cette terre, que mon p\u00e8re a b\u00e9ni avec tant d'amour, mais maintenant, vous ne croyez plus en Dieu, tout le monde a cr\u00e9\u00e9 ses propres idoles, assez de mes enfants atteints de m\u00e9chancet\u00e9, avouent et soyez pr\u00eat chaque journ\u00e9e. Bient\u00f4t, mes anges descendront pour r\u00e9conforter mes pauvres enfants, renforcer votre foi et ouvrent vos c\u0153urs \u00e0 la gr\u00e2ce afin d'\u00eatre transform\u00e9, c'est le moment. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per avere ascoltato e risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore.  Figli miei, pregate per i sacerdoti che si sono perduti e per la mia Chiesa dove il demonio serpeggia. Figli cari, pregate per i governanti affinch\u00e9 non portino avanti il loro progetto.  Figli miei, l\u2019umanit\u00e0 \u00e8 ormai senza ritorno verso il baratro, pregate e mettete tutto nelle piaghe di mio Figlio Ges\u00f9. Figli, vedrete tante cose che i vostri occhi non hanno mai visto, cantate Lodi al Signore, unica vostra salvezza. Mi rattrista molto vedere il sudiciume su questa terra, che il Padre mio ha benedetto con tanto amore, eppure adesso non credete pi\u00f9 in Dio, ognuno ha creato i propri idoli, basta figli miei con la cattiveria, confessatevi e siate pronti ogni giorno. Presto scenderanno i miei angeli per confortare i miei poveri figli afflitti, rafforzate la vostra fede e aprite i cuori alla grazia per potervi trasformare, questo \u00e8 il tempo.  Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, Amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam za to, \u017ce us\u0142yszeli\u015bcie i odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za kap\u0142an\u00f3w, kt\u00f3rzy si\u0119 zagubili i za m\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, w kt\u00f3rym grasuje diabe\u0142. Drogie dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za w\u0142adc\u00f3w, aby nie realizowali swojego projektu. Dzieci moje, ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest ju\u017c bez powrotu w przepa\u015b\u0107, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 i w\u0142\u00f3\u017ccie wszystko w rany mojego Syna Jezusa. Dzieci moje, ujrzycie wiele rzeczy, kt\u00f3rych wasze oczy nigdy nie widzia\u0142y; \u015bpiewajcie chwa\u0142\u0119 Panu, waszemu jedynemu zbawieniu. Bardzo mnie smuci, gdy widz\u0119 brud na tej ziemi, kt\u00f3r\u0105 m\u00f3j Ojciec pob\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0142 z tak wielk\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, a jednak teraz ju\u017c nie wierzycie w Boga, ka\u017cdy stworzy\u0142 swoje w\u0142asne bo\u017cki, do\u015b\u0107 moje dzieci z niegodziwo\u015bci\u0105, wyznajcie i b\u0105d\u017acie gotowi ka\u017cdego dnia. Wkr\u00f3tce moi anio\u0142owie zst\u0105pi\u0105, aby pocieszy\u0107 moje biedne, strapione dzieci, wzmocni\u0107 wasz\u0105 wiar\u0119 i otworzy\u0107 wasze serca na \u0142ask\u0119, aby\u015bcie mogli zosta\u0107 przemienieni, to jest ten czas. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Queridos filhos, obrigado por ter escutado e respondido \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, oram pelos sacerdotes que est\u00e3o perdidos e pela minha igreja onde o diabo est\u00e1 vagando. Queridos filhos, orem pelos governantes para que eles n\u00e3o realizem seu projeto. Meus filhos, a humanidade \u00e9 agora sem retorno para o abismo, orar e colocar tudo nas feridas do meu filho Jesus. Meus filhos, voc\u00ea ver\u00e1 muitas coisas que seus olhos nunca viram, cantam louvores ao Senhor, sua \u00fanica salva\u00e7\u00e3o. Me tristeza muito para ver a sujeira nesta terra, que meu pai aben\u00e7oou com tanto amor, mas agora voc\u00ea n\u00e3o acredita mais em Deus, todo mundo criou seus pr\u00f3prios \u00eddolos, o suficiente para os meus filhos com maldade, confessar e estar pronto a cada dia. Logo meus anjos descer\u00e3o para confortar meus pobres filhos aflitos, fortalecer sua f\u00e9 e abrir seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es para serem transformados, a fim de serem transformados, esta \u00e9 a hora. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u542c\u53d6\u5e76\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u7948\u6c42\u90a3\u4e9b\u4e22\u5931\u7684\u7267\u5e08\u548c\u6211\u7684\u6559\u4f1a\uff0c\u5728\u90a3\u91cc\u9b54\u9b3c\u6b63\u5728\u5f98\u5f8a\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e3a\u7edf\u6cbb\u8005\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e0d\u8fdb\u884c\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u9879\u76ee\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4eba\u7c7b\u73b0\u5728\u6ca1\u6709\u56de\u5f52\u6df1\u6e0a\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u5e76\u5c06\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u653e\u5165\u6211\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u4f24\u53e3\u4e2d\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u4f60\u773c\u775b\u4ece\u672a\u89c1\u8fc7\u7684\u5f88\u591a\u4e1c\u897f\uff0c\u5531\u6b4c\u7ed9\u4e3b\uff0c\u4f60\u552f\u4e00\u7684\u6551\u6069\u3002\u5b83\u975e\u5e38\u4f24\u5fc3\u5730\u770b\u5230\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5730\u7403\u4e0a\u7684\u6c61\u79fd\uff0c\u6211\u7236\u4eb2\u5df2\u7ecf\u62e5\u6709\u8fd9\u4e48\u591a\u7684\u7231\uff0c\u4f46\u73b0\u5728\u4f60\u4e0d\u518d\u76f8\u4fe1\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u6bcf\u4e2a\u4eba\u90fd\u521b\u9020\u4e86\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u5076\u50cf\uff0c\u8db3\u591f\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u90aa\u6076\uff0c\u627f\u8ba4\u5e76\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u4e86\u65e5\u3002\u5f88\u5feb\u6211\u7684\u5929\u4f7f\u4f1a\u89c9\u5f97\u8212\u670d\u6211\u7684\u8d2b\u56f0\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u52a0\u5f3a\u4f60\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\uff0c\u655e\u5f00\u5fc3\u6249\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u6539\u53d8\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u65f6\u5019\u4e86\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":18,"month_string":"January","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people: I love you; I invite you to remain in my Will, working and acting as who you are: my true children. Cherish each moment so that you would live it in fraternity, with a heart of flesh and with total awareness. Obey, loving my father above all things, without forgetting my Mother and my beloved captain of the heavenly host. My angelic legions remain over humanity in order to come to whoever requests them to do so. You are experiencing purification and nature is in turmoil. The elements are stirred up by the reception of various solar flares that alter the earth\u2019s magnetism, causing communications to be impaired and activating tectonic faults. The human body is altered when receiving what your organism does not normally assimilate. Humanity is living through times of uncertainty. The moment is approaching when misused science will cause you to live in darkness, so I have called you to prepare. Pray, children, war is approaching and humanity will suffer. Pray, children, volcanoes continue becoming active and my children suffer. Pray, children, follow the true magisterium of my church. Do not fear the darkness, fear losing your soul. Remain vigilant, my children! The moon will appear as bloody, foreshadowing the pain of those who are mine. The so-called ring of fire in the Pacific is shaking the earth from the depths of the sea with greater force than in the past, influenced by the sun. You will see a ring in the sun - a ring of fire, which will be seen from many countries and from one in particular. I call you again, children, to prepare yourselves spiritually and with what my children are able to store. Look at the animals that anticipate the weather and store food for when they cannot go out to find what they need to survive. My people need to be cautious when my House warns them. Those who cannot store food will be helped by me. Do not fear, do not fear, do not be anxious. Now is the time! Pay attention to the signs and signals.... Do not be spiritually blind! Quicken your step, as the elite are rising in haste, taking greater power. Bear in mind that 'I am who I am'. I guard you; I love you and I forewarn you so that you would not be taken by surprise. Come to me: receive me in the Eucharist, but before coming to me, be reconciled with your neighbour. Do not judge, as that is for me to do. Come to me with a pure heart, in inner silence, so that you would not be like the pharisees. Maintain inner peace: go into the inner chamber and meet with me - I am waiting for you. Be fraternal: do not use my churches to destroy your brothers and sisters. Forgive and love one another as my people. I bless you with my heart. I bless you with my love. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j ukochany ludu, kocham was; zach\u0119cam was do pozostania w mojej Woli, pracuj\u0105c i dzia\u0142aj\u0105c jako ci, kt\u00f3rymi jeste\u015bcie: moje prawdziwe dzieci. Piel\u0119gnujcie ka\u017cd\u0105 chwil\u0119, aby\u015bcie prze\u017cywali j\u0105 w braterstwie, z sercem z cia\u0142a i z ca\u0142kowit\u0105 \u015bwiadomo\u015bci\u0105. B\u0105d\u017acie pos\u0142uszni, kochaj\u0105c mojego Ojca ponad wszystko, nie zapominaj\u0105c o mojej Matce i moim ukochanym kapitanie zast\u0119p\u00f3w niebieskich. Moje anielskie legiony pozostaj\u0105 nad ludzko\u015bci\u0105, aby przyj\u015b\u0107 do tego, kto ich o to poprosi. Prze\u017cywacie oczyszczenie i przyroda jest w zamieszaniu. Elementy s\u0105 wzburzone przez odbi\u00f3r r\u00f3\u017cnych rozb\u0142ysk\u00f3w s\u0142onecznych, kt\u00f3re zmieniaj\u0105 magnetyzm ziemi, powoduj\u0105c zak\u0142\u00f3cenia w komunikacji i aktywuj\u0105c uskoki tektoniczne. Cia\u0142o ludzkie ulega zmianom, gdy otrzymuje to, czego organizm normalnie nie przyswaja. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 \u017cyje w czasach niepewno\u015bci. Zbli\u017ca si\u0119 chwila, gdy niew\u0142a\u015bciwie wykorzystana nauka spowoduje, \u017ce b\u0119dziecie \u017cy\u0107 w ciemno\u015bci, dlatego wezwa\u0142em was do przygotowania si\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, zbli\u017ca si\u0119 wojna i ludzko\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dzie cierpie\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, wulkany nadal staj\u0105 si\u0119 aktywne i moje dzieci cierpi\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, post\u0119pujcie zgodnie z prawdziwym magisterium mojego Ko\u015bcio\u0142a. Nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119 ciemno\u015bci, b\u00f3jcie si\u0119 utraty duszy. Pozosta\u0144cie czujni, moje dzieci! Ksi\u0119\u017cyc uka\u017ce si\u0119 jako krwawy, zapowiadaj\u0105c b\u00f3l tych, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0105 Moimi. Tak zwany pier\u015bcie\u0144 ognia na Pacyfiku wstrz\u0105sa ziemi\u0105 z g\u0142\u0119bi morza z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 si\u0142\u0105 ni\u017c w przesz\u0142o\u015bci, pod wp\u0142ywem s\u0142o\u0144ca. Zobaczycie pier\u015bcie\u0144 na s\u0142o\u0144cu - pier\u015bcie\u0144 ognia, kt\u00f3ry b\u0119dzie widoczny z wielu kraj\u00f3w i z jednego w szczeg\u00f3lno\u015bci. Wzywam was ponownie, dzieci, aby\u015bcie przygotowali si\u0119 duchowo i za pomoc\u0105 tego, co moje dzieci s\u0105 w stanie zmagazynowa\u0107. Sp\u00f3jrzcie na zwierz\u0119ta, kt\u00f3re przewiduj\u0105 pogod\u0119 i przechowuj\u0105 \u017cywno\u015b\u0107 na czas, kiedy nie mog\u0105 wyj\u015b\u0107 na zewn\u0105trz, aby znale\u017a\u0107 to, co jest im potrzebne do prze\u017cycia. M\u00f3j lud musi by\u0107 ostro\u017cny, gdy M\u00f3j Dom go ostrzega. Ci, kt\u00f3rzy nie mog\u0105 przechowywa\u0107 \u017cywno\u015bci, otrzymaj\u0105 ode Mnie pomoc. Nie obawiajcie si\u0119, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, nie b\u0105d\u017acie niespokojni. Teraz jest czas! Zwracajcie uwag\u0119 na znaki i sygna\u0142y.... Nie b\u0105d\u017acie duchowo \u015blepi! Przyspieszcie kroku, gdy\u017c elity powstaj\u0105 w po\u015bpiechu, bior\u0105c wi\u0119ksz\u0105 w\u0142adz\u0119. Pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce \"Jestem, kt\u00f3ry jestem\". Strzeg\u0119 ci\u0119, kocham ci\u0119 i uprzedzam ci\u0119, aby\u015b nie by\u0142 zaskoczony. Przyjd\u017a do mnie: przyjmij mnie w Eucharystii, ale zanim przyjdziesz do mnie, pojednaj si\u0119 z bli\u017anim. Nie s\u0105d\u017acie, bo to nale\u017cy do Mnie. Przychod\u017acie do mnie z czystym sercem, w wewn\u0119trznej ciszy, aby\u015bcie nie byli jak faryzeusze. Zachowaj wewn\u0119trzny pok\u00f3j: wejd\u017a do wewn\u0119trznej komnaty i spotkaj si\u0119 ze mn\u0105 - czekam na ciebie. B\u0105d\u017acie braterscy: nie wykorzystujcie moich ko\u015bcio\u0142\u00f3w do niszczenia waszych braci i si\u00f3str. Przebaczajcie i kochajcie si\u0119 wzajemnie jako m\u00f3j lud. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moim sercem. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":18,"month_string":"January","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. Beloved daughter, you must tell everyone that they need not fear anything if they are in the Lord. I ask that there be union in prayer, do not be tempted by fear, but unite, you know well how strong community prayer is! Be vigilant and do not be like the foolish virgins, but fill your lamps with oil. My children, Jesus takes many souls with Him, remember: one will be taken and one will be left. When you want to reach God and you are ready, the Lord will be happy to welcome these souls into paradise, many instead will have to purify themselves and others will remain on earth to continue their mission, so as you can understand, do not be tied to the things of the world, but pray for your souls.  Go to Mass and participate in the sacrifice, feed on the body of my Son, while there is still time. Persecution will be great when they decide to unify religions. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen reagiert haben. Geliebte Tochter, Sie m\u00fcssen jedem sagen, dass sie nichts f\u00fcrchten, wenn sie im Herrn sind. Ich bitte, dass es Gewerkschaft im Gebet geben, nicht von der Angst versucht werden, aber vereinigen Sie sich, Sie wissen gut, wie starkes Gemeinschaftsgebet ist! Seien Sie wachsam und sei nicht wie die dummen Jungfrauen, sondern f\u00fcllen Sie Ihre Lampen mit \u00d6l. Meine Kinder, Jesus nimmt viele Seelen mit, erinnern sich an: Man wird genommen und einer bleibt \u00fcbrig. Wenn Sie Gott erreichen m\u00f6chten und Sie bereit sind, freut sich der Herr, diese Seelen in das Paradies begr\u00fc\u00dfen zu lassen. Viele werden stattdessen selbst reinigen, und andere werden auf der Erde bleiben, um ihre Mission fortzusetzen, so dass Sie nicht verstehen k\u00f6nnen, also nicht an die Dinge der Welt gebunden, bete aber f\u00fcr deine Seelen. Gehen Sie zur Masse und nehmen Sie an dem Opfer teil, f\u00fcttere den K\u00f6rper meines Sohnes, w\u00e4hrend es noch Zeit ist. Die Verfolgung wird gro\u00dfartig sein, wenn sie sich daf\u00fcr entscheiden, Religionen zu vereinheitlichen. Jetzt verlasse ich Sie mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Estimados hijos, gracias por responder a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Querida hija, debes decirles a todos que no deber\u00edan temer nada si est\u00e1n en el Se\u00f1or. Pido que haya un sindicato en oraci\u00f3n, no se dejen sentir tentados por el miedo, pero \u00fanete, \u00bfsabes lo fuerte que la oraci\u00f3n de la comunidad es fuerte? Estar vigilante y no hacer las v\u00edrgenes de Stolte, pero llenas tus l\u00e1mparas con aceite. Mis hijos, Jes\u00fas toma muchas almas, recuerda: se tomar\u00e1 uno y se dejar\u00e1 uno. Cuando quieras llegar a Dios y est\u00e1s listo, el Se\u00f1or estar\u00e1 encantado de darle la bienvenida a estas almas en el para\u00edso, muchos tendr\u00e1n que purificar y otros permanecer\u00e1n en la tierra para continuar su misi\u00f3n, por lo que puede entenderlo, no estar relacionado con Las cosas del mundo, pero rezan por tus almas. Ve a la misa y participa en el sacrificio, lucha contra el cuerpo de mi hijo, hasta que tengas tiempo. La persecuci\u00f3n ser\u00e1 excelente, cuando decidan unificar las religiones. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Fille bien-aim\u00e9e, vous devez dire \u00e0 tout le monde qu'ils n'ont pas besoin de craindre quoi que ce soit s'ils sont dans le Seigneur. Je demande qu'il y ait un syndicat dans la pri\u00e8re, ne soyez pas tent\u00e9 par la peur, mais unir, vous savez bien \u00e0 quel point la pri\u00e8re communautaire est forte! Soyez vigilant et ne soyez pas comme les vierges insens\u00e9es, mais remplissez vos lampes avec de l'huile. Mes enfants, J\u00e9sus prend de nombreuses \u00e2mes avec lui, rappelez-vous: on sera pris et on partira. Lorsque vous voulez atteindre Dieu et que vous \u00eates pr\u00eat, le Seigneur sera heureux d'accueillir ces \u00e2mes dans le paradis, de nombreuses personnes devront plut\u00f4t se purifier et d'autres resteront sur Terre pour continuer leur mission, de sorte que vous pouvez comprendre, ne pas \u00eatre attach\u00e9 aux choses du monde, mais priez pour vos \u00e2mes. Allez en masse et participer au sacrifice, nourrir le corps de mon fils, alors qu'il y ait encore du temps. La pers\u00e9cution sera excellente quand ils d\u00e9cident d'unifier les religions. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore.  Figlia cara, devi dire a tutti che non devono temere nulla se sono nel Signore. Chiedo che ci sia l\u2019unione nella preghiera, non fatevi tentare dalla paura, ma unitevi, sapete bene quanto \u00e8 forte la preghiera comunitaria! Siate vigili e non fate come le vergini stolte, ma riempite d\u2019olio le vostre lampade.  Figli miei, Ges\u00f9 prende con s\u00e9 molte anime, ricordate: uno sar\u00e0 preso e uno verr\u00e0 lasciato. Quando si vuole raggiungere Dio e si \u00e8 pronti, il Signore sar\u00e0 felice di accogliere queste anime in paradiso, molti invece dovranno purificarsi e altri resteranno sulla terra per continuare la propria missione, quindi come potrete comprendere, non siate legati alle cose del mondo, ma pregate per le vostre anime.  Andate alla messa e partecipate al sacrificio, cibatevi del corpo di mio Figlio, finch\u00e9 siete in tempo. La persecuzione sar\u00e0 grande, quando decideranno di unificare le religioni. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, Amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Umi\u0142owana c\u00f3rko, musisz powiedzie\u0107 wszystkim, \u017ce nie maj\u0105 si\u0119 czego obawia\u0107, je\u015bli s\u0105 w Panu. Prosz\u0119 o zjednoczenie w modlitwie, nie dajcie si\u0119 skusi\u0107 l\u0119kowi, ale zjednoczcie si\u0119, dobrze wiecie, jak silna jest modlitwa wsp\u00f3lnotowa! B\u0105d\u017acie czujni i nie b\u0105d\u017acie jak g\u0142upie panny, lecz nape\u0142nijcie wasze lampy oliw\u0105. Moje dzieci, Jezus zabiera ze sob\u0105 wiele dusz, pami\u0119tajcie: jedna b\u0119dzie wzi\u0119ta, a druga zostawiona. Gdy b\u0119dziecie chcieli dotrze\u0107 do Boga i b\u0119dziecie gotowi, Pan z rado\u015bci\u0105 przyjmie te dusze do raju, lecz wiele z nich b\u0119dzie musia\u0142o si\u0119 oczy\u015bci\u0107, a inne pozostan\u0105 na ziemi, by kontynuowa\u0107 swoj\u0105 misj\u0119, wi\u0119c jak rozumiecie, nie przywi\u0105zujcie si\u0119 do rzeczy tego \u015bwiata, lecz m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za swoje dusze. Chod\u017acie na Msz\u0119 \u015bw. i uczestniczcie w ofierze, karmcie si\u0119 Cia\u0142em mojego Syna, p\u00f3ki jeszcze jest czas. Prze\u015bladowania b\u0119d\u0105 wielkie, gdy zdecyduj\u0105 si\u0119 na ujednolicenie religii. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Queridos filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Filha amada, voc\u00ea deve dizer a todos que eles n\u00e3o precisam temer nada se estiverem no Senhor. Pe\u00e7o que haja uni\u00e3o em ora\u00e7\u00e3o, n\u00e3o seja tentado pelo medo, mas se unem, voc\u00ea sabe bem qu\u00e3o forte \u00e9 a ora\u00e7\u00e3o da comunidade! Seja vigilante e n\u00e3o seja como as virgens tolas, mas encha suas l\u00e2mpadas com \u00f3leo. Meus filhos, Jesus pega muitas almas com ele, lembre-se: um ser\u00e1 levado e um ser\u00e1 deixado. Quando voc\u00ea quer chegar a Deus e voc\u00ea est\u00e1 pronto, o Senhor ficar\u00e1 feliz em receber essas almas no para\u00edso, muitos, em vez disso, ter\u00e3o que se purificar e os outros permanecer\u00e3o na terra para continuar sua miss\u00e3o, assim como voc\u00ea pode entender, n\u00e3o amarrado \u00e0s coisas do mundo, mas ore por suas almas. V\u00e1 para a missa e participe do sacrif\u00edcio, alimente no corpo do meu filho, enquanto ainda h\u00e1 tempo. A persegui\u00e7\u00e3o ser\u00e1 \u00f3tima quando decidirem unificar as religi\u00f5es. Agora eu deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o maternal em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u4f60\u5fc5\u987b\u544a\u8bc9\u5927\u5bb6\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u4ed6\u4eec\u5728\u4e3b\u4e2d\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e0d\u9700\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\u4efb\u4f55\u4e1c\u897f\u3002\u6211\u8981\u6c42\u5728\u7977\u544a\u4e2d\u6709\u8054\u76df\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u88ab\u6050\u60e7\u8bf1\u60d1\uff0c\u4f46\u56e2\u7ed3\u4e00\u81f4\uff0c\u4f60\u77e5\u9053\u793e\u533a\u7977\u544a\u7684\u5f3a\u70c8\u7977\u544a\u3002\u4fdd\u6301\u8b66\u60d5\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u50cf\u611a\u8822\u7684\u5904\u5973\uff0c\u4f46\u7528\u6cb9\u586b\u5145\u706f\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8036\u7a23\u5e26\u7740\u8bb8\u591a\u7075\u9b42\uff0c\u8bb0\u4f4f\uff1a\u4e00\u4e2a\u4eba\u4f1a\u88ab\u62ff\u8d70\uff0c\u4e00\u4e2a\u4eba\u5c06\u88ab\u7559\u4e0b\u3002\u5f53\u4f60\u60f3\u8981\u5230\u8fbe\u4e0a\u5e1d\u800c\u4f60\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u4e86\uff0c\u4e3b\u5c06\u4e50\u4e8e\u6b22\u8fce\u8fd9\u4e9b\u7075\u9b42\u8fdb\u5165\u5929\u5802\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u5fc5\u987b\u51c0\u5316\u81ea\u5df1\uff0c\u5176\u4ed6\u4eba\u5c06\u7559\u5728\u5730\u7403\u4e0a\u7ee7\u7eed\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u4f7f\u547d\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u5c3d\u53ef\u80fd\u7406\u89e3\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u4e0e\u4e16\u754c\u7684\u4e1c\u897f\u7ed1\u5b9a\uff0c\u4f46\u4e3a\u4f60\u7684\u7075\u9b42\u7948\u7977\u3002\u52aa\u529b\u53c2\u52a0\u727a\u7272\uff0c\u5728\u6211\u513f\u5b50\u7684\u8eab\u4f53\u4e0a\u5582\u517b\uff0c\u867d\u7136\u8fd8\u6709\u65f6\u95f4\u3002\u5f53\u4ed6\u4eec\u51b3\u5b9a\u7edf\u4e00\u5b97\u6559\u65f6\uff0c\u8feb\u5bb3\u4f1a\u5f88\u68d2\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":22,"month_string":"January","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear and loving children, thank you for responding to my call in your heart and thank you for kneeling down. My children, look around you, nothing is the same as before, but you seek love, be love for your brothers, be love for those who suffer, my true children of light express love and it is almost tangible. My children, I tell you once again, do not be afraid, do not be in anguish because these feelings do not come from God, be light for your brothers and advise them to take refuge in my Immaculate Heart and in that of my Son Jesus, where they will find joy and consolation. Pray for America because she will be trampled underfoot. I am beside you, do not be afraid of everything you see because everything will be renewed, do not feel feelings of anger, but of pure joy. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe und liebevolle Kinder, danke, dass Sie sich auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen reagieren und danke, dass Sie sich niedergeschlagen haben. Meine Kinder, schau dich um dich, nichts ist das gleiche wie zuvor, aber du suchst Liebe, sei Liebe zu deinen Br\u00fcdern, sei Liebe f\u00fcr diejenigen, die leiden, meine wahren Kinder von Licht ausdr\u00fccken, und es ist fast greifbar. Meine Kinder, ich sage dir noch einmal, habe keine Angst, sei nicht inhaft, weil diese Gef\u00fchle nicht von Gott kommen, f\u00fcr deine Br\u00fcder leichte und raten, in meinem makellosen Herzen zu schaffen und in meinem Sohn Jesus , wo sie Freude und Trost finden werden. Beten Sie f\u00fcr Amerika, weil sie unter den F\u00fc\u00dfen trampelt wird. Ich bin neben dir, habe keine Angst vor allem, was du siehst, weil alles erneuert wird, f\u00fchle keine Gef\u00fchle der Wut, sondern von reiner Freude. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Estimados y cari\u00f1osos ni\u00f1os, gracias por responder a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n y gracias por doblarse sus rodillas. Mis hijos, miran a tu alrededor, nada es como antes, pero est\u00e1s buscando amor, s\u00e9 amor por tus hermanos, s\u00e9 amor por los que sufren, mis verdaderos hijos de luz expresan amor y es casi tangible. Mis hijos, le digo de nuevo, no tengas miedo, no te preocupes porque estos sentimientos no vienen a Dios, sean ligeros para tus hermanos y se recomiendan a refugiarse en mi coraz\u00f3n inmaculado y en mi hijo Jes\u00fas, Donde encontrar\u00e1n alegr\u00eda y consolaci\u00f3n. Ora por Am\u00e9rica porque ser\u00e1 pisoteado. Estoy a tu lado, no tengas miedo de todo lo que ves por qu\u00e9 todo se renovar\u00e1, no sentir\u00e1 sentimientos de ira, sino de pura alegr\u00eda. Ahora te bendigo en nombre del padre del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Cher et aimer les enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur et merci de vous avoir agenouill\u00e9. Mes enfants, regardez autour de vous, rien n'est pareil qu'avant, mais vous cherchez l'amour, soyez amour pour vos fr\u00e8res, que ce soit l'amour pour ceux qui souffrent, mes vrais enfants d'amour l\u00e9ger et qui sont presque tangibles. Mes enfants, je vous raconte une fois encore, n'ayez pas peur, ne soyez pas dans l'angoisse, car ces sentiments ne viennent pas de Dieu, soyez l\u00e9gers pour vos fr\u00e8res et leur conseillent de se r\u00e9fugier dans mon c\u0153ur immacul\u00e9 et dans celui de mon fils J\u00e9sus , o\u00f9 ils trouveront la joie et la consolation. Priez pour l'Am\u00e9rique parce qu'elle sera pi\u00e9tin\u00e9e sous le pied. Je suis \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 de vous, n'ayez pas peur de tout ce que vous voyez parce que tout sera renouvel\u00e9, ne ressentez pas de sentiments de col\u00e8re, mais de pure joie. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari e amorevoli figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore e grazie per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia. Figli miei, guardate intorno a voi, niente \u00e8 pi\u00f9 come prima, ma voi cercate l\u2019amore, siate amore per i vostri fratelli, siate amore per coloro che soffrono, i miei veri figli di luce esprimono amore ed \u00e8 quasi tangibile. Figli miei, vi dico ancora una volta, non abbiate paura, non siate nell\u2019angoscia perch\u00e9 questi sentimenti non vengono da Dio, siate luce per i vostri fratelli e consigliate loro di rifugiarsi nel mio cuore immacolato e in quello di mio Figlio Ges\u00f9, dove troveranno gioia e consolazione. Pregate per l\u2019America perch\u00e9 verr\u00e0 calpestata. Io vi sono accanto, non abbiate paura di tutto ci\u00f2 che vedrete perch\u00e9 tutto sar\u00e0 rinnovato, non provate sentimenti di rabbia, ma di gioia pura. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, Amen.","text_pl":"Drogie i kochaj\u0105ce dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach i dzi\u0119kuj\u0119, \u017ce ukl\u0119kneli\u015bcie. Dzieci moje, rozejrzyjcie si\u0119 wok\u00f3\u0142 siebie, nic nie jest takie samo jak dawniej, lecz wy szukacie mi\u0142o\u015bci, b\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 dla waszych braci, b\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 dla tych, kt\u00f3rzy cierpi\u0105, moje prawdziwe dzieci \u015bwiat\u0142a wyra\u017caj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 i jest ona prawie namacalna. Dzieci moje, jeszcze raz wam m\u00f3wi\u0119: nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, nie dr\u0119czcie si\u0119, bo te uczucia nie pochodz\u0105 od Boga, b\u0105d\u017acie \u015bwiat\u0142em dla waszych braci i porad\u017acie im, by schronili si\u0119 w moim Niepokalanym Sercu i w Sercu mojego Syna Jezusa, gdzie znajd\u0105 rado\u015b\u0107 i pocieszenie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ameryk\u0119, poniewa\u017c zostanie ona zdeptana. Jestem blisko was, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119 tego wszystkiego, co zobaczycie, bo wszystko b\u0119dzie odnowione, nie odczuwajcie uczu\u0107 gniewu, ale czyst\u0105 rado\u015b\u0107. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Crian\u00e7as queridas e amantes, obrigado por responder ao meu chamado em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o e obrigado por se ajoelhar. Meus filhos, olha em torno de voc\u00ea, nada \u00e9 o mesmo que antes, mas voc\u00ea procura amor, seja amor por seus irm\u00e3os, seja amor por aqueles que sofrem, meus verdadeiros filhos de Luz Expressam e \u00e9 quase tang\u00edvel. Meus filhos, eu te digo mais uma vez, n\u00e3o tenha medo, n\u00e3o fique em ang\u00fastia porque esses sentimentos n\u00e3o v\u00eam de Deus, sejam leves para seus irm\u00e3os e aconselh\u00e1-los a se refugiar no meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o imaculado e na do meu filho Jesus , onde encontrar\u00e3o alegria e consolo. Ore pela Am\u00e9rica porque ela ser\u00e1 pisoteada sob os p\u00e9s. Eu estou ao seu lado, n\u00e3o tenha medo de tudo o que voc\u00ea v\u00ea porque tudo ser\u00e1 renovado, n\u00e3o sente sentimentos de raiva, mas de pura alegria. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\uff0c\u6148\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u590d\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u8dea\u5012\u4e0b\u6765\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u73af\u987e\u56db\u5468\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u4ec0\u4e48\u7c7b\u4f3c\u7684\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u4f60\u5bfb\u6c42\u7231\u60c5\uff0c\u5bf9\u4f60\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\u4eec\u6765\u8bf4\uff0c\u7231\u662f\u90a3\u4e9b\u906d\u53d7\u7684\u4eba\uff0c\u6211\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u6d45\u8272\u8868\u8fbe\u7684\u7231\u60c5\uff0c\u5b83\u51e0\u4e4e\u6709\u5f62\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u518d\u6b21\u544a\u8bc9\u4f60\u4e00\u6b21\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u75db\u82e6\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u8fd9\u4e9b\u611f\u89c9\u4e0d\u662f\u6765\u81ea\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u4e3a\u4f60\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\u4eec\u4eae\u4e86\uff0c\u5e76\u5efa\u8bae\u4ed6\u4eec\u5728\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u5b8c\u7f8e\u4e4b\u5fc3\u548c\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u91cc\u907f\u96be\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u53d1\u73b0\u5feb\u4e50\u548c\u5b89\u6170\u3002\u4e3a\u7f8e\u56fd\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5979\u4f1a\u88ab\u8e29\u8e0f\u3002\u6211\u5728\u4f60\u8eab\u8fb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\u4f60\u6240\u770b\u5230\u7684\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u4f1a\u88ab\u7eed\u7b7e\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u611f\u53d7\u5230\u6124\u6012\u7684\u611f\u89c9\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u7eaf\u7cb9\u7684\u5feb\u4e50\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":24,"month_string":"January","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: In the unity of the most Holy Trinity, as prince of the heavenly militias, I bless you. Receive love and good. I am sent to share with you: My heavenly legions are at my signal to assist you in the face of the persecution and harassment to which you will be subjected. As humanity you will witness the misuse of the free will of those who, when they wish, will not be able to humanly turn back. The decision of evil is to divide the people of God in all areas, this is how the serpent moves crawling so as not to be seen. Because of this I call you, I summon you to live in Divine Love, in fraternity, since before the weapon of love, the devil flees. At the same time, invoke our Queen and Mother of the End Times to free you from the insidiousness of the evil one. The earth is a receiver, not only of celestial bodies coming from space, but also of what man himself has taken and placed in space, without foreseeing that the effects of the solar storms that the sun generates at this time, affect some of those satellites that will be one more danger for humanity. Children of the Holy Trinity, be converted and decide for the good! Ratify for yourselves the belonging to our King and Lord Jesus Christ and to our Queen and Mother of the End Times by praying in silence and meditating the prayer of the creed. Beloved children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: The abyss toward which humanity is advancing is saturated with the lust for power, the desire to obtain world supremacy in order to hand it over to the one who already! Is on earth demanding for himself absolute domination over all that exists. The disaster coming from armed conflicts will be the cause for humanity to be scourged to the point of exhaustion. Do not be surprised at the economic collapse of great powers. You, as creatures of faith, maintain the tranquillity of those who know that they are protected by their Lord and their God. As people of God, you will see great miracles in your favour, therefore I call you not to fear. Children of God, do not fear, but keep the assurance that you will never be abandoned. Pray, people of God, pray. Nations will march against nations and nature will make those who think they are invincible to bend. Then allies will no longer be so, abandoning the one who summoned them to war, though later they will unite again, not before suffering is brought upon mankind in one form or another. Fear not, at all times we are with you if you are faithful to the Holy Trinity and to our Queen and Mother. Signs and signals abound to alert you, to move the hearts and minds of those who are sceptical at this time. The sun will be darkened by the force of a volcano. The earth continues to tremble as a harbinger of things to come. Stand firm without forgetting that our King and Lord Jesus Christ will send you his angel of peace, who will provide you with strength to continue on the safe path. Beloved children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, human creature forgets that our King is the knower of all human actions and deeds. Be creatures of goodness so that you may remain filled with the Divine Spirit. Be strong, go ahead! You are not alone; our King and Lord Jesus Christ pours his love upon his children. 'Blessed is he who comes in the name of the lord'. On spiritual alert, people of God! Do not fear, be persevering. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: W jedno\u015bci Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 wojsk niebieskich, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Przyjmijcie mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 i dobro. Jestem pos\u0142any, aby si\u0119 z wami podzieli\u0107: Moje niebia\u0144skie legiony s\u0105 na m\u00f3j sygna\u0142, aby was wspomaga\u0107 w obliczu prze\u015bladowa\u0144 i szykan, kt\u00f3rym b\u0119dziecie poddani. Jako ludzko\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dziecie \u015bwiadkami nadu\u017cywania wolnej woli przez tych, kt\u00f3rzy gdy zechc\u0105, nie b\u0119d\u0105 mogli po ludzku zawr\u00f3ci\u0107. Decyzj\u0105 z\u0142a jest podzielenie ludu Bo\u017cego we wszystkich dziedzinach, tak porusza si\u0119 w\u0105\u017c, pe\u0142zaj\u0105c, aby nie by\u0107 widocznym. Z tego powodu wzywam was, wzywam was do \u017cycia w Bo\u017cej Mi\u0142o\u015bci, w braterstwie, gdy\u017c przed broni\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci diabe\u0142 ucieka. Jednocze\u015bnie przywo\u0142ujcie nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119 Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych, aby uwolni\u0142a was od podst\u0119pno\u015bci z\u0142ego. Ziemia jest odbiornikiem, nie tylko cia\u0142 niebieskich pochodz\u0105cych z kosmosu, ale tak\u017ce tego, co sam cz\u0142owiek zabra\u0142 i umie\u015bci\u0142 w kosmosie, nie przewiduj\u0105c, \u017ce skutki burz s\u0142onecznych, kt\u00f3re s\u0142o\u0144ce generuje w tym czasie, wp\u0142ywaj\u0105 na niekt\u00f3re z tych satelit\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re b\u0119d\u0105 jeszcze jednym zagro\u017ceniem dla ludzko\u015bci. Dzieci Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej, nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119 i zdecydujcie na dobro! Ratyfikujcie dla siebie przynale\u017cno\u015b\u0107 do naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa oraz do naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych, modl\u0105c si\u0119 w ciszy i medytuj\u0105c modlitw\u0119 Credo. Umi\u0142owane dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, otch\u0142a\u0144, ku kt\u00f3rej zmierza ludzko\u015b\u0107, jest przesycona \u017c\u0105dz\u0105 w\u0142adzy, pragnieniem zdobycia supremacji nad \u015bwiatem, aby przekaza\u0107 j\u0105 Temu, kt\u00f3ry ju\u017c! jest na ziemi, \u017c\u0105daj\u0105c dla siebie absolutnego panowania nad wszystkim, co istnieje. Katastrofa p\u0142yn\u0105ca z konflikt\u00f3w zbrojnych b\u0119dzie przyczyn\u0105 sponiewierania ludzko\u015bci a\u017c do wyczerpania. Nie dziwcie si\u0119 upadkowi gospodarczemu wielkich mocarstw. Wy, jako stworzenia wiary, zachowajcie spok\u00f3j tych, kt\u00f3rzy wiedz\u0105, \u017ce s\u0105 chronieni przez swojego Pana i swojego Boga. Jako lud Bo\u017cy zobaczycie wielkie cuda na wasz\u0105 korzy\u015b\u0107, dlatego wzywam was, aby\u015bcie si\u0119 nie l\u0119kali. Dzieci Bo\u017ce, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, ale zachowajcie pewno\u015b\u0107, \u017ce nigdy nie zostaniecie opuszczeni. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. Narody b\u0119d\u0105 maszerowa\u0107 przeciwko narodom, a natura sprawi, \u017ce ci, kt\u00f3rzy my\u015bl\u0105, \u017ce s\u0105 niezwyci\u0119\u017ceni, ugn\u0105 si\u0119. Wtedy nie b\u0119dzie ju\u017c sojusznik\u00f3w, kt\u00f3rzy porzuc\u0105 tego, kt\u00f3ry wezwa\u0142 ich na wojn\u0119, cho\u0107 p\u00f3\u017aniej zn\u00f3w si\u0119 zjednocz\u0105, ale nie wcze\u015bniej ni\u017c wtedy, gdy na ludzko\u015b\u0107 spadnie cierpienie w takiej czy innej formie. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, w ka\u017cdej chwili jeste\u015bmy z wami, je\u015bli jeste\u015bcie wierni Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej i naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matce. Znaki i sygna\u0142y obfituj\u0105, aby was ostrzec, aby poruszy\u0107 serca i umys\u0142y tych, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0105 sceptyczni w tym czasie. S\u0142o\u0144ce zostanie zaciemnione przez si\u0142\u0119 wulkanu. Ziemia nadal dr\u017cy jako zwiastun rzeczy, kt\u00f3re maj\u0105 nadej\u015b\u0107. St\u00f3jcie mocno, nie zapominaj\u0105c, \u017ce nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus po\u015ble wam swojego Anio\u0142a Pokoju, kt\u00f3ry dostarczy wam si\u0142y, by\u015bcie mogli dalej kroczy\u0107 bezpieczn\u0105 drog\u0105. Umi\u0142owane dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, ludzkie stworzenie zapomina, \u017ce nasz Kr\u00f3l jest znawc\u0105 wszystkich ludzkich dzia\u0142a\u0144 i czyn\u00f3w. B\u0105d\u017acie stworzeniami dobra, aby\u015bcie mogli pozosta\u0107 nape\u0142nieni Duchem Bo\u017cym. B\u0105d\u017acie silni, id\u017acie naprz\u00f3d! Nie jeste\u015bcie sami; nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus wylewa swoj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 na swoje dzieci. \"B\u0142ogos\u0142awiony, kt\u00f3ry przychodzi w imi\u0119 Pana\". W duchowej gotowo\u015bci, ludu Bo\u017cy! Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, b\u0105d\u017acie wytrwali. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":25,"month_string":"January","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for having responded to my call in your hearts. My children, these are hard times and there will come times when the confusion will be even greater. My children, pray so much so that the war that will come may be mitigated, the power of prayer is great. Pray for the Church, for the hunger for power has exceeded all limits and no longer has anything to do with God. Pray for the holy priests, that light may always accompany them on their journey as true shepherds. When you pray and feel peace in your heart, I am there with you to protect you. My children, the Warning is very, very near, many will kneel down and acknowledge the power of God asking for forgiveness and many will not believe because they are taken by the power of Satan and will die without repentance. Be ready children, I warn you because I want all my children to be saved. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, das sind schwere Zeiten und es wird Zeiten kommen, wenn die Verwirrung noch gr\u00f6\u00dfer ist. Meine Kinder, beten so sehr, dass der Krieg, der das kommen wird, gemildert werden kann, die Kraft des Gebets ist gro\u00dfartig. Beten Sie f\u00fcr die Kirche, denn der Hunger nach Macht hat alle Grenzen \u00fcberschritten und hat nichts mit Gott mehr zu tun. Bete f\u00fcr die heiligen Priester, das Licht kann sie immer auf ihrer Reise als echte Hirten begleiten. Wenn Sie beten und Frieden in Ihrem Herzen f\u00fchlen, bin ich mit Ihnen da, um Sie zu sch\u00fctzen. Meine Kinder, die Warnung ist sehr, ganz in der N\u00e4he, viele werden viele kn\u00e4ren und die Kraft Gottes anerkennen, die nach Vergebung bittet, und viele werden nicht glauben, weil sie von der Macht des Satans aufgenommen werden und ohne Reue sterben werden. Sei fertig Kinder, ich warne dich, weil ich will, dass alle meine Kinder gerettet werden sollen. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Estimados hijos, gracias por responder a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, estos son tiempos dif\u00edciles y momentos llegar\u00e1n en los que la confusi\u00f3n ser\u00e1 a\u00fan mayor. Hijos, oren tanto, para que la guerra que llegue pueda ser mitigada, el poder de la oraci\u00f3n es excelente. Ore por la Iglesia, porque el hambre del poder ha superado cada l\u00edmite y ya no tiene que ver con Dios. Ora por los santos sacerdotes, para que la luz siempre pueda acompa\u00f1arlos en su viaje de pastores reales. Al orar y sentir la paz en tu coraz\u00f3n, estoy all\u00ed contigo para protegerte. Mis hijos, la advertencia es mucho, pero muy cerca, tantos nudizar\u00e1n al reconocer el poder de Dios pidiendo perd\u00f3n y muchos no creer\u00e1n porque hice del poder de Satan\u00e1s y morir\u00e1n sin arrepentimiento. Est\u00e9 preparado para los ni\u00f1os, le advierto porque quiero que todos mis hijos ahorren. Ahora te bendigo en nombre del padre del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, ce sont des moments difficiles et il y aura des moments o\u00f9 la confusion sera encore plus grande. Mes enfants, prient tellement que la guerre qui viendra peut \u00eatre att\u00e9nu\u00e9e, le pouvoir de la pri\u00e8re est g\u00e9nial. Priez pour l'\u00e9glise, car la faim du pouvoir a d\u00e9pass\u00e9 toutes les limites et n'a plus rien \u00e0 voir avec Dieu. Priez pour les saintes pr\u00eatres, que la lumi\u00e8re peut toujours les accompagner dans leur voyage en tant que vrais bergers. Lorsque vous priez et ressentez la paix dans votre c\u0153ur, je suis l\u00e0 avec vous pour vous prot\u00e9ger. Mes enfants, l'avertissement est tr\u00e8s, tr\u00e8s proche, beaucoup vous d\u00e9rouleront et reconnaissent le pouvoir de Dieu demandant pardon et beaucoup ne croiront pas parce qu'ils sont pris par le pouvoir de Satan et mourra sans repentir. Soyez pr\u00eat pour enfants, je vous avertit parce que je veux que tous mes enfants soient sauv\u00e9s. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, questi sono tempi duri e arriveranno momenti in cui la confusione sar\u00e0 ancora pi\u00f9 grande. Figli, pregate tanto, affinch\u00e9 la guerra che arriver\u00e0 possa essere mitigata, la potenza della preghiera \u00e8 grande. Pregate per la Chiesa, perch\u00e9 la fame di potere ha superato ogni limite e non ha pi\u00f9 a che vedere con Dio. Pregate per i santi sacerdoti, affinch\u00e9 la luce possa sempre accompagnarli nel loro cammino di veri pastori. Quando pregate e sentite la pace nel vostro cuore, Io sono l\u00ec con voi per proteggervi. Figli miei, l\u2019avvertimento \u00e8 molto, ma molto vicino, tanti si inginocchieranno riconoscendo la potenza di Dio chiedendo perdono e tanti non crederanno perch\u00e9 presi dal potere di satana e moriranno senza pentimento. Siate pronti figli, Io vi avverto perch\u00e9 voglio che tutti i miei figli si salvino. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, Amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, to s\u0105 ci\u0119\u017ckie czasy i nadejd\u0105 takie, w kt\u00f3rych zamieszanie b\u0119dzie jeszcze wi\u0119ksze. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 nieustannie, aby wojna, kt\u00f3ra nadejdzie, zosta\u0142a z\u0142agodzona, moc modlitwy jest wielka. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, poniewa\u017c g\u0142\u00f3d w\u0142adzy przekroczy\u0142 wszelkie granice i nie ma ju\u017c nic wsp\u00f3lnego z Bogiem. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za \u015bwi\u0119tych kap\u0142an\u00f3w, aby \u015bwiat\u0142o zawsze towarzyszy\u0142o im na ich drodze jako prawdziwym pasterzom. Kiedy modlisz si\u0119 i czujesz pok\u00f3j w swoim sercu, jestem tam z tob\u0105, aby ci\u0119 chroni\u0107. Moje dzieci, Ostrze\u017cenie jest bardzo, bardzo bliskie, wielu ukl\u0119knie w uznaniu Bo\u017cej mocy i b\u0119dzie prosi\u0107 o przebaczenie, a wielu nie uwierzy, poniewa\u017c zostali porwani przez moc szatana i umr\u0105 bez pokuty. B\u0105d\u017acie gotowe dzieci, ostrzegam was, bo chc\u0119, aby wszystkie moje dzieci by\u0142y zbawione. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Queridos filhos, obrigado por ter respondido \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, estes s\u00e3o tempos dif\u00edceis e haver\u00e1 momentos em que a confus\u00e3o ser\u00e1 ainda maior. Meus filhos, oram tanto para que a guerra que vir\u00e1 seja mitigada, o poder da ora\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e9 \u00f3timo. Ore pela Igreja, pois a fome de poder excedeu todos os limites e n\u00e3o mais tem nada a ver com Deus. Ore pelos Santos Sacerdotes, essa luz pode sempre acompanh\u00e1-los em sua jornada como verdadeiros pastores. Quando voc\u00ea reza e sente a paz em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o, eu estou l\u00e1 com voc\u00ea para proteg\u00ea-lo. Meus filhos, o aviso \u00e9 muito, muito perto, muitos v\u00e3o se ajoelhar e reconhecer o poder de Deus pedindo perd\u00e3o e muitos n\u00e3o v\u00e3o acreditar porque s\u00e3o levados pelo poder de Satan\u00e1s e morrer\u00e3o sem arrependimento. Seja preparado crian\u00e7as, eu aviso porque quero que todos os meus filhos sejam salvos. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e9b\u662f\u8270\u96be\u7684\u65f6\u671f\uff0c\u56f0\u60d1\u4f1a\u66f4\u5927\u7684\u65f6\u5019\u4f1a\u6709\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5982\u6b64\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u53ef\u80fd\u4f1a\u51cf\u8f7b\u7684\u6218\u4e89\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u7684\u529b\u91cf\u5f88\u68d2\u3002\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6e34\u671b\u6743\u529b\u5df2\u7ecf\u8d85\u8fc7\u4e86\u6240\u6709\u9650\u5236\uff0c\u4e0d\u518d\u4e0e\u4e0a\u5e1d\u6709\u4efb\u4f55\u5173\u7cfb\u3002\u4e3a\u5723\u4eba\u796d\u53f8\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5149\u660e\u53ef\u80fd\u968f\u8eab\u966a\u4f34\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f5c\u4e3a\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u7267\u7f8a\u4eba\u7684\u65c5\u7a0b\u3002\u5f53\u4f60\u7948\u7977\u548c\u611f\u53d7\u5230\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u548c\u5e73\u65f6\uff0c\u6211\u548c\u4f60\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u6765\u4fdd\u62a4\u4f60\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8b66\u544a\u975e\u5e38\u8fd1\uff0c\u5f88\u591a\u4eba\u4f1a\u8dea\u4e0b\u5e76\u627f\u8ba4\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u529b\u91cf\u8981\u6c42\u5bbd\u6055\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u4e0d\u4f1a\u76f8\u4fe1\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u4eec\u88ab\u6492\u65e6\u7684\u529b\u91cf\u6240\u91c7\u53d6\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u4e0d\u4f1a\u6094\u6539\u3002\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u8b66\u544a\u4f60\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u60f3\u8981\u6240\u6709\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u90fd\u4f1a\u88ab\u62ef\u6551\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":29,"month_string":"January","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for being here and for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, always kneel down, prayers recited with faith and heart comfort me. My heart and that of my Son Jesus bleed, I look at this humanity, which so easily falls into the clutches of Satan, all this for a false freedom. Remember, my children, that only prayer will make you free. Forgive those who judge you without understanding. My daughter, before you, Jesus was accused of being unholy and insane; yet, He was the Son of God. My daughter, offer your humiliation and your pain, one day they will understand that yours are words from heaven. My children, follow my directions, live the messages and pray a lot, only in this way will you be able to enter the Kingdom of God, many will be the temptations, but you, children of my heart, be faithful and open your hearts to grace and learn to offer and give thanks. Never be afraid, with God near, there will be nothing to fear. Now I leave you my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie hier sind, und um auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen zu reagieren. Meine Kinder, immer knien, Gebete, die mit Glauben und Herz reagierten, tr\u00f6sten mich. Mein Herz und das meines Sohnes Jesus blutete, ich sehe diese Menschheit an, die so leicht in die Kupplungen des Satans f\u00e4llt, all das f\u00fcr eine falsche Freiheit. Denken Sie daran, meine Kinder, dass nur Gebet Sie frei machen wird. Vergib den denen, die dich urteilen, ohne zu verstehen. Meine Tochter, vor Ihnen, wurde Jesus vorgeworfen, unheilig und verr\u00fcckt zu sein; Trotzdem war er der Sohn Gottes. Meine Tochter, Bieten Sie Ihre Dem\u00fctigung und Ihren Schmerz an, eines Tages werden sie verstehen, dass Ihre Worte vom Himmel sind. Meine Kinder folgen meinen Anweisungen, live die Botschaften und beten viel, nur auf diese Weise werden Sie in der Lage sein, das Reich Gottes in Betracht zu ziehen, viele werden die Versuchungen sein, aber Sie, Kinder meines Herzens, sind treu und \u00f6ffnen Ihre Herzen zu gern und zu lernen, anbieten und danke zu geben. Habe niemals Angst, mit Gott in der N\u00e4he, es wird nichts zu bef\u00fcrchten geben. Jetzt verlasse ich Ihnen meinen m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed y por responder a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Los ni\u00f1os, siempre doblan las rodillas, las oraciones act\u00faan con fe y con mi coraz\u00f3n. Mi coraz\u00f3n y el de mi hijo, Jes\u00fas sangra, mira a esta humanidad, que con tanta facilidad cae en las arrugas de Satan\u00e1s, todo esto por una falsa libertad. Recuerda a los m\u00edos hijos, que solo la oraci\u00f3n te har\u00e1 libre. Perdona a los que te juzgan sin entender. Mi hija, delante de ti, Jes\u00fas fue acusado de ser indemblido y loco; Y, sin embargo, era el Hijo de Dios. Mi hija, ofrecen tu humillaci\u00f3n y tu dolor, un d\u00eda entender\u00e1 que los tuyos son palabras provienen del cielo. Mis hijos, sigue mis indicaciones, viven los mensajes y rezan tanto, solo para que puedas ingresar al Reino de Dios, tantos ser\u00e1n tentaciones, pero t\u00fa, hijos de mi coraz\u00f3n, ser\u00e1n fieles y abrimos tus corazones a Grace y aprende a Ofrezca y gracias. Nunca tengas miedo, con Dios cerca, no habr\u00e1 nada que temer. Ahora te dejo mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del padre del Hijo del Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici et de r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, vous agenouillez toujours, les pri\u00e8res r\u00e9cit\u00e9es avec la foi et le c\u0153ur me r\u00e9confortent. Mon c\u0153ur et celui de mon fils J\u00e9sus saignaient, je regarde cette humanit\u00e9, qui tombe si facilement dans les griffes de Satan, tout cela pour une fausse libert\u00e9. N'oubliez pas que mes enfants, que seule la pri\u00e8re vous rendra libre. Pardonnez ceux qui vous jugent sans comprendre. Ma fille, devant vous, J\u00e9sus \u00e9tait accus\u00e9 d'\u00eatre impies et insens\u00e9; Pourtant, il \u00e9tait le fils de Dieu. Ma fille, offrez votre humiliation et votre douleur, un jour, ils comprendront que les v\u00f4tres sont des mots du ciel. Mes enfants, suivez mes instructions, vivez les messages et prions beaucoup, seulement de cette fa\u00e7on pourrez-vous entrer dans le royaume de Dieu, beaucoup seront les tentations, mais vous, enfants de mon c\u0153ur, soyez fid\u00e8le et ouvre vos c\u0153urs Grace et apprendre \u00e0 offrir et \u00e0 remercier. N'ayez jamais peur, avec Dieu pr\u00e8s, il n'y aura rien \u00e0 craindre. Maintenant, je vous laisse ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per essere qui e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, piegate sempre le vostre ginocchia, le preghiere recitate con fede e con il cuore mi confortano. Il mio cuore e quello di mio Figlio Ges\u00f9 sanguinano, guardo questa umanit\u00e0, che con tanta facilit\u00e0 cade nelle grinfie di satana, tutto questo per una falsa libert\u00e0. Ricordate figli miei, che solo la preghiera vi render\u00e0 liberi. Perdonate coloro che vi giudicano senza capire. Figlia mia, prima di te, Ges\u00f9 \u00e8 stato accusato di essere indemoniato e pazzo; eppure, era il Figlio di Dio. Figlia mia, offri la tua umiliazione e il tuo dolore, un giorno capiranno che le tue sono parole venute dal cielo. Figli miei, seguite le mie indicazioni, vivete i messaggi e pregate tanto, solo cos\u00ec potrete entrare nel Regno di Dio, tante saranno le tentazioni, ma voi, figli del mio cuore, siate fedeli e aprite i vostri cuori alla grazia e imparate ad offrire e ringraziare. Non abbiate mai paura, con Dio vicino, non ci sar\u00e0 nulla da temere. Ora vi lascio la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre del Figlio dello Spirito Santo, Amen.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj i \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, zawsze kl\u0119kajcie, modlitwy odmawiane z wiar\u0105 i sercem pocieszaj\u0105 mnie. Serce moje i mojego Syna Jezusa krwawi, gdy patrz\u0119 na t\u0119 ludzko\u015b\u0107, kt\u00f3ra tak \u0142atwo wpada w szpony szatana, a wszystko to dla fa\u0142szywej wolno\u015bci. Pami\u0119tajcie, moje dzieci, \u017ce tylko modlitwa uczyni was wolnymi. Wybaczcie tym, kt\u00f3rzy os\u0105dzaj\u0105 was bez zrozumienia. Moja c\u00f3rko, przed tob\u0105 Jezus zosta\u0142 oskar\u017cony o op\u0119tanie i szale\u0144stwo, a przecie\u017c by\u0142 Synem Bo\u017cym. Moja c\u00f3rko, ofiaruj swoje upokorzenie i sw\u00f3j b\u00f3l; pewnego dnia zrozumiej\u0105, \u017ce twoje s\u0142owa pochodz\u0105 z Nieba. Moje dzieci, pod\u0105\u017cajcie za moimi wskazaniami, \u017cyjcie or\u0119dziami i m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 nieustannie, tylko w ten spos\u00f3b b\u0119dziecie mogli wej\u015b\u0107 do Kr\u00f3lestwa Bo\u017cego, wiele b\u0119dzie pokus, ale wy, dzieci mojego serca, b\u0105d\u017acie wierne i otw\u00f3rzcie wasze serca na \u0142ask\u0119 i nauczcie si\u0119 ofiarowywa\u0107 i dzi\u0119kowa\u0107. Nigdy si\u0119 nie l\u0119kajcie, z Bogiem przy sobie, nie b\u0119dzie si\u0119 czego ba\u0107. Teraz zostawiam wam moje matczyne b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por estar aqui e responder \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, sempre se ajoelham, ora\u00e7\u00f5es recitadas com f\u00e9 e cora\u00e7\u00e3o me confortam. Meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o e do meu filho Jesus sangram, eu olho para essa humanidade, que t\u00e3o facilmente cai nas garras de Satan\u00e1s, tudo isso por uma falsa liberdade. Lembre-se, meus filhos, que apenas ora\u00e7\u00e3o ir\u00e1 libertar. Perdoe aqueles que te julgam sem entender. Minha filha, diante de voc\u00ea, Jesus foi acusada de ser profana e insana; No entanto, ele era o Filho de Deus. Minha filha, oferecer sua humilha\u00e7\u00e3o e sua dor, um dia eles v\u00e3o entender que os seus s\u00e3o palavras do c\u00e9u. Meus filhos, siga minhas instru\u00e7\u00f5es, viva as mensagens e ore muito, apenas desta maneira voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 capaz de entrar no Reino de Deus, muitos ser\u00e3o as tenta\u00e7\u00f5es, mas voc\u00ea, filhos do meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o, ser fiel e abrir seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es para gra\u00e7a e aprender a oferecer e agradecer. Nunca tenha medo, com Deus perto, n\u00e3o haver\u00e1 nada a temer. Agora eu deixo voc\u00ea minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o maternal em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u548c\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u603b\u662f\u8dea\u4e0b\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u4e0e\u4fe1\u4ef0\u548c\u5fc3\u7075\u62b1\u6028\uff0c\u5b89\u6170\u6211\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\u810f\u548c\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u6d41\u8840\uff0c\u6211\u770b\u7740\u8fd9\u4e2a\u4eba\u6027\uff0c\u8fd9\u5f88\u5bb9\u6613\u843d\u5165\u6492\u65e6\u7684\u79bb\u5408\u5668\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u662f\u865a\u5047\u7684\u81ea\u7531\u3002\u8bb0\u4f4f\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u7948\u7977\u4f1a\u8ba9\u4f60\u81ea\u7531\u3002\u539f\u8c05\u90a3\u4e9b\u6ca1\u6709\u7406\u89e3\u5224\u65ad\u4f60\u7684\u4eba\u3002\u5728\u4f60\u4e4b\u524d\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\u88ab\u6307\u8d23\u662f\u4e0d\u5723\u6d01\u800c\u75af\u72c2\u7684;\u7136\u800c\uff0c\u4ed6\u662f\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u63d0\u4f9b\u4f60\u7684\u7f9e\u8fb1\u548c\u4f60\u7684\u75db\u82e6\uff0c\u6709\u4e00\u5929\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u660e\u767d\u4f60\u7684\u5929\u5802\u7684\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6cbf\u7740\u6211\u7684\u6307\u793a\uff0c\u751f\u6d3b\u7684\u4fe1\u606f\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u5f88\u591a\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u8fd9\u6837\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u8fd9\u6837\uff0c\u4f60\u80fd\u8fdb\u5165\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u738b\u56fd\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u4f1a\u662f\u8bf1\u60d1\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u4f60\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\u7075\uff0c\u5fe0\u5b9e\uff0c\u5949\u627f\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u6069\u5178\u5e76\u5b66\u4f1a\u63d0\u4f9b\u5e76\u611f\u8c22\u3002\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u4e0e\u4e0a\u5e1d\u5728\u9644\u8fd1\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u4ec0\u4e48\u53ef\u4ee5\u62c5\u5fc3\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u6211\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":1,"day":30,"month_string":"January","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: These are times of uneasiness for humanity that waits without knowing that, although they deny it, this state flares up in faithless creatures who do not love and do not adore the Sacrosanct Trinity. Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: 'Holy, Holy, Holy, Lord, Almighty God, He who Was, who Is, and who Is to come'. Great is the Divine Power to redeem them from sin! In this generation, as in previous ones, disobedience has been the cause of great evils for mankind: man, rebels against God and man falls prey to his own inventions. We keep you before us, my legions are watching you every moment and I invite you to be doers of the Divine Will. Decide now! To seek salvation... And for this it is necessary that you be creatures of unwavering and firm faith, thirsty for the salvation of all humanity. What would become of the human creature without the Divine Presence? What will become of the human creature in front of his conscience? People of God, the core of the earth is being subjected unpredictably to the influence of the sun, the moon and celestial bodies that travel through space prowling the orbit of the earth, which affects the elements on earth and the human creature suffers what it has not suffered before. At this time, they must be wary of the sea and be vigilant so that they are not at risk. The elements have changed and are rushing upon the earth to purify it. The earth will continue to shudder from its hotter core and heat is rising to the surface. This leads to dormant volcanoes awakening and active volcanoes increasing their activity preventing several countries from using their flight paths and human creatures will not be able to reach where they reside until new routes are re-established. The human creature is enjoying life as if nothing is happening at the moment. Disease plagues mankind and will continue to be present, mutating and with new diseases that will be prolonged. Some are spread from the air by misused science and mankind is not aware of it. The human creature more and more distant from the Holy Trinity and from our Queen and Mother focuses on the pleasures of the world, ignoring the signs and signals of this moment, leaving aside what heaven indicates. Europe will find itself in a dawning and will be 'Babel'... And all mankind will suffer as a result. God's children must educate themselves in what is coming for mankind, loving God must not keep them in the ignorance in which most of God's people live. Instruct themselves! So that they do not deny the undeniable and do not stray from the right path. Faith and reason do not contradict each other. They contradict each other when the human ego penetrates the mind of the human creature and keeps it in a constant debate between faith and reason. The human ego is strong in some creatures and manages to divert them from the path. Ah, people of God, you will witness the power of the elements that are agitated by the changes that the earth is undergoing from its core. Changes exerted by the influence of the sun, the moon and the asteroids that from where they are already influencing the alterations of the earth's magnetic field, which contributes to the shaking of the tectonic faults on earth. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: Who will resist in the face of the coming changes? Those who do not waver or waver in professing the faith? Those who prepare themselves in faith and their trust in Divine Mercy is stronger because they have been partakers of the greatness of the Holy Trinity.... Those will stand firm. This is the moment in which they must maintain confidence in the divine promises. 'Give thanks to the lord for his love, for his wonders with the sons of Adam! For he has broken in pieces the gates of bronze, and shattered the bars of iron.' Fear not, you are children of the highest. Do not fear and keep the faith. Pray for all mankind, pray. With my sword on high I protect you. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: S\u0105 to czasy niepokoju dla ludzko\u015bci, kt\u00f3ra czeka, nie wiedz\u0105c, \u017ce cho\u0107 zaprzecza temu, stan ten rozpala si\u0119 w wiaro\u0142omnych stworzeniach, kt\u00f3re nie kochaj\u0105 i nie adoruj\u0105 \u015awi\u0119tej Tr\u00f3jcy. Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: \"\u015awi\u0119ty, \u015awi\u0119ty, \u015awi\u0119ty, Pan B\u00f3g wszechmog\u0105cy, Kt\u00f3ry by\u0142 i Kt\u00f3ry jest, i Kt\u00f3ry przychodzi\". Wielka jest Boska Moc odkupienia ich od grzechu! W tym pokoleniu, jak i w poprzednich, niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwo sta\u0142o si\u0119 przyczyn\u0105 wielkiego z\u0142a dla ludzko\u015bci: cz\u0142owiek, buntuje si\u0119 przeciwko Bogu i cz\u0142owiek pada ofiar\u0105 w\u0142asnych wymys\u0142\u00f3w. Trzymamy was przed sob\u0105, moje legiony obserwuj\u0105 was w ka\u017cdej chwili i zach\u0119cam was, aby\u015bcie byli wykonawcami Woli Bo\u017cej. Decydujcie si\u0119 teraz! Szuka\u0107 zbawienia... A do tego potrzeba, aby\u015bcie byli istotami o niezachwianej i mocnej wierze, spragnionymi zbawienia ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci. Co sta\u0142oby si\u0119 z ludzkim stworzeniem bez Boskiej Obecno\u015bci? Czym\u017ce stanie si\u0119 stworzenie ludzkie wobec swego sumienia? Ludu Bo\u017cy, j\u0105dro ziemi poddawane jest w spos\u00f3b nieprzewidywalny wp\u0142ywom s\u0142o\u0144ca, ksi\u0119\u017cyca i cia\u0142 niebieskich, kt\u00f3re przemierzaj\u0105 przestrze\u0144 kosmiczn\u0105, grasuj\u0105c po orbicie ziemi, co wp\u0142ywa na \u017cywio\u0142y na ziemi, a stworzenie ludzkie cierpi to, czego jeszcze nie cierpia\u0142o. W tym czasie musz\u0105 one uwa\u017ca\u0107 na morze i by\u0107 czujne, aby nie by\u0142y zagro\u017cone. \u017bywio\u0142y zmieni\u0142y si\u0119 i p\u0119dz\u0105 na ziemi\u0119, aby j\u0105 oczy\u015bci\u0107. Ziemia b\u0119dzie nadal dr\u017ce\u0107 od jej gor\u0119tszego j\u0105dra, a ciep\u0142o wznosi si\u0119 na powierzchni\u0119. Prowadzi to do przebudzenia u\u015bpionych wulkan\u00f3w i zwi\u0119kszenia aktywno\u015bci aktywnych wulkan\u00f3w, co uniemo\u017cliwia kilku krajom korzystanie z ich tras lotniczych, a ludzkie istoty nie b\u0119d\u0105 w stanie dotrze\u0107 tam, gdzie mieszkaj\u0105, dop\u00f3ki nowe trasy nie zostan\u0105 przywr\u00f3cone. Ludzkie istoty ciesz\u0105 si\u0119 \u017cyciem, jakby nic si\u0119 w tej chwili nie dzia\u0142o. Choroby n\u0119kaj\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107 i b\u0119d\u0105 nadal obecne, mutuj\u0105 z nowymi chorobami, kt\u00f3re b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 przed\u0142u\u017ca\u0107. Niekt\u00f3re s\u0105 rozprzestrzeniane z powietrza przez \u017ale wykorzystan\u0105 nauk\u0119 i ludzko\u015b\u0107 nie jest tego \u015bwiadoma. Istota ludzka coraz bardziej oddalona od Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej i od naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki skupia si\u0119 na przyjemno\u015bciach tego \u015bwiata, ignoruj\u0105c znaki i sygna\u0142y tej chwili, pomijaj\u0105c to, co wskazuje niebo. Europa znajdzie si\u0119 w epoce \"Babel\"... I ca\u0142a ludzko\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dzie w zwi\u0105zku z tym cierpie\u0107. Dzieci Bo\u017ce musz\u0105 si\u0119 edukowa\u0107 w tym, co nadchodzi dla ludzko\u015bci, kochaj\u0105cy B\u00f3g nie mo\u017ce ich trzyma\u0107 w niewiedzy, w kt\u00f3rej \u017cyje wi\u0119kszo\u015b\u0107 ludu Bo\u017cego. Instruowa\u0107 samych siebie! Aby nie zaprzeczali temu, co niezaprzeczalne i nie zbaczali z w\u0142a\u015bciwej drogi. Wiara i rozum nie s\u0105 ze sob\u0105 sprzeczne. Przecz\u0105 sobie, gdy ludzkie ego przenika do umys\u0142u ludzkiego stworzenia i utrzymuje je w ci\u0105g\u0142ej debacie mi\u0119dzy wiar\u0105 a rozumem. Ludzkie ego jest silne w niekt\u00f3rych stworzeniach i udaje mu si\u0119 odwr\u00f3ci\u0107 je od \u015bcie\u017cki. Ach, ludu Bo\u017cy, b\u0119dziecie \u015bwiadkami pot\u0119gi \u017cywio\u0142\u00f3w wzburzonych przez zmiany, jakim podlega ziemia ze swego j\u0105dra. Zmian wywieranych przez wp\u0142yw s\u0142o\u0144ca, ksi\u0119\u017cyca i asteroid, kt\u00f3re sk\u0105din\u0105d ju\u017c wp\u0142ywaj\u0105 na zmiany ziemskiego pola magnetycznego, co przyczynia si\u0119 do wstrz\u0105s\u00f3w uskok\u00f3w tektonicznych na ziemi. Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Kto si\u0119 oprze w obliczu nadchodz\u0105cych zmian? Ci, kt\u00f3rzy nie zachwiej\u0105 si\u0119 lub zachwiej\u0105 si\u0119 w wyznawaniu wiary? Ci, kt\u00f3rzy przygotowuj\u0105 si\u0119 w wierze, a ich ufno\u015b\u0107 w Mi\u0142osierdzie Bo\u017ce jest silniejsza, poniewa\u017c stali si\u0119 uczestnikami wielko\u015bci Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej.... Ci b\u0119d\u0105 sta\u0107 mocno. Jest to moment, w kt\u00f3rym musz\u0105 zachowa\u0107 ufno\u015b\u0107 w Boskie obietnice. \"Dzi\u0119kujcie Panu za Jego mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, za Jego cuda z synami Adama! Bo z\u0142ama\u0142 w kawa\u0142ki bramy z br\u0105zu, a roztrzaska\u0142 kraty z \u017celaza.\"  Nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, jeste\u015bcie dzie\u0107mi najwy\u017cszego. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119 i zachowujcie wiar\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za ca\u0142\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. Z moim mieczem na wysoko\u015bci chroni\u0119 was. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":3,"month_string":"February","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My beloved children, thank you for being here and for responding to My call in your heart. My children, you are living in the worst times of the deluge, you have had so much time for your conversion, yet, you prefer the world, you prefer to sin often not having understood that one day you will be face to face with my Jesus. Pray, children, so that your prayers may divert what is most wickedly passing through the minds of your politicians. Help my Son Jesus with prayer. The earth will tremble. My children, put everything in the wounds of Jesus, take my hands and I will protect you and bring you to Him. My children, pray for the Church and for the holy priests so that they may always remain faithful to the true teaching of the faith. My children, the time is over for the wicked and mercy will be infinite for the righteous. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen. Today, many will be the graces that will descend upon you.","text_de":"Meine geliebten Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie hier sind, und um auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen zu reagieren. Meine Kinder, du lebst in den schlimmsten Zeiten der Sintflut, du hast so viel Zeit f\u00fcr deine Bekehrung gehabt, aber du bevorzugst die Welt, du lieber lieber, dass sie oft nicht verstanden haben, dass man eines Tages nicht mit meinem Angesicht gesprochen hat Jesus. Beten Sie, Kinder, also, damit Ihre Gebete vielleicht umleiten k\u00f6nnen, was am meisten von den K\u00f6pfen Ihrer Politiker f\u00fchrt. Hilf meinem Sohn Jesus mit Gebet. Die Erde wird zittern. Meine Kinder, legte alles in die Wunden Jesu, nehmen meine H\u00e4nde und ich werde dich sch\u00fctzen und dich zu ihm bringen. Meine Kinder, bete f\u00fcr die Kirche und f\u00fcr die heiligen Priester, damit sie der wahren Lehre des Glaubens immer treu bleiben k\u00f6nnen. Meine Kinder, die Zeit ist vorbei f\u00fcr die B\u00f6sen und der Barmherzigkeit wird unendlich f\u00fcr die Gerechten sein. Jetzt verlasse ich Sie mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen. Heute werden viele die Gnaden sein, die auf Sie abstammen.","text_es":"Amaba a mis hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed y por responder a mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, usted est\u00e1 experimentando los peores momentos de la inundaci\u00f3n, ha tenido tanto tiempo para su conversi\u00f3n, sin embargo, usted prefiere el mundo, prefiere pecar a menudo no habi\u00e9ndose dado cuenta de que un d\u00eda estar\u00e1s cara a cara con mi Jes\u00fas. Rezando a los ni\u00f1os, para que sus oraciones puedan dislocarse, lo m\u00e1s p\u00e9rfido pasa a sus pol\u00edticos. Ayuda a mi hijo Jes\u00fas con la oraci\u00f3n. La tierra tiemble. Mis hijos, ponen todo en las heridas de Jes\u00fas, tome mis manos y le proteger\u00e9 y lo llevar\u00e9 a \u00e9l. Mis hijos, oren por la iglesia y para los santos sacerdotes para que siempre se mantengan fieles al verdadero magisterio de la fe. Mis hijos, el tiempo termin\u00f3 por los malvados y la misericordia ser\u00e1n infinitos para los justos. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del Padre, del Hijo del Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n. Hoy en d\u00eda, muchas ser\u00e1n las gracias que descender\u00e1n sobre ti.","text_fr":"Mes enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, merci d'\u00eatre ici et de r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, vous vivez dans les pires moments du d\u00e9luge, vous avez eu tellement de temps pour votre conversion, mais vous pr\u00e9f\u00e9rez le monde, vous pr\u00e9f\u00e9rez que vous pr\u00e9f\u00e9rez ne pas avoir compris qu'un jour, vous serez face \u00e0 face avec mon J\u00e9sus. Priez, les enfants, de sorte que vos pri\u00e8res puissent d\u00e9tourner ce qui est le plus mal \u00e0 travers l'esprit de vos politiciens. Aidez mon fils J\u00e9sus avec la pri\u00e8re. La terre va trembler. Mes enfants, mettent tout dans les blessures de J\u00e9sus, prenez mes mains et je vais vous prot\u00e9ger et vous amener \u00e0 lui. Mes enfants, prions pour l'\u00e9glise et pour les saintes pr\u00eatres afin qu'ils puissent toujours rester fid\u00e8les \u00e0 la v\u00e9ritable enseignement de la foi. Mes enfants, le temps est fini pour les m\u00e9chants et la mis\u00e9ricorde sera infini pour les justes. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen. Aujourd'hui, beaucoup seront les gr\u00e2ces qui vous descendent sur vous.","text_it":"Amati figli miei, grazie per essere qui e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, state vivendo i tempi peggiori del diluvio, avete avuto tanto tempo per la vostra conversione, eppure, voi preferite il mondo, preferite peccare spesso non avendo capito che un giorno sarete faccia a faccia con il mio Ges\u00f9. Pregate figli, affinch\u00e9 le vostre preghiere possano sviare ci\u00f2 che di pi\u00f9 perfido passa nella mente dei vostri politici. Aiutate mio Figlio Ges\u00f9 con la preghiera. La terra tremer\u00e0. Figli miei, mettete tutto nelle piaghe di Ges\u00f9, prendete le mie mani ed Io vi protegger\u00f2 e vi porter\u00f2 a Lui. Figli miei, pregate per la chiesa e per i santi sacerdoti affinch\u00e9 rimangano sempre fedeli al vero magistero della fede. Figli miei, il tempo \u00e8 finito per i malvagi e la misericordia sar\u00e0 infinita per i giusti. Ora vi lascio con la mia materna benedizione nel nome del Padre, del Figlio dello Spirito Santo, amen. Oggi, tante saranno le grazie che scenderanno su di voi.","text_pl":"Moje kochane dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj i \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, \u017cyjecie w najgorszych czasach potopu, mieli\u015bcie tak wiele czasu na nawr\u00f3cenie, a jednak wolicie \u015bwiat, wolicie cz\u0119sto grzeszy\u0107, nie rozumiej\u0105c, \u017ce pewnego dnia staniecie twarz\u0105 w twarz z moim Jezusem. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, aby wasze modlitwy odwr\u00f3ci\u0142y to, co jest najbardziej perfidne w umys\u0142ach waszych polityk\u00f3w. Pom\u00f3\u017c mojemu Synowi Jezusowi w modlitwie. Ziemia b\u0119dzie dr\u017ce\u0107. Dzieci moje, z\u0142\u00f3\u017ccie wszystko w rany Jezusa, we\u017acie mnie za r\u0119ce, a ja b\u0119d\u0119 was strzeg\u0142a i przyprowadz\u0119 was do Niego. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 i za \u015bwi\u0119tych kap\u0142an\u00f3w, aby zawsze byli wierni prawdziwej nauce wiary. Dzieci moje, czas dla z\u0142ych si\u0119 sko\u0144czy\u0142, a mi\u0142osierdzie b\u0119dzie niesko\u0144czone dla sprawiedliwych. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen. Dzi\u015b zst\u0105pi na was wiele \u0142ask.","text_pt":"Meus amados filhos, obrigado por estar aqui e responder \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, voc\u00ea est\u00e1 vivendo nos piores momentos do dil\u00favio, voc\u00ea teve tanto tempo para sua convers\u00e3o, mas voc\u00ea prefere o mundo, voc\u00ea prefere pecado muitas vezes n\u00e3o tendo entendido que um dia voc\u00ea estar\u00e1 cara a cara com o meu Jesus. Ore, as crian\u00e7as, de modo que suas ora\u00e7\u00f5es possam desviar o que \u00e9 mais perversamente passando pelas mentes dos seus pol\u00edticos. Ajude meu filho Jesus com ora\u00e7\u00e3o. A terra tremer\u00e1. Meus filhos, colocar tudo nas feridas de Jesus, pegam minhas m\u00e3os e eu vou proteg\u00ea-lo e te levar para ele. Meus filhos, oram pela igreja e pelos santos sacerdotes para que possam sempre permanecer fi\u00e9is ao verdadeiro ensino da f\u00e9. Meus filhos, o tempo acabar com o \u00edmpio e a miseric\u00f3rdia ser\u00e1 infinito para os justos. Agora eu deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o maternal em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m. Hoje, muitas ser\u00e3o as gra\u00e7as que v\u00e3o descer sobre voc\u00ea.","text_zh":"\u6211\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u548c\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u7075\u56de\u5e94\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4f60\u751f\u6d3b\u5728\u6d2a\u6c34\u7684\u6700\u7cdf\u7cd5\u200b\u200b\u65f6\u671f\uff0c\u4f60\u6709\u8fd9\u4e48\u591a\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\u6765\u8f6c\u6362\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u66f4\u559c\u6b22\u8fd9\u4e2a\u4e16\u754c\uff0c\u4f60\u66f4\u559c\u6b22\u72af\u7f6a\u5f80\u5f80\u6ca1\u6709\u7406\u89e3\uff0c\u6709\u4e00\u5929\u4f60\u4f1a\u9762\u5bf9\u8138\u4e0a\u7684\u8036\u7a23\u3002\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8ba9\u4f60\u7684\u7948\u7977\u53ef\u4ee5\u8f6c\u79fb\u5230\u653f\u6cbb\u5bb6\u7684\u5934\u8111\u4e2d\u6700\u90aa\u6076\u7684\u7a0b\u5ea6\u3002\u5e2e\u52a9\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u7948\u7977\u3002\u5730\u7403\u4f1a\u98a4\u6296\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u628a\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u653e\u5728\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u4f24\u53e3\u4e2d\uff0c\u7275\u7740\u6211\u7684\u624b\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u4fdd\u62a4\u4f60\u5e76\u5e26\u4f60\u53bb\u4ed6\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u548c\u5723\u6d01\u796d\u53f8\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u4ed6\u4eec\u53ef\u80fd\u603b\u662f\u5fe0\u4e8e\u4fe1\u4ef0\u7684\u771f\u6b63\u6559\u5b66\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u65f6\u95f4\u7ed3\u675f\u4e86\u90aa\u6076\uff0c\u601c\u60af\u5c06\u662f\u4e49\u4eba\u7684\u65e0\u9650\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002\u4eca\u5929\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u5c06\u6210\u4e3a\u5c06\u62b5\u5236\u4f60\u7684\u683c\u96f7\u65af\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":5,"month_string":"February","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for answering my call in your hearts and for bending your knees in prayer. My children, tell everyone to return to God, His laws and commandments, repent my children and ask for God's mercy, which can be granted in true repentance, confess. Jesus is near, always be ready. My children, beware of the waters that will invade the earth, which is ready for its transformation. Pray for my priests, for some of them are creating so much confusion among my children, pray that the light may enter their hearts. My children, today I will bless these candles so that they may bring the light of the Holy Spirit into your homes. I am with you. Now I bless you, in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen beantwortet haben, und um Ihre Knie im Gebet zu biegen. Meine Kinder, sagen, dass es allen zur\u00fcckkommt, um zu Gott zur\u00fcckzukehren, seine Gesetze und Gebote, um meine Kinder neu zu bereuen und um Gottes Barmherzigkeit zu bitten, der in echter Reue gew\u00e4hrt werden kann. Jesus ist in der N\u00e4he, sei immer bereit. Meine Kinder, h\u00fcte dich vor den Gew\u00e4ssern, die auf die Erde eindringen, was f\u00fcr ihre Transformation bereit ist. Beten Sie f\u00fcr meine Priester, denn einige von ihnen schaffen so viel Verwirrung zwischen meinen Kindern, beten Sie, dass das Licht in ihre Herzen eintreten kann. Meine Kinder, heute werde ich diese Kerzen segnen, damit sie das Licht des Heiligen Geistes in Ihre H\u00e4user bringen k\u00f6nnen. Ich bin bei dir. Jetzt segne ich dich, im Namen der heiligsten Dreieinigkeit, des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada a su coraz\u00f3n y para doblar las rodillas en la oraci\u00f3n. Mis hijos, diles a todos que regresen a Dios, a sus leyes y sus mandamientos, arrepientan a mis hijos y le preguntan a la misericordia de Dios, que se puede otorgar en verdadero arrepentimiento, confesado. Jes\u00fas est\u00e1 cerca, encontremos listos. Mis hijos, atenci\u00f3n a las aguas que invadir\u00e1n la Tierra, que est\u00e1 listo para su transformaci\u00f3n. Ore por mis sacerdotes, porque algunos de ellos est\u00e1n creando tanta confusi\u00f3n entre mis hijos, oren para que la luz entre en sus corazones. Hoy los ni\u00f1os bendecir\u00e9 estas velas, para que puedan traer la luz del Esp\u00edritu Santo a sus hogares. Estoy con usted. Ahora te bendigo, en nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Padre, Hijo y Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs et de plier vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re. Mes enfants, disent \u00e0 tout le monde de retourner \u00e0 Dieu, ses lois et ses commandements, se repentir mes enfants et demander la mis\u00e9ricorde de Dieu, qui peut \u00eatre accord\u00e9e dans une v\u00e9ritable repentance, avoue. J\u00e9sus est proche, soyez toujours pr\u00eat. Mes enfants, m\u00e9fiez-vous des eaux qui envahiront la Terre, qui est pr\u00eate pour sa transformation. Priez pour mes pr\u00eatres, car certains d'entre eux cr\u00e9ent autant de confusion chez mes enfants, prient pour que la lumi\u00e8re puisse entrer dans leurs c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, aujourd'hui, je b\u00e9nirai ces bougies afin qu'elles puissent apporter la lumi\u00e8re du Saint-Esprit dans vos maisons. Je suis avec toi. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis, au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9, du p\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore e per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia nella preghiera. Bambini miei, dite a tutti di tornare a Dio, alle sue leggi e ai suoi comandamenti, pentitevi figli miei e chiedete la misericordia di Dio, che potr\u00e0 essere accordata nel vero pentimento, confessatevi. Ges\u00f9 \u00e8 vicino, fatevi trovare sempre pronti. Figli miei, attenzione alle acque che invaderanno la terra, che \u00e8 pronta alla sua trasformazione. Pregate per i miei sacerdoti, perch\u00e9 alcuni di loro stanno creando tanta confusione tra i miei figli, pregate affinch\u00e9 la luce entri nei loro cuori. Figli, oggi benedir\u00f2 queste candele, affinch\u00e9 possano portare la luce dello Spirito Santo nelle le vostre case. Io sono con voi. Ora vi benedico, nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, Padre, Figlio e Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach i ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie do modlitwy. Dzieci moje, powiedzcie wszystkim, aby powr\u00f3cili do Boga, do Jego praw i przykaza\u0144, nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119, dzieci moje, i pro\u015bcie o mi\u0142osierdzie Bo\u017ce, kt\u00f3re mo\u017ce by\u0107 udzielone w prawdziwej pokucie, wyspowiadajcie si\u0119. Jezus jest blisko, zawsze b\u0105d\u017acie gotowi. Dzieci moje, strze\u017ccie si\u0119 w\u00f3d, kt\u00f3re wtargn\u0105 na ziemi\u0119, kt\u00f3ra jest gotowa na swoj\u0105 przemian\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za moich kap\u0142an\u00f3w, poniewa\u017c niekt\u00f3rzy z nich wprowadzaj\u0105 tyle zamieszania w\u015br\u00f3d moich dzieci; m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, aby \u015bwiat\u0142o mog\u0142o wej\u015b\u0107 do ich serc. Dzieci moje, dzi\u015b pob\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 te \u015bwiece, aby wnosi\u0142y do waszych dom\u00f3w \u015bwiat\u0142o Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego. Jestem z Wami. Teraz ja was b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por responder a minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e para dobrar os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, dizem que todos retornam a Deus, suas leis e mandamentos, se arrependem de meus filhos e pedem a miseric\u00f3rdia de Deus, que pode ser concedida em verdadeiro arrependimento, confesso. Jesus est\u00e1 pr\u00f3ximo, esteja sempre pronto. Meus filhos, cuidado com as \u00e1guas que invadir\u00e3o a terra, que est\u00e1 pronta para sua transforma\u00e7\u00e3o. Ore por meus sacerdotes, pois alguns deles est\u00e3o criando muita confus\u00e3o entre meus filhos, orar para que a luz possa entrar em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, hoje vou aben\u00e7oar essas velas para que elas possam trazer a luz do Esp\u00edrito Santo em suas casas. Eu estou contigo. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo, em nome da trindade mais sagrada, pai e filho e o Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u56de\u7b54\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u7977\u544a\u4e2d\u5f2f\u66f2\u819d\u76d6\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u544a\u8bc9\u5927\u5bb6\u8fd4\u56de\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u4ed6\u7684\u6cd5\u5f8b\u548c\u8beb\u547d\uff0c\u6094\u6539\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u5e76\u8981\u6c42\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u601c\u60af\uff0c\u8fd9\u53ef\u4ee5\u771f\u6b63\u6094\u6539\uff0c\u627f\u8ba4\u3002\u8036\u7a23\u5728\u9644\u8fd1\uff0c\u59cb\u7ec8\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u4e86\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5c0f\u5fc3\u5c06\u4fb5\u5165\u5730\u7403\u7684\u6c34\u57df\uff0c\u8fd9\u5df2\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u8f6c\u578b\u3002\u4e3a\u6211\u7684\u7267\u5e08\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e2d\u7684\u4e00\u4e9b\u4eba\u5728\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4e4b\u95f4\u521b\u9020\u4e86\u5982\u6b64\u591a\u7684\u6df7\u4e71\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u5149\u7ebf\u53ef\u4ee5\u8fdb\u5165\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u5fc3\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4eca\u5929\u6211\u4f1a\u795d\u798f\u8fd9\u4e9b\u8721\u70db\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u4ed6\u4eec\u53ef\u4ee5\u5c06\u5723\u7075\u7684\u5149\u7ebf\u5e26\u5165\u4f60\u7684\u5bb6\u91cc\u3002\u6211\u548c\u4f60\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u4ee5\u6700\u795e\u5723\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\uff0c\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":6,"month_string":"February","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: in love and faith toward the Almighty, be life for every heart. I invite you to look at what is happening on earth and not to look only at what you live in your square meter. This blindness induces the ignorance of those who claim that nothing is happening. The earth is in darkness. This darkness does not come from outside, but from the evil that nestles within the human creature. They live at a time when infidelity has invaded the environment in which the human creature lives and the human creature has welcomed it with pleasure, which leads to grave baseness. The infernal spirits have drawn up strategies knowing the human creature and his weakness for the sins of the flesh unleashing immorality, so much so that they have surpassed the sins of Sodom and Gomorrah. The infidelity of humanity towards the holy trinity and towards our King and mother of the last times is shocking, yet you will see with horror the cause of the schism of the Church. Sons of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: infidelity to the divinity causes the human creature of science to be motivated to use science to do evil to his own brethren. The military power of the most powerful powers is to be feared by you, because they keep in their possession weapons that have not been shown to humanity and possess great destructive power. Families have been transformed into places of individualism and cruelty; of disconsolation and not of formation nor of love, as a favourable result to what the elite expected. The suffering continues for the human race.... Strange sounds come out of the ground, being these the creaking of the tectonic plates preparing for strong earthquakes. The earth has become intoxicated by the sins of human generations. As part of humanity, they know that they are waiting for the dreaded third world war. People of God, the powers are inflaming each other. Wars have within them their own interests and at this moment the scarce economy of one of the powers and the desire for territorial expansion of another power prevails, which has spread its ideology throughout the earth, fomenting communism and social revolutions, which in the end are part of the preamble to war. People of God, the sickness that is raging throughout humanity is part of that silent war that has begun, the third world war. Pay attention to the signs and signals, see how nature invades the earth and leads man to suffer. The elements give no respite. Pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, be aware that a conspiracy arises against world renowned figures, unleashing fury among the powers. Pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, pray. Rome suffers to the point of exhaustion. Italy suffers greatly. Pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, pray without holding back, pray being active doers in the likeness of the divine working and acting. Be practitioners of fraternity, nourish yourselves with the body and blood of our divine redeemer present in the holy Eucharist, love our Queen and Mother, pray the holy rosary. Prepare yourselves to be true children, be love above all, obedient and keep the faith even if you are afraid of what you see. Do not lose faith. Be persevering without straying into the seemingly easy and safe. The people of God are never helpless. We are ready to defend you against the powers of hell so that you do not succumb to evil. The divine blessing continually makes itself present upon his faithful children. Do not fear, but instead maintain the certainty of the Divine Power that is above all power. Our Queen and Mother stand firm over humanity that will enter into chaos and by divine design will burst forth at the moment of desolation as mother of Divine Mercy to the aid of the children of God. In unity to the sacred hearts, I bless you. Prepare yourselves children of God and be converted now! Receive the love from above. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.  ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owani naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: w mi\u0142o\u015bci i wierze wobec Wszechmocnego b\u0105d\u017acie \u017cyciem dla ka\u017cdego serca. Zach\u0119cam was do spojrzenia na to, co dzieje si\u0119 na ziemi, a nie do patrzenia tylko na to, czym \u017cyjecie na swoim metrze kwadratowym. Ta \u015blepota wywo\u0142uje niewiedz\u0119 tych, kt\u00f3rzy twierdz\u0105, \u017ce nic si\u0119 nie dzieje. Ziemia jest pogr\u0105\u017cona w ciemno\u015bci. Ta ciemno\u015b\u0107 nie pochodzi z zewn\u0105trz, ale ze z\u0142a, kt\u00f3re zagnie\u017cd\u017ca si\u0119 w ludzkim stworzeniu. \u017byj\u0105 w czasach, gdy niewierno\u015b\u0107 wtargn\u0119\u0142a do \u015brodowiska, w kt\u00f3rym \u017cyje ludzkie stworzenie, a ludzkie stworzenie przyj\u0119\u0142o j\u0105 z rado\u015bci\u0105, co prowadzi do ci\u0119\u017ckiej pod\u0142o\u015bci. Duchy piekielne opracowa\u0142y strategie, znaj\u0105c stworzenie ludzkie i jego s\u0142abo\u015b\u0107 do grzech\u00f3w cia\u0142a wyzwalaj\u0105c niemoralno\u015b\u0107, tak wielk\u0105, \u017ce przewy\u017cszy\u0142a ona grzechy Sodomy i Gomory. Niewierno\u015b\u0107 ludzko\u015bci wobec \u015bwi\u0119tej tr\u00f3jcy i wobec naszego Kr\u00f3la i Matki Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych jest szokuj\u0105ca, a jednak z przera\u017ceniem zobaczycie przyczyn\u0119 schizmy Ko\u015bcio\u0142a. Synowie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: niewierno\u015b\u0107 wobec bosko\u015bci powoduje, \u017ce ludzkie stworzenie nauki jest zmotywowane do wykorzystania nauki do czynienia z\u0142a w\u0142asnym braciom. Pot\u0119ga militarna najpot\u0119\u017cniejszych mocarstw ma budzi\u0107 wasz\u0105 obaw\u0119, poniewa\u017c trzymaj\u0105 one w swoim posiadaniu bro\u0144, kt\u00f3ra nie zosta\u0142a pokazana ludzko\u015bci, a ma wielk\u0105 moc niszcz\u0105c\u0105. Rodziny zosta\u0142y przekszta\u0142cone w miejsca indywidualizmu i okrucie\u0144stwa; rozczarowania, a nie formacji ani mi\u0142o\u015bci, jako wynik korzystny dla tego, czego oczekiwa\u0142y elity. Cierpienie trwa dla rasy ludzkiej.... Z ziemi wydobywaj\u0105 si\u0119 dziwne d\u017awi\u0119ki, b\u0119d\u0105ce skrzypieniem p\u0142yt tektonicznych przygotowuj\u0105cych si\u0119 do silnych trz\u0119sie\u0144 ziemi. Ziemia odurzy\u0142a si\u0119 grzechami ludzkich pokole\u0144. Jako cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 ludzko\u015bci wiedz\u0105, \u017ce czeka ich straszna trzecia wojna \u015bwiatowa. Ludu Bo\u017cy, mocarstwa rozpalaj\u0105 si\u0119 wzajemnie. Wojny maj\u0105 w sobie w\u0142asne interesy i w tej chwili przewa\u017ca sk\u0105pa gospodarka jednego z mocarstw i ch\u0119\u0107 ekspansji terytorialnej innego mocarstwa, kt\u00f3re rozprzestrzeni\u0142o swoj\u0105 ideologi\u0119 po ca\u0142ej ziemi, podsycaj\u0105c komunizm i rewolucje spo\u0142eczne, kt\u00f3re w ko\u0144cu s\u0105 cz\u0119\u015bci\u0105 preambu\u0142y do wojny. Ludu Bo\u017cy, choroba, kt\u00f3ra szaleje po\u015br\u00f3d ludzko\u015bci, jest cz\u0119\u015bci\u0105 tej cichej wojny, kt\u00f3ra si\u0119 rozpocz\u0119\u0142a, trzeciej wojny \u015bwiatowej. Zwr\u00f3\u0107cie uwag\u0119 na znaki i sygna\u0142y, zobaczcie, jak natura wdziera si\u0119 na ziemi\u0119 i prowadzi cz\u0142owieka do cierpienia. \u017bywio\u0142y nie daj\u0105 wytchnienia. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, b\u0105d\u017acie \u015bwiadomi, \u017ce powstaje spisek przeciwko znanym postaciom \u015bwiatowym, rozp\u0119tuj\u0105c furi\u0119 w\u015br\u00f3d mocarstw. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. Rzym cierpi a\u017c do wyczerpania. W\u0142ochy cierpi\u0105 bardzo. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, nie cofaj\u0105c si\u0119 przed niczym, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, b\u0119d\u0105c czynnymi wykonawcami na podobie\u0144stwo Boskiego dzia\u0142ania i dzia\u0142ania. Praktykujcie braterstwo, karmcie si\u0119 Cia\u0142em i Krwi\u0105 naszego Boskiego Odkupiciela obecnego w \u015bwi\u0119tej Eucharystii, kochajcie nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119, odmawiajcie \u015bwi\u0119ty r\u00f3\u017caniec. Przygotujcie si\u0119 do bycia prawdziwymi dzie\u0107mi, b\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 ponad wszystko, pos\u0142uszni i zachowujcie wiar\u0119, nawet je\u015bli boicie si\u0119 tego, co widzicie. Nie tra\u0107cie wiary. B\u0105d\u017acie wytrwali, nie b\u0142\u0105dz\u0105c w tym, co pozornie \u0142atwe i bezpieczne. Lud Bo\u017cy nigdy nie jest bezradny. Jeste\u015bmy gotowi broni\u0107 was przed mocami piekielnymi, aby\u015bcie nie ulegli z\u0142u. Boskie b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo stale uobecnia si\u0119 na jego wiernych dzieci. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, lecz zachowujcie pewno\u015b\u0107 Boskiej mocy, kt\u00f3ra jest ponad wszelk\u0105 moc\u0105. Nasza Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka stoj\u0105 mocno nad ludzko\u015bci\u0105, kt\u00f3ra pogr\u0105\u017cy si\u0119 w chaosie i w boskim zamy\u015ble wybuchnie w chwili spustoszenia jako Matka Bo\u017cego Mi\u0142osierdzia na pomoc dzieciom Bo\u017cym. W jedno\u015bci \u015bwi\u0119tych serc b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Przygotujcie si\u0119 dzieci Bo\u017ce i nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119 teraz! Przyjmijcie mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 z g\u00f3ry. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":8,"month_string":"February","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear daughter, thank you for listening to my call in your heart. My daughter, pray that the hearts of stone may become flesh again. Humanity has not yet understood that this is a spiritual war between good and evil, between the Church and the anti-Church, between Christ and the Antichrist, between eternal life and eternal perdition. My children, you are exchanging evil for good and good for evil, you are not reacting and do not want to wake up from this demonic torpor, remember that soon you will be before God's judgment.  My children, do not accept everything that comes from evil, but accept only the good, live the Holy Scriptures, approach confession and the Eucharist worthily, without profaning the body of my Son, which is more and more tortured. Jesus and his disciples did not remain silent; follow their example. My children, the West will start a war against Russia and China, these events must unite you and not isolate you because only in this way will you be stronger. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Sehr geehrte Tochter, vielen Dank, dass Sie meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen angeh\u00f6rt haben. Meine Tochter bete, dass die Herzen von Stein wieder fleisch werden. Die Menschheit hat noch nicht verstanden, dass dies ein spiritueller Krieg zwischen Gut und B\u00f6se zwischen der Kirche und der Anti-Kirche zwischen Christus und dem Antichristen ist, zwischen dem ewigen Leben und ewiger Perdition. Meine Kinder, du tauschst das B\u00f6se aus, um gut und gut f\u00fcr das B\u00f6se, du reagierst nicht und wollen nicht von dieser d\u00e4monischen Torpor aufwachen, denken Sie daran, dass Sie bald vor Gottes Urteil sein werden. Meine Kinder akzeptieren nicht alles, was aus dem B\u00f6sen kommt, aber akzeptieren nur das Gute, live die heiligen Schriften, den Anflugkreis und die Eucharistie w\u00fcrdig, ohne den K\u00f6rper meines Sohnes zu profitieren, der immer mehr gefoltert ist. Jesus und seine J\u00fcnger waren nicht still; folge ihrem Beispiel. Meine Kinder, der Westen wird einen Krieg gegen Russland und China beginnen, diese Ereignisse m\u00fcssen Sie vereinen und Sie nicht isolieren, weil Sie nur auf diese Weise st\u00e4rker sein werden. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Querida mi hija, gracias por escuchar mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Mi hija, ora por los corazones de piedra para ser carne. La humanidad, todav\u00eda no ha entendido, que esta es una guerra espiritual entre el bien y el mal, entre la Iglesia y la Iglesia, entre Cristo y el Anticristo, entre la vida eterna y la perdici\u00f3n eterna. Mis hijos, est\u00e1s intercambiando, malvado por el bien y bueno para el mal, no reaccionas y no quiere despertarte de esta tortura demon\u00edaca, recuerde que pronto estar\u00e1 ante el juicio de Dios. Los ni\u00f1os, no aceptan todo lo que Viene del mal, pero solo los buenos aceptados, viven las Escrituras Sagradas, se acercan a la Confesi\u00f3n y la Eucarist\u00eda dignamente, sin perfilar el cuerpo de mi hijo, cada vez m\u00e1s atormentado. Jes\u00fas y sus disc\u00edpulos no estaban en silencio, siguen su ejemplo. Hijos, Occidente har\u00e1 que una guerra estall\u00f3 contra Rusia y China, estos eventos deben unirte y no aislarlo porque solo para que sea m\u00e1s fuerte. Ahora te bendigo en nombre del padre del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Cher fille, merci d'avoir \u00e9cout\u00e9 mon appel dans votre coeur. Ma fille, prie que les c\u0153urs de la pierre deviennent \u00e0 nouveau chair. L'humanit\u00e9 n'a pas encore compris qu'il s'agissait d'une guerre spirituelle entre le bien et le mal, entre l'\u00e9glise et l'anti-\u00e9glise, entre Christ et l'Ant\u00e9christ, entre la vie \u00e9ternelle et la perdition \u00e9ternelle. Mes enfants, vous \u00e9changez du mal pour le bien et le bien pour le mal, vous ne r\u00e9agissez pas et ne voulez pas vous r\u00e9veiller de cette torpeur d\u00e9moniaque, rappelez-vous que vous serez bient\u00f4t devant le jugement de Dieu. Mes enfants, n'acceptent pas tout ce qui vient du mal, mais n'accepte que le bien, vivez les Saintes \u00c9critures, l'approche de la confession et l'Eucharistie dignement, sans profanifier le corps de mon fils, de plus en plus tortur\u00e9. J\u00e9sus et ses disciples ne sont pas rest\u00e9s silencieux; Suivez leur exemple. Mes enfants, l'Occident commenceront une guerre contre la Russie et la Chine, ces \u00e9v\u00e9nements doivent vous unir et ne pas vous isoler car uniquement de cette fa\u00e7on, vous serez plus fort. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cara figlia mia, grazie per aver ascoltato la mia chiamata nel tuo cuore. Figlia mia, prega affinch\u00e9 i cuori di pietra tornino ad essere di carne. L\u2019umanit\u00e0, ancora non ha compreso, che questa \u00e8 una guerra spirituale tra il bene e il male, tra la Chiesa e l\u2019anti-chiesa, tra Cristo e l\u2019anticristo, tra la vita eterna e la perdizione eterna. Figli miei, state scambiando, il male per il bene ed il bene per il male, non reagite e non volete svegliarvi da questo torpore demoniaco, ricordate che presto sarete davanti al giudizio di Dio.  Figli, non accettate tutto ci\u00f2 che viene dal male, ma accettate solo il bene, vivete le Sacre Scritture, accostatevi alla confessione e all\u2019Eucarestia degnamente, senza profanare il corpo di mio Figlio, sempre pi\u00f9 martoriato. Ges\u00f9 e i suoi discepoli, non stavano nel silenzio, seguite il loro esempio.  Figli, l\u2019Occidente far\u00e0 scoppiare una guerra contro la Russia e la Cina, questi eventi devono unirvi e non isolarvi perch\u00e9 solo cos\u00ec sarete pi\u00f9 forti. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dziecko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce wys\u0142ucha\u0142a\u015b w swoim sercu mojego wezwania. Moja c\u00f3rko, m\u00f3dl si\u0119, aby serca z kamienia powr\u00f3ci\u0142y do serc z cia\u0142a. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 nie zrozumia\u0142a jeszcze, \u017ce jest to duchowa wojna mi\u0119dzy dobrem a z\u0142em, mi\u0119dzy Ko\u015bcio\u0142em a anty-Ko\u015bcio\u0142em, mi\u0119dzy Chrystusem a Antychrystem, mi\u0119dzy \u017cyciem wiecznym a wiecznym zatraceniem. Dzieci moje, zamieniacie z\u0142o na dobro, a dobro na z\u0142o, nie reagujecie i nie chcecie si\u0119 obudzi\u0107 z tego demonicznego letargu, pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce wkr\u00f3tce staniecie przed Bo\u017cym S\u0105dem. Dzieci moje, nie przyjmujcie niczego, co pochodzi od z\u0142a, lecz przyjmujcie tylko dobro, \u017cyjcie Pismem \u015awi\u0119tym, przyst\u0119pujcie godnie do spowiedzi i Eucharystii, nie profanuj\u0105c cia\u0142a mojego Syna, kt\u00f3ry jest coraz bardziej um\u0119czony. Jezus i Jego uczniowie nie milczeli, bierzcie z nich przyk\u0142ad. Dzieci moje, Zach\u00f3d rozpocznie wojn\u0119 z Rosj\u0105 i Chinami, te wydarzenia musz\u0105 was zjednoczy\u0107, a nie izolowa\u0107, bo tylko w ten spos\u00f3b b\u0119dziecie silniejsi. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Querida filha, obrigado por ouvir minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Minha filha, ore para que os cora\u00e7\u00f5es de pedra possam se tornar carne novamente. A humanidade ainda n\u00e3o entendeu que esta \u00e9 uma guerra espiritual entre o bem e o mal, entre a Igreja e a anti-igreja, entre Cristo e o Anticristo, entre a vida eterna e a perdi\u00e7\u00e3o eterna. Meus filhos, voc\u00ea est\u00e1 trocando o mal para o bem e bom para o mal, voc\u00ea n\u00e3o est\u00e1 reagindo e n\u00e3o quer acordar desse torpor demon\u00edaco, lembre-se de que logo voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 diante do julgamento de Deus. Meus filhos, n\u00e3o aceitam tudo o que vem do mal, mas aceita apenas o bem, vive as sagradas Escrituras, abordam a confiss\u00e3o e a Eucaristia, sem profanando o corpo do meu filho, o que \u00e9 cada vez mais torturado. Jesus e seus disc\u00edpulos n\u00e3o permaneceram em sil\u00eancio; Siga seu exemplo. Meus filhos, o Ocidente vai come\u00e7ar uma guerra contra a R\u00fassia e a China, esses eventos devem unir voc\u00ea e n\u00e3o isolar voc\u00ea porque s\u00f3 dessa maneira voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 mais forte. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u5fc3\u91cc\u542c\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u77f3\u5934\u7684\u5fc3\u810f\u53ef\u80fd\u518d\u6b21\u53d8\u6210\u8089\u4f53\u3002\u4eba\u7c7b\u5c1a\u4e0d\u6e05\u695a\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u5584\u6076\u4e4b\u95f4\u7684\u7cbe\u795e\u6218\u4e89\uff0c\u6559\u4f1a\u4e0e\u53cd\u6559\u4f1a\u4e4b\u95f4\uff0c\u57fa\u7763\u4e0e\u654c\u57fa\u7763\u4e4b\u95f4\uff0c\u6c38\u751f\u548c\u6c38\u6052\u7684\u706d\u4ea1\u4e4b\u95f4\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4f60\u6b63\u5728\u4e3a\u90aa\u6076\u7684\u597d\u548c\u90aa\u6076\u4ea4\u6362\u90aa\u6076\uff0c\u4f60\u6ca1\u6709\u53cd\u5e94\uff0c\u4e0d\u60f3\u4ece\u8fd9\u4e2a\u6076\u4f5c\u5267\u4e2d\u9192\u6765\uff0c\u8bb0\u4f4f\u5f88\u5feb\u4f60\u4f1a\u5728\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u5224\u65ad\u4e4b\u524d\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e0d\u63a5\u53d7\u6765\u81ea\u90aa\u6076\u7684\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u4f46\u53ea\u63a5\u53d7\u597d\u7684\uff0c\u751f\u6d3b\u7684\u5723\u7ecf\uff0c\u5fcf\u6094\u548c\u5723\u9910\u7684\u4eba\u4eec\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u4eb5\u6e0e\u6211\u513f\u5b50\u7684\u8eab\u4f53\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u8d8a\u6765\u8d8a\u591a\u7684\u6298\u78e8\u3002\u8036\u7a23\u548c\u4ed6\u7684\u95e8\u5f92\u5e76\u6ca1\u6709\u4fdd\u6301\u6c89\u9ed8;\u9075\u5faa\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u4f8b\u5b50\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u897f\u65b9\u5c06\u5f00\u59cb\u53cd\u5bf9\u4fc4\u7f57\u65af\u548c\u4e2d\u56fd\u7684\u6218\u4e89\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e9b\u4e8b\u4ef6\u5fc5\u987b\u56e2\u7ed3\u8d77\u6765\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u5b64\u7acb\u4f60\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u53ea\u6709\u8fd9\u6837\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u66f4\u5f3a\u5927\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":12,"month_string":"February","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: I come with the blessing of our King to address each of your children. Keep yourselves within peace, fraternity, unity and above all, within the love that comes from the Sacred Hearts. It is imperative that every human creature persevere in the faith and be a creature of good, with a soft heart and initiate a radical change of life. As people of God, they must abandon all discord, otherwise, by human will, they will enter into temptation and fall into nauseating waters. How can we make them understand that the time is the moment of the fulfilment of prophecies, which can occur several times in a single moment? People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, I call you to conversion and instead human creatures harbour undue feelings in their hearts, which will not come out until they have a true encounter with our King and Lord Jesus Christ. People of God, receive our King and Lord present in the sacrament of the Eucharist, it is indispensable. The allies of Satan wish to prevent the arrival of our beloved Angel of Peace so that as people of God you will not be protected by him. They must be true children and not bad copies of a true child of God. Faithful people, many of the powers of the world engage in the grievous act of war. By allying themselves with the eagle, some countries seek to be strong. The moment of betrayal will come and the eagle will be abandoned by some of its allies, who unite and in a single act, abandon it, finding itself extremely wounded. Again, they return to the eagle's side when all is chaos and the power of the nations is strengthened. Pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, the devil prepares emissaries to prevent the arrival of our beloved Angel of Peace. Pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, offer your deeds and acts in fraternity to counteract the insidiousness of evil. Pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, pray for humanity, it is surprised by the earthquakes that shake one place and another. Go forward, people of God! With the sword of faith held high! Continue to be confident in the power of prayer. Go forward, in faith, without fear! The protection of my legions attends you. I bless and protect you. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.  ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Przychodz\u0119 z b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem naszego Kr\u00f3la, aby zwr\u00f3ci\u0107 si\u0119 do ka\u017cdego z waszych dzieci. Zachowujcie si\u0119 w pokoju, braterstwie, jedno\u015bci, a przede wszystkim w mi\u0142o\u015bci, kt\u00f3ra pochodzi od Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszych Serc. Konieczne jest, aby ka\u017cde ludzkie stworzenie wytrwa\u0142o w wierze i by\u0142o stworzeniem dobrym, o mi\u0119kkim sercu i zapocz\u0105tkowa\u0142o radykaln\u0105 zmian\u0119 \u017cycia. Jako lud Bo\u017cy musz\u0105 porzuci\u0107 wszelk\u0105 niezgod\u0119, w przeciwnym razie, z woli ludzkiej, wejd\u0105 w pokus\u0119 i wpadn\u0105 w md\u0142e wody. Jak u\u015bwiadomi\u0107 im, \u017ce czas to moment wype\u0142nienia si\u0119 proroctw, kt\u00f3re w jednej chwili mog\u0105 wyst\u0105pi\u0107 kilka razy? Ludu Bo\u017cy, przyjmij naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, wzywam ci\u0119 do nawr\u00f3cenia, a zamiast tego ludzkie stworzenia nosz\u0105 w swoich sercach nienale\u017cne uczucia, kt\u00f3re nie wyjd\u0105 na jaw, dop\u00f3ki nie dojdzie do prawdziwego spotkania z naszym Kr\u00f3lem i Panem Jezusem Chrystusem. Ludu Bo\u017cy, przyjmijcie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana obecnego w sakramencie Eucharystii, jest to niezb\u0119dne. Sprzymierze\u0144cy szatana chc\u0105 zapobiec przybyciu naszego ukochanego Anio\u0142a Pokoju, aby\u015bcie jako lud Bo\u017cy nie byli przez niego chronieni. Musz\u0105 to by\u0107 prawdziwe dzieci, a nie s\u0142abe kopie prawdziwego dziecka Bo\u017cego. Wierny ludu, wiele pot\u0119g \u015bwiata anga\u017cuje si\u0119 w ci\u0119\u017cki akt wojny. Sprzymierzaj\u0105c si\u0119 z or\u0142em, niekt\u00f3re kraje staraj\u0105 si\u0119 by\u0107 silne. Nadejdzie chwila zdrady i orze\u0142 zostanie opuszczony przez niekt\u00f3rych swoich sojusznik\u00f3w, kt\u00f3rzy zjednocz\u0105 si\u0119 i jednym aktem porzuc\u0105 go, znajduj\u0105c si\u0119 w stanie wielkiej rany. Ponownie powracaj\u0105 na stron\u0119 or\u0142a, gdy wszystko jest chaosem i wzmacnia si\u0119 si\u0142a narod\u00f3w. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, diabe\u0142 przygotowuje emisariuszy, aby zapobiec przybyciu naszego ukochanego Anio\u0142a Pokoju. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, ofiarujcie swoje czyny i dzia\u0142ania w braterskiej wsp\u00f3lnocie, aby przeciwdzia\u0142a\u0107 podst\u0119pno\u015bci z\u0142a. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za ludzko\u015b\u0107, jest ona zaskoczona trz\u0119sieniami ziemi, kt\u00f3re wstrz\u0105saj\u0105 jednym miejscem i drugim. Id\u017acie naprz\u00f3d, ludzie Bo\u017cy! Z mieczem wiary trzymanym wysoko! Trwajcie w ufno\u015bci w moc modlitwy. Id\u017acie naprz\u00f3d, w wierze, bez l\u0119ku! Ochrona moich legion\u00f3w towarzyszy wam. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was i chroni\u0119. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.  ","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":12,"month_string":"February","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for having responded to my call in your hearts. Beloved children, I urge you, return to God with genuine faith, do it quickly, do not waste any more time because the time is over. My children, you will see very strange things in your eyes, but I say to you: never be afraid. My children, the times you are going through will be worse, but remember, do not be afraid of the time that is ending, but be joyful of the wonderful world that awaits you. The new Jerusalem will come soon. Children, pray for the powerful of the earth and for the leaders of the Church, that they may avoid the great schism that is about to be. remember that I am Mother and you are My children. Now I bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen geantwortet haben. Geliebte Kinder, ich fordere Sie auf, kehren Sie mit echtem Glauben an Gott zur\u00fcck, machen Sie es schnell, verschwenden Sie nicht mehr Zeit, weil die Zeit vorbei ist. Meine Kinder, du wirst sehr seltsame Dinge in deinen Augen sehen, aber ich sage dir: keine Angst. Meine Kinder, die Zeiten, die Sie durchgehen, werden schlimmer sein, aber denken Sie daran, haben Sie keine Angst vor der Zeit, die endet, sondern sei fr\u00f6hlich der wunderbaren Welt, die Sie erwartet. Das neue Jerusalem wird bald kommen. Kinder, beten f\u00fcr die M\u00e4chte der Erde und f\u00fcr die F\u00fchrer der Kirche, dass sie den gro\u00dfen Schisma vermeiden k\u00f6nnen, der gerade sein soll. Denken Sie daran, dass ich Mutter bin und Sie sind meine Kinder. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen der heiligsten Dreieinigkeit, des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Estimados hijos, gracias por responder a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Hijos adornados, por favor regrese a Dios con fe genuina, pronto obtendr\u00e1 m\u00e1s tiempo porque la hora ha terminado. Mis hijos, ver\u00e1s cosas muy extra\u00f1as a tus ojos, pero te lo digo: nunca temes. Mis hijos, los tiempos en los que vayas a conocer ser\u00e1n peores, pero recordar\u00e1s, no tengas miedo del tiempo que termina, pero s\u00e9 alegre del mundo maravilloso esper\u00e1ndote. El nuevo Jerusal\u00e9n llegar\u00e1 pronto. Hijos, oren por los poderosos de la tierra y para los l\u00edderes de la Iglesia, para evitar el gran cisma que va a ser. Recuerda que soy madre y ustedes son mis hijos. Ahora te bendigo en nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, el padre hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Amen.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, je vous exhorte, retourne \u00e0 Dieu avec une foi v\u00e9ritable, faites-le rapidement, ne gaspillez pas plus de temps parce que le temps est termin\u00e9. Mes enfants, vous verrez des choses tr\u00e8s \u00e9tranges dans vos yeux, mais je vous dis \u00e0 vous: jamais avoir peur. Mes enfants, les fois que vous traversez seront pires, mais rappelez-vous, n'ayez pas peur du temps qui se termine, mais soyez joyeux du monde merveilleux qui vous attend. La nouvelle J\u00e9rusalem viendra bient\u00f4t. Les enfants, prient pour le puissant de la terre et des dirigeants de l'\u00c9glise, qu'ils peuvent \u00e9viter le grand schisme qui est sur le point d'\u00eatre. N'oubliez pas que je suis m\u00e8re et vous \u00eates mes enfants. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9, du p\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli adorati, Io vi prego, ritornate a Dio con la fede genuina, fate presto, non perdete altro tempo perch\u00e9 il tempo \u00e8 finito. Figli miei, vedrete cose molto strane ai vostri occhi, ma Io vi dico: non abbiate mai paura. Figli miei, i tempi in cui andate incontro saranno peggiori, ma ricordate, non abbiate paura del tempo che finisce, ma siate gioiosi del mondo meraviglioso che vi attende. La nuova Gerusalemme arriver\u00e0 presto. Figli, pregate per i potenti della terra e per i vertici della Chiesa, affinch\u00e9 evitino il grande scisma che sta per essere. ricordate che Io sono Madre e voi siete i miei figli. Ora vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, Padre Figlio e Spirito Santo, amen","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, b\u0142agam was, powr\u00f3\u0107cie do Boga z prawdziw\u0105 wiar\u0105, zr\u00f3bcie to szybko, nie tra\u0107cie wi\u0119cej czasu, bo czas si\u0119 sko\u0144czy\u0142. Dzieci moje, ujrzycie rzeczy bardzo dziwne, ale powiadam wam: nigdy si\u0119 nie b\u00f3jcie. Dzieci moje, czasy, kt\u00f3re prze\u017cywacie, b\u0119d\u0105 jeszcze gorsze, ale pami\u0119tajcie, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119 czasu, kt\u00f3ry si\u0119 ko\u0144czy, ale b\u0105d\u017acie rado\u015bni z powodu wspania\u0142ego \u015bwiata, kt\u00f3ry was czeka. Nowa Jerozolima nadejdzie wkr\u00f3tce. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za mo\u017cnych ziemi i za przyw\u00f3dc\u00f3w Ko\u015bcio\u0142a, aby unikn\u0119li wielkiego roz\u0142amu, kt\u00f3ry wkr\u00f3tce nast\u0105pi. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Queridos filhos, obrigado por ter respondido \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Crian\u00e7as amadas, pe\u00e7o a voc\u00ea, retornar a Deus com genu\u00edna f\u00e9, fa\u00e7a isso rapidamente, n\u00e3o perca mais tempo porque o tempo acabou. Meus filhos, voc\u00ea ver\u00e1 coisas muito estranhas em seus olhos, mas eu digo a voc\u00ea: nunca tenha medo. Meus filhos, as vezes que voc\u00ea est\u00e1 passando ser\u00e1 pior, mas lembre-se, n\u00e3o tenha medo do tempo que est\u00e1 terminando, mas seja alegre do mundo maravilhoso que espera por voc\u00ea. O novo Jerusal\u00e9m vir\u00e1 em breve. As crian\u00e7as, oram pelo poderoso da Terra e pelos l\u00edderes da Igreja, que possam evitar o grande cisma que est\u00e1 prestes a ser. Lembre-se que sou m\u00e3e e voc\u00eas s\u00e3o meus filhos. Agora te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Pai e Filho e O Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u6566\u4fc3\u4f60\uff0c\u7528\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u56de\u5f52\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u8fc5\u901f\u505a\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u518d\u6d6a\u8d39\u65f6\u95f4\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u65f6\u95f4\u7ed3\u675f\u4e86\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u4f60\u773c\u4e2d\u975e\u5e38\u5947\u602a\u7684\u4e1c\u897f\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\u5bf9\u4f60\u8bf4\uff1a\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u4f1a\u5bb3\u6015\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4f60\u7ecf\u5386\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\u4f1a\u66f4\u7cdf\uff0c\u4f46\u8bf7\u8bb0\u4f4f\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\u7ed3\u675f\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u5f88\u9ad8\u5174\u662f\u4f60\u7b49\u5f85\u4f60\u7684\u7f8e\u597d\u4e16\u754c\u3002\u65b0\u7684\u8036\u8def\u6492\u51b7\u5c06\u5f88\u5feb\u6765\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e3a\u5730\u7403\u7684\u5f3a\u5927\u548c\u6559\u4f1a\u9886\u5bfc\u4eba\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u53ef\u80fd\u4f1a\u907f\u514d\u5373\u5c06\u6210\u4e3a\u7684\u4f1f\u5927\u7684\u5206\u88c2\u3002\u8bf7\u8bb0\u4f4f\uff0c\u6211\u662f\u6bcd\u4eb2\uff0c\u4f60\u662f\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u6700\u795e\u5723\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\uff0c\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":14,"month_string":"February","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"Message of Jesus 2:00 a.m.: My children, worship your God with all the love you have in your heart, kneel before the King of Kings, talk to Me, I anticipated that when you hear about euthanasia, children against parents, unscrupulous murderers and winds of war, it means that the time is near, but you will not fear if you stay with Me. Pray, for this humanity has pierced my heart and you stand by me so that I may recognize you before my Father. Children and brothers, open your hearts to grace, your ears to hearing, be essential without thinking of the false light of this world. With pride and arrogance, they have destroyed the paradise left to you by My Father. Perverse humanity, not even a little love for Me, yet I took your sins by embracing death as a sacrificial lamb, all was forgiven you. You are living worse than Sodom and Gomorrah and so what do you expect? The time of mercy is at an end and the time of justice will begin. My priests have besmirched and used My Most Holy Name to float heresies and blasphemies. Oh! how great will be their pain! My children, keep me company a little longer and console me with your love and I will reward you generously. I love you and bless you in the Name of the Father, in My Name and in the Holy Spirit. Message of Jesus at 5:00 a.m.: My beloved, this night is so dark, darkness has descended on the whole earth and you, little ones and defenseless, in front of all this, can do nothing, only pray to Our Father to calm all this. Men of the Church are making massacres of hearts, they, instead, who should love, have put aside the Son of God, embracing everything that suits them best. I ask the priests who, in soul and spirit, are still in solidarity with me, to prepare themselves to accept all the sufferings and all the pains that will befall them. Help these distracted and lost sons, I am with you to beg for all this so that no soul is taken away from My Father. My sister, tonight the worst thing my heart could witness happened, even the heads of state do not take positions in My Name and for this reason your suffering will be great. You, with your little prayers and with the light of your soul, have strengthened my heart, return to me so that nothing can harm you. Daughter, the sufferings will be many and strong, but he who opens his heart to My Father has nothing to fear. You, the chosen ones, continue with unceasing prayer so that my pierced heart may have some refreshment. I will lay my hands on those who call upon me and bless them together with their families. Pray with an open heart together with My Mother who is so merciful and so full of love for you. I now bless you in the name of My Father, in My Holy Name and in the Holy Spirit.","text_de":"Botschaft von Jesus 2:00 Uhr: Meine Kinder, verehrt Ihren Gott mit der ganzen Liebe, die Sie in Ihrem Herzen haben, vor dem K\u00f6nig der K\u00f6nige knien, mit mir sprechen, ich erwartete, dass, wenn Sie von Euthanasie, Kinder gegen Eltern, skrupellose Murten und Winde des Krieges, bedeutet das, dass die Zeit in der N\u00e4he ist, aber Sie werden nicht f\u00fcrchten, wenn Sie bei mir bleiben. Beten Sie, denn diese Menschheit hat mein Herz durchbohrt und Sie stehen von mir, damit ich Sie vor meinem Vater erkenne. Kinder und Br\u00fcder \u00f6ffnen Ihre Herzen, um zu greifen, Ihre Ohren zu h\u00f6ren, eigentlich zu sein, ohne an das falsche Licht dieser Welt zu denken. Mit Stolz und Arroganz haben sie das Paradies von meinem Vater an Sie zerst\u00f6rt. Perverse Menschheit, nicht einmal ein bisschen Liebe f\u00fcr mich, doch ich nahm deinen S\u00fcnden, indem ich den Tod als Opferlamm umarmen, alles wurde dir vergeben. Sie leben schlechter als Sodom und Gomorrah und was erwarten Sie also? Die Zeit der Gnade ist am Ende und die Zeit der Gerechtigkeit wird beginnen. Meine Priester haben beschmr\u00fct und benutzt meinen heiligsten Namen, um H\u00e4resies und Blasphemies zu schweben. Oh! Wie gro\u00df wird ihr Schmerz sein! Meine Kinder, halte mich ein wenig l\u00e4nger und tr\u00f6ste mich mit deiner Liebe, und ich werde dich gro\u00dfz\u00fcgig belohnen. Ich liebe dich und segne dich im Namen des Vaters, in meinem Namen und im Heiligen Geist. Botschaft von Jesus um 5:00 Uhr: Mein Geliebter, diese Nacht ist so dunkel, die Dunkelheit hat auf der gesamten Erde herabgestiegen, und Sie, kleine und wehrlos, vor all dem, k\u00f6nnen nichts tun, nur um unseren Vater zu beruhigen alles. M\u00e4nner der Kirche machen Massacres of Hearts, sie sollten stattdessen, der lieben sollte, den Sohn Gottes beiseite legen, alles umarmen, was mit ihnen zu ihnen passt.Ich frage die Priester, die in Seele und Geist immer noch in Solidarit\u00e4t mit mir sind, um sich darauf vorzubereiten, alle Leiden und alle Schmerzen zu akzeptieren, die sie treffen werden. Helfen Sie diesen abgelenkten und verlorenen S\u00f6hnen, ich bin mit Ihnen, um das alles zu betteln, damit keine Seele mein Vater weggenommen wird. Meine Schwester, heute Nacht, das Schlimmste, was mein Herz sein k\u00f6nnte, passierte, auch die Staatsk\u00f6pfe nehmen keine Positionen in meinem Namen, und aus diesem Grund wird dein Leiden gro\u00dfartig sein. Sie, mit deinen kleinen Gebeten und mit dem Licht Ihrer Seele, haben mein Herz gest\u00e4rkt, zur\u00fcckkehren, damit Sie nichts schaden k\u00f6nnen. Tochter, die Leiden, werden viele und stark sein, aber er, der sein Herz meines Vaters \u00f6ffnet, hat nichts zu bef\u00fcrchten. Sie, die Auserw\u00e4hlten, fahren weiterhin mit dem unaufh\u00f6rlichen Gebet, so dass mein durchbohrtes Herz etwas Erfrischung haben kann. Ich werde meine H\u00e4nde auf diejenigen legen, die mich anrufen und sie zusammen mit ihren Familien segnen. Bete zusammen mit einem offenen Herzen zusammen mit meiner Mutter, die so barmherzig ist und so voller Liebe f\u00fcr Sie ist. Ich segne dich jetzt im Namen meines Vaters, in meinem heiligen Namen und im Heiligen Geist.","text_es":"Mensaje de Jes\u00fas a las 2:00 am: mis hijos, ama a tu Dios con todo el amor que tienes en mi coraz\u00f3n, arrod\u00edllate al rey de los reyes, h\u00e1blame, me dijera que cuando se siente a hablar de la eutanasia, los ni\u00f1os contra los padres. , asesinos sin escr\u00fapulos y vientos de guerra, significa que el tiempo est\u00e1 cerca, pero no temes si est\u00e1s conmigo. Ora, porque esta humanidad perfor\u00f3 mi coraz\u00f3n y te sientas a mi lado para que pueda reconocerlo frente a mi padre. Los ni\u00f1os y los hermanos abren tus corazones a Grace, tus o\u00eddos escuchados, ser esenciales sin pensar en la Falsa Luz de este mundo. Con orgullo y orgullo, destruyeron el para\u00edso te dej\u00f3 de mi padre. Humanidad perversa, ni siquiera un poco de amor por m\u00ed, sin embargo, he tomado tus pecados abrazando la muerte como un cordero sacrificial, todo hab\u00eda sido perdonado. \u00bfEst\u00e1s viviendo peor que Sodoma y Gomor y luego, \u00bfqu\u00e9 esperas? El momento de la misericordia est\u00e1 al final y comenzar\u00e1 el momento de la justicia. Mis sacerdotes tienen desagradables y usan mi santo nombre para aletear herej\u00edas y blasfemias. \u00a1Oh! \u00a1Qu\u00e9 genial ser\u00e1 su dolor! Ni\u00f1os, me convierten en una peque\u00f1a compa\u00f1\u00eda y me consola con tu amor y los volv\u00ed a mejorar generosamente. Te amo y te bendice en nombre del Padre, en mi nombre y el Esp\u00edritu Santo. Mensaje de Jes\u00fas a las 5:00 am de la ma\u00f1ana: me am\u00f3, esta ma\u00f1ana tan oscura, la oscuridad cay\u00f3 sobre toda la tierra y tu peque\u00f1o y indefenso, frente a todo esto, no puedes hacer nada, solo orando a nuestro Padre. que coloca todo esto.Los hombres de la iglesia est\u00e1n haciendo masacre de corazones, en cambio, deben amar, dejan de lado al Hijo de Dios, abrazando todo lo que lo hace m\u00e1s c\u00f3modo. Pido a los sacerdotes que, en alma y esp\u00edritu, siguen s\u00f3lidos conmigo, para prepararse para aceptar todo el sufrimiento y todos los dolores que los golpear\u00e1n. Ayuda a estos ni\u00f1os distra\u00eddos y perdidos, estoy contigo para suplicar todo esto porque no se quita alma a mi padre. Mi hermana, esta noche ha sucedido lo peor en lo que mi coraz\u00f3n podr\u00eda ayudar, incluso los jefes de estado no toman posiciones en mi nombre y por esta raz\u00f3n, su sufrimiento ser\u00e1 mucho. T\u00fa, con tus peque\u00f1as oraciones y con la luz del alma, he refrescado mi coraz\u00f3n, vuelve a m\u00ed para que nada pueda escalar. Hija, los sufrimientos ser\u00e1n muchos y fuertes, pero que abre su coraz\u00f3n a mi padre, nada debe temer. Usted, elegido, contin\u00fae con la oraci\u00f3n incesante para que mi coraz\u00f3n haya perforado pueda tener un poco de refresco. Pondr\u00e9 las manos a quienes me invocan y los bendices junto con sus familias. Ore con el coraz\u00f3n abierto junto con mi madre tan misericordiosa y tan llena de amor por ti. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre de mi padre, en mi santo nombre y el Esp\u00edritu Santo.","text_fr":"Message de J\u00e9sus \u00e0 2h00: Mes enfants, adorer votre Dieu avec tout l'amour que vous avez dans votre c\u0153ur, s'agenouillez-vous devant le roi des rois, me parlais, je pr\u00e9vois que lorsque vous entendez parler de l'euthanasie, des enfants contre les parents, des meurtriers sans scrupules, des meurtriers sans scrupules et les vents de guerre, cela signifie que le temps est proche, mais vous ne craignez pas si vous restez avec moi. Priez, car cette humanit\u00e9 a perc\u00e9 mon c\u0153ur et que vous vous tenez par moi pour que je puisse vous reconna\u00eetre devant mon p\u00e8re. Enfants et fr\u00e8res, ouvrent vos c\u0153urs \u00e0 la gr\u00e2ce, vos oreilles \u00e0 entendre, \u00eatre essentielles sans penser \u00e0 la fausse lumi\u00e8re de ce monde. Avec fiert\u00e9 et arrogance, ils ont d\u00e9truit le paradis laiss\u00e9 \u00e0 vous par mon p\u00e8re. L'humanit\u00e9 perverse, pas m\u00eame un peu d'amour pour moi, mais j'ai pris vos p\u00e9ch\u00e9s en embrassant la mort comme un agneau sacrificiel, tout \u00e9tait pardonn\u00e9. Vous vivez pire que Sodome et Gomorrah et que vous attendez-vous? L'heure de la mis\u00e9ricorde est \u00e0 la fin et le temps de la justice commencera. Mes pr\u00eatres ont bafouill\u00e9 et ont utilis\u00e9 mon plus saint nom pour flotter h\u00e9r\u00e9sides et blasph\u00e8mes. Oh! Quelle sera sa douleur! Mes enfants, gardez-moi une petite entreprise un peu plus longtemps et me console avec votre amour et je vous r\u00e9compenserai g\u00e9n\u00e9reusement. Je t'aime et te b\u00e9nisse au nom du p\u00e8re, en mon nom et dans le Saint-Esprit. Message de J\u00e9sus \u00e0 5h00: Ma bien-aim\u00e9e, cette nuit est si sombre, l'obscurit\u00e9 est descendue sur toute la terre et vous, petits et sans d\u00e9fense, devant tout cela, ne peut rien faire, prie seulement notre p\u00e8re de calmer tout \u00e7a. Les hommes de l'\u00e9glise font des massacres de c\u0153urs, ils devraient aimer, qui devraient aimer, ont mis de c\u00f4t\u00e9 le Fils de Dieu, embrassant tout ce qui leur convient le mieux.Je demande aux pr\u00eatres qui, dans l'\u00e2me et l'esprit, sont toujours en solidarit\u00e9 avec moi, de se pr\u00e9parer \u00e0 accepter toutes les souffrances et toutes les douleurs qui vont les arriver. Aidez-vous ces fils distraits et perdus, je suis avec vous de mendier pour tout cela afin que aucune \u00e2me ne soit emmen\u00e9e de mon p\u00e8re. Ma s\u0153ur, ce soir, la pire chose que mon c\u0153ur puisse t\u00e9moigner, m\u00eame les chefs d'\u00c9tat ne prennent pas de positions \u00e0 mon nom et pour cette raison, vos souffrances seront formidables. Avec vos petites pri\u00e8res et avec la lumi\u00e8re de votre \u00e2me, vous avez renforc\u00e9 mon c\u0153ur, revenez-moi pour que rien ne puisse vous nuire. Fille, les souffrances seront nombreuses et fortes, mais celui qui ouvre son c\u0153ur \u00e0 mon p\u00e8re n'a rien \u00e0 craindre. Vous, les choisies, continuez avec une pri\u00e8re incessante pour que mon c\u0153ur perc\u00e9 puisse avoir du rafra\u00eechissement. Je vais poser mes mains sur ceux qui m'appellent et les b\u00e9niront avec leurs familles. Priez avec un coeur ouvert avec ma m\u00e8re qui est si mis\u00e9ricordieuse et si pleine d'amour pour vous. Je vous b\u00e9nes maintenant au nom de mon p\u00e8re, dans mon saint nom et dans le Saint-Esprit.","text_it":"Messaggio di Ges\u00f9 ore 2:00 del mattino: Figli miei, adorate il vostro Dio con tutto l\u2019amore che avete nel cuore, inginocchiatevi al Re dei Re, parlate con me, vi avevo anticipato che quando sentirete parlare di eutanasia, figli contro genitori, assassini senza scrupoli e venti di guerra, significa che il tempo \u00e8 vicino, ma voi non temete se starete con me. Pregate, perch\u00e9 questa umanit\u00e0 ha trafitto il mio cuore e voi statemi accanto cos\u00ec che io vi possa riconoscere davanti al Padre mio. Figli e fratelli aprite i vostri cuori alla grazia, le vostre orecchie all\u2019udito, siate essenziali senza pensare alla luce falsa di questo mondo. Con la superbia e l\u2019orgoglio hanno distrutto il paradiso lasciatovi dal Padre mio.  Umanit\u00e0 perversa, neanche un po\u2019 d\u2019amore per me, eppure Io ho preso i vostri peccati abbracciando la morte come agnello sacrificale, tutto vi era stato perdonato. State vivendo peggio di Sodoma e Gomorra e allora cosa vi aspettate? Il tempo della misericordia \u00e8 alla fine e inizier\u00e0 il tempo della giustizia. I miei sacerdoti hanno infangato e usato il mio Santissimo Nome per far fluttuare eresie e blasfemie. Oh! quanto sar\u00e0 grande il loro dolore! Figli, fatemi ancora un po\u2019 compagnia e consolatemi con il vostro amore ed Io vi ricompenser\u00f2 generosamente. Vi amo e vi benedico nel nome del Padre, nel mio Nome e dello Spirito Santo. Messaggio di Ges\u00f9 ore 5:00 del mattino: Amata mia, questa notte tanto buia, le tenebre sono scese su tutta la terra e voi piccoli e indifesi, davanti a tutto questo, non potete fare nulla, solo pregare il Padre Nostro affinch\u00e9 plachi tutto questo. Uomini della Chiesa stanno facendo stragi di cuori, loro, invece, che dovrebbero amare, hanno messo da parte il Figlio di Dio, abbracciando tutto ci\u00f2 che a loro fa pi\u00f9 comodo. Chiedo ai sacerdoti che, in anima e spirito, sono ancora solidali con me, di prepararsi ad accettare tutte le sofferenze e tutti i dolori che li colpiranno. Aiutate questi figli distratti e persi, Io sono con voi ad elemosinare tutto questo perch\u00e9 nessuna anima venga portata via al Padre mio. Sorella mia, questa notte \u00e8 accaduta la cosa peggiore alla quale il mio cuore potesse assistere, anche i capi di Stato non prendono posizioni nel mio Nome e per questo la vostra sofferenza sar\u00e0 tanta. Voi, con le vostre piccole preghiere e con la luce dell\u2019anima, avete rinfrancato il mio cuore, tornate a me affinch\u00e9 nulla possa scalfirvi. Figlia, le sofferenze saranno tante e forti ma chi apre il proprio cuore al Padre mio nulla deve temere. Voi, scelti, continuate con la preghiera incessante affinch\u00e9 il cuore mio trafitto possa avere un po\u2019 di refrigerio. Io poser\u00f2 le mani su coloro che mi invocano e li benedir\u00f2 insieme alle loro famiglie. Pregate con il cuore aperto insieme a mia Madre tanto misericordiosa e tanto piena d\u2019amore per voi. Ora ti benedico nel nome del Padre mio, nel mio Santo nome e dello Spirito Santo.","text_pl":"Or\u0119dzie Jezusa  - godz. 2.00: Dzieci moje, uwielbiajcie waszego Boga z ca\u0142\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, jak\u0105 macie w sercu, ukl\u0119knijcie przed Kr\u00f3lem kr\u00f3l\u00f3w, rozmawiajcie ze mn\u0105, uprzedzi\u0142em was, \u017ce gdy us\u0142yszycie o eutanazji, dzieciach przeciwko rodzicom, mordercach bez skrupu\u0142\u00f3w i wichrach wojny, to znaczy, \u017ce czas jest bliski, ale nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, je\u015bli pozostajecie ze mn\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, bo to cz\u0142owiecze\u0144stwo przeszy\u0142o moje serce, a wy stoicie przy mnie, abym m\u00f3g\u0142 was rozpozna\u0107 przed moim Ojcem. Dzieci i bracia, otw\u00f3rzcie wasze serca na \u0142ask\u0119, wasze uszy na s\u0142uchanie, b\u0105d\u017acie niez\u0142omni, nie my\u015bl\u0105c o fa\u0142szywym \u015bwietle tego \u015bwiata. Z pych\u0105 i arogancj\u0105 zniszczyli raj pozostawiony wam przez mojego Ojca. Przewrotna ludzko\u015b\u0107, nawet odrobiny mi\u0142o\u015bci do Mnie, a jednak wzi\u0105\u0142em na siebie wasze grzechy, przyjmuj\u0105c \u015bmier\u0107 jako baranek ofiarny, wszystko zosta\u0142o wam odpuszczone. \u017byjecie gorzej ni\u017c w Sodomie i Gomorze, wi\u0119c czego si\u0119 spodziewacie? Ko\u0144czy si\u0119 czas mi\u0142osierdzia, a zacznie si\u0119 czas sprawiedliwo\u015bci. Moi kap\u0142ani zniewa\u017cyli i u\u017cyli Mojego Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszego Imienia, aby szerzy\u0107 herezje i blu\u017anierstwa. O! Jak wielki b\u0119dzie ich b\u00f3l! Dzieci moje, dotrzymajcie mi towarzystwa jeszcze troch\u0119 i pocieszcie mnie wasz\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, a ja wam to hojnie wynagrodz\u0119. Kocham was i b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca, w Imi\u0119 moje i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego. Or\u0119dzie Jezusa na godz. 5.00: Umi\u0142owani moi, ta noc jest tak ciemna, ciemno\u015b\u0107 zst\u0105pi\u0142a na ca\u0142\u0105 ziemi\u0119, a wy, maluczcy i bezbronni, wobec tego wszystkiego nie mo\u017cecie nic zrobi\u0107, tylko modli\u0107 si\u0119 Modlitw\u0105 Pa\u0144sk\u0105, aby to wszystko uspokoi\u0107. Ludzie Ko\u015bcio\u0142a dokonuj\u0105 masakry serc, ale ci, kt\u00f3rzy powinni kocha\u0107, od\u0142o\u017cyli na bok Syna Bo\u017cego, przyjmuj\u0105c wszystko, co im odpowiada. Prosz\u0119 kap\u0142an\u00f3w, kt\u00f3rzy dusz\u0105 i duchem nadal s\u0105 ze mn\u0105 solidarni, aby przygotowali si\u0119 na przyj\u0119cie wszystkich cierpie\u0144 i b\u00f3lu, kt\u00f3re ich spotkaj\u0105. Pom\u00f3\u017c tym rozproszonym i zagubionym synom, jestem z tob\u0105, aby b\u0142aga\u0107 o to wszystko, aby \u017cadna dusza nie zosta\u0142a zabrana od mojego Ojca. Siostro moja, dzi\u015b w nocy sta\u0142a si\u0119 najgorsza rzecz, jakiej moje serce mog\u0142o by\u0107 \u015bwiadkiem; nawet g\u0142owy pa\u0144stw nie zajmuj\u0105 stanowisk w moje Imi\u0119 i dlatego twoje cierpienie b\u0119dzie wielkie. Ty, swoimi ma\u0142ymi modlitwami i \u015bwiat\u0142em swojej duszy, umocni\u0142a\u015b moje serce; wr\u00f3\u0107 do mnie, aby nic nie mog\u0142o ci zaszkodzi\u0107. C\u00f3rko, cierpienia b\u0119d\u0105 liczne i silne, ale kto otwiera swoje serce przed moim Ojcem, nie ma si\u0119 czego obawia\u0107. Wy, wybrani, trwajcie na nieustannej modlitwie, aby moje zranione serce dozna\u0142o pokrzepienia. W\u0142o\u017c\u0119 r\u0119ce na tych, kt\u00f3rzy mnie wzywaj\u0105, i pob\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 ich wraz z rodzinami. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 z otwartym sercem razem z moj\u0105 Matk\u0105, kt\u00f3ra jest tak mi\u0142osierna i tak pe\u0142na mi\u0142o\u015bci do was. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 mojego Ojca, w moje \u015awi\u0119te Imi\u0119 i w Duchu \u015awi\u0119tym.","text_pt":"Mensagem de Jesus 2:00: Meus filhos, adorar seu deus com todo o amor que voc\u00ea tem em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o, ajoelhe-se diante do rei dos reis, fale comigo, eu esperava que quando voc\u00ea oute sobre a eutan\u00e1sia, crian\u00e7as contra os pais, assassinos inescrupulosos E ventos de guerra, isso significa que a hora \u00e9 pr\u00f3xima, mas voc\u00ea n\u00e3o temer\u00e1 se ficar comigo. Ore, pois essa humanidade perfurou meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o e voc\u00ea est\u00e1 por mim para que eu possa reconhec\u00ea-lo antes de meu pai. Crian\u00e7as e irm\u00e3os, abram seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es para gra\u00e7a, seus ouvidos para ouvir, ser essencial sem pensar na falsa luz deste mundo. Com orgulho e arrog\u00e2ncia, eles destru\u00edram o para\u00edso para voc\u00ea pelo meu pai. A humanidade perversa, nem mesmo um pouco de amor por mim, mas eu levei seus pecados, abra\u00e7ando a morte como um cordeiro sacrificial, tudo o foi perdoado. Voc\u00ea est\u00e1 vivendo pior do que Sodoma e Gomorra e ent\u00e3o o que voc\u00ea espera? O tempo da miseric\u00f3rdia est\u00e1 no fim e o tempo da justi\u00e7a come\u00e7ar\u00e1. Meus sacerdotes t\u00eam besunhado e usou meu nome mais sagrado para flutuar as heresias e blasf\u00eamias. Oh! Qu\u00e3o grande ser\u00e1 a dor deles! Meus filhos, mantenha-me companhia um pouco mais e console com seu amor e eu recompensarei voc\u00ea generosamente. Eu te amo e aben\u00e7oe voc\u00ea em nome do pai, em meu nome e no Esp\u00edrito Santo. Mensagem de Jesus \u00e0s 5:00: Minha amada, esta noite \u00e9 t\u00e3o escura, a escurid\u00e3o desceu em toda a terra e voc\u00ea, pequeninos e indefeso, na frente de tudo isso, n\u00e3o pode fazer nada, apenas orar ao nosso pai para acalmar tudo isso. Homens da igreja est\u00e3o fazendo massacres de cora\u00e7\u00f5es, eles, em vez disso, que devem amar, deixar de lado o Filho de Deus, abra\u00e7ando tudo o que lhe convier melhor.Pe\u00e7o aos sacerdotes que, em alma e esp\u00edrito, ainda est\u00e3o em solidariedade comigo, para se preparar para aceitar todos os sofrimentos e todas as dores que acontecer\u00e3o. Ajude estes filhos distra\u00eddos e perdidos, estou com voc\u00ea para implorar por tudo isso para que nenhuma alma seja tirada do meu pai. Minha irm\u00e3, esta noite A pior coisa que meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o poderia testemunhar aconteceu, at\u00e9 mesmo os chefes de estado n\u00e3o tomam posi\u00e7\u00f5es em meu nome e, por essa raz\u00e3o, o seu sofrimento ser\u00e1 \u00f3timo. Voc\u00ea, com suas pequenas ora\u00e7\u00f5es e com a luz da sua alma, fortaleceu meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o, voltasse a mim para que nada possa prejudicar voc\u00ea. Filha, os sofrimentos ser\u00e3o muitos e fortes, mas aquele que abre seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o para meu pai n\u00e3o tem nada a temer. Voc\u00ea, os escolhidos, continuam com a ora\u00e7\u00e3o incessante para que meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o perfurado possa ter algum refresco. Eu vou colocar minhas m\u00e3os naqueles que me chamam e os aben\u00e7oam junto com suas fam\u00edlias. Ore com um cora\u00e7\u00e3o aberto junto com minha m\u00e3e que \u00e9 t\u00e3o misericordiosa e t\u00e3o cheia de amor por voc\u00ea. Eu agora te aben\u00e7oo em nome de meu pai, no meu santo nome e no Esp\u00edrito Santo.","text_zh":"\u8036\u7a23\u7559\u8a002:00\u548c\u6218\u4e89\u7684\u98ce\uff0c\u8fd9\u610f\u5473\u7740\u65f6\u95f4\u8fd1\u5728\u54ab\u5c3a\uff0c\u4f46\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u548c\u6211\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\uff0c\u4f60\u4e0d\u4f1a\u62c5\u5fc3\u3002\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u8fd9\u4e2a\u4eba\u6027\u523a\u7a7f\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u4f60\u7ad9\u5728\u6211\u8eab\u8fb9\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u6211\u5728\u7236\u4eb2\u9762\u524d\u8ba4\u8bc6\u4f60\u3002\u513f\u7ae5\u548c\u5144\u5f1f\u4eec\uff0c\u655e\u5f00\u5fc3\u6249\uff0c\u8ba9\u4f60\u7684\u8033\u6735\u542c\u5230\u542c\u529b\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u8003\u8651\u8fd9\u4e2a\u4e16\u754c\u7684\u865a\u5047\u5149\u660e\u3002\u51ed\u501f\u9a84\u50b2\u548c\u50b2\u6162\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u6467\u6bc1\u4e86\u7236\u4eb2\u7559\u7ed9\u4f60\u7684\u5929\u5802\u3002\u4e0d\u7ecf\u5386\u4eba\u6027\uff0c\u751a\u81f3\u5bf9\u6211\u6765\u8bf4\u751a\u81f3\u6ca1\u6709\u4e00\u70b9\u7231\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\u901a\u8fc7\u5c06\u6b7b\u4ea1\u4f5c\u4e3a\u727a\u7272\u7f94\u7f8a\u5e26\u6765\u4e86\u4f60\u7684\u7f6a\uff0c\u6240\u6709\u4eba\u90fd\u88ab\u539f\u8c05\u4e86\u4f60\u3002\u4f60\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\u6bd4\u592a\u591a\u548c\u86fe\u6469\u62c9\u66f4\u7cdf\u7cd5\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u4f60\u671f\u5f85\u4ec0\u4e48\uff1f\u601c\u60af\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\u662f\u7ed3\u675f\uff0c\u53f8\u6cd5\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\u5c06\u5f00\u59cb\u3002\u6211\u7684\u796d\u53f8\u5df2\u7ecf\u66fe\u7ecf\u66fe\u7ecf\u7528\u8fc7\u6f02\u6d6e\u7684\u5f02\u7aef\u548c\u4eb5\u6e0e\u795e\u59d3\u3002\u54e6\uff01\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u75db\u82e6\u6709\u591a\u68d2\uff01\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8ba9\u6211\u7684\u516c\u53f8\u4fdd\u6301\u4e00\u70b9\uff0c\u8ba9\u6211\u4e0e\u4f60\u7684\u7231\u4fdd\u6301\u6211\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u6177\u6168\u5730\u5956\u52b1\u4f60\u3002\u6211\u7231\u4f60\uff0c\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u5728\u6211\u7684\u540d\u5b57\u548c\u5723\u7075\u4e2d\u3002\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u6d88\u606f\u5728\u51cc\u66685:00\uff1a\u6211\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u591c\u665a\u662f\u5982\u6b64\u9ed1\u6697\uff0c\u9ed1\u6697\u5df2\u7ecf\u4e0b\u964d\u4e86\u6574\u4e2a\u5730\u7403\u548c\u4f60\uff0c\u5c0f\u51b3\u5b9a\uff0c\u5728\u6240\u6709\u8fd9\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u90fd\u53ef\u4ee5\u505a\u4efb\u4f55\u4e8b\u60c5\uff0c\u53ea\u80fd\u5411\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u53ea\u5411\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u53ea\u5411\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u53ea\u5411\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u53ea\u5411\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u53ea\u5411\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u53ea\u7948\u7977\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\u5e73\u9759\u8fd9\u4e9b\u6240\u6709\u3002\u6559\u4f1a\u7684\u7537\u4eba\u6b63\u5728\u5236\u4f5c\u5c60\u6740\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u5e94\u8be5\u7231\u7684\u4eba\uff0c\u629b\u5f03\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u513f\u5b50\uff0c\u62e5\u62b1\u6700\u9002\u5408\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u4e00\u5207\u3002\u6211\u95ee\u5728\u7075\u9b42\u548c\u7cbe\u795e\u4e2d\uff0c\u796d\u53f8\u4eec\u4ecd\u7136\u4e0e\u6211\u56e2\u7ed3\u4e00\u81f4\uff0c\u51c6\u5907\u81ea\u5df1\u63a5\u53d7\u6240\u6709\u75db\u82e6\u548c\u6240\u6709\u4f1a\u964d\u4e34\u5b83\u4eec\u7684\u75db\u82e6\u3002\u5e2e\u52a9\u8fd9\u4e9b\u5206\u6563\u6ce8\u610f\u529b\u548c\u5931\u53bb\u7684\u513f\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u548c\u4f60\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u4e5e\u6c42\u8fd9\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u6ca1\u6709\u7075\u9b42\u4ece\u7236\u4eb2\u5e26\u8d70\u3002\u6211\u59d0\u59d0\uff0c\u4eca\u665a\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\u810f\u53ef\u4ee5\u89c1\u8bc1\u7684\u6700\u7cdf\u7cd5\u7684\u4e8b\u60c5\uff0c\u5373\u4f7f\u662f\u56fd\u5bb6\u7684\u5934\u4e5f\u4e0d\u662f\u6211\u7684\u540d\u5b57\u5360\u636e\u804c\u4f4d\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u8fd9\u4e2a\u539f\u56e0\u4f60\u7684\u75db\u82e6\u4f1a\u5f88\u68d2\u3002\u4f60\uff0c\u7528\u4f60\u7684\u5c0f\u7948\u7977\u548c\u501f\u7740\u4f60\u7684\u7075\u9b42\uff0c\u52a0\u5f3a\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u56de\u5230\u4e86\u6211\uff0c\u8fd9\u6837\u4ec0\u4e48\u90fd\u6ca1\u6709\u4f24\u5bb3\u4f60\u3002\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u75db\u82e6\u4f1a\u5f88\u591a\uff0c\u4f46\u4ed6\u5411\u7236\u4eb2\u6253\u5f00\u4e86\u4ed6\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u4ec0\u4e48\u53ef\u6015\u7684\u3002\u4f60\u662f\u6240\u9009\u7684\uff0c\u7ee7\u7eed\u4e0d\u65ad\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u6211\u7684\u523a\u7a7f\u5fc3\u810f\u53ef\u80fd\u6709\u4e00\u4e9b\u8336\u70b9\u3002\u6211\u4f1a\u628a\u6211\u7684\u624b\u653e\u5728\u90a3\u4e9b\u53eb\u6211\u7684\u4eba\u8eab\u4e0a\uff0c\u4e0e\u5bb6\u4eba\u4e00\u8d77\u795d\u798f\u4ed6\u4eec\u3002\u4e0e\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u4e00\u8d77\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u6bcd\u4eb2\u662f\u5982\u6b64\u4ec1\u6148\uff0c\u5145\u6ee1\u7231\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u3002\u6211\u73b0\u5728\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u5728\u6211\u7684\u5723\u4eba\u540d\u5b57\u548c\u5723\u7075\u4e2d\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":16,"month_string":"February","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people, I bless you. My heart maintains the constant desire to have you in me. Children, I speak to you so that you may keep yourselves in permanent foresight, the madness of the man of power is extreme. They do not analyse the consequences, but allow themselves to act on impulse so that their desires may be fulfilled. They will know of an attack on a leader, of an attack without foundation and this will cause fire to fall upon the earth. My children: the sun in its extreme emanation of fiery streams comes to emanate great heat upon the earth. You will see nature dry up in the midst of extreme heat. Man will feel unable to sustain himself on earth. It is at this time that ignorance goes before mankind, dominated by creatures in powerful hands, who will make my children succumb to the tragedy of the disastrous world war. My children: you must be creatures ready for conversion, but now! Before it is too late... Evil rises, you will think that I abandon you when you see your brothers rise up against me in the middle of the day. The altars in my temples will be destroyed and all that they contain will be eliminated. Human creature wishes to erase every trace of me. It will not succeed; it would be as if it could live without air. It will be a time of pain and hope as I will send my beloved St. Michael the Archangel, guarding my beloved Angel of Peace to sustain you with my word, to call you to continue resisting for the imminent arrival of my mother who will fight evil. My people, keep in mind my faithful Elijah. Convert, prepare yourselves! Faith is indispensable in each of my children so that they may remain without doubting my love for my people. Pray my children, pray for my Church. Pray my children, pray, the earth is shaken stronger. Pray my children, pray and repent, confess sins and live in grace. Pray my children, pray, keep at peace with your brothers. Pray my children, pray of space comes suffering for mankind. Be cautious, my children, come to me, though the majority of mankind declares itself against me. Keep the faith, do not lose it even for an instant. Faith is gold in the hearts, minds and thoughts of mine. Without faith you are nothing, without faith every wind moves you to one side or the other. I bless you my people, I bless you children. My peace be in each of you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.  ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Moje serce podtrzymuje nieustanne pragnienie posiadania was we Mnie. Dzieci, m\u00f3wi\u0119 do was, aby\u015bcie zachowali sta\u0142\u0105 przewidywalno\u015b\u0107, szale\u0144stwo cz\u0142owieka w\u0142adzy jest skrajne. Nie analizuj\u0105 oni konsekwencji, ale pozwalaj\u0105 sobie na dzia\u0142anie pod wp\u0142ywem impulsu, aby ich pragnienia mog\u0142y zosta\u0107 spe\u0142nione. B\u0119d\u0105 wiedzie\u0107 o ataku na przyw\u00f3dc\u0119, o ataku bez podstaw i to spowoduje, \u017ce ogie\u0144 spadnie na ziemi\u0119. Dzieci moje: S\u0142o\u0144ce w swojej ekstremalnej emanacji ognistych strumieni przychodzi, by emanowa\u0107 na ziemi\u0119 wielkie ciep\u0142o. Zobaczycie, \u017ce przyroda wyschnie w\u015br\u00f3d ekstremalnego gor\u0105ca. Cz\u0142owiek b\u0119dzie czu\u0142 si\u0119 niezdolny do utrzymania si\u0119 na ziemi. W\u0142a\u015bnie w tym czasie ignorancja idzie przed ludzko\u015bci\u0105, zdominowan\u0105 przez istoty w pot\u0119\u017cnych r\u0119kach, kt\u00f3re sprawi\u0105, \u017ce moje dzieci ulegn\u0105 tragedii katastrofalnej wojny \u015bwiatowej. Moje dzieci: musicie by\u0107 istotami gotowymi do nawr\u00f3cenia, ale teraz! Zanim b\u0119dzie za p\u00f3\u017ano... Z\u0142o wzbiera, pomy\u015blicie, \u017ce was opuszczam, gdy zobaczycie, jak wasi bracia powstaj\u0105 przeciwko Mnie w \u015brodku dnia. O\u0142tarze w moich \u015bwi\u0105tyniach zostan\u0105 zniszczone i wszystko, co zawieraj\u0105, zostanie wyeliminowane. Ludzkie stworzenie pragnie wymaza\u0107 ka\u017cdy \u015blad po mnie. Nie uda mu si\u0119 to; by\u0142oby to tak, jakby m\u00f3g\u0142 \u017cy\u0107 bez powietrza. B\u0119dzie to czas b\u00f3lu i nadziei, gdy\u017c po\u015bl\u0119 mojego ukochanego Micha\u0142a Archanio\u0142a, strzeg\u0105cego mojego ukochanego Anio\u0142a Pokoju, aby podtrzymywa\u0142 was moim s\u0142owem, aby wzywa\u0142 was do dalszego oporu na zbli\u017caj\u0105ce si\u0119 przyj\u015bcie mojej Matki, kt\u00f3ra b\u0119dzie walczy\u0107 ze z\u0142em. M\u00f3j ludu, pami\u0119taj o moim wiernym Eliaszu nawr\u00f3\u0107 si\u0119, przygotuj si\u0119! Wiara jest niezb\u0119dna w ka\u017cdym z moich dzieci, aby mog\u0142y pozosta\u0107 bez zw\u0105tpienia w moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do mojego ludu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za m\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ziemia jest wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119ta mocniej. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 i pokutujcie, wyznajcie grzechy i \u017cyjcie w \u0142asce. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, zachowujcie pok\u00f3j z waszymi bra\u0107mi. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, z kosmosu przychodzi cierpienie dla ludzko\u015bci. B\u0105d\u017acie ostro\u017cne, moje dzieci, przychod\u017acie do mnie, cho\u0107 wi\u0119kszo\u015b\u0107 ludzko\u015bci o\u015bwiadcza si\u0119 przeciwko mnie. Zachowajcie wiar\u0119, nie tra\u0107cie jej nawet na chwil\u0119. Wiara jest z\u0142otem w sercach, umys\u0142ach i my\u015blach moich. Bez wiary jeste\u015bcie niczym, bez wiary ka\u017cdy wiatr porusza was w jedn\u0105 lub drug\u0105 stron\u0119. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, m\u00f3j ludu, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, dzieci. M\u00f3j pok\u00f3j niech b\u0119dzie w ka\u017cdym z was. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":19,"month_string":"February","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: as prince of the heavenly legions and by Divine Mandate, I share with you and command of your obedience and peace. I call you to be fraternal so that you would help one another. Put the divine calls into practice. Do not only read them, but internalize and bring each call to life; in this way, you will be prepared for the unexpected actions that may present themselves to humanity. Nature continues to advance: man continues to suffer from the elements, which are growing stronger and are becoming more unexpected all the time. Grow through spiritual nourishment \u2014 the holy Eucharist. Be creatures of immovable faith: do not despair at the slightest piece of news. Strengthen yourselves with the love of the most Holy Trinity and of our Queen and Mother of the End Times. The spiritual battle is fierce: it is spread throughout the earth and over all humanity. As your protectors, we deliver you from so many misfortunes, from so many falls, as long as you allow us to do so. The tentacles of the antichrist are moving hastily, inflaming the minds of the leaders of the powers. The core of the war is not what is being presented to you, but rather the economy of the country of the north and the bear\u2019s desire for power. Do not look on the surface, go deeper. (at this moment St. Michael the archangel gives me the vision of a giant bear watching everything that is happening next to it. I look at it and it makes an impression: nothing escapes its notice, it anticipates everything. I also see the eagle that represents the country of the north, going from one place to another; it comes and goes insistently in search of support, but the bear does not need support: it has in its hands a totally unknown weapon, which will help it neutralize its adversaries). St. Michael the Archangel says to me: as the people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ you should have prepared yourselves! And St. Michael the Archangel waves his arms forcefully, saying to me: this generation pays no heed! \u2026 our King and Lord Jesus Christ has been insistent in asking you to prepare yourselves spiritually, to prepare yourselves with food and everything that is absolutely essential, and at the same time to keep personal and other medicines that will be useful for the plague that the devil has prepared. You must have the medicines that heaven has given you in order to overcome the illnesses that will come. Only faith in what the father\u2019s house has revealed to you will heal you, together with the use of the sacramentals. Do not speculate concerning the sacramentals: they all depend on your faith. Use the oil of the good Samaritan, the oil of St. Michael the archangel, calendula for haemorrhagic diseases. It is important that you strengthen your immune system. Daughter, explain to them that I will show you. (St. Michael the archangel shows me the way in which evil will attack us in the midst of the war. First will come spiritual, then material attack on food, clothing, medicines that are essential for some people, together with the restriction of individual freedoms as a result of the new disease). St. Michael the Archangel continues: people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, terrorist attacks will arise again. Do not travel, do not hurry \u2014 wait: it will be extremely dangerous. Disease will be sent through human beings and international means of transport. Be careful. People of God: persevere, be creatures of faith, continue without wavering. 'If God is with you, who is against you?\u201d our Queen and Mother of the end times keeps you under her mantle; she protects you if you obey. I bless you with the love of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.  ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 legion\u00f3w niebieskich i z mandatu Bo\u017cego dziel\u0119 z wami i nakazuj\u0119 wam pos\u0142usze\u0144stwo i pok\u00f3j. Wzywam was do braterstwa, aby\u015bcie sobie wzajemnie pomagali. Wprowadzajcie w \u017cycie te boskie wezwania. Nie tylko czytajcie je, ale zinterioryzujcie i wprowad\u017acie w \u017cycie ka\u017cde wezwanie; w ten spos\u00f3b b\u0119dziecie przygotowani na nieoczekiwane dzia\u0142ania, kt\u00f3re mog\u0105 si\u0119 pojawi\u0107 przed ludzko\u015bci\u0105. Natura wci\u0105\u017c idzie do przodu: cz\u0142owiek wci\u0105\u017c cierpi z powodu \u017cywio\u0142\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re rosn\u0105 w si\u0142\u0119 i staj\u0105 si\u0119 ca\u0142y czas bardziej nieoczekiwane. Wzrastajcie poprzez pokarm duchowy - \u015bwi\u0119t\u0105 Eucharysti\u0119. B\u0105d\u017acie istotami o niewzruszonej wierze: nie rozpaczajcie po najmniejszej wiadomo\u015bci. Umacniajcie si\u0119 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Tr\u00f3jcy i naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych. Walka duchowa jest zaci\u0119ta: toczy si\u0119 na ca\u0142ej ziemi i nad ca\u0142\u0105 ludzko\u015bci\u0105. Jako wasi obro\u0144cy, wybawiamy was od tak wielu nieszcz\u0119\u015b\u0107, od tak wielu upadk\u00f3w, dop\u00f3ki nam na to pozwalacie. Macki antychrysta poruszaj\u0105 si\u0119 pospiesznie, rozpalaj\u0105c umys\u0142y przyw\u00f3dc\u00f3w mocarstw. Sednem wojny nie jest to, co jest wam przedstawiane, ale raczej gospodarka kraju p\u00f3\u0142nocy i nied\u017awiedzia \u017c\u0105dza w\u0142adzy. Nie patrzcie na powierzchni\u0119, si\u0119gnijcie g\u0142\u0119biej. (W tej chwili \u015bw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142 daje mi wizj\u0119 gigantycznego nied\u017awiedzia obserwuj\u0105cego wszystko, co dzieje si\u0119 obok niego. Patrz\u0119 na niego i robi to wra\u017cenie: nic nie umyka jego uwadze, wszystko przewiduje. Widz\u0119 te\u017c or\u0142a, kt\u00f3ry reprezentuje kraj p\u00f3\u0142nocy, przechodz\u0105cego z jednego miejsca na drugie; przylatuje i odlatuje natarczywie w poszukiwaniu wsparcia, ale nied\u017awied\u017a nie potrzebuje wsparcia: ma w r\u0119kach zupe\u0142nie nieznan\u0105 bro\u0144, kt\u00f3ra pomo\u017ce mu zneutralizowa\u0107 przeciwnik\u00f3w). \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142 m\u00f3wi do mnie: jako lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa powinni\u015bcie byli si\u0119 przygotowa\u0107! A \u015bw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142 macha z moc\u0105 r\u0119kami, m\u00f3wi\u0105c do mnie: to pokolenie nie zwraca uwagi! Nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus z naciskiem prosi\u0142 was, aby\u015bcie przygotowali si\u0119 duchowo, aby\u015bcie przygotowali si\u0119 w \u017cywno\u015b\u0107 i wszystko, co jest absolutnie niezb\u0119dne, a jednocze\u015bnie, aby\u015bcie zachowali swoje i inne lekarstwa, kt\u00f3re przydadz\u0105 si\u0119 na zaraz\u0119, kt\u00f3r\u0105 przygotowa\u0142 diabe\u0142. Musicie mie\u0107 lekarstwa, kt\u00f3re da\u0142o wam niebo, aby pokona\u0107 choroby, kt\u00f3re nadejd\u0105. Tylko wiara w to, co objawi\u0142 wam Dom Ojca, uzdrowi was, wraz ze stosowaniem sakramentali\u00f3w. [Nie spekulujcie na temat sakramentali\u00f3w: wszystkie zale\u017c\u0105 od waszej wiary. U\u017cywajcie oleju dobrego Samarytanina, oleju \u015bw. Micha\u0142a Archanio\u0142a, nagietka przy chorobach krwotocznych. Wa\u017cne jest, aby\u015b wzmocni\u0142a sw\u00f3j system odporno\u015bciowy. C\u00f3rko, wyt\u0142umacz im, \u017ce Ja ci poka\u017c\u0119. (\u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142 pokazuje mi spos\u00f3b, w jaki z\u0142o zaatakuje nas w czasie wojny. Najpierw przyjdzie duchowy, potem materialny atak na \u017cywno\u015b\u0107, odzie\u017c, leki, kt\u00f3re s\u0105 niezb\u0119dne dla niekt\u00f3rych ludzi, wraz z ograniczeniem wolno\u015bci jednostki w wyniku nowej choroby). \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142 kontynuuje: ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, ataki terrorystyczne pojawi\u0105 si\u0119 ponownie. Nie podr\u00f3\u017cujcie, nie spieszcie si\u0119 - przeczekajcie: b\u0119dzie to niezwykle niebezpieczne. Choroby b\u0119d\u0105 wysy\u0142ane przez ludzi i mi\u0119dzynarodowe \u015brodki transportu. B\u0105d\u017acie ostro\u017cni. Ludu Bo\u017cy: wytrwajcie, b\u0105d\u017acie istotami wiary, trwajcie bez wahania. \"Je\u015bli B\u00f3g jest z wami, kt\u00f3\u017c jest przeciwko wam?\" nasza Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka czas\u00f3w ostatecznych trzyma was pod swoim p\u0142aszczem; chroni was, je\u015bli b\u0119dziecie pos\u0142uszni. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":19,"month_string":"February","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for having responded to My call in your hearts. My children, I want to keep you always under My blessed mantle to protect you and make you feel My great love. Dear children, be faithful to the Gospel, feed on the body of my Son and His Holy Word, do not turn away from God so as not to be easy prey for the infernal enemy. My children, embrace the hope of new heavens and new earth that await you, entrust everything to Him, do not be executioners of injustice, wait for God's mercy, with the warning many things will change, do not fear. Children, be like true warriors in the front line, fight for the Faith that will make you free and with the weapon of the Holy Rosary in your hands. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, ich m\u00f6chte Sie immer unter meinem gesegneten Mantel halten, um Sie zu sch\u00fctzen, und lassen Sie sich meine gro\u00dfe Liebe f\u00fchlen. Liebe Kinder, seien Sie dem Evangelium treu, f\u00fcttert dem K\u00f6rper meines Sohnes und seines heiligen Wortes, wenden Sie sich nicht von Gott ab, um nicht so ein einfacher Beute f\u00fcr den inneren Feind zu sein. Meine Kinder, umarmen die Hoffnung auf neue Himmel und neue Erde, die Sie erwarten, alles anvertrauen, alles anvertrauen, seien Sie nicht Henker der Ungerechtigkeit, warten Sie nicht um Hilfsmittel von Ungerechtigkeit, warten Sie auf Gottes Barmherzigkeit, mit der Warnung Viele Dinge werden sich \u00e4ndern, nicht f\u00fcrchten. Kinder, sei wie wahre Krieger in der Front, k\u00e4mpfen um den Glauben, der dich frei machen und mit der Waffe des Heiligen Rosenkranzes in deinen H\u00e4nden. Jetzt verlasse ich Sie mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder a mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Ni\u00f1os, siempre te mantengo bajo mi beato Mantle para protegerte y hacerte sentir mi gran amor. Los seres queridos de los ni\u00f1os, ser fieles al Evangelio, alimentar al cuerpo de mi Hijo y su Santa Palabra, no eliminan de Dios para evitar ser una presa f\u00e1cil para el enemigo infernal. Mis hijos, abrazan la esperanza de nuevos cielos y nuevas tierras que te esperan, se conf\u00edan a \u00e9l, no sean jueces de injusticia, espere la misericordia de Dios, con la advertencia que cambiar\u00e1n muchas cosas, no teman. Los hijos, sean tan verdaderos guerreros en la l\u00ednea del frente, luchan por la fe que te har\u00e1 libre y con el arma del Santo Rosario en tus manos. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del padre del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, je veux vous garder toujours sous mon Mantelet b\u00e9ni pour vous prot\u00e9ger et vous faire sentir mon grand amour. Chers enfants, soyez fid\u00e8le \u00e0 l'\u00c9vangile, nourrir le corps de mon fils et de son mot sacr\u00e9, ne se d\u00e9tourne pas de Dieu pour ne pas \u00eatre une proie facile pour l'ennemi infernal. Mes enfants, embrassent l'espoir de nouveaux cieux et de nouvelles terres qui vous attendent, confient tout pour lui, ne sont pas des bourgeons d'injustice, attendent la mis\u00e9ricorde de Dieu, avec l'avertissement de nombreuses choses changeront, ne craignez pas. Les enfants, soyez comme de vrais guerriers en premi\u00e8re ligne, se battent pour la foi qui vous rendra libre et avec l'arme du Saint Rosaire entre vos mains. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, Io voglio tenervi sempre sotto il mio manto benedetto per proteggervi e farvi sentire il mio grande amore. Figli cari, siate fedeli al vangelo, cibatevi del corpo di mio Figlio e della sua Santa Parola, non allontanatevi da Dio per non essere prede facili del nemico infernale. Figli miei, abbracciate la speranza di nuovi cieli e nuova terra che vi attendono, affidate tutto a Lui, non siate giustizieri di ingiustizia, attendete la misericordia di Dio, con l\u2019avvertimento molte cose cambieranno, non temete. Figli, siate come veri guerrieri in prima linea, combattete per la Fede che vi render\u00e0 liberi e con l\u2019arma del Santo Rosario tra le mani. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, chc\u0119 was zawsze trzyma\u0107 pod moim b\u0142ogos\u0142awionym p\u0142aszczem, aby was chroni\u0107 i aby\u015bcie czuli moj\u0105 wielk\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107. Moje drogie dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie wierne Ewangelii, karmcie si\u0119 Cia\u0142em mojego Syna i Jego \u015awi\u0119tym S\u0142owem, nie odwracajcie si\u0119 od Boga, aby nie sta\u0107 si\u0119 \u0142atwym \u0142upem dla piekielnego wroga. Dzieci moje, przyjmijcie nadziej\u0119 nowych niebios i nowej ziemi, kt\u00f3re was czekaj\u0105, powierzcie wszystko Jemu, nie b\u0105d\u017acie katami niesprawiedliwo\u015bci, oczekujcie Bo\u017cego mi\u0142osierdzia, z ostrze\u017ceniem, \u017ce wiele rzeczy si\u0119 zmieni, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119. Dzieci moje, b\u0105d\u017acie jak prawdziwi wojownicy na pierwszej linii frontu, walczcie za wiar\u0119, kt\u00f3ra uczyni was wolnymi, z broni\u0105 R\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ca \u015awi\u0119tego w r\u0119kach. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por ter respondido \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, eu quero mant\u00ea-lo sempre sob o meu manto aben\u00e7oado para proteg\u00ea-lo e fazer voc\u00ea sentir meu grande amor. Queridos filhos, ser fiel ao evangelho, alimentar-se no corpo do meu filho e sua palavra santa, n\u00e3o se afaste de Deus para n\u00e3o ser uma presa f\u00e1cil para o inimigo infernal. Meus filhos, abra\u00e7am a esperan\u00e7a de novos c\u00e9us e nova terra que esperam por voc\u00ea, confiar tudo a ele, n\u00e3o ser carrascos de injusti\u00e7a, espere pela miseric\u00f3rdia de Deus, com a advert\u00eancia muitas coisas mudar\u00e3o, n\u00e3o temem. As crian\u00e7as, sejam como verdadeiras guerreiras na linha de frente, lutem pela f\u00e9 que ir\u00e3o libertar e com a arma do Santo Ros\u00e1rio em suas m\u00e3os. Agora eu deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o maternal em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u60f3\u8ba9\u4f60\u6c38\u8fdc\u5728\u6211\u5e78\u798f\u7684\u5730\u5e54\u4e0b\u4fdd\u62a4\u4f60\uff0c\u8ba9\u4f60\u611f\u53d7\u5230\u6211\u7684\u4f1f\u5927\u7231\u60c5\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5fe0\u4e8e\u798f\u97f3\uff0c\u5582\u517b\u6211\u513f\u5b50\u7684\u8eab\u4f53\u548c\u4ed6\u7684\u795e\u5723\u8bcd\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u8f6c\u5411\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u4ee5\u514d\u5bf9\u5730\u72f1\u654c\u4eba\u8f7b\u677e\u727a\u7272\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u62e5\u62b1\u65b0\u7684\u5929\u5802\u548c\u65b0\u5730\u7403\u7b49\u5f85\u7740\u4f60\uff0c\u59d4\u6258\u4e86\u4ed6\u7684\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u523d\u5b50\u624b\u4e0d\u516c\u6b63\uff0c\u7b49\u5f85\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u601c\u60af\uff0c\u968f\u7740\u8b66\u544a\u5f88\u591a\u4e8b\u60c5\u4f1a\u6539\u53d8\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5c31\u50cf\u524d\u7ebf\u7684\u771f\u6b63\u6218\u58eb\uff0c\u4e3a\u4f60\u624b\u91cc\u6323\u624e\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\uff0c\u8ba9\u4f60\u81ea\u7531\u7684\u6b66\u5668\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":24,"month_string":"February","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart, I hold you within my motherly womb, Ark of Salvation. My beloved ones: you are protected by the merciful love of my son. At this moment the hearts of my children are beating in haste knowing that the drums of war have ceased to beat and, in their place, they hear the roar of the detonations of weapons. My son and this mother we find ourselves in mourning before the suffering of those who are suffering what will spread to the rest of the world. People of my Son, do not retreat, offer all that is within your reach for all humanity. The claws of the devil accelerate the world suffering and the arrival of the antichrist. What they live is the strategy of evil to divide humanity. Offer the holy Eucharist for humanity. As my Son's people do not stop praying, offering, loving the divine will by following the true magisterium of my Son's church and being creatures of good. Beloved children: prepare yourselves and offer yourselves immediately.... Go to the Eucharistic celebration, offer to receive in a state of grace the holy Eucharist for those who suffer the onslaught of the selfish interests of two powers, which will be joined by more nations with desires for power, which is what prevails at this moment. They are living through very difficult times in which the power of prayer will keep them on their feet. It is imperative that you increase your love for the Holy Trinity so that faith will remain firm in you. Selfishness has gone beyond all limits. The lust for power has come to light and what the contending powers were hiding has been made known. The Warning is approaching and you must be creatures of good, love and fraternity, repenting of your errors and beginning a new life. It is never too late, you are not alone, my son protects you. Keep yourselves in unity, love my divine son and be faithful disciples of my son. I keep you in my womb. People of my Son, beloved people, I bless you. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca, trzymam was w moim matczynym \u0142onie, Arce Zbawienia. Umi\u0142owani moi: jeste\u015bcie chronieni mi\u0142osiern\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 mojego Syna. W tej chwili serca moich dzieci bij\u0105 z po\u015bpiechem, wiedz\u0105c, \u017ce b\u0119bny wojenne przesta\u0142y bi\u0107, a na ich miejsce s\u0142ysz\u0105 ryk detonacji broni. M\u00f3j Synu i ta Matka, kt\u00f3r\u0105 znajdujemy w \u017ca\u0142obie przed cierpieniem tych, kt\u00f3rzy cierpi\u0105, co rozprzestrzeni si\u0119 na reszt\u0119 \u015bwiata. Ludu mojego Syna, nie wycofuj si\u0119, ofiaruj wszystko, co jest w twoim zasi\u0119gu dla ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci. Szpony diab\u0142a przyspieszaj\u0105 cierpienie \u015bwiata i nadej\u015bcie antychrysta. To, czym \u017cyj\u0105, to strategia z\u0142a, aby podzieli\u0107 ludzko\u015b\u0107. Ofiaruj za ludzko\u015b\u0107 \u015bwi\u0119t\u0105 Eucharysti\u0119. Jako lud mojego Syna nie przestawajcie modli\u0107 si\u0119, ofiarowywa\u0107, kocha\u0107 wol\u0119 Bo\u017c\u0105, post\u0119puj\u0105c zgodnie z prawdziwym magisterium Ko\u015bcio\u0142a mojego Syna i b\u0119d\u0105c stworzeniami dobra. Umi\u0142owane dzieci: przygotujcie si\u0119 i ofiarujcie si\u0119 natychmiast.... Id\u017acie na celebracj\u0119 eucharystyczn\u0105, ofiarujcie si\u0119, aby przyj\u0105\u0107 w stanie \u0142aski \u015bwi\u0119t\u0105 Eucharysti\u0119 za tych, kt\u00f3rzy cierpi\u0105 z powodu napa\u015bci egoistycznych interes\u00f3w dw\u00f3ch mocarstw, do kt\u00f3rych do\u0142\u0105cz\u0105 kolejne narody z pragnieniami w\u0142adzy, co w tej chwili przewa\u017ca. Prze\u017cywaj\u0105 oni bardzo trudne czasy, w kt\u00f3rych moc modlitwy utrzyma ich na nogach. Koniecznie musicie zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 swoj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej, aby wiara pozosta\u0142a w was mocna. Samolubstwo przekroczy\u0142o wszelkie granice. \u017b\u0105dza w\u0142adzy wysz\u0142a na jaw i to, co skrywa\u0142y walcz\u0105ce si\u0142y, sta\u0142o si\u0119 znane. Ostrze\u017cenie zbli\u017ca si\u0119 i musicie by\u0107 istotami dobra, mi\u0142o\u015bci i braterstwa, \u017ca\u0142uj\u0105c swoich b\u0142\u0119d\u00f3w i rozpoczynaj\u0105c nowe \u017cycie. Nigdy nie jest za p\u00f3\u017ano, nie jeste\u015bcie sami, m\u00f3j Syn was chroni. Utrzymujcie si\u0119 w jedno\u015bci, kochajcie mojego Boskiego Syna i b\u0105d\u017acie wiernymi uczniami mojego Syna. Trzymam was w moim \u0142onie. Ludu mojego Syna, umi\u0142owany ludu, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":24,"month_string":"February","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for kneeling in prayer and answering My call in your heart. My daughter, I know and share your pain. I, Mother of love and sorrow, I suffer so much for not being heard and all this would not have happened. I have repeatedly asked for the consecration of Russia to My Immaculate Heart, but my cry of pain has gone unheard. My daughter, this war will bring death and destruction, the living will not be enough to bury the dead. My children, pray for the consecrated who have abandoned charity, true Faith and morality, desecrating the Body of my Son, driving the faithful to tremendous errors and this will be the cause of terrible suffering. My children, pray, pray, pray very much. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie sich beim Gebet niederschlagen und meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen beantworten. Meine Tochter, ich kenne und teile deinen Schmerz. Ich, Mutter von Liebe und Leid, ich leidet so sehr, dass ich nicht geh\u00f6rt wurde und das alles w\u00e4re nicht passiert. Ich habe wiederholt um die Weihe von Russland zu meinem makellosen Herzen gefragt, aber mein Schmerzschrei ist unbekannt. Meine Tochter, dieser Krieg, wird Tod und Zerst\u00f6rung bringen, der Leben wird nicht genug sein, um die Toten zu begraben. Meine Kinder, beten Sie f\u00fcr den geweihten, der Wohlt\u00e4tigkeitsorganisation, den wahren Glauben und die Moral aufgegeben hat und den K\u00f6rper meines Sohnes entweiht, die treue Faktoren treiben, und dies wird die Ursache des schrecklichen Leidens sein. Meine Kinder, beten, beten, beten sehr viel. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Ni\u00f1os, gracias por doblar las rodillas en oraci\u00f3n y por responder a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mi hija, conozco y comparte su dolor, soy madre de amor y doloroso, sufro tanto como para no haber sido escuchado y todo esto no suceder\u00eda. Pregunt\u00e9 la consagraci\u00f3n de Rusia a mi coraz\u00f3n inmaculado varias veces, pero mi grito de dolor se qued\u00f3 inaudito. Mi hija, esta guerra conducir\u00e1 a la muerte y la destrucci\u00f3n, no ser\u00e1 suficiente para enterrar a los muertos. Mis hijos, oren por los consagrados que han abandonado la caridad, la verdadera fe y la moralidad, descendiendo al cuerpo de mi hijo, empujando a los fieles a errores tremendos y esto causar\u00e1 un terrible sufrimiento. Mis hijos, oren, oran, oren tanto. Ahora te bendigo en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci de s'agenouiller dans la pri\u00e8re et de r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Ma fille, je sais et partagez votre douleur. Moi d'amour et de chagrin, je souffre tellement de ne pas \u00eatre entendue et tout cela n'aurait pas eu lieu. J'ai demand\u00e9 \u00e0 plusieurs reprises la cons\u00e9cration de la Russie \u00e0 mon c\u0153ur immacul\u00e9, mais mon cri de douleur est devenu inou\u00ef. Ma fille, cette guerre apportera la mort et la destruction, la vie ne suffira pas \u00e0 enterrer les morts. Mes enfants, prient pour les consacr\u00e9s qui ont abandonn\u00e9 la charit\u00e9, la vraie foi et la moralit\u00e9, la profanation du corps de mon fils, conduisant les fid\u00e8les \u00e0 des erreurs \u00e9normes et que ce sera la cause des terribles souffrances. Mes enfants, prier, prier, prier beaucoup. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli, grazie per aver piegato le ginocchia nella preghiera e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figlia mia, conosco e condivido il tuo dolore, Io Madre d\u2019amore e addolorata, soffro tanto per non essere stata ascoltata e tutto ci\u00f2 non sarebbe accaduto. Ho chiesto pi\u00f9 volte la consacrazione della Russia al Mio Cuore Immacolato, ma il mio urlo di dolore \u00e8 rimasto inascoltato. Figlia mia, questa guerra porter\u00e0 morte e distruzione, non basteranno i vivi per seppellire i morti. Figli miei, pregate per i consacrati che hanno abbandonato la carit\u00e0, la vera Fede e la moralit\u00e0, dissacrando il Corpo di mio Figlio, spingendo i fedeli ad errori tremendi e questo sar\u00e0 causa di sofferenze terribili. Figli miei, pregate, pregate, pregate tanto. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce ukl\u0119kneli\u015bcie do modlitwy i odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moja c\u00f3rko, znam i podzielam tw\u00f3j b\u00f3l, ja, Matka mi\u0142o\u015bci i smutku, tak bardzo cierpi\u0119, bo gdybym zosta\u0142a wys\u0142uchana, to to wszystko nie mia\u0142oby miejsca. Wiele razy prosi\u0142em o po\u015bwi\u0119cenie Rosji memu Niepokalanemu Sercu, ale moje wo\u0142anie o b\u00f3l pozosta\u0142o niewys\u0142uchane. Moja c\u00f3rko, ta wojna przyniesie \u015bmier\u0107 i zniszczenie; \u017cywych nie wystarczy, by pogrzeba\u0107 umar\u0142ych. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za osoby konsekrowane, kt\u00f3re porzuci\u0142y mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, prawdziw\u0105 wiar\u0119 i moralno\u015b\u0107, bezczeszcz\u0105c Cia\u0142o mojego Syna, prowadz\u0105c wiernych do strasznych b\u0142\u0119d\u00f3w, co b\u0119dzie przyczyn\u0105 strasznych cierpie\u0144. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 bardzo mocno. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por se ajoelhar em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e responder a minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Minha filha, eu sei e compartilho sua dor. Eu, m\u00e3e de amor e tristeza, sofro tanto por n\u00e3o ser ouvido e tudo isso n\u00e3o teria acontecido. Eu tenho repetidamente pedi a consagra\u00e7\u00e3o da R\u00fassia ao meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o imaculado, mas meu grito de dor foi in\u00e9dito. Minha filha, esta guerra trar\u00e1 morte e destrui\u00e7\u00e3o, a vida n\u00e3o ser\u00e1 suficiente para enterrar os mortos. Meus filhos, oram pelo consagrado que abandonaram a caridade, a verdadeira f\u00e9 e moralidade, profanando o corpo do meu filho, dirigindo os fi\u00e9is aos tremendos erros e esta ser\u00e1 a causa do sofrimento terr\u00edvel. Meus filhos, oram, orem, ore muito. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u8dea\u5728\u7948\u7977\u4e2d\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u91cc\u56de\u7b54\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u6211\u77e5\u9053\u5e76\u5206\u4eab\u4f60\u7684\u75db\u82e6\u3002\u6211\uff0c\u7231\u60c5\u548c\u60b2\u4f24\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\uff0c\u6211\u906d\u53d7\u4e86\u8fd9\u4e48\u591a\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6ca1\u6709\u542c\u5230\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u4e0d\u4f1a\u53d1\u751f\u3002\u6211\u4e00\u518d\u8981\u6c42\u4fc4\u7f57\u65af\u7684\u5949\u732e\u7ed9\u6211\u7684\u5b8c\u7f8e\u5fc3\u810f\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\u7684\u75db\u82e6\u54ed\u6ce3\u5df2\u7ecf\u95fb\u6240\u672a\u95fb\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8fd9\u573a\u6218\u4e89\u4f1a\u5e26\u6765\u6b7b\u4ea1\u548c\u6bc1\u706d\uff0c\u751f\u6d3b\u5c06\u4e0d\u8db3\u4ee5\u57cb\u846c\u6b7b\u8005\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u7948\u6c42\u5949\u732e\u7684\u6148\u5584\u673a\u6784\uff0c\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u548c\u9053\u5fb7\uff0c\u4eb5\u6e0e\u6211\u513f\u5b50\u7684\u8eab\u4f53\uff0c\u9a7e\u9a76\u5fe0\u8bda\u7684\u9519\u8bef\uff0c\u8fd9\u5c06\u662f\u53ef\u6015\u75db\u82e6\u7684\u539f\u56e0\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u975e\u5e38\u7948\u7977\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":26,"month_string":"February","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for being here in prayer and for kneeling in this blessed home. Beloved children, do not be afraid, although the times are very bad, the war will also reach Europe and especially Rome, they have turned their backs on God and for this they will suffer suffering and destruction. Beloved children, Jesus is preparing your souls, be more spiritual, otherwise you will be only corpses that mechanically do the same things every day, without ever taking care of the spirit, which at this time is the most important thing. My children, this war is opening the doors to the Antichrist, but do you not understand that things are speeding up? Do you not see that nothing is like before? My children, grant my children true faith, speak of God, I put everything into your hands, pray for peace and for those who will have left the earth because of this war, but many will soon reach Paradise. Dear children, I am with you, together with Jesus, to pray to the Father. Now I bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie hier im Gebet stehen und in diesem gesegneten Zuhause kniend sind. Geliebte Kinder, keine Angst, obwohl die Zeiten sehr schlecht sind, wird der Krieg auch Europa und vor allem Rom erreichen, sie haben ihren R\u00fccken auf Gott gedreht, und daf\u00fcr werden sie Leiden und Zerst\u00f6rung erleiden. Geliebte Kinder, Jesus, bereitet Ihre Seelen vor, sei mehr spiritueller, sonst werden Sie nur Leichen sein, die jeden Tag mechanisch die gleichen Dinge tun, ohne sich jemals um den Geist aufzupassen, was zu diesem Zeitpunkt das Wichtigste ist. Meine Kinder, dieser Krieg, \u00f6ffnet die T\u00fcren dem Antichristen, aber verstehst du nicht, dass die Dinge beschleunigen? Siehst du nicht, dass nichts wie zuvor ist? Meine Kinder, gew\u00e4hren meinen Kindern wahrer Glaube, sprechen Sie von Gott, ich legte alles in die H\u00e4nde, bete f\u00fcr den Frieden und f\u00fcr diejenigen, die die Erde wegen dieses Krieges verlassen haben, aber viele werden bald das Paradies erreichen. Liebe Kinder, ich bin zusammen mit Jesus mit dir zusammen mit Jesus, um zum Vater zu beten. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen der heiligsten Dreieinigkeit, des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y para doblar las rodillas en esta bendita casa. A los ni\u00f1os amados, no tengas miedo, a pesar de que los tiempos son muy feos, la guerra tambi\u00e9n llegar\u00e1 a Europa y, sobre todo, Roma, se volvieron a Dios y por esto sufrir\u00e1n sufrimiento y destrucci\u00f3n. Amados a los ni\u00f1os, Jes\u00fas est\u00e1 preparando tus almas, s\u00e9 m\u00e1s espiritual, de lo contrario, solo ser\u00e1s cad\u00e1veres que mec\u00e1nicamente hacen las mismas cosas todos los d\u00edas, sin tratar con el Esp\u00edritu, que en este momento es lo m\u00e1s importante. Los ni\u00f1os, esta guerra est\u00e1 abriendo las puertas al anticristo, pero \u00bfno entiendes que las cosas se est\u00e1n acelerando? \u00bfNo ves nada m\u00e1s que antes? Mis hijos, le garantizamos la verdadera fe a mis hijos, hablar de Dios, puse todo en tus manos, ore por la paz y para aquellos que han dejado la Tierra que se dejen, pero muchos llegar\u00e1n pronto a Paradise. Ni\u00f1os queridos, estoy contigo, junto con Jes\u00fas, para orar al Padre. Ahora te bendigo en nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Padre, Hijo y Esp\u00edritu Santo.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re et pour agenouiller dans cette maison b\u00e9nie. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, n'ayez pas peur, bien que le temps soit tr\u00e8s mauvais, la guerre atteindra \u00e9galement l'Europe et surtout Rome, ils ont tourn\u00e9 le dos \u00e0 Dieu et pour cela, ils souffriront de la souffrance et de la destruction. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, J\u00e9sus pr\u00e9pare votre \u00e2me, soyez plus spirituel, sinon vous ne serez que des cadavres qui font de la m\u00eame chose chaque jour, sans jamais prendre soin de l'Esprit, ce qui est la plus importante la plus importante. Mes enfants, cette guerre ouvre les portes \u00e0 l'Ant\u00e9christ, mais ne comprenez-vous pas que les choses acc\u00e9l\u00e8rent-elles? Ne voyez-vous pas que rien n'est comme avant? Mes enfants, accorde \u00e0 mes enfants la vraie foi, parlent de Dieu, je mets tout dans tes mains, prie pour la paix et pour ceux qui auront quitt\u00e9 la terre \u00e0 cause de cette guerre, mais beaucoup vont bient\u00f4t atteindre le paradis. Chers enfants, je suis avec vous, avec J\u00e9sus, pour prier le P\u00e8re. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9, du p\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia in questa casa Benedetta. Figli amati, non abbiate paura, nonostante i tempi siano molto brutti, la guerra raggiunger\u00e0 anche l\u2019Europa e soprattutto Roma, hanno girato le spalle a Dio e per questo subiranno sofferenza e distruzione. Figli amati, Ges\u00f9 sta preparando le vostre anime, siate pi\u00f9 spirituali, altrimenti sarete solo cadaveri che meccanicamente fanno le stesse cose tutti i giorni, senza mai occuparsi dello spirito, che in questo momento \u00e8 la cosa pi\u00f9 importante. Figli, questa guerra sta aprendo le porte all\u2019anticristo, ma non capite che le cose si stanno velocizzando? Non vedete che niente pi\u00f9 \u00e8 come prima? Figli miei, garantite voi la fede vera ai miei figli, parlate di Dio, Io rimetto tutto nelle vostre mani, pregate per la pace e per coloro che a causa di questa guerra avranno lasciato la terra, ma molti raggiungeranno presto il paradiso. Figli cari, Io sono con voi, insieme a Ges\u00f9, per pregare il Padre. Ora vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, Padre, Figlio e Spirito Santo.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj na modlitwie i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie w tym b\u0142ogos\u0142awionym domu. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, cho\u0107 czasy s\u0105 bardzo z\u0142e, wojna dotrze tak\u017ce do Europy, a zw\u0142aszcza do Rzymu, kt\u00f3ry odwr\u00f3ci\u0142 si\u0119 od Boga i z tego powodu b\u0119dzie cierpia\u0142 i dozna zniszczenia. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, Jezus przygotowuje wasze dusze, b\u0105d\u017acie bardziej uduchowieni, bo inaczej b\u0119dziecie tylko trupami, kt\u00f3re mechanicznie wykonuj\u0105 codziennie te same czynno\u015bci, nie dbaj\u0105c o ducha, kt\u00f3ry w tym czasie jest najwa\u017cniejszy. Dzieci moje, ta wojna otwiera drzwi dla Antychrysta, ale czy nie rozumiecie, \u017ce sprawy nabieraj\u0105 tempa? Czy nie widzicie, \u017ce nic ju\u017c nie jest takie, jak by\u0142o przedtem? Moje dzieci, wy gwarantujecie prawdziw\u0105 wiar\u0119 moim dzieciom, m\u00f3wcie o Bogu, wszystko sk\u0142adam w wasze r\u0119ce, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 o pok\u00f3j i za tych, kt\u00f3rzy opuszcz\u0105 ziemi\u0119 z powodu tej wojny, ale wielu z nich wkr\u00f3tce dotrze do raju. Drogie dzieci, jestem z wami, razem z Jezusem, aby modli\u0107 si\u0119 do Ojca. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por se ajoelhar nesta casa aben\u00e7oada. Crian\u00e7as amadas, n\u00e3o t\u00eam medo, embora os tempos sejam muito ruins, a guerra tamb\u00e9m alcan\u00e7ar\u00e1 a Europa e especialmente Roma, eles viram as costas em Deus e, por isso, sofrer\u00e3o sofrimento e destrui\u00e7\u00e3o. Crian\u00e7as amadas, Jesus est\u00e1 preparando suas almas, seja mais espiritual, caso contr\u00e1rio, voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 apenas cad\u00e1veres que mecanicamente fazem as mesmas coisas todos os dias, sem cuidar do Esp\u00edrito, que neste momento \u00e9 a coisa mais importante. Meus filhos, esta guerra est\u00e1 abrindo as portas para o anticristo, mas voc\u00ea n\u00e3o entende que as coisas est\u00e3o acelerando? Voc\u00ea n\u00e3o v\u00ea que nada \u00e9 como antes? Meus filhos, conceder meus filhos verdadeira f\u00e9, fala de Deus, eu coloquei tudo em suas m\u00e3os, rezo pela paz e para aqueles que deixar\u00e3o a terra por causa dessa guerra, mas muitos logo chegar\u00e3o ao para\u00edso. Queridos filhos, estou com voc\u00ea, junto com Jesus, orar ao Pai. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Pai e Filho e O Esp\u00edrito Santo.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u7977\u544a\u4e2d\uff0c\u5728\u8fd9\u4e2a\u795d\u798f\u7684\u5bb6\u91cc\u8dea\u4e0b\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u867d\u7136\u65f6\u4ee3\u975e\u5e38\u7cdf\u7cd5\uff0c\u4f46\u6218\u4e89\u4e5f\u5c06\u5230\u8fbe\u6b27\u6d32\uff0c\u7279\u522b\u662f\u7f57\u9a6c\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u5df2\u7ecf\u8f6c\u8fc7\u8eab\u6765\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u4e3a\u6b64\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u906d\u53d7\u75db\u82e6\u548c\u7834\u574f\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8036\u7a23\u6b63\u5728\u51c6\u5907\u4f60\u7684\u7075\u9b42\uff0c\u66f4\u4e3a\u7cbe\u795e\uff0c\u5426\u5219\u4f60\u53ea\u4f1a\u6bcf\u5929\u673a\u68b0\u5730\u505a\u540c\u6837\u7684\u4e8b\u60c5\uff0c\u800c\u6ca1\u6709\u7167\u987e\u7cbe\u795e\uff0c\u8fd9\u5728\u6b64\u65f6\u662f\u6700\u91cd\u8981\u7684\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8fd9\u573a\u6218\u4e89\u6b63\u5728\u5411\u654c\u57fa\u7763\u8005\u6253\u5f00\u95e8\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u4e0d\u660e\u767d\u4e8b\u60c5\u6b63\u5728\u52a0\u5feb\uff1f\u4f60\u6ca1\u6709\u770b\u5230\u4efb\u4f55\u4e1c\u897f\u90fd\u6ca1\u6709\uff1f\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u7ed9\u4e88\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\uff0c\u8c08\u5230\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u6211\u628a\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u653e\u5728\u4f60\u7684\u624b\u4e2d\uff0c\u4e3a\u548c\u5e73\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u8fd9\u573a\u6218\u4e89\uff0c\u90a3\u4e9b\u5c06\u79bb\u5f00\u5730\u7403\u7684\u4eba\uff0c\u4f46\u5f88\u591a\u5f88\u5feb\u5c31\u4f1a\u5230\u8fbe\u5929\u5802\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u548c\u4f60\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u548c\u8036\u7a23\u4e00\u8d77\u7948\u7977\u7236\u4eb2\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u6700\u795e\u5723\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\uff0c\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":2,"day":28,"month_string":"February","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people: my Heart remains open for those who wish to come to me. My Mercy is infinite. I am waiting for you with my Divine Love so that you may be new creatures. My beloved ones: you are living at a time that is leading you towards the fulfilment of all that has been revealed by my House. Even if you see a slight respite, it will not last, due to the arrogance of world leaders with a desire for power. How I grieve over the pain that is increasing for humanity! Pride has no limits, power leads man to use everything he has created to immobilize those whom he regards as his opponents.  As in lairs, they are plotting in order to catch people unawares. Children, where have you left your hearts of flesh? They are killing deliberately in order to increase the war, o humanity, how you are drawing upon yourselves suffering to the point of exhaustion! Children, pray for the Middle East. Children, pray for France. Children, pray for Italy. Children, pray for China. Pray, my children, pray for those who are suffering and mourning at this moment. My people, you will experience the horror that comes from those who maintain plans for conquest. How you make my heart suffer! How many tears I shed for humanity! My children, you are gradually entering further and further into this sad scenario of war, which will grow until it becomes more than purification. You are living, my children, you are living in the insensitivity of those who watch the destruction and lamentation of their fellow men via technological means, as if these were deadly games. You have become so accustomed to fictional death that you are not moved by the anguish of others. My people, war will gallop across the earth in the midst of conflicts and revenge until an unsuspecting humanity is caught by surprised and what has been expected happens... How my heart grieves over this, my children, how it grieves!  I love you, my children, remain on alert. Pestilence is coming, sent anew. My children, be creatures of faith, stay close to me, receive me duly prepared, before my churches are closed. 'Come to me': I love you infinitely. I bless you. You are my children.  Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu: Moje Serce pozostaje otwarte dla tych, kt\u00f3rzy chc\u0105 do Mnie przyj\u015b\u0107. Moje Mi\u0142osierdzie jest niesko\u0144czone. Czekam na was z moj\u0105 Bosk\u0105 Mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, aby\u015bcie byli nowymi stworzeniami. Moi umi\u0142owani: \u017cyjecie w czasie, kt\u00f3ry prowadzi was ku wype\u0142nieniu wszystkiego, co zosta\u0142o objawione przez M\u00f3j Dom. Nawet je\u015bli zobaczycie lekkie wytchnienie, nie b\u0119dzie ono trwa\u0142e, z powodu arogancji \u015bwiatowych przyw\u00f3dc\u00f3w z pragnieniem w\u0142adzy. Jak\u017ce bolej\u0119 nad b\u00f3lem, kt\u00f3ry narasta dla ludzko\u015bci! Pycha nie ma granic, w\u0142adza prowadzi cz\u0142owieka do wykorzystania wszystkiego, co stworzy\u0142, aby unieruchomi\u0107 tych, kt\u00f3rych uwa\u017ca za swoich przeciwnik\u00f3w. Jak w legowisku, knuj\u0105, by zaskoczy\u0107 ludzi. Dzieci, gdzie zostawili\u015bcie wasze serca z cia\u0142a? Zabijaj\u0105 celowo, aby wzm\u00f3c wojn\u0119, o ludzko\u015bci, jak\u017ce \u015bci\u0105gacie na siebie cierpienie a\u017c do wyczerpania! Dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Bliski Wsch\u00f3d. Dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Francj\u0119. Dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za W\u0142ochy. Dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Chiny. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za tych, kt\u00f3rzy w tej chwili cierpi\u0105 i op\u0142akuj\u0105. M\u00f3j ludu, do\u015bwiadczycie horroru, kt\u00f3ry pochodzi od tych, kt\u00f3rzy utrzymuj\u0105 plany podboju. Jak\u017ce sprawiacie, \u017ce moje serce cierpi! Ile \u0142ez wylewam za ludzko\u015b\u0107! Moje dzieci, stopniowo wchodzicie coraz dalej w ten smutny scenariusz wojny, kt\u00f3ra b\u0119dzie ros\u0142a, a\u017c stanie si\u0119 czym\u015b wi\u0119cej ni\u017c oczyszczeniem. \u017byjecie, moje dzieci, \u017cyjecie w nieczu\u0142o\u015bci tych, kt\u00f3rzy ogl\u0105daj\u0105 zniszczenie i lament swoich bli\u017anich za pomoc\u0105 \u015brodk\u00f3w technologicznych, jakby to by\u0142y \u015bmiertelne gry. Tak bardzo przyzwyczaili\u015bcie si\u0119 do fikcyjnej \u015bmierci, \u017ce nie porusza was udr\u0119ka innych. M\u00f3j ludu, wojna b\u0119dzie galopowa\u0107 po ziemi w\u015br\u00f3d konflikt\u00f3w i zemsty, dop\u00f3ki niczego niespodziewaj\u0105ca si\u0119 ludzko\u015b\u0107 nie zostanie zaskoczona i nie stanie si\u0119 to, czego oczekiwano... Jak\u017ce moje serce si\u0119 nad tym smuci, moje dzieci, jak\u017ce si\u0119 smuci! Kocham was, moje dzieci, pozosta\u0144cie w gotowo\u015bci. Nadchodzi zaraza, zes\u0142ana na nowo. Moje dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie istotami wiary, pozosta\u0144cie blisko Mnie, przyjmijcie Mnie nale\u017cycie przygotowanego, zanim moje ko\u015bcio\u0142y zostan\u0105 zamkni\u0119te. \"Przyjd\u017acie do Mnie\": Kocham was niesko\u0144czenie. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Jeste\u015bcie moimi dzie\u0107mi. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":1,"month_string":"March","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children, thank you for bending your knees in prayer and answering my call in your heart. My children, pray for peace in the world, for this war will go on because of world leaders who continue to think only of power and the things of the world. My children, purification will test everyone, be on God's side. Pray for a political leader who will suffer an attack. Pray for the church and for all the innocents, who will wash the sins of humanity with their blood. Pray for the Italian government, because there is a warmonger within it. Pray for France. Pray, because perverse humanity is the cause of all this. Now I bless you, in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Geliebte Kinder, danke, dass Sie Ihre Knie im Gebet biegen und meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen beantworten. Meine Kinder, bete f\u00fcr den Frieden auf der Welt, denn dieser Krieg wird wegen Weltf\u00fchrern weitergehen, die weiterhin nur an Macht und den Dingen der Welt denken. Meine Kinder, Reinigung wird jeden testen, auf Gottes Seite sein. Bete f\u00fcr einen politischen F\u00fchrer, der einen Angriff leiden wird. Beten Sie f\u00fcr die Kirche und f\u00fcr alle Unschuldige, die die S\u00fcnden der Menschheit mit ihrem Blut waschen werden. Beten Sie f\u00fcr die italienische Regierung, denn es gibt einen KarmonGer darin. Bete f\u00fcr Frankreich. Beten Sie, weil perverse Menschheit die Ursache von all dem ist. Jetzt segne ich dich, im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"A los ni\u00f1os amados, gracias por doblar las rodillas en la oraci\u00f3n y por responder a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, oren por la paz en el mundo, porque esta guerra seguir\u00e1 adelante debido a los l\u00edderes mundiales que contin\u00faan pensando solo sobre el poder y las cosas del mundo. Mis hijos, la purificaci\u00f3n se pondr\u00e1 a prueba, estar\u00e1 en el lado de Dios. Ora por un l\u00edder pol\u00edtico que sufrir\u00e1 un ataque. Ore por la Iglesia y por todos los inocentes, que con su sangre lavar\u00e1 los pecados de la humanidad. Ore por el gobierno italiano, porque dentro de \u00e9l hay un warfondo. Ore por Francia. Ora, porque la humanidad perversa se debe a todo esto. Ahora te bendigo, en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Amen.","text_fr":"Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, merci de plier vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re et de r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, prions pour la paix dans le monde, car cette guerre se poursuivra \u00e0 cause des dirigeants mondiaux qui continuent de ne penser que du pouvoir et des choses du monde. Mes enfants, la purification va tester tout le monde, \u00eatre sur le c\u00f4t\u00e9 de Dieu. Priez pour un chef politique qui subira une attaque. Priez pour l'\u00e9glise et pour tous les innocents, qui laveront les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s de l'humanit\u00e9 avec leur sang. Priez pour le gouvernement italien, car il y a une chaleureuse \u00e0 l'int\u00e9rieur. Priez pour la France. Priez, car l'humanit\u00e9 pervers est la cause de tout cela. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Amati figli, grazie per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia nella preghiera e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, pregate per la pace nel mondo, perch\u00e9 questa guerra andr\u00e0 avanti a causa di leader mondiali che continuano a pensare solo al potere e alle cose del mondo. Figli miei, la purificazione metter\u00e0 tutti alla prova, siate dalla parte di Dio. Pregate per un leader politico che subir\u00e0 un attentato.  Pregate per la chiesa e per tutti gli innocenti, che con il loro sangue laveranno i peccati dell\u2019umanit\u00e0. Pregate per il governo italiano, perch\u00e9 all\u2019interno di esso vi \u00e8 un guerrafondaio. Pregate per la Francia. Pregate, perch\u00e9 l\u2019umanit\u00e0 perversa \u00e8 causa di tutto questo. Ora vi benedico, nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie do modlitwy i odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 o pok\u00f3j na \u015bwiecie, poniewa\u017c ta wojna b\u0119dzie trwa\u0142a z powodu przyw\u00f3dc\u00f3w \u015bwiatowych, kt\u00f3rzy nadal my\u015bl\u0105 tylko o w\u0142adzy i o sprawach tego \u015bwiata. Dzieci moje, oczyszczenie b\u0119dzie pr\u00f3b\u0105 dla wszystkich, b\u0105d\u017acie po stronie Boga. M\u00f3dl si\u0119 za przyw\u00f3dc\u0119 politycznego, kt\u00f3ry ucierpi w wyniku zamachu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 i za wszystkich niewinnych, kt\u00f3rzy swoj\u0105 krwi\u0105 zmyj\u0105 grzechy ludzko\u015bci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za rz\u0105d w\u0142oski, poniewa\u017c jest w nim pod\u017cegacz wojenny. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Francj\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, bo przyczyn\u0105 tego wszystkiego jest przewrotna ludzko\u015b\u0107. Teraz ja was b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Crian\u00e7as amadas, obrigado por dobrar os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e responder a minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, oram pela paz no mundo, pois esta guerra continuar\u00e1 por causa dos l\u00edderes mundiais que continuam a pensar apenas em poder e das coisas do mundo. Meus filhos, a purifica\u00e7\u00e3o vai testar todos, estar no lado de Deus. Ore por um l\u00edder pol\u00edtico que sofrer\u00e1 um ataque. Ore pela igreja e por todos os inocentes, que lavar\u00e3o os pecados da humanidade com seu sangue. Ore pelo governo italiano, porque h\u00e1 um warmonger dentro dele. Ore pela Fran\u00e7a. Ore, porque a humanidade perversa \u00e9 a causa de tudo isso. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo, em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u7977\u544a\u4e2d\u5f2f\u66f2\u4f60\u7684\u819d\u76d6\u5e76\u5728\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u91cc\u56de\u7b54\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e3a\u4e16\u754c\u4e0a\u7684\u548c\u5e73\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u8fd9\u573a\u6218\u4e89\u5c06\u7ee7\u7eed\u56e0\u4e3a\u4e16\u754c\u9886\u5bfc\u8005\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u53ea\u7ee7\u7eed\u8ba4\u4e3a\u662f\u4e16\u754c\u7684\u529b\u91cf\u548c\u4e8b\u7269\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u51c0\u5316\u4f1a\u6d4b\u8bd5\u6bcf\u4e2a\u4eba\uff0c\u90fd\u5728\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u8eab\u8fb9\u3002\u7948\u6c42\u5c06\u906d\u53d7\u653b\u51fb\u7684\u653f\u6cbb\u9886\u5bfc\u8005\u3002\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u548c\u6240\u6709\u65e0\u8f9c\u8005\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u5c06\u7528\u8840\u6db2\u6e05\u6d17\u4eba\u7c7b\u7684\u7f6a\u3002\u4e3a\u610f\u5927\u5229\u653f\u5e9c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u5185\u90e8\u6709\u4e00\u4e2a\u8b66\u60d5\u3002\u4e3a\u6cd5\u56fd\u7948\u7977\u3002\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4e0d\u7ecf\u7684\u4eba\u7c7b\u662f\u6240\u6709\u8fd9\u4e00\u5207\u7684\u539f\u56e0\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":3,"month_string":"March","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: as prince of the heavenly armies, I address each one of you in particular. May the Trinitarian blessing be upon each one of you in this very special time of lent. I stand before human creatures with my heavenly armies desirous to stop the great loss of souls who have joined the ranks of the devil. Be at ease and allow us to act in you.... Humanity lives difficult moments for those who possess consciousness and recognize the times and moments of mockery for those who have lost consciousness and have given themselves too evil. There comes a slight pause in this agony of war for the children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ before they suffer from communism throughout the whole world. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, dissent leads to social uprisings to take place in various countries and the journey of the human creature will be more painful on earth. When it happens, look at it as an opportunity for purification, not with terror, but with the certainty of Divine Protection, with faith. Underhanded death comes, a creature of influence falls and sustains the actions of other nations. The dreaded world war emerges, it rides in the Middle East. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ have forgotten that the earth continues to shake, be on alert. This lent in particular: live it by going to the sacraments. Repent, make reparation, offer as much as you can. Become new creatures of faith, hope and charity. Pray with your hearts for suffering humanity. Pray for yourselves that you will not allow evil to dominate your mind and make you prey to its wickedness. Pray for France, it is suffering from communism. Pray for England, it is destabilized. Pray for Spain, war is coming to her. Pray for Argentina, its people are inflamed. The Angel of Peace will come, he will help you, he comes after the public presentation of the antichrist, although he is already watching over you. Without fear, trusting in the Holy Trinity, unite yourselves to our Queen and Mother of the End Times and make reparation for humanity. My legions stand before each of you. Receive my blessing of strength. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 wojsk niebieskich zwracam si\u0119 do ka\u017cdego z was w spos\u00f3b szczeg\u00f3lny. Niech Trynitarne b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo sp\u0142ynie na ka\u017cdego z was w tym szczeg\u00f3lnym czasie Wielkiego Postu. Staj\u0119 przed ludzkimi stworzeniami z moimi niebia\u0144skimi wojskami pragn\u0105cymi powstrzyma\u0107 ogromne straty dusz, kt\u00f3re wst\u0105pi\u0142y w szeregi diab\u0142a. B\u0105d\u017acie spokojni i pozw\u00f3lcie nam dzia\u0142a\u0107 w was.... Ludzko\u015b\u0107 prze\u017cywa trudne chwile dla tych, kt\u00f3rzy maj\u0105 \u015bwiadomo\u015b\u0107 i rozpoznaj\u0105 czasy i chwile szyderstwa dla tych, kt\u00f3rzy stracili \u015bwiadomo\u015b\u0107 i oddali si\u0119 za z\u0142o. Przychodzi lekka przerwa w tej agonii wojennej dla dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, zanim b\u0119d\u0105 cierpie\u0107 z powodu komunizmu na ca\u0142ym \u015bwiecie. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, niezgoda prowadzi do powsta\u0144 spo\u0142ecznych, kt\u00f3re b\u0119d\u0105 mia\u0142y miejsce w r\u00f3\u017cnych krajach i podr\u00f3\u017c stworzenia ludzkiego b\u0119dzie bardziej bolesna na ziemi. Kiedy to si\u0119 dzieje, patrzcie na to jako na okazj\u0119 do oczyszczenia, nie z przera\u017ceniem, ale z pewno\u015bci\u0105 Boskiej Ochrony, z wiar\u0105. Przychodzi podst\u0119pna \u015bmier\u0107, upada istota wp\u0142ywowa i podtrzymuje dzia\u0142ania innych narod\u00f3w. Pojawia si\u0119 straszna wojna \u015bwiatowa, je\u017adzi po Bliskim Wschodzie. Lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa zapomnia\u0142, \u017ce ziemia wci\u0105\u017c si\u0119 trz\u0119sie, b\u0105d\u017acie czujni. Prze\u017cyj ten Wielki Post, przyst\u0119puj\u0105c do sakrament\u00f3w. Nawracajcie si\u0119, czy\u0144cie zado\u015b\u0107uczynienie, ofiarujcie tyle, ile mo\u017cecie. Sta\u0144cie si\u0119 nowymi stworzeniami wiary, nadziei i mi\u0142o\u015bci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 sercem za cierpi\u0105c\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za siebie, aby\u015bcie nie pozwolili z\u0142u zdominowa\u0107 waszego umys\u0142u i uczyni\u0107 was ofiarami jego niegodziwo\u015bci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Francj\u0119, kt\u00f3ra cierpi z powodu komunizmu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Angli\u0119, jest zdestabilizowana. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Hiszpani\u0119, zbli\u017ca si\u0119 do niej wojna. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Argentyn\u0119, jej lud jest rozpalony. Anio\u0142 Pokoju przyjdzie, pomo\u017ce wam, przychodzi po publicznej prezentacji antychrysta, cho\u0107 ju\u017c czuwa nad wami. Bez l\u0119ku, ufaj\u0105c Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej, zjednoczcie si\u0119 z nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0105 czas\u00f3w ostatecznych i dokonajcie zado\u015b\u0107uczynienia za ludzko\u015b\u0107. Moje legiony stoj\u0105 przed ka\u017cdym z was. Przyjmijcie moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo si\u0142y. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":3,"month_string":"March","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts and for bending your knees in prayer. My children, in spite of all that you see around you, you often do not realize and think that the war does not belong to you because it is not at home, but unfortunately this will not be the case, this is the reason for my continuous call to conversion. My children, I beg you, accept all my messages with love, I will guide you so that you do not lose your way, but instead of coming closer to God, you are moving away. My children, the way you have taken is not right, more will come, yet you continue to live your little life without thinking that around you, the devil is destroying everything and you have no care for your souls. Do you believe that this is what life is all about? But do you not believe that there is eternal damnation if you let the devil lead you? My children, pray for the Middle East, the Warning is here. Be ready, children, I beg you. Do not miss confession and the Eucharist, for you must make up for it when you can no longer use them. Give me your hands and I will lead you where there is joy and pure love. I leave you peace and take it to your families. I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen. Our Lady says that she will also bring down graces on those present, especially on a young girl who has a tumor, some of you, today prayed for this intention.","text_de":"Geliebte Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie sich auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen reagieren und um Ihre Knie im Gebet zu biegen. Meine Kinder, trotz allem, was Sie um Sie herum sehen, erkennen Sie oft nicht, dass der Krieg nicht zu Ihnen geh\u00f6rt, weil es nicht zu Hause ist, aber leider ist dies nicht der Fall, dies ist der Grund f\u00fcr meine Kontinuierlicher Anruf zur Konvertierung. Meine Kinder, ich bitte Sie, akzeptiere alle meine Botschaften mit Liebe, ich werde dich dazu f\u00fchren, dass du dich nicht verliere, aber nicht n\u00e4her an Gott kommst, zieht du weg. Meine Kinder, die Art, wie Sie genommen haben Glauben Sie, dass dies das Leben ist, dreht sich alles? Aber glauben Sie nicht, dass es ewige Verdammnis gibt, wenn Sie den Teufel Sie f\u00fchren lassen? Meine Kinder, bete f\u00fcr den Nahen Osten, die Warnung ist hier. Sei bereit, Kinder, ich bitte dich. Verpassen Sie nicht das Gest\u00e4ndnis und die Eucharistie, denn Sie m\u00fcssen es ausmachen, wenn Sie sie nicht mehr verwenden k\u00f6nnen. Gib mir deine H\u00e4nde und ich werde dich dazu bringen, wo Freude und reine Liebe gibt. Ich hinterlasse Ihnen Frieden und bringen Sie es in Ihre Familien. Ich segne dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, amen. Unsere Frau sagt, dass sie auch Gnaden auf den Gegenwart bringen wird, vor allem auf einem jungen M\u00e4dchen, das einen Tumor hat, einige von Ihnen, heute, heute f\u00fcr diese Absicht gebetet.","text_es":"A los ni\u00f1os amados, gracias por responder a mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n y para doblar las rodillas en la oraci\u00f3n. Mis hijos, a pesar de todo lo que ves a tu alrededor, a menudo no te das cuenta y crees que la guerra no te pertenece porque no est\u00e1 en casa, sino que, desafortunadamente, no ser\u00e1 as\u00ed, esta es la raz\u00f3n de mi atractivo continuo para conversi\u00f3n. Ni\u00f1os, por favor, bienvenido todos mis mensajes con amor, lo llevar\u00e9 a no hacer que pierda el camino, pero en su lugar me acercar\u00e9 a Dios, te alejas. Mis hijos, la forma en que emprendes no est\u00e1 bien, vendr\u00e1 otro, sin embargo, contin\u00faas viviendo tu peque\u00f1a vida sin pensar que a tu alrededor, el diablo est\u00e1 destruyendo todo y no te preocupas por tus almas. \u00bfCrees que la vida es todo esto? Pero, \u00bfno crees que existe la condenaci\u00f3n eterna, si te dejas ser guiado por el diablo? Mis hijos, oren por el Medio Oriente, la advertencia est\u00e1 aqu\u00ed. Encuentre listo, ni\u00f1os, por favor. No se pierda la confesi\u00f3n y la Eucarist\u00eda, porque tiene que compensar cuando ya no puede usarlo. Dame tus manos y te llevar\u00e9 donde hay pura alegr\u00eda y amor. Te dejo la paz y lo llevo a tus familias. Te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y del Esp\u00edritu Santo. Am\u00e9n. La Madonna dice que tambi\u00e9n caer\u00e1 gracias a los presentes, especialmente en una ni\u00f1a que tiene un tumor, algunos de ustedes, hoy oraron por esta intenci\u00f3n.","text_fr":"Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs et de plier vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re. Mes enfants, malgr\u00e9 tout ce que vous voyez autour de vous, vous ne r\u00e9alisez souvent pas et pensez que la guerre ne vous appartient pas car ce n'est pas \u00e0 la maison, mais malheureusement, cela ne sera pas le cas, c'est la raison de mes appel continu \u00e0 la conversion. Mes enfants, je vous prie, acceptez tous mes messages avec amour, je vais vous guider afin que vous ne perdiez pas votre chemin, mais au lieu de vous rapprocher de Dieu, vous vous enlevez. Mes enfants, la fa\u00e7on dont vous avez pris n'est pas correct, plus vous viendrez, mais vous continuerez \u00e0 vivre votre petite vie sans penser que autour de vous, le diable d\u00e9truit tout et vous n'avez pas de soin de vos \u00e2mes. Croyez-vous que c'est ce que fait la vie? Mais ne croyez-vous pas qu'il y a une damnation \u00e9ternelle si vous laissez le diable vous conduire? Mes enfants, prient pour le Moyen-Orient, l'avertissement est ici. Soyez pr\u00eat, des enfants, je vous demande. Ne manquez pas la confession et l'Eucharistie, car vous devez le compenser lorsque vous ne pouvez plus les utiliser. Donnez-moi vos mains et je vous m\u00e8nerai o\u00f9 il y a de la joie et du pur amour. Je vous laisse la paix et je l'emm\u00e8ne \u00e0 vos familles. Je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen. Notre-Dame dit qu'elle attirara \u00e9galement les gr\u00e2ces sur les personnes pr\u00e9sentes, surtout sur une jeune fille qui a une tumeur, certaines d'entre vous aujourd'hui pri\u00e9es pour cette intention.","text_it":"Amati figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore e per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia nella preghiera. Figli miei, nonostante tutto ci\u00f2 che vedete intorno a voi, spesso non vi rendete conto e pensate che la guerra non vi appartiene perch\u00e9 non \u00e8 a casa vostra, ma purtroppo non sar\u00e0 cos\u00ec, questo \u00e8 il motivo del mio continuo appello alla conversione. Figli, vi prego, accogliete tutti i miei messaggi con amore, Io vi guider\u00f2 per non farvi perdere la strada, ma voi invece di avvicinarvi a Dio vi allontanate. Figli miei, la via da voi intrapresa non \u00e8 giusta, altro arriver\u00e0, eppure continuate a vivere la vostra piccola vita senza pensare che intorno a voi, il demonio sta distruggendo tutto e non avete cura delle vostre anime. Credete che la vita sia tutta questa? Ma non credete che esiste la dannazione eterna, se vi farete guidare dal demonio? Figli miei, pregate per il Medio Oriente, l\u2019Avvertimento \u00e8 qui. Fatevi trovare pronti, figli, Io vi prego. Non fatevi mancare la confessione e l\u2019Eucarestia, perch\u00e9 dovete compensare quando non potrete pi\u00f9 usufruirne. Datemi le vostre mani e Io vi condurr\u00f2 dove c\u2019\u00e8 la gioia e l\u2019amore puro. Vi lascio la pace e portatela alle vostre famiglie. Vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo. Amen. La Madonna dice che far\u00e0 scendere anche delle grazie sui presenti, in particolare su una ragazza giovane che ha un tumore, qualcuno di voi, oggi ha pregato per questa intenzione.","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie do modlitwy. Moje dzieci, pomimo tego wszystkiego, co widzicie wok\u00f3\u0142 siebie, cz\u0119sto nie przyjmujecie tego do wiadomo\u015bci i my\u015blicie, \u017ce wojna nie jest wasza, bo nie ma jej w domu, ale niestety tak nie b\u0119dzie, to jest pow\u00f3d mojego ci\u0105g\u0142ego wzywania do nawr\u00f3cenia. Dzieci moje, b\u0142agam was, przyjmijcie z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 wszystkie moje or\u0119dzia. B\u0119d\u0119 was prowadzi\u0142a, aby\u015bcie zbli\u017cali si\u0119 do Boga, zamiast si\u0119 gubi\u0107 i b\u0142\u0105dzi\u0107. Dzieci moje, droga, kt\u00f3r\u0105 obrali\u015bcie, nie jest w\u0142a\u015bciwa, nadejdzie co\u015b jeszcze, a jednak nadal \u017cyjecie swoim ma\u0142ym \u017cyciem, nie my\u015bl\u0105c o tym, \u017ce wok\u00f3\u0142 was diabe\u0142 niszczy wszystko, a wy nie dbacie o swoje dusze. Czy wierzysz, \u017ce o to w\u0142a\u015bnie chodzi w \u017cyciu? Czy nie wierzysz, \u017ce wieczne pot\u0119pienie istnieje, je\u015bli pozwolisz, by prowadzi\u0142 ci\u0119 diabe\u0142? Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Bliski Wsch\u00f3d, nadesz\u0142o Ostrze\u017cenie. B\u0105d\u017acie gotowi, dzieci, b\u0142agam was. Nie opuszczajcie spowiedzi i Eucharystii, bo musicie wynagrodzi\u0107 za to, \u017ce nie b\u0119dziecie ju\u017c mogli z nich korzysta\u0107. Podajcie mi wasze r\u0119ce, a ja was poprowadz\u0119 tam, gdzie jest rado\u015b\u0107 i czysta mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107. Pozostawiam wam pok\u00f3j, zabierzcie go do waszych rodzin. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen. Matka Bo\u017ca m\u00f3wi, \u017ce obdarzy \u0142askami tak\u017ce obecnych, a w szczeg\u00f3lno\u015bci m\u0142od\u0105 dziewczyn\u0119, kt\u00f3ra ma nowotw\u00f3r; niekt\u00f3rzy modlili si\u0119 dzi\u015b w tej intencji.","text_pt":"Crian\u00e7as amadas, obrigado por responder ao meu chamado em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e para dobrar os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, apesar de tudo o que voc\u00ea v\u00ea ao seu redor, muitas vezes voc\u00ea n\u00e3o percebe e pensa que a guerra n\u00e3o pertence a voc\u00ea porque n\u00e3o est\u00e1 em casa, mas infelizmente isso n\u00e3o ser\u00e1 o caso, esta \u00e9 a raz\u00e3o para o meu chamada cont\u00ednua para a convers\u00e3o. Meus filhos, eu te imploro, aceito todas as minhas mensagens com amor, vou gui\u00e1-lo para que voc\u00ea n\u00e3o perca o seu caminho, mas em vez de se aproximar de Deus, voc\u00ea est\u00e1 se afastando. Meus filhos, do jeito que voc\u00ea tomou n\u00e3o \u00e9 certo, mais vir\u00e1, mas voc\u00ea continua a viver sua pequena vida sem pensar que ao seu redor, o diabo est\u00e1 destruindo tudo e voc\u00ea n\u00e3o tem cuidado para suas almas. Voc\u00ea acredita que \u00e9 isso que a vida \u00e9 toda? Mas voc\u00ea n\u00e3o acredita que h\u00e1 condena\u00e7\u00e3o eterna se voc\u00ea deixar o diabo te levar? Meus filhos, oram pelo Oriente M\u00e9dio, o aviso est\u00e1 aqui. Esteja pronto, as crian\u00e7as, eu te imploro. N\u00e3o perca confiss\u00e3o e a Eucaristia, pois voc\u00ea deve compensar quando voc\u00ea n\u00e3o pode mais us\u00e1-los. D\u00ea-me suas m\u00e3os e eu vou te levar onde h\u00e1 alegria e amor puro. Eu te deixo paz e levo para suas fam\u00edlias. Eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m. Nossa Senhora diz que ela tamb\u00e9m derrubar\u00e1 gra\u00e7as naqueles presentes, especialmente em uma jovem que tem um tumor, alguns de voc\u00eas, hoje oraram por essa inten\u00e7\u00e3o.","text_zh":"\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u56de\u5e94\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u7977\u544a\u4e2d\u5f2f\u66f2\u819d\u76d6\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5c3d\u7ba1\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u8eab\u8fb9\u770b\u5230\u7684\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u4f60\u7ecf\u5e38\u6ca1\u6709\u610f\u8bc6\u5230\uff0c\u5e76\u8ba4\u4e3a\u6218\u4e89\u4e0d\u5c5e\u4e8e\u4f60\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u4e0d\u5728\u5bb6\u91cc\uff0c\u4f46\u4e0d\u5e78\u7684\u662f\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e0d\u662f\u8fd9\u6837\u7684\uff0c\u8fd9\u5c31\u662f\u6211\u7684\u539f\u56e0\u8fde\u7eed\u8c03\u7528\u8f6c\u6362\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6c42\u6c42\u4f60\uff0c\u63a5\u53d7\u6240\u6709\u4e0e\u7231\u7684\u4fe1\u606f\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u6307\u5bfc\u4f60\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u4f60\u4e0d\u4f1a\u5931\u53bb\u4f60\u7684\u65b9\u5f0f\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u66f4\u63a5\u8fd1\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4f60\u6b63\u5728\u8d70\u5f00\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4f60\u6240\u91c7\u53d6\u7684\u65b9\u5f0f\u662f\u4e0d\u5bf9\u7684\uff0c\u66f4\u613f\u610f\u6765\uff0c\u7136\u800c\u4f60\u7ee7\u7eed\u8fc7\u7740\u4f60\u7684\u5c0f\u751f\u6d3b\u800c\u4e0d\u601d\u8003\u5728\u4f60\u8eab\u8fb9\uff0c\u9b54\u9b3c\u6b63\u5728\u6467\u6bc1\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u4f60\u5bf9\u4f60\u7684\u7075\u9b42\u4e0d\u5173\u5fc3\u4f60\u7684\u7075\u9b42\u3002\u4f60\u76f8\u4fe1\u8fd9\u662f\u751f\u6d3b\u7684\u5168\u90e8\u5417\uff1f\u4f46\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u8ba9\u9b54\u9b3c\u5e26\u9886\u4f60\uff0c\u4f60\u4e0d\u76f8\u4fe1\u6709\u6c38\u6052\u7684\u8bc5\u5492\u5417\uff1f\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e3a\u4e2d\u4e1c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u8b66\u544a\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u3002\u51c6\u5907\u597d\uff0c\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6c42\u6c42\u4f60\u3002\u4e0d\u8981\u9519\u8fc7\u5fcf\u6094\u548c\u5723\u9910\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4f60\u5fc5\u987b\u5728\u4e0d\u518d\u4f7f\u7528\u5b83\u4eec\u65f6\u5f25\u8865\u5b83\u3002\u7ed9\u6211\u4f60\u7684\u624b\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u5e26\u7ed9\u4f60\u5728\u54ea\u91cc\u6709\u5feb\u4e50\u548c\u7eaf\u6d01\u7684\u7231\u3002\u6211\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u4f60\u7684\u548c\u5e73\uff0c\u628a\u5b83\u5e26\u5230\u4f60\u7684\u5bb6\u5ead\u3002\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u592b\u4eba\u8bf4\uff0c\u5979\u4e5f\u5c06\u5bf9\u90a3\u4e9b\u793c\u7269\u5e26\u6765\u7684\u8363\u8a89\uff0c\u7279\u522b\u662f\u5728\u4e00\u4e2a\u6709\u80bf\u7624\u7684\u5e74\u8f7b\u5973\u5b69\uff0c\u4f60\u4eec\u4e2d\u7684\u4e00\u4e9b\u4eba\uff0c\u4eca\u5929\u4e3a\u8fd9\u4e2a\u610f\u56fe\u7948\u7977\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":7,"month_string":"March","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved children: receive my blessing in this time of turmoil. You are my people and I protect you all. I call you to remain attentive, in a state of spiritual alertness before the snares of the devil upon you. Pride accompanies the human creature and dominates him, leading him to fall into grave faults, disobedience and injustice towards his brothers. That bad counsellor annuls the fear of me and elevates the human ego to unthinkable levels. If you wish to be love, you must banish such a bad companion so that she does not turn your heart into stone. During this lent I call you to examine yourselves deeply so that you may place your actions and the reaction you receive from your brothers and sisters on a scale and thus be able to discern if you possess this evil. If you possess pride, you are not lost if you intend to convert. This lent is special... I have opened my mercy to all my children so that as many of my children as possible may enter into it, due to what is happening and will happen to humanity. My spirit remains attentive to the good will of mankind, whom I call to pacify themselves spiritually. In the midst of great human evils, I give them great eternal goods if they are merciful and creatures of faith. Love for your neighbour is indispensable, perfect yourselves in humility. As much as you must make amends to your brothers and sisters, do it now, do not put it off until tomorrow. My people: this is a time of great spiritual battle. You well know that this battle is of a spiritual order, it is between good and evil. You need to exhale as much good as possible so that evil does not eat away at your insides and incline you to vomit the evil insidiousness of the oppressor of souls on your brothers. Many live the fruits of disobedience to my Mother's request. My children with hardened hearts continued to overshadow my mother and to ignore her.... That is what the devil desired and the human creature granted it to him.... My people, know me in Sacred Scripture. It is necessary for my people to know me, to scrutinize my word and thus subject every moment to the fulfilment of my word and be witnesses of the Gospel. Come to me! I desire to nourish you with my body and blood and as witnesses of my will, you must remain with firm faith, convinced and converted. In the face of what is approaching, it is necessary that the faith of my people be strengthened by receiving me in the Eucharist and through the prayer of the holy rosary, that they remain by the hand of my mother. My people will be victorious. My cross is what gives victory to my children, not weapons. Pray children, pray for France, she suffers because of the war. Pray children, pray, you will live the horrors of human cruelty. Pray children, pray for Spain is taken by surprise. Pray children, pray for Italy, rivers of blood flow in the waters of its rivers. Pray children, pray, China will rise against Russia to the astonishment of the world. My mother is treasure for my people and she will bring you my Angel of Peace. My children: receive my blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Moje ukochane dzieci: przyjmijcie moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo w tym czasie zamieszania. Jeste\u015bcie moim ludem i chroni\u0119 was wszystkich. Wzywam was, aby\u015bcie pozostali uwa\u017cni, w stanie duchowej czujno\u015bci przed zastawionymi na was sid\u0142ami diab\u0142a. Pycha towarzyszy ludzkiemu stworzeniu i dominuje nad nim, prowadz\u0105c go do popadania w powa\u017cne b\u0142\u0119dy, niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwo i niesprawiedliwo\u015b\u0107 wobec braci. Ten z\u0142y doradca uniewa\u017cnia strach przede Mn\u0105 i wynosi ludzkie ego na niewyobra\u017calne poziomy. Je\u015bli chcecie by\u0107 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, musicie wygna\u0107 tak\u0105 z\u0142\u0105 towarzyszk\u0119, aby nie zamieni\u0142a waszego serca w kamie\u0144. Podczas tego postu wzywam was do g\u0142\u0119bokiego zbadania siebie, aby\u015bcie mogli umie\u015bci\u0107 swoje dzia\u0142ania i reakcje, kt\u00f3re otrzymujecie od waszych braci i si\u00f3str na skali i w ten spos\u00f3b by\u0107 w stanie rozpozna\u0107, czy posiadacie to z\u0142o. Je\u015bli posiadacie pych\u0119, nie jeste\u015bcie straceni, je\u015bli zamierzacie si\u0119 nawr\u00f3ci\u0107. Ten Wielki Post jest szczeg\u00f3lny... Otworzy\u0142am moje Mi\u0142osierdzie dla wszystkich moich dzieci, aby jak najwi\u0119cej moich dzieci mog\u0142o w nie wej\u015b\u0107, ze wzgl\u0119du na to, co dzieje si\u0119 i b\u0119dzie si\u0119 dzia\u0142o z ludzko\u015bci\u0105. Duch m\u00f3j pozostaje czujny na dobr\u0105 wol\u0119 ludzko\u015bci, kt\u00f3r\u0105 wzywam do duchowej pacyfikacji. Po\u015br\u00f3d wielkiego z\u0142a ludzkiego daj\u0119 im wielkie dobra wieczne, je\u015bli s\u0105 mi\u0142osierni i s\u0105 stworzeniami wiary. Mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do bli\u017aniego jest nieodzowna, doskonalcie si\u0119 w pokorze. O ile musicie zado\u015b\u0107uczyni\u0107 swoim braciom i siostrom, zr\u00f3bcie to teraz, nie odk\u0142adajcie tego na jutro. M\u00f3j ludu, jest to czas wielkiej walki duchowej. Wiecie dobrze, \u017ce ta walka jest w porz\u0105dku duchowym, jest mi\u0119dzy dobrem a z\u0142em. Musicie wydycha\u0107 jak najwi\u0119cej dobra, aby z\u0142o nie z\u017cera\u0142o waszych wn\u0119trzno\u015bci i nie sk\u0142ania\u0142o was do wymiotowania na waszych braci z\u0142ych podst\u0119p\u00f3w ciemi\u0119\u017cyciela dusz. Wielu \u017cyje owocami niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwa wobec pro\u015bby mojej Matki. Moje dzieci o zatwardzia\u0142ych sercach nadal przy\u0107miewa\u0142y moj\u0105 Matk\u0119 i ignorowa\u0142y j\u0105.... Tego w\u0142a\u015bnie pragn\u0105\u0142 diabe\u0142, a ludzkie stworzenie mu to przyzna\u0142o.... M\u00f3j ludu, poznaj Mnie w Pi\u015bmie \u015awi\u0119tym. Konieczne jest, aby m\u00f3j lud zna\u0142 Mnie, bada\u0142 moje s\u0142owo i w ten spos\u00f3b podporz\u0105dkowywa\u0142 ka\u017cd\u0105 chwil\u0119 wype\u0142nieniu mojego s\u0142owa i by\u0142 \u015bwiadkiem Ewangelii. Przyjd\u017acie do mnie! Pragn\u0119 karmi\u0107 was moim Cia\u0142em i Krwi\u0105, a jako \u015bwiadkowie mojej woli musicie pozosta\u0107 z mocn\u0105 wiar\u0105, przekonani i nawr\u00f3ceni. W obliczu tego, co si\u0119 zbli\u017ca, konieczne jest, aby wiara mojego ludu zosta\u0142a wzmocniona przez przyj\u0119cie mnie w Eucharystii i przez modlitw\u0119 r\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ca \u015bwi\u0119tego, aby pozostawa\u0142 on przy r\u0119ce mojej Matki. M\u00f3j lud b\u0119dzie zwyci\u0119ski. M\u00f3j krzy\u017c jest tym, co daje zwyci\u0119stwo moim dzieciom, nie bro\u0144. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Francj\u0119, ona cierpi z powodu wojny. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, b\u0119dziecie \u017cy\u0107 okropno\u015bciami ludzkiego okrucie\u0144stwa. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Hiszpani\u0119 jest wzi\u0119ta z zaskoczenia. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za W\u0142ochy, w wodach ich rzek p\u0142yn\u0105 rzeki krwi. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, Chiny powstan\u0105 przeciwko Rosji ku zdumieniu \u015bwiata. Moja Matka jest skarbem dla mojego ludu i przyniesie wam mojego Anio\u0142a Pokoju. Moje dzieci: przyjmijcie moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":8,"month_string":"March","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear daughter, thank you for accepting my call in your heart. Daughter, I beg you to ask all My children to remove the pride that still rages in their hearts. Enough with the discord that drives away the brothers and enough with arrogance, but bend your knees to the Lord. Repent my children, it is not too late, repent to the end and do not be tempted by the devil because his cunning is sharp. Pray for the world, for there will be no more peace, do penance dear children, it is no longer time to live for the things of the world, but raise your eyes to heaven and be more spiritual, your elevation will bring you only benefits. The earth is now made up of a perverse humanity deaf to my calls as a Mother. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father, the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Sehr geehrte Tochter, danke, dass Sie meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen angenommen haben. Tochter, ich bitte Sie, alle meine Kinder zu fragen, um den Stolz zu entfernen, der immer noch in ihren Herzen treibt. Genug mit der Zwietracht, die die Br\u00fcder und genug mit Arroganz wegt, aber beugen Sie die Knie dem Herrn. Meine Kinder bereuen, es ist nicht zu sp\u00e4t, um das Ende aufzuberufen und nicht vom Teufel versucht, weil seine List scharf ist. Beten Sie f\u00fcr die Welt, denn es wird nicht mehr Frieden geben, Sehr geehrte Kinder? . Die Erde besteht jetzt aus einer perversenen Menschheit, die zu meinen Anrufen als Mutter ist. Jetzt verlasse ich Sie mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters, des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Querida mi hija, gracias por dar la bienvenida a mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Hija, por favor, p\u00eddale a todos mis hijos que eliminen el orgullo que a\u00fan se libran en sus corazones. Solo con el ordenado que se quita a los hermanos y es suficiente con la arrogancia, pero dobla las rodillas al Se\u00f1or. Arrepentiendo a mis hijos, no es demasiado tarde, arrepi\u00e9ntete hasta el final y no te ayude del diablo porque su astucia es picante. Ora por el mundo, porque no habr\u00e1 m\u00e1s paz, hizo que la penitencia quereros hijos, ya no es tiempo para vivir por las cosas del mundo, sino que buscar el cielo y ser m\u00e1s espiritual, su elevaci\u00f3n lo traer\u00e1 solo beneficios. . La tierra est\u00e1 ahora compuesta por una humanidad perversa y sordo a mi madre llama. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Cher fille, merci d'avoir accept\u00e9 mon appel dans votre coeur. Fille, je vous prie de demander \u00e0 tous mes enfants de retirer la fiert\u00e9 qui rage toujours dans leurs c\u0153urs. Assez avec la discorde qui l\u00e8ve les fr\u00e8res et assez d'arrogance, mais pliez vos genoux au Seigneur. Repentaient mes enfants, il n'est pas trop tard, repentez-vous \u00e0 la fin et ne soyez pas tent\u00e9 par le diable car sa ruse est tranchante. Priez pour le monde, car il n'y aurait plus de paix, de la p\u00e9nitence ch\u00e8re enfants, il n'est plus temps de vivre pour les choses du monde, mais \u00e9lever les yeux au ciel et \u00eatre plus spirituel, votre \u00e9l\u00e9vation ne vous apportera que des avantages . La Terre est maintenant compos\u00e9e d'une humanit\u00e9 perverse sourd \u00e0 mes appels en tant que m\u00e8re. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re, du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cara figlia mia, grazie per aver accolto la mia chiamata nel tuo cuore. Figlia, ti prego di chiedere a tutti i miei figli di togliere la superbia che ancora imperversa nei loro cuori. Basta con la zizzania che allontana i fratelli e basta con l\u2019arroganza, ma piegate le vostre ginocchia al Signore. Pentitevi figli miei, non \u00e8 troppo tardi, pentitevi fino alla fine e non fatevi tentare dal demonio perch\u00e9 la sua astuzia \u00e8 pungente. Pregate per il mondo, perch\u00e9 non ci sar\u00e0 pi\u00f9 pace, fate penitenza figli cari, non \u00e8 pi\u00f9 tempo di vivere per le cose del mondo, ma alzate lo sguardo verso il cielo e siate pi\u00f9 spirituali, la vostra elevazione vi porter\u00e0 solo benefici. La terra ormai \u00e8 costituita da un\u2019umanit\u00e0 perversa e sorda ai miei richiami di Madre.  Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Droga c\u00f3rko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce przyj\u0119\u0142a\u015b w swoim sercu moje wezwanie. C\u00f3rko, b\u0142agam ci\u0119, aby\u015b poprosi\u0142a wszystkie moje dzieci o usuni\u0119cie pychy, kt\u00f3ra nadal szaleje w ich sercach. Dosy\u0107 ju\u017c ciemnoty, kt\u00f3ra odp\u0119dza braci, dosy\u0107 ju\u017c arogancji, ukl\u0119knijcie przed Panem. Nawracajcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, jeszcze nie jest za p\u00f3\u017ano, nawracajcie si\u0119 do ko\u0144ca i nie dajcie si\u0119 kusi\u0107 diab\u0142u, bo jego przebieg\u0142o\u015b\u0107 jest przenikliwa. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za \u015bwiat, bo nie b\u0119dzie ju\u017c pokoju, czy\u0144cie pokut\u0119, drogie dzieci, nie czas ju\u017c \u017cy\u0107 dla rzeczy tego \u015bwiata, ale podnie\u015bcie oczy ku niebu i b\u0105d\u017acie bardziej duchowi, wasze wywy\u017cszenie przyniesie wam same korzy\u015bci. Ziemia sk\u0142ada si\u0119 obecnie z przewrotnej ludzko\u015bci, kt\u00f3ra jest g\u0142ucha na moje wezwania jako Matki. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Querida filha, obrigado por aceitar minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Filha, pe\u00e7o que voc\u00ea pe\u00e7a a todos os meus filhos para remover o orgulho que ainda se enfrentam em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. O suficiente com a disc\u00f3rdia que afasta os irm\u00e3os e o suficiente com arrog\u00e2ncia, mas dobre os joelhos ao Senhor. Arrependa meus filhos, n\u00e3o \u00e9 tarde demais, arrependa-se at\u00e9 o fim e n\u00e3o seja tentado pelo diabo porque sua ast\u00facia \u00e9 afiada. Ore para o mundo, pois n\u00e3o haver\u00e1 mais paz, fazer penit\u00eancia Queridos filhos, j\u00e1 n\u00e3o \u00e9 mais tempo para viver pelas coisas do mundo, mas levantam os olhos para o c\u00e9u e ser mais espiritual, sua eleva\u00e7\u00e3o lhe trar\u00e1 apenas benef\u00edcios . A terra \u00e9 agora composta de uma humanidade perversa surda \u00e0s minhas chamadas como m\u00e3e. Agora eu deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o maternal em nome do Pai, o Filho e o Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u5fc3\u91cc\u63a5\u53d7\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u6c42\u6c42\u4f60\u95ee\u6240\u6709\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u53bb\u9664\u4ecd\u7136\u5728\u4ed6\u4eec\u5fc3\u4e2d\u8086\u8650\u7684\u9a84\u50b2\u3002\u8db3\u591f\u7684\u4e0d\u548c\u8c10\u5192\u7740\u5144\u5f1f\u4eec\u7684\u4e0d\u548c\u8c10\uff0c\u50b2\u6162\uff0c\u4f46\u5c48\u670d\u4e8e\u8dea\u5730\u3002\u6094\u6539\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5b83\u8fd8\u4e0d\u592a\u665a\uff0c\u6094\u6539\u5230\u6700\u540e\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u88ab\u9b54\u9b3c\u8bf1\u60d1\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u7684\u72e1\u733e\u662f\u654f\u9510\u7684\u3002\u4e3a\u4e16\u754c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6ca1\u6709\u66f4\u597d\u7684\u548c\u5e73\uff0c\u505a\u5fcf\u6094\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5b83\u4e0d\u518d\u9002\u5408\u4e16\u754c\u7684\u4e1c\u897f\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u5c06\u4f60\u7684\u773c\u775b\u62ac\u5230\u5929\u5802\uff0c\u66f4\u4e3a\u7cbe\u795e\uff0c\u4f60\u7684\u6d77\u62d4\u4f1a\u7ed9\u4f60\u5e26\u6765\u798f\u5229\u3002\u5730\u7403\u73b0\u5728\u7531\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u547c\u53eb\u8005\u6b6a\u6b6a\u626d\u626d\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u6211\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":10,"month_string":"March","author":"Holy Father","text_en":"I, your Father am here to remind you that I love you all. Do not be afraid, My Son was the first man taken and called a heretic by the fathers of the Church. So what are you afraid of? Do not be afraid. He has conquered death and I will be with you always. Why do you not understand? Because mankind does not understand that I love you all and as Father, I feel the duty to be by your side, protecting you. As Father, I will protect you before all those who will call you heretics. Do not worry. Watch now how everything will fall apart. Even your shelter will be ready for that time. I am urging everything, so that when Mary Most Holy tells you that it is time to go, you will have to go to the Blue Cross (blessed hill of Trevignano Romano) and there you will never be touched, because I personally have sanctified that place. Do not worry, let go of human things and have Faith, everything will come true as per My plan. The angels, in the place blessed by Me, will protect you and make you safe, they will make you invisible and I will not make you lack anything. I am a good Father, but I am a just Father. I love you My children, I love you so much, do not be afraid, do not fear, all that you will have will be by My grace alone. I leave you now. Your Father, Amen.","text_de":"Ich, dein Vater, bin hier, um dich daran zu erinnern, dass ich dich alle liebe. Haben Sie keine Angst, mein Sohn war der erste Mann, der von den V\u00e4tern der Kirche genommen und als Ketzer genannt wurde. Also, wovor hast du Angst? F\u00fcrchte dich nicht. Er hat den Tod erobert und ich werde immer bei dir sein. Warum verstehst du nicht? Weil die Menschheit nicht versteht, dass ich dich all und als Vater liebe, f\u00fchle ich die Pflicht, an deiner Seite zu sein, dich zu sch\u00fctzen. Als Vater werde ich Sie vor allem sch\u00fctzen, die Sie Ketzer anrufen. Mach dir keine Sorgen. Sehen Sie sich jetzt an, wie alles auseinander f\u00e4llt. Sogar Ihr Tierheim ist f\u00fcr diese Zeit bereit. Ich fordere alles auf Ort. Mach dir keine Sorgen, lassen Sie menschliche Dinge los und haben Glauben, alles wird als mein Plan wahr werden. Die Engel, an dem von mir gesegten Ort, sch\u00fctzen Sie und machen Sie sicher, sie werden Sie unsichtbar machen, und ich werde Sie nicht dazu bringen, dass Sie nichts fehlt. Ich bin ein guter Vater, aber ich bin nur ein Vater. Ich liebe dich, meine Kinder, ich liebe dich so sehr, hab nicht Angst, nicht f\u00fcrchten, nicht f\u00fcrchten, alles, was du hast, werden von meiner Gnade alleine sein werden. Ich lasse dich jetzt. Dein Vater, Amen.","text_es":"Yo, tu padre est\u00e1 aqu\u00ed para recordarte que los amo a todos. No tengas miedo, mi hijo fue el primer hombre que tom\u00f3 y llam\u00f3 her\u00e9tico de los padres de la iglesia. Entonces, \u00bfqu\u00e9 intentas? No tengas miedo. Gan\u00f3 la muerte y siempre estar\u00e9 contigo. \u00bfPor qu\u00e9 no entiendes? Debido a que la humanidad no entiende que los amo a todos y como padre, siento el deber de permanecer a tu lado, protegi\u00e9ndote. Como padre, te proteger\u00e9 frente a todos los que te llamar\u00e1n herejes. No te preocupes. Mira ahora como todo caer\u00e1. Incluso su refugio estar\u00e1 listo para ese per\u00edodo. Estoy instando a todo, de modo que cuando Mar\u00eda m\u00e1s santo, le dir\u00e1 que ahora ser\u00e1 ir, tendr\u00e1s que ir a la Cruz Azul (Benedetta Hill de Trevignano Romano) y nunca ser\u00e1s tocado, porque yo Personalmente han santificado ese lugar. No se preocupe, suelte las cosas humanas y tenga fe, todo se dar\u00e1 cuenta como en mi proyecto. Los \u00e1ngeles, en el lugar por m\u00ed, bendito, lo proteger\u00e1n y lo pondr\u00e1n de manera segura, lo har\u00e1n invisibles y no perder\u00e9 nada. Soy un buen padre, pero soy un padre adecuado. Te amo a mis hijos, te quiero mucho, no tengas miedo, no temes, todo lo que tendr\u00e1s solo por mi gracia. Ahora te dejo. Tu padre, am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"JE, votre p\u00e8re suis ici pour vous rappeler que je t'aime tous. N'ayez pas peur, mon fils \u00e9tait le premier homme pris et appel\u00e9 un h\u00e9r\u00e9tique par les p\u00e8res de l'\u00e9glise. Alors de quoi as-tu peur? N'ayez pas peur. Il a conquis la mort et je serai avec vous toujours. Pourquoi ne comprenez-vous pas? Parce que l'humanit\u00e9 ne comprend pas que je vous aime tous et comme p\u00e8re, je ressens le devoir d'\u00eatre \u00e0 vos c\u00f4t\u00e9s, de vous prot\u00e9ger. En tant que p\u00e8re, je vous prot\u00e9gerai avant tous ceux qui vous appelleront des h\u00e9r\u00e9tiques. Ne vous inqui\u00e9tez pas. Regardez maintenant comment tout va tomber en morceaux. M\u00eame votre refuge sera pr\u00eat pour cette \u00e9poque. Je demande tout, de sorte que lorsque Mary le plus saint vous dit qu'il est temps d'y aller, vous devrez vous rendre \u00e0 la croix bleue (colline b\u00e9nie de Trevignano Romano) et vous ne serez jamais touch\u00e9, car je n'ai personnellement pas sanctifi\u00e9 que lieu. Ne vous inqui\u00e9tez pas, laissez tomber les choses humaines et avoir la foi, tout va r\u00e9aliser selon mon plan. Les anges, \u00e0 la place b\u00e9nis par moi, vous prot\u00e9geront et vous permettront de vous prot\u00e9ger, ils vous rendront invisible et je ne vous ferai pas manquer de rien. Je suis un bon p\u00e8re, mais je suis un p\u00e8re juste. Je t'aime mes enfants, je t'aime tellement, n'ayez pas peur, ne craignez pas, tout ce que vous aurez que vous serez seul. Je te laisse maintenant. Ton p\u00e8re, amen.","text_it":"Io, vostro Padre sono qui per ricordarvi che vi amo tutti. Non abbiate paura, mio Figlio fu il primo uomo preso e chiamato eretico dai padri della Chiesa. E allora di cosa temete? Non abbiate paura. Lui ha vinto la morte e Io sar\u00f2 con voi sempre. Perch\u00e9 non capite? Perch\u00e9 l\u2019umanit\u00e0 non capisce che Io vi amo tutti e come Padre, sento il dovere di starvi accanto, proteggendovi. Come Padre, vi protegger\u00f2 davanti a tutti coloro che vi chiameranno eretici. Non preoccupatevi. Guardate adesso come tutto precipiter\u00e0. Anche il vostro rifugio sar\u00e0 pronto per quel periodo. Io sto sollecitando tutto, in modo che quando Maria Santissima, vi dir\u00e0 che sar\u00e0 ora di andare, voi dovrete recarvi alla croce blu (collina benedetta  di trevignano romano ) e l\u00ec non sarete mai toccati, perch\u00e9 Io personalmente ho santificato quel posto. Non preoccupatevi, lasciate andare le cose umane e abbiate Fede, tutto si realizzer\u00e0 come da mio progetto. Gli angeli, nel luogo da me benedetto, vi proteggeranno e vi metteranno al sicuro, vi renderanno invisibili ed Io non vi far\u00f2 mancare nulla. Io sono un Padre buono, ma sono un Padre giusto. Vi amo figli miei, vi amo tanto, non abbiate paura, non temete, tutto ci\u00f2 che avrete sar\u00e0 solo per grazia mia. Ora vi lascio. Vostro Padre, Amen.","text_pl":"Ja, wasz Ojciec, jestem tutaj, aby przypomnie\u0107 wam, \u017ce kocham was wszystkich. Nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, m\u00f3j Syn by\u0142 pierwszym cz\u0142owiekiem, kt\u00f3rego ojcowie Ko\u015bcio\u0142a schwytali i nazwali heretykiem. Czego wi\u0119c si\u0119 obawiacie? Nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119. On zwyci\u0119\u017cy\u0142 \u015bmier\u0107 i zawsze b\u0119dzie z wami. Dlaczego nie potraficie tego zrozumie\u0107? Poniewa\u017c ludzko\u015b\u0107 nie rozumie, \u017ce kocham was wszystkich i jako Ojciec czuj\u0119 si\u0119 w obowi\u0105zku by\u0107 u waszego boku, chroni\u0107 was. Jako Ojciec b\u0119d\u0119 was broni\u0142 przed wszystkimi, kt\u00f3rzy b\u0119d\u0105 was nazywa\u0107 heretykami. Nie martwcie si\u0119. Zobaczcie teraz, jak wszystko si\u0119 rozpadnie. Nawet Tw\u00f3j schron b\u0119dzie gotowy na ten czas. Przynaglam was do wszystkiego, aby\u015bcie, gdy Naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Maryja Panna powie wam, \u017ce nadszed\u0142 czas odej\u015bcia, udali si\u0119 pod B\u0142\u0119kitny Krzy\u017c (b\u0142ogos\u0142awione wzg\u00f3rze Trevignano Romano) i tam nigdy nie zostaniecie dotkni\u0119ci, poniewa\u017c sam u\u015bwi\u0119ci\u0142em to miejsce. Nie martwcie si\u0119, porzu\u0107cie ludzkie sprawy i miejcie wiar\u0119, wszystko spe\u0142ni si\u0119 zgodnie z moim planem. Anio\u0142owie, w miejscu pob\u0142ogos\u0142awionym przeze mnie, b\u0119d\u0105 was chroni\u0107 i uczyni\u0105 was bezpiecznymi, sprawi\u0105, \u017ce b\u0119dziecie niewidzialni, a ja sprawi\u0119, \u017ce niczego wam nie zabraknie. Jestem dobrym Ojcem, ale jestem te\u017c Ojcem sprawiedliwym. Kocham was, moje dzieci, tak bardzo was kocham, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, wszystko, co b\u0119dziecie mieli, b\u0119dzie tylko dzi\u0119ki mojej \u0142asce. Opuszczam was teraz. Wasz Ojciec, Amen.","text_pt":"Eu, seu pai estou aqui para lembrar que eu te amo todos. N\u00e3o tenha medo, meu filho foi o primeiro homem levado e chamado de herege pelos pais da igreja. Ent\u00e3o, o que voc\u00ea tem medo? N\u00e3o tenha medo. Ele conquistou a morte e eu estarei sempre com voc\u00ea. Por que voc\u00ea n\u00e3o entende? Porque a humanidade n\u00e3o entende que eu amo todos voc\u00eas e como pai, sinto o dever de estar ao seu lado, protegendo voc\u00ea. Como pai, vou te proteger antes de todos aqueles que lhe chamam de hereges. N\u00e3o se preocupe. Assista agora como tudo vai desmoronar. At\u00e9 mesmo o seu abrigo estar\u00e1 pronto para esse tempo. Eu estou pedindo tudo, de modo que quando Maria mais sagrada lhe disser que \u00e9 hora de ir, voc\u00ea ter\u00e1 que ir para a cruz azul (Blessed Hill of Trevignano Romano) e l\u00e1 voc\u00ea nunca ser\u00e1 tocado, porque eu pessoalmente santificou isso Lugar, colocar. N\u00e3o se preocupe, solte as coisas humanas e tenha f\u00e9, tudo se tornar\u00e1 realidade de acordo com o meu plano. Os anjos, no lugar aben\u00e7oados por mim, ir\u00e3o proteg\u00ea-lo e torn\u00e1-lo seguro, eles far\u00e3o voc\u00ea invis\u00edvel e eu n\u00e3o farei voc\u00ea falta de nada. Eu sou um bom pai, mas sou apenas pai. Eu te amo meus filhos, eu te amo muito, n\u00e3o tenha medo, n\u00e3o tenha medo, tudo o que voc\u00ea ter\u00e1 ser\u00e1 pela minha gra\u00e7a sozinho. Eu te deixo agora. Seu pai, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\uff0c\u4f60\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u63d0\u9192\u4f60\uff0c\u6211\u7231\u4f60\u4eec\u3002\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u662f\u7b2c\u4e00\u4e2a\u88ab\u6559\u4f1a\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\u6240\u62cd\u6444\u7684\u4e00\u4e2a\u4eba\uff0c\u79f0\u4e3a\u4e00\u4e2a\u9057\u4ea7\u3002\u90a3\u4e48\u4f60\u5bb3\u6015\u4ec0\u4e48\uff1f\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\u3002\u4ed6\u5f81\u670d\u4e86\u6b7b\u4ea1\uff0c\u6211\u5c06\u6c38\u8fdc\u548c\u4f60\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u3002\u4f60\u4e3a\u4ec0\u4e48\u4e0d\u660e\u767d\uff1f\u56e0\u4e3a\u4eba\u7c7b\u4e0d\u660e\u767d\u6211\u7231\u4f60\u4eec\u6240\u6709\u548c\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u6211\u89c9\u5f97\u5728\u4f60\u8eab\u8fb9\u7684\u8d23\u4efb\uff0c\u4fdd\u62a4\u4f60\u3002\u4f5c\u4e3a\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u5728\u6240\u6709\u79f0\u4e3a\u60a8\u7684\u5927\u6559\u7269\u7684\u4eba\u4e4b\u524d\u4fdd\u62a4\u4f60\u3002\u4e0d\u7528\u62c5\u5fc3\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u770b\u770b\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u4f1a\u5206\u5f00\u3002\u5373\u4f7f\u662f\u4f60\u7684\u5e87\u62a4\u6240\u4e5f\u5c06\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u8fd9\u6bb5\u65f6\u95f4\u3002\u6211\u6b63\u5728\u6566\u4fc3\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u5f53\u739b\u4e3d\u6700\u5723\u6d01\u544a\u8bc9\u4f60\u662f\u65f6\u5019\u53bb\u4e86\uff0c\u4f60\u5fc5\u987b\u53bb\u84dd\u5341\u5b57\uff08\u7279\u96f7\u5c3c\u5c3c\u4e9a\u8bfa\u7f57\u9a6c\u7684\u5e78\u798f\u5c71\uff09\uff0c\u5728\u90a3\u91cc\uff0c\u4f60\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u4f1a\u78b0\u5230\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u4e2a\u4eba\u5df2\u7ecf\u6210\u5723\u4e86\u5730\u65b9\u3002\u522b\u62c5\u5fc3\uff0c\u653e\u5f00\u4eba\u7c7b\u7684\u4e1c\u897f\uff0c\u6709\u4fe1\u5fc3\uff0c\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u4f1a\u6839\u636e\u6211\u7684\u8ba1\u5212\u5b9e\u73b0\u3002\u5929\u4f7f\u5728\u6211\u7684\u5730\u65b9\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u4f1a\u4fdd\u62a4\u4f60\u5e76\u8ba9\u4f60\u5b89\u5168\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u8ba9\u4f60\u770b\u4e0d\u89c1\uff0c\u6211\u4e0d\u4f1a\u8ba9\u4f60\u7f3a\u4e4f\u4efb\u4f55\u4e1c\u897f\u3002\u6211\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u597d\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u53ea\u662f\u7236\u4eb2\u3002\u6211\u7231\u4f60\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u7231\u4f60\u8fd9\u4e48\u591a\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u6240\u6709\u4f60\u90fd\u4f1a\u88ab\u6211\u7684\u6069\u5178\u72ec\u81ea\u4e00\u4eba\u3002\u6211\u73b0\u5728\u79bb\u5f00\u4f60\u4e86\u3002\u4f60\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":12,"month_string":"March","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for having responded to My call in your hearts. My children, the heavens are invaded by darkness, which will take many souls including those of the Church. Receive your brothers without fear, for it could also happen to you. My children, to give you consolation, I tell you that after the ruins on earth, you will see the new Jerusalem descend and it will be similar to paradise. The world will be reborn and will bow down before God, there will be worldwide conversion including China, you will have many years of peace, harmony and much love among brothers, do not be afraid, because this purification will be necessary to be reborn all over again. The hand and the protection on this blessed hill (hill of Trevignano Romano) will always be there and will serve to convert many people. One day you will see the angels here, manifest themselves with the crown of the Savior on their hands and with the sound of lyres, they will sing Praises and Hymns to the Lord. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, der Himmel, die Himmel sind von der Dunkelheit eingedrungen, die viele Seelen einschlie\u00dflich derjenigen der Kirche dauert. Erhalten Sie Ihre Br\u00fcder ohne Angst, denn es k\u00f6nnte Ihnen auch passieren. Meine Kinder, um Ihnen den Trost zu geben, sage ich Ihnen, dass Sie nach den Ruinen auf der Erde das neue Jerusalem absteigen sehen werden, und es wird dem Paradies \u00e4hnlich sein. Die Welt wird wiedergeboren und wird sich vor Gott verbeugen, es wird eine weltweite Umstellung einschlie\u00dflich China geben. Sie werden viele Jahre Frieden, Harmonie und viel Liebe unter den Br\u00fcdern haben, nicht f\u00fcrchten, da diese Reinigung alle notwendig sein wird, um alle wiedergeboren zu werden erneut. Die Hand und der Schutz dieses gesegneten H\u00fcgels (H\u00fcgel von Trevignano Romano) werden immer da sein und werden dazu dienen, viele Menschen umzuwandeln. Eines Tages sehen Sie hier die Engel, manifestieren sich mit der Krone des Erretters auf den H\u00e4nden und mit dem Klang von Lyres, singen sie dem Herrn Lob und Hymnen. Jetzt verlasse ich Sie mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Ni\u00f1os, gracias por responder a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, los cielos son invadidos por la oscuridad, que tomar\u00e1n muchas almas entendidas a las de la Iglesia. Bienvenido a tus hermanos sin miedo, porque tambi\u00e9n podr\u00eda pasarte. Mis hijos, para darte consuelo. Te lo digo, que despu\u00e9s de los escombros en la Tierra, ver\u00e1s la nueva descenda de Jerusal\u00e9n y se parecer\u00e1 al Paradise. El mundo renacer\u00e1 y se inclinar\u00e1 ante Dios, habr\u00e1 la conversi\u00f3n mundial, incluida China, tendr\u00e1 tantos a\u00f1os de paz, armon\u00eda y mucho amor entre los hermanos, no tenga miedo, porque esta purificaci\u00f3n ser\u00e1 necesaria para ser renaci\u00f3 todo lo nuevo. La mano y la protecci\u00f3n en esta colina de Benedetta (Trevignano Roman Hill) siempre ser\u00e1n y servir\u00e1n para convertir a muchas personas. Un d\u00eda, ver\u00e1s los \u00e1ngeles aqu\u00ed presente, se manifiestan con la guirnalda del Salvador en las manos y con el sonido del cetre, cantar\u00e1n alabanzas y himnos al Se\u00f1or. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del padre del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, les cieux sont envahis par les t\u00e9n\u00e8bres, qui prendront de nombreuses \u00e2mes, y compris celles de l'\u00e9glise. Recevez vos fr\u00e8res sans crainte, car cela pourrait \u00e9galement vous arriver. Mes enfants, pour vous donner une consolation, je vous dis que apr\u00e8s les ruines de la Terre, vous verrez le nouveau J\u00e9rusalem descend et ce sera semblable au paradis. Le monde sera rena\u00eetre et s'inclinera devant Dieu, il y aura une conversion mondiale, y compris la Chine, vous aurez de nombreuses ann\u00e9es de paix, d'harmonie et d'amour parmi les fr\u00e8res, n'ayez pas peur, car cette purification sera n\u00e9cessaire pour rena\u00eetre tous \u00e0 nouveau. La main et la protection sur cette colline b\u00e9nie (colline de Trevignano Romano) sera toujours l\u00e0 et servira \u00e0 convertir de nombreuses personnes. Un jour, vous verrez les anges ici, se manifestent avec la couronne du Sauveur sur leurs mains et avec le son de Lyres, ils chanteront des louanges et des hymnes au Seigneur. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, i cieli sono invasi dalle tenebre, che prenderanno molte anime comprese quelle della Chiesa. Accogliete i vostri fratelli senza aver paura, perch\u00e9 potrebbe accadere anche a voi.  Figli miei, per darvi consolazione vi dico, che dopo le macerie sulla terra, vedrete scendere la nuova Gerusalemme e sar\u00e0 simile al paradiso. Il mondo rinascer\u00e0 e si inchiner\u00e0 davanti a Dio, ci sar\u00e0 la conversione mondiale compresa la Cina, avrete tanti anni di pace, armonia e tanto amore tra fratelli, non abbiate paura, perch\u00e9 questa purificazione sar\u00e0 necessaria per rinascere tutto nuovo. La mano e la protezione su questa collina Benedetta (collina di Trevignano Romano) ci sar\u00e0 sempre e servir\u00e0 a convertire molte persone. Un giorno vedrete gli angeli qui presenti, manifestarsi con la corona del Salvatore sulle mani e con il suono delle cetre, canteranno Lodi e Inni al Signore. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, niebo ogarn\u0119\u0142a ciemno\u015b\u0107, kt\u00f3ra poch\u0142onie wiele dusz, tak\u017ce tych nale\u017c\u0105cych do Ko\u015bcio\u0142a. Przyjmujcie swoich braci bez l\u0119ku, bo i was mo\u017ce to spotka\u0107.  Dzieci moje, aby was pocieszy\u0107, zapowiadam wam, \u017ce po zrujnowanej ziemi ujrzycie zst\u0119puj\u0105ce nowe Jeruzalem i b\u0119dzie ono jak raj. \u015awiat si\u0119 odrodzi i pok\u0142oni si\u0119 przed Bogiem, nast\u0105pi nawr\u00f3cenie na ca\u0142ym \u015bwiecie, w tym w Chinach, b\u0119dziecie mieli wiele lat pokoju, harmonii i wielkiej mi\u0142o\u015bci mi\u0119dzy bra\u0107mi, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, poniewa\u017c to oczyszczenie b\u0119dzie konieczne, aby odrodzi\u0107 si\u0119 na nowo. R\u0119ka i ochrona na tym b\u0142ogos\u0142awionym wzg\u00f3rzu (wzg\u00f3rze Trevignano Romano) b\u0119d\u0105 zawsze obecne i pos\u0142u\u017c\u0105 do nawr\u00f3cenia wielu ludzi. Pewnego dnia ujrzycie tu anio\u0142\u00f3w, objawiaj\u0105cych si\u0119 z koron\u0105 Zbawiciela na r\u0119kach i przy d\u017awi\u0119ku lir, \u015bpiewaj\u0105cych Panu pie\u015bni pochwalne i hymny. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por ter respondido \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, os c\u00e9us s\u00e3o invadidos por escurid\u00e3o, o que levar\u00e1 muitas almas, incluindo as da igreja. Receba seus irm\u00e3os sem medo, pois tamb\u00e9m poderia acontecer com voc\u00ea. Meus filhos, para lhe dar consolo, eu te digo que depois das ru\u00ednas da terra, voc\u00ea ver\u00e1 o novo Jerusal\u00e9m descer e ser\u00e1 semelhante ao para\u00edso. O mundo ser\u00e1 renascer e se curvar\u00e1 diante de Deus, haver\u00e1 convers\u00e3o mundial, incluindo a China, voc\u00ea ter\u00e1 muitos anos de paz, harmonia e muito amor entre os irm\u00e3os, n\u00e3o tem medo, porque essa purifica\u00e7\u00e3o ser\u00e1 necess\u00e1ria para renascer em todos os mais uma vez. A m\u00e3o e a prote\u00e7\u00e3o nesta colina aben\u00e7oada (Hill of Trevignano Romano) estar\u00e3o sempre l\u00e1 e servir\u00e1 para converter muitas pessoas. Um dia voc\u00ea ver\u00e1 os anjos aqui, manifestar-se com a coroa do Salvador em suas m\u00e3os e com o som de Lyres, eles cantar\u00e3o louvores e hinos ao Senhor. Agora eu deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o maternal em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5929\u5802\u88ab\u9ed1\u6697\u5165\u4fb5\uff0c\u8fd9\u5c06\u9700\u8981\u8bb8\u591a\u7075\u9b42\uff0c\u5305\u62ec\u6559\u5802\u3002\u6536\u5230\u4f60\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u6050\u60e7\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u4e5f\u53ef\u80fd\u53d1\u751f\u5728\u4f60\u8eab\u4e0a\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7ed9\u4f60\u5b89\u6170\uff0c\u6211\u544a\u8bc9\u4f60\uff0c\u5728\u5730\u7403\u4e0a\u7684\u5e9f\u589f\u540e\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u65b0\u7684\u8036\u8def\u6492\u51b7\u4e0b\u964d\uff0c\u5b83\u5c06\u7c7b\u4f3c\u4e8e\u5929\u5802\u3002\u4e16\u754c\u5c06\u91cd\u751f\u5e76\u5c06\u5728\u4e0a\u5e1d\u9762\u524d\u97a0\u8eac\uff0c\u5c06\u4f1a\u6709\u5168\u4e16\u754c\u7684\u8f6c\u6362\u5728\u5185\uff0c\u5728\u5185\u7684\u4e2d\u56fd\uff0c\u4f60\u5c06\u6709\u591a\u5e74\u7684\u548c\u5e73\uff0c\u548c\u8c10\u548c\u5144\u5f1f\u4e4b\u95f4\u7684\u5927\u7231\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u8fd9\u51c0\u5316\u5c06\u662f\u5fc5\u8981\u7684\u518d\u6b21\u3002\u8fd9\u53ea\u5e78\u798f\u7684\u5c71\u4e18\uff08Trevignano Romano\u5c71\uff09\u7684\u624b\u548c\u4fdd\u62a4\u5c06\u6c38\u8fdc\u5728\u90a3\u91cc\uff0c\u5c06\u6709\u52a9\u4e8e\u8f6c\u6362\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u3002\u6709\u4e00\u5929\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u770b\u5230\u5929\u4f7f\uff0c\u7528\u624b\u638c\u63e1\u6551\u4e16\u4e3b\u7684\u738b\u51a0\uff0c\u5e76\u7528Lys\u7684\u58f0\u97f3\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u5411\u4e3b\u5531\u6b4c\u548c\u8d5e\u7f8e\u8bd7\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":13,"month_string":"March","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: as prince of the heavenly legions, I bless you and share with you the divine word so that you may prepare yourselves. You are beloved of the Holy Trinity and of our Queen and Mother of the End Times. You will face trials in all aspects, but above all in faith. Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, live this lent with conscience as you have never lived it before. You have before you the Divine Mercy to make amends. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: as a church you must strengthen yourselves in faith. The henchmen of the antichrist impose a new religion as the only true religion. I must manifest to you that it is not true nor does it come from our King and Lord Jesus Christ, but it is born from the entrails of Satan himself, created so that the antichrist may dominate them. It is coming, saturated with imposition, persecution, discord, lies, hatred and betrayal. Christians will return to the catacombs where there will be the true light that the devil cannot extinguish. The unbelieving man prefers to deny the prophecies than to accept what some human creatures are already experiencing: the pain of war, unexpected death, injustice, terror. As prince of the heavenly legions, I must affirm to you that war is not words, but painful and bloody deeds, plans drawn up to invade Europe, part of America together with some islands and some countries of the east. So human creatures will be foreigners wandering from country to country. They will be surprised without even thinking about it. The persecutors will arrive without being expected and like a plague will invade by air and land in their desire to take over Europe they will reach several countries. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ are heading down the road of famine as a result of the war, which like a plague is spreading from country to country. I invite you to take current events seriously. These are spreading as treachery is happening from place to place, especially in the Balkans, where treachery and death are coming. The people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ will be strangers, wandering from place to place as the tentacle of war advances unstoppably and relentlessly. I speak to you with certain words: the time will seem long years before the human miseries with which you must live. You must find yourselves prepared, children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: prepared to face, not only the fury of nature, but the sudden flight of the nation in which you live before the sudden and unlooked-for invasion. Europe will be hit at several points. The invasion of the nations will be sudden, it will be unexpected, you will be going about your business when you will hear and see the planes overhead and the weapons of war entering your countries. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: pray, pray without ceasing for the salvation of souls, for the famine on the planet and for the innocent who suffer. Be creatures of good, go to the eucharistic celebration, honour our Queen and Mother. Be creatures of faith, strengthen each other. Each one of you is a temple and it is a grave sin to act in a manner or verbally against a brother. Be cautious so that at the warning you will not suffer any more. People of our Queen and Mother, human creatures are judged in love. Therefore, be love and the rest will be given to you in addition. I bless you with the blessing that I receive from our King and Lord Jesus Christ. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.  ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 legion\u00f3w niebieskich b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was i dziel\u0119 si\u0119 z wami s\u0142owem Bo\u017cym, aby\u015bcie mogli si\u0119 przygotowa\u0107. Jeste\u015bcie umi\u0142owani przez Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 \u015awi\u0119t\u0105 i przez nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119 Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych. Staniecie w obliczu pr\u00f3b we wszystkich aspektach, ale przede wszystkim w wierze. Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, prze\u017cyjcie ten post z sumieniem, jak nigdy dot\u0105d. Macie przed sob\u0105 Mi\u0142osierdzie Bo\u017ce, aby zado\u015b\u0107uczyni\u0107. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, jako Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 musicie umocni\u0107 si\u0119 w wierze. Poplecznicy antychrysta narzucaj\u0105 now\u0105 religi\u0119 jako jedyn\u0105 prawdziw\u0105. Musz\u0119 wam objawi\u0107, \u017ce nie jest ona prawdziwa ani nie pochodzi od naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, ale jest zrodzona z wn\u0119trzno\u015bci samego szatana, stworzona po to, aby antychryst m\u00f3g\u0142 nad nimi dominowa\u0107. Nadchodzi, nasycony narzucaniem, prze\u015bladowaniem, niezgod\u0105, k\u0142amstwami, nienawi\u015bci\u0105 i zdrad\u0105. Chrze\u015bcijanie powr\u00f3c\u0105 do katakumb, gdzie b\u0119dzie prawdziwe \u015bwiat\u0142o, kt\u00f3rego diabe\u0142 nie mo\u017ce zgasi\u0107. Cz\u0142owiek niewierz\u0105cy woli zaprzeczy\u0107 proroctwom, ni\u017c przyj\u0105\u0107 to, czego niekt\u00f3re ludzkie stworzenia ju\u017c do\u015bwiadczaj\u0105: b\u00f3l wojny, niespodziewan\u0105 \u015bmier\u0107, niesprawiedliwo\u015b\u0107, terror. Jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 niebia\u0144skich legion\u00f3w musz\u0119 wam potwierdzi\u0107, \u017ce wojna to nie s\u0142owa, ale bolesne i krwawe czyny, plany sporz\u0105dzone w celu najazdu na Europ\u0119, cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 Ameryki wraz z niekt\u00f3rymi wyspami i niekt\u00f3rymi krajami wschodu. Tak wi\u0119c istoty ludzkie b\u0119d\u0105 obcokrajowcami w\u0119druj\u0105cymi z kraju do kraju. B\u0119d\u0105 zaskakiwane, nie my\u015bl\u0105c nawet o tym. Prze\u015bladowcy przyjd\u0105, nie spodziewaj\u0105c si\u0119 i jak zaraza b\u0119d\u0105 naje\u017cd\u017ca\u0107 drog\u0105 powietrzn\u0105 i l\u0105dow\u0105 w swoim pragnieniu zaw\u0142adni\u0119cia Europ\u0105 dotr\u0105 do kilku kraj\u00f3w. Lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa zmierza drog\u0105 g\u0142odu w wyniku wojny, kt\u00f3ra jak zaraza rozprzestrzenia si\u0119 z kraju do kraju. Zach\u0119cam do powa\u017cnego traktowania bie\u017c\u0105cych wydarze\u0144. Rozprzestrzeniaj\u0105 si\u0119 one jak zdrada z miejsca na miejsce, szczeg\u00f3lnie na Ba\u0142kanach, gdzie zdrada i \u015bmier\u0107 nadchodz\u0105. Lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa b\u0119dzie obcy, w\u0119druj\u0105cy z miejsca na miejsce, gdy macki wojny posuwaj\u0105 si\u0119 niepowstrzymanie i nieub\u0142aganie. M\u00f3wi\u0119 do was pewnymi s\u0142owami: czas ten b\u0119dzie wydawa\u0142 si\u0119 d\u0142ugimi latami przed ludzkimi nieszcz\u0119\u015bciami, z kt\u00f3rymi musicie \u017cy\u0107. Musicie znale\u017a\u0107 si\u0119 przygotowani, dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: przygotowani na stawienie czo\u0142a nie tylko furii natury, ale tak\u017ce nag\u0142ej ucieczce narodu, w kt\u00f3rym \u017cyjecie przed nag\u0142\u0105 i nieprzewidzian\u0105 inwazj\u0105. Europa zostanie uderzona w kilku punktach. Inwazja narod\u00f3w b\u0119dzie nag\u0142a, b\u0119dzie niespodziewana, b\u0119dziecie zajmowa\u0107 si\u0119 swoimi sprawami, gdy us\u0142yszycie i zobaczycie samoloty nad g\u0142ow\u0105 i bro\u0144 wojenn\u0105 wkraczaj\u0105c\u0105 do waszych kraj\u00f3w. Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 bez przerwy o zbawienie dusz, o g\u0142\u00f3d na planecie i za niewinnych, kt\u00f3rzy cierpi\u0105. B\u0105d\u017acie istotami dobra, udajcie si\u0119 na celebracj\u0119 eucharystyczn\u0105, uczcijcie nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119. B\u0105d\u017acie istotami wiary, umacniajcie si\u0119 wzajemnie. Ka\u017cdy z was jest \u015bwi\u0105tyni\u0105 i ci\u0119\u017ckim grzechem jest post\u0119powanie w spos\u00f3b lub s\u0142ownie przeciwko bratu. B\u0105d\u017acie ostro\u017cni, aby\u015bcie przy ostrze\u017ceniu nie cierpieli wi\u0119cej. Ludu naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki, stworzenia ludzkie s\u0105 s\u0105dzone w mi\u0142o\u015bci. Dlatego b\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, a reszta b\u0119dzie wam dana dodatkowo. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem, kt\u00f3re otrzymuj\u0119 od naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":15,"month_string":"March","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My beloved children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts and for bending your knees in prayer. Beloved children, how much pain I feel in my heart, I look at you, you are walking on ground undermined not only by bombs, but by evil. In spite of my innumerable appeals, you still doubt, yet I, your Mother, have always warned of what would come if there were no true conversion in you; listen to me! My children, I ask you once again: entrust your life and your days to God, have faith in Him, the Just One who can do everything. Men are not ready for what will suddenly come, they believe only the voices of the world and not the Holy words of a Mother who cries and grieves for all. I want to save you, do you understand this warning? The famine will advance without mercy, help each other among brothers. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine geliebten Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen geantwortet haben, und um Ihre Knie im Gebet zu biegen. Geliebte Kinder, wie viel Schmerz f\u00fchle ich mich in meinem Herzen, ich sehe dich an, du gehst auf Boden, nicht nur von Bomben, sondern von B\u00f6sen untergraben. Trotz meiner unz\u00e4hligen Attraktionen haben Sie immer noch zweifelt, aber ich habe Ihre Mutter immer daran gewarnt, was kommen w\u00fcrde, wenn es keine echte Bekehrung in Ihnen gab; h\u00f6rt mir zu! Meine Kinder, ich frage dich noch einmal: Vertraue dein Leben und deine Tage an Gott, habe den Glauben an ihn, der nur eine, die alles tun kann. M\u00e4nner sind nicht bereit f\u00fcr das, was pl\u00f6tzlich kommen wird, sie glauben nur die Stimmen der Welt und nicht die heiligen Worte einer Mutter, die f\u00fcr alle weint und traut. Ich m\u00f6chte Sie retten, verstehen Sie diese Warnung? Die Hungersnot wird ohne Barmherzigkeit vorr\u00fccken, gegenseitig bei Br\u00fcdern helfen. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis queridos hijos, gracias por responder a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n y para doblar las rodillas en la oraci\u00f3n. A los ni\u00f1os amados, cu\u00e1nto dolor me siento en mi coraz\u00f3n, te miro, est\u00e1s caminando en un terreno minado no solo de bombas, sino del mal. A pesar de que mis innumerables apelaciones a\u00fan dudaban, sin embargo, tengo a tu madre, siempre he advertido qu\u00e9 vendr\u00eda en ti, no hab\u00eda una conversi\u00f3n real, \u00a1esc\u00fachame! Mis hijos, le pregunto una vez m\u00e1s: conf\u00eda tu vida y tus d\u00edas a Dios, tenga fe en \u00e9l, el derecho que todo puede. Los hombres no est\u00e1n listos para lo que pasar\u00e1 repentinamente, creen solo a las voces del mundo y no a las santas palabras de una madre que llora y molestias a todos. Quiero salvarte, \u00bfentiendes esta advertencia? La hambruna avanzar\u00e1 sin piedad, te ayudar\u00e1 entre hermanos. Ahora te bendigo en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs et de plier vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, combien de douleur je me sens dans mon c\u0153ur, je te regarde, tu marches sur le sol min\u00e9 non seulement par des bombes, mais par le mal. En d\u00e9pit de mes innombrables appels, vous doutez toujours, pourtant, \u00e0 votre m\u00e8re, avez toujours averti de ce qui viendrait s'il n'y avait pas de v\u00e9ritable conversion en vous; \u00e9coute moi! Mes enfants, je vous demande une fois de plus: confier votre vie et vos journ\u00e9es \u00e0 Dieu, prenez la foi en lui, le juste qui peut tout faire. Les hommes ne sont pas pr\u00eats pour ce qui sera soudainement venu, ils ne croient que les voix du monde et non les paroles saintes d'une m\u00e8re qui pleure et des grieves pour tous. Je veux vous sauver, comprenez-vous cet avertissement? La famine va avancer sans piti\u00e9, s'entraider les uns des autres parmi les fr\u00e8res. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei cari, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore e per aver piegato le ginocchia nella preghiera. Figli amati, quanto dolore sento nel mio cuore, vi guardo, state camminando su un terreno minato non solo da bombe, ma dal male.  Nonostante i miei innumerevoli appelli ancora dubitate, eppure Io vostra Madre, ho sempre avvertito di ci\u00f2 che sarebbe arrivato se in voi, non ci fosse stata, la vera conversione, ascoltatemi!  Figli miei, vi chiedo ancora una volta: affidate la vostra vita e le vostre giornate a Dio, abbiate fede in Lui, il Giusto che tutto pu\u00f2. Gli uomini non sono pronti a ci\u00f2 che arriver\u00e0 improvvisamente, credono solo alle voci del mondo e non alle parole Sante di una Madre che piange e si addolora per tutti. Voglio salvarvi, capite questo monito? La carestia avanzer\u00e0 senza piet\u00e0, aiutatevi tra fratelli. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moje drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie do modlitwy. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, jak\u017ce wielki b\u00f3l czuj\u0119 w sercu, gdy patrz\u0119 na was, chodzicie po ziemi podkopanej nie tylko przez bomby, ale tak\u017ce przez z\u0142o. Mimo moich niezliczonych wezwa\u0144 wci\u0105\u017c w\u0105tpicie, a przecie\u017c Ja, wasza Matka, zawsze ostrzega\u0142am, co b\u0119dzie, je\u015bli nie nast\u0105pi w was prawdziwe nawr\u00f3cenie; pos\u0142uchajcie mnie! Dzieci moje, jeszcze raz prosz\u0119 was: powierzcie Bogu wasze \u017cycie i wasze dni, miejcie wiar\u0119 w Niego, Sprawiedliwego, kt\u00f3ry wszystko mo\u017ce. Ludzie nie s\u0105 gotowi na to, co przyjdzie nagle, wierz\u0105 tylko g\u0142osom \u015bwiata, a nie \u015bwi\u0119tym s\u0142owom Matki, kt\u00f3ra p\u0142acze i boleje nad wszystkimi. Chc\u0119 was ocali\u0107, czy rozumiecie to ostrze\u017cenie? G\u0142\u00f3d b\u0119dzie post\u0119powa\u0142 bez lito\u015bci, pomagajcie sobie nawzajem w\u015br\u00f3d braci. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus amados filhos, obrigado por responder ao meu chamado em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e para dobrar os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Crian\u00e7as amadas, quanta dor me sinto em meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o, olho para voc\u00ea, voc\u00ea est\u00e1 andando no ch\u00e3o n\u00e3o apenas por bombas, mas pelo mal. Apesar dos meus in\u00fameros apelos, voc\u00ea ainda duvida, mas eu, sua m\u00e3e, sempre avisou o que viria se n\u00e3o houvesse convers\u00e3o verdadeira em voc\u00ea; Me escute! Meus filhos, pe\u00e7o-lhe mais uma vez: confiar sua vida e seus dias a Deus, ter f\u00e9 nele, o apenas um que pode fazer tudo. Os homens n\u00e3o est\u00e3o prontos para o que de repente vir\u00e3o, eles acreditam apenas as vozes do mundo e n\u00e3o as palavras sagradas de uma m\u00e3e que chora e tristes para todos. Eu quero te salvar, voc\u00ea entende esse aviso? A fome vai avan\u00e7ar sem miseric\u00f3rdia, ajudar uns aos outros entre os irm\u00e3os. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u7948\u7977\u4e2d\u5f2f\u66f2\u819d\u76d6\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u5fc3\u91cc\u6709\u591a\u5c11\u75db\u82e6\uff0c\u6211\u770b\u7740\u4f60\uff0c\u4f60\u5728\u5730\u4e0a\u884c\u8d70\u4e0d\u4ec5\u53d7\u5230\u70b8\u5f39\u800c\u88ab\u70b8\u6bc1\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u90aa\u6076\u3002\u5c3d\u7ba1\u6211\u4e0d\u53ef\u80fd\u6709\u5438\u5f15\u529b\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u4ecd\u7136\u6000\u7591\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\uff0c\u4f60\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u6ca1\u6709\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u8f6c\u6362\uff0c\u4f60\u603b\u662f\u8b66\u544a\u4e86\u4ec0\u4e48;\u542c\u6211\u8bf4\uff01\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u518d\u6b21\u95ee\u4f60\u4e00\u6b21\uff1a\u59d4\u6258\u4f60\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\u548c\u4f60\u7684\u65e5\u5b50\uff0c\u5bf9\u4ed6\u6709\u4fe1\u5fc3\uff0c\u53ea\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u53ef\u4ee5\u505a\u5230\u6240\u6709\u4e8b\u60c5\u7684\u4eba\u3002\u7537\u4eba\u8fd8\u6ca1\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u7a81\u7136\u6765\u7684\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u53ea\u76f8\u4fe1\u4e16\u754c\u7684\u58f0\u97f3\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u4e00\u4f4d\u54ed\u6ce3\u548c\u60b2\u4f24\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u5723\u8a00\u3002\u6211\u60f3\u6551\u4f60\uff0c\u4f60\u660e\u767d\u8fd9\u4e2a\u8b66\u544a\u5417\uff1f\u9965\u8352\u5c06\u6beb\u4e0d\u601c\u60af\u5730\u63a8\u8fdb\uff0c\u4e92\u76f8\u5e2e\u52a9\u5144\u5f1f\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":17,"month_string":"March","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: as the captain of the heavenly host, I bless you with the blessing of my King and Lord Jesus Christ. I call you to urgent conversion, now, in haste, before you become more confused. As the mystical body you must obey and adhere to Sacred Scripture. Pay attention, do not stray down paths contrary to the Divine Will. It is necessary for you to practice the sacraments and to be reconciled with your brothers and sisters. Be love, peace, mercy and receive the holy Eucharist properly prepared. Offer to our Queen and Mother the holy rosary prayed with the heart. It is essential for you to be love... In the face of love, the devil flees. Do not judge others and you will not be judged. For as you judge, so you will be judged, and the same measure you use for others will be used for you. I see human beings turning away from our King and Lord Jesus Christ and our Queen and Mother. I see them joining the ranks of evil, ready to bring down their brothers and sisters without mercy or remorse. Humanity is immersed in the ideology of communism, which together with freemasonry keeps the people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ and the children of our Queen and Mother of the End Times in distrust and division. People of our Queen and Mother, be wary of falling and no longer being able to get up. Conversion, conversion immediately! How stubborn you are in deciding to continue to impart evil, cooperating with communism and spreading its ideology, whose aim is to seize territorial power and dominion over the peoples in every respect. How you will mourn! How you will mourn, children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ! Disease is looming again... Famine has spread over the earth as arranged by the mighty within the great powers, who are leading you towards the abyss, following a pact with evil, which will succeed in making humanity suffer as never before. People of our Queen and Mother, pray, plead, cry out, for our Queen welcomes sincere and heartfelt supplications. You must maintain inner peace so that you might share peace with your brothers and sisters. This generation is in need of the love emanating from the Sacred Hearts to soften the hardened hearts of men. How are you in need of prayer! How you need to confess your sins in true and authentic repentance! Bend your pride and your thoughts so that you may be worthy of the maternal protection to which the most Holy Trinity has entrusted the times of this generation. People of our Queen and Mother, without separating yourselves from the blessed hand of her who is the mother of our King and Lord Jesus Christ and commander of the heavenly host, you are and will be protected by our queen, from whom the most Holy Trinity has ordained intercession for the good of humanity, having chosen her to crush and chain the infernal dragon. What is coming for humanity finds the Queen and Mother of heaven and earth before her children, whom she defends and delivers from all evil, if they worship her most holy Son and are fulfillers of the Divine Will. Go forth, people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, with firm faith in the power of our Queen and Mother, without doubting that in the end her Immaculate Heart will triumph! You will see every knee bow before our Queen and every creature exclaim: 'hail Mary most pure, hail Mary most pure, hail Mary most pure'. Faithful people - firm, without renouncing your call; faithful people - firm in the battle against evil in the name of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, we protect you, I bless you. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: jako kapitan zast\u0119p\u00f3w niebieskich b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem mojego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Wzywam was do pilnego nawr\u00f3cenia, teraz, w po\u015bpiechu, zanim jeszcze bardziej si\u0119 pogubicie. Jako cia\u0142o mistyczne musicie by\u0107 pos\u0142uszni i trzyma\u0107 si\u0119 Pisma \u015awi\u0119tego. Zwracajcie uwag\u0119, nie zbaczajcie na drogi sprzeczne z Wol\u0105 Bo\u017c\u0105. Konieczne jest, aby\u015bcie praktykowali sakramenty i byli pojednani z bra\u0107mi i siostrami. B\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, pokojem, mi\u0142osierdziem i przyjmujcie \u015bwi\u0119t\u0105 Eucharysti\u0119 odpowiednio przygotowani. Ofiarujcie naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matce r\u00f3\u017caniec \u015bwi\u0119ty odmawiany sercem. Jest to niezb\u0119dne, aby\u015bcie byli mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105... W obliczu mi\u0142o\u015bci diabe\u0142 ucieka. Nie s\u0105d\u017acie innych, a nie b\u0119dziecie s\u0105dzeni. Bo jak wy s\u0105dzicie, tak i wy b\u0119dziecie s\u0105dzeni, a ta sama miara, kt\u00f3rej u\u017cywacie wobec innych, b\u0119dzie u\u017cyta wobec was. Widz\u0119 istoty ludzkie odwracaj\u0105ce si\u0119 od naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa oraz naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki. Widz\u0119, jak wst\u0119puj\u0105 w szeregi z\u0142a, gotowi sprowadzi\u0107 na ziemi\u0119 swoich braci i siostry bez lito\u015bci i wyrzut\u00f3w sumienia. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest zanurzona w ideologii komunizmu, kt\u00f3ra wraz z masoneri\u0105 utrzymuje lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa oraz dzieci naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych w nieufno\u015bci i podziale. Ludu naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki, b\u0105d\u017acie ostro\u017cni, bo upadniecie i ju\u017c nie b\u0119dziecie mogli si\u0119 podnie\u015b\u0107. Nawr\u00f3cenie, nawr\u00f3cenie natychmiastowe! Jak\u017ce jeste\u015bcie uparci, decyduj\u0105c si\u0119 na dalsze zaszczepianie z\u0142a, wsp\u00f3\u0142pracuj\u0105c z komunizmem i szerz\u0105c jego ideologi\u0119, kt\u00f3rej celem jest przej\u0119cie w\u0142adzy terytorialnej i panowanie nad ludami pod ka\u017cdym wzgl\u0119dem. Jak\u017ce b\u0119dziecie op\u0142akiwa\u0107! Jak\u017ce b\u0119dziecie op\u0142akiwa\u0107, dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa! Choroby zn\u00f3w si\u0119 zbli\u017caj\u0105... G\u0142\u00f3d rozprzestrzeni\u0142 si\u0119 po ziemi, jak to zosta\u0142o zaaran\u017cowane przez mo\u017cnych w wielkich mocarstwach, kt\u00f3rzy prowadz\u0105 was ku otch\u0142ani, pod\u0105\u017caj\u0105c za paktem ze z\u0142em, kt\u00f3ry zdo\u0142a uczyni\u0107 ludzko\u015b\u0107 cierpi\u0105c\u0105 jak nigdy dot\u0105d. Ludzie naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, b\u0142agajcie, wo\u0142ajcie, gdy\u017c nasza Kr\u00f3lowa przyjmuje szczere i serdeczne b\u0142agania. Musicie zachowa\u0107 wewn\u0119trzny pok\u00f3j, aby\u015bcie mogli dzieli\u0107 pok\u00f3j z waszymi bra\u0107mi i siostrami. To pokolenie potrzebuje mi\u0142o\u015bci emanuj\u0105cej z Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszych Serc, aby zmi\u0119kczy\u0107 zatwardzia\u0142e serca ludzi. Jak bardzo potrzebujecie modlitwy! Jak bardzo potrzebujecie wyzna\u0107 swoje grzechy w prawdziwej i autentycznej pokucie! Nagnijcie swoj\u0105 pych\u0119 i swoje my\u015bli, aby\u015bcie byli godni matczynej opieki, kt\u00f3rej Tr\u00f3jca Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsza powierzy\u0142a czasy tego pokolenia. Ludu naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki, nie oddzielaj\u0105c si\u0119 od b\u0142ogos\u0142awionej r\u0119ki tej, kt\u00f3ra jest Matk\u0105 naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa i dow\u00f3dc\u0105 zast\u0119p\u00f3w niebieskich, jeste\u015b i b\u0119dziesz chroniony przez nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105, kt\u00f3rej naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Tr\u00f3jca wy\u015bwi\u0119ci\u0142a wstawiennictwo dla dobra ludzko\u015bci, wybrawszy j\u0105 do zmia\u017cd\u017cenia i zakucia w \u0142a\u0144cuchy piekielnego smoka. To, co nadchodzi dla ludzko\u015bci, znajduje Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka nieba i ziemi przed swoimi dzie\u0107mi, kt\u00f3rych broni i wybawia od wszelkiego z\u0142a, je\u015bli czcz\u0105 Jej naj\u015bwi\u0119tszego Syna i s\u0105 wype\u0142niaczami Woli Bo\u017cej. Id\u017acie, ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, z mocn\u0105 wiar\u0105 w pot\u0119g\u0119 naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki, nie w\u0105tpi\u0105c, \u017ce w ko\u0144cu Jej Niepokalane Serce zatriumfuje! Zobaczycie, \u017ce ka\u017cde kolano ugnie si\u0119 przed nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i ka\u017cde stworzenie zawo\u0142a: \" Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza\". Wierny ludu - stanowczy, nie wyrzekaj\u0105c si\u0119 swego powo\u0142ania; wierny ludu - stanowczy w walce ze z\u0142em w imi\u0119 naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, chronimy was, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":19,"month_string":"March","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for answering my call in your hearts and for bending your knees in prayer. My dear children, always be ready for what will happen suddenly, Europe will be invaded, pray for the West, pray for the Pope, for this is the hour of his great sorrow and concern. My children, remember that prayer is the only medicine for your soul and your body, open your hearts to Grace, because only in this way will you be able to have peace in your hearts, despite the dark times. Dear children, do not be afraid, but take my hands and I will bring you to my Son Jesus. My children, persecution will be great, so always be in faith even when all seems lost, trust in God, He will be close to you every day, until the end.  Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen beantwortet haben, und um Ihre Knie im Gebet zu biegen. Meine lieben Kinder, immer bereit f\u00fcr das, was pl\u00f6tzlich passieren wird, Europa wird eingedrungen, beten Sie f\u00fcr den Westen, beten Sie f\u00fcr den Papst, denn dies ist die Stunde seiner gro\u00dfen Trauer und Sorge. Meine Kinder, denken Sie daran, dass das Gebet die einzige Medizin f\u00fcr Ihre Seele und Ihr K\u00f6rper ist, \u00f6ffnen Sie Ihre Herzen, um die Ern\u00e4hrung zu er\u00f6ffnen, denn nur auf diese Weise werden Sie trotz der dunklen Zeiten Frieden in Ihren Herzen haben k\u00f6nnen. Liebe Kinder, f\u00fcrchten keine Angst, aber nehmen Sie meine H\u00e4nde, und ich werde Sie zu meinem Sohn Jesus bringen. Meine Kinder, die Verfolgung wird gro\u00dfartig sein, also sei immer im Glauben, auch wenn alles verloren geht, das Vertrauen in Gott, er wird jeden Tag in der N\u00e4he sein, bis zum Ende. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n y para doblar las rodillas en la oraci\u00f3n. Mis queridos hijos, siempre est\u00e1s listo para lo que suceder\u00e1 de repente, Europa ser\u00e1 invadida, or\u00f3 por Occidente, or\u00f3 por el Papa, porque este es el momento de su gran dolor y preocupaci\u00f3n. Mis hijos, recuerde que la oraci\u00f3n es la \u00fanica medicina para su alma y para su cuerpo, abre sus corazones a la gracia, porque solo para que podr\u00e1 tener paz en sus corazones, a pesar de los tiempos oscuros. Los ni\u00f1os queridos, no tengas miedo, sino que me toman las manos y te llevan a mi hijo Jes\u00fas. Los ni\u00f1os, la persecuci\u00f3n ser\u00e1 excelente, as\u00ed que siempre estar\u00e1 en fe, incluso cuando todo parece perdido, se conf\u00eda a Dios, estar\u00e1 cerca de Dios. Usted todos los d\u00edas, hasta el final. Ahora te bendigo en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs et de plier vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re. Mes chers enfants, toujours pr\u00eat pour ce qui se passera soudainement, l'Europe sera envahie, prie pour l'Occident, prie pour le pape, car c'est l'heure de son grand chagrin et de ses pr\u00e9occupations. Mes enfants, rappelez-vous que la pri\u00e8re est le seul m\u00e9dicament pour votre \u00e2me et votre corps, ouvrez vos c\u0153urs \u00e0 Grace, car seulement de cette fa\u00e7on pourrez-vous avoir la paix dans vos c\u0153urs, malgr\u00e9 les temps sombres. Chers enfants, n'ayez pas peur, mais prenez mes mains et je vous am\u00e8nerai \u00e0 mon fils J\u00e9sus. Mes enfants, la pers\u00e9cution sera g\u00e9niale, alors toujours \u00eatre de la foi, m\u00eame quand tout semble perdu, faire confiance \u00e0 Dieu, il sera proche de vous tous les jours, jusqu'\u00e0 la fin. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore e per aver piegato le ginocchia nella preghiera. Bambini miei cari, siate sempre pronti per ci\u00f2 che accadr\u00e0 all\u2019improvviso, l\u2019Europa sar\u00e0 invasa, pregate per l\u2019Occidente, pregate per il Papa, perch\u00e9 questa \u00e8 l\u2019ora del suo grande dolore e preoccupazione. Figli miei, ricordate che la preghiera \u00e8 l\u2019unica medicina per la vostra anima e per il vostro corpo, aprite i vostri cuori alla Grazia, perch\u00e9 solo cos\u00ec riuscirete ad avere pace nei vostri cuori, nonostante i tempi bui. Figli cari, non abbiate paura, ma prendete le mie mani e vi porter\u00f2 a mio Figlio Ges\u00f9. Figli, la persecuzione sar\u00e0 grande, quindi siate sempre nella fede anche quando tutto sembrer\u00e0 perduto, affidatevi a Dio, Lui sar\u00e0 vicino a voi tutti i giorni, fino alla fine. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach i zgi\u0119li\u015bcie kolana w modlitwie. Moje drogie dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie zawsze gotowi na to, co si\u0119 nagle wydarzy, Europa zostanie najechana, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Zach\u00f3d, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Papie\u017ca, bo to jest godzina jego wielkiego smutku i troski. Dzieci moje, pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce modlitwa jest jedynym lekarstwem dla waszej duszy i waszego cia\u0142a, otw\u00f3rzcie wasze serca na \u0141ask\u0119, bo tylko w ten spos\u00f3b b\u0119dziecie mogli mie\u0107 pok\u00f3j w waszych sercach, pomimo mrocznych czas\u00f3w. Drogie dzieci, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, ale we\u017acie mnie za r\u0119k\u0119, a ja zaprowadz\u0119 was do mojego Syna Jezusa. Moje dzieci, prze\u015bladowania b\u0119d\u0105 wielkie, dlatego zawsze b\u0105d\u017acie pe\u0142ni wiary, nawet gdy wszystko wydaje si\u0119 stracone, powierzcie si\u0119 Bogu, On b\u0119dzie blisko was ka\u017cdego dnia, a\u017c do ko\u0144ca. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por responder a minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e para dobrar os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus queridos filhos, sempre estarem prontos para o que acontecer\u00e3o de repente, a Europa ser\u00e1 invadida, orar pelo Ocidente, orar pelo papa, pois esta \u00e9 a hora de sua grande tristeza e preocupa\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, lembre-se de que a ora\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e9 o \u00fanico rem\u00e9dio para sua alma e seu corpo, abra seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es para gra\u00e7a, porque s\u00f3 assim voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 capaz de ter paz em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es, apesar dos tempos sombrios. Queridos filhos, n\u00e3o t\u00eam medo, mas tire minhas m\u00e3os e eu vou te levar ao meu filho Jesus. Meus filhos, a persegui\u00e7\u00e3o ser\u00e1 \u00f3tima, ent\u00e3o sempre esteja na f\u00e9, mesmo quando tudo parece perdido, confie em Deus, ele estar\u00e1 perto de voc\u00ea todos os dias, at\u00e9 o fim. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u56de\u7b54\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u7977\u544a\u4e2d\u5f2f\u66f2\u819d\u76d6\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u59cb\u7ec8\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u7a81\u7136\u53d1\u751f\u7684\u4e8b\u60c5\uff0c\u6b27\u6d32\u5c06\u88ab\u4fb5\u5165\uff0c\u4e3a\u897f\u65b9\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4e3a\u6559\u7687\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u8fd9\u662f\u4ed6\u60b2\u4f24\u548c\u5173\u6ce8\u7684\u4e00\u5c0f\u65f6\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8bb0\u4f4f\u7977\u544a\u662f\u4f60\u7075\u9b42\u548c\u4f60\u7684\u8eab\u4f53\u552f\u4e00\u7684\u836f\uff0c\u655e\u5f00\u5fc3\u6249\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u53ea\u6709\u8fd9\u6837\uff0c\u5c3d\u7ba1\u9ed1\u6697\u65f6\u5149\uff0c\u4f60\u53ea\u80fd\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u62e5\u6709\u548c\u5e73\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u4f46\u6293\u4f4f\u6211\u7684\u624b\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u628a\u4f60\u5e26\u5230\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8feb\u5bb3\u4f1a\u5f88\u68d2\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u5373\u4f7f\u5728\u6240\u6709\u4f3c\u4e4e\u4e22\u5931\uff0c\u5bf9\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u4fe1\u4efb\u65f6\uff0c\u4ed6\u603b\u662f\u5728\u4fe1\u4ef0\u4e2d\uff0c\u4ed6\u6bcf\u5929\u90fd\u4f1a\u63a5\u8fd1\u4f60\uff0c\u76f4\u5230\u6700\u540e\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":23,"month_string":"March","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved children: my blessing is with you at this time of lament. Confusion has taken hold of a great part of my people, they live rejecting me, profaning the name of my most holy Mother, most pure, most chaste, refuge of sinners, consoler of the afflicted. My Mother, defender of Christians, inseparable Mother of all men, is mocked by those who believe that they are not looked upon by our most Holy Trinity. 'I am who I am', and my most holy Mother is the supreme general of the heavenly armies. To my Mother our most Holy Trinity has entrusted the custody of this generation, at this special time, so that they may not be lost. My mother will be together with my people, a people who suffer from event to event until they reach purification. My beloved people, without entering into the confusion of the world, enter into inner silence, far from the worldly, taking the most holy hand of my Mother so that together with her you may free yourselves from evil and keep yourselves on the true path that leads you to my house. My Mother of silence, Mother of faith teaches you to be creatures of silence, not in the face of injustice, but in the face of the lack of love for your brothers. Each one of my children at the warning will judge himself, first in love towards our Holy Trinity and then in love towards his brothers and they will judge themselves in each of the commandments.... Therefore conversion, conversion, conversion, repentance, repentance, repentance, prayer with the heart, duly prepared and with firm purpose of amendment. As spiritual blind, they do not look at what our Holy Trinity has made known to them so that they may be converted, they have not understood the urgency of spiritual growth in the face of the pain that is already upon all humanity. I call you to keep your spirits alert to the wolves that surround you. I invite you to bend your knees for my church, for those who make up my church. Pray my children, pray for the Middle East as it prepares for war. Pray my children, pray that they will stand with me. Pray my children, pray for how much they will suffer from the elements. Pray my children, pray for Switzerland, France, Spain and Greece, they will suffer from war. Pray my children for your brothers who suffer because of war. Live in faith, feed on my body and my blood, feed on my love. Do not fear children, do not fear. I bless you, resist, children, my mother does not forsake you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Moje kochane dzieci: moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo jest z wami w tym czasie lamentu. Du\u017ca cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 mojego ludu popad\u0142a w zam\u0119t, \u017cyje, odrzucaj\u0105c mnie, profanuj\u0105c imi\u0119 mojej naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Matki, najczystszej, najczystszej, ucieczki grzesznik\u00f3w, pocieszycielki strapionych. Moja Matka, obro\u0144czyni chrze\u015bcijan, nieod\u0142\u0105czna Matka wszystkich ludzi, jest wy\u015bmiewana przez tych, kt\u00f3rzy uwa\u017caj\u0105, \u017ce nie patrzy na nich nasza naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Tr\u00f3jca. \"Jestem, kt\u00f3ry Jestem\", a moja naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Matka jest najwy\u017cszym genera\u0142em wojsk niebieskich. Mojej Matce nasza naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Tr\u00f3jca powierzy\u0142a opiek\u0119 nad tym pokoleniem, w tym szczeg\u00f3lnym czasie, aby nie zosta\u0142o ono stracone. Moja Matka b\u0119dzie razem z moim ludem, ludem, kt\u00f3ry cierpi od wydarzenia do wydarzenia, a\u017c osi\u0105gnie oczyszczenie. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludzie, nie wchodz\u0105c w zam\u0119t \u015bwiata, wejd\u017acie w wewn\u0119trzn\u0105 cisz\u0119, z dala od tego, co doczesne, bior\u0105c naj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105 r\u0119k\u0119 mojej Matki, aby\u015bcie razem z Ni\u0105 mogli uwolni\u0107 si\u0119 od z\u0142a i trzyma\u0107 si\u0119 prawdziwej drogi, kt\u00f3ra prowadzi was do mojego domu. Moja Matka ciszy, Matka wiary uczy was by\u0107 istotami milczenia, nie w obliczu niesprawiedliwo\u015bci, ale w obliczu braku mi\u0142o\u015bci do waszych braci. Ka\u017cde z moich dzieci na ostrze\u017ceniu os\u0105dzi siebie, najpierw w mi\u0142o\u015bci do naszej Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej, a potem w mi\u0142o\u015bci do swoich braci i os\u0105dzi siebie w ka\u017cdym z przykaza\u0144.... Dlatego nawr\u00f3cenie, nawr\u00f3cenie, nawr\u00f3cenie, pokuta, pokuta, modlitwa sercem, nale\u017cycie przygotowana i ze stanowczym celem poprawy. Jako duchowi \u015blepcy nie patrz\u0105 na to, co nasza \u015awi\u0119ta Tr\u00f3jca im objawi\u0142a, aby si\u0119 nawr\u00f3cili, nie zrozumieli pilnej potrzeby duchowego wzrostu w obliczu b\u00f3lu, kt\u00f3ry ju\u017c jest na ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci. Wzywam was, aby\u015bcie byli czujni na wilki, kt\u00f3re was otaczaj\u0105. Zach\u0119cam was do zgi\u0119cia kolan za m\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, za tych, kt\u00f3rzy tworz\u0105 m\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Bliski Wsch\u00f3d, kt\u00f3ry przygotowuje si\u0119 do wojny. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 o to, aby sta\u0142y ze mn\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 o to, jak bardzo b\u0119d\u0105 cierpie\u0107 z powodu \u017cywio\u0142\u00f3w. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Szwajcari\u0119, Francj\u0119, Hiszpani\u0119 i Grecj\u0119, one b\u0119d\u0105 cierpie\u0107 z powodu wojny. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci za waszych braci, kt\u00f3rzy cierpi\u0105 z powodu wojny. \u017byjcie w wierze, karmcie si\u0119 moim cia\u0142em i moj\u0105 krwi\u0105, karmcie si\u0119 moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119 dzieci, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, opornych, dzieci, moja Matka nie opuszcza was. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":24,"month_string":"March","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear daughter, thank you for listening to My call in your heart. Men still do not understand the reason for my coming, I want to save this humanity, to which I say: stop raising your curiosity in reading my messages, but live them. I see my children getting lost and I want to show them the way. I am coming as a loving Mother to show the light in the midst of darkness. With your prayers and True Faith you can avoid the third world war, but still you are closed in your shells and do not see beyond, catastrophes are coming, but you do not abandon the sacraments. Despite my tears, your hearts are hard and you do not let the light in, I ask that your Faith be not only of words, but of deeds, you have the most powerful weapon, the prayer of the Holy Rosary, pray. As time goes by, the Christian Faith will no longer be professed and you will be forced to hide, be prepared for this as well, communism advances with rapidity. All of this will take place and will be the punishment for the heresies and blasphemies that have been perpetrated until now. Now, my daughter, I leave you with my Motherly blessing, in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Sehr geehrte Tochter, vielen Dank, dass Sie meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen angeh\u00f6rt haben. M\u00e4nner verstehen den Grund f\u00fcr mein Kommen immer noch nicht, ich m\u00f6chte diese Menschheit retten, zu der ich sage: H\u00f6r auf, deine Neugier zu erheben, um meine Nachrichten zu lesen, aber leben Sie sie. Ich sehe, dass meine Kinder verloren gehen, und ich m\u00f6chte ihnen den Weg zeigen. Ich komme als liebevolle Mutter, um das Licht inmitten der Dunkelheit zu zeigen. Mit Ihren Gebeten und ihrem wahren Glauben k\u00f6nnen Sie den dritten Weltkrieg vermeiden, aber Sie sind immer noch in Ihren Muscheln geschlossen und sehen nicht dar\u00fcber hinaus, Katastrophen kommen, aber Sie geben die Sakramente nicht auf. Trotz meiner Tr\u00e4nen sind Ihre Herzen hart und Sie lassen das Licht nicht herein, ich frage nicht, dass Ihr Glaube nicht nur von Worten ist, sondern von Taten, Sie haben die m\u00e4chtigste Waffe, das Gebet des Heiligen Rosenkranzes, beten Sie. Mit der Zeit wird der christliche Glaube nicht mehr bearbeitet, und Sie werden gezwungen sein, sich zu verbergen, darauf herzustellen, dass der Kommunismus mit der Schnelligkeit vorsteht. All dies findet statt und wird die Bestrafung f\u00fcr die bisherigen H\u00e4resien und Blasphemies bestrebt. Nun, meine Tochter, verlasse ich Sie mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen, im Namen des Vaters und des Sohns und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Querida hija, gracias por escuchar mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Los hombres a\u00fan no entienden por qu\u00e9 ven\u00eda mi venida, quiero salvar a esta humanidad, a quien digo: Deja de elevar la curiosidad al leer mis mensajes, pero vivirlos. Veo a mis hijos para perderse y me gustar\u00eda mostrarles el camino. Vengo como madre amorosa para mostrar la luz en medio de la oscuridad. Con tus oraciones y con fe real puedes evitar la Guerra Mundial de la Tercera Mundial, pero todav\u00eda est\u00e1s cerrado en tus conchas y no lo ves m\u00e1s, las cat\u00e1strofes est\u00e1n llegando, pero no abandona los sacramentos. A pesar de mis l\u00e1grimas, tus corazones son duros y no tienes la luz, le pido que tu fe no sean solo palabras, sino de hechos, tienes el arma m\u00e1s poderosa, la oraci\u00f3n del Santo Rosario, ora. Con el progreso del tiempo, la fe cristiana no ser\u00e1 m\u00e1s profesada y se te ver\u00e1 obligado a ocultarlo, prepararse para esto, avanza el comunismo con la velocidad. Todo tendr\u00e1 lugar y ser\u00e1 el castigo por las herej\u00edas, los blasfemias y las blasfemias que se perpetran hasta ahora. Ahora, mi hija, te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna, en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Cher fille, merci d'avoir \u00e9cout\u00e9 mon appel dans votre coeur. Les hommes ne comprennent toujours pas la raison de ma venue, je veux sauver cette humanit\u00e9, \u00e0 laquelle je dis: arr\u00eatez de soulever votre curiosit\u00e9 en lisant mes messages, mais vivez-les. Je vois que mes enfants se perdent et je veux leur montrer le chemin. Je viens comme une m\u00e8re aimante pour montrer la lumi\u00e8re au milieu des t\u00e9n\u00e8bres. Avec vos pri\u00e8res et votre vraie foi, vous pouvez \u00e9viter la troisi\u00e8me guerre mondiale, mais vous \u00eates toujours ferm\u00e9 dans vos coquilles et que vous ne voyez pas au-del\u00e0 des catastrophes, mais vous n'abandonnez pas les sacrements. Malgr\u00e9 mes larmes, vos c\u0153urs sont difficiles et que vous ne laissez pas la lumi\u00e8re dans, je vous demande que votre foi soit non seulement de mots, mais d'actes, vous avez l'arme la plus puissante, la pri\u00e8re du Saint Rosaire, prie. Au fil du temps, la foi chr\u00e9tienne ne sera plus professe et vous serez oblig\u00e9 de vous cacher, en vous pr\u00e9parez \u00e9galement, le communisme avance avec rapidit\u00e9. Tout cela aura lieu et sera la punition pour les h\u00e9r\u00e9sies et les blasph\u00e8mes qui ont \u00e9t\u00e9 perp\u00e9tr\u00e9s jusqu'\u00e0 pr\u00e9sent. Maintenant, ma fille, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cara figlia, grazie per aver ascoltato la mia chiamata nel tuo cuore. Gli uomini ancora non capiscono il perch\u00e9 della mia venuta, Io voglio salvare questa umanit\u00e0, alla quale dico: smettete di innalzare la curiosit\u00e0 nel leggere i miei messaggi, ma viveteli. Vedo i miei figli perdersi e vorrei mostrare loro la strada. Vengo come Madre amorevole per far vedere la luce in mezzo alle tenebre. Con le vostre preghiere e con Vera Fede potrete evitare la terza guerra mondiale, ma ancora siete chiusi nei vostri gusci e non vedete oltre, le catastrofi stanno arrivando, ma voi non abbandonate i sacramenti.  Nonostante le mie lacrime, i vostri cuori sono duri e non fate entrare la luce, chiedo che la vostra Fede non sia solo di parole, ma di fatti, avete l\u2019arma pi\u00f9 potente, la preghiera del Santo Rosario, pregate. Con l\u2019avanzare del tempo, la Fede Cristiana non sar\u00e0 pi\u00f9 professata e sarete costretti a nascondervi, siate preparati anche a questo, il comunismo avanza con celerit\u00e0. Tutto quanto avverr\u00e0 e sar\u00e0 la punizione per le eresie, le bestemmie e le blasfemie che fino ad oggi sono perpetrate. Ora, figlia mia, ti lascio con la mia benedizione Materna, nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Droga c\u00f3rko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce wys\u0142ucha\u0142a\u015b w swoim sercu mojego wo\u0142ania. Ludzie nadal nie rozumiej\u0105 powodu mojego przyj\u015bcia, chc\u0119 ocali\u0107 t\u0119 ludzko\u015b\u0107, kt\u00f3rej m\u00f3wi\u0119: przesta\u0144cie rozbudza\u0107 swoj\u0105 ciekawo\u015b\u0107, czytaj\u0105c moje or\u0119dzia, ale \u017cyjcie nimi. Widz\u0119, \u017ce moje dzieci si\u0119 gubi\u0105 i chc\u0119 im wskaza\u0107 drog\u0119. Przychodz\u0119 jako kochaj\u0105ca Matka, aby ukaza\u0107 \u015bwiat\u0142o po\u015br\u00f3d ciemno\u015bci. Dzi\u0119ki waszym modlitwom i prawdziwej wierze mo\u017cecie unikn\u0105\u0107 trzeciej wojny \u015bwiatowej, ale nadal jeste\u015bcie zamkni\u0119ci w swoich skorupach i nie widzicie dalej. Nadchodz\u0105 katastrofy, lecz nie porzucajcie sakrament\u00f3w. Pomimo moich \u0142ez, wasze serca s\u0105 twarde i nie wpuszczacie \u015bwiat\u0142a, prosz\u0119, aby wasza wiara by\u0142a nie tylko s\u0142owami, ale i czynami, macie najpot\u0119\u017cniejsz\u0105 bro\u0144, modlitw\u0119 R\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ca \u015awi\u0119tego, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. Z czasem wiara chrze\u015bcija\u0144ska przestanie by\u0107 wyznawana i b\u0119dziecie zmuszeni do ukrywania si\u0119, b\u0105d\u017acie na to przygotowani, komunizm rozwija si\u0119 bardzo szybko. Wszystko to si\u0119 spe\u0142ni i b\u0119dzie kar\u0105 za herezje i blu\u017anierstwa, kt\u00f3re do tej pory by\u0142y pope\u0142niane. Teraz, moja c\u00f3rko, zostawiam ci\u0119 z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem, w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Querida filha, obrigado por ouvir minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Os homens ainda n\u00e3o entendem a raz\u00e3o para a minha vinda, eu quero salvar essa humanidade, ao qual eu digo: Pare de aumentar sua curiosidade em ler minhas mensagens, mas viv\u00ea-las. Eu vejo meus filhos se perdem e quero mostrar-lhes o caminho. Eu estou vindo como uma m\u00e3e amorosa para mostrar a luz no meio da escurid\u00e3o. Com suas ora\u00e7\u00f5es e verdadeira f\u00e9, voc\u00ea pode evitar a terceira guerra mundial, mas ainda assim voc\u00ea est\u00e1 fechado em suas conchas e n\u00e3o v\u00ea al\u00e9m, as cat\u00e1strofes est\u00e3o chegando, mas voc\u00ea n\u00e3o abandona os sacramentos. Apesar das minhas l\u00e1grimas, seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es s\u00e3o dif\u00edceis e voc\u00ea n\u00e3o deixa a luz, pe\u00e7o que sua f\u00e9 n\u00e3o seja apenas de palavras, mas de a\u00e7\u00f5es, voc\u00ea tem a arma mais poderosa, a ora\u00e7\u00e3o do Santo Ros\u00e1rio, ore. Com o passar do tempo, a f\u00e9 crist\u00e3 n\u00e3o ser\u00e1 mais professada e voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 for\u00e7ada a se esconder, estar preparado para isso tamb\u00e9m, o comunismo avan\u00e7a com rapidez. Tudo isso acontecer\u00e1 e ser\u00e1 a puni\u00e7\u00e3o pelas heresias e blasf\u00eamias que foram perpetradas at\u00e9 agora. Agora, minha filha, eu deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o maternal, em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u5fc3\u91cc\u542c\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u7537\u4eba\u4ecd\u7136\u4e0d\u660e\u767d\u6211\u6765\u7684\u539f\u56e0\uff0c\u6211\u60f3\u62ef\u6551\u8fd9\u4e2a\u4eba\u6027\uff0c\u6211\u8bf4\uff1a\u505c\u6b62\u63d0\u9ad8\u4f60\u7684\u597d\u5947\u5fc3\u9605\u8bfb\u6211\u7684\u6d88\u606f\uff0c\u4f46\u6d3b\u7740\u3002\u6211\u770b\u5230\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u8ff7\u8def\u4e86\uff0c\u6211\u60f3\u5411\u4ed6\u4eec\u5c55\u793a\u3002\u6211\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u5145\u6ee1\u7231\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\uff0c\u5728\u9ed1\u6697\u4e2d\u5c55\u793a\u5149\u7ebf\u3002\u968f\u7740\u4f60\u7684\u7948\u7977\u548c\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\uff0c\u4f60\u53ef\u4ee5\u907f\u514d\u7b2c\u4e09\u6b21\u4e16\u754c\u5927\u6218\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u4ecd\u7136\u5728\u4f60\u7684\u8d1d\u58f3\u4e2d\u95ed\u4e0a\u800c\u4e0d\u770b\u5230\u8d85\u8d8a\uff0c\u707e\u96be\u5373\u5c06\u5230\u6765\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u6ca1\u6709\u653e\u5f03\u5723\u793c\u3002\u5c3d\u7ba1\u6211\u7684\u773c\u6cea\uff0c\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u5f88\u96be\uff0c\u4f60\u4e0d\u8ba9\u5149\u660e\uff0c\u6211\u8981\u6c42\u4f60\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u4e0d\u4ec5\u4ec5\u662f\u8a00\u8bed\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u5bf9\u884c\u4e3a\uff0c\u4f60\u6709\u6700\u5f3a\u5927\u7684\u6b66\u5668\uff0c\u5723\u7f57\u5c3c\u4e9a\u7684\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u3002\u968f\u7740\u65f6\u95f4\u7684\u63a8\u79fb\uff0c\u57fa\u7763\u6559\u4fe1\u4ef0\u5c06\u4e0d\u518d\u81ea\u79f0\uff0c\u4f60\u5c06\u88ab\u8feb\u9690\u85cf\uff0c\u4e3a\u6b64\u505a\u597d\u51c6\u5907\uff0c\u5171\u4ea7\u4e3b\u4e49\u8fc5\u901f\u8fdb\u5c55\u3002\u6240\u6709\u8fd9\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u5c06\u53d1\u751f\uff0c\u5e76\u5c06\u6210\u4e3a\u8fc4\u4eca\u4e3a\u6b62\u72af\u4e0b\u7684\u8650\u5f85\u548c\u4eb5\u6e0e\u7684\u60e9\u7f5a\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u6211\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u6bcd\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\uff0c\u963f\u66fc\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":25,"month_string":"March","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My daughter, thank you for accepting my call into your heart. Daughter, that day while I was humming Praises to God and asking for peace for the whole earth, behold a wonderful angel came and lit up the room and his sweet voice announced to me that I would have a son by the Holy Spirit, despite my virginity and spoke to me of the greatness of Jesus. I prayed all my life for peace, just as I do today, yet men did not listen to me and even now they do not listen. My daughter, today, many believe that this consecration can have validity, but the war has begun, my Son is angry, because if it had been pronounced in time, peace would have descended on this humanity, but it will not be so, because no one can offend God. My daughter, everything will be slightly mitigated by prayers recited with true faith. Soon you will experience dark times for the reasons I have just told you, please return to God. I bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity.","text_de":"Meine Tochter, danke, dass Sie meinen Anruf in Ihr Herz angenommen haben. Tochter, an diesem Tag, w\u00e4hrend ich Gott gebl\u00fcht hatte und nach Frieden f\u00fcr die ganze Erde bat, siehe einen wunderbaren Engel kam und beleuchtete das Zimmer und seine s\u00fc\u00dfe Stimme k\u00fcndigte mir an, dass ich trotz meines einen Sohn des Heiligen Geistes hatte Jungfr\u00e4ulichkeit und sprach mit mir von der Gr\u00f6\u00dfe Jesu. Ich habe mein ganzes Leben f\u00fcr den Frieden gebetet, genau wie ich heute tue, aber M\u00e4nner h\u00f6rten mir nicht zu und selbst jetzt h\u00f6ren sie nicht zu. Meine Tochter, heute, dass diese Weihe eine G\u00fcltigkeit haben kann, aber der Krieg hat begonnen, mein Sohn ist w\u00fctend, denn wenn es in der Zeit ausgesprochen worden w\u00e4re, h\u00e4tte der Frieden auf diese Menschheit stiegen, aber es ist nicht so, weil Niemand kann Gott beleidigen. Meine Tochter, alles wird von Gebeten leicht gemildert, um mit echten Glauben gerufen zu werden. Bald erleben Sie dunkle Zeiten aus den Gr\u00fcnden, die ich Ihnen gerade erz\u00e4hlt habe, bitte kehren Sie an Gott zur\u00fcck. Ich segne dich im Namen der heiligsten Dreieinigkeit.","text_es":"Mi hija, gracias por dar la bienvenida a mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Hija, ese d\u00eda mientras lo hac\u00edamos a Dios y le pedimos la paz a la Tierra a toda la Tierra, aqu\u00ed vino un \u00e1ngel maravilloso que ilumin\u00f3 la habitaci\u00f3n y su dulce voz anunci\u00f3 que habr\u00eda tenido un hijo por el Esp\u00edritu Santo, a pesar de mi virginidad y habl\u00f3. sobre la grandeza de Jes\u00fas. Rezo por toda mi vida por la paz, as\u00ed como hoy, pero los hombres no me escucharon e incluso ahora no escuchan. Mi hija, hoy, muchos creen que esta consagraci\u00f3n puede ser v\u00e1lida, pero comenz\u00f3 la guerra, mi hijo est\u00e1 enojado, porque si hubiera sido pronunciado en el tiempo, la paz caer\u00eda sobre esta humanidad, pero no ser\u00e1 as\u00ed, porque nadie Puede ofender a Dios. Mi hija, todo ser\u00e1 ligeramente mitigado por las oraciones que act\u00faan con la verdadera fe. Pronto vivir\u00e1s tiempos oscuros por las razones por las que acabo de narrar, por favor, vuelva a Dios. Te bendigo en el nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad.","text_fr":"Ma fille, merci d'avoir accept\u00e9 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Fille, ce jour-l\u00e0 alors que j'\u00e9tais des louanges \u00e0 Dieu et que je demandais la paix pour la Terre enti\u00e8re, voici qu'un ange merveilleux est venu et \u00e9clair\u00e9 la pi\u00e8ce et sa douce voix m'a annonc\u00e9 que j'aurais un fils par le Saint-Esprit, malgr\u00e9 mon virginit\u00e9 et me parla de la grandeur de J\u00e9sus. J'ai pri\u00e9 toute ma vie pour la paix, tout comme moi aujourd'hui, mais les hommes ne m'ont pas \u00e9cout\u00e9 et m\u00eame maintenant ils n'\u00e9coutent pas. Ma fille, aujourd'hui, beaucoup pensent que cette cons\u00e9cration peut avoir une validit\u00e9, mais la guerre a commenc\u00e9, mon fils est en col\u00e8re, car si elle avait \u00e9t\u00e9 prononc\u00e9e \u00e0 temps, la paix serait descendue sur cette humanit\u00e9, mais ce ne sera pas aussi, car Personne ne peut offenser Dieu. Ma fille, tout sera l\u00e9g\u00e8rement att\u00e9nu\u00e9 par des pri\u00e8res r\u00e9cit\u00e9es avec une vraie foi. Bient\u00f4t, vous ressentirez des temps sombres pour les raisons pour lesquelles je viens de vous dire, veuillez retourner \u00e0 Dieu. Je vous b\u00e9nis au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9.","text_it":"Figlia mia, grazie per aver accolto la mia chiamata nel tuo cuore. Figlia, quel giorno mentre canticchiavo Lodi a Dio e chiedevo la pace per la terra tutta, ecco che arriv\u00f2 un angelo meraviglioso che illumin\u00f2 la stanza e la sua voce dolce mi annunci\u00f2 che avrei avuto un figlio per opera dello Spirito Santo, nonostante la mia verginit\u00e0 e mi parl\u00f2 della grandezza di Ges\u00f9. Pregai per tutta la mia vita per la pace, cos\u00ec come oggi, eppure gli uomini non mi hanno ascoltato e anche adesso non ascoltano. Figlia mia, oggi, molti credono che questa consacrazione possa avere validit\u00e0, ma la guerra ha avuto inizio, mio Figlio \u00e8 adirato, perch\u00e9 se fosse stata pronunciata in tempo, la pace sarebbe scesa su questa umanit\u00e0, ma non sar\u00e0 cos\u00ec, perch\u00e9 nessuno pu\u00f2 offendere Dio. Figlia mia, tutto verr\u00e0 lievemente mitigato dalle preghiere recitate con vera fede. Presto vivrete tempi bui per i motivi che ti ho appena narrato, vi prego tornate a Dio. Ti benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0.","text_pl":"Moja c\u00f3rko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce przyj\u0119\u0142a\u015b w swoim sercu moje wezwanie. C\u00f3rko, tego dnia, kiedy nuci\u0142am pie\u015bni pochwalne dla Boga i prosi\u0142am o pok\u00f3j dla ca\u0142ego \u015bwiata, przyszed\u0142 cudowny anio\u0142 i roz\u015bwietli\u0142 pomieszczenie, a jego s\u0142odki g\u0142os oznajmi\u0142 mi, \u017ce b\u0119d\u0119 mia\u0142a syna za spraw\u0105 Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, pomimo mojego dziewictwa, i opowiedzia\u0142 mi o wielko\u015bci Jezusa. Ca\u0142e \u017cycie modli\u0142am si\u0119 o pok\u00f3j, tak jak i dzisiaj, ale ludzie mnie nie s\u0142uchali i nie s\u0142uchaj\u0105 nawet teraz. Moja c\u00f3rko, dzisiaj wielu wierzy, \u017ce ta konsekracja mo\u017ce by\u0107 wa\u017cna, ale rozpocz\u0119\u0142a si\u0119 wojna, m\u00f3j Syn jest zagniewany, bo gdyby zosta\u0142a wypowiedziana na czas, pok\u00f3j zst\u0105pi\u0142by na t\u0119 ludzko\u015b\u0107, ale tak si\u0119 nie stanie, bo nikt nie mo\u017ce obra\u017ca\u0107 Boga. Moja c\u00f3rko, wszystko zostanie nieco z\u0142agodzone przez modlitwy odmawiane z prawdziw\u0105 wiar\u0105. Wkr\u00f3tce prze\u017cyjecie mroczne chwile z powod\u00f3w, o kt\u00f3rych w\u0142a\u015bnie wam powiedzia\u0142em, prosz\u0119, powr\u00f3\u0107cie do Boga. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej.","text_pt":"Minha filha, obrigado por aceitar minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Filha, naquele dia, enquanto eu estava cantarolando elogios a Deus e pedindo paz para toda a terra, eis um anjo maravilhoso veio e iluminou o quarto e sua voz doce anunciou para mim que eu teria um filho pelo Esp\u00edrito Santo, apesar de meu virgindade e falou comigo da grandeza de Jesus. Eu orei toda a minha vida pela paz, assim como eu fa\u00e7o hoje, mas os homens n\u00e3o me ouvem e at\u00e9 agora eles n\u00e3o ouvem. Minha filha, hoje, muitos acreditam que esta consagra\u00e7\u00e3o pode ter validade, mas a guerra come\u00e7ou, meu filho est\u00e1 zangado, porque se tivesse sido pronunciado no tempo, a paz teria descido nessa humanidade, mas n\u00e3o ser\u00e1 assim, porque Ningu\u00e9m pode ofender a Deus. Minha filha, tudo ser\u00e1 ligeiramente mitigado por ora\u00e7\u00f5es recitadas com a verdadeira f\u00e9. Logo voc\u00ea experimentar\u00e1 tempos sombrios por as raz\u00f5es pelas quais acabei de lhe contar, por favor retorne a Deus. Eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u63a5\u53d7\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\u810f\u3002\u90a3\u4e00\u5929\uff0c\u5f53\u6211\u54fc\u5531\u7740\u4e0a\u5e1d\u5e76\u4e3a\u6574\u4e2a\u5730\u7403\u5bfb\u6c42\u548c\u5e73\u65f6\uff0c\u5973\u513f\u6765\u770b\u770b\u4e00\u4e2a\u7f8e\u5999\u7684\u5929\u4f7f\u6765\u4e86\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u4ed6\u7684\u751c\u871c\u7684\u58f0\u97f3\u5ba3\u5e03\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u6709\u4e00\u4e2a\u513f\u5b50\uff0c\u5c3d\u7ba1\u6211\u6709\u7ae5\u8d1e\u5e76\u4e0e\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u4f1f\u5927\u8c08\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7948\u7977\u6211\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\uff0c\u5c31\u50cf\u6211\u4eca\u5929\u4e00\u6837\uff0c\u4f46\u7537\u4eba\u6ca1\u6709\u542c\u6211\uff0c\u751a\u81f3\u73b0\u5728\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e0d\u542c\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u4eca\u5929\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u8ba4\u4e3a\u8fd9\u79cd\u5949\u732e\u53ef\u4ee5\u6709\u6709\u6548\u6027\uff0c\u4f46\u6218\u4e89\u5df2\u7ecf\u5f00\u59cb\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u751f\u6c14\u4e86\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5982\u679c\u5b83\u5df2\u7ecf\u53d1\u8868\u4e86\u5ba3\u5e03\uff0c\u4f46\u548c\u5e73\u5c31\u4f1a\u5bf9\u8fd9\u4e2a\u4eba\u6027\u8d77\u6765\uff0c\u4f46\u5b83\u4e0d\u4f1a\u90a3\u4e48\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6ca1\u6709\u4eba\u53ef\u4ee5\u5192\u72af\u4e0a\u5e1d\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u4f1a\u88ab\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u7948\u7977\u7a0d\u5fae\u51cf\u8f7b\u3002\u5f88\u5feb\u4f60\u4f1a\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u521a\u544a\u8bc9\u4f60\u7684\u539f\u56e0\u800c\u4f53\u9a8c\u9ed1\u6697\u65f6\u5149\uff0c\u8bf7\u8fd4\u56de\u4e0a\u5e1d\u3002\u6211\u4ee5\u6700\u795e\u5723\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":26,"month_string":"March","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for responding to My call in your hearts and for bending your knees in prayer. My children, I have already spoken, I ask you: open your hearts to grace to be worthy of all that God has in store for you. My children, pray for peace, but first of all for inner peace; do not lose yourselves in ephemeral things, but think more of your soul. Again I ask you: convert, look at the dark times, do not wait for God's Final Judgment, but be aware of all that will come, if you are not ready you will not be able to face the warning. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen geantwortet haben, und um Ihre Knie im Gebet zu biegen. Meine Kinder, ich habe bereits gesprochen, ich frage Sie: \u00d6ffnen Sie Ihre Herzen, um Gnaden zu gr\u00fc\u00dfen, um allem, was Gott f\u00fcr Sie im Laden hat. Meine Kinder, bete f\u00fcr den Frieden, aber vor allem f\u00fcr inneren Frieden; Verliere dich nicht in ephemeren Dingen, aber denken Sie mehr von Ihrer Seele. Wieder frage ich Sie: Konvertieren, schauen Sie sich die dunklen Zeiten an, warten Sie nicht auf das endg\u00fcltige Urteil Gottes, aber seien Sie sich dessen bewusst, dass Sie kommen, wenn Sie nicht fertig sind, k\u00f6nnen Sie sich nicht der Warnung stellen. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder a mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n y para doblar las rodillas en la oraci\u00f3n. Mis hijos, ya he hablado, te lo pido: abre tus corazones a Grace para ser digno de todo lo que Dios tiene en la tienda para ti. Los ni\u00f1os, oren por la paz, pero en primer lugar para la paz interior, no se pierden las cosas ef\u00edmeras, pero piensan m\u00e1s sobre su alma. Todav\u00eda le pregunto: Convi\u00e9rtete, mira los tiempos oscuros, no espere el juicio final de Dios, pero tenga en cuenta todo lo que vendr\u00e1, si no est\u00e1 listo, no podr\u00e1 enfrentar la advertencia. Ahora te bendigo en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs et de plier vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re. Mes enfants, j'ai d\u00e9j\u00e0 parl\u00e9, je vous demande: ouvrez vos c\u0153urs \u00e0 la gr\u00e2ce digne de tout ce que Dieu a en r\u00e9serve pour vous. Mes enfants, prier pour la paix, mais tout d'abord pour la paix int\u00e9rieure; Ne vous perdez pas dans des choses \u00e9ph\u00e9m\u00e8res, mais pensez plus de votre \u00e2me. Encore une fois, je vous demande: convertir, regarder les temps sombres, n'attendez pas le jugement final de Dieu, mais soyez conscient de tout ce qui viendra, si vous n'\u00eates pas pr\u00eat, vous ne pourrez pas faire face \u00e0 l'avertissement. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore e per aver piegato le ginocchia nella preghiera. Figli miei, Io ho gi\u00e0 parlato, vi chiedo: aprite i vostri cuori alla grazia per essere degni di tutto ci\u00f2 che Dio ha in serbo per voi. Figli, pregate per la pace, ma prima di tutto per la pace interiore, non perdetevi in cose effimere, ma pensate pi\u00f9 alla vostra anima. Ancora vi chiedo: convertitevi, guardate i tempi bui, non attendete il giudizio finale di Dio, ma siate consapevoli di tutto ci\u00f2 che arriver\u00e0, se non sarete pronti non potrete affrontare l\u2019avvertimento. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach i \u017ce ukl\u0119kneli\u015bcie do modlitwy. Dzieci moje, ju\u017c o tym m\u00f3wi\u0142am, prosz\u0119 was: otw\u00f3rzcie wasze serca na \u0142ask\u0119, aby\u015bcie byli godni tego wszystkiego, co B\u00f3g ma dla was w zanadrzu. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 o pok\u00f3j, ale przede wszystkim o pok\u00f3j wewn\u0119trzny; nie zatracajcie si\u0119 w rzeczach ulotnych, ale my\u015blcie bardziej o swojej duszy. Ponownie prosz\u0119 was: nawracajcie si\u0119, patrzcie na ciemne czasy, nie czekajcie na Ostateczny S\u0105d Bo\u017cy, ale b\u0105d\u017acie \u015bwiadomi wszystkiego, co nadejdzie, je\u015bli nie jeste\u015bcie gotowi, nie b\u0119dziecie w stanie stawi\u0107 czo\u0142a ostrze\u017ceniu. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por responder ao meu chamado em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e para dobrar os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, j\u00e1 falei, pe\u00e7o-lhe: Abra seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es para gra\u00e7a para ser digno de tudo o que Deus tem reservado para voc\u00ea. Meus filhos, oram pela paz, mas antes de tudo pela paz interior; N\u00e3o se perca em coisas ef\u00eameras, mas pense mais da sua alma. Mais uma vez eu pergunto: converter, olhe para os tempos sombrios, n\u00e3o espere pelo julgamento final de Deus, mas esteja ciente de tudo o que vir\u00e1, se voc\u00ea n\u00e3o estiver pronto, voc\u00ea n\u00e3o ser\u00e1 capaz de enfrentar o aviso. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u7977\u544a\u4e2d\u5f2f\u66f2\u819d\u76d6\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u5df2\u7ecf\u8bf4\u8fc7\u4e86\uff0c\u6211\u95ee\u4f60\uff1a\u655e\u5f00\u5fc3\u6249\u6765\u6069\u5178\uff0c\u503c\u5f97\u6240\u6709\u4e0a\u5e1d\u5728\u5546\u5e97\u91cc\u7684\u6240\u6709\u4eba\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e3a\u548c\u5e73\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4f46\u9996\u5148\u662f\u5185\u5fc3\u7684\u548c\u5e73;\u4e0d\u8981\u5728\u77ed\u6682\u7684\u4e8b\u60c5\u4e2d\u8ff7\u5931\u81ea\u5df1\uff0c\u4f46\u60f3\u60f3\u66f4\u591a\u4f60\u7684\u7075\u9b42\u3002\u6211\u518d\u6b21\u95ee\u4f60\uff1a\u8f6c\u6362\uff0c\u770b\u770b\u9ed1\u6697\u65f6\u5149\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u7b49\u5f85\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u6700\u7ec8\u5224\u65ad\uff0c\u4f46\u8981\u610f\u8bc6\u5230\u6240\u6709\u90fd\u4f1a\u6765\u7684\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u8fd8\u6ca1\u51c6\u5907\u597d\uff0c\u4f60\u5c06\u65e0\u6cd5\u9762\u5bf9\u8b66\u544a\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":27,"month_string":"March","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: I bless you as head of the heavenly legions. Our King and Lord are adored and revered forever and ever, Amen. Humanity, prepare yourselves, repent of the evil committed, confess your sins and dispose yourselves to conversion, it is necessary for the faith to be cemented on a solid foundation. Extremely strong moments are approaching. The earthquakes increase their intensity, the water of the seas with its unexpected and high waves cause fear to man. Pray with the heart duly prepared spiritually, love and fulfil the commandments and the sacraments. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, do not allow yourselves to be confused, keep yourselves on the only way of salvation, the way of the Cross, which contains infinite love, faith, hope and charity. What is happening to this generation is not by chance, it is the work of those who obey the orders of evil in preparation for what they need for the absolute domination of all human creatures. Evil is rapidly taking possession of humanity, leading it to become insensitive and unrecognizable in its disobedience towards the Paternal House. Hunger takes possession of humanity as soon as the nation\u2019s move forward in the strife, which does not arise by chance or differences between nations, but have been traced from before by the devil himself and his own. Children of our Queen and Mother of the End Times, be constant preparators on behalf of humanity for the constant offenses to such an exalted Queen and Mother. Pray, pray for your suffering brothers. Pray, pray to our Queen and Mother for all mankind. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, the human creature believes to intervene in the divine designs and soon forgets that God alone is just judge, omnipotent and merciful. Receive my blessing. I protect you with my legions at the service of the Holy Trinity. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was jako zwierzchnik legion\u00f3w niebieskich. Naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana wielbimy i czcimy na wieki wiek\u00f3w, Amen. Ludzko\u015bci, przygotujcie si\u0119, \u017ca\u0142ujcie za pope\u0142nione z\u0142o, wyznajcie swoje grzechy i uspos\u00f3bcie si\u0119 do nawr\u00f3cenia, jest to konieczne, aby wiara zosta\u0142a scementowana na solidnym fundamencie. Zbli\u017caj\u0105 si\u0119 wyj\u0105tkowo silne chwile. Trz\u0119sienia ziemi zwi\u0119kszaj\u0105 swoj\u0105 intensywno\u015b\u0107, wody m\u00f3rz swoimi niespodziewanymi i wysokimi falami wywo\u0142uj\u0105 strach u cz\u0142owieka. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 sercem nale\u017cycie przygotowanym duchowo, kochajcie i wype\u0142niajcie przykazania i sakramenty. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, nie dajcie si\u0119 zwie\u015b\u0107, trzymajcie si\u0119 jedynej drogi zbawienia, drogi krzy\u017cowej, kt\u00f3ra zawiera w sobie niesko\u0144czon\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, wiar\u0119, nadziej\u0119 i mi\u0142osierdzie. To, co dzieje si\u0119 z tym pokoleniem, nie jest przypadkiem, jest to dzie\u0142o tych, kt\u00f3rzy pos\u0142usznie wykonuj\u0105 rozkazy z\u0142a, przygotowuj\u0105c to, co jest im potrzebne do absolutnej dominacji nad wszystkimi ludzkimi stworzeniami. Z\u0142o szybko bierze w posiadanie ludzko\u015b\u0107, doprowadzaj\u0105c j\u0105 do nieczu\u0142o\u015bci i nierozpoznawalno\u015bci w jej niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwie wobec Domu Ojcowskiego. G\u0142\u00f3d bierze w posiadanie ludzko\u015b\u0107, gdy tylko narody posuwaj\u0105 si\u0119 naprz\u00f3d w niesnaskach, kt\u00f3re nie powstaj\u0105 przez przypadek lub r\u00f3\u017cnice mi\u0119dzy narodami, ale zosta\u0142y wy\u015bledzone od dawien dawna przez samego diab\u0142a i jego w\u0142asnych. Dzieci naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych, b\u0105d\u017acie nieustannymi przygotowuj\u0105cymi w imieniu ludzko\u015bci na ci\u0105g\u0142e obra\u017canie tak wywy\u017cszonej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za waszych cierpi\u0105cych braci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 do naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki za ca\u0142\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107. Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, ludzkie stworzenie wierzy, by ingerowa\u0107 w boskie projekty i szybko zapomina, \u017ce tylko B\u00f3g jest S\u0119dzi\u0105 Sprawiedliwym, Wszechmocnym i Mi\u0142osiernym. Przyjmij moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo. Chroni\u0119 was moimi legionami w s\u0142u\u017cbie Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":3,"day":31,"month_string":"March","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart: people of my Divine Son: receive my motherly blessing. Receive my word as balm for each of you, children of my Divine Son. My children: I shed my tears of sorrow for this generation that continues to be mired in sin and disobedience. I shed my tears for the pains, sacrileges, heresies with which you offend my Divine Son and for the interrupted life of the innocent, giving them death. I shed my tears of sorrow for what is coming for all mankind, for the sufferings, persecutions, revolts, social uprisings, diseases and famines. I shed my tears for the temples closed by order of those who come to dominate humanity and prevent my children from worshipping my Divine Son. I shed my tears over the earth and water for the elements that rise up and cause harm to the human creature. Beloved children: the pains you are facing and will face will overcome humanity; therefore, the calls to conversion, to the urgency that the human creature not allow itself to live in ignorance of the law of God, of sacred scripture, of the sacraments, of the works of mercy and in the practice of lovelessness and impiety. Children, stay away from anyone who makes rash judgments.... 'For as you judge, so you will be judged, and the same measure you use for others will be used for you.' Satan is favouring the division of my son's church, do not fall into his traps: gather, pray, discern! Pay attention to the elements, these agitated ones are rushing against the human creature. At this moment the human creature lives saturated by the worldly and hastens to work and act against his brothers. Pray children, pray, pray, the earth trembles and my children suffer. Pray children, pray for the Middle East. Pray children, pray for the advance of world power over mankind. Pray children, pray for the church, pray and confront with firm faith all that desires to confuse you. Pray children, pray for Argentina. Pray children, the war comes where it is not expected. I love you little children. Each one within your mission fulfil what my son has entrusted to you. I invite you to be more of my son. I am with you, do not fear, I protect you. My motherly love remains upon each of my children. Live in the peace of my son. I love you. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca: ludzie mojego Boskiego Syna: przyjmijcie moje matczyne b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo. Przyjmijcie moje s\u0142owo jako balsam dla ka\u017cdego z was, dzieci mojego Boskiego Syna. Moje dzieci, wylewam moje \u0142zy smutku za to pokolenie, kt\u00f3re nadal jest pogr\u0105\u017cone w grzechu i niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwie. Wylewam moje \u0142zy za b\u00f3le, \u015bwi\u0119tokradztwa, herezje, kt\u00f3rymi obra\u017cacie mojego Boskiego Syna i za przerwanie \u017cycia niewinnych, daj\u0105c im \u015bmier\u0107. Wylewam \u0142zy \u017calu za to, co nadchodzi dla ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci, za cierpienia, prze\u015bladowania, bunty, powstania spo\u0142eczne, choroby i g\u0142\u00f3d. Wylewam \u0142zy za \u015bwi\u0105tynie zamkni\u0119te z rozkazu tych, kt\u00f3rzy przychodz\u0105, aby zdominowa\u0107 ludzko\u015b\u0107 i uniemo\u017cliwi\u0107 moim dzieciom oddawanie czci mojemu Boskiemu Synowi. Wylewam moje \u0142zy nad ziemi\u0105 i wod\u0105 za \u017cywio\u0142y, kt\u00f3re powstaj\u0105 i wyrz\u0105dzaj\u0105 szkody ludzkiemu stworzeniu. Umi\u0142owane dzieci: b\u00f3le, z kt\u00f3rymi si\u0119 stykacie i z kt\u00f3rymi b\u0119dziecie si\u0119 styka\u0107, pokonaj\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107; st\u0105d wezwania do nawr\u00f3cenia, do pilnej potrzeby, aby stworzenie ludzkie nie pozwoli\u0142o sobie na \u017cycie w nieznajomo\u015bci prawa Bo\u017cego, Pisma \u015awi\u0119tego, sakrament\u00f3w, dzie\u0142 mi\u0142osierdzia oraz w praktykowaniu bezmi\u0142o\u015bci i bezbo\u017cno\u015bci. Dzieci, trzymajcie si\u0119 z dala od ka\u017cdego, kto wydaje pochopne s\u0105dy.... \"Bo jak wy s\u0105dzicie, tak b\u0119dziecie s\u0105dzeni i ta sama miara, kt\u00f3rej u\u017cywacie wobec innych, b\u0119dzie u\u017cyta wobec was.\" Szatan sprzyja podzia\u0142owi ko\u015bcio\u0142a mojego syna, nie wpadajcie w jego pu\u0142apki, zbierajcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, rozeznawajcie! Zwr\u00f3\u0107cie uwag\u0119 na \u017cywio\u0142y, te wzburzone p\u0119dz\u0105 przeciwko ludzkiemu stworzeniu. W tej chwili stworzenie ludzkie \u017cyje nasycone \u015bwiatowo\u015bci\u0105 i spieszy si\u0119 do pracy i dzia\u0142ania przeciwko swoim braciom. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ziemia dr\u017cy, a moje dzieci cierpi\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Bliski Wsch\u00f3d. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 o post\u0119p w\u0142adzy \u015bwiatowej nad ludzko\u015bci\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 i konfrontujcie z mocn\u0105 wiar\u0105 wszystko, co pragnie was zmyli\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Argentyn\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, wojna przychodzi tam, gdzie si\u0119 jej nie oczekuje. Kocham was, ma\u0142e dzieci. Ka\u017cde z nich w ramach swojej misji wype\u0142nia to, co powierzy\u0142 wam m\u00f3j Syn. Zach\u0119cam was, aby\u015bcie byli bardziej moim Synem. Jestem z wami, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, chroni\u0119 was. Moja matczyna mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 pozostaje nad ka\u017cdym z moich dzieci. \u017byjcie w pokoju mojego syna. Kocham was. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":3,"month_string":"April","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children, thank you for responding to My call in your hearts. My children, thank you for kneeling in prayer. Daughter, look at my bleeding heart, surrounded by a crown of thorns. My heart bleeds because you have not yet understood what God's Justice will be, it will be worse than the day of the Great Flood. Pray children, convert your hearts, change your lives so that you are not found unprepared. My children, in a short time a strong earthquake will be on the whole earth to awaken your consciences, do not be asleep but keep watch. My children, everything is sick, the Church will be judged because it has become only a political institution and is no longer entrusted to God. Pray for the pastors who are lost and pray for France. My daughter, you must say to stock up on food and water to make up for the dark times. My children, I now bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen. Our Lady was joyful today because she saw so many people united in prayer, but she was also sad and held in her hands a bleeding heart with a crown of thorns around it.","text_de":"Geliebte Kinder, danke, dass Sie meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen beantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie sich auf das Gebet niedergeschlagen haben. Tochter, schau dir mein blutendes Herz an, umgeben von einer Dornenkrone. Mein Herz blutet, weil Sie nicht verstanden haben, was Gottes Gerechtigkeit schlechter sein wird als der Tag der gro\u00dfen Flut. Beten Sie Kinder, konvertieren Sie Ihre Herzen, \u00e4ndern Sie Ihr Leben, damit Sie nicht als unvorbereitet angesehen werden. Meine Kinder, bald auf der ganzen Erde werden ein starkes Erdbeben sein, das Ihr Gewissen aufwachen wird. Nicht einschlafen, aber ansehen. Meine Kinder, alles ist krank, die Kirche wird beurteilt, weil er nur eine politische Institution wurde und nicht mehr dem Gott anvertraut wird. Bete f\u00fcr verlorene Hirten und f\u00fcr Frankreich. Meine Tochter, Sie m\u00fcssen ihnen sagen, dass sie Nahrungsmittel- und Wasserbedarf herstellen, um sich f\u00fcr eine schwarze Stunde zu sch\u00fctzen. Meine Kinder, ich segne dich jetzt im Namen der Heiligen Dreieinigkeit, des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen. Unsere Dame war heute freudig, weil sie so viele Menschen in einem Gebet vereint sah, aber sie war auch traurig und hielt ein blutendes Herz in ihren H\u00e4nden, um die sie eine Dornenkrone war.","text_es":"A los ni\u00f1os amados, gracias por responder a mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, gracias por doblar las rodillas en la oraci\u00f3n. Hija, mira mi coraz\u00f3n sangriento, rodeado de una corona de espinas. Mi coraz\u00f3n sangra porque a\u00fan no ha entendido lo que ser\u00e1 la justicia de Dios, ser\u00e1 peor que el d\u00eda de la inundaci\u00f3n universal. Ore a los ni\u00f1os, convierte tu coraz\u00f3n, cambia tus vidas para no dejarte que te encuentres desprevenido. Mis hijos, pronto, un terremoto fuerte estar\u00e1 en toda la tierra para despertar sus conciencias, no est\u00e9s dormido, pero observ\u00e9. Mis hijos, todo est\u00e1 enfermo, la Iglesia ser\u00e1 juzgada porque solo se ha convertido en una instituci\u00f3n pol\u00edtica y ya no se le conf\u00eda a Dios. Ora por los pastores que se han perdido y orado por Francia. Mi hija, debes decir para hacer acciones de comida y agua para recuperar los momentos oscuros. Mis hijos, ahora te bendigo en nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Padre, Hijo y Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n. Nuestra Se\u00f1ora de hoy fue alegre porque vio a tanta gente se uni\u00f3 a la oraci\u00f3n, pero tambi\u00e9n estaba triste y sosten\u00eda un coraz\u00f3n sangrante con una corona de espinas en sus manos.","text_fr":"Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, merci que vous avez r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, merci que vous vous plaisouuises \u00e0 la pri\u00e8re. Fille, regarde mon c\u0153ur saignant, entour\u00e9 d'une couronne d'\u00e9pines. Mon c\u0153ur saignant, parce que vous n'avez pas compris ce que la justice de Dieu sera pire que le jour de la grande inondation. Priez des enfants, convertissez vos c\u0153urs, changez votre vie afin que vous ne soyez pas consid\u00e9r\u00e9 comme non pr\u00e9par\u00e9. Mes enfants, bient\u00f4t sur toute la terre seront un tremblement de terre fort qui r\u00e9veillera votre conscience; Ne vous endormez pas, mais regardez. Mes enfants, tout est malade, l'\u00c9glise sera jug\u00e9e parce qu'il ne devint qu'une institution politique et n'est plus confi\u00e9e \u00e0 Dieu. Priez pour les bergers perdus et pour la France. Ma fille, vous devez leur dire de faire de la nourriture et des approvisionnements en eau pour vous prot\u00e9ger pendant une heure noire. Mes enfants, je vous b\u00e9nis maintenant au nom de la Sainte Trinit\u00e9, du p\u00e8re et du fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen. Notre-Dame \u00e9tait joyeuse aujourd'hui, car elle a vu tellement de personnes unies dans la pri\u00e8re, mais elle \u00e9tait aussi triste et a tenu un c\u0153ur saignant dans ses mains autour desquelles elle \u00e9tait une couronne d'\u00e9pines.","text_it":"Figli amati, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore.  Figli miei, grazie per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia nella preghiera. Figlia, guarda il mio cuore sanguinate, attorniato da una corona di spine. Il mio cuore sanguina perch\u00e9 non avete ancora compreso cosa sar\u00e0 la giustizia di Dio, sar\u00e0 peggio del giorno del diluvio universale. Pregate figli, convertite il vostro cuore, cambiate le vostre vite per non farvi trovare impreparati. Figli miei, a breve un forte terremoto sar\u00e0 su tutta la terra per risvegliare le vostre coscienze, non siate addormentati ma vegliate. Figli miei, tutto \u00e8 malato, la Chiesa verr\u00e0 giudicata perch\u00e9 \u00e8 diventata solamente un\u2019istituzione politica e non \u00e8 pi\u00f9 affidata a Dio. Pregate per i pastori che si sono perduti e pregate per la Francia. Figlia mia, devi dire di fare scorte di cibo e di acqua per sopperire ai momenti bui. Figli miei, ora vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, Padre, Figlio e Spirito Santo, amen. La Madonna oggi era gioiosa perch\u00e9 ha visto cos\u00ec tante persone unite nella preghiera, ma era anche triste e teneva tra le sue mani un cuore sanguinante con intorno una corona di spine.","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie do modlitwy. C\u00f3rko, sp\u00f3jrz na moje krwawi\u0105ce serce, otoczone koron\u0105 cierniow\u0105. Moje serce krwawi, poniewa\u017c nie zrozumieli\u015bcie jeszcze, jaka b\u0119dzie Sprawiedliwo\u015b\u0107 Bo\u017ca, b\u0119dzie ona gorsza ni\u017c dzie\u0144 Wielkiego Potopu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, nawr\u00f3\u0107cie wasze serca, zmie\u0144cie wasze \u017cycie, aby\u015bcie nie zostali uznani za nieprzygotowanych. Dzieci moje, wkr\u00f3tce na ca\u0142ej ziemi b\u0119dzie odczuwalne silne trz\u0119sienie ziemi, kt\u00f3re obudzi wasze sumienia; nie zasypiajcie, lecz czuwajcie. Dzieci moje, wszystko jest chore, Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 zostanie os\u0105dzony, poniewa\u017c sta\u0142 si\u0119 jedynie instytucj\u0105 polityczn\u0105 i nie jest ju\u017c powierzony Bogu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za zagubionych pasterzy i za Francj\u0119. Moja c\u00f3rko, musisz im powiedzie\u0107, \u017ceby zrobili zapasy \u017cywno\u015bci i wody, aby zabezpieczy\u0107 si\u0119 na czarn\u0105 godzin\u0119. Dzieci moje, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was teraz w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen. Matka Bo\u017ca by\u0142a dzi\u015b radosna, bo widzia\u0142a tak wielu ludzi zjednoczonych na modlitwie, ale by\u0142a te\u017c smutna i trzyma\u0142a w r\u0119kach krwawi\u0105ce serce, wok\u00f3\u0142 kt\u00f3rego by\u0142a korona cierniowa.","text_pt":"Crian\u00e7as amadas, obrigado que voc\u00ea respondeu minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, obrigado que voc\u00ea se ajoelhou \u00e0 ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Filha, olhe meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o sangrando, rodeado por uma coroa de espinhos. Meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o sangrando, porque voc\u00ea n\u00e3o entendeu o que a justi\u00e7a de Deus ser\u00e1 pior do que o dia de grande inunda\u00e7\u00e3o. Ore crian\u00e7as, converter seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es, mude sua vida para que voc\u00ea n\u00e3o seja considerado despreparado. Meus filhos, em breve, toda a Terra ser\u00e1 um forte terremoto que acordar\u00e1 sua consci\u00eancia; N\u00e3o durma, mas observe. Meus filhos, tudo est\u00e1 doente, a igreja ser\u00e1 julgada porque se tornou apenas uma institui\u00e7\u00e3o pol\u00edtica e n\u00e3o \u00e9 mais confiada a Deus. Ore por pastores perdidos e para a Fran\u00e7a. Minha filha, voc\u00ea deve dizer a eles para fazer alimentos e suprimentos de \u00e1gua para se proteger por uma hora preta. Meus filhos, te aben\u00e7oo agora em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Pai e Filho e o Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m. Nossa Senhora era alegre hoje, porque ela viu tantas pessoas unidas em ora\u00e7\u00e3o, mas ela tamb\u00e9m estava triste e segurava um cora\u00e7\u00e3o sangrando em suas m\u00e3os em torno da qual ela era uma coroa de espinhos.","text_zh":"\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\uff0c\u4f60\u5728\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u7b54\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\uff0c\u4f60\u8dea\u5230\u7977\u544a\u3002\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u770b\u7740\u6211\u7684\u6d41\u8840\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u88ab\u8346\u68d8\u738b\u51a0\u5305\u56f4\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\u810f\u51fa\u8840\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4f60\u4e0d\u660e\u767d\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u6b63\u4e49\u4f1a\u6bd4\u5927\u6d2a\u6c34\u7684\u65e5\u5b50\u66f4\u7cdf\u7cd5\u3002\u7948\u7977\u513f\u7ae5\uff0c\u8f6c\u6362\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u6539\u53d8\u4f60\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u4f60\u4e0d\u88ab\u8ba4\u4e3a\u6ca1\u6709\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u5f88\u5feb\u5c31\u4f1a\u6210\u4e3a\u4e00\u4e2a\u5f3a\u70c8\u7684\u5730\u9707\uff0c\u5c06\u5524\u9192\u4f60\u7684\u826f\u5fc3;\u4e0d\u8981\u7761\u7740\u4e86\uff0c\u4f46\u770b\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u751f\u75c5\u4e86\uff0c\u6559\u4f1a\u5c06\u88ab\u5224\u65ad\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u53ea\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u653f\u6cbb\u673a\u6784\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u4e0d\u518d\u59d4\u6258\u7ed9\u4e0a\u5e1d\u3002\u7948\u6c42\u5931\u53bb\u7684\u7267\u7f8a\u4eba\u548c\u6cd5\u56fd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u4f60\u5fc5\u987b\u544a\u8bc9\u4ed6\u4eec\u5236\u4f5c\u98df\u7269\u548c\u6c34\u4f9b\u5e94\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fdd\u62a4\u81ea\u5df1\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u9ed1\u8272\u7684\u5c0f\u65f6\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u73b0\u5728\u4ee5\u5723\u4e09\u4e00\uff0c\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u592b\u4eba\u4eca\u5929\u5f88\u6109\u5feb\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5979\u770b\u5230\u4e86\u8fd9\u4e48\u591a\u4eba\u56e2\u7ed3\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u7977\u544a\uff0c\u4f46\u5979\u4e5f\u5f88\u4f24\u5fc3\uff0c\u5728\u5979\u7684\u624b\u4e2d\u62b1\u7740\u4e00\u9897\u6d41\u8840\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u5979\u662f\u8346\u68d8\u7684\u51a0\u5195\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":4,"month_string":"April","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart: receive the blessing of this mother who loves you. Come to me so that I may lead you to my divine son Jesus Christ. Each one of you knows the good that you have done and the evil you have caused. I invite you to repent now so that you would do not live in sin, otherwise sin will make you increasingly inclined towards evil and confusion. My Son's people must allow themselves to be freed from the bondage of sin at this most delicate of times for humanity. The devil not only lurks, but lashes out against my children, seducing and leading them into the sea of the most abominable sins, this generation being disposed towards sin. In this battle between good and evil the people of my son are being mutilated. This leads my Divine Son to suffer continuously at the lack of spiritual defence on the part of his children. They advance, yes, but towards horror and terror, to which they are being directed. Human works and actions are insecure due to the wavering faith that you have; because of this 'you are neither cold nor hot'. Children of my Immaculate Heart: this present war has religion at its core - man's desire for the expansion of his religion, which is not the one that my Son founded. Children of my Immaculate Heart: pray the holy rosary: it is urgent in the face of the coming suffering. You have been asked so much for the conversion of each one of you, but you have disobeyed! This is leading you to purification on a global level. Nothing will be as it was before - nothing. I grieve over so much sin by which my Son is so offended. I warn you as Mother and yet I am not heard... Not even facing another plague, nor facing food shortages, nor facing the spectre of war, which advances without stopping. I am not being heard! Various calls have been fulfilled before your eyes, but you do not want to believe: on the contrary, you rebel and you will suffer on account of such disrespect. Pray, children, pray for Europe: war will advance upon it and more so upon Italy. Pray, children, pray: the devil is wreaking havoc within my Son's church - pray. Pray, children, pray, children: you must convert, given the approach of so much suffering. Pray, children, pray. Pray, children, pray. How many souls will be lost due to abandoning faith in my Divine Son! Pray, children, pray, pray, pray. My children, the war seems static, but this is not the case: it advances, it does not stop. Pray with your heart, pray. Be more spiritual and pray. The elements will rise up more forcefully against humanity. Pray, children, pray the holy rosary. Children, walk in the good, wish good to your brothers and sisters. Practice good: evil flees before good. Be creatures of unwavering faith in the protection of my Divine Son, his most precious blood protects you. May faith not decrease but rather be strengthened within you. People of my Son: you are not alone. Pray with your heart and our Sacred Hearts will protect you at all times. Be creatures of adoration; be creatures of hope in the promises that you have received. I bless you, my children, I cover you with my maternal mantle. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca: przyjmijcie b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo tej Matki, kt\u00f3ra was kocha. Przyjd\u017acie do mnie, abym mog\u0142a was zaprowadzi\u0107 do mojego Boskiego Syna Jezusa Chrystusa. Ka\u017cdy z was zna dobro, kt\u00f3re uczyni\u0142 i z\u0142o, kt\u00f3re spowodowa\u0142. Zach\u0119cam was do pokuty teraz, aby\u015bcie nie \u017cyli w grzechu, w przeciwnym razie grzech sprawi, \u017ce b\u0119dziecie coraz bardziej sk\u0142onni do z\u0142a i zam\u0119tu. Lud mojego Syna musi pozwoli\u0107 si\u0119 uwolni\u0107 z niewoli grzechu w tym najdelikatniejszym dla ludzko\u015bci czasie. Diabe\u0142 nie tylko czai si\u0119, ale rzuca si\u0119 na moje dzieci, uwodz\u0105c je i prowadz\u0105c w morze najobrzydliwszych grzech\u00f3w, to pokolenie jest usposobione do grzechu. W tej walce dobra ze z\u0142em lud mojego Syna jest okaleczany. To sprawia, \u017ce m\u00f3j Boski Syn nieustannie cierpi z powodu braku duchowej obrony ze strony swoich dzieci. Post\u0119puj\u0105 one, owszem, ale w kierunku grozy i terroru, do kt\u00f3rego s\u0105 kierowane. Ludzkie dzie\u0142a i czyny s\u0105 niepewne z powodu chwiejnej wiary, kt\u00f3r\u0105 posiadacie; z tego powodu \"nie jeste\u015bcie ani zimni, ani gor\u0105cy\". Dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca: ta obecna wojna ma u podstaw religi\u0119 - d\u0105\u017cenie cz\u0142owieka do rozszerzenia swojej religii, kt\u00f3ra nie jest t\u0105, kt\u00f3r\u0105 za\u0142o\u017cy\u0142 m\u00f3j Syn. Dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca: odmawiajcie r\u00f3\u017caniec \u015bwi\u0119ty: jest on pilny w obliczu nadchodz\u0105cych cierpie\u0144. Tak bardzo proszono was o nawr\u00f3cenie ka\u017cdego z was, ale wy byli\u015bcie niepos\u0142uszni! To prowadzi was do oczyszczenia na poziomie globalnym. Nic nie b\u0119dzie takie jak przedtem - nic. Bolej\u0119 nad tak wielk\u0105 ilo\u015bci\u0105 grzechu, przez kt\u00f3ry M\u00f3j Syn jest tak obra\u017cany. Ostrzegam was jako Matka, a jednak nie jestem wys\u0142uchana... Ani w obliczu kolejnej zarazy, ani w obliczu niedobor\u00f3w \u017cywno\u015bci, ani w obliczu widma wojny, kt\u00f3ra post\u0119puje bez ustanku. Nie jestem wys\u0142uchana! Na waszych oczach spe\u0142niaj\u0105 si\u0119 r\u00f3\u017cne wezwania, ale wy nie chcecie uwierzy\u0107: przeciwnie, buntujecie si\u0119 i b\u0119dziecie cierpie\u0107 z powodu takiego braku szacunku. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Europ\u0119: wojna posuwa si\u0119 na ni\u0105, a jeszcze bardziej na W\u0142ochy. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: diabe\u0142 czyni spustoszenie w ko\u015bciele mojego Syna - m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci: musicie si\u0119 nawr\u00f3ci\u0107, bior\u0105c pod uwag\u0119 zbli\u017caj\u0105ce si\u0119 tak wielkie cierpienie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. Ile dusz zostanie utraconych z powodu porzucenia wiary w mojego Boskiego Syna! M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. Moje dzieci, wojna wydaje si\u0119 statyczna, ale tak nie jest: post\u0119puje, nie zatrzymuje si\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 sercem, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. B\u0105d\u017acie bardziej duchowi i m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. \u017bywio\u0142y powstan\u0105 z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 si\u0142\u0105 przeciwko ludzko\u015bci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, odmawiajcie r\u00f3\u017caniec \u015bwi\u0119ty. Dzieci, chod\u017acie w dobru, \u017cyczcie dobra swoim braciom i siostrom. Praktykujcie dobro: z\u0142o ucieka przed dobrem. B\u0105d\u017acie istotami o niezachwianej wierze w ochron\u0119 mojego Boskiego Syna, jego najdro\u017csza krew was chroni. Niech wiara nie maleje, lecz niech si\u0119 w was umacnia. Ludu mojego Syna: nie jeste\u015b sam. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 sercem, a nasze Naj\u015bwi\u0119tsze Serca b\u0119d\u0105 was zawsze chroni\u0107. B\u0105d\u017acie istotami adoracji; b\u0105d\u017acie istotami nadziei w obietnicach, kt\u00f3re otrzymali\u015bcie. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, moje dzieci, okrywam was moim matczynym p\u0142aszczem. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":5,"month_string":"April","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My daughter, thank you for having responded to My call in your heart. Daughter, this humanity, instead of praying and entrusting itself to God, seeks places of refuge to save its life, but still I tell you: there will be no place, even the most hidden before God's Judgment. Pray to my Immaculate Heart and that of my Son Jesus, they will be the safest shelters, have faith in God and think more about the salvation of your soul. Listen to me with love and walk on the path that I have indicated to you in your heart, then you will guarantee the realization of the Triumph of my Immaculate Heart and you will be its witnesses. Consecrate yourselves to Me, and I will protect you under My Blessed Mantle. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Tochter, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in meinem Herzen geantwortet haben. Tochter, diese Menschheit, anstatt Gott zu beten und anzuregen Beten Sie zu meinem makellosen Herzen und meinen Sohn Jesu, sie werden der sicherste Schutz sein, den Glauben an Gott halten und an die Erl\u00f6sung Ihrer Seele nachdenken. H\u00f6r mir mit Liebe und gehe so, wie Sie in Ihr Herz hingewiesen werden, und dann garantieren Sie die Umsetzung meines makellosen Herz-Triumphs und Sie werden Zeuge sein. Hast du mir widmacht, und ich werde dich unter meinem gesegten Mantel sch\u00fctzen. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mi hija, gracias por responder mi llamada a tu coraz\u00f3n. Hija, esta humanidad, en lugar de orar y confiar a Dios, busca lugares para refugiarse a salvar sus vidas, pero todav\u00eda le digo: no habr\u00e1 lugar, incluso si lo m\u00e1s oculto ante el juicio de Dios. Ora mi coraz\u00f3n Inmaculada y la de mi Hijo Jes\u00fas, ser\u00e1 el refugio m\u00e1s seguro, tenga fe en Dios y piense m\u00e1s sobre la salvaci\u00f3n de su alma. Esc\u00fachame con amor y camina por el camino que he indicado en tu coraz\u00f3n, entonces asegurar\u00e1s la realizaci\u00f3n del triunfo de mi coraz\u00f3n inmaculado y ser\u00e1s presenciado. Consagr\u00e1ndome, y te proteger\u00e9 bajo mi beato Mantle. Ahora te bendigo en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Ma fille, merci que tu as r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans mon c\u0153ur. Fille, cette humanit\u00e9, au lieu de prier et de confier \u00e0 Dieu, cherche des lieux de refuge pour sauver votre vie, mais nous disons n\u00e9anmoins vous dire: devant le tribunal de Dieu, il n'y aura pas d'abri, m\u00eame le plus cach\u00e9. Priez avec mon c\u0153ur immacul\u00e9 et mon fils de J\u00e9sus, ils seront l'abri le plus s\u00fbr, gardez la foi en Dieu et pensez au salut de votre \u00e2me. \u00c9coutez-moi avec amour et allez comme vous avez soulign\u00e9 dans votre c\u0153ur, puis vous garantirez la mise en \u0153uvre de mon c\u0153ur impeccable triomphe et vous y trouverez. Avez-vous consacr\u00e9 \u00e0 moi et je vous prot\u00e9gerai sous mon manteau b\u00e9ni. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figlia mia, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel tuo cuore. Figlia, questa umanit\u00e0, invece di pregare e affidarsi a Dio, cerca i posti dove rifugiarsi per salvare la propria vita, ma ancora vi dico: non ci sar\u00e0 un posto, anche se il pi\u00f9 nascosto dinanzi al giudizio di Dio. Pregate il mio Cuore Immacolato e quello di mio Figlio Ges\u00f9, saranno i rifugi pi\u00f9 sicuri, abbiate fede in Dio e pensate di pi\u00f9 alla salvezza della vostra anima. Ascoltatemi con amore e camminate sul percorso che Io vi ho indicato nel vostro cuore, allora garantirete la realizzazione del Trionfo del mio Cuore immacolato e voi ne sarete testimoni. Consacratevi a me, ed Io vi protegger\u00f2 sotto il mio Manto Benedetto. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moja c\u00f3rko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce odpowiedzia\u0142a\u015b na moje wezwanie w swoim sercu. C\u00f3rko, ta ludzko\u015b\u0107, zamiast modli\u0107 si\u0119 i powierza\u0107 si\u0119 Bogu, szuka miejsc schronienia, aby ocali\u0107 swoje \u017cycie, ale mimo to m\u00f3wi\u0119 wam: przed S\u0105dem Bo\u017cym nie b\u0119dzie schronienia, nawet najbardziej ukrytego. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 do mojego Niepokalanego Serca i do Serca mojego Syna Jezusa, one b\u0119d\u0105 najbezpieczniejszym schronieniem, miejcie wiar\u0119 w Boga i my\u015blcie raczej o zbawieniu waszej duszy. S\u0142uchajcie mnie z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 i id\u017acie drog\u0105, kt\u00f3r\u0105 wam wskaza\u0142am w waszym sercu, a wtedy zagwarantujecie realizacj\u0119 Tryumfu mojego Niepokalanego Serca i b\u0119dziecie jego \u015bwiadkami. Po\u015bwi\u0119\u0107cie si\u0119 Mi, a Ja b\u0119d\u0119 was chroni\u0142a pod Moim Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszym P\u0142aszczem. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Minha filha, obrigado que voc\u00ea respondeu \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o no meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Filha, esta humanidade, em vez de orar e confiar a Deus, procura lugares de ref\u00fagio para salvar sua vida, mas, no entanto, dizendo-lhe: Antes da corte de Deus, n\u00e3o haver\u00e1 abrigo, mesmo o mais oculto. Ore ao meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o imaculado e meu filho de Jesus, eles ser\u00e3o o abrigo mais seguro, manter a f\u00e9 em Deus e pensar sobre a salva\u00e7\u00e3o de sua alma. Ou\u00e7a-me com amor e v\u00e1 da maneira que voc\u00ea apontou em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o, e ent\u00e3o voc\u00ea garante a implementa\u00e7\u00e3o do meu imaculado Triunfo Cora\u00e7\u00e3o e voc\u00ea testemunhar\u00e1. Voc\u00ea dedicou a mim e eu vou te proteger sob o meu beijo aben\u00e7oado. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\uff0c\u4f60\u5728\u5fc3\u91cc\u56de\u590d\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e2a\u4eba\u6027\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7948\u7977\u548c\u59d4\u6258\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u5bfb\u627e\u907f\u96be\u6240\u7684\u5730\u65b9\uff0c\u4ee5\u62ef\u6551\u4f60\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\uff0c\u4f46\u4ecd\u7136\u544a\u8bc9\u4f60\uff1a\u5728\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u6cd5\u5ead\u4e4b\u524d\uff0c\u4e5f\u4e0d\u4f1a\u6709\u5e87\u62a4\u6240\uff0c\u751a\u81f3\u662f\u6700\u9690\u85cf\u7684\u3002\u7948\u6c42\u6211\u7684\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u5fc3\u810f\u548c\u6211\u7684\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u513f\u5b50\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u5c06\u662f\u6700\u5b89\u5168\u7684\u5e87\u62a4\u6240\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u5e76\u601d\u8003\u7075\u9b42\u7684\u6551\u8d4e\u3002\u7528\u7231\u60c5\u542c\u6211\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u8d70\u4e0a\u4f60\u5fc3\u4e2d\u6240\u6307\u51fa\u7684\u65b9\u5f0f\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u4f60\u4f1a\u4fdd\u8bc1\u6211\u7684\u5b8c\u7f8e\u5fc3\u7075\u80dc\u5229\u7684\u5b9e\u65bd\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u89c1\u8bc1\u3002\u4f60\u6709\u6ca1\u6709\u6295\u5165\u6211\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u4fdd\u62a4\u4f60\u5728\u6211\u5e78\u798f\u7684\u5916\u5957\u4e0b\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":8,"month_string":"April","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My brothers, thank you for being here under my Cross. My brothers, today I have given you the grace of peace in hearts and souls, but only one person among you will witness my living presence in this place. My brothers, put everything in my wounds, especially your sufferings, so that I may give you my grace and mercy. My brothers, pray for the war and for humanity which is suffering so many atrocities. My brothers, recognize Me as your King, soon I will be with you with all My love. Now I bless you, passing by your side, in the name of the Father, in my Name and in the name of the Holy Spirit.","text_de":"Meine Br\u00fcder, danke, dass Sie hier unter meinem Kreuz hier sind. Meine Br\u00fcder, heute habe ich Ihnen die Gnade des Friedens in Herzen und Seelen gegeben, aber nur eine Person unter Ihnen wird meine lebende Pr\u00e4senz an diesem Ort erleben. Meine Br\u00fcder, legte alles in meine Wunden, vor allem deine Leiden, so dass ich dir meine Gnade und Barmherzigkeit geben darf. Meine Br\u00fcder, beten f\u00fcr den Krieg und f\u00fcr die Menschheit, die so viele Grausamkeiten leidet. Meine Br\u00fcder, erkenne mich als dein K\u00f6nig, bald werde ich mit all meiner Liebe bei dir sein. Jetzt segne ich dich, vorbei an deiner Seite, im Namen des Vaters, in meinem Namen und im Namen des Heiligen Geistes.","text_es":"Mis hermanos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed debajo de mi cruz. Hermanos, hoy te di la gracia de la paz en el coraz\u00f3n y en el alma, pero solo una persona entre t\u00fa testificar\u00e1 mi presencia viva en este lugar. Mis hermanos, ponen todo en mis llagas, especialmente tu sufrimiento, para que pueda darte mi gracia y misericordia. Hermanos, rezan por la guerra y por la humanidad que sufren tantas atrocidades. Mis hermanos, me reconocen como tu rey, pronto estar\u00e9 contigo con todo mi amor. Ahora te bendigo, pas\u00e1ndote a continuaci\u00f3n, en nombre del Padre, en mi nombre y el Esp\u00edritu Santo.","text_fr":"Mes fr\u00e8res, merci d'\u00eatre ici sous ma croix. Mes fr\u00e8res, aujourd'hui, je vous ai donn\u00e9 la gr\u00e2ce de la paix dans les c\u0153urs et les \u00e2mes, mais une seule personne parmi vous t\u00e9moignera de ma pr\u00e9sence vivante \u00e0 cet endroit. Mes fr\u00e8res, tout mettre dans mes blessures, surtout vos souffrances, afin que je puisse vous donner ma gr\u00e2ce et ma mis\u00e9ricorde. Mes fr\u00e8res, prient pour la guerre et pour l'humanit\u00e9 qui souffre tant d'atrocit\u00e9s. Mes fr\u00e8res, reconnaissez-moi comme votre roi, je serai bient\u00f4t avec vous avec tout mon amour. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis, passez \u00e0 vos c\u00f4t\u00e9s, au nom du P\u00e8re, en mon nom et au nom du Saint-Esprit.","text_it":"Fratelli miei, grazie per essere qui sotto la mia croce. Fratelli, oggi vi ho fatto la grazia della pace nel cuore e nell\u2019anima, ma solo una persona tra di voi testimonier\u00e0 la mia presenza viva in questo luogo. Fratelli miei, mettete tutto nelle mie piaghe, soprattutto le vostre sofferenze, affinch\u00e9 Io possa darvi la mia grazia e misericordia. Fratelli, pregate per la guerra e per l\u2019umanit\u00e0 che sta subendo tante atrocit\u00e0. Fratelli miei, riconoscetemi come vostro Re, presto sar\u00f2 con voi con tutto il mio amore. Ora vi benedico, passandovi accanto, nel nome del Padre, nel mio Nome e dello Spirito Santo.","text_pl":"Bracia moi, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj pod moim Krzy\u017cem. Bracia, dzisiaj da\u0142em wam \u0142ask\u0119 pokoju w sercach i duszach, ale tylko jedna osoba spo\u015br\u00f3d was b\u0119dzie \u015bwiadkiem mojej \u017cywej obecno\u015bci w tym miejscu. Bracia moi, w\u0142\u00f3\u017ccie wszystko w moje rany, a zw\u0142aszcza w wasze cierpienia, abym m\u00f3g\u0142 was obdarzy\u0107 moj\u0105 \u0142ask\u0105 i mi\u0142osierdziem. Bracia moi, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za wojn\u0119 i za ludzko\u015b\u0107, kt\u00f3ra do\u015bwiadcza tak wielu okrucie\u0144stw. Bracia moi, uznajcie mnie za waszego Kr\u00f3la; wkr\u00f3tce b\u0119d\u0119 z wami z ca\u0142\u0105 moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, przechodz\u0105c obok was, w imi\u0119 Ojca, w moje Imi\u0119 i w imi\u0119 Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego.","text_pt":"Meus irm\u00e3os, obrigado por estar aqui debaixo da minha cruz. Meus irm\u00e3os, hoje eu lhe dei a gra\u00e7a da paz em cora\u00e7\u00f5es e almas, mas apenas uma pessoa entre voc\u00eas testemunhar\u00e1 minha presen\u00e7a viva neste lugar. Meus irm\u00e3os, coloque tudo em minhas feridas, especialmente seus sofrimentos, para que eu possa lhe dar minha gra\u00e7a e miseric\u00f3rdia. Meus irm\u00e3os, oram pela guerra e pela humanidade que est\u00e1 sofrendo tantas atrocidades. Meus irm\u00e3os, me reconhecem como seu rei, em breve estarei com voc\u00ea com todo o meu amor. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo, passando ao seu lado, em nome do Pai, em meu nome e em nome do Esp\u00edrito Santo.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u6211\u7684\u5341\u5b57\u67b6\u4e0b\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\uff0c\u4eca\u5929\u6211\u8d50\u7ed9\u4f60\u5fc3\u7075\u548c\u7075\u9b42\u7684\u6069\u5178\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u4eec\u4e2d\u95f4\u53ea\u6709\u4e00\u4e2a\u4eba\u4f1a\u5728\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5730\u65b9\u89c1\u8bc1\u6211\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\u5b58\u5728\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\uff0c\u628a\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u653e\u5728\u4f24\u53e3\u4e2d\uff0c\u7279\u522b\u662f\u4f60\u7684\u75db\u82e6\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u6211\u53ef\u80fd\u4f1a\u7ed9\u4f60\u6211\u7684\u6069\u5178\u548c\u601c\u60af\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\u4eec\u4e3a\u6218\u4e89\u548c\u4eba\u7c7b\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u906d\u53d7\u8fd9\u4e48\u591a\u66b4\u884c\u7684\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\uff0c\u8ba4\u8bc6\u5230\u6211\u4f5c\u4e3a\u4f60\u7684\u56fd\u738b\uff0c\u6211\u5f88\u5feb\u5c31\u4f1a\u548c\u4f60\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u5728\u7236\u4eb2\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u4e0a\uff0c\u4ee5\u6211\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":9,"month_string":"April","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: receive the blessing that the Holy Trinity sends to each one of you. This blessing will be palpable in the life of each one of you, if you receive this call with faith and with a contrite and humbled heart. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, the actions and deeds of each one of you are not surprising. The most Holy Trinity knows how much you act and act, your intention and what you carry in your heart. Continue faithful as worthy children of our King and Lord and of our Mother and Queen of the End Times. Remain in faith, without doubting, being steadfast creatures and eager to do good. Calamities fall most harshly when human creatures despise our King. We are his protectors and companions on the way, therefore as prince of the heavenly legions I must tell you: the scourges upon humanity are greater before the disobedience of the human creature. Natural disasters act with greater force. Some disasters are caused by nature, others are caused by man who uses science for evil. The sun increases its eruptions, suffocating man and the earth itself, which responds by shuddering. The war is presented as a fight for territories, keeping hidden the reality that it has been programmed as part of the arrival of the antichrist. The blood of a creature of power is shed, war spreads. How many 'woes' are and will be heard throughout the earth, the present time being the time of wailing. Powers confront each other with unknown armaments and mankind is astonished. People who walk: this is the crucial moment! This is why I have insisted that you be prudent and 'judge not'. Those who have been spared so far from God's Judgment will not escape their own judgment at the Warning. Pray, people of God, pray, repent and persevere in the faith, prayer is necessary. Pray people of God, the crossroads for mankind hardened and will know the pain. Pray, people of God, prayer is urgent for the countries that are strongly shaken. Nourish the spirit with the holy Eucharist, be unity. Those who walk alone are prey to the wolves. Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, keep food in reserve. Do you wish to save the soul? Walk against the current of the world. At this time the children of our Mother and Queen of the End Times pray with their hearts. I protect you my beloved, I bless you. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: przyjmijcie b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo, kt\u00f3re Tr\u00f3jca \u015awi\u0119ta zsy\u0142a na ka\u017cdego z was. To b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo b\u0119dzie odczuwalne w \u017cyciu ka\u017cdego z was, je\u015bli przyjmiecie to wezwanie z wiar\u0105 oraz ze skruszonym i pokornym sercem. Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, dzia\u0142ania i czyny ka\u017cdego z was nie s\u0105 zaskakuj\u0105ce. Naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Tr\u00f3jca zna wasze dzia\u0142ania i czyny, wasze intencje i to, co nosicie w sercu. Trwajcie wiernie jako godne dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana oraz naszej Matki i Kr\u00f3lowej czas\u00f3w ostatecznych. Trwajcie w wierze, nie w\u0105tpi\u0105c, b\u0119d\u0105c niez\u0142omnymi istotami i gorliwymi w czynieniu dobra. Kl\u0119ski spadaj\u0105 najostrzej, gdy ludzkie stworzenia gardz\u0105 naszym Kr\u00f3lem. Jeste\u015bmy Jego obro\u0144cami i towarzyszami w drodze, dlatego jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 legion\u00f3w niebieskich musz\u0119 wam powiedzie\u0107: plagi na ludzko\u015bci s\u0105 wi\u0119ksze przed niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwem ludzkiego stworzenia. Kl\u0119ski \u017cywio\u0142owe dzia\u0142aj\u0105 z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 si\u0142\u0105. Niekt\u00f3re katastrofy s\u0105 spowodowane przez natur\u0119, inne przez cz\u0142owieka, kt\u00f3ry wykorzystuje nauk\u0119 do z\u0142a. S\u0142o\u0144ce zwi\u0119ksza swoje erupcje, dusz\u0105c cz\u0142owieka i sam\u0105 ziemi\u0119, kt\u00f3ra reaguje wstrz\u0105sem. Wojna jest przedstawiana jako walka o terytoria, ukrywaj\u0105c rzeczywisto\u015b\u0107, \u017ce zosta\u0142a zaprogramowana jako cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 nadej\u015bcia antychrysta. Przelewana jest krew istoty w\u0142adzy, wojna si\u0119 rozprzestrzenia. Ile\u017c to \"nieszcz\u0119\u015b\u0107\" jest i b\u0119dzie s\u0142yszanych na ca\u0142ej ziemi, przy czym obecny czas jest czasem zawodzenia. Pot\u0119gi \u015bcieraj\u0105 si\u0119 ze sob\u0105 z nieznanym uzbrojeniem, a ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest zdumiona. Ludu, kt\u00f3ry idziesz: to jest decyduj\u0105cy moment! Dlatego nalega\u0142em, aby\u015bcie byli rozwa\u017cni i \"nie os\u0105dzali\". Ci, kt\u00f3rzy do tej pory zostali oszcz\u0119dzeni przed S\u0105dem Bo\u017cym, nie unikn\u0105 w\u0142asnego s\u0105du przy Ostrze\u017ceniu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, pokutujcie i wytrwajcie w wierze, modlitwa jest konieczna. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludu Bo\u017cy, droga krzy\u017cowa dla ludzko\u015bci zatwardzia\u0142a i pozna b\u00f3l. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, modlitwa jest pilna dla kraj\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re s\u0105 mocno wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119te. Karmcie ducha \u015bwi\u0119t\u0105 Eucharysti\u0105, b\u0105d\u017acie jedno\u015bci\u0105. Ci, kt\u00f3rzy id\u0105 samotnie, padaj\u0105 ofiar\u0105 wilk\u00f3w. Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, zachowaj pokarm w rezerwie. Czy chcecie zbawi\u0107 dusz\u0119? Id\u017acie pod pr\u0105d \u015bwiata. W tym czasie dzieci naszej Matki i Kr\u00f3lowej Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych modl\u0105 si\u0119 sercem. Chroni\u0119 was moi ukochani, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. \u015awi\u0119ty Michale Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":12,"month_string":"April","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people: you are my children, and for each one of you I surrendered to my Cross, on which I embodied my Love for the salvation of humanity. I desire that all would be saved, that all would convert and be nourished at the banquet at my table. I come once again as a beggar of love to knock at the door of each person\u2019s heart and conscience. I want you to open the door to me, but I know that not all will do so, therefore I give you my blessing in advance and wait with my heart in my hands for you to return to me and stop living in worldliness. How many of my children tell me that they are not of the world, yet they live by the world\u2019s teachings, they take pleasure in comfort while being unable to endure privation! I find so many of my children telling me: 'Lord, you know that I am not worldly\u201d, but they live by the world, by appearances, in order to be well-received in every social circle; they live by pride and despise those who are not their equals. These attitudes make them worldly, living by 'what they will say about me and how I will be viewed'. They must change now because the world and the flesh will leave them with no benefit. Faith in my word has declined so much that some do not even name it so as not to commit themselves. They consider Holy Scripture to be one more book that has gone out of fashion and therefore believe that it must be reformed. Woe to him or those who distort the Holy Scripture: it would be better for them not to have been born! There are Ten Commandments and they cannot be altered or pass unnoticed. This is the law and above it there is no other law; you cannot alter, erase or change it. How you have forgotten me! The commandments are not subject to ideologies, human beings or circumstances: they are ten and they stand written. Let whoever changes them be anathema. As this time progresses, it is bringing you closer to the renunciation of obedience to my word by some of my consecrated, bringing my church closer to schism. My beloved people, prepare yourselves! There are so many who call themselves my children and yet are against me... There are so many who wish to omit my word, the commandments and the sacraments in order to bring forth the new religion, which is total licence and the renunciation of me and my Mother.... They will deny the Creed and Our Father will be changed. Beware, my people, this is not me! They wish to deceive you and bring you closer to evil, to the antichrist - little by little so that my children would not notice. My people, rebellion is advancing: war continues to take hold of territories and new nations will be involved. Violence is spreading. Pray, my people, pray for Argentina; the people will rebel and, in the turmoil, they will claim the life of a victim in power. Argentina must pray. Pray, my people, pray; famine will increase, plague will advance, coming from hands marked with the suffering of their brothers and sisters; confinement will be applied again. Pray, my people, pray, America will be shaken, then it will be the land of those fleeing Europe. Pray, my people, pray to my blessed mother, protection of sinners. My mother will keep you in inner silence. Pray, my people: whatever happens, keep the faith. Pray with your heart and you will be heard. Be merciful; maintain your trust in Divine Protection and in the guardianship of my beloved St. Michael the Archangel and his legions. Come to me without fear, with faith, hope and charity. Do not despair, I remain with my people whom I will not leave on their own. Receive my blessing. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu: jeste\u015bcie moimi dzie\u0107mi i za ka\u017cdego z was odda\u0142em si\u0119 pod m\u00f3j Krzy\u017c, na kt\u00f3rym zawar\u0142em moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do zbawienia ludzko\u015bci. Pragn\u0119, aby wszyscy zostali zbawieni, aby si\u0119 nawr\u00f3cili i zostali nakarmieni na uczcie przy moim stole. Przychodz\u0119 raz jeszcze jako \u017cebrak mi\u0142o\u015bci, aby zapuka\u0107 do drzwi serca i sumienia ka\u017cdego cz\u0142owieka. Chc\u0119, aby\u015bcie otworzyli mi drzwi, ale wiem, \u017ce nie wszyscy to zrobi\u0105, dlatego z g\u00f3ry udzielam wam mojego b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwa i czekam z sercem w d\u0142oniach, a\u017c powr\u00f3cicie do mnie i przestaniecie \u017cy\u0107 w \u015bwiatowo\u015bci. Ile\u017c to moich dzieci m\u00f3wi mi, \u017ce nie s\u0105 ze \u015bwiata, a jednak \u017cyj\u0105 wed\u0142ug nauk \u015bwiata, czerpi\u0105 przyjemno\u015b\u0107 z wyg\u00f3d, nie mog\u0105c znie\u015b\u0107 niedostatku! Znajduj\u0119 tak wiele moich dzieci, kt\u00f3re m\u00f3wi\u0105 mi: \"Panie, Ty wiesz, \u017ce nie jestem \u015bwiatowy\", ale \u017cyj\u0105 wed\u0142ug \u015bwiata, wed\u0142ug pozor\u00f3w, aby by\u0107 dobrze odbieranym w ka\u017cdym kr\u0119gu spo\u0142ecznym; \u017cyj\u0105 dum\u0105 i gardz\u0105 tymi, kt\u00f3rzy nie s\u0105 im r\u00f3wni. Takie postawy czyni\u0105 ich \u015bwiatowymi, \u017cyj\u0105cymi tym, \"co o mnie powiedz\u0105 i jak b\u0119d\u0119 postrzegany\". Musz\u0105 si\u0119 teraz zmieni\u0107, bo \u015bwiat i cia\u0142o nie pozostawi\u0105 im \u017cadnych korzy\u015bci. Wiara w moje s\u0142owo tak bardzo podupad\u0142a, \u017ce niekt\u00f3rzy nawet nie wymieniaj\u0105 go, aby si\u0119 nie zaanga\u017cowa\u0107. Uwa\u017caj\u0105 Pismo \u015awi\u0119te za jeszcze jedn\u0105 ksi\u0105\u017ck\u0119, kt\u00f3ra wysz\u0142a z mody i dlatego uwa\u017caj\u0105, \u017ce musi by\u0107 zreformowana. Biada temu lub tym, kt\u00f3rzy zniekszta\u0142caj\u0105 Pismo \u015awi\u0119te: by\u0142oby lepiej dla nich, aby nie urodzi\u0107! Istnieje dziesi\u0119\u0107 przykaza\u0144 i nie mog\u0105 by\u0107 zmienione lub przej\u015b\u0107 niezauwa\u017cone. To jest prawo i ponad nim nie ma innego prawa; nie mo\u017cna go zmieni\u0107, wymaza\u0107 lub zmieni\u0107. Jak\u017ce zapomnieli\u015bcie o mnie! Przykazania nie podlegaj\u0105 ideologiom, ludziom ani okoliczno\u015bciom: jest ich dziesi\u0119\u0107 i stoj\u0105 napisane. Kto je zmienia, niech b\u0119dzie anatem\u0105. W miar\u0119 jak ten czas post\u0119puje, przybli\u017ca was do wyrzeczenia si\u0119 pos\u0142usze\u0144stwa mojemu s\u0142owu przez niekt\u00f3rych moich konsekrowanych, przybli\u017caj\u0105c m\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 do schizmy. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludzie, przygotujcie si\u0119! Jest tak wielu, kt\u00f3rzy nazywaj\u0105 si\u0119 moimi dzie\u0107mi, a jednak s\u0105 przeciwko Mnie... Jest tak wielu, kt\u00f3rzy chc\u0105 pomin\u0105\u0107 moje s\u0142owo, przykazania i sakramenty, aby wprowadzi\u0107 now\u0105 religi\u0119, kt\u00f3ra jest ca\u0142kowit\u0105 licencj\u0105 i wyrzeczeniem si\u0119 Mnie i mojej Matki.... Zaprzecz\u0105 oni Credo i Ojcze Nasz zostanie zmieniony. Strze\u017ccie si\u0119, m\u00f3j ludu, to nie Ja! Chc\u0105 was zwie\u015b\u0107 i zbli\u017cy\u0107 do z\u0142a, do antychrysta - poma\u0142u, aby moje dzieci nie zauwa\u017cy\u0142y. M\u00f3j ludu, bunt post\u0119puje: wojna nadal zajmuje terytoria, a nowe narody b\u0119d\u0105 w ni\u0105 zaanga\u017cowane. Przemoc si\u0119 rozprzestrzenia. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3j ludu, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Argentyn\u0119; lud zbuntuje si\u0119 i w zamieszaniu odbierze \u017cycie ofierze u w\u0142adzy. Argentyna musi si\u0119 modli\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3j ludu, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119; g\u0142\u00f3d si\u0119 nasili, zaraza posunie si\u0119 naprz\u00f3d, wychodz\u0105c z r\u0105k naznaczonych cierpieniem ich braci i si\u00f3str; uwi\u0119zienie zostanie ponownie zastosowane. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3j ludu, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119; Ameryka zostanie wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119ta, wtedy b\u0119dzie ziemi\u0105 tych, kt\u00f3rzy uciekaj\u0105 z Europy. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3j ludu, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 do mojej b\u0142ogos\u0142awionej Matki, ochrony grzesznik\u00f3w. Moja Matka zachowa was w wewn\u0119trznej ciszy. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3j ludu: cokolwiek si\u0119 stanie, zachowajcie wiar\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 sercem, a zostaniecie wys\u0142uchani. B\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142osierni; zachowajcie ufno\u015b\u0107 w Bosk\u0105 Opiek\u0119 i w opiek\u0119 mojego ukochanego \u015awi\u0119tego Micha\u0142a Archanio\u0142a i jego legion\u00f3w. Przychod\u017acie do mnie bez l\u0119ku, z wiar\u0105, nadziej\u0105 i mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Nie rozpaczajcie, pozostaj\u0119 z moim ludem, kt\u00f3rego nie pozostawi\u0119 samemu sobie. Przyjmijcie moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":12,"month_string":"April","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"I am the Immaculate Virgin, the spouse of the Holy Spirit, the humble servant of God, the Mother of Jesus, who was betrayed, mocked and humiliated. Even today that sword pierces my heart. Children, you are at a crossroads, make the right choice, my Son is waiting for you. I will protect my faithful and humble children, who have distinguished themselves by their courage and love. My children, repent, acknowledge your God as the only God and Savior and He by His great Mercy will forgive you. Now I bless you my beloved daughter and thank you for welcoming me into your heart, in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit.","text_de":"Ich bin die makellose Jungfrau, der Ehepartner des Heiligen Geistes, der bescheidene Diener Gottes, die Mutter von Jesus, die verraten, verspottet und gedem\u00fctigt. Noch heute durchbohrt das Schwert mein Herz. Kinder, du bist an einer Kreuzung, machen die richtige Wahl, mein Sohn wartet auf dich. Ich werde meine treuen und bescheidenen Kinder sch\u00fctzen, die sich von ihrem Mut und ihrer Liebe unterschieden haben. Meine Kinder, bereuen, Ihren Gott als den einzigen Gott und den Erretter anerkennen und er von seiner gro\u00dfen Gnade wird Ihnen vergeben. Jetzt segne ich Ihnen meine geliebte Tochter und danke, dass Sie mich in Ihr Herz begr\u00fc\u00dfen, im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes.","text_es":"Soy la inmaculada virgen, la novia del Esp\u00edritu Santo, el humilde siervo de Dios, la Madre de Jes\u00fas, que fue traicionada, burlada y humillada. Todav\u00eda hoy esa espada perfora mi coraz\u00f3n. Los ni\u00f1os, est\u00e1s frente a un cruce, toman la decisi\u00f3n correcta, mi hijo te espera. Proteger\u00e9 a mis hijos fieles y humildes, que se han distinguido con coraje y amor. Mis hijos, se arrepienten, reconocen a tu Dios como el \u00fanico Dios y Salvatore y \u00e9l te perdonar\u00e1 por su gran misericordia. Ahora bendigo a mi hija favorita y gracias por darme en tu coraz\u00f3n, padre, hijo y esp\u00edritu santo.","text_fr":"Je suis la vierge immacul\u00e9e, le conjoint du Saint-Esprit, le humble serviteur de Dieu, la m\u00e8re de J\u00e9sus, trahi, moqu\u00e9e et humili\u00e9e. M\u00eame aujourd'hui, l'\u00e9p\u00e9e perce mon c\u0153ur. Enfants, vous \u00eates au carrefour, faites le bon choix, mon fils vous attend. Je prot\u00e9gerai mes enfants fid\u00e8les et humbles, qui se sont distingu\u00e9s par leur courage et leur amour. Mes enfants, se repentent, reconnaissent votre Dieu comme seul Dieu et Sauveur et il par sa grande mis\u00e9ricorde vous pardonnera. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis ma fille bien-aim\u00e9e et merci de m'avoir accueillir dans votre c\u0153ur, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit.","text_it":"Io sono la Vergine Immacolata, la sposa dello Spirito Santo, l\u2019umile serva di Dio, la Madre di Ges\u00f9, il quale fu tradito, deriso e umiliato. Ancora oggi quella spada trafigge il mio cuore. Figli, siete davanti ad un bivio, fate la scelta giusta, mio Figlio vi aspetta. Io protegger\u00f2 i miei figli fedeli e umili, che si sono contraddistinti per il coraggio e l\u2019amore. Figli miei, pentitevi, riconoscete il vostro Dio come unico Dio e Salvatore e Lui per la Sua grande misericordia vi perdoner\u00e0. Ora ti benedico figlia mia prediletta e grazie per avermi accolta nel tuo cuore, Padre, Figlio e Spirito Santo.","text_pl":"Jestem Niepokalan\u0105 Dziewic\u0105, oblubienic\u0105 Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, pokorn\u0105 s\u0142u\u017cebnic\u0105 Bo\u017c\u0105, Matk\u0105 Jezusa, kt\u00f3ry zosta\u0142 zdradzony, wyszydzony i upokorzony. Jeszcze dzi\u015b ten miecz przeszywa moje serce. Moje dzieci, jeste\u015bcie na rozdro\u017cu, dokonajcie w\u0142a\u015bciwego wyboru, m\u00f3j Syn czeka na was. B\u0119d\u0119 strzeg\u0142a moje wierne i pokorne dzieci, kt\u00f3re odznaczy\u0142y si\u0119 odwag\u0105 i mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Dzieci moje, nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119, uznajcie waszego Boga za jedynego Boga i Zbawiciela, a On przez swoje wielkie Mi\u0142osierdzie przebaczy wam. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 ci\u0119, moja umi\u0142owana c\u00f3rko, i dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce przyj\u0105\u0142e\u015b mnie do swojego serca, w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego.","text_pt":"Eu sou a Virgem Imaculada, o c\u00f4njuge do Esp\u00edrito Santo, o humilde servo de Deus, a M\u00e3e de Jesus, que foi tra\u00edda, zombada e humilhada. At\u00e9 hoje essa espada perfura meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Crian\u00e7as, voc\u00ea est\u00e1 em uma encruzilhada, fa\u00e7a a escolha certa, meu filho est\u00e1 esperando por voc\u00ea. Eu vou proteger meus fidentes e humildes filhos, que se distinguiram por sua coragem e amor. Meus filhos, arrependem-se, reconhecem seu Deus como o \u00fanico Deus e Salvador e ele por sua grande miseric\u00f3rdia vai te perdoar. Agora eu aben\u00e7oei a minha amada filha e obrigado por me acolher em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o, em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo.","text_zh":"\u6211\u662f\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u5904\u5973\uff0c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u914d\u5076\uff0c\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u5351\u5fae\u4ec6\u4eba\uff0c\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\uff0c\u88ab\u80cc\u53db\uff0c\u5632\u7b11\u548c\u7f9e\u8fb1\u3002\u5373\u4f7f\u4eca\u5929\uff0c\u5251\u523a\u7a7f\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4f60\u5728\u5341\u5b57\u8def\u53e3\uff0c\u505a\u51fa\u6b63\u786e\u7684\u9009\u62e9\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u5728\u7b49\u4f60\u3002\u6211\u5c06\u4fdd\u62a4\u6211\u7684\u5fe0\u8bda\u548c\u8c26\u865a\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u901a\u8fc7\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u52c7\u6c14\u548c\u7231\u6765\u51dd\u89c6\u81ea\u5df1\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6094\u6539\uff0c\u8ba9\u4f60\u7684\u4e0a\u5e1d\u4f5c\u4e3a\u552f\u4e00\u7684\u4e0a\u5e1d\u548c\u6551\u4e16\u4e3b\uff0c\u4ed6\u7684\u4f1f\u5927\u601c\u60af\u4f1a\u539f\u8c05\u4f60\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u6211\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u8fdb\u5165\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u91cc\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":16,"month_string":"April","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear daughter, thank you for listening to my call in your heart. I am the Mother of Sorrows over the death of my Son, who is still being crucified today by men and false shepherds, Console my Mother's heart, I saw my only Son die crucified, and I with Him, and again a second sorrow when He was laid in the tomb, closed with a stone and I felt lonely, yet I still remember when on the cross He said: 'Woman, here is your Son' and there I became the Mother of all of you, I kept the sorrow in my heart and in silence. Now my children, console me with your prayers, just as I console you when you invoke me. Now I leave you my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Sehr geehrte Tochter, vielen Dank, dass Sie meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen angeh\u00f6rt haben. Ich bin die Mutter der Sorgen \u00fcber den Tod meines Sohnes, der noch heute von M\u00e4nnern und falschen Hirten gekreuzigt wird, die das Herz meiner Mutter konsolen, ich sah, wie mein einziger Sohn kreuzigte, und ich mit ihm und wieder ein zweiter Trauer, wenn er wurde in das Grab gelegt, mit einem Stein geschlossen, und ich f\u00fchlte mich einsam, doch erinnere mich immer noch, als er am Kreuz sagte mein Herz und schweigend. Nun, meine Kinder, tr\u00f6ste mich mit deinen Gebeten, so wie ich Sie tr\u00f6ste, wenn Sie mich aufrufen. Jetzt verlasse ich Ihnen meinen m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Querida hija, gracias por escuchar mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Soy la madre de Afarnad por la muerte de mi hijo, que a\u00fan es crucificado por hombres y falsos pastores, consola mi coraz\u00f3n de madre, vi a mi \u00fanico hijo morir crucificado, y yo con \u00e9l, y todav\u00eda un segundo dolor cuando fue colocado. En el sepulcro, se cerr\u00f3 con una piedra y me sent\u00ed sola, pero lo recuerdo de nuevo cuando estaba en la cruz, dijo: \"Mujer, aqu\u00ed est\u00e1 tu hijo\" y all\u00ed me convert\u00ed en madre de todos ustedes, he tomado el dolor en mi coraz\u00f3n. y silencio. Ahora mis hijos, me consuelan con oraciones, as\u00ed como te consuelo cuando me invocas. Ahora te dejo mi bendici\u00f3n materna en nombre del padre del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Cher fille, merci d'avoir \u00e9cout\u00e9 mon appel dans votre coeur. Je suis la m\u00e8re des chagrins au-dessus de la mort de mon fils, qui est toujours crucifi\u00e9e aujourd'hui par des hommes et de faux bergers, console le c\u0153ur de ma m\u00e8re, j'ai vu mon seul fils meurt crucifi\u00e9, et moi avec lui, et encore une deuxi\u00e8me chagrin quand il a \u00e9t\u00e9 pos\u00e9 dans la tombe, ferm\u00e9 avec une pierre et je me sentais seuls, mais je me souviens encore que je me souviens quand sur la croix, il a dit: \"Femme, voici ton fils 'et l\u00e0 je suis devenu la m\u00e8re de tous, j'ai gard\u00e9 le chagrin mon coeur et en silence. Maintenant, mes enfants me consolent avec vos pri\u00e8res, tout comme je vous consolis quand vous m'inquisterez. Maintenant, je vous laisse ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cara figlia, grazie per aver ascoltato la mia chiamata nel tuo cuore. Io sono la Madre Addolorata per la morte di mio Figlio, il quale ancora oggi viene crocifisso dagli uomini e dai falsi pastori, Consolate il mio cuore di Madre, ho visto il mio unico Figlio morire crocifisso, ed Io con Lui, e ancora un secondo dolore quando fu deposto nel sepolcro, chiuso con un sasso e mi sentii sola, eppure ricordo ancora quando sulla croce disse: \u201cDonna, ecco tuo Figlio\u201d e l\u00ec divenni Madre di tutti voi, ho serbato il dolore nel mio cuore e nel silenzio. Ora figli miei, consolatemi con le preghiere, cos\u00ec come Io consolo voi quando mi invocate. Ora vi lascio la mia Materna benedizione nel nome del Padre del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Droga c\u00f3rko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce ws\u0142ucha\u0142a\u015b si\u0119 w moje wo\u0142anie w twoim sercu. Jestem Matk\u0105 Bolesn\u0105 z powodu \u015bmierci mojego Syna, kt\u00f3ry jeszcze dzisiaj jest krzy\u017cowany przez ludzi i fa\u0142szywych pasterzy. Pocieszaj\u0105c moje matczyne serce, widzia\u0142am, jak m\u00f3j jedyny Syn umiera na krzy\u017cu, a ja razem z Nim, i poczu\u0142am drugi smutek, kiedy zosta\u0142 z\u0142o\u017cony w grobie, zamkni\u0119tym kamieniem, i poczu\u0142am si\u0119 samotna, ale wci\u0105\u017c pami\u0119tam, jak na krzy\u017cu powiedzia\u0142: 'Niewiasto, oto syn Tw\u00f3j' i tam sta\u0142am si\u0119 Matk\u0105 was wszystkich, zachowa\u0142am smutek w moim sercu i w ciszy. A teraz, moje dzieci, pocieszajcie mnie waszymi modlitwami, tak jak Ja was pocieszam, gdy mnie wzywacie. Teraz zostawiam wam moje matczyne b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Querida filha, obrigado por ouvir minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Eu sou a m\u00e3e de tristezas sobre a morte do meu filho, que ainda est\u00e1 sendo crucificado hoje por homens e pastores falsos, console o cora\u00e7\u00e3o da minha m\u00e3e, eu vi meu \u00fanico filho morreu crucificado, e eu com ele, e novamente uma segunda tristeza quando ele foi colocado no t\u00famulo, fechado com uma pedra e eu me senti solit\u00e1rio, mas ainda me lembro quando na cruz ele disse: 'Mulher, aqui \u00e9 o seu filho' e l\u00e1 eu me tornei a m\u00e3e de todos voc\u00eas, mantive a tristeza em meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o e em sil\u00eancio. Agora meus filhos, console-me com suas ora\u00e7\u00f5es, assim como consolei voc\u00ea quando voc\u00ea me invoca. Agora eu deixo voc\u00ea minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o maternal em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u5728\u5fc3\u91cc\u542c\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u662f\u6211\u513f\u5b50\u53bb\u4e16\u7684\u60b2\u4f24\u6bcd\u4eb2\uff0c\u4ecd\u7136\u88ab\u7537\u4eba\u548c\u5047\u7267\u7f8a\u4eba\u9489\u5728\u5341\u5b57\u67b6\u4e0a\uff0c\u63a7\u5236\u53f0\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u5fc3\u810f\uff0c\u6211\u770b\u5230\u6211\u552f\u4e00\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u6b7b\u4e86\u5341\u5b57\u67b6\uff0c\u6211\u548c\u4ed6\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\uff0c\u518d\u4e00\u6b21\u60b2\u4f24\u4e86\u88ab\u5360\u636e\u4e86\u575f\u5893\uff0c\u7528\u77f3\u5934\u95ed\u4e0a\u4e86\uff0c\u6211\u611f\u5230\u5b64\u72ec\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\u8fd8\u8bb0\u5f97\u5728\u5341\u5b57\u67b6\u4e0a\u65f6\u4ed6\u8bf4\uff1a'\u5973\u4eba\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u4f60\u7684\u513f\u5b50'\u548c\u90a3\u91cc\u6211\u6210\u4e86\u4f60\u4eec\u6240\u6709\u4eba\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\uff0c\u6211\u62b1\u7740\u60b2\u4f24\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\u548c\u6c89\u9ed8\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u7528\u4f60\u7684\u7948\u7977\u63a7\u5236\u6211\uff0c\u5c31\u50cf\u6211\u8c03\u67e5\u6211\u7684\u65f6\u5019\u4e00\u6837\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u6211\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":17,"month_string":"April","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people: may my blessing be in each one of you a motive for conversion in this commemoration of my Resurrection. I invite you to spread my call so that your brothers do not continue in the spiritual blindness that plunges them into the abyss of denial, of foolishness and of continuing to disregard my calls because of human selfishness. The human creature is in urgent need of spiritual eye salve to eliminate all that holds him back and leads him to continue denying the calls of my House. How much they will grieve for not having believed! Children, the advance of what is to come for humanity is not long in coming. That is why I have alerted you for so many years now and that is why my most holy Mother and St. Michael the Archangel have sent you their word of loving announcement about what is coming up upon humanity and it is now! My people, this generation is ignorant of what is happening and science has hidden for decades so as not to alarm. There is no longer any reason to wait, they have not obeyed me and they will be alarmed by the announcements of science. My children, only with conversion will you be able to mitigate the suffering you face. You have forgotten my calls in the face of the solar flares towards the earth. Fires and illnesses increase in human creatures that alter their organism. Man is not prepared to receive these quantities of solar radiation, which will cause the human creature to suffer alterations in his organism. This increase of heat causes the shortage of water necessary for them to subsist. I announced to you the melting of the polar ice and with this the increase of the oceans and the danger for the coastal areas. They have forgotten that years ago I warned them of the great famine on earth, famine and pestilence in all countries. They forgot that I warned them of severe earthquakes all over the earth, of the activation of volcanoes and super volcanoes causing a greenhouse effect with the lowering of temperatures all over the planet. The human creature has built industries and means of transportation indiscriminately and they are already suffering the consequences. The sun's rays will be diminished, prevented from penetrating because of the gases that will cover the earth. The means of transport will be reduced: the terrestrial and aerial ones. The earth will shake strongly and the expected great earthquakes will arrive and transform the earth. You have forgotten the grave threat that is approaching from space and will graze the earth causing very serious havoc. You have forgotten that I announced to you that you are at war, in escalating war. One country or another will enter this scenario and from one moment to the next war will make the earth something unknown. My children: before man destroys my creation, man will destroy himself and I will have rescued my people. You have forgotten that I forewarned you that Europe will suffer. The war advances destroying countries to reach Italy and seize Rome. My beloved people, look with spiritual eye salve. The war carries in its entrails the spiritual struggle to reach Rome, which is a great goal. Do not fear. You must remember what I have revealed to you before and you have forgotten. I will not allow you to destroy the earth. My people, do not fear. I, the owner of all that exists, protect you. You continue firm in the faith, being my people and receiving me in the holy Eucharist, praying, not praying, praying with your hearts for all mankind. Let no one think himself righteous... The righteous of the righteous is the one who loves them, their lord and God. My special blessing upon my children this day. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.   ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, niech moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo b\u0119dzie w ka\u017cdym z was motywem do nawr\u00f3cenia w t\u0119 pami\u0105tk\u0119 mojego Zmartwychwstania. Zach\u0119cam was do rozpowszechniania mojego wezwania, aby wasi bracia nie trwali w duchowej \u015blepocie, kt\u00f3ra pogr\u0105\u017ca ich w otch\u0142ani zaprzeczenia, g\u0142upoty i dalszego lekcewa\u017cenia moich wezwa\u0144 z powodu ludzkiego egoizmu. Stworzenie ludzkie pilnie potrzebuje duchowego \u015brodka na oczy, aby usun\u0105\u0107 to wszystko, co go powstrzymuje i prowadzi do dalszego odrzucania wezwa\u0144 mojego Domu. Jak bardzo b\u0119d\u0105 \u017ca\u0142owa\u0107, \u017ce nie uwierzyli! Dzieci, wyprzedzenie tego, co ma nadej\u015b\u0107 dla ludzko\u015bci, nie jest d\u0142ugie. Dlatego ostrzega\u0142em was przez tyle lat i dlatego moja naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Matka i \u015bwi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142 wys\u0142ali wam swoje s\u0142owa pe\u0142nej mi\u0142o\u015bci zapowiedzi tego, co nadchodzi na ludzko\u015b\u0107 i to ju\u017c teraz! M\u00f3j ludu, to pokolenie jest nie\u015bwiadome tego, co si\u0119 dzieje, a nauka przez dziesi\u0105tki lat ukrywa\u0142a, aby nie alarmowa\u0107. Nie ma ju\u017c powodu, aby czeka\u0107, nie byli Mi pos\u0142uszni i b\u0119d\u0105 alarmowani przez zapowiedzi nauki. Moje dzieci, tylko dzi\u0119ki nawr\u00f3ceniu b\u0119dziecie mogli z\u0142agodzi\u0107 cierpienie, kt\u00f3re was spotyka. Zapomnieli\u015bcie o moich wezwaniach w obliczu rozb\u0142ysk\u00f3w s\u0142onecznych w kierunku ziemi. Po\u017cary i choroby zmieniaj\u0105ce organizm istot ludzkich wzrastaj\u0105. Cz\u0142owiek nie jest przygotowany na przyj\u0119cie tych ilo\u015bci promieniowania s\u0142onecznego, kt\u00f3re spowoduj\u0105 u istoty ludzkiej zmiany w jej organizmie. Ten wzrost ciep\u0142a powoduje niedob\u00f3r wody niezb\u0119dnej do ich utrzymania. Zapowiedzia\u0142em wam topnienie lodu polarnego, a wraz z tym wzrost w\u00f3d ocean\u00f3w i niebezpiecze\u0144stwo dla obszar\u00f3w przybrze\u017cnych. Zapomnieli, \u017ce przed laty ostrzega\u0142em ich przed wielkim g\u0142odem na ziemi, g\u0142odem i zaraz\u0105 we wszystkich krajach. Zapomnieli, \u017ce ostrzega\u0142em ich o silnych trz\u0119sieniach ziemi na ca\u0142ej ziemi, o uaktywnieniu wulkan\u00f3w i superwulkan\u00f3w powoduj\u0105cych efekt cieplarniany z obni\u017ceniem temperatur na ca\u0142ej planecie. Istota ludzka bezkrytycznie zbudowa\u0142a przemys\u0142 i \u015brodki transportu i ju\u017c ponosi tego konsekwencje. Promienie s\u0142oneczne b\u0119d\u0105 zmniejszone, uniemo\u017cliwione do przenikania z powodu gaz\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re pokryj\u0105 ziemi\u0119. Zmniejsz\u0105 si\u0119 \u015brodki transportu: ziemskiego i powietrznego. Ziemia b\u0119dzie si\u0119 mocno trz\u0105\u015b\u0107, a spodziewane wielkie trz\u0119sienia ziemi dotr\u0105 i przekszta\u0142c\u0105 ziemi\u0119. Zapomnieli\u015bcie o powa\u017cnym zagro\u017ceniu, kt\u00f3re zbli\u017ca si\u0119 z kosmosu i otrze si\u0119 o Ziemi\u0119, powoduj\u0105c bardzo powa\u017cne spustoszenia. Zapomnieli\u015bcie, \u017ce og\u0142osi\u0142em wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie w stanie wojny, w eskalacji wojny. Ten czy inny kraj wejdzie w ten scenariusz i od jednej chwili do nast\u0119pnej wojna uczyni z ziemi co\u015b nieznanego. Moje dzieci: zanim cz\u0142owiek zniszczy moje stworzenie, cz\u0142owiek zniszczy siebie i Ja uratuj\u0119 m\u00f3j lud. Zapomnieli\u015bcie, \u017ce ostrzega\u0142em was, \u017ce Europa b\u0119dzie cierpie\u0107. Wojna posuwa si\u0119 naprz\u00f3d, niszcz\u0105c kraje, aby dotrze\u0107 do W\u0142och i zaj\u0105\u0107 Rzym. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludzie, patrzcie z duchowym ratunkiem na oczy. Wojna niesie w swoich wn\u0119trzno\u015bciach duchow\u0105 walk\u0119 o dotarcie do Rzymu, kt\u00f3ry jest wielkim celem. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119. Musicie pami\u0119ta\u0107 o tym, co wam wcze\u015bniej objawi\u0142em, a wy zapomnieli\u015bcie. Nie pozwol\u0119 wam zniszczy\u0107 ziemi. M\u00f3j ludu, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119. Ja, w\u0142a\u015bciciel wszystkiego, co istnieje, chroni\u0119 was. Trwajcie mocno w wierze, b\u0119d\u0105c moim ludem i przyjmuj\u0105c Mnie w \u015bwi\u0119tej Eucharystii, modl\u0105c si\u0119, nie modl\u0105c si\u0119, modl\u0105c si\u0119 sercem za ca\u0142\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107. Niech nikt nie uwa\u017ca si\u0119 za sprawiedliwego... Sprawiedliwym ze sprawiedliwych jest ten, kto kocha ich, ich Pana i Boga. Moje szczeg\u00f3lne b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo na moje dzieci w tym dniu. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":19,"month_string":"April","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My daughter, thank you for responding to my call and for bending your knees in prayer. Daughter, the Resurrection of my Jesus must be the Resurrection of all of you, change your lives, seek the things of Heaven, be ready because my most faithful children will receive many gifts. I see the rebirth of some of you and this comforts me. My Son will be seen by all, believers and non-believers, those who have believed will have great rewards. My daughter, the wicked are ready, they are waiting for a command, Rome will be struck, my faithful will be persecuted, but I say to you: do not be afraid, the devil has a precise aim to destroy everything that represents the house of God, but the underworld will not prevail. Continue in constant prayer! Children, your prayers made with the heart have come and much will be mitigated but what is written will come to pass, do not forget the prophecies, pestilence and war will reach Europe. The earth is ready for the great earthquake, but remember that I love you and will protect you together with my angels. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and of the Son and of the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Tochter, vielen Dank, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf geantwortet haben, und um Ihre Knie im Gebet zu biegen. Tochter, die Auferstehung meines Jesus muss die Auferstehung aller von Ihnen sein, \u00e4ndern Sie Ihr Leben, suchen Sie die Dinge des Himmels, seien Sie bereit, weil meine am treuesten Kinder viele Geschenke erhalten werden. Ich sehe die Wiedergeburt einiger von euch und das tr\u00f6stet mich. Mein Sohn wird von allen, Gl\u00e4ubigen und Nichtgl\u00e4ubigen gesehen, die glaubten, dass diejenigen gro\u00dfartige Belohnungen haben werden. Meine Tochter, die B\u00f6sen sind bereit, sie warten auf einen Befehl, Rom wird getroffen, meine Gl\u00e4ubigen werden verfolgt, aber ich sage Ihnen: Keine Angst, der Teufel hat ein genaues Ziel, alles zu zerst\u00f6ren, was das Haus darstellt Gott, aber die Unterwelt wird nicht herrschen. Fahren Sie mit st\u00e4ndigem Gebet fort! Kinder, Ihre Gebete, die mit dem Herzen hergestellt wurden, sind gekommen und viel werden gemildert, aber das geschriebene, was geschrieben wird, wird nicht vergessen, die Prophezeiungen nicht vergessen, Pestillenz und Krieg werden Europa erreichen. Die Erde ist bereit f\u00fcr das gro\u00dfe Erdbeben, aber denken Sie daran, dass ich Sie liebe und Sie gemeinsam mit meinen Engeln sch\u00fctzen wird. Jetzt verlasse ich Sie mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mi hija, gracias por responder a mi llamada y para doblar las rodillas en la oraci\u00f3n. Hija, la resurrecci\u00f3n de mi Jes\u00fas tendr\u00e1 que ser la resurrecci\u00f3n de todos ustedes, cambi\u00f3 sus vidas, busque las cosas del cielo, mant\u00e9ngase listo porque a mis hijos m\u00e1s fieles muchos ser\u00e1n los regalos que recibir\u00e1n. Veo al renacimiento de algunos de ustedes y esto me consuela. Mi hijo ser\u00e1 visto por todos, creyentes y no creyentes, aquellos que han cre\u00eddo tendr\u00e1n grandes recompensas. Mi hija, los malvados est\u00e1n listos, esperan un comando, se golpear\u00e1 a Roma, mis fieles ser\u00e1n perseguidos, pero le digo: No tengas miedo, el diablo tiene un prop\u00f3sito preciso que destruye todo lo que representa la Casa de Dios, pero El inframundo no prevalecer\u00e1. \u00a1Contin\u00faa en la oraci\u00f3n de Assidua! Los ni\u00f1os, sus oraciones hechas con el coraz\u00f3n llegadas y se mitigar\u00e1n mucho, pero lo que se describe se llevar\u00e1 a cabo, no se olvide de las profec\u00edas, la pestilencia y la guerra llegar\u00e1n a Europa. La tierra est\u00e1 lista para el gran terremoto, pero recuerda que te amo y te protege junto con mis \u00e1ngeles. Ahora te dejo con mi nombre de bendici\u00f3n maternal del Padre y el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo. Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Ma fille, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel et de faire plier vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re. Fille, la r\u00e9surrection de mon J\u00e9sus doit \u00eatre la r\u00e9surrection de vous tous, changez de vie, cherchez les choses du ciel, soyez pr\u00eat parce que mes enfants les plus fid\u00e8les recevront de nombreux cadeaux. Je vois la renaissance de certains d'entre vous et cela me r\u00e9conforte. Mon fils sera vu par tous, croyants et non-croyants, ceux qui ont cru auront de grandes r\u00e9compenses. Ma fille, les m\u00e9chants sont pr\u00eats, ils attendent une commande, Rome sera frapp\u00e9, mes fid\u00e8les seront pers\u00e9cut\u00e9s, mais je vous dis: N'ayez pas peur, le diable a un but pr\u00e9cis de d\u00e9truire tout ce qui repr\u00e9sente la maison de Dieu, mais le monde souterrain ne pr\u00e9vaudra pas. Continuez dans la pri\u00e8re constante! Les enfants, vos pri\u00e8res fabriqu\u00e9es avec le c\u0153ur sont venues et beaucoup seront att\u00e9nu\u00e9es, mais ce qui est \u00e9crit viendra passer, n'oublie pas les proph\u00e9ties, la peste et la guerre atteindront l'Europe. La terre est pr\u00eate pour le grand tremblement de terre, mais rappelez-vous que je vous aime et vous prot\u00e9gerez avec mes anges. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figlia mia, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata e per aver piegato le ginocchia nella preghiera. Figlia, la Resurrezione del mio Ges\u00f9 dovr\u00e0 essere la Resurrezione di tutti voi, cambiate le vostre vite, cercate le cose del cielo, tenetevi pronti perch\u00e9 ai miei figli pi\u00f9 fedeli tanti saranno i doni che riceveranno. Io vedo la rinascita di alcuni di voi e questo mi conforta. Mio Figlio sar\u00e0 visto da tutti, credenti e non credenti, coloro che avranno creduto avranno grandi ricompense. Figlia mia, i malvagi sono gi\u00e0 pronti, attendono un comando, Roma sar\u00e0 colpita, i miei fedeli saranno perseguitati, ma Io vi dico: non abbiate paura, il demonio ha uno scopo preciso distruggere tutto ci\u00f2 che rappresenta la casa di Dio, ma gli inferi non prevarranno. Continuate nella preghiera assidua! Figli, le vostre preghiere fatte con il cuore sono arrivate e molto verr\u00e0 mitigato ma ci\u00f2 che \u00e8 scritto avverr\u00e0, non dimenticate le profezie, la pestilenza e la guerra raggiunger\u00e0 l\u2019Europa. La terra \u00e8 pronta per il grande terremoto, ma ricordate che io vi amo e vi protegger\u00f2 insieme ai miei angeli. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nome del Padre e del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo. Amen.","text_pl":"C\u00f3rko moja, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce odpowiedzia\u0142a\u015b na moje wezwanie i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119\u0142a\u015b do modlitwy. C\u00f3rko, Zmartwychwstanie mojego Jezusa musi by\u0107 Zmartwychwstaniem was wszystkich, zmie\u0144cie swoje \u017cycie, szukajcie tego, co niebieskie, b\u0105d\u017acie gotowi, bo moje najwierniejsze dzieci otrzymaj\u0105 wiele dar\u00f3w. Widz\u0119 odrodzenie niekt\u00f3rych z was i to mnie pociesza. M\u00f3j Syn b\u0119dzie widziany przez wszystkich, wierz\u0105cych i niewierz\u0105cych; ci, kt\u00f3rzy uwierzyli, otrzymaj\u0105 wielk\u0105 nagrod\u0119. Moja c\u00f3rko, niegodziwi s\u0105 ju\u017c gotowi, czekaj\u0105 na rozkaz, Rzym zostanie uderzony, moi wierni b\u0119d\u0105 prze\u015bladowani, ale Ja wam m\u00f3wi\u0119: nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, diabe\u0142 ma \u015bci\u015ble okre\u015blony cel, aby zniszczy\u0107 wszystko, co stanowi Dom Bo\u017cy, ale otch\u0142a\u0144 nie zwyci\u0119\u017cy. Trwajcie na wytrwa\u0142ej modlitwie! Moje dzieci, wasze modlitwy zanoszone z serca dotar\u0142y i du\u017co zostanie z\u0142agodzone, ale to, co jest napisane, spe\u0142ni si\u0119, nie zapominajcie o proroctwach, zaraza i wojna dotr\u0105 do Europy. Ziemia jest gotowa na wielkie trz\u0119sienie ziemi, ale pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce was kocham i b\u0119d\u0119 was chroni\u0107 wraz z moimi anio\u0142ami. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Minha filha, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o e por dobrar os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Filha, a ressurrei\u00e7\u00e3o do meu Jesus deve ser a ressurrei\u00e7\u00e3o de todos voc\u00eas, mudar suas vidas, buscar as coisas do c\u00e9u, estar pronto porque minhas crian\u00e7as mais fi\u00e9is receber\u00e3o muitos presentes. Eu vejo o renascimento de alguns de voc\u00eas e isso me conforta. Meu filho ser\u00e1 visto por todos, crentes e n\u00e3o-crentes, aqueles que acreditaram ter\u00e3o grandes recompensas. Minha filha, os \u00edmpios est\u00e3o prontos, eles est\u00e3o esperando por um comando, Roma ser\u00e1 atingido, meus fi\u00e9is ser\u00e3o perseguidos, mas eu digo a voc\u00ea: N\u00e3o tenha medo, o diabo tem um objetivo preciso de destruir tudo o que representa a casa de Deus, mas o submundo n\u00e3o prevalecer\u00e1. Continue em uma ora\u00e7\u00e3o constante! As crian\u00e7as, suas ora\u00e7\u00f5es feitas com o cora\u00e7\u00e3o vieram e muito ser\u00e3o mitigadas, mas o que est\u00e1 escrito acontecer\u00e1, n\u00e3o se esque\u00e7a das profecias, pestil\u00eancia e guerra chegar\u00e3o \u00e0 Europa. A terra est\u00e1 pronta para o grande terremoto, mas lembre-se que eu te amo e ir\u00e1 proteg\u00ea-lo junto com meus anjos. Agora eu deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o maternal em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u7948\u7977\u4e2d\u5f2f\u66f2\u819d\u76d6\u3002\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u6211\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u590d\u6d3b\u5fc5\u987b\u662f\u4f60\u4eec\u6240\u6709\u4eba\u7684\u590d\u6d3b\uff0c\u6539\u53d8\u4f60\u7684\u751f\u547d\uff0c\u5bfb\u6c42\u5929\u4e0a\u7684\u4e1c\u897f\uff0c\u51c6\u5907\u597d\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u6700\u5fe0\u5b9e\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4f1a\u6536\u5230\u8bb8\u591a\u793c\u7269\u3002\u6211\u770b\u5230\u4f60\u4eec\u4e2d\u7684\u4e00\u4e9b\u4eba\u7684\u91cd\u751f\uff0c\u8fd9\u8ba9\u6211\u611f\u5230\u8212\u9002\u3002\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u5c06\u88ab\u6240\u6709\u4eba\uff0c\u4fe1\u5f92\u548c\u975e\u4fe1\u5f92\u770b\u5230\uff0c\u90a3\u4e9b\u76f8\u4fe1\u7684\u4eba\u4f1a\u6709\u5f88\u5927\u7684\u5956\u52b1\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u90aa\u6076\u7684\u51c6\u5907\u597d\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u6b63\u5728\u7b49\u5f85\u4e00\u4e2a\u547d\u4ee4\uff0c\u7f57\u9a6c\u5c06\u88ab\u51fb\u4e2d\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5fe0\u8bda\u4f1a\u8feb\u5bb3\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\u5bf9\u4f60\u8bf4\uff1a\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u9b54\u9b3c\u6709\u4e00\u4e2a\u7cbe\u786e\u7684\u76ee\u6807\u662f\u6467\u6bc1\u4ee3\u8868\u623f\u5b50\u7684\u4e00\u5207\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u4f46\u9ed1\u793e\u4f1a\u4e0d\u4f1a\u5360\u4e0a\u98ce\u3002\u7ee7\u7eed\u6301\u7eed\u7977\u544a\uff01\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4f60\u7528\u5fc3\u7684\u7948\u7977\u5df2\u7ecf\u5230\u6765\uff0c\u5f88\u5927\uff0c\u4f46\u5199\u7684\u662f\u5199\u7684\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5fd8\u8bb0\u9884\u8a00\uff0c\u761f\u75ab\u548c\u6218\u4e89\u5c06\u5230\u8fbe\u6b27\u6d32\u3002\u5730\u7403\u5df2\u7ecf\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u4e86\u5927\u5730\u9707\uff0c\u4f46\u8bf7\u8bb0\u4f4f\u6211\u7231\u4f60\uff0c\u5e76\u4f1a\u548c\u5929\u4f7f\u4e00\u8d77\u4fdd\u62a4\u4f60\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u6211\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":21,"month_string":"April","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for having responded to my call in your hearts. My children, today is the anniversary of my meeting with my chosen one and I thank her and her spouse for having always given precious time in order to carry out this great work of Grace. My children, I also thank you, who have supported all this with your faith, believing in my presence and accepting the signs sent from Heaven and for those who have opened their hearts, nothing will be lacking, the graces will be many, even the smallest, which sometimes you do not realize. My children, my children, I have called you one by one to be courageous witnesses and I am here again to ask you to help me bring souls to God. Prayer for today's event will free many souls. The plague will come, pray for the land of my Son. I now bless you in the name of the Holy Trinity, Father and the Son and Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, heute ist der Jahrestag meines Treffens mit meinem Auserw\u00e4hlten und ich danke ihr und ihrem Ehepartner, dass er immer wertvolle Zeit gegeben hat, um dieses gro\u00dfartige Gnadenwerk auszuf\u00fchren. Meine Kinder, ich danke Ihnen auch, die all dies mit Ihrem Glauben unterst\u00fctzt haben, an meine Gegenwart glauben und die Zeichen akzeptiert haben, die aus dem Himmel gesandt sind, und f\u00fcr diejenigen, die ihr Herz ge\u00f6ffnet haben, wird nichts fehlen, die Gnaden werden viele sein, sogar die Kleinstes, was man manchmal nicht merkt. Meine Kinder, meine Kinder, ich habe dich einzeln als mutige Zeugen bezeichnet und bin wieder hier, um dich zu bitten, mir zu helfen, Seelen zu Gott zu bringen. Das Gebet f\u00fcr die heutige Veranstaltung wird viele Seelen befreien. Die Pest wird kommen, f\u00fcr das Land meines Sohnes beten. Ich segne dich jetzt im Namen der Heiligen Dreifaltigkeit, Vater und der Sohn und der Heilige Geist, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, hoy es el aniversario de mi reuni\u00f3n con mi elegido y le agradezco a ella y a su novio por haber dado un tiempo precioso, para continuar con esta gran obra de gracia. Mis hijos, tambi\u00e9n les agradezco, que han apoyado todo esto con su fe, creyendo en mi presencia y dando la bienvenida a los letreros enviados desde el cielo y para aquellos que han abierto el coraz\u00f3n, nada se perder\u00e1, las gracias ser\u00e1n muchas, incluso los M\u00e1s peque\u00f1o, incluso el m\u00e1s peque\u00f1o, de los cuales a veces no se nota. Ni\u00f1os, mis hijos, los llam\u00e9 uno por uno, para ser testigos valientes y estoy aqu\u00ed, todav\u00eda para pedirte que me ayudes a traer almas a Dios. La oraci\u00f3n por el evento de hoy liberar\u00e1 a muchas almas. La pestilencia llegar\u00e1, reza por la tierra de mi hijo. Ahora te bendiga en el nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Padre, Hijo y Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, aujourd'hui, c'est l'anniversaire de ma rencontre avec mon \u00e9lu et je la remercie et son conjoint d'avoir toujours donn\u00e9 du temps pr\u00e9cieux afin de mener \u00e0 bien ce grand travail de gr\u00e2ce. Mes enfants, je vous remercie aussi, qui a soutenu tout cela avec votre foi, croyant en ma pr\u00e9sence et acceptant les signes envoy\u00e9s du ciel et pour ceux qui ont ouvert leur c\u0153ur, rien ne lui manquera, les gr\u00e2ces seront nombreuses, m\u00eame les Le plus petit, ce que vous ne r\u00e9alisez parfois pas. Mes enfants, mes enfants, je vous ai appel\u00e9 un par un pour \u00eatre des t\u00e9moins courageux et je suis de nouveau ici pour vous demander de m'aider \u00e0 apporter des \u00e2mes \u00e0 Dieu. La pri\u00e8re pour l'\u00e9v\u00e9nement d'aujourd'hui lib\u00e9rera de nombreuses \u00e2mes. La peste viendra, priera pour le pays de mon fils. Je vous b\u00e9nis maintenant au nom de la Sainte Trinit\u00e9, P\u00e8re et Fils et Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, oggi \u00e8 l\u2019anniversario del mio incontro con la mia prescelta ed Io ringrazio lei e il suo sposo di aver donato sempre tempo prezioso, al fine di portare avanti questa grande opera di Grazia. Figli miei, ringrazio anche voi, che avete supportato tutto questo con la vostra fede, credendo nella mia presenza e accogliendo i segni inviati dal cielo e per coloro che hanno aperto il cuore, nulla mancher\u00e0, le grazie saranno tante, anche le pi\u00f9 piccole, di cui a volte non vi accorgete. Figli, bambini miei, Io vi ho chiamati uno per uno, per essere testimoni coraggiosi e sono qui, ancora per chiedervi di aiutarmi a portare anime a Dio. La preghiera per l\u2019evento di oggi, liberer\u00e0 tante anime. Arriver\u00e0 la pestilenza, pregate per la terra di mio Figlio. Ora vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, Padre, Figlio e Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, dzi\u015b jest rocznica mojego spotkania z moj\u0105 wybran\u0105 i dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 jej i jej ma\u0142\u017conkowi za to, \u017ce zawsze po\u015bwi\u0119cali sw\u00f3j cenny czas, aby realizowa\u0107 to wielkie dzie\u0142o \u0141aski. Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 r\u00f3wnie\u017c wam, kt\u00f3rzy wspierali\u015bcie to wszystko swoj\u0105 wiar\u0105, wierz\u0105c w moj\u0105 obecno\u015b\u0107 i przyjmuj\u0105c znaki wysy\u0142ane z nieba, a tym, kt\u00f3rzy otworzyli swoje serca, niczego nie zabraknie; b\u0119dzie wiele \u0142ask, nawet tych najmniejszych, z kt\u00f3rych czasem nie zdajecie sobie sprawy. Moje dzieci, moje dzieci, wzywa\u0142em was wszystkich, aby\u015bcie byli odwa\u017cnymi \u015bwiadkami, i jestem tu ponownie, aby prosi\u0107 was o pomoc w przyprowadzeniu dusz do Boga. Modlitwa w intencji dzisiejszego wydarzenia uwolni wiele dusz. Nadejdzie zaraza, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za ziemi\u0119 mojego Syna. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por terem respondido \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, hoje \u00e9 o anivers\u00e1rio do meu encontro com o meu escolhido e agrade\u00e7o a ela e a sua esposa por sempre ter dado tempo precioso para realizar esse grande trabalho de gra\u00e7a. Meus filhos, eu tamb\u00e9m agrade\u00e7o, que apoiaram tudo isso com sua f\u00e9, acreditando na minha presen\u00e7a e aceitando os sinais enviados do c\u00e9u e para aqueles que abriram seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es, nada estar\u00e1 faltando, as gra\u00e7as ser\u00e3o muitas, at\u00e9 mesmo o Menor, que \u00e0s vezes voc\u00ea n\u00e3o percebe. Meus filhos, meus filhos, chamei voc\u00ea um por um para serem testemunhas corajosas e estou aqui novamente para pedir que voc\u00ea me ajude a trazer almas a Deus. A ora\u00e7\u00e3o para o evento de hoje liberar\u00e1 muitas almas. A praga vir\u00e1, ore pela terra do meu filho. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Santa Trindade, Pai, Filho e Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4eca\u5929\u662f\u6211\u4e0e\u6211\u9009\u62e9\u7684\u4f1a\u9762\u7684\u5468\u5e74\u7eaa\u5ff5\u65e5\uff0c\u6211\u611f\u8c22\u5979\u548c\u5979\u7684\u914d\u5076\u4e00\u76f4\u7ed9\u4e88\u5b9d\u8d35\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u8fdb\u884c\u8fd9\u9879\u4f1f\u5927\u7684\u6069\u5178\u5de5\u4f5c\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u4e5f\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4ee5\u60a8\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u652f\u6301\u6240\u6709\u8fd9\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u76f8\u4fe1\u6211\u7684\u5b58\u5728\u5e76\u63a5\u53d7\u4ece\u5929\u4e0a\u5bc4\u51fa\u7684\u8ff9\u8c61\uff0c\u5bf9\u4e8e\u90a3\u4e9b\u655e\u5f00\u5fc3hearts\u7684\u4eba\uff0c\u4efb\u4f55\u4eba\u90fd\u4e0d\u4f1a\u7f3a\u5c11\uff0c\u6069\u5178\u5c06\u662f\u5f88\u591a\uff0c\u751a\u81f3\u662f\u6700\u5c0f\uff0c\u6709\u65f6\u60a8\u6ca1\u6709\u610f\u8bc6\u5230\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u4e00\u4e2a\u4eba\u6253\u7535\u8bdd\u7ed9\u4f60\uff0c\u6210\u4e3a\u52c7\u6562\u7684\u89c1\u8bc1\u4eba\uff0c\u6211\u518d\u6b21\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u8981\u6c42\u4f60\u5e2e\u52a9\u6211\u628a\u7075\u9b42\u5e26\u7ed9\u4e0a\u5e1d\u3002\u4eca\u5929\u7684\u6d3b\u52a8\u7948\u7977\u5c06\u91ca\u653e\u8bb8\u591a\u7075\u9b42\u3002\u761f\u75ab\u4f1a\u6765\uff0c\u4e3a\u6211\u513f\u5b50\u7684\u571f\u5730\u7948\u7977\u3002\u6211\u73b0\u5728\u4ee5\u5723\u4e09\u4e00\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\uff0c\u963f\u4eec\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":22,"month_string":"April","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My dearly beloved people: I bless you with my Heart, in which Mercy overflows for my children. I invite you to work and act for the good. I invite you to give form to my Love so that my Mercy may be poured out on my people in abundance. My Mercy stands before each person, wishing to be received by all my own. My people: take refuge in my Infinite Mercy, source of forgiveness and hope for all my children, wellspring of conversion for the repentant, grace that descends from my Holy Spirit to the heart of each one of you so that you would receive my Love in the measure that each of you desires. Not denying myself to sinners, I go out to meet them with the abundant balm of my forgiveness so that hope in my Mercy may not be held back by human thinking. I go forth to the repentant sinner, to the sinner who grieves over their sins, to the person who feels sorry for having offended me, to the one who decides to offer me a firm purpose of amendment. I wait with my infinite patience for sinners who feel hopelessly condemned and unworthy of my Mercy that burns with love for these children of mine. My mother seeks them, calling them again and again to come to me. I am Merciful and the Just judge at the same time. You need to be aware that my Mercy is not a structure upon which my children can stand in sin, distant from me, justifying themselves deliberately in order to continue sinning. Come to me, my children: night will soon fall and the darkness will prevent you from distinguishing the true from the false throne and the true staff from the false one. They will lead you like sheep to the slaughter because they have not obeyed me and have hardened your hearts. Pray my children, pray for one another so that all might remain faithful to me. Pray my children, pray for those who refuse to receive my Mercy. Pray, my children, pray for spiritual strength and that you would resist without denying me. Pray, my children, that you would draw sheep into my fold and not drive them away. Pray, my children, that you would recognize me and not go down wrong paths. The changes have begun and yet few mention them. The man consecrated in order to serve me is not zealous for my affairs and does not warn my mystical body of the evil that is undermining it. It is urgent for my children to enter into a responsible spirituality so that they might be aware of the value of being my children and be responsible for the knowledge with which I supply them. Dearly beloved children, come to me; repent, accept my Mercy at this time, allow my holy spirit to penetrate each one of you and strengthen you; may he nourish you with knowledge and may the faith remain immovable within you. Events are already upon humanity and my children are being manipulated so that they would be controlled by those who hold power on earth. My people, there are so many sick people before your eyes - yes, spiritually sick, having neither peace nor charity towards their brothers and sisters. So many who are sick due to the human ego, who will only be able to see their errors when they need and seek me - only then, not before. My people: I will send a merciful grace for all humanity so that it might be received by my children who so desire it. This grace, prior to the warning, will descend from my house; it will be given throughout the earth and a multitude of my children will feel great pain at their offenses and will be my forgiveness. Only in this way will some of my children join my true Church and walk towards me in order to save their souls. You will go through very difficult moments, my children, but you must not forget that 'I am who I am' and that my infinite mercy remains upon every human being. I never abandon you: you are my children and 'I am your God'. In the face of great pains, you will receive much goodness from my house and the great grace for all humanity, from which you will emerge strengthened in the faith. My people, I love you. Your merciful Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moim Sercem, w kt\u00f3rym przelewa si\u0119 Mi\u0142osierdzie dla moich dzieci. Zach\u0119cam was do pracy i dzia\u0142ania dla dobra. Zach\u0119cam was do nadania formy mojej Mi\u0142o\u015bci, aby moje Mi\u0142osierdzie wyla\u0142o si\u0119 na m\u00f3j lud w obfito\u015bci. Moje Mi\u0142osierdzie stoi przed ka\u017cdym cz\u0142owiekiem, pragn\u0105c by\u0107 przyj\u0119te przez wszystkich moich. Ludu m\u00f3j, uciekaj si\u0119 do mojego niesko\u0144czonego Mi\u0142osierdzia, \u017ar\u00f3d\u0142a przebaczenia i nadziei dla wszystkich moich dzieci, \u017ar\u00f3d\u0142a nawr\u00f3cenia dla skruszonych, \u0142aski, kt\u00f3ra zst\u0119puje z mojego Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego do serca ka\u017cdego z was, aby\u015bcie otrzymali moj\u0105 Mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 w takiej mierze, jakiej ka\u017cdy z was pragnie. Nie odmawiaj\u0105c si\u0119 grzesznikom, wychodz\u0119 im na spotkanie z obfitym balsamem mojego przebaczenia, aby nadzieja w moje Mi\u0142osierdzie nie by\u0142a powstrzymywana przez ludzkie my\u015blenie. Wychodz\u0119 do skruszonego grzesznika, do grzesznika, kt\u00f3ry \u017cali si\u0119 nad swoimi grzechami, do osoby, kt\u00f3ra czuje \u017cal, \u017ce mnie obrazi\u0142a, do tego, kt\u00f3ry postanawia ofiarowa\u0107 mi stanowczy cel poprawy. Czekam z moj\u0105 niesko\u0144czon\u0105 cierpliwo\u015bci\u0105 na grzesznik\u00f3w, kt\u00f3rzy czuj\u0105 si\u0119 beznadziejnie pot\u0119pieni i niegodni mojego Mi\u0142osierdzia, kt\u00f3re p\u0142onie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 do tych moich dzieci. Matka moja szuka ich, wzywaj\u0105c ich wci\u0105\u017c na nowo, aby przyszli do mnie. Jestem Mi\u0142osiernym i Sprawiedliwym s\u0119dzi\u0105 jednocze\u015bnie. Musicie by\u0107 \u015bwiadomi, \u017ce moje Mi\u0142osierdzie nie jest struktur\u0105, na kt\u00f3rej moje dzieci mog\u0105 sta\u0107 w grzechu, oddalone ode mnie, usprawiedliwiaj\u0105c si\u0119 celowo, aby dalej grzeszy\u0107. Przyjd\u017acie do mnie, moje dzieci: wkr\u00f3tce zapadnie noc i ciemno\u015bci uniemo\u017cliwi\u0105 wam odr\u00f3\u017cnienie tronu prawdziwego od fa\u0142szywego i laski pasterskiej prawdziwej od fa\u0142szywej. Poprowadz\u0105 was jak owce na rze\u017a, poniewa\u017c nie byli mi pos\u0142uszni i zatwardzili wasze serca. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za siebie nawzajem, aby wszyscy pozostali mi wierni. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za tych, kt\u00f3rzy odmawiaj\u0105 przyj\u0119cia mojego Mi\u0142osierdzia. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, o si\u0142\u0119 duchow\u0105 i o to, aby\u015bcie stawiali op\u00f3r, nie zapieraj\u0105c si\u0119 mnie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, aby\u015bcie przyci\u0105gali owce do mojej owczarni, a nie odp\u0119dzali je. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, aby\u015bcie mnie rozpoznali i nie schodzili na z\u0142e drogi. Zmiany ju\u017c si\u0119 zacz\u0119\u0142y, a jednak ma\u0142o kto o nich wspomina. Cz\u0142owiek po\u015bwi\u0119cony, aby mi s\u0142u\u017cy\u0107, nie jest gorliwy w moich sprawach i nie ostrzega mojego mistycznego cia\u0142a przed z\u0142em, kt\u00f3re je podkopuje. Pilne jest, aby moje dzieci wesz\u0142y w odpowiedzialn\u0105 duchowo\u015b\u0107, aby by\u0142y \u015bwiadome warto\u015bci bycia moimi dzie\u0107mi i by\u0142y odpowiedzialne za wiedz\u0119, w kt\u00f3r\u0105 je zaopatruj\u0119. Drogie dzieci, przyjd\u017acie do mnie; nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119, przyjmijcie w tym czasie moje Mi\u0142osierdzie, pozw\u00f3lcie, aby m\u00f3j \u015bwi\u0119ty duch przenikn\u0105\u0142 ka\u017cdego z was i umocni\u0142 was; niech was od\u017cywi wiedz\u0105 i niech wiara pozostanie w was niewzruszona. Wydarzenia s\u0105 ju\u017c na ludzko\u015bci i moje dzieci s\u0105 manipulowane, aby by\u0142y kontrolowane przez tych, kt\u00f3rzy posiadaj\u0105 w\u0142adz\u0119 na ziemi. Ludu m\u00f3j, przed waszymi oczami jest tak wielu chorych - tak, chorych duchowo, niemaj\u0105cych ani pokoju, ani mi\u0142o\u015bci do swoich braci i si\u00f3str. Tak wielu chorych z powodu ludzkiego ego, kt\u00f3rzy b\u0119d\u0105 mogli zobaczy\u0107 swoje b\u0142\u0119dy dopiero wtedy, gdy b\u0119d\u0105 mnie potrzebowa\u0107 i szuka\u0107 - dopiero wtedy, nie wcze\u015bniej. M\u00f3j ludu, ze\u015bl\u0119 \u0142ask\u0119 mi\u0142osiern\u0105 dla ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci, aby mog\u0142y j\u0105 otrzyma\u0107 Moje dzieci, kt\u00f3re tego pragn\u0105. Ta \u0142aska, poprzedzaj\u0105ca ostrze\u017cenie, zst\u0105pi z mojego domu; b\u0119dzie udzielona na ca\u0142ej ziemi i rzesza moich dzieci odczuje wielki b\u00f3l z powodu swoich przewinie\u0144 i b\u0119dzie mi przebacza\u0107. Tylko w ten spos\u00f3b niekt\u00f3re z moich dzieci do\u0142\u0105cz\u0105 do mojego prawdziwego Ko\u015bcio\u0142a i b\u0119d\u0105 sz\u0142y ku Mnie, aby uratowa\u0107 swoje dusze. B\u0119dziecie przechodzi\u0107 przez bardzo trudne chwile, moje dzieci, ale nie wolno wam zapomina\u0107, \u017ce \"Jestem, kt\u00f3ry Jestem\" i \u017ce moje niesko\u0144czone mi\u0142osierdzie pozostaje nad ka\u017cdym cz\u0142owiekiem. Nigdy was nie opuszczam: jeste\u015bcie moimi dzie\u0107mi i \"Ja jestem waszym Bogiem\". W obliczu wielkich b\u00f3l\u00f3w otrzymacie wiele dobroci z mojego domu i wielk\u0105 \u0142ask\u0119 dla ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci, z kt\u00f3rej wyjdziecie umocnieni w wierze. M\u00f3j ludu, kocham ci\u0119. Wasz mi\u0142osierny Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":22,"month_string":"April","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My dearly beloved people: I bless you with my Heart, in which Mercy overflows for my children. I invite you to work and act for the good. I invite you to give form to my Love so that my Mercy may be poured out on my people in abundance. My Mercy stands before each person, wishing to be received by all my own. My people: take refuge in my Infinite Mercy, source of forgiveness and hope for all my children, wellspring of conversion for the repentant, grace that descends from my Holy Spirit to the heart of each one of you so that you would receive my Love in the measure that each of you desires. Not denying myself to sinners, I go out to meet them with the abundant balm of my forgiveness so that hope in my Mercy may not be held back by human thinking. I go forth to the repentant sinner, to the sinner who grieves over their sins, to the person who feels sorry for having offended me, to the one who decides to offer me a firm purpose of amendment. I wait with my infinite patience for sinners who feel hopelessly condemned and unworthy of my Mercy that burns with love for these children of mine. My mother seeks them, calling them again and again to come to me. I am Merciful and the Just judge at the same time. You need to be aware that my Mercy is not a structure upon which my children can stand in sin, distant from me, justifying themselves deliberately in order to continue sinning. Come to me, my children: night will soon fall and the darkness will prevent you from distinguishing the true from the false throne and the true staff from the false one. They will lead you like sheep to the slaughter because they have not obeyed me and have hardened your hearts. Pray my children, pray for one another so that all might remain faithful to me. Pray my children, pray for those who refuse to receive my Mercy. Pray, my children, pray for spiritual strength and that you would resist without denying me. Pray, my children, that you would draw sheep into my fold and not drive them away. Pray, my children, that you would recognize me and not go down wrong paths. The changes have begun and yet few mention them. The man consecrated in order to serve me is not zealous for my affairs and does not warn my mystical body of the evil that is undermining it. It is urgent for my children to enter into a responsible spirituality so that they might be aware of the value of being my children and be responsible for the knowledge with which I supply them. Dearly beloved children, come to me; repent, accept my Mercy at this time, allow my holy spirit to penetrate each one of you and strengthen you; may he nourish you with knowledge and may the faith remain immovable within you. Events are already upon humanity and my children are being manipulated so that they would be controlled by those who hold power on earth. My people, there are so many sick people before your eyes - yes, spiritually sick, having neither peace nor charity towards their brothers and sisters. So many who are sick due to the human ego, who will only be able to see their errors when they need and seek me - only then, not before. My people: I will send a merciful grace for all humanity so that it might be received by my children who so desire it. This grace, prior to the warning, will descend from my house; it will be given throughout the earth and a multitude of my children will feel great pain at their offenses and will be my forgiveness. Only in this way will some of my children join my true Church and walk towards me in order to save their souls. You will go through very difficult moments, my children, but you must not forget that 'I am who I am' and that my infinite mercy remains upon every human being. I never abandon you: you are my children and 'I am your God'. In the face of great pains, you will receive much goodness from my house and the great grace for all humanity, from which you will emerge strengthened in the faith. My people, I love you. Your merciful Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: jeste\u015bcie w drodze ku uroczysto\u015bci Mi\u0142osierdzia Bo\u017cego. Lud Bo\u017cy musi by\u0107 zjednoczony. Ewangelizacja to wsp\u00f3lna sprawa, to nieustanne praktykowanie braterskiej mi\u0142o\u015bci. Jeste\u015bcie robotnikami w winnicy i powinni\u015bcie pracowa\u0107 na polu wam powierzonym, wiedz\u0105c, \u017ce w winnicy jest tylko jeden pan i w\u0142adca. Lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa jest wezwany do zachowania osobistego pokoju i przekazywania go swoim braciom i siostrom. Ci, kt\u00f3rzy nie maj\u0105 wewn\u0119trznego pokoju, nie maj\u0105 m\u0105dro\u015bci, aby zachowa\u0107 r\u00f3wnowag\u0119 po\u015br\u00f3d burz. B\u0105d\u017acie pe\u0142ni szacunku wobec siebie nawzajem; m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 do naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych. Ludu Bo\u017cy, w tej chwili diabe\u0142 przenikn\u0105\u0142 trucizn\u0105 niekt\u00f3re istoty ludzkie, maj\u0105c na celu stworzenie w\u015br\u00f3d nich roz\u0142amu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, aby nasza Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka pomog\u0142a wam i aby\u015bcie byli nosicielami prawdziwego pokoju, gdy\u017c \"od ka\u017cdego, komu wiele dano, wiele wymaga\u0107 si\u0119 b\u0119dzie\". W tym czasie, kiedy ludzko\u015b\u0107 widzi na ma\u0142\u0105 skal\u0119, zach\u0119cam was do spojrzenia okiem or\u0142a na to wszystko, co si\u0119 dzieje. Dobrze wiecie, \u017ce ci, kt\u00f3rzy dominuj\u0105 nad ludzko\u015bci\u0105, utrzymuj\u0105 to, co jest dla nich korzystne i podkopuj\u0105 instytucj\u0119 Ko\u015bcio\u0142a naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Dlatego b\u0105d\u017acie stworzeniami pokoju, kt\u00f3re z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 pracuj\u0105 na polach Kr\u00f3la, aby\u015bcie nie zostali pomyleni z k\u0105kolem. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, ludzie Bo\u017cy. Moje niebia\u0144skie legiony nieustannie was strzeg\u0105. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":22,"month_string":"April","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: you are on your way towards the celebration of Divine Mercy. The people of God must be united. Evangelization is a common cause, a constant practising of fraternal love. You are workers in the vineyard and you should labour in the field entrusted to you, knowing that in the vineyard there is only one lord and master. The people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ are called to maintain personal peace and to transmit it to their brothers and sisters. Those who do not have inner peace do not have the wisdom to maintain equanimity in the midst of storms. Be respectful towards one another; pray to our Queen and Mother of the End Times. People of God, at the moment the devil has infiltrated some human beings with poison, aiming to create disunity among them. Pray that our Queen and Mother would help you and that you would be bearers of true peace, as 'from everyone to whom much has been given, much will be required'. At this time when humanity is seeing on a small scale, I invite you to look with the eye of an eagle at all that is happening. You know full well that those who dominate humanity are maintaining what is favourable to them and undermining the institution of the Church of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Therefore, be creatures of peace who work lovingly in the fields of the King, in order that you might not be confused with the tares. I bless you, people of God. My heavenly legions are continually guarding you. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moim Sercem, w kt\u00f3rym przelewa si\u0119 Mi\u0142osierdzie dla moich dzieci. Zach\u0119cam was do pracy i dzia\u0142ania dla dobra. Zach\u0119cam was do nadania formy mojej Mi\u0142o\u015bci, aby moje Mi\u0142osierdzie wyla\u0142o si\u0119 na m\u00f3j lud w obfito\u015bci. Moje Mi\u0142osierdzie stoi przed ka\u017cdym cz\u0142owiekiem, pragn\u0105c by\u0107 przyj\u0119te przez wszystkich moich. Ludu m\u00f3j, uciekaj si\u0119 do mojego niesko\u0144czonego Mi\u0142osierdzia, \u017ar\u00f3d\u0142a przebaczenia i nadziei dla wszystkich moich dzieci, \u017ar\u00f3d\u0142a nawr\u00f3cenia dla skruszonych, \u0142aski, kt\u00f3ra zst\u0119puje z mojego Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego do serca ka\u017cdego z was, aby\u015bcie otrzymali moj\u0105 Mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 w takiej mierze, jakiej ka\u017cdy z was pragnie. Nie odmawiaj\u0105c si\u0119 grzesznikom, wychodz\u0119 im na spotkanie z obfitym balsamem mojego przebaczenia, aby nadzieja w moje Mi\u0142osierdzie nie by\u0142a powstrzymywana przez ludzkie my\u015blenie. Wychodz\u0119 do skruszonego grzesznika, do grzesznika, kt\u00f3ry \u017cali si\u0119 nad swoimi grzechami, do osoby, kt\u00f3ra czuje \u017cal, \u017ce mnie obrazi\u0142a, do tego, kt\u00f3ry postanawia ofiarowa\u0107 mi stanowczy cel poprawy. Czekam z moj\u0105 niesko\u0144czon\u0105 cierpliwo\u015bci\u0105 na grzesznik\u00f3w, kt\u00f3rzy czuj\u0105 si\u0119 beznadziejnie pot\u0119pieni i niegodni mojego Mi\u0142osierdzia, kt\u00f3re p\u0142onie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 do tych moich dzieci. Matka moja szuka ich, wzywaj\u0105c ich wci\u0105\u017c na nowo, aby przyszli do mnie. Jestem Mi\u0142osiernym i Sprawiedliwym s\u0119dzi\u0105 jednocze\u015bnie. Musicie by\u0107 \u015bwiadomi, \u017ce moje Mi\u0142osierdzie nie jest struktur\u0105, na kt\u00f3rej moje dzieci mog\u0105 sta\u0107 w grzechu, oddalone ode mnie, usprawiedliwiaj\u0105c si\u0119 celowo, aby dalej grzeszy\u0107. Przyjd\u017acie do mnie, moje dzieci: wkr\u00f3tce zapadnie noc i ciemno\u015bci uniemo\u017cliwi\u0105 wam odr\u00f3\u017cnienie tronu prawdziwego od fa\u0142szywego i laski pasterskiej prawdziwej od fa\u0142szywej. Poprowadz\u0105 was jak owce na rze\u017a, poniewa\u017c nie byli mi pos\u0142uszni i zatwardzili wasze serca. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za siebie nawzajem, aby wszyscy pozostali mi wierni. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za tych, kt\u00f3rzy odmawiaj\u0105 przyj\u0119cia mojego Mi\u0142osierdzia. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, o si\u0142\u0119 duchow\u0105 i o to, aby\u015bcie stawiali op\u00f3r, nie zapieraj\u0105c si\u0119 mnie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, aby\u015bcie przyci\u0105gali owce do mojej owczarni, a nie odp\u0119dzali je. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, aby\u015bcie mnie rozpoznali i nie schodzili na z\u0142e drogi. Zmiany ju\u017c si\u0119 zacz\u0119\u0142y, a jednak ma\u0142o kto o nich wspomina. Cz\u0142owiek po\u015bwi\u0119cony, aby mi s\u0142u\u017cy\u0107, nie jest gorliwy w moich sprawach i nie ostrzega mojego mistycznego cia\u0142a przed z\u0142em, kt\u00f3re je podkopuje. Pilne jest, aby moje dzieci wesz\u0142y w odpowiedzialn\u0105 duchowo\u015b\u0107, aby by\u0142y \u015bwiadome warto\u015bci bycia moimi dzie\u0107mi i by\u0142y odpowiedzialne za wiedz\u0119, w kt\u00f3r\u0105 je zaopatruj\u0119. Drogie dzieci, przyjd\u017acie do mnie; nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119, przyjmijcie w tym czasie moje Mi\u0142osierdzie, pozw\u00f3lcie, aby m\u00f3j \u015bwi\u0119ty duch przenikn\u0105\u0142 ka\u017cdego z was i umocni\u0142 was; niech was od\u017cywi wiedz\u0105 i niech wiara pozostanie w was niewzruszona. Wydarzenia s\u0105 ju\u017c na ludzko\u015bci i moje dzieci s\u0105 manipulowane, aby by\u0142y kontrolowane przez tych, kt\u00f3rzy posiadaj\u0105 w\u0142adz\u0119 na ziemi. Ludu m\u00f3j, przed waszymi oczami jest tak wielu chorych - tak, chorych duchowo, niemaj\u0105cych ani pokoju, ani mi\u0142o\u015bci do swoich braci i si\u00f3str. Tak wielu chorych z powodu ludzkiego ego, kt\u00f3rzy b\u0119d\u0105 mogli zobaczy\u0107 swoje b\u0142\u0119dy dopiero wtedy, gdy b\u0119d\u0105 mnie potrzebowa\u0107 i szuka\u0107 - dopiero wtedy, nie wcze\u015bniej. M\u00f3j ludu, ze\u015bl\u0119 \u0142ask\u0119 mi\u0142osiern\u0105 dla ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci, aby mog\u0142y j\u0105 otrzyma\u0107 Moje dzieci, kt\u00f3re tego pragn\u0105. Ta \u0142aska, poprzedzaj\u0105ca ostrze\u017cenie, zst\u0105pi z mojego domu; b\u0119dzie udzielona na ca\u0142ej ziemi i rzesza moich dzieci odczuje wielki b\u00f3l z powodu swoich przewinie\u0144 i b\u0119dzie mi przebacza\u0107. Tylko w ten spos\u00f3b niekt\u00f3re z moich dzieci do\u0142\u0105cz\u0105 do mojego prawdziwego Ko\u015bcio\u0142a i b\u0119d\u0105 sz\u0142y ku Mnie, aby uratowa\u0107 swoje dusze. B\u0119dziecie przechodzi\u0107 przez bardzo trudne chwile, moje dzieci, ale nie wolno wam zapomina\u0107, \u017ce \"Jestem, kt\u00f3ry Jestem\" i \u017ce moje niesko\u0144czone mi\u0142osierdzie pozostaje nad ka\u017cdym cz\u0142owiekiem. Nigdy was nie opuszczam: jeste\u015bcie moimi dzie\u0107mi i \"Ja jestem waszym Bogiem\". W obliczu wielkich b\u00f3l\u00f3w otrzymacie wiele dobroci z mojego domu i wielk\u0105 \u0142ask\u0119 dla ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci, z kt\u00f3rej wyjdziecie umocnieni w wierze. M\u00f3j ludu, kocham ci\u0119. Wasz mi\u0142osierny Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":22,"month_string":"April","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: you are on your way towards the celebration of Divine Mercy. The people of God must be united. Evangelization is a common cause, a constant practising of fraternal love. You are workers in the vineyard and you should labour in the field entrusted to you, knowing that in the vineyard there is only one lord and master. The people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ are called to maintain personal peace and to transmit it to their brothers and sisters. Those who do not have inner peace do not have the wisdom to maintain equanimity in the midst of storms. Be respectful towards one another; pray to our Queen and Mother of the End Times. People of God, at the moment the devil has infiltrated some human beings with poison, aiming to create disunity among them. Pray that our Queen and Mother would help you and that you would be bearers of true peace, as 'from everyone to whom much has been given, much will be required'. At this time when humanity is seeing on a small scale, I invite you to look with the eye of an eagle at all that is happening. You know full well that those who dominate humanity are maintaining what is favourable to them and undermining the institution of the Church of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Therefore, be creatures of peace who work lovingly in the fields of the King, in order that you might not be confused with the tares. I bless you, people of God. My heavenly legions are continually guarding you. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: jeste\u015bcie w drodze ku uroczysto\u015bci Mi\u0142osierdzia Bo\u017cego. Lud Bo\u017cy musi by\u0107 zjednoczony. Ewangelizacja to wsp\u00f3lna sprawa, to nieustanne praktykowanie braterskiej mi\u0142o\u015bci. Jeste\u015bcie robotnikami w winnicy i powinni\u015bcie pracowa\u0107 na polu wam powierzonym, wiedz\u0105c, \u017ce w winnicy jest tylko jeden pan i w\u0142adca. Lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa jest wezwany do zachowania osobistego pokoju i przekazywania go swoim braciom i siostrom. Ci, kt\u00f3rzy nie maj\u0105 wewn\u0119trznego pokoju, nie maj\u0105 m\u0105dro\u015bci, aby zachowa\u0107 r\u00f3wnowag\u0119 po\u015br\u00f3d burz. B\u0105d\u017acie pe\u0142ni szacunku wobec siebie nawzajem; m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 do naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych. Ludu Bo\u017cy, w tej chwili diabe\u0142 przenikn\u0105\u0142 trucizn\u0105 niekt\u00f3re istoty ludzkie, maj\u0105c na celu stworzenie w\u015br\u00f3d nich roz\u0142amu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, aby nasza Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka pomog\u0142a wam i aby\u015bcie byli nosicielami prawdziwego pokoju, gdy\u017c \"od ka\u017cdego, komu wiele dano, wiele wymaga\u0107 si\u0119 b\u0119dzie\". W tym czasie, kiedy ludzko\u015b\u0107 widzi na ma\u0142\u0105 skal\u0119, zach\u0119cam was do spojrzenia okiem or\u0142a na to wszystko, co si\u0119 dzieje. Dobrze wiecie, \u017ce ci, kt\u00f3rzy dominuj\u0105 nad ludzko\u015bci\u0105, utrzymuj\u0105 to, co jest dla nich korzystne i podkopuj\u0105 instytucj\u0119 Ko\u015bcio\u0142a naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Dlatego b\u0105d\u017acie stworzeniami pokoju, kt\u00f3re z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 pracuj\u0105 na polach Kr\u00f3la, aby\u015bcie nie zostali pomyleni z k\u0105kolem. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, ludzie Bo\u017cy. Moje niebia\u0144skie legiony nieustannie was strzeg\u0105. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":23,"month_string":"April","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for having responded to my call in your hearts. My children, how much love I feel for you! Beloved children, tomorrow is the day of Divine Mercy, soon you will see Jesus with His rays illuminating the world, welcome Him in all His grace and kneel down. Children, I, your mother, ask only one thing, convert, cry out to the world before it is too late. My children, do not ridicule prophecies by rejecting them, but welcome them, they will serve to warn you of what may happen, for this I ask you to pray hard. My children, God will purify this land of enemies and stench and will reap all the best fruits, protecting those who have great love for Him. Now I leave you, with my motherly blessing, in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, wie viel Liebe f\u00fchle ich f\u00fcr dich! Geliebte Kinder, morgen ist der Tag der g\u00f6ttlichen Barmherzigkeit. Bald werden Sie Jesus mit seinen Strahlen sehen, die die Welt beleuchten, ihn in all seiner Gnade begr\u00fc\u00dfen und knien. Kinder, ich, deine Mutter, frage nur eine Sache, konvertieren, schreie zur Welt, bevor es zu sp\u00e4t ist. Meine Kinder, machen Sie Prophezeiungen nicht, indem sie sie ablehnen, aber begr\u00fc\u00dfen sie, sie werden dazu dienen, Sie vor dem zu warnen, was passieren kann. Denn dies bitte ich Sie, hart zu beten. Meine Kinder, Gott, wird dieses Land der Feinde und Gestank reinigen und alle besten Fr\u00fcchte ernten und diejenigen besch\u00fctzen, die gro\u00dfe Liebe zu ihm haben. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. \u00a1Ni\u00f1os, cu\u00e1nto amor siento por ti! Amados hijos, ma\u00f1ana es el d\u00eda de la misericordia divina, pronto ver\u00e1s a Jes\u00fas con sus rayos iluminar el mundo, darle la bienvenida en toda su gracia y arrodillarse. Hijos, yo, tu madre, solo le pido una cosa, converso, grito en el mundo antes de que sea demasiado tarde. Ni\u00f1os, no rid\u00edculos de las profec\u00edas rechaz\u00e1ndolos, pero les dan la bienvenida, servir\u00e1n para advertirle sobre lo que puede suceder, por esta raz\u00f3n le pido que ore mucho. Mis hijos, Dios purificar\u00e1 esta tierra de los enemigos y el fier y recolectar\u00e1 todas las mejores frutas, protegiendo a quienes sienten un gran amor por \u00e9l. Ahora te dejo, con mi bendici\u00f3n materna, en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y El Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, \u00e0 quel point je ressens pour toi! Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, demain est le jour de la mis\u00e9ricorde divine, bient\u00f4t vous verrez J\u00e9sus avec ses rayons illuminant le monde, accueille-le dans toute sa gr\u00e2ce et s'agenouillera. Les enfants, moi, ta m\u00e8re, je demande une seule chose, convertissez-vous, crie au monde avant qu'il ne soit trop tard. Mes enfants, ne ridiculisez pas les proph\u00e9ties en les rejetant, mais les accueillent, ils serviront \u00e0 vous avertir de ce qui pourrait arriver, car je vous demande de prier dur. Mes enfants, Dieu purifiera cette terre d'ennemis et de puanteur et r\u00e9coltera tous les meilleurs fruits, prot\u00e9geant ceux qui aiment beaucoup pour lui. Maintenant, je vous quitte, avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, quanto amore sento per voi!  Figli amati, domani \u00e8 la giornata della Divina Misericordia, presto vedrete Ges\u00f9 con i suoi raggi illuminare il mondo, accoglietelo in tutta la sua grazia e inginocchiatevi. Figli, Io, vostra madre chiedo solo una cosa, convertitevi, urlatelo al mondo prima che sia troppo tardi. Figli, non ridicolizzate le profezie respingendole, ma accoglietele, serviranno a mettervi in guardia su ci\u00f2 che potr\u00e0 accadere, per questo vi chiedo di pregare tanto. Figli miei, Dio purificher\u00e0 questa terra dai nemici e dal fetore e raccoglier\u00e0 tutti i frutti migliori, proteggendo coloro che provano grande amore per Lui. Ora vi lascio, con la mia benedizione materna, nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, jak wielk\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 czuj\u0119 do was!  Umi\u0142owane dzieci, jutro jest dzie\u0144 Mi\u0142osierdzia Bo\u017cego, wkr\u00f3tce ujrzycie Jezusa z Jego promieniami roz\u015bwietlaj\u0105cymi \u015bwiat, przyjmijcie Go w ca\u0142ej Jego \u0142asce i ukl\u0119knijcie. Dzieci, ja, wasza matka, prosz\u0119 tylko o jedno, nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119, wo\u0142ajcie do \u015bwiata, zanim b\u0119dzie za p\u00f3\u017ano. Dzieci moje, nie wy\u015bmiewajcie si\u0119 z proroctw, odrzucaj\u0105c je, ale je przyjmijcie, one pos\u0142u\u017c\u0105 wam do ostrze\u017cenia przed tym, co mo\u017ce si\u0119 wydarzy\u0107, dlatego tak bardzo prosz\u0119 was o modlitw\u0119. Moje dzieci, B\u00f3g oczy\u015bci t\u0119 ziemi\u0119 z wrog\u00f3w i smrodu i zbierze wszystkie najlepsze owoce, chroni\u0105c tych, kt\u00f3rzy maj\u0105 wielk\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do Niego. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem, w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por terem respondido \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, quanto amor eu sinto por voc\u00ea! Crian\u00e7as amadas, amanh\u00e3 \u00e9 o dia da miseric\u00f3rdia divina, em breve voc\u00ea ver\u00e1 Jesus com seus raios iluminando o mundo, bem -vindo -O em toda a sua gra\u00e7a e se ajoelhar\u00e1. Filhos, eu, sua m\u00e3e, pergunto apenas uma coisa, convertendo, clama ao mundo antes que seja tarde demais. Meus filhos, n\u00e3o ridicularizam as profecias rejeitando -os, mas os recebem, eles servir\u00e3o para alert\u00e1 -lo sobre o que pode acontecer, pois pe\u00e7o que voc\u00ea ore com for\u00e7a. Meus filhos, Deus purificar\u00e1 esta terra de inimigos e fedor e colher\u00e1 os melhores frutos, protegendo aqueles que t\u00eam grande amor por ele. Agora eu deixo voc\u00ea, com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna, em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u5bf9\u4f60\u6709\u591a\u7231\uff01\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u660e\u5929\u662f\u795e\u5723\u601c\u60af\u7684\u65e5\u5b50\uff0c\u5f88\u5feb\u60a8\u5c31\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u8036\u7a23\u5e26\u7740\u4ed6\u7684\u5149\u8292\u7167\u4eae\u4e16\u754c\uff0c\u4ee5\u4ed6\u7684\u4e00\u5207\u6069\u5178\u6b22\u8fce\u4ed6\uff0c\u8dea\u4e0b\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\uff0c\u4f60\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\uff0c\u53ea\u95ee\u4e00\u4ef6\u4e8b\uff0c\u8f6c\u6362\uff0c\u5728\u4e3a\u65f6\u5df2\u665a\u4e4b\u524d\u5411\u4e16\u754c\u54ed\u6ce3\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u901a\u8fc7\u62d2\u7edd\u9884\u8a00\u6765\u5632\u7b11\u9884\u8a00\uff0c\u4f46\u6b22\u8fce\u4ed6\u4eec\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u8b66\u544a\u60a8\u53ef\u80fd\u53d1\u751f\u7684\u4e8b\u60c5\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u8981\u60a8\u52aa\u529b\u7948\u7977\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e0a\u5e1d\u4f1a\u51c0\u5316\u654c\u4eba\u548c\u6076\u81ed\u7684\u571f\u5730\uff0c\u5e76\u5c06\u6536\u83b7\u6240\u6709\u6700\u597d\u7684\u6c34\u679c\uff0c\u4fdd\u62a4\u90a3\u4e9b\u5bf9\u4ed6\u6709\u7740\u6781\u5927\u7231\u7684\u4eba\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7ed9\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u79bb\u5f00\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":26,"month_string":"April","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My children, why do you not take great care of My Work? I have given you a place to be followed and blessed, I have told you that one day that place will be like Eden and you only watch and take care of your little garden. Brothers, you act as My Apostles did, when I asked them to keep watch, they fell asleep, do not be careless about the works of God and respect with Love the place blessed by My Father, where I lay My feet and where My Most Holy Mother instructs you for the times to come. One day it will be your refuge, do not forget it. Pray for the Pope and for my Church, for they are faltering, the earth will continue to shake. Now I leave you with my blessing in the name of the Father, my Most Holy Name and the Holy Spirit.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, warum k\u00fcmmerst du dich nicht sehr um meine Arbeit? Ich habe Ihnen einen Platz gegeben, an dem Sie verfolgt und gesegnet werden k\u00f6nnen. Ich habe Ihnen gesagt, dass eines Tages dieser Ort wie Eden sein wird und Sie nur Ihren kleinen Garten beobachten und aufpassen. Br\u00fcder, du handelst wie meine Apostel, als ich sie bat, die Uhr zu beobachten, sie schliefen ein, seien Die heilige Mutter weist Sie an, dass die Zeiten kommen. Eines Tages wird es Ihre Zuflucht sein, vergessen Sie es nicht. Bete f\u00fcr den Papst und f\u00fcr meine Kirche, denn sie ins Stocken geraten, wird die Erde weiterhin zittern. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem Segen im Namen des Vaters, meinem heiligsten Namen und des Heiligen Geistes.","text_es":"Mis hijos, \u00bfpor qu\u00e9 no te importa mucho mi trabajo? Di un lugar para ser seguido y bendecido, te dije que alg\u00fan d\u00eda ese lugar ser\u00e1 como Eden y t\u00fa te miras y solo tratas con tu huerto. Hermanos, act\u00faan como mis ap\u00f3stoles, cuando ped\u00ed que la vigilara, se quedaron dormidos, no sean independientemente de las obras de Dios y respeten el lugar bendecido con mi Padre con amor, donde pongo mis pies y donde mi Santa Madre, Te instruye por los tiempos que vendr\u00e1n. Un d\u00eda ser\u00e1 tu refugio, no lo olvides. Ore por el Papa y por mi iglesia, porque est\u00e1n vacilando, la tierra continuar\u00e1 temblando. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n en el nombre del Padre, de mi Santo Nombre y el Esp\u00edritu Santo.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, pourquoi ne prenez-vous pas grand soin de mon travail? Je vous ai donn\u00e9 un endroit pour \u00eatre suivi et b\u00e9ni, je vous ai dit qu'un jour cet endroit sera comme Eden et que vous ne regardez que et prenez soin de votre petit jardin. Fr\u00e8res, vous agissez comme mes ap\u00f4tres l'ont fait, quand je leur ai demand\u00e9 de surveiller, ils se sont endormis, ne sont pas insouciants sur les \u0153uvres de Dieu et le respect avec amour le lieu b\u00e9ni par mon p\u00e8re, o\u00f9 je mets mes pieds et o\u00f9 mon plus Sainte M\u00e8re vous instruit pour que les temps viennent. Un jour, ce sera votre refuge, ne l'oubliez pas. Priez pour le pape et pour mon \u00e9glise, car ils vacillent, la terre continuera \u00e0 trembler. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction dans le nom du P\u00e8re, mon plus saint nom et le Saint-Esprit.","text_it":"Figli miei, perch\u00e9 non avete molta cura della Mia Opera? Io ho dato un luogo per essere seguiti e benedetti, vi ho detto che un giorno quel luogo sar\u00e0 come l\u2019Eden e voi guardate e vi occupate solo del vostro orticello. Fratelli, agite come i miei Apostoli, quando avevo chiesto di vegliare, si sono addormentati, non siate incuranti per le opere di Dio e rispettate con Amore il luogo benedetto dal Padre mio, dove Io poso i miei piedi e dove la mia Santissima Madre, vi istruisce per i tempi che arriveranno. Un giorno sar\u00e0 il vostro rifugio, non dimenticatelo. Pregate per il Papa e per la mia Chiesa, perch\u00e9 stanno vacillando, la terra continuer\u00e0 a tremare. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione nel nome del Padre, del mio Santissimo nome e dello Spirito Santo.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dlaczego nie troszczycie si\u0119 o moje dzie\u0142o? Da\u0142em wam miejsce, w kt\u00f3rym b\u0119dziecie czci\u0107 i b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0107, powiedzia\u0142em wam, \u017ce pewnego dnia to miejsce b\u0119dzie jak Eden, a wy tylko patrzycie na sw\u00f3j ma\u0142y ogr\u00f3dek i dbacie o niego. Bracia, post\u0119pujcie tak, jak czynili to Moi Aposto\u0142owie, kiedy prosi\u0142em ich, aby czuwali, a oni zasn\u0119li, nie b\u0105d\u017acie oboj\u0119tni na dzie\u0142a Bo\u017ce i z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 szanujcie miejsce pob\u0142ogos\u0142awione przez Mojego Ojca, gdzie k\u0142ad\u0119 Moje stopy i gdzie Moja Naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Matka poucza was na nadchodz\u0105ce czasy. Pewnego dnia b\u0119dzie to twoje schronienie, nie zapominaj o tym. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za papie\u017ca i za m\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, bo oni s\u0142abn\u0105, a ziemia nadal b\u0119dzie dr\u017ce\u0107. Teraz zostawiam was z moim b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca, Mojego Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszego Imienia i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, por que voc\u00ea n\u00e3o cuida muito do meu trabalho? Eu lhe dei um lugar para ser seguido e aben\u00e7oado, disse que um dia esse lugar ser\u00e1 como Eden e voc\u00ea s\u00f3 assiste e cuida do seu pequeno jardim. Irm\u00e3os, voc\u00ea age como meus ap\u00f3stolos, quando pedi que eles vigiassem, adormeceram, n\u00e3o se descuvem com as obras de Deus e respeitem o amor ao lugar aben\u00e7oado por meu pai, onde deito meus p\u00e9s e onde o meu mais A Santa M\u00e3e o instrui para os pr\u00f3ximos tempos. Um dia ser\u00e1 seu ref\u00fagio, n\u00e3o esque\u00e7a. Ore pelo papa e pela minha igreja, pois eles est\u00e3o vacilando, a terra continuar\u00e1 a tremer. Agora deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o em nome do Pai, meu mais santo nome e o Esp\u00edrito Santo.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e3a\u4ec0\u4e48\u4f60\u4e0d\u7167\u987e\u6211\u7684\u5de5\u4f5c\uff1f\u6211\u7ed9\u4e86\u60a8\u4e00\u4e2a\u503c\u5f97\u5173\u6ce8\u548c\u795d\u798f\u7684\u5730\u65b9\uff0c\u6211\u544a\u8bc9\u8fc7\u60a8\uff0c\u6709\u4e00\u5929\uff0c\u90a3\u4e2a\u5730\u65b9\u5c31\u50cf\u4f0a\u7538\u56ed\u4e00\u6837\uff0c\u60a8\u53ea\u80fd\u770b\u7740\u5e76\u7167\u987e\u60a8\u7684\u5c0f\u82b1\u56ed\u3002\u5144\u5f1f\u4eec\uff0c\u4f60\u50cf\u6211\u7684\u4f7f\u5f92\u4e00\u6837\uff0c\u5f53\u6211\u8981\u6c42\u4ed6\u4eec\u4fdd\u6301\u89c2\u5bdf\u65f6\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u7761\u7740\u4e86\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bf9\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u884c\u4e3a\u4e0d\u5c0f\u5fc3\uff0c\u5c0a\u91cd\u6211\u7236\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u7684\u5730\u65b9\uff0c\u6211\u8eba\u5728\u90a3\u91cc\uff0c\u6211\u6700\u5927\u7684\u5730\u65b9\u5723\u6bcd\u4eb2\u6307\u793a\u4f60\u6765\u7684\u65f6\u5019\u3002\u6709\u4e00\u5929\uff0c\u8fd9\u5c06\u662f\u60a8\u7684\u907f\u96be\u6240\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5fd8\u8bb0\u5b83\u3002\u4e3a\u6559\u7687\u548c\u6211\u7684\u6559\u4f1a\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u4eec\u6b65\u5c65\u8e52\u8dda\uff0c\u5730\u7403\u5c06\u7ee7\u7eed\u6447\u6643\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u7684\u540d\u4e49\uff0c\u6211\u6700\u5723\u7075\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u795d\u798f\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":27,"month_string":"April","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: I come to call you to follow the Divine Love.... From which comes faith, hope and charity. The words of our King and Lord Jesus Christ are not empty words, they are words of life in abundance. Listen humanity! Be attentive to the Divine Calls in the face of the constant fall of peace and freedom of the human creature. Our King and Lord Jesus Christ shows you the way to follow so that you will not fall prey to those who will confuse you and make you captives. I invite you to conversion and to look deeply into your personal deeds and actions. I see so many children of God who do not look at themselves, do not scrutinize themselves so as not to face the monster of their overgrown and excessive 'ego'. They must remain attentive so that their actions may be a blessing for their brothers and sisters and not a stop before the daily life in which the human creature has submerged, in which they do not even have a moment to unite themselves to our King and Lord Jesus Christ. I call you to repentance... I call you to pray... I call you to practice the works of mercy, so that the affairs of our King will be more familiar to you and you will deepen your love for your neighbour. Freemasonry has entered the house of God and is contaminating with its errors those who serve in the house of God, leading them to follow what is not the divine will, but the will of men. Without forgetting our King and Lord Jesus Christ and his surrender for every human creature, give thanks to our King and Lord Jesus Christ because he is good and he is mercy and justice at the same time. You are heading towards great trials, not only because of war and great deeds to the detriment of mankind, but because of the transformation of men who embrace the dangerous spiritual novelties that lead them away from God and confront them with grave trials in the faith. People of God, you will see brothers leave the faith, others will deny religion and some will be transformed into persecutors of their brothers. The famine is coming which, together with the loss of faith, will make of the human creature a servant of evil. Remain attentive, the antichrist moves on earth with freedom and maintains interference in the decisions for humanity. Let each one be a guardian of his brother so that you may continue to be faithful to the Holy Trinity. Remain in Divine Love, be merciful and faithful to our King and Lord Jesus Christ. I invite you to pray for one another in the face of the continuous wave of novelties that approach humanity and confuse you. Pray, people of God, pray that the faith may remain firm in each one of you. Pray, people of God, pray for your brothers and sisters who suffer from the oppression of communism. Pray, people of God, pray for those who will suffer from the action of serious earthquakes. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: belong to our King, do not follow false ideologies that lead you to lose your soul. Be persevering in the faith. I bless and protect you. With my sword held high I defend you if you ask for it. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.  ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owani naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Przychodz\u0119, aby wezwa\u0107 was do na\u015bladowania Boskiej Mi\u0142o\u015bci.... Z kt\u00f3rej wyp\u0142ywa wiara, nadzieja i mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107. S\u0142owa naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa nie s\u0105 pustymi s\u0142owami, s\u0105 to s\u0142owa \u017cycia w obfito\u015bci. S\u0142uchajcie ludzko\u015bci! B\u0105d\u017acie uwa\u017cni na Boskie Wezwania w obliczu ci\u0105g\u0142ego upadku pokoju i wolno\u015bci ludzkiego stworzenia. Nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus wskazuje wam drog\u0119, kt\u00f3r\u0105 macie pod\u0105\u017ca\u0107, aby\u015bcie nie padli ofiar\u0105 tych, kt\u00f3rzy was zmyl\u0105 i uczyni\u0105 niewolnikami. Zach\u0119cam was do nawr\u00f3cenia i do g\u0142\u0119bokiego spojrzenia na wasze osobiste uczynki i dzia\u0142ania. Widz\u0119 tak wiele dzieci Bo\u017cych, kt\u00f3re nie patrz\u0105 na siebie, nie analizuj\u0105 siebie, aby nie stan\u0105\u0107 przed potworem swojego przero\u015bni\u0119tego i nadmiernego \"ego\". Musz\u0105 pozosta\u0107 uwa\u017cni, aby ich czyny by\u0142y b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem dla ich braci i si\u00f3str, a nie przystankiem przed codzienno\u015bci\u0105, w kt\u00f3rej zanurzy\u0142o si\u0119 ludzkie stworzenie, w kt\u00f3rej nie maj\u0105 nawet chwili, aby zjednoczy\u0107 si\u0119 z naszym Kr\u00f3lem i Panem Jezusem Chrystusem. Wzywam was do pokuty... Wzywam was do modlitwy... Wzywam was do praktykowania uczynk\u00f3w mi\u0142osierdzia, aby sprawy naszego Kr\u00f3la by\u0142y wam bli\u017csze i aby\u015bcie pog\u0142\u0119bili mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do bli\u017aniego. Masoneria wesz\u0142a do domu Bo\u017cego i zanieczyszcza swoimi b\u0142\u0119dami tych, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0142u\u017c\u0105 w domu Bo\u017cym, prowadz\u0105c ich do pod\u0105\u017cania za tym, co nie jest wol\u0105 Bo\u017c\u0105, ale wol\u0105 ludzi. Nie zapominaj\u0105c o naszym Kr\u00f3lu i Panu Jezusie Chrystusie i jego oddaniu za ka\u017cde ludzkie stworzenie, dzi\u0119kujcie naszemu Kr\u00f3lowi i Panu Jezusowi Chrystusowi, bo jest dobry i jest Mi\u0142osierdziem i Sprawiedliwo\u015bci\u0105 jednocze\u015bnie. Zmierzacie ku wielkim pr\u00f3bom, nie tylko z powodu wojny i wielkich czyn\u00f3w na szkod\u0119 ludzko\u015bci, ale z powodu przemiany ludzi, kt\u00f3rzy przyjmuj\u0105 niebezpieczne nowo\u015bci duchowe, kt\u00f3re oddalaj\u0105 ich od Boga i stawiaj\u0105 przed ci\u0119\u017ckimi pr\u00f3bami w wierze. Ludzie Bo\u017cy, zobaczycie, jak bracia odchodz\u0105 od wiary, inni wypieraj\u0105 si\u0119 religii, a niekt\u00f3rzy przemieni\u0105 si\u0119 w prze\u015bladowc\u00f3w swoich braci. Nadchodzi g\u0142\u00f3d, kt\u00f3ry wraz z utrat\u0105 wiary uczyni z ludzkiego stworzenia s\u0142ugi z\u0142a. B\u0105d\u017acie czujni, antychryst porusza si\u0119 po ziemi z wolna i utrzymuje ingerencj\u0119 w decyzje dla ludzko\u015bci. Niech ka\u017cdy b\u0119dzie opiekunem swojego brata, aby\u015bcie nadal byli wierni Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej. Trwajcie w Bo\u017cej Mi\u0142o\u015bci, b\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142osierni i wierni naszemu Kr\u00f3lowi i Panu Jezusowi Chrystusowi. Zach\u0119cam was do modlitwy za siebie nawzajem w obliczu ci\u0105g\u0142ej fali nowo\u015bci, kt\u00f3re zbli\u017caj\u0105 si\u0119 do ludzko\u015bci i wprowadzaj\u0105 w b\u0142\u0105d. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, aby wiara pozosta\u0142a mocna w ka\u017cdym z was. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za waszych braci i siostry, kt\u00f3rzy cierpi\u0105 z powodu ucisku komunizmu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludzie Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za tych, kt\u00f3rzy b\u0119d\u0105 cierpie\u0107 z powodu dzia\u0142ania powa\u017cnych trz\u0119sie\u0144 ziemi. Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: nale\u017ccie do naszego Kr\u00f3la, nie pod\u0105\u017cajcie za fa\u0142szywymi ideologiami, kt\u00f3re prowadz\u0105 was do zatracenia duszy. B\u0105d\u017acie wytrwali w wierze. Ja was b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 i chroni\u0119. Z moim mieczem trzymanym wysoko broni\u0119 was, je\u015bli o to poprosicie. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":4,"day":30,"month_string":"April","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for having responded to My call in your hearts. Dear children, I know your hearts and I say to you: come here, to this blessed place, where I will take your hands to lift you up when you fall, I will dry your tears when you are afflicted and I will console you when you are in despair. I am here, your most tender Mother to help you and I am still here as your teacher on your path. Follow the commandments left to you and feed on the sacraments. My children, the war will advance. Pray because the drought will be great because of the lack of water. Pray for the priests and for the souls that are being lost, because unfortunately evil has entered the house of God. Now I leave you with my Motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Liebe Kinder, ich kenne deine Herzen und ich sage zu dir: Komm her, zu diesem gesegneten Ort, an dem ich deine H\u00e4nde nehmen werde, um dich zu erheben, wenn du f\u00e4llt, ich werde deine Tr\u00e4nen trocknen, wenn du betroffen bist und ich dich tr\u00f6sten, wenn Sie sind in Verzweiflung. Ich bin hier, deine z\u00e4rtlichste Mutter, die dir hilft, und ich bin immer noch hier als dein Lehrer auf deinem Weg. Befolgen Sie die Ihnen \u00fcberlassenen Gebote und ern\u00e4hren Sie sich von den Sakramenten. Meine Kinder, der Krieg wird voranschreiten. Beten Sie, weil die D\u00fcrre aufgrund des Wassermangels gro\u00dfartig sein wird. Bete f\u00fcr die Priester und f\u00fcr die Seelen, die verloren gehen, weil das B\u00f6se leider in das Haus Gottes eingetreten ist. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Queridos hijos, conozco sus corazones y les digo: ven aqu\u00ed, en este lugar bendecido, donde tomar\u00e9 mis manos para levantarme cuando caigas, te secar\u00e9 las l\u00e1grimas cuando te afecten y te consolar\u00e9 cuando est\u00e9s desesperado. Estoy aqu\u00ed, tu madre muy tierna para ayudarte y todav\u00eda estoy aqu\u00ed como maestra para tu viaje. Sigue los mandamientos que te han dejado y se alimentan de los sacramentos. Mis hijos, la guerra avanzar\u00e1. Ore porque la sequ\u00eda ser\u00e1 excelente debido al agua que desaparecer\u00e1. Ore por los sacerdotes y por las almas que se est\u00e1n perdiendo, porque desafortunadamente el mal ha entrado en la casa de Dios. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Chers enfants, je connais vos c\u0153urs et je vous dis: venez ici, \u00e0 cet endroit b\u00e9ni, o\u00f9 je prends vos mains pour vous soulever lorsque vous tomberez, je s\u00e9cherai vos larmes lorsque vous serez afflig\u00e9 et je vous consolerai quand Vous \u00eates en d\u00e9sespoir. Je suis ici, votre m\u00e8re la plus tendre pour vous aider et je suis toujours l\u00e0 en tant que professeur sur votre chemin. Suivez les commandements qui vous sont laiss\u00e9s et se nourrissez des sacrements. Mes enfants, la guerre avancera. Priez parce que la s\u00e9cheresse sera grande en raison du manque d'eau. Priez pour les pr\u00eatres et pour les \u00e2mes qui sont perdues, car malheureusement le mal est entr\u00e9 dans la maison de Dieu. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli cari, conosco i vostri cuori e vi dico: venite qui, in questo luogo Benedetto, dove Io vi prender\u00f2 le mani per rialzarvi quando cadrete, asciugher\u00f2 le vostre lacrime quando sarete afflitti e vi consoler\u00f2 quando sarete disperati. Io sono qui, vostra tenerissima Madre per aiutarvi e sono ancora qui come maestra per il vostro cammino. Seguite i comandamenti che vi sono stati lasciati e cibatevi dei sacramenti. Figli miei, la guerra avanzer\u00e0. Pregate perch\u00e9 la siccit\u00e0 sar\u00e0 grande a causa dell\u2019acqua che mancher\u00e0. Pregate per i sacerdoti e per le anime che si stanno perdendo, perch\u00e9 purtroppo il male \u00e8 entrato nella casa di Dio. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione Materna nel nome del Padre, del figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Drogie dzieci, znam wasze serca i m\u00f3wi\u0119 wam: przyjd\u017acie tutaj, do tego b\u0142ogos\u0142awionego miejsca, gdzie wezm\u0119 wasze r\u0119ce, aby was podnie\u015b\u0107, gdy upadniecie, osusz\u0119 wasze \u0142zy, gdy b\u0119dziecie utrudzeni, i pociesz\u0119 was, gdy b\u0119dziecie zrozpaczeni. Jestem tutaj, wasza najczulsza Matka, aby wam pom\u00f3c i nadal jestem tutaj jako wasz nauczyciel na waszej drodze. Post\u0119pujcie zgodnie z przykazaniami, kt\u00f3re zosta\u0142y wam pozostawione, i karmcie si\u0119 sakramentami. Moje dzieci, wojna b\u0119dzie post\u0119powa\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, poniewa\u017c susza b\u0119dzie wielka z powodu braku wody. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za kap\u0142an\u00f3w i za dusze, kt\u00f3re s\u0105 gubione, bo niestety z\u0142o wesz\u0142o do domu Bo\u017cego. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por terem respondido \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Caros filhos, eu conhe\u00e7o seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e digo a voc\u00ea: Venha aqui, para este lugar aben\u00e7oado, onde vou levar suas m\u00e3os para levant\u00e1 -lo quando voc\u00ea cair, eu vou secar suas l\u00e1grimas quando estiver afligido e eu o consolarei quando Voc\u00ea est\u00e1 em desespero. Estou aqui, sua m\u00e3e mais terna para ajud\u00e1 -lo e ainda estou aqui como seu professor no seu caminho. Siga os mandamentos deixados para voc\u00ea e alimente -se dos sacramentos. Meus filhos, a guerra avan\u00e7ar\u00e1. Ore porque a seca ser\u00e1 grande por causa da falta de \u00e1gua. Ore pelos padres e pelas almas que est\u00e3o sendo perdidas, porque infelizmente o mal entrou na Casa de Deus. Agora deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u77e5\u9053\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u6211\u5bf9\u4f60\u8bf4\uff1a\u6765\u8fd9\u91cc\uff0c\u6765\u5230\u8fd9\u4e2a\u6709\u798f\u7684\u5730\u65b9\uff0c\u5f53\u4f60\u8dcc\u5012\u65f6\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u63e1\u4f4f\u4f60\u7684\u624b\u6765\u62ac\u8d77\u4f60\uff0c\u5f53\u4f60\u906d\u53d7\u6298\u78e8\u65f6\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u5e72\u4f60\u7684\u773c\u6cea\u4f60\u611f\u5230\u7edd\u671b\u3002\u6211\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\uff0c\u60a8\u6700\u6e29\u67d4\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u53ef\u4ee5\u5e2e\u52a9\u60a8\uff0c\u800c\u6211\u4ecd\u7136\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u9053\u8def\u4e0a\u4f5c\u4e3a\u60a8\u7684\u8001\u5e08\u3002\u9075\u5faa\u7559\u7ed9\u60a8\u7684\u8beb\u547d\uff0c\u4ee5\u5723\u793c\u4e3a\u98df\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6218\u4e89\u5c06\u524d\u8fdb\u3002\u7948\u7977\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5e72\u65f1\u4f1a\u56e0\u4e3a\u7f3a\u6c34\u800c\u53d8\u5f97\u5de8\u5927\u3002\u4e3a\u796d\u53f8\u548c\u6b63\u5728\u4e22\u5931\u7684\u7075\u9b42\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4e0d\u5e78\u7684\u662f\uff0c\u90aa\u6076\u8fdb\u5165\u4e86\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u5c4b\u5b50\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7ed9\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":1,"month_string":"May","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart: I bless you as Queen and Mother. I bless your minds, thoughts and hearts. I bless you with my love so that as children of my Divine Son you would be obedient to his call. My little children: you must hasten and be more spiritual. The times are urgent; evil does not wait and is drawing up its plans for dominating my children. Fear not: this mother keeps you protected and my mantle embraces humanity. Little children, the power of communism is making itself felt on earth; its desire for conquest goes beyond a single country. I suffer due to the ignorance of those who deny the times in which they are living: war will spread and hunger will appear, faced with which the human race will forget its principles. The dragon is showing its tentacles: pestilence, war, famine and dominion over humanity, eliminating religions to establish one single religion. People of my Son, keep your lamps burning with the finest oil. Some people continue to be foolish without taking stock of the reality through which humanity is passing. Foolish children! You do not know the prophecies contained in Sacred Scripture. If you knew them, you would understand the times in which you find yourselves and the signs and signals of this moment. Everything is found in Sacred Scripture, yet humanity no longer believes in the most Holy Trinity, scorns me and denies being God's workmanship. Children, you treat the fact that the firmament is warning you as a spectacle... The moon will turn red and with it human suffering and pain will increase. Pray, cry out and fast if your health allows it. Repent and confess your sins with a firm purpose of amendment. Walk towards my Son, present in the holy Eucharist, and set out on your path towards a new life as true children of my Son. Enter into inner silence and look at yourselves, being severe - very severe, without disguising your personal acts and actions: look at yourselves in terms of your character, your treatment of your fellow men, anger, resentment, lack of love for yourselves and for your neighbour. Look at yourselves! Change must happen at this moment. You must soften your hearts of stone before it is too late. You are heading towards difficult times for all humanity. I offer you my hands to guide you to my Son, my heart to shelter you and my womb so that you might grow within it. Pray, children, pray: those who hold power on earth are leading humanity into pain. Pray, children, pray, the earth will shake forcefully. Pray, children, pray for the church of my Son. Beloved children, people of my Son, pray. I grieve for my children who do not obey. I grieve for Europe, which will suffer unexpectedly. In this month dedicated to this mother who loves you, I ask you for the communion of reparation on Saturdays and Sundays offered for the conversion of all men, for world peace, for my favoured sons, so that they may maintain the people of my Son as a community of love and fraternity. You should offer this in a state of grace and with firm faith. By fulfilling my requests, you will receive the grace to increase your faith in my Divine Son and you will have greater protection from the heavenly legions. Maintain unity. I bless you, my children. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca: B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was jako Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 wasze umys\u0142y, my\u015bli i serca. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, aby\u015bcie jako dzieci mojego Boskiego Syna byli pos\u0142uszni Jego wezwaniu. Moje ma\u0142e dzieci: musicie si\u0119 spieszy\u0107 i by\u0107 bardziej duchowymi. Czasy s\u0105 nagl\u0105ce, z\u0142o nie czeka i przygotowuje swoje plany panowania nad moimi dzie\u0107mi. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119: ta Matka was chroni, a m\u00f3j p\u0142aszcz otacza ludzko\u015b\u0107. Ma\u0142e dzieci, si\u0142a komunizmu daje o sobie zna\u0107 na ziemi, jego pragnienie podboju wykracza poza jeden kraj. Cierpi\u0119 z powodu ignorancji tych, kt\u00f3rzy zaprzeczaj\u0105 czasom, w kt\u00f3rych \u017cyj\u0105: rozprzestrzeni si\u0119 wojna i pojawi si\u0119 g\u0142\u00f3d, wobec kt\u00f3rego ludzko\u015b\u0107 zapomni o swoich zasadach. Smok pokazuje swoje macki: zaraza, wojna, g\u0142\u00f3d i panowanie nad ludzko\u015bci\u0105, eliminuj\u0105c religie, aby ustanowi\u0107 jedn\u0105 jedyn\u0105 religi\u0119. Ludzie mojego Syna, utrzymujcie wasze lampy p\u0142on\u0105ce z najlepsz\u0105 oliw\u0105. Niekt\u00f3rzy ludzie nadal pozostaj\u0105 g\u0142upi, nie dokonuj\u0105c bilansu rzeczywisto\u015bci, przez kt\u00f3r\u0105 przechodzi ludzko\u015b\u0107. G\u0142upie dzieci! Nie znacie proroctw zawartych w Pi\u015bmie \u015awi\u0119tym. Gdyby\u015bcie je znali, zrozumieliby\u015bcie czasy, w kt\u00f3rych si\u0119 znajdujecie oraz znaki i sygna\u0142y tej chwili. Wszystko znajduje si\u0119 w Pi\u015bmie \u015awi\u0119tym, a jednak ludzko\u015b\u0107 nie wierzy ju\u017c w Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105, wyszydza Mnie i zaprzecza, \u017ce jest dzie\u0142em Bo\u017cym. Dzieci, to, \u017ce firmament was ostrzega, traktujecie jako widowisko... Ksi\u0119\u017cyc stanie si\u0119 czerwony, a wraz z nim wzro\u015bnie ludzkie cierpienie i b\u00f3l. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, wo\u0142ajcie i po\u015b\u0107cie, je\u015bli zdrowie na to pozwala. \u017ba\u0142ujcie i wyznajcie swoje grzechy z mocnym celem poprawy. Id\u017acie w kierunku mojego Syna, obecnego w \u015bwi\u0119tej Eucharystii, i wyruszcie w drog\u0119 ku nowemu \u017cyciu jako prawdziwe dzieci mojego Syna. Wejd\u017acie w wewn\u0119trzne milczenie i sp\u00f3jrzcie na siebie, b\u0119d\u0105c surowymi - bardzo surowymi, nie ukrywaj\u0105c waszych osobistych czyn\u00f3w i dzia\u0142a\u0144: sp\u00f3jrzcie na siebie pod wzgl\u0119dem waszego charakteru, waszego traktowania bli\u017anich, gniewu, urazy, braku mi\u0142o\u015bci do siebie i do bli\u017aniego. Sp\u00f3jrzcie na siebie! Zmiana musi nast\u0105pi\u0107 w tej chwili. Musicie zmi\u0119kczy\u0107 swoje kamienne serca, zanim b\u0119dzie za p\u00f3\u017ano. Zmierzacie do trudnych czas\u00f3w dla ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci. Ofiaruj\u0119 wam moje r\u0119ce, aby prowadzi\u0142y was do mojego Syna, moje serce, aby was chroni\u0142o i moje \u0142ono, aby\u015bcie mogli w nim wzrasta\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: ci, kt\u00f3rzy sprawuj\u0105 w\u0142adz\u0119 na ziemi, prowadz\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107 do b\u00f3lu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: ziemia zatrz\u0119sie si\u0119 z moc\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 mojego Syna. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, ludu mojego Syna, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. Bolej\u0119 nad moimi dzie\u0107mi, kt\u00f3re nie s\u0105 pos\u0142uszne. Bolej\u0119 nad Europ\u0105, kt\u00f3ra niespodziewanie ucierpi. W tym miesi\u0105cu po\u015bwi\u0119conym tej kochaj\u0105cej was Matce prosz\u0119 was o Komuni\u0119 \u015bw. wynagradzaj\u0105c\u0105 w soboty i niedziele ofiarowan\u0105 za nawr\u00f3cenie wszystkich ludzi, za pok\u00f3j na \u015bwiecie, za moich ulubionych syn\u00f3w, aby utrzymywali lud mojego Syna jako wsp\u00f3lnot\u0119 mi\u0142o\u015bci i braterstwa. Powinni\u015bcie to ofiarowa\u0107 w stanie \u0142aski i z mocn\u0105 wiar\u0105. Spe\u0142niaj\u0105c moje pro\u015bby, otrzymacie \u0142ask\u0119 zwi\u0119kszenia wiary w mojego Boskiego Syna i b\u0119dziecie mieli wi\u0119ksz\u0105 ochron\u0119 ze strony legion\u00f3w niebieskich. Zachowajcie jedno\u015b\u0107. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, moje dzieci. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":3,"month_string":"May","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for having responded to my call in your hearts. Beloved children, how much tenderness my Mother's heart feels when I see my children kneeling with great faith. My children, soon you will witness the Warning, the meeting with my Jesus who loves you so much; await this gesture of mercy, but not with fear, but with joy. Beloved children, go to confession so that you will be ready for when He comes; always be vigilant, my children, I love you and I want to guide you like a mother. My children, pray for the Church and especially for the bishops, cardinals and priests, so that they may abandon all pride and begin to proclaim the word of God, so that they may no longer deal with politics, but like Peter, be fishers of souls. Now I give you my Motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Geliebte Kinder, wie viel Z\u00e4rtlichkeit f\u00fchlt sich das Herz meiner Mutter an, wenn ich sehe, dass meine Kinder vor gro\u00dfem Glauben knien. Meine Kinder, bald werden Sie die Warnung miterleben, das Treffen mit meinem Jesus, der Sie so sehr liebt. Warten Sie auf diese Geste der Barmherzigkeit, aber nicht mit Angst, sondern mit Freude. Geliebte Kinder, gehen Sie zum Gest\u00e4ndnis, damit Sie bereit sind, wenn er kommt; Sei immer wachsam, meine Kinder, ich liebe dich und ich m\u00f6chte dich wie eine Mutter f\u00fchren. Meine Kinder beten f\u00fcr die Kirche und besonders f\u00fcr die Bisch\u00f6fe, Kardin\u00e4le und Priester, damit sie alle Stolz aufgeben und anfangen, das Wort Gottes zu verk\u00fcnden, damit sie sich nicht mehr mit Politik befassen, sondern wie Peter Fischer von Seifischer Seelen. Jetzt gebe ich dir meinen m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Amados a los ni\u00f1os, cu\u00e1nta ternura siente a mi madre como madre, cuando veo a mis hijos que doblan las rodillas con gran fe. Hijos, pronto testificar\u00e1n la advertencia, el encuentro con mi Jes\u00fas que te ama tanto, espera este gesto de misericordia, pero no con miedo, sino con alegr\u00eda. Amados a los ni\u00f1os, confesar que te encuentres listo para cuando venga, siempre mira a los ni\u00f1os, te amo y quiero guiarte como una madre, grande estar\u00e1 sufriendo para aquellos que no quieren reconocer a Dios. Mis hijos, rezan por los Iglesia y, sobre todo, para los obispos, cardenales y sacerdotes, de modo que abandonen todo orgullo y comiencen a proclamar la Palabra de Dios, para que ya no traten con la pol\u00edtica, pero como Peter, son pescadores de almas. Ahora te doy mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, combien ressent le c\u0153ur de ma m\u00e8re quand je vois mes enfants \u00e0 genoux avec une grande foi. Mes enfants, vous assisteront bient\u00f4t \u00e0 l'avertissement, \u00e0 la rencontre avec mon J\u00e9sus qui vous aime tant; Attendez ce geste de mis\u00e9ricorde, mais pas de peur, mais de joie. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, allez-y pour vous \u00eatre pr\u00eats \u00e0 \u00eatre pr\u00eats \u00e0 quand il viendra; Soyez toujours vigilant, mes enfants, je t'aime et je veux te guider comme une m\u00e8re. Mes enfants, prient pour l'\u00e9glise et surtout pour les \u00e9v\u00eaques, les cardinaux et les pr\u00eatres, afin qu'ils puissent abandonner toute fiert\u00e9 et commencer \u00e0 proclamer la parole de Dieu, afin qu'ils ne s'occupent plus de la politique, mais comme Peter, soyez p\u00eacheurs de \u00e2mes. Maintenant, je vous donne ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli amati, quanta tenerezza sente il mio cuore di Madre, quando vedo i miei bambini che piegano le ginocchia con grande fede. Figli, presto assisterete all\u2019avvertimento, all\u2019incontro con il mio Ges\u00f9 che tanto vi ama, attendete questo gesto di misericordia, ma non con paura, ma con gioia. Figli amati, confessatevi per trovarvi pronti per quando Lui verr\u00e0, vegliate sempre figli, Io vi amo e voglio guidarvi come una Madre, grande sar\u00e0 la sofferenza per coloro che non vogliono riconoscere Dio. Figli miei, pregate per la Chiesa e soprattutto per i vescovi, cardinali e sacerdoti, affinch\u00e9 abbandonino ogni orgoglio e inizino a proclamare la parola di Dio, affinch\u00e9 non si occupino pi\u00f9 di politica, ma come Pietro, siano pescatori di anime. Ora vi do la mia benedizione Materna nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, ile\u017c czu\u0142o\u015bci czuje moje matczyne serce, gdy widz\u0119, jak moje dzieci kl\u0119kaj\u0105 z wielk\u0105 wiar\u0105. Dzieci moje, wkr\u00f3tce b\u0119dziecie \u015bwiadkami Ostrze\u017cenia - spotkania z moim Jezusem, kt\u00f3ry tak bardzo was kocha; oczekujcie na ten gest mi\u0142osierdzia, ale nie z l\u0119kiem, lecz z rado\u015bci\u0105. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, id\u017acie do spowiedzi, aby\u015bcie byli gotowi na Jego przyj\u015bcie; b\u0105d\u017acie zawsze czujni, moje dzieci, kocham was i chc\u0119 was prowadzi\u0107 jak matka; wielkie b\u0119dzie cierpienie tych, kt\u00f3rzy nie chc\u0105 uzna\u0107 Boga. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, a szczeg\u00f3lnie za biskup\u00f3w, kardyna\u0142\u00f3w i kap\u0142an\u00f3w, aby porzucili wszelk\u0105 pych\u0119 i zacz\u0119li g\u0142osi\u0107 s\u0142owo Bo\u017ce, aby nie zajmowali si\u0119 ju\u017c polityk\u0105, ale jak Piotr byli rybakami dusz. Teraz udzielam wam mojego matczynego b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwa w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por terem respondido \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Filhos amados, quanta ternura sente o cora\u00e7\u00e3o de minha m\u00e3e quando vejo meus filhos ajoelhados com grande f\u00e9. Meus filhos, em breve voc\u00ea testemunhar\u00e1 o aviso, a reuni\u00e3o com meu Jesus que te ama tanto; Aguarde esse gesto de miseric\u00f3rdia, mas n\u00e3o com medo, mas com alegria. Crian\u00e7as amadas, v\u00e3o confiss\u00e3o para que voc\u00ea esteja pronto para quando ele vier; Sempre esteja vigilante, meus filhos, eu te amo e quero gui\u00e1 -lo como uma m\u00e3e. Meus filhos, oram pela igreja e especialmente pelos bispos, cardeais e padres, para que possam abandonar todo orgulho e come\u00e7ar a proclamar a Palavra de Deus, para que n\u00e3o lidem mais com a pol\u00edtica, mas como Pedro, sejam pescadores de almas. Agora eu te dou minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5f53\u6211\u770b\u5230\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u8dea\u4e0b\u65f6\uff0c\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u5fc3\u611f\u89c9\u5230\u4e86\u591a\u5c11\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5f88\u5feb\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u76ee\u7779\u4e0e\u6211\u5982\u6b64\u7231\u4f60\u7684\u8036\u7a23\u4f1a\u9762\u7684\u8b66\u544a\uff1b\u7b49\u5f85\u7740\u8fd9\u79cd\u601c\u60af\u7684\u624b\u52bf\uff0c\u4f46\u4e0d\u662f\u6050\u60e7\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u5145\u6ee1\u559c\u60a6\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u53bb\u4f9b\u8ba4\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u60a8\u5728\u4ed6\u6765\u65f6\u505a\u597d\u51c6\u5907\u3002\u6c38\u8fdc\u4fdd\u6301\u8b66\u60d5\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u7231\u4f60\uff0c\u6211\u60f3\u50cf\u5988\u5988\u4e00\u6837\u6307\u5bfc\u4f60\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5c24\u5176\u662f\u4e3a\u4e3b\u6559\uff0c\u7ea2\u8863\u4e3b\u6559\u548c\u796d\u53f8\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u4ed6\u4eec\u53ef\u4ee5\u653e\u5f03\u6240\u6709\u7684\u81ea\u8c6a\u611f\u5e76\u5f00\u59cb\u5ba3\u626c\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u9053\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e0d\u518d\u5904\u7406\u653f\u6cbb\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u50cf\u5f7c\u5f97\u4e00\u6837\u7075\u9b42\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7ed9\u4f60\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":6,"month_string":"May","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear daughter, thank you for welcoming Me into your heart. You need never fear, for when you proclaim the Holy Word, I will be with you. The Church, today, has put up walls between my Son and true doctrine and despite the suffering it is causing to the Blessed and Most Sacred Heart of Jesus, He is there to protect it. The Church, instead of feeding my children, with the body and blood of Jesus, has alienated His presence and despite this, He is always ready to offer His help. Repent! My daughter, Freemasonry and their extravagant evil force, have alienated the representatives of the Church from the true Christian faith, insulting the body of Jesus, offering it in a wrong way and forcing my children not to kneel and receive it on their hands, proclaiming a great lie. I ask you: return to the true faith and allow me to help you in the dark moments that will come. I tell you: the true Church will be reborn and will be greater and more luxuriant. Now, I advise you to pray, for your time is coming to an end. I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Tochter, danke, dass du mich in deinem Herzen willkommen gehei\u00dfen hast. Du brauchst niemals Angst, denn wenn du das heilige Wort verk\u00fcndet hast, werde ich bei dir sein. Die Kirche hat heute Mauern zwischen meinem Sohn und der wahren Lehre aufgebracht, und trotz des Leidens, das sie f\u00fcr das gesegnete und heiligste Herz Jesu verursacht, ist er da, um sie zu sch\u00fctzen. Die Kirche hat, anstatt meine Kinder mit dem K\u00f6rper und dem Blut Jesu zu ern\u00e4hren, seine Anwesenheit entfremdet und trotzdem ist er immer bereit, seine Hilfe anzubieten. Bereuen! Meine Tochter, Freimaurerei und ihre extravagante b\u00f6se Kraft, haben die Vertreter der Kirche vom wahren christlichen Glauben entfremdet, den K\u00f6rper Jesu beleidigt, sie falsch anbot und meine Kinder zwingt, nicht zu knien und sie an ihren H\u00e4nden zu empfangen, zu verk\u00fcnden Eine gro\u00dfe L\u00fcge. Ich frage Sie: Kehre zum wahren Glauben zur\u00fcck und erlaube mir, dir in den dunklen Momenten zu helfen, die kommen werden. Ich sage Ihnen: Die wahre Kirche wird wiedergeboren und wird gr\u00f6\u00dfer und \u00fcppiger. Jetzt rate ich Ihnen, zu beten, denn Ihre Zeit geht zu Ende. Ich segne dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Querida hija, gracias por darme la bienvenida en tu coraz\u00f3n. Nunca tienes que temer, porque cuando proclames la Santa Palabra, estar\u00e9 contigo. La iglesia, hoy, ha levantado muros entre mi hijo y la verdadera doctrina y, a pesar del sufrimiento que est\u00e1 causando el bendito y muy sagrado coraz\u00f3n de Jes\u00fas, \u00e9l est\u00e1 all\u00ed para protegerlo. La iglesia, en lugar de alimentar a mis hijos, del cuerpo y la sangre de Jes\u00fas, ha alejado su presencia y, a pesar de esto, siempre est\u00e1 listo para ofrecer su ayuda. \u00a1Arrepentirse! Mi hija, la masoner\u00eda y su extravagante fuerza malvada, han eliminado a los representantes de la iglesia con una verdadera fe cristiana, insultando el cuerpo de Jes\u00fas, ofreci\u00e9ndolo incorrectamente y obligando a mis hijos a arrodillarse y recibirla en las manos, proclamando una gran mentira . Te pregunto: Vuelve a la verdadera fe y perm\u00edtame ayudarte en los momentos oscuros que vendr\u00e1n. Te digo: la verdadera iglesia renacer\u00e1 y ser\u00e1 m\u00e1s grande y m\u00e1s exuberante. Ahora, le aconsejo que ore, porque el tiempo disponible llega al final. Te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n","text_fr":"Ch\u00e8re fille, merci de m'avoir accueilli dans votre c\u0153ur. Vous n'avez jamais besoin de craindre, car lorsque vous proclamez la Sainte Parole, je serai avec vous. L'\u00c9glise, aujourd'hui, a mis des murs entre mon fils et la vraie doctrine et malgr\u00e9 la souffrance, cela fait au c\u0153ur b\u00e9ni et le plus sacr\u00e9 de J\u00e9sus, il est l\u00e0 pour le prot\u00e9ger. L'\u00e9glise, au lieu de nourrir mes enfants, avec le corps et le sang de J\u00e9sus, a ali\u00e9n\u00e9 sa pr\u00e9sence et malgr\u00e9 cela, il est toujours pr\u00eat \u00e0 offrir son aide. Se repentir! Ma fille, la franc-ma\u00e7onnerie et leur force mal\u00e9fique extravagante, ont ali\u00e9n\u00e9 les repr\u00e9sentants de l'\u00c9glise de la vraie foi chr\u00e9tienne, insultant le corps de J\u00e9sus, l'offrant de mauvaise mani\u00e8re et for\u00e7ant mes enfants \u00e0 ne pas s'agenouiller et \u00e0 le recevoir sur leurs mains, proclamant un grand mensonge. Je vous demande: retourner \u00e0 la vraie foi et me permettre de vous aider dans les moments sombres qui viendront. Je vous le dis: la vraie \u00e9glise rena\u00eetra et sera plus grande et plus luxuriante. Maintenant, je vous conseille de prier, pour votre temps, vous termine. Je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cara figlia, grazie per avermi accolta nel tuo cuore. Non devi mai temere, perch\u00e9 quando tu proclami la Santa Parola, Io sar\u00f2 con te. La Chiesa, oggi, ha alzato muri tra mio Figlio e la vera dottrina e nonostante la sofferenza che sta causando al Benedetto e Sacratissimo cuore di Ges\u00f9, Lui \u00e8 l\u00ec a proteggerla. La Chiesa, invece di cibare i miei figli, del corpo e sangue di Ges\u00f9, ha alienato la sua presenza e nonostante questo, Lui \u00e8 sempre pronto ad offrire il Suo aiuto. Pentitevi! Figlia mia, la massoneria e la loro stravagante forza malvagia, hanno allontanato i rappresentanti della Chiesa dalla vera fede cristiana, insultando il corpo di Ges\u00f9, offrendolo in maniera errata e costringendo i miei figli a non inginocchiarsi ed a riceverlo sulle mani, proclamando una grande menzogna. Vi chiedo: tornate alla vera fede e permettetemi di aiutarvi nei momenti tenebrosi che arriveranno. Vi dico: la vera Chiesa rinascer\u00e0 e sar\u00e0 pi\u00f9 grande e rigogliosa. Ora, vi consiglio di pregare, perch\u00e9 il tempo a disposizione giunge alla fine. Vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen","text_pl":"Droga c\u00f3rko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce przyj\u0119\u0142a\u015b mnie do swojego serca. Nie musicie si\u0119 l\u0119ka\u0107, bo gdy b\u0119dziecie g\u0142osi\u0107 S\u0142owo Bo\u017ce, Ja b\u0119d\u0119 z wami. Dzisiejszy Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 postawi\u0142 mury mi\u0119dzy moim Synem a prawdziw\u0105 nauk\u0105 i pomimo cierpienia, jakie sprawia Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszemu Sercu Jezusa, On jest tam, aby go chroni\u0107. Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, zamiast karmi\u0107 moje dzieci Cia\u0142em i Krwi\u0105 Jezusa, odsun\u0105\u0142 od siebie Jego obecno\u015b\u0107, a mimo to jest On zawsze gotowy, by ofiarowa\u0107 swoj\u0105 pomoc. Nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119! Moja c\u00f3rko, masoneria i jej pozaziemskie si\u0142y z\u0142a oderwa\u0142y przedstawicieli Ko\u015bcio\u0142a od prawdziwej wiary chrze\u015bcija\u0144skiej, zniewa\u017caj\u0105c Cia\u0142o Jezusa, ofiarowuj\u0105c je w niew\u0142a\u015bciwy spos\u00f3b i zmuszaj\u0105c moje dzieci, aby nie kl\u0119ka\u0142y i przyjmowa\u0142y go na d\u0142o\u0144, g\u0142osz\u0105c wielkie k\u0142amstwo. Prosz\u0119 was: powr\u00f3\u0107cie do prawdziwej wiary i pozw\u00f3lcie mi pom\u00f3c wam w mrocznych chwilach, kt\u00f3re nadejd\u0105. M\u00f3wi\u0119 wam: prawdziwy Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 odrodzi si\u0119 i b\u0119dzie wi\u0119kszy i wspanialszy. Teraz zalecam wam modlitw\u0119, bo czas si\u0119 ko\u0144czy. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Querida filha, obrigado por me receber em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Voc\u00ea n\u00e3o precisa ter medo, pois quando proclamar a Palavra Santa, estarei com voc\u00ea. A Igreja, hoje, colocou paredes entre meu filho e a verdadeira doutrina e, apesar do sofrimento que est\u00e1 causando ao cora\u00e7\u00e3o aben\u00e7oado e mais sagrado de Jesus, ele est\u00e1 l\u00e1 para proteg\u00ea -lo. A igreja, em vez de alimentar meus filhos, com o corpo e o sangue de Jesus, alienou sua presen\u00e7a e, apesar disso, ele est\u00e1 sempre pronto para oferecer sua ajuda. Arrepender-se! Minha filha, Ma\u00e7onaria e sua for\u00e7a maligna extravagante, alienaram os representantes da Igreja da verdadeira f\u00e9 crist\u00e3, insultando o corpo de Jesus, oferecendo -o de uma maneira errada e for\u00e7ando meus filhos a n\u00e3o se ajoelhar e receber em suas m\u00e3os, proclamando uma \u00f3tima mentira. Pe\u00e7o -lhe: volte \u00e0 verdadeira f\u00e9 e me permita ajud\u00e1 -lo nos momentos sombrios que vir\u00e3o. Eu lhe digo: a verdadeira igreja ser\u00e1 renascido e ser\u00e1 maior e mais luxuriante. Agora, aconselho voc\u00ea a orar, pois seu tempo est\u00e1 chegando ao fim. Eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u6b22\u8fce\u6211\u8fdb\u5165\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u3002\u60a8\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u5fc5\u62c5\u5fc3\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5f53\u60a8\u5ba3\u544a\u5723\u8a00\u65f6\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u548c\u60a8\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u3002\u4eca\u5929\uff0c\u6559\u4f1a\u5df2\u7ecf\u5728\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u6559\u4e49\u4e4b\u95f4\u94fa\u8bbe\u4e86\u5899\uff0c\u5c3d\u7ba1\u8036\u7a23\u662f\u6709\u798f\u548c\u6700\u795e\u5723\u7684\u5fc3\u9020\u6210\u7684\u82e6\u96be\uff0c\u4f46\u4ed6\u4ecd\u5728\u90a3\u91cc\u4fdd\u62a4\u5b83\u3002\u6559\u4f1a\u6ca1\u6709\u7528\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u8eab\u4f53\u548c\u9c9c\u8840\u5582\u517b\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u758f\u8fdc\u4e86\u4ed6\u7684\u540c\u5728\uff0c\u5c3d\u7ba1\u5982\u6b64\uff0c\u4ed6\u603b\u662f\u51c6\u5907\u63d0\u4f9b\u5e2e\u52a9\u3002\u6094\u6539\uff01\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\u5171\u6d4e\u4f1a\u53ca\u5176\u5962\u4f88\u7684\u90aa\u6076\u529b\u91cf\u4f7f\u6559\u4f1a\u7684\u4ee3\u8868\u4e0e\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u57fa\u7763\u6559\u4fe1\u4ef0\u758f\u8fdc\u4e86\uff0c\u4fae\u8fb1\u4e86\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u8eab\u4f53\uff0c\u4ee5\u9519\u8bef\u7684\u65b9\u5f0f\u63d0\u4f9b\u4e86\u5b83\uff0c\u5e76\u8feb\u4f7f\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u4e0d\u8dea\u4e0b\u5e76\u63a5\u53d7\u5b83\uff0c\u5ba3\u5e03\u4e00\u4e2a\u4f1f\u5927\u7684\u8c0e\u8a00\u3002\u6211\u95ee\u4f60\uff1a\u56de\u5230\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\uff0c\u8ba9\u6211\u5728\u5373\u5c06\u5230\u6765\u7684\u9ed1\u6697\u65f6\u523b\u4e3a\u60a8\u63d0\u4f9b\u5e2e\u52a9\u3002\u6211\u544a\u8bc9\u4f60\uff1a\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u6559\u4f1a\u5c06\u91cd\u751f\uff0c\u5e76\u4e14\u4f1a\u66f4\u52a0\u66f4\u5927\uff0c\u66f4\u8302\u76db\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u5efa\u8bae\u60a8\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u60a8\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\u5373\u5c06\u7ed3\u675f\u3002\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":7,"month_string":"May","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: by Divine Mandate, as prince of the heavenly legions I share with you that humanity must be attentive at this time. Not living in the truth, human beings are rising up against one another\u2026 humanity is besieged, oppressed, disturbed and repressed so that inconstancy and insecurity penetrate its thinking, and it is therefore surrendering to the conditions that will lead it to acclaim the antichrist. Human beings\u2019 conceited ego leads them to feel that they alone possess reason. Seized by demons, human beings impose themselves and trample their brothers and sisters without compassion. Humanity is approaching perdition to the point of becoming tarnished, with people being indistinguishable from one another. Contrary to expectations, the great obligation will arrive and timid humanity will bow down and submit. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: go forward in obedience, without wasting this moment. Convert, pray, offer sacrifices and fast, if your condition allows it. Make reparation in advance; the Church of our King is being invaded by the forces of evil in order to undermine her, causing the mystical body to fall into unbelief. Among the people of our king charity has ceased to exist. The progression of imposition by force and the hold of the powerful over the people of God are growing ever stronger, negating your freedom. 'He who has ears to hear let him hear\u201d. Remain on constant alert. The mark of evil will be unmasked; humanity will be summoned in order for it to be 'sealed\u201d. Do not lose eternal life, children of God, do not lose it. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, you must nurture faith in order to resist spiritually in the face of the empire of evil. The power of the devil is looming over humanity so that it would surrender into his hands. Strengthen your faith with fraternal love above all. Be peaceful people: this is how Christians are recognized, in fraternal love. Pray, people of God, pray: the bear is causing pain, great pain. Pray, people of God: the dragon is moving stealthily in order to awaken with power before the eyes of humanity. Pray, people of God, pray: the earth is in peril and unbelieving humanity scorns what is sacred. The man of God remains vigilant. The earth will shake, the reddish moon announces the proximity of pain and of the Warning. In the midst of unbelief, my legions seek creatures of firm faith who remain in prayer for humanity - souls of reparation for offenses against the Sacred Hearts. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: with my sword I defend you against danger. Be faithful to the most Holy Trinity. Love our Queen and Mother of the End Times, when the Warning is rapidly approaching. Onward - I defend you against evil and my legions keep you from danger. Be true. Do not be afraid: we are your defenders and companions on the way. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: z Boskiego mandatu, jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 legion\u00f3w niebieskich dziel\u0119 si\u0119 z wami tym, \u017ce ludzko\u015b\u0107 musi by\u0107 w tym czasie uwa\u017cna. Nie \u017cyj\u0105c w prawdzie, ludzie powstaj\u0105 przeciwko sobie... ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest obl\u0119\u017cona, uciskana, niepokojona i represjonowana, tak \u017ce niesta\u0142o\u015b\u0107 i niepewno\u015b\u0107 przenikaj\u0105 do jej my\u015blenia, dlatego poddaje si\u0119 warunkom, kt\u00f3re doprowadz\u0105 j\u0105 do uznania antychrysta. Zarozumia\u0142e ego cz\u0142owieka prowadzi go do przekonania, \u017ce tylko on posiada rozum. Zaw\u0142adni\u0119ci przez demony, ludzie narzucaj\u0105 si\u0119 i depcz\u0105 swoich braci i siostry bez wsp\u00f3\u0142czucia. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 zbli\u017ca si\u0119 do zguby, a\u017c do zepsucia, a ludzie staj\u0105 si\u0119 nie do odr\u00f3\u017cnienia od siebie. Wbrew oczekiwaniom nadejdzie wielki obowi\u0105zek, a p\u0142ochliwa ludzko\u015b\u0107 ukorzy si\u0119 i podporz\u0105dkuje. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: id\u017a naprz\u00f3d w pos\u0142usze\u0144stwie, nie marnuj\u0105c tej chwili. Nawracajcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, sk\u0142adajcie ofiary i po\u015b\u0107cie, je\u015bli wasz stan na to pozwala.  Czy\u0144cie zawczasu zado\u015b\u0107uczynienie; Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 naszego Kr\u00f3la jest naje\u017cd\u017cany przez si\u0142y z\u0142a, aby go os\u0142abi\u0107, powoduj\u0105c, \u017ce cia\u0142o mistyczne popada w niewiar\u0119. W\u015br\u00f3d ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la dobroczynno\u015b\u0107 przesta\u0142a istnie\u0107. Post\u0119p narzucania si\u0142\u0105 i panowanie pot\u0119\u017cnych nad ludem Bo\u017cym s\u0105 coraz silniejsze, neguj\u0105c wasz\u0105 wolno\u015b\u0107. \"Kto ma uszy do s\u0142uchania, niechaj s\u0142ucha\". Pozosta\u0144cie w ci\u0105g\u0142ej czujno\u015bci. Znak z\u0142a zostanie zdemaskowany; ludzko\u015b\u0107 zostanie wezwana, aby mog\u0142a zosta\u0107 \"zapiecz\u0119towana\". Nie tra\u0107cie \u017cycia wiecznego, dzieci Bo\u017ce, nie tra\u0107cie go. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, musisz piel\u0119gnowa\u0107 wiar\u0119, aby stawia\u0107 duchowy op\u00f3r w obliczu imperium z\u0142a. Moc diab\u0142a unosi si\u0119 nad ludzko\u015bci\u0105, aby podda\u0142a si\u0119 w jego r\u0119ce. Umacniajcie wasz\u0105 wiar\u0119 przede wszystkim mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 bratersk\u0105. B\u0105d\u017acie lud\u017ami pokoju: tak rozpoznaje si\u0119 chrze\u015bcijan, w mi\u0142o\u015bci braterskiej. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: nied\u017awied\u017a sprawia b\u00f3l, wielki b\u00f3l. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy: smok porusza si\u0119 ukradkiem, aby obudzi\u0107 si\u0119 z moc\u0105 na oczach ludzko\u015bci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: ziemia jest w niebezpiecze\u0144stwie, a niewierz\u0105ca ludzko\u015b\u0107 gardzi tym, co \u015bwi\u0119te. Cz\u0142owiek Bo\u017cy pozostaje czujny. Ziemia si\u0119 zatrz\u0119sie, czerwonawy ksi\u0119\u017cyc zapowiada blisko\u015b\u0107 b\u00f3lu i Ostrze\u017cenia. Po\u015br\u00f3d niewiary Moje legiony szukaj\u0105 istot o mocnej wierze, kt\u00f3re trwaj\u0105 w modlitwie za ludzko\u015b\u0107 - dusze zado\u015b\u0107uczynienia za przewinienia wobec Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszych Serc. Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: moim mieczem broni\u0119 was przed niebezpiecze\u0144stwem. B\u0105d\u017acie wierni Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej. Kochajcie nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119 czas\u00f3w ostatecznych, gdy szybko zbli\u017ca si\u0119 Ostrze\u017cenie. Naprz\u00f3d - Ja broni\u0119 was przed z\u0142em, a Moje legiony zachowuj\u0105 was od niebezpiecze\u0144stw. B\u0105d\u017acie wierni. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119: jeste\u015bmy waszymi obro\u0144cami i towarzyszami w drodze.  Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":10,"month_string":"May","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for responding to My call in your hearts. I see many of you worried about the times that will come, but I am here to comfort you, think that all evil will be defeated and you my fighting soldiers, you will have graces and mercy, you will see with your eyes, you will touch with your hands all the graces that will descend. Beloved children, pray much and thus together with me you will witness the victory of my Immaculate Heart. Pray for the Church, pray for Japan and China that they may be relieved of the pains they will cause. My children, look to the heavens, there you will see the signs of the times. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Ich sehe viele von Ihnen, die sich Sorgen \u00fcber die Zeiten machen, die kommen werden, aber ich bin hier, um Sie zu tr\u00f6sten, denke, dass alles B\u00f6se besiegt wird und Sie meine k\u00e4mpfenden Soldaten, Sie werden Gnaden und Barmherzigkeit haben, Sie werden mit Ihren Augen sehen, Sie werden es tun Ber\u00fchren Sie mit Ihren H\u00e4nden alle Gnaden, die absteigen. Geliebte Kinder, beten Sie viel und so werden Sie zusammen mit mir den Sieg meines makellosen Herzens erleben. Bete f\u00fcr die Kirche, bete f\u00fcr Japan und China, dass sie von den Schmerzen entlastet werden, die sie verursachen werden. Meine Kinder schauen in den Himmel, dort sehen Sie die Anzeichen der Zeit. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Veo a muchos de ustedes preocupados por los tiempos que llegar\u00e1n, pero estoy aqu\u00ed para consolarlos, piense que todo el mal ser\u00e1 derrotado y ustedes mis soldados de luchadores, tendr\u00e1n gracias y misericordia, ver\u00e1 con sus propios ojos, Tocar\u00e1 todas las gracias con sus propias manos que bajar\u00e1n. Queridos hijos, rezan mucho y, por lo tanto, conmigo ser\u00e1 testigo con la victoria de mi coraz\u00f3n inmaculado. Ore por la iglesia, ore por Jap\u00f3n y China para que los dolores que se causen sean a s\u00ed mismos puedan aliviarse. Hijos, miran el cielo, all\u00ed ver\u00e1s los signos de los tiempos. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Je vois que beaucoup d'entre vous s'inqui\u00e8tent des temps qui viendront, mais je suis ici pour vous r\u00e9conforter, pense que tout le mal sera vaincu et que vous combattez mes soldats, vous aurez des gr\u00e2ces et de la mis\u00e9ricorde, vous verrez avec vos yeux, vous allez Touchez avec vos mains toutes les gr\u00e2ces qui descendront. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, priez beaucoup et ainsi avec moi, vous assistera \u00e0 la victoire de mon c\u0153ur immacul\u00e9. Priez pour l'\u00c9glise, priez pour le Japon et la Chine afin qu'ils soient soulag\u00e9s des douleurs qu'ils causeront. Mes enfants, regardent les cieux, l\u00e0, vous verrez les signes de l'\u00e9poque. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Vedo molti di voi preoccupati per i tempi che arriveranno, ma Io sono qui per confortarvi, pensate che tutto il male sar\u00e0 sconfitto e voi miei soldati combattenti, avrete grazie e misericordia, vedrete con i vostri occhi, toccherete con le vostre mani tutte le grazie che scenderanno. Figli cari, pregate tanto e cos\u00ec insieme a me sarete testimoni della vittoria del mio Cuore Immacolato. Pregate per la Chiesa, pregate per il Giappone e la Cina affinch\u00e9 possano alleviarsi i dolori che causeranno. Figli, guardate il cielo, l\u00ec vedrete i segni dei tempi. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Widz\u0119, \u017ce wielu z was martwi si\u0119 o czasy, kt\u00f3re nadejd\u0105, ale jestem tu, aby was pocieszy\u0107, pomy\u015blcie, \u017ce wszelkie z\u0142o zostanie pokonane, a wy, moi walcz\u0105cy \u017co\u0142nierze, dost\u0105picie \u0142ask i mi\u0142osierdzia, zobaczycie oczami, dotkniecie r\u0119kami wszystkich \u0142ask, kt\u00f3re zst\u0105pi\u0105. Drogie dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 mocno, a w ten spos\u00f3b, razem ze mn\u0105, b\u0119dziecie \u015bwiadkami zwyci\u0119stwa mojego Niepokalanego Serca. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Japoni\u0119 i Chiny, aby zosta\u0142y uwolnione od b\u00f3lu, kt\u00f3ry spowoduj\u0105. Dzieci moje, sp\u00f3jrzcie w niebo, tam zobaczycie znaki czasu. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Eu vejo muitos de voc\u00eas preocupados com os tempos que vir\u00e3o, mas estou aqui para confort\u00e1 -lo, acho que todo o mal ser\u00e1 derrotado e seus soldados de luta, voc\u00ea ter\u00e1 gra\u00e7as e miseric\u00f3rdia, voc\u00ea ver\u00e1 com seus olhos, voc\u00ea vai Toque com as m\u00e3os todas as gra\u00e7as que descer\u00e3o. Crian\u00e7as amadas, orem muito e, portanto, juntamente comigo, voc\u00ea testemunhar\u00e1 a vit\u00f3ria do meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o imaculado. Ore pela igreja, ore pelo Jap\u00e3o e pela China para que possam ser aliviados das dores que causar\u00e3o. Meus filhos, olhe para os c\u00e9us, l\u00e1 voc\u00ea ver\u00e1 os sinais dos tempos. Agora deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u770b\u5230\u5f88\u591a\u4eba\u90fd\u62c5\u5fc3\u4f1a\u5230\u6765\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u6211\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u5b89\u6170\u4f60\uff0c\u8ba4\u4e3a\u6240\u6709\u90aa\u6076\u90fd\u4f1a\u88ab\u51fb\u8d25\uff0c\u800c\u6211\u7684\u6218\u58eb\u58eb\u5175\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u6709\u5bbd\u5bb9\u548c\u601c\u60af\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u4f60\u7684\u773c\u775b\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u7528\u624b\u89e6\u6478\u6240\u6709\u5c06\u4f1a\u4e0b\u964d\u7684\u6069\u8d50\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5f88\u591a\u4eba\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u4e0e\u6211\u4e00\u8d77\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u76ee\u7779\u6211\u5b8c\u7f8e\u65e0\u7455\u7684\u5fc3\u7684\u80dc\u5229\u3002\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4e3a\u65e5\u672c\u548c\u4e2d\u56fd\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ee5\u514d\u4ed6\u4eec\u9020\u6210\u7684\u75db\u82e6\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u770b\u7740\u5929\u5802\uff0c\u60a8\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u65f6\u4ee3\u7684\u8ff9\u8c61\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7ed9\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":12,"month_string":"May","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved children of our Lady of the Rosary of Fatima: on this feast day I call you as the people of God to accept the call of our Queen to pray the holy rosary, persevering in this act of faith, of love, of gratitude and at the same time of reparation for the offenses committed by this generation against our King and Lord Jesus Christ and against our Queen and Mother. Humanity continues to stumble due to its overbearing 'internal babel', leaving behind order, peace, respect, love of neighbour, charity and forgiveness. Confusion has taken hold of humanity, which has raised up its 'internal babel', inflating human egos so that their goals are not ones of peace but of domination and power. Our Queen holds out her hand to the simple and humble of heart.... To those who love 'in spirit and in truth'... To those who, without petty interests, seek the common good without neglecting human beings who are burdened with sins and who, in repentance, seek forgiveness in order to save their souls. Our Queen and Mother wish that all her children would be saved, which is why she goes among this humanity, moving hearts so that they would soften. You need the nourishment of the Eucharist... It is urgent that you receive the Divine Nourishment with total reverence and properly prepared. This time and its events are putting you to the test; therefore, from now on, offer up, bless, pray, sacrifice yourselves in reparation for sins and as an offering for your personal conversion and that of your brothers and sisters. Children of our Lady: with the holy rosary in your hands, prepare yourselves to be firm in the faith. This moment is decisive. Conflicts are progressing and armies blinded by the ambition of conquest will advance regardless; they will profane churches, which will have to be closed so that they would no longer be profaned, and humanity will be overcome with pain and desolation. Therefore, nourish yourselves with the body and blood of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Keep in mind that the Angel of Peace will arrive accompanied by our Queen. The sky will shine in announcement of such a great marvel of Divine Love, as men are unworthy of such a great act of love by the Eternal Father. The Angel of Peace is hope for those who persevere, protection for the humble and oppressed and shelter for the helpless. Be true children of our Queen and Mother; allow her to guide and intercede for each one of you so that under her protection you might resist with firm faith during the passage of the trial and so that you would not fall into the perversity of the antichrist. As prince of the celestial legions, I alert you so that you would mature in faith given the trials that humanity will face. Earthquakes will continue with increased force; pray for those who will suffer as a result. Love our Queen and Mother; treasure her as a precious pearl, venerate her - she is the mother of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. The most holy trinity has entrusted the protection of each one of you to our Queen and Mother at this time which is so critical in human history. Beloved, be firm in the faith, maintain unity and fraternal love. That is how Christians are to be recognized - in fraternal love. With my heavenly legions and my sword on high I protect and bless you. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci Matki Bo\u017cej R\u00f3\u017ca\u0144cowej z Fatimy: w dniu tego \u015bwi\u0119ta wzywam was jako lud Bo\u017cy, aby\u015bcie przyj\u0119li wezwanie naszej Kr\u00f3lowej do odmawiania r\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ca \u015bwi\u0119tego, wytrwali w tym akcie wiary, mi\u0142o\u015bci, wdzi\u0119czno\u015bci, a zarazem zado\u015b\u0107uczynienia za przewinienia pope\u0142nione przez to pokolenie wobec naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa oraz wobec naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 nadal potyka si\u0119 z powodu nadmiernego \"wewn\u0119trznego babel\", pozostawiaj\u0105c za sob\u0105 porz\u0105dek, pok\u00f3j, szacunek, mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 bli\u017aniego, mi\u0142osierdzie i przebaczenie. Zam\u0119t ogarn\u0105\u0142 ludzko\u015b\u0107, kt\u00f3ra podnios\u0142a sw\u00f3j \"wewn\u0119trzny babel\", nadymaj\u0105c ludzkie ego tak, \u017ce ich celem nie jest pok\u00f3j, ale dominacja i w\u0142adza. Nasza Kr\u00f3lowa wyci\u0105ga r\u0119k\u0119 do prostych i pokornego serca.... Do tych, kt\u00f3rzy kochaj\u0105 \"w duchu i w prawdzie\"... Do tych, kt\u00f3rzy bez ma\u0142ostkowych interes\u00f3w szukaj\u0105 wsp\u00f3lnego dobra, nie zaniedbuj\u0105c istot ludzkich obci\u0105\u017conych grzechami, kt\u00f3re w pokucie szukaj\u0105 przebaczenia, aby uratowa\u0107 swoje dusze. Nasza Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka pragnie, aby wszystkie Jej dzieci zosta\u0142y zbawione, dlatego idzie w\u015br\u00f3d tej ludzko\u015bci, poruszaj\u0105c serca, aby zmi\u0119k\u0142y. Potrzebujecie pokarmu Eucharystii... Pilne jest, aby\u015bcie przyjmowali Boski Pokarm z ca\u0142kowit\u0105 czci\u0105 i odpowiednio przygotowani. Ten czas i jego wydarzenia wystawiaj\u0105 was na pr\u00f3b\u0119; dlatego od tej pory ofiarujcie si\u0119, b\u0142ogos\u0142awcie, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, po\u015bwi\u0119cajcie si\u0119 w zado\u015b\u0107uczynieniu za grzechy i jako ofiara za osobiste nawr\u00f3cenie wasze i waszych braci. Dzieci Matki Bo\u017cej: z r\u00f3\u017ca\u0144cem \u015bwi\u0119tym w d\u0142oniach przygotujcie si\u0119 na mocne trwanie w wierze. Ten moment jest decyduj\u0105cy. Konflikty post\u0119puj\u0105, a armie za\u015blepione ambicj\u0105 podboju b\u0119d\u0105 posuwa\u0107 si\u0119 naprz\u00f3d bez wzgl\u0119du na wszystko; b\u0119d\u0105 profanowa\u0107 ko\u015bcio\u0142y, kt\u00f3re trzeba b\u0119dzie zamkn\u0105\u0107, aby nie by\u0142y ju\u017c profanowane, a ludzko\u015b\u0107 ogarnie b\u00f3l i spustoszenie. Dlatego od\u017cywiajcie si\u0119 cia\u0142em i krwi\u0105 naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce Anio\u0142 Pokoju przyb\u0119dzie w towarzystwie naszej Kr\u00f3lowej. Niebo zab\u0142y\u015bnie w zapowiedzi tak wielkiego cudu Boskiej Mi\u0142o\u015bci, gdy\u017c ludzie s\u0105 niegodni tak wielkiego aktu mi\u0142o\u015bci Ojca Przedwiecznego. Anio\u0142 Pokoju jest nadziej\u0105 dla tych, kt\u00f3rzy wytrwaj\u0105, ochron\u0105 dla pokornych i uci\u015bnionych oraz schronieniem dla bezradnych. B\u0105d\u017acie prawdziwymi dzie\u0107mi naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki; pozw\u00f3lcie Jej prowadzi\u0107 i wstawia\u0107 si\u0119 za ka\u017cdym z was, aby\u015bcie pod Jej opiek\u0105 mogli z mocn\u0105 wiar\u0105 opiera\u0107 si\u0119 w czasie przechodzenia pr\u00f3by i aby\u015bcie nie popadli w przewrotno\u015b\u0107 antychrysta. Jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 niebia\u0144skich legion\u00f3w ostrzegam was, aby\u015bcie dojrzewali w wierze, bior\u0105c pod uwag\u0119 pr\u00f3by, kt\u00f3rym ludzko\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dzie musia\u0142a stawi\u0107 czo\u0142a. Trz\u0119sienia ziemi b\u0119d\u0105 nadal wyst\u0119powa\u0107 ze zwi\u0119kszon\u0105 si\u0142\u0105; m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za tych, kt\u00f3rzy b\u0119d\u0105 cierpie\u0107 w ich wyniku. Kochajcie nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119; cencie J\u0105 jak drogocenn\u0105 per\u0142\u0119, czcijcie J\u0105 - jest Matk\u0105 naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Tr\u00f3jca powierzy\u0142a ochron\u0119 ka\u017cdego z was naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matce w tym czasie, kt\u00f3ry jest tak krytyczny w historii ludzko\u015bci. Umi\u0142owani, b\u0105d\u017acie mocni w wierze, zachowujcie jedno\u015b\u0107 i bratersk\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107. Tak w\u0142a\u015bnie maj\u0105 by\u0107 rozpoznawani chrze\u015bcijanie - w mi\u0142o\u015bci braterskiej. Z moimi niebia\u0144skimi legionami i moim mieczem na wysoko\u015bciach chroni\u0119 was i b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":13,"month_string":"May","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for being here and for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, pray, pray, pray, today as then, (Fatima apparition) I continue to ask for prayers and conversion. If everything had been done as I requested, you would have experienced peace but instead the gates of hell have been opened and you My little ones, if you do not strengthen yourselves in faith, you will walk on the road to perdition. I am here, with a broken heart, for all that you are allowing. My children, look at the Church, she does not want to recognize Me as Coredemptrix, I am the Queen of Heaven and Earth, She who leads you to My Son Jesus, I am His Mother and of all of you, accept this truth. My children, pray for my Ukrainian children, who were thrown into two pits still alive. My children, the earth will tremble more and more, but you do not fear, for I am here to protect you, there is no more time, be more and more spiritual and watch the signs of heaven and earth. Now I leave you, with my motherly blessing, in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie hier sind und auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder beten, beten, beten, heute wie damals (Fatima -Erscheinung). Ich bitte weiterhin um Gebete und Bekehrung. Wenn alles getan worden w\u00e4re, wie ich angefordert h\u00e4tte, h\u00e4tten Sie Frieden erlebt, aber stattdessen wurden die Tore der H\u00f6lle ge\u00f6ffnet und Sie meine Kleinen, wenn Sie sich nicht im Glauben st\u00e4rken, werden Sie auf dem Weg zum Verderben gehen. Ich bin hier mit einem gebrochenen Herzen, denn alles, was Sie zulassen. Meine Kinder, schauen sich die Kirche an, sie will mich nicht als Coredemptrix erkennen, ich bin die K\u00f6nigin des Himmels und der Erde, die dich zu meinem Sohn Jesus f\u00fchrt, ich bin seine Mutter und von euch allen, akzeptiere diese Wahrheit. Meine Kinder beten f\u00fcr meine ukrainischen Kinder, die in zwei noch lebende Gruben geworfen wurden. Meine Kinder, die Erde wird immer mehr zittern, aber Sie haben keine Angst, denn ich bin hier, um Sie zu besch\u00fctzen, es gibt keine Zeit mehr, mehr und spiritueller und beobachten Sie die Zeichen von Himmel und Erde. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed y por haber respondido mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, rezan, rezan, rezan, hoy como entonces, (aparici\u00f3n en F\u00e1tima) sigo pidiendo oraciones y conversi\u00f3n. Si todo se hubiera hecho como ped\u00ed, habr\u00edas vivido la paz y, en cambio, las puertas del inframundo y ustedes, mis peque\u00f1os, se han abierto, si no lo fortalecen en la fe, caminar\u00e1 en el camino hacia la perdici\u00f3n. Estoy aqu\u00ed, con mi coraz\u00f3n roto, por todo lo que est\u00e1s permitiendo. Mis hijos, miran a la iglesia, no quieren reconocerme como un colegio. esta verdad. Ni\u00f1os, rezan por mis hijos ucranianos, que fueron arrojados a dos todav\u00eda vivos. Mis hijos, la tierra temblar\u00e1 m\u00e1s y m\u00e1s fuerte, pero no temes, porque estoy aqu\u00ed para protegerse, ya no hay tiempo, hay m\u00e1s y m\u00e1s espiritual y mira los signos del cielo y la tierra. Ahora te dejo, con mi bendici\u00f3n materna, en el nombre del Padre, del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici et d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, priez, priez, priez, aujourd'hui comme alors, (apparition de Fatima) Je continue \u00e0 demander des pri\u00e8res et de la conversion. Si tout avait \u00e9t\u00e9 fait comme je le demandais, vous auriez v\u00e9cu la paix, mais au lieu de cela, les portes de l'enfer ont \u00e9t\u00e9 ouvertes et vous mes petits, si vous ne vous renforcez pas dans la foi, vous marcherez sur la route de la perdition. Je suis ici, avec un c\u0153ur bris\u00e9, pour tout ce que vous autorisez. Mes enfants, regardent l'\u00e9glise, elle ne veut pas me reconna\u00eetre comme coredemptrix, je suis la reine du ciel et de la terre, elle qui vous conduit \u00e0 mon fils J\u00e9sus, je suis sa m\u00e8re et de vous tous, acceptez cette v\u00e9rit\u00e9. Mes enfants, prient pour mes enfants ukrainiens, qui ont \u00e9t\u00e9 jet\u00e9s dans deux fosses encore en vie. Mes enfants, la terre tremblera de plus en plus, mais vous ne craignez pas, car je suis ici pour vous prot\u00e9ger, il n'y a plus de temps, \u00eatre de plus en plus spirituel et regarder les signes du ciel et de la terre. Maintenant, je vous quitte, avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per essere qui e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, pregate, pregate, pregate, oggi come allora, (apparizione a Fatima) continuo a chiedere preghiere e conversione. Se tutto fosse stato fatto come da me richiesto, avreste vissuto la pace e invece sono state aperte le porte degli inferi e voi piccoli miei, se non vi rafforzate nella fede, camminerete sulla strada della perdizione. Io sono qui, con il cuore infranto, per tutto ci\u00f2 che state permettendo. Figli miei, guardate la Chiesa, non vuole riconoscermi come Corredentrice, Io sono la Regina del cielo e della terra, Colei che vi porta a mio Figlio Ges\u00f9, Io sono Madre Sua e di tutti voi, accettate questa verit\u00e0. Figli, pregate per i miei figli ucraini, i quali sono stati buttati in due fosse ancora vivi. Figli miei, la terra tremer\u00e0 sempre pi\u00f9 forte, ma voi non temete, perch\u00e9 Io sono qui per proteggervi, non c\u2019\u00e8 pi\u00f9 tempo, siate sempre pi\u00f9 spirituali e guardate i segni del cielo e della terra. Ora vi lascio, con la mia benedizione materna, nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj i \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzi\u015b tak jak wtedy (objawienie w Fatimie) nadal prosz\u0119 o modlitw\u0119 i nawr\u00f3cenie. Gdyby wszystko odby\u0142o si\u0119 zgodnie z moj\u0105 pro\u015bb\u0105, zaznaliby\u015bcie pokoju; tymczasem bramy piekielne zosta\u0142y otwarte, a wy, moje male\u0144stwa, je\u015bli nie umocnicie si\u0119 w wierze, b\u0119dziecie kroczy\u0107 drog\u0105 zatracenia. Jestem tu, ze z\u0142amanym sercem, z powodu wszystkiego, na co pozwalasz. Dzieci moje, sp\u00f3jrzcie na Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, nie chce uzna\u0107 mnie za Wsp\u00f3\u0142odkupicielk\u0119, jestem Kr\u00f3low\u0105 Nieba i Ziemi, T\u0105, kt\u00f3ra prowadzi was do mojego Syna Jezusa, jestem Jego Matk\u0105 i was wszystkich, przyjmijcie t\u0119 prawd\u0119. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za moje ukrai\u0144skie dzieci, kt\u00f3re jeszcze \u017cywe zosta\u0142y wrzucone do dw\u00f3ch grob\u00f3w. Dzieci moje, ziemia b\u0119dzie dr\u017ce\u0107 coraz bardziej, ale nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, bo Ja jestem tu, aby was chroni\u0107, nie ma ju\u017c czasu, b\u0105d\u017acie coraz bardziej duchowi i patrzcie na znaki nieba i ziemi. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem, w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por estar aqui e por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, ore, ore, ore, hoje, como ent\u00e3o, (apari\u00e7\u00e3o de F\u00e1tima), continuo pedindo ora\u00e7\u00f5es e convers\u00e3o. Se tudo tivesse sido feito como eu solicitei, voc\u00ea teria experimentado paz, mas, em vez disso, os port\u00f5es do inferno foram abertos e voc\u00eas meus pequenos, se n\u00e3o se fortalecer\u00e3o na f\u00e9, voc\u00ea caminhar\u00e1 no caminho da perdi\u00e7\u00e3o. Estou aqui, com o cora\u00e7\u00e3o partido, por tudo o que voc\u00ea est\u00e1 permitindo. Meus filhos, olhe para a igreja, ela n\u00e3o quer me reconhecer como coredemptrix, eu sou a rainha do c\u00e9u e a terra, ela que o leva ao meu filho Jesus, eu sou sua m\u00e3e e de todos voc\u00eas, aceita essa verdade. Meus filhos, oram por minhas crian\u00e7as ucranianas, que foram jogadas em dois po\u00e7os ainda vivos. Meus filhos, a terra tremer\u00e1 cada vez mais, mas voc\u00ea n\u00e3o tem medo, pois estou aqui para proteg\u00ea -lo, n\u00e3o h\u00e1 mais tempo, seja cada vez mais espiritual e observe os sinais do c\u00e9u e da terra. Agora eu deixo voc\u00ea, com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna, em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u5e76\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4eca\u5929\uff08\u6cd5\u8482\u739b\u5e7b\u5f71\uff09\u6211\u7ee7\u7eed\u8981\u6c42\u7948\u7977\u548cconversion\u4f9d\u3002\u5982\u679c\u4e00\u5207\u6309\u7167\u6211\u7684\u8981\u6c42\u5b8c\u6210\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u7ecf\u5386\u548c\u5e73\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\uff0c\u5730\u72f1\u4e4b\u95e8\u5df2\u7ecf\u6253\u5f00\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5c0f\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u60a8\u4e0d\u4ee5\u4fe1\u5fc3\u6765\u589e\u5f3a\u81ea\u5df1\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48\u60a8\u5c06\u8d70\u4e0a\u706d\u4ea1\u7684\u9053\u8def\u3002\u6211\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\uff0c\u5fc3\u788e\u4e86\uff0c\u60a8\u6240\u5141\u8bb8\u7684\u4e00\u5207\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u770b\u7740\u6559\u5802\uff0c\u5979\u4e0d\u60f3\u8ba4\u8bc6\u6211\u4e3acoredemptrix\uff0c\u6211\u662f\u5929\u5730\u7684\u5973\u738b\uff0c\u5979\u5c06\u60a8\u5e26\u5230\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u8eab\u4e0a\uff0c\u6211\u662f\u4ed6\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u548c\u4f60\u4eec\u6240\u6709\u4eba\uff0c\u63a5\u53d7\u8fd9\u4e2a\u771f\u7406\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e3a\u6211\u7684\u4e4c\u514b\u5170\u5b69\u5b50\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u88ab\u6254\u8fdb\u4e24\u4e2a\u8fd8\u6d3b\u7740\u7684\u5751\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5730\u7403\u4f1a\u8d8a\u6765\u8d8a\u98a4\u6296\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u4e0d\u60e7\u6015\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u4fdd\u62a4\u4f60\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u66f4\u591a\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\uff0c\u8d8a\u6765\u8d8a\u591a\u7684\u7cbe\u795e\uff0c\u89c2\u770b\u5929\u5730\u7684\u8ff9\u8c61\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7ed9\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u79bb\u5f00\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":15,"month_string":"May","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: as prince of the heavenly legions, I bless you. I call you to remain in prayer, united to our King and Lord Jesus Christ and to our Queen and Mother of the End Times. Continue with faith and fear offending our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Fear failing in love and charity. Fear that the fresh water that nourishes fraternity would dry up in you. Only by helping one another will you be able to continue in the unity of the faithful people, overcoming the adversities, which are becoming greater all the time. Store food. Be obedient and keep provisions. Food will be scarce worldwide and humanity will fall into despair. Have foresight. Medicines will be lacking: be prepared, and for this you have received from the father\u2019s house the indications that are indispensable for you to fight disease with the fruit of nature. You are in the Great Tribulation. Maintain a firm faith so that you would not succumb when the cruellest of persecutions arrives for the faithful people. Continue on the path to which our King and Lord Jesus Christ has called you, offering penance, prayer, confessing the sins that you have committed and nourishing yourselves with the body and blood of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Bear witness that you are true Christians. Waiting for a great sign in order to convert may lead you to lose your salvation. Beware! You cannot imagine the coming suffering. You have no idea of what is to come. This red moon activated volcanoes before appearing. This red moon especially acts upon volcanoes, tectonic faults and human beings. You must remain in peace so that your spirit would not be disturbed and you must live without resentment, otherwise the latter will increase. I therefore call upon you to convert and not to waste the present moment in banalities, because if you invest your time in the affairs of heaven, heaven itself will multiply your time. If you do not pray, you will not receive the fruit and the abundant graces that the Divine Spirit pours out on those who pray with their hearts. It is a hard moment that you are going through; it is not easy - be prudent, be prudent. Do not forget that I call you to conversion: you need to convert. Pray for your brothers and sisters who do not seek conversion. The demons are on earth, tempting you continuously. You must fight to cleanse your thoughts and minds and to keep yourselves away from evil. Prepare what you can prepare; the rest will be multiplied, but prepare it now, before you are unable to do so due to the lack of what is necessary. I keep you on alert. As the people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ you must not doubt the protection of the heavenly armies, as we have been sent to guard the people of God. Our Queen and Mother love you and her motherly mantle constantly covers you. Do not fear be abandoned: you are protected and will be protected at all times. Do not falter in your faith. I bless you with the blessing that our King and Lord Jesus Christ holds over his children. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 legion\u00f3w niebieskich b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Wzywam was do trwania w modlitwie, zjednoczonej z naszym Kr\u00f3lem i Panem Jezusem Chrystusem oraz z nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0105 Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych. Trwajcie z wiar\u0105 i b\u00f3jcie si\u0119 obra\u017ca\u0107 naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. B\u00f3jcie si\u0119 zawie\u015b\u0107 w mi\u0142o\u015bci i mi\u0142osierdziu. B\u00f3jcie si\u0119, aby nie wysch\u0142a w was \u015bwie\u017ca woda, kt\u00f3ra karmi braterstwo. Tylko pomagaj\u0105c sobie nawzajem, b\u0119dziecie mogli trwa\u0107 w jedno\u015bci wiernego ludu, pokonuj\u0105c przeciwno\u015bci, kt\u00f3re ca\u0142y czas staj\u0105 si\u0119 wi\u0119ksze. Przechowujcie \u017cywno\u015b\u0107. B\u0105d\u017acie pos\u0142uszni i zachowujcie zapasy. \u017bywno\u015bci b\u0119dzie ma\u0142o na ca\u0142ym \u015bwiecie i ludzko\u015b\u0107 popadnie w rozpacz. B\u0105d\u017acie przewiduj\u0105cy. B\u0119dzie brakowa\u0142o lekarstw: b\u0105d\u017acie przygotowani, a na to otrzymali\u015bcie z domu Ojca wskazania, kt\u00f3re s\u0105 wam niezb\u0119dne do zwalczania chor\u00f3b owocami natury. Znajdujesz si\u0119 w Wielkim Ucisku. Zachowajcie mocn\u0105 wiar\u0119, aby\u015bcie nie ulegli, gdy nadejd\u0105 najokrutniejsze prze\u015bladowania dla wiernego ludu. Kontynuujcie drog\u0119, na kt\u00f3r\u0105 powo\u0142a\u0142 was nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus, ofiaruj\u0105c pokut\u0119, modlitw\u0119, wyznaj\u0105c pope\u0142nione grzechy i karmi\u0105c si\u0119 Cia\u0142em i Krwi\u0105 naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Dajcie \u015bwiadectwo, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie prawdziwymi chrze\u015bcijanami. Oczekiwanie na wielki znak, aby si\u0119 nawr\u00f3ci\u0107, mo\u017ce doprowadzi\u0107 do utraty zbawienia. Uwa\u017cajcie! Nie mo\u017cecie sobie wyobrazi\u0107 nadchodz\u0105cego cierpienia. Nie masz poj\u0119cia o tym, co ma nadej\u015b\u0107. Ten czerwony ksi\u0119\u017cyc aktywowa\u0142 wulkany przed pojawieniem si\u0119. Ten czerwony ksi\u0119\u017cyc szczeg\u00f3lnie dzia\u0142a na wulkany, uskoki tektoniczne i istoty ludzkie. Musicie pozosta\u0107 w pokoju, \u017ceby wasz duch nie by\u0142 zak\u0142\u00f3cony i musicie \u017cy\u0107 bez urazy, w przeciwnym razie ta ostatnia b\u0119dzie si\u0119 powi\u0119ksza\u0107. Dlatego wzywam was do nawr\u00f3cenia i niemarnowania obecnej chwili na bana\u0142y, poniewa\u017c je\u015bli zainwestujecie sw\u00f3j czas w sprawy nieba, samo niebo pomno\u017cy wasz czas. Je\u015bli nie b\u0119dziecie si\u0119 modli\u0107, nie otrzymacie owoc\u00f3w i obfitych \u0142ask, kt\u00f3re Duch Bo\u017cy wylewa na tych, kt\u00f3rzy modl\u0105 si\u0119 sercem. To trudny moment, kt\u00f3ry prze\u017cywacie; nie jest \u0142atwy - b\u0105d\u017acie rozwa\u017cni, b\u0105d\u017acie roztropni. Nie zapominajcie, \u017ce wzywam was do nawr\u00f3cenia: musicie si\u0119 nawr\u00f3ci\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za waszych braci i siostry, kt\u00f3rzy nie szukaj\u0105 nawr\u00f3cenia. Demony s\u0105 na ziemi, kusz\u0105 was nieustannie. Musicie walczy\u0107 o oczyszczenie waszych my\u015bli i umys\u0142\u00f3w i o to, by trzyma\u0107 si\u0119 z dala od z\u0142a. Przygotujcie to, co mo\u017cecie przygotowa\u0107; reszta zostanie pomno\u017cona, ale przygotujcie to teraz, zanim nie b\u0119dziecie mogli tego zrobi\u0107 z powodu braku tego, co konieczne. Trzymam was w gotowo\u015bci. Jako lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa nie wolno wam w\u0105tpi\u0107 w ochron\u0119 wojsk niebieskich, gdy\u017c zostali\u015bmy pos\u0142ani, aby strzec ludu Bo\u017cego. Nasza Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka kocha was, a Jej matczyny p\u0142aszcz nieustannie was okrywa. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119 by\u0107 opuszczeni: jeste\u015bcie chronieni i b\u0119dziecie chronieni przez ca\u0142y czas. Nie s\u0142abnijcie w waszej wierze. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 ci\u0119 b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem, kt\u00f3re nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus sprawuje nad swoimi dzie\u0107mi. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":17,"month_string":"May","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for being here in prayer. Beloved children, also today I thank you for responding to my call. My heart is distressed for all that will happen. I see many closed hearts, many of my children being lost and not listening to my loving call. My children, I ask you to be courageous witnesses, there is no more time, listen to your Mother's words, stock up on water, food and medicine, everything is about to end. Please children, help me. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass du hier im Gebet bist. Geliebte Kinder, auch heute danke ich Ihnen, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf geantwortet haben. Mein Herz ist beunruhigt \u00fcber alles, was passieren wird. Ich sehe viele geschlossene Herzen, viele meiner Kinder sind verloren und h\u00f6ren nicht auf meinen liebevollen Anruf. Meine Kinder, ich bitte Sie, mutige Zeugen zu sein, es gibt keine Zeit mehr, h\u00f6r auf die Worte deiner Mutter, f\u00fcge Wasser, Essen und Medizin, alles ist kurz vor dem Ende. Bitte Kinder, hilf mir. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n. Amados hijos, incluso hoy les agradezco por responder mi llamada. Mi coraz\u00f3n est\u00e1 desconsolado por todo lo que suceder\u00e1. Veo muchos corazones cerrados, muchos de mis hijos que est\u00e1n perdidos y no escuchan mi llamada amorosa. Mis hijos, les pido que sean testigos valientes, ya no hay tiempo, escuche las palabras de su madre, hagan productos de agua, alimentos y medicamentos, todo est\u00e1 a punto de terminar. Por favor, ni\u00f1os, ay\u00fadame. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, aussi aujourd'hui je vous remercie d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel. Mon c\u0153ur est en d\u00e9tresse pour tout ce qui se passera. Je vois beaucoup de c\u0153urs ferm\u00e9s, beaucoup de mes enfants sont perdus et n'\u00e9coutent pas mon appel aimant. Mes enfants, je vous demande d'\u00eatre des t\u00e9moins courageux, il n'y a plus de temps, \u00e9coutez les paroles de votre m\u00e8re, faites le plein d'eau, de nourriture et de m\u00e9decine, tout est sur le point de se terminer. S'il vous pla\u00eet enfants, aidez-moi. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera. Figli amati, anche oggi vi ringrazio per aver risposto alla mia chiamata. Il mio cuore \u00e8 affranto per tutto ci\u00f2 che accadr\u00e0. Vedo molti cuori chiusi, molti dei miei figli che si perdono e non ascoltano la mia amorevole chiamata. Figli miei, vi chiedo di essere testimoni coraggiosi, non c\u2019\u00e8 pi\u00f9 tempo, ascoltate le parole di vostra Madre, fate scorte di acqua, cibo e medicine, tutto sta per finire. Vi prego figli, aiutatemi. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj na modlitwie. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, r\u00f3wnie\u017c dzisiaj dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie. Moje serce jest zasmucone tym wszystkim, co si\u0119 wydarzy. Widz\u0119 wiele zamkni\u0119tych serc, wiele moich dzieci, kt\u00f3re s\u0105 zagubione i nie s\u0142uchaj\u0105 mojego mi\u0142osnego wo\u0142ania. Dzieci moje, prosz\u0119 was, b\u0105d\u017acie odwa\u017cnymi \u015bwiadkami, nie ma ju\u017c czasu, s\u0142uchajcie s\u0142\u00f3w waszej Matki, zr\u00f3bcie zapasy wody, \u017cywno\u015bci i lekarstw, wszystko si\u0119 ko\u0144czy. Prosz\u0119, moje dzieci, pom\u00f3\u017ccie mi. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Filhos Amados, tamb\u00e9m hoje agrade\u00e7o por responder \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o. Meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o est\u00e1 angustiado por tudo o que acontecer\u00e1. Eu vejo muitos cora\u00e7\u00f5es fechados, muitos dos meus filhos est\u00e3o perdidos e n\u00e3o ouvindo meu chamado amoroso. Meus filhos, pe\u00e7o que sejam testemunhas corajosas, n\u00e3o h\u00e1 mais tempo, ou\u00e7a as palavras de sua m\u00e3e, estocam \u00e1gua, comida e rem\u00e9dio, tudo est\u00e1 prestes a terminar. Por favor, crian\u00e7as, ajude -me. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4eca\u5929\u4e5f\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u590d\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\u4e3a\u6240\u6709\u53d1\u751f\u7684\u4e8b\u60c5\u611f\u5230\u6cae\u4e27\u3002\u6211\u770b\u5230\u8bb8\u591a\u5c01\u95ed\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u8bb8\u591a\u5b69\u5b50\u8ff7\u8def\u4e86\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u542c\u6211\u7231\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u8981\u6c42\u60a8\u6210\u4e3a\u52c7\u6562\u7684\u89c1\u8bc1\u4eba\uff0c\u4e0d\u518d\u6709\u65f6\u95f4\uff0c\u542c\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u8bdd\uff0c\u50a8\u5b58\u6c34\uff0c\u98df\u7269\u548c\u836f\u54c1\uff0c\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u5c06\u7ed3\u675f\u3002\u8bf7\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5e2e\u6211\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":21,"month_string":"May","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people: receive my Sacred Heart together with my blessing. I remain with each one of you. Each human being decides whether they want to open the door of their heart to me. All of heaven stands before my children to help them, and you should not be afraid of what is coming, but should trust in my protection. You must believe that you are not alone. You are living within the purification that is necessary at this time in order for my children to be saved. The 'wolves in sheep\u2019s clothing\u201d are engaged in carrying out the orders of the antichrist, feeding the infernal dragon in order to make it grow by supporting immorality, the killing of the innocent and the destruction of the family through laws contrary to this beloved institution. My Mother has called you to repentance, yet you have not repented\u2026 the banner of this generation is ignominy and immorality. Man has given his hand to the devil; therefore, the chastisements will not stop. These will be so severe that you cannot imagine them. Humanity\u2019s suffering is not far from you, but a twinkling of an eye away. Foolishly, you will continue to reject and deny the signs and signals until famine overtakes mankind, and lamentation, together with social revolts, will be throughout the earth. This famine is necessary for the antichrist in order for him to exert his force upon the people and oblige them to seal themselves in order to obtain food and medicines, and finally he will dominate them. My beloved people, diseases are progressing, one after another being sent to humanity to keep you frightened and constrained. This skin disease was foreseen for you: the diseases are not coming by themselves. Pray, come to me: I am your God. My beloved people, it is not only pain that my people will experience. In the principal sanctuaries dedicated to my most holy Mother in each country, a miracle of Maternal Love will occur for 3 hours. My mother will alert you in advance. Children, you are not alone, keep your faith alive and firm. I am your God. Pray my children, pray for Italy: it will suffer severely. Pray, my children, pray, Japan will be strongly shaken. Pray, my children, pray, my people will not be abandoned, no matter how severe the moment may be. Pray, my children, pray, night will come in the twinkling of an eye. My people, my cross is a sign of salvation and redemption: carry it with you. I am your God, and I will never abandon you. I bless you with my love. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, przyjmijcie moje Naj\u015bwi\u0119tsze Serce wraz z moim b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem. Ja pozostaj\u0119 z ka\u017cdym z was. Ka\u017cdy cz\u0142owiek decyduje, czy chce otworzy\u0107 drzwi swojego serca dla mnie. Ca\u0142e niebo stoi przed moimi dzie\u0107mi, aby im pom\u00f3c, a wy nie powinni\u015bcie si\u0119 ba\u0107 tego, co nadchodzi, ale powinni\u015bcie ufa\u0107 w moj\u0105 ochron\u0119. Musicie wierzy\u0107, \u017ce nie jeste\u015bcie sami. \u017byjecie w ramach oczyszczenia, kt\u00f3re jest konieczne w tym czasie, aby moje dzieci zosta\u0142y uratowane. \"Wilki w owczej sk\u00f3rze\" zajmuj\u0105 si\u0119 wykonywaniem rozkaz\u00f3w antychrysta, karmi\u0105c piekielnego smoka, aby m\u00f3g\u0142 rosn\u0105\u0107 poprzez popieranie niemoralno\u015bci, zabijanie niewinnych i niszczenie rodziny poprzez prawa sprzeczne z t\u0105 ukochan\u0105 instytucj\u0105. Moja Matka wzywa\u0142a was do pokuty, ale wy nie pokutowali\u015bcie... sztandarem tego pokolenia jest ha\u0144ba i niemoralno\u015b\u0107. Cz\u0142owiek poda\u0142 r\u0119k\u0119 diab\u0142u; dlatego karcenia nie ustan\u0105. B\u0119d\u0105 one tak dotkliwe, \u017ce nie mo\u017cecie ich sobie wyobrazi\u0107. Cierpienia ludzko\u015bci nie s\u0105 daleko od was, lecz w mgnieniu oka. G\u0142upio b\u0119dziecie nadal odrzuca\u0107 i negowa\u0107 znaki i sygna\u0142y, a\u017c g\u0142\u00f3d ogarnie ludzko\u015b\u0107 i lament, wraz z buntami spo\u0142ecznymi, b\u0119dzie na ca\u0142ej ziemi. Ten g\u0142\u00f3d jest konieczny dla antychrysta, aby m\u00f3g\u0142 wywrze\u0107 swoj\u0105 si\u0142\u0119 na lud i zobowi\u0105za\u0107 go do uszczelnienia si\u0119 w celu uzyskania \u017cywno\u015bci i lek\u00f3w, a w ko\u0144cu zdominuje go. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, choroby post\u0119puj\u0105, jedna po drugiej s\u0105 wysy\u0142ane na ludzko\u015b\u0107, aby utrzyma\u0107 was w strachu i ograniczeniu. Ta choroba sk\u00f3ry zosta\u0142a przewidziana dla was: choroby nie przychodz\u0105 same z siebie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, przyjd\u017acie do Mnie: Ja jestem waszym Bogiem. . M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, nie tylko b\u00f3lu do\u015bwiadczy m\u00f3j lud. W g\u0142\u00f3wnych sanktuariach po\u015bwi\u0119conych mojej naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Matce w ka\u017cdym kraju, przez 3 godziny b\u0119dzie mia\u0142 miejsce cud Matczynej Mi\u0142o\u015bci. Moja Matka powiadomi was z wyprzedzeniem. Dzieci, nie jeste\u015bcie sami, zachowajcie \u017cyw\u0105 i mocn\u0105 wiar\u0119. Ja jestem waszym Bogiem. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za W\u0142ochy: b\u0119d\u0105 cierpia\u0142y dotkliwie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, Japonia b\u0119dzie mocno wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119ta. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3j lud nie zostanie opuszczony, bez wzgl\u0119du na to, jak ci\u0119\u017cka b\u0119dzie chwila. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, noc nadejdzie w mgnieniu oka. M\u00f3j ludu, m\u00f3j krzy\u017c jest znakiem zbawienia i odkupienia: no\u015bcie go ze sob\u0105. Ja jestem waszym Bogiem i nigdy was nie opuszcz\u0119. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":21,"month_string":"May","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for being here in prayer and for answering my call in your hearts. My children, you are experiencing dark times and going forward they will become darkness, but you always look to the light. How many times has Jesus promised you protection, has He ever failed you? How many times have you been in difficulty, yet He has never abandoned you. My children, my children, never be afraid, no matter what happens, pray, pray, pray a lot, cover the earth with your prayers, pray for the priests who are defying God, pray for the powerful because they are plotting. My children, they want to take away your freedom, but you have faith and be in the truth, only it will make you free. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie hier im Gebet sind und meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen beantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, Sie erleben dunkle Zeiten und gehen in Zukunft Dunkelheit, aber Sie schauen immer auf das Licht. Wie oft hat Jesus Ihnen den Schutz versprochen, hat er Sie jemals versagt? Wie oft waren Sie in Schwierigkeiten, aber er hat Sie nie verlassen. Meine Kinder, meine Kinder, haben niemals Angst, egal was passiert, beten, beten, beten, viel mit Ihren Gebeten bedecken, f\u00fcr die Priester beten, die sich Gott widersetzen, beten f\u00fcr die M\u00e4chtigen, weil sie planen. Meine Kinder wollen deine Freiheit wegnehmen, aber du hast Glauben und in der Wahrheit, nur dass es dich frei machen wird. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por haber respondido mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Ni\u00f1os, vives en tiempos oscuros y contin\u00faan, se convertir\u00e1n en oscuridad, pero siempre miras la luz. \u00bfCu\u00e1ntas veces te ha prometido Jes\u00fas protecci\u00f3n, alguna vez te ha decepcionado? \u00bfCu\u00e1ntas veces has estado en la dificultad, pero nunca te ha abandonado? Los ni\u00f1os, mis hijos, nunca temen, lo que suceda, reza, reza, reza mucho, cubre la tierra con tus oraciones, reza por los sacerdotes que desaf\u00edan a Dios, rezan por los poderosos porque son conspiraci\u00f3n. Mis hijos, quieren quitarle la libertad, pero usted tiene fe y estar\u00e1 en la verdad, solo que lo har\u00e1 libre. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re et d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, vous vivez des temps sombres et \u00e0 l'avenir, ils deviendront l'obscurit\u00e9, mais vous regardez toujours la lumi\u00e8re. Combien de fois J\u00e9sus vous a-t-il promis une protection, vous a-t-il d\u00e9j\u00e0 \u00e9chou\u00e9? Combien de fois avez-vous \u00e9t\u00e9 en difficult\u00e9, mais il ne vous a jamais abandonn\u00e9. Mes enfants, mes enfants, n'ont jamais peur, quoi qu'il arrive, priez, priez, priez beaucoup, couvrez la terre de vos pri\u00e8res, priez pour les pr\u00eatres qui d\u00e9fier Dieu, priez pour les puissants parce qu'ils complotent. Mes enfants, ils veulent enlever votre libert\u00e9, mais vous avez la foi et \u00eatre dans la v\u00e9rit\u00e9, mais cela vous rendra libre. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, state vivendo tempi bui e andando avanti diventeranno tenebre, ma voi guardate sempre la luce. Quante volte Ges\u00f9 vi ha promesso protezione, vi ha mai deluso? Quante volte siete stati nella difficolt\u00e0, eppure non vi ha mai abbandonato.  Figli, bambini miei, non temete mai, qualunque cosa accadr\u00e0, pregate, pregate, pregate tanto, coprite la terra con le vostre preghiere, pregate per i sacerdoti che stanno sfidando Dio, pregate per i potenti perch\u00e9 stanno complottando. Figli miei, vogliono togliervi la libert\u00e0, ma voi abbiate fede e siate nella verit\u00e0, solo essa vi render\u00e0 liberi. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam za obecno\u015b\u0107 na modlitwie i za odpowied\u017a na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, prze\u017cywacie mroczne czasy i w przysz\u0142o\u015bci stan\u0105 si\u0119 one ciemno\u015bci\u0105, ale wy zawsze patrzycie w stron\u0119 \u015bwiat\u0142a. Ile razy Jezus obieca\u0142 ci ochron\u0119 i czy kiedykolwiek ci\u0119 rozczarowa\u0142? Ile razy by\u0142e\u015b w trudnej sytuacji, ale On nigdy ci\u0119 nie opu\u015bci\u0142. Dzieci moje, dzieci moje, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, cokolwiek si\u0119 stanie, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 gorliwie, pokryjcie ziemi\u0119 waszymi modlitwami, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za kap\u0142an\u00f3w, kt\u00f3rzy sprzeciwiaj\u0105 si\u0119 Bogu, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za mo\u017cnych, bo knuj\u0105. Dzieci moje, chc\u0105 wam odebra\u0107 wolno\u015b\u0107, ale wy miejcie wiar\u0119 i post\u0119pujcie w prawdzie, tylko ona uczyni was wolnymi. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por atender minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, voc\u00ea est\u00e1 enfrentando tempos sombrios e, daqui para frente, eles se tornar\u00e3o escurid\u00e3o, mas voc\u00ea sempre olha para a luz. Quantas vezes Jesus prometeu prote\u00e7\u00e3o, ele j\u00e1 falhou em voc\u00ea? Quantas vezes voc\u00ea esteve em dificuldade, mas ele nunca o abandonou. Meus filhos, meus filhos, nunca tenham medo, n\u00e3o importa o que aconte\u00e7am, orem, orem, orem muito, cobrem a terra com suas ora\u00e7\u00f5es, orem pelos sacerdotes que est\u00e3o desafiando a Deus, ore pelos poderosos porque est\u00e3o planejando. Meus filhos, eles querem tirar sua liberdade, mas voc\u00ea tem f\u00e9 e est\u00e1 na verdade, s\u00f3 que isso o libertar\u00e1. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u63a5\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u60a8\u6b63\u5728\u7ecf\u5386\u9ed1\u6697\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\uff0c\u524d\u8fdb\uff0c\u5b83\u4eec\u4f1a\u53d8\u6210\u9ed1\u6697\uff0c\u4f46\u60a8\u603b\u662f\u770b\u7740\u5149\u660e\u3002\u8036\u7a23\u6709\u591a\u5c11\u6b21\u5411\u60a8\u4fdd\u8bc1\u4fdd\u62a4\uff0c\u4ed6\u66fe\u7ecf\u8ba9\u60a8\u5931\u8d25\u5417\uff1f\u60a8\u9047\u5230\u4e86\u591a\u5c11\u6b21\u56f0\u96be\uff0c\u4f46\u4ed6\u4ece\u672a\u629b\u5f03\u8fc7\u60a8\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u65e0\u8bba\u53d1\u751f\u4ec0\u4e48\u4e8b\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4e3a\u90a3\u4e9b\u8fdd\u6297\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u795e\u7236\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u200b\u200b\u4e3a\u6709\u6743\u52bf\u7684\u5f3a\u5927\u800c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u4eec\u6b63\u5728\u8c0b\u6740\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u60f3\u5265\u593a\u60a8\u7684\u81ea\u7531\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u60a8\u6709\u4fe1\u5fc3\u5e76\u638c\u63e1\u771f\u7406\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u5b83\u4f1a\u8ba9\u60a8\u81ea\u7531\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":24,"month_string":"May","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My dear children, thank you for responding to My call in your hearts. Children, even when you think you are alone, I, your Mother am here. Children, war and famine will be felt more and more strongly, but faith in God will protect you; do not be afraid. In this time be united and do not be means of discord. Children, pray for the hypocritical and perverse bishops, pray for the Church, which is bleeding, as is my Son. Pray for the Pope. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father, the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine lieben Kinder, danke, dass du auf meinen Anruf in deinem Herzen geantwortet hast. Kinder, auch wenn du denkst, du bist allein, ich bin hier. Kinder, Krieg und Hungersnot werden immer st\u00e4rker empfunden werden, aber der Glaube an Gott wird Sie besch\u00fctzen. Sei nicht \u00e4ngstlich. In dieser Zeit vereint sein und kein Mittel der Zwietracht sein. Kinder, beten f\u00fcr die scheinheiligen und perversen Bisch\u00f6fe, beten f\u00fcr die Kirche, die blutet, ebenso wie mein Sohn. Bete f\u00fcr den Papst. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters, des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Ni\u00f1os, incluso cuando crees que est\u00e1s solo, yo, tu madre, estoy aqu\u00ed. Los ni\u00f1os, la guerra y la hambruna se sentir\u00e1n m\u00e1s fuertes y fuertes, pero la fe en Dios te proteger\u00e1, no tengas miedo. En este per\u00edodo, estar unido y no sean medios de discordia. Ni\u00f1os, rezan por obispos hip\u00f3critas y perversos, rezan por la iglesia, que sangran, as\u00ed como a mi hijo. Ore por el Papa. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Les enfants, m\u00eame lorsque vous pensez que vous \u00eates seul, moi, votre m\u00e8re suis ici. Les enfants, la guerre et la famine se sentiront de plus en plus fortement, mais la foi en Dieu vous prot\u00e9gera; n'ayez pas peur. En ce temps, soyez unis et ne soyez pas des moyens de discorde. Les enfants, prient pour les \u00e9v\u00eaques hypocrites et perverses, prient pour l'\u00e9glise, qui saigne, tout comme mon fils. Priez pour le pape. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re, du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia  chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, anche quando pensate di essere soli, Io, vostra Madre sono qui. Figli, la guerra e la carestia si faranno sentire sempre pi\u00f9 forte, ma la fede in Dio vi protegger\u00e0, non abbiate paura. In questo periodo siate uniti e non siate mezzi di discordia. Figli, pregate per i vescovi ipocriti e perversi, pregate per la Chiesa, che sta sanguinando, cos\u00ec come mio Figlio. Pregate per il Papa. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moje drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, nawet gdy my\u015blicie, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie sami, Ja, wasza Matka, jestem tutaj. Dzieci moje, wojna i g\u0142\u00f3d b\u0119d\u0105 coraz bardziej odczuwalne, ale wiara w Boga b\u0119dzie was chroni\u0107, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119. W tym czasie b\u0105d\u017acie zjednoczeni i nie b\u0105d\u017acie powodem roz\u0142amu. Dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za biskup\u00f3w ob\u0142udnych i przewrotnych, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, kt\u00f3ry krwawi tak jak m\u00f3j Syn. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za papie\u017ca. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus queridos filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Filhos, mesmo quando voc\u00ea pensa que est\u00e1 sozinho, eu, sua m\u00e3e estou aqui. Filhos, guerra e fome ser\u00e3o sentidos cada vez mais fortemente, mas a f\u00e9 em Deus o proteger\u00e1; N\u00e3o tenha medo. Nesse momento, estar\u00e1 unido e n\u00e3o seja meios de disc\u00f3rdia. Os filhos, orem pelos bispos hip\u00f3critas e perversos, orem pela igreja, que est\u00e1 sangrando, assim como meu filho. Ore pelo papa. Agora deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5373\u4f7f\u60a8\u8ba4\u4e3a\u81ea\u5df1\u4e00\u4e2a\u4eba\uff0c\u6211\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u3002\u513f\u7ae5\uff0c\u6218\u4e89\u548c\u9965\u8352\u5c06\u8d8a\u6765\u8d8a\u5f3a\u70c8\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u5bf9\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u4f1a\u4fdd\u62a4\u4f60\u3002\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\u3002\u5728\u8fd9\u6bb5\u65f6\u95f4\u91cc\uff0c\u56e2\u7ed3\u8d77\u6765\uff0c\u4e0d\u662f\u4e0d\u548c\u8c10\u7684\u624b\u6bb5\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e3a\u865a\u4f2a\u548c\u4e0d\u6b63\u5f53\u7684\u4e3b\u6559\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u6d41\u8840\u7684\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u4e5f\u662f\u5982\u6b64\u3002\u4e3a\u6559\u7687\u7948\u7977\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u963f\u95e8\uff08Amen\uff09\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u79bb\u5f00\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":27,"month_string":"May","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people: my blessing constantly remains upon you. In every act and in every work in favour of the common good, my blessings increase for my people in general. Maintain faith; you must personally make it flourish constantly so that it may be strengthened and so that unity with my House would be greater and stronger. Do not neglect prayer, confession and receiving me, worthily prepared. My church is being severely tested. I call you not to lose the faith: 'I am your God.' My Church is being tested so that she would be purified and so that the evil that has infiltrated within her would be cast away. My Church faces pain: mourning will cover her. Take refuge in me and in my Mother in this moment of suffering. Maintain peace, so damaged by the human race, so distorted and belittled. You will discover grave lies with which your minds have been flooded with thoughts and judgments contrary to love and truth. As humanity you have been led into mortal distress. At this time, you are dependent upon technology for economic survival and humanity will do what is necessary to acquire what is assumed to be indispensable in life. The great powers are detonating weapons.... My people suffer to the core: this is being provoked by those powers that serve evil and wish to dethrone me. You are living in a state of alert because of the skin disease that I had already announced to you. Yet this will not end here, but another skin disease will appear, generated by misused science, which is today\u2019s Herod. Persevere, my children, being attentive to healing plants, about which my house is letting you know and whose use has been explained to you. I love you, my children, and I desire the good of each one of you. I therefore call you to mark yourselves with holy water, just as in your homes the door and window frames must remain sealed with holy water. World peace is at its point of greatest tension. Without respect for persons, the allies of evil will wreak great havoc on humanity at the cost of grave pains against life. The devil despises life, which is why he is intent on acting against life and in favour of division. My people must journey on without accepting the innovations that will be presented to you to distinguish people from one another, for these are traps of the evil one to subject you to his nefarious plans. My children are living in tension and constant anger, enraged against their fellow men.... You will see how, for no reason, human beings will kill others for their satisfaction. Thus, goes humanity, inflamed without knowing the cause, but I know it: it is the devil who is acting in order to take rapid possession of humanity. Fight with the weapons of my love. What is not love does not belong to me. I bless you, my people, I bless you. I love you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu: moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo nieustannie pozostaje nad tob\u0105. W ka\u017cdym czynie i w ka\u017cdej pracy na rzecz dobra wsp\u00f3lnego wzrasta moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo dla ca\u0142ego mojego ludu. Zachowujcie wiar\u0119; musicie osobi\u015bcie dba\u0107 o jej nieustanny rozkwit, aby si\u0119 umacnia\u0142a i aby jedno\u015b\u0107 z moim Domem by\u0142a wi\u0119ksza i silniejsza. Nie zaniedbujcie modlitwy, spowiedzi i przyjmowania Mnie, godnie przygotowanego. M\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 jest poddawany ci\u0119\u017ckim pr\u00f3bom. Wzywam was, aby\u015bcie nie tracili wiary: \"Ja jestem twoim Bogiem\". M\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 jest poddawany pr\u00f3bom, aby zosta\u0142 oczyszczony i aby zosta\u0142o wyrzucone z\u0142o, kt\u00f3re w nim przenikn\u0119\u0142o. M\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 stoi w obliczu b\u00f3lu: okryje go \u017ca\u0142oba. W tej chwili cierpienia schroncie si\u0119 we Mnie i w mojej Matce. Zachowajcie pok\u00f3j, tak zniszczony przez rodzaj ludzki, tak zniekszta\u0142cony i umniejszony. Odkryjecie powa\u017cne k\u0142amstwa, kt\u00f3rymi wasze umys\u0142y zosta\u0142y zalane my\u015blami i s\u0105dami sprzecznymi z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 i prawd\u0105. Jako ludzko\u015b\u0107 zostali\u015bcie doprowadzeni do \u015bmiertelnego nieszcz\u0119\u015bcia. W tym czasie jeste\u015bcie zale\u017cni od technologii dla ekonomicznego przetrwania i ludzko\u015b\u0107 zrobi to, co jest konieczne, aby zdoby\u0107 to, co jest uwa\u017cane za niezb\u0119dne w \u017cyciu. Wielkie mocarstwa detonuj\u0105 bro\u0144.... M\u00f3j lud cierpi do g\u0142\u0119bi: jest to prowokowane przez te pot\u0119gi, kt\u00f3re s\u0142u\u017c\u0105 z\u0142u i chc\u0105 mnie zdetronizowa\u0107. \u017byjecie w stanie alarmu z powodu choroby sk\u00f3ry, kt\u00f3r\u0105 ju\u017c wam zapowiedzia\u0142em. Jednak na tym si\u0119 nie sko\u0144czy, ale pojawi si\u0119 inna choroba sk\u00f3ry, wywo\u0142ana przez \u017ale u\u017cyt\u0105 nauk\u0119, kt\u00f3ra jest dzisiejszym Herodem. Wytrwajcie, moje dzieci, zwracaj\u0105c uwag\u0119 na ro\u015bliny lecznicze, o kt\u00f3rych m\u00f3j dom daje wam zna\u0107 i kt\u00f3rych zastosowanie zosta\u0142o wam wyja\u015bnione. Kocham was, moje dzieci, i pragn\u0119 dobra ka\u017cdego z was. Dlatego wzywam was do naznaczenia si\u0119 wod\u0105 \u015bwi\u0119con\u0105, tak jak w waszych domach ramy drzwi i okien musz\u0105 pozosta\u0107 szczelnie zamkni\u0119te wod\u0105 \u015bwi\u0119con\u0105. Pok\u00f3j na \u015bwiecie znajduje si\u0119 w punkcie najwi\u0119kszego napi\u0119cia. Bez szacunku dla os\u00f3b, sprzymierze\u0144cy z\u0142a dokonaj\u0105 wielkiego spustoszenia w ludzko\u015bci, kosztem ci\u0119\u017ckiego b\u00f3lu przeciwko \u017cyciu. Diabe\u0142 gardzi \u017cyciem, dlatego zamierza dzia\u0142a\u0107 przeciwko \u017cyciu i na rzecz podzia\u0142u. M\u00f3j lud musi i\u015b\u0107 dalej, nie przyjmuj\u0105c innowacji, kt\u00f3re zostan\u0105 wam przedstawione, aby odr\u00f3\u017cni\u0107 ludzi od siebie, poniewa\u017c s\u0105 to pu\u0142apki z\u0142ego, aby podda\u0107 was jego nikczemnym planom. Moje dzieci \u017cyj\u0105 w napi\u0119ciu i ci\u0105g\u0142ym gniewie, rozw\u015bcieczone przeciwko swoim bli\u017anim.... Zobaczycie, jak bez powodu istoty ludzkie b\u0119d\u0105 zabija\u0107 innych dla swojej satysfakcji. Tak idzie ludzko\u015b\u0107, rozpalona bez znajomo\u015bci przyczyny, ale Ja j\u0105 znam: to diabe\u0142 dzia\u0142a, aby szybko zaw\u0142adn\u0105\u0107 ludzko\u015bci\u0105. Walczcie broni\u0105 mojej mi\u0142o\u015bci. Co nie jest mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, nie nale\u017cy do Mnie. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, m\u00f3j ludu, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Kocham was. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":28,"month_string":"May","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, only intense and unceasing prayer will comfort my blessed and aching heart and that of my Son. My children, pray because you do not know what is coming, the dark night is very near, light the blessed candles in your homes. My children, the angels fight with swords, but you, with the Holy Rosary in your hands, continue this prayer that is so dear to me. My children, open your hearts so that joy and hope may enter because I am coming to prepare you, do not be afraid of what you will see, for My blessed Mantle is upon you. Lift up your arms and praise the Lord. Beloved children, always remember my infinite Motherly love for you. Now I bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, Father and Son and Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Geliebte Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, nur intensives und unaufh\u00f6rliches Gebet werden mein gesegnetes und schmerzendes Herz und das meines Sohnes tr\u00f6sten. Meine Kinder, beten, weil du nicht wei\u00dft, was kommt, die dunkle Nacht ist sehr nahe, hell die gesegneten Kerzen in deinen H\u00e4usern. Meine Kinder, die Engel k\u00e4mpfen mit Schwertern, aber Sie setzen mit dem heiligen Rosenkranz in Ihren H\u00e4nden dieses Gebet fort, das mir so lieb ist. Meine Kinder \u00f6ffnen Ihre Herzen, damit Freude und Hoffnung eintreten k\u00f6nnen, weil ich komme, um Sie vorzubereiten, haben Sie keine Angst vor dem, was Sie sehen werden, denn mein gesegneter Mantel liegt auf Ihnen. Hebe deine Arme hoch und lobe den Herrn. Geliebte Kinder, erinnern Sie sich immer an meine unendliche m\u00fctterliche Liebe zu Ihnen. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen der heiligsten Dreifaltigkeit, Vater und Sohn und Heiliger Geist, Amen.","text_es":"Amados hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, solo la oraci\u00f3n intensa e incesante consolar\u00e1 mi coraz\u00f3n bendecido y doloroso y el de mi hijo. Mis hijos, rezan porque no sabes lo que viene, la noche oscura est\u00e1 muy cerca, enciende las velas bendecidas en tus hogares. Mis hijos, los \u00e1ngeles pelean con espadas, pero t\u00fa, con el Rosario Santo en tus manos, contin\u00faan esta oraci\u00f3n tan querida. Mis hijos, abren los corazones para que la alegr\u00eda y la esperanza puedan venir a prepararte, no tengas miedo de lo que ver\u00e1s, porque mi bendito manto est\u00e1 sobre ti. Levanta los brazos y alaban al Se\u00f1or. Amados hijos, siempre recuerda mi amor infinito como madre para ti. Ahora te bendiga en el nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Padre, Hijo y Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, seule pri\u00e8re intense et incessante r\u00e9conforteront mon c\u0153ur b\u00e9ni et douloureux et celui de mon fils. Mes enfants, priez parce que vous ne savez pas ce qui va arriver, la nuit noire est tr\u00e8s proche, allume les bougies b\u00e9nies dans vos maisons. Mes enfants, les anges se battent avec des \u00e9p\u00e9es, mais vous, avec le Saint Rosaire dans vos mains, continuez cette pri\u00e8re qui m'est si ch\u00e8re. Mes enfants, ouvrent vos c\u0153urs pour que la joie et l'espoir puissent entrer parce que je viens vous pr\u00e9parer, n'ayez pas peur de ce que vous verrez, car mon manteau b\u00e9ni est sur vous. Soulevez vos bras et louez le Seigneur. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, souvenez-vous toujours de mon amour maternel infini pour vous. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9, P\u00e8re et Fils et Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli amati, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, solo la preghiera intensa e incessante conforter\u00e0 il mio benedetto e dolorante cuore e quello di mio Figlio. Figli miei, pregate perch\u00e9 non sapete cosa sta arrivando, la notte buia \u00e8 molto vicina, accendete nelle vostre case le candele benedette. Figli miei, gli angeli combattono con le spade, ma voi, con il Santo Rosario tra le mani, continuate questa preghiera a me tanto cara. Figli miei, aprite i vostri cuori affinch\u00e9 possa entrare la gioia e la speranza perch\u00e9 Io vengo a prepararvi, non abbiate paura di ci\u00f2 che vedrete, perch\u00e9 il mio Manto benedetto \u00e8 su di voi. Innalzate le vostre braccia e Lodate il Signore. Figli amati, ricordatevi sempre il mio infinito amore di Madre per voi. Ora vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, Padre, Figlio e Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, tylko intensywna i nieustanna modlitwa mo\u017ce pocieszy\u0107 moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awione i bolesne serce i serce mojego Syna. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, poniewa\u017c nie wiecie, co nadchodzi, ciemna noc jest bardzo bliska, zapalcie w waszych domach pob\u0142ogos\u0142awione \u015bwiece. Dzieci moje, anio\u0142owie walcz\u0105 mieczami, ale wy, z r\u00f3\u017ca\u0144cem \u015bwi\u0119tym w r\u0119kach, kontynuujcie t\u0119 modlitw\u0119, kt\u00f3ra jest mi tak droga. Dzieci moje, otw\u00f3rzcie wasze serca, aby zago\u015bci\u0142a w nich rado\u015b\u0107 i nadzieja, bo przychodz\u0119, aby was przygotowa\u0107, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119 tego, co zobaczycie, bo m\u00f3j b\u0142ogos\u0142awiony p\u0142aszcz jest nad wami. Podnie\u015bcie r\u0119ce i chwalcie Pana. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, pami\u0119tajcie zawsze o mojej niesko\u0144czonej matczynej mi\u0142o\u015bci do was. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Filhos Amados, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, apenas uma ora\u00e7\u00e3o intensa e incessante confortar\u00e3o meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o aben\u00e7oado e dolorido e o do meu filho. Meus filhos, orem porque voc\u00ea n\u00e3o sabe o que est\u00e1 por vir, a noite escura est\u00e1 muito pr\u00f3xima, acende as velas aben\u00e7oadas em suas casas. Meus filhos, os anjos lutam com espadas, mas voc\u00ea, com o Santo Ros\u00e1rio em suas m\u00e3os, continuam esta ora\u00e7\u00e3o que \u00e9 t\u00e3o querida para mim. Meus filhos, abrem seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es para que alegria e esperan\u00e7a possam entrar porque estou vindo para prepar\u00e1 -lo, n\u00e3o tenha medo do que voc\u00ea ver\u00e1, pois meu manto aben\u00e7oado est\u00e1 sobre voc\u00ea. Levante seus bra\u00e7os e louve o Senhor. Crian\u00e7as amadas, lembre -se sempre do meu amor materno infinito por voc\u00ea. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Pai, Filho e Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u5f3a\u70c8\u800c\u4e0d\u65ad\u7684\u7948\u7977\u4f1a\u5b89\u6170\u6211\u7684\u5e78\u798f\u548c\u9178\u75db\u7684\u5fc3\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u7684\u5fc3\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u60a8\u4e0d\u77e5\u9053\u4f1a\u53d1\u751f\u4ec0\u4e48\uff0c\u6f06\u9ed1\u7684\u591c\u665a\u975e\u5e38\u8fd1\uff0c\u7167\u4eae\u4e86\u60a8\u5bb6\u4e2d\u6709\u798f\u7684\u8721\u70db\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5929\u4f7f\u4eec\u7528\u5251\u6218\u6597\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u60a8\u7528\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u5ff5\u73e0\u638c\u63e1\u5728\u6211\u7684\u624b\u4e2d\uff0c\u7ee7\u7eed\u5bf9\u6211\u5982\u6b64\u73cd\u8d35\u7684\u7948\u7977\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u655e\u5f00\u5fc3hearts\uff0c\u4ee5\u4f7f\u559c\u60a6\u548c\u5e0c\u671b\u8fdb\u5165\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u8981\u4e3a\u60a8\u505a\u597d\u51c6\u5907\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\u60a8\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u7684\u4e1c\u897f\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u7684\u795d\u798f\u7684\u5730\u5e54\u5728\u60a8\u8eab\u4e0a\u3002\u4e3e\u8d77\u4f60\u7684\u624b\u81c2\uff0c\u8d5e\u7f8e\u4e3b\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6c38\u8fdc\u8bb0\u4f4f\u6211\u5bf9\u4f60\u7684\u65e0\u9650\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u7231\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u6700\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\uff0c\u963f\u4eec\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":5,"day":31,"month_string":"May","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My children and brothers, thank you for bending your knees, under my Cross. Brothers, feed on what I have left you, my living presence, in body and blood. Adore the Blessed Sacrament and many will be the graces you will receive. My children, take advantage of these times when you can have my body freely, soon they will deceive you, saying it is only a remembrance. I, myself, give you this warning, read the Holy Gospel often, all this will be erased and you will have to do it secretly. I say this, this is sacred truth. My brothers, ask me for consolation and union among brothers, open your hearts to the power of the Holy Spirit, who will make new men of you. Be at the service of the weakest, be humble and abandon pride and haughtiness, especially, those who, reading my and my Mother's messages, ridicule everything, but if they would only read, meditate and pray, I myself would respond in their hearts. Now I bless you in the name of the Father, in My Name and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder und Br\u00fcder, danke, dass Sie sich die Knie unter meinem Kreuz gebeugt haben. Br\u00fcder, ern\u00e4hren sich von dem, was ich dir verlassen habe, meine lebende Pr\u00e4senz, in K\u00f6rper und Blut. Besitz das gesegnete Sakrament und viele werden die Gnaden sein, die Sie erhalten. Meine Kinder nutzen diese Zeiten, in denen Sie meinen K\u00f6rper frei haben k\u00f6nnen, bald werden sie Sie t\u00e4uschen und sagen, dass es nur eine Erinnerung ist. Ich selbst, ich gebe dir diese Warnung, lese das heilige Evangelium oft, all dies wird gel\u00f6scht und du musst es heimlich tun. Ich sage das, das ist die heilige Wahrheit. Meine Br\u00fcder, bitten mich um Trost und Vereinigung zwischen Br\u00fcdern, \u00f6ffnen Sie Ihre Herzen f\u00fcr die Kraft des Heiligen Geistes, der neue M\u00e4nner von Ihnen machen wird. Seien Sie im Dienste des Schw\u00e4chsten, seien Sie dem\u00fctig und geben Sie Stolz und Hochm\u00fctigkeit auf, insbesondere diejenigen, die, die Botschaften meiner Mutter und die Botschaften meiner Mutter lesen, alles verspotten, aber wenn sie nur lesen, meditieren und beten w\u00fcrden, w\u00fcrde ich selbst in ihren Herzen antworten. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters, in meinem Namen und dem Heiligen Geist, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos y hermanos, gracias por doblar las rodillas, debajo de mi cruz. Hermanos, se alimentan de lo que te dej\u00e9, mi presencia viva, en el cuerpo y en la sangre. Amas el Sant\u00edsimo Sacramento y habr\u00e1 muchas gracias que recibir\u00e1s. Ni\u00f1os, aprovechen estos momentos en que puedas tener mi cuerpo libremente, pronto te enga\u00f1ar\u00e1n, diciendo que es solo un recuerdo. Yo, en persona, te doy esta advertencia, a menudo leo el Santo Evangelio, todo esto ser\u00e1 cancelado y tendr\u00e1s que hacerlo en secreto. Lo digo, esta es la verdad sacrosana. Mis hermanos, me piden el consuelo y la uni\u00f3n entre hermanos, abren tu coraz\u00f3n al poder del Esp\u00edritu Santo, que te har\u00e1 nuevos hombres. Est\u00e9 al servicio de los m\u00e1s d\u00e9biles, sea humilde y abandone el orgullo y el orgullo, sobre todo, aquellos que leen mis mensajes y de mi madre, ridiculizan todo, pero si solo leen, meditan y rezan, responder\u00eda en sus corazones. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, en mi nombre y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants et mes fr\u00e8res, merci d'avoir pli\u00e9 vos genoux, sous ma croix. Fr\u00e8res, se nourrissez de ce que je vous ai laiss\u00e9, ma pr\u00e9sence vivante, dans le corps et le sang. Adorez le Saint-Sacrement et beaucoup seront les gr\u00e2ces que vous recevrez. Mes enfants, profitent de ces moments o\u00f9 vous pouvez avoir mon corps librement, bient\u00f4t ils vous tromperont, disant que ce n'est qu'un souvenir. Moi-m\u00eame, je vous donne cet avertissement, lis souvent le Saint \u00c9vangile, tout cela sera effac\u00e9 et vous devrez le faire secr\u00e8tement. Je dis cela, c'est la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 sacr\u00e9e. Mes fr\u00e8res, me demandent la consolation et l'union parmi les fr\u00e8res, ouvrent votre c\u0153ur au pouvoir du Saint-Esprit, qui fera de nouveaux hommes de vous. Soyez au service des plus faibles, soyez humbles et abandonnez la fiert\u00e9 et la hauteur, surtout, ceux qui, lisant mes messages et ma m\u00e8re, ridiculisent tout, mais s'ils lisaient, m\u00e9ditent et priaient, je r\u00e9pondrais moi-m\u00eame dans leur c\u0153ur. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re, en mon nom et au Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli e fratelli miei, grazie per aver piegato le ginocchia, sotto la mia croce. Fratelli, cibatevi di ci\u00f2 che vi ho lasciato, la mia presenza viva, nel corpo e nel sangue. Adorate il Santissimo Sacramento e tante saranno le grazie che riceverete. Figli, approfittate di questi tempi in cui potrete avere il mio corpo liberamente, presto vi inganneranno, dicendo che \u00e8 solo un ricordo. Io, in persona, vi do questo avvertimento, leggete spesso il Santo Vangelo, tutto questo verr\u00e0 cancellato e dovrete farlo di nascosto. Io lo dico, questa \u00e8 verit\u00e0 sacrosanta. Fratelli miei, chiedetemi la consolazione e l\u2019unione tra fratelli, aprite il vostro cuore alla potenza dello Spirito Santo, che far\u00e0 di voi uomini nuovi. Siate al servizio dei pi\u00f9 deboli, siate umili e abbandonate l\u2019orgoglio e la superbia, soprattutto, coloro che leggendo i messaggi miei e di mia Madre, ridicolizzano tutto, ma se solo leggessero, meditando e pregando, Io stesso risponderei nei loro cuori. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, nel Mio Nome e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Synowie moi i bracia, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie pod moim Krzy\u017cem. Bracia, karmcie si\u0119 tym, co wam zostawi\u0142em, moj\u0105 \u017cyw\u0105 obecno\u015bci\u0105 w Ciele i Krwi. Adorujcie Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszy Sakrament, a wiele \u0142ask otrzymacie. Dzieci moje, korzystajcie z tych chwil, kiedy mo\u017cecie swobodnie dysponowa\u0107 moim cia\u0142em, bo wkr\u00f3tce zwiod\u0105 was, m\u00f3wi\u0105c, \u017ce to tylko pami\u0105tka. Sam daj\u0119 wam to ostrze\u017cenie, czytajcie cz\u0119sto Ewangeli\u0119, to wszystko zostanie usuni\u0119te i b\u0119dziecie musieli robi\u0107 to w tajemnicy. Ja to m\u00f3wi\u0119, to jest \u015bwi\u0119ta prawda. Bracia moi, pro\u015bcie o pociech\u0119 i jedno\u015b\u0107 mi\u0119dzy bra\u0107mi, otw\u00f3rzcie wasze serca na moc Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, kt\u00f3ry uczyni z was nowych ludzi. S\u0142u\u017ccie najs\u0142abszym, b\u0105d\u017acie pokorni, porzu\u0107cie pych\u0119 i arogancj\u0119, zw\u0142aszcza ci, kt\u00f3rzy czytaj\u0105c or\u0119dzia moje i mojej Matki, wszystko wy\u015bmiewaj\u0105, lecz gdyby tylko czytali, rozwa\u017cali i modlili si\u0119, Ja sam odpowiedzia\u0142bym w ich sercach. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca, w Imi\u0119 Moje i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos e irm\u00e3os, obrigado por dobrar os joelhos, sob a minha cruz. Irm\u00e3os, alimentam -se do que eu te deixei, minha presen\u00e7a viva, no corpo e no sangue. Adore o Sant\u00edssimo Sacramento e muitos ser\u00e3o as gra\u00e7as que voc\u00ea receber\u00e1. Meus filhos, aproveitam esses momentos em que voc\u00ea pode ter meu corpo livremente, em breve eles o enganar\u00e3o, dizendo que \u00e9 apenas uma lembran\u00e7a. Eu, eu mesmo, dou -lhe esse aviso, leio o Santo Evangelho com frequ\u00eancia, tudo isso ser\u00e1 apagado e voc\u00ea ter\u00e1 que faz\u00ea -lo secretamente. Eu digo isso, isso \u00e9 verdade sagrada. Meus irm\u00e3os, pedem consola\u00e7\u00e3o e uni\u00e3o entre os irm\u00e3os, abrem seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es ao poder do Esp\u00edrito Santo, que far\u00e3o novos homens de voc\u00ea. Fique a servi\u00e7o dos mais fracos, seja humilde e abandone o orgulho e a arrog\u00e2ncia, especialmente aqueles que, lendo minhas mensagens e de minha m\u00e3e, ridicularizam tudo, mas se eles apenas leiam, meditassem e orassem, eu mesmo responderia em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, em meu nome e no Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u548c\u5144\u5f1f\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u6211\u7684\u5341\u5b57\u67b6\u4e0b\u5f2f\u8170\u3002\u5144\u5f1f\uff0c\u4ee5\u6211\u7559\u4e0b\u7684\u4e1c\u897f\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u751f\u7269\uff0c\u8eab\u4f53\u548c\u9c9c\u8840\u4e3a\u98df\u3002\u5d07\u62dc\u6709\u798f\u7684\u5723\u793c\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u5c06\u662f\u60a8\u5c06\u83b7\u5f97\u7684\u6069\u5178\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5229\u7528\u60a8\u53ef\u4ee5\u81ea\u7531\u5730\u62e5\u6709\u6211\u7684\u8eab\u4f53\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u5f88\u5feb\u5c31\u4f1a\u6b3a\u9a97\u60a8\uff0c\u8bf4\u8fd9\u53ea\u662f\u4e00\u79cd\u8bb0\u5fc6\u3002\u6211\u672c\u4eba\uff0c\u7ed9\u4f60\u8fd9\u4e2a\u8b66\u544a\uff0c\u7ecf\u5e38\u9605\u8bfb\u5723\u798f\u97f3\uff0c\u6240\u6709\u8fd9\u4e9b\u90fd\u5c06\u88ab\u5220\u9664\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u5fc5\u987b\u79d8\u5bc6\u5730\u8fdb\u884c\u3002\u6211\u8fd9\u6837\u8bf4\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u795e\u5723\u7684\u771f\u7406\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\u4eec\uff0c\u8bf7\u6211\u5728\u5144\u5f1f\u4e4b\u95f4\u5b89\u6170\u548c\u7ed3\u5408\uff0c\u5411\u5723\u7075\u7684\u529b\u91cf\u655e\u5f00\u5fc3hearts\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u5c06\u6210\u4e3a\u60a8\u7684\u65b0\u4eba\u3002\u4e3a\u6700\u5f31\u8005\u670d\u52a1\uff0c\u8c26\u865a\uff0c\u653e\u5f03\u81ea\u8c6a\u548c\u50b2\u6162\uff0c\u5c24\u5176\u662f\u90a3\u4e9b\u9605\u8bfb\u6211\u548c\u6211\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u4fe1\u606f\uff0c\u5632\u7b11\u4e00\u5207\u7684\u4eba\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u5982\u679c\u4ed6\u4eec\u53ea\u8bfb\uff0c\u51a5\u60f3\u548c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u6211\u672c\u4eba\u5c31\u4f1a\u5728\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u4ee5\u6211\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u548c\u5723\u7075\uff0c\u963f\u4eec\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":2,"month_string":"June","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved children: I cover you with the love of my Spirit to endow you with all that is necessary for my children to possess to labour in my Kingdom. My people pass through the path of my passion. My people will carry my Cross; yes, my Cross of glory and majesty. Without fearing my Cross, my children will carry it in order to leave all that is sin on it. My children, it is necessary for you to understand that the man who lives of and for the flesh does not understand the affairs of the spirit; he will work and act in the flesh, very far from my Will. My children live in a constant conversion, striving, distancing themselves from all that is of the world, praying and offering for the conversion of their brothers, those who live in the worldly. My people, live moving forward, navigating and striving hand in hand with my blessed Mother so that my Mother may lift you up when you feel you can no longer go on. Prepare yourselves spiritually, now! Anger ferments within my children and they lose their sanity confronting one another, besieged by the devil, who at this moment advances knowing that he is defeated by my most holy Mother. My beloved ones, famine is advancing without warning. Scarcity has already reached some countries and still they despise my calls. With the famine, the human creature is agitated by the deprivation of what is necessary and revolts break out from country to country like a plague. The powerful of the world will offer you help in exchange for joining the ranks of the antichrist. Pray my children, pray for the Middle East. Pray my children, pray for your brothers who suffer from war. Pray my children, pray before the scourges of nature. My people: keep faith in continual growth and be experts in love. My law must be engraved in your heart. Pray, knowing that my Holy Spirit defeats hardened hearts, impenetrable hearts of stone in which my love is unknown. My people, I love you: I mourn for what is happening and will happen with more strength.... I mourn for the suffering of my children, that is why I go one by one like a beggar who finds all his nourishment in love. Continue to trust in my love and my protection for each of my children. For me each one is my great treasure. Keep hope alive, I will never be defeated. 'I am your Lord and your God and you are my children. Will you succeed in defeating them? I assure you of my guardianship and my permanent protection. Come to me! My blessing is with you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Moje ukochane dzieci, okrywam was mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 mojego Ducha, aby obdarzy\u0107 was tym wszystkim, co jest konieczne do posiadania przez moje dzieci, aby mog\u0142y pracowa\u0107 w moim Kr\u00f3lestwie. M\u00f3j lud przechodzi przez drog\u0119 mojej m\u0119ki. M\u00f3j lud b\u0119dzie ni\u00f3s\u0142 m\u00f3j Krzy\u017c; tak, m\u00f3j Krzy\u017c chwa\u0142y i majestatu. Nie boj\u0105c si\u0119 mojego Krzy\u017ca, moje dzieci b\u0119d\u0105 go nios\u0142y, aby zostawi\u0107 na nim wszystko, co jest grzechem. Moje dzieci, trzeba, aby\u015bcie zrozumieli, \u017ce cz\u0142owiek, kt\u00f3ry \u017cyje z cia\u0142a i dla cia\u0142a, nie rozumie spraw ducha; b\u0119dzie pracowa\u0142 i dzia\u0142a\u0142 w ciele, bardzo daleko od mojej Woli. Moje dzieci \u017cyj\u0105 w ci\u0105g\u0142ym nawr\u00f3ceniu, d\u0105\u017ceniu, oddalaniu si\u0119 od wszystkiego, co jest ze \u015bwiata, modl\u0105c si\u0119 i ofiaruj\u0105c za nawr\u00f3cenie swoich braci, tych, kt\u00f3rzy \u017cyj\u0105 doczesno\u015bci\u0105. M\u00f3j ludu, \u017cyjcie w ci\u0105g\u0142ym ruchu naprz\u00f3d, nawiguj\u0105c i walcz\u0105c r\u0119ka w r\u0119k\u0119 wraz z moj\u0105 b\u0142ogos\u0142awion\u0105 Matk\u0105, aby moja Matka mog\u0142a was podnie\u015b\u0107, gdy poczujecie, \u017ce nie mo\u017cecie ju\u017c d\u0142u\u017cej i\u015b\u0107. Przygotujcie si\u0119 duchowo, teraz! Gniew fermentuje w moich dzieciach i trac\u0105 one rozs\u0105dek, konfrontuj\u0105c si\u0119 ze sob\u0105, obl\u0119\u017cone przez diab\u0142a, kt\u00f3ry w tej chwili posuwa si\u0119 naprz\u00f3d, wiedz\u0105c, \u017ce jest pokonany przez moj\u0105 naj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105 Matk\u0119. Moi ukochani, g\u0142\u00f3d nadchodzi bez ostrze\u017cenia. Niedostatek dotar\u0142 ju\u017c do niekt\u00f3rych kraj\u00f3w i nadal gardz\u0105 moimi wezwaniami. Wraz z g\u0142odem, ludzkie stworzenie jest wzburzone z powodu pozbawienia go tego, co konieczne i bunty wybuchaj\u0105 z kraju do kraju jak plaga. Pot\u0119\u017cni tego \u015bwiata zaoferuj\u0105 wam pomoc w zamian za wst\u0105pienie w szeregi antychrysta. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Bliski Wsch\u00f3d. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za waszych braci, kt\u00f3rzy cierpi\u0105 z powodu wojny. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 przed plagami natury. M\u00f3j ludu: utrzymujcie wiar\u0119 w ci\u0105g\u0142ym wzro\u015bcie i b\u0105d\u017acie ekspertami w mi\u0142o\u015bci. Moje prawo musi by\u0107 wyryte w waszym sercu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, wiedz\u0105c, \u017ce m\u00f3j Duch \u015awi\u0119ty pokonuje zatwardzia\u0142e serca, nieprzeniknione serca z kamienia, w kt\u00f3rych moja mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 jest nieznana. M\u00f3j ludu, kocham ci\u0119: Op\u0142akuj\u0119 to, co si\u0119 dzieje i b\u0119dzie si\u0119 dzia\u0142o z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 si\u0142\u0105.... Op\u0142akuj\u0119 cierpienie moich dzieci, dlatego id\u0119 jeden po drugim jak \u017cebrak, kt\u00f3ry w mi\u0142o\u015bci znajduje ca\u0142y sw\u00f3j pokarm. Ufajcie nadal w moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 i moj\u0105 opiek\u0119 nad ka\u017cdym z moich dzieci. Dla mnie ka\u017cde z nich jest moim wielkim skarbem. Zachowaj \u017cyw\u0105 nadziej\u0119, nigdy nie zostan\u0119 pokonany. \"Jestem waszym Panem i waszym Bogiem, a wy jeste\u015bcie moimi dzie\u0107mi. Czy uda ci si\u0119 je pokona\u0107? Zapewniam was o mojej opiece i sta\u0142ej ochronie. Przyjd\u017acie do mnie! Moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo jest z wami. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":3,"month_string":"June","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, thank you for kneeling in prayer. My children, await the Warning ,which is closer than you think, but await it with great joy, God's love will show you wonderful things, those who will be afraid is because they have not yet freed themselves from sin, despite my continuous call. My children, this is the time of your purification and you must live it with full acceptance. Children, please, I still touch the earth because I want you to be saved. you live my messages with humility, prayer and brotherhood, you will be like the little remnant, who stayed close to my Jesus, be apostles and have the courage of faith. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen. I will be with you until the end of prayer.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie im Gebet knien. Meine Kinder warten auf die Warnung, die n\u00e4her als Sie denken, aber erwarten Sie sie mit gro\u00dfer Freude, Gottes Liebe wird Ihnen wundervolle Dinge zeigen, diejenigen, die Angst haben, ist, weil sie sich trotz meines kontinuierlichen Anrufs noch nicht von der S\u00fcnde befreit haben. Meine Kinder, dies ist die Zeit Ihrer Reinigung und Sie m\u00fcssen sie mit voller Akzeptanz leben. Kinder, bitte, ich ber\u00fchre immer noch die Erde, weil ich m\u00f6chte, dass du gerettet wirst. Du lebst meine Botschaften mit Demut, Gebet und Br\u00fcderlichkeit, du wirst wie der kleine \u00dcberrest sein, der meinem Jesus nahe blieb, Apostel und den Mut des Glaubens haben. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes Amen. Ich werde bis zum Ende des Gebets bei dir sein.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, gracias por doblar las rodillas durante la oraci\u00f3n. Ni\u00f1os, esperan la advertencia, que est\u00e1 m\u00e1s cerca de lo que piensas, pero esperan con gran alegr\u00eda, el amor de Dios te mostrar\u00e1 cosas maravillosas, que tendr\u00e1n miedo es porque a\u00fan no se ha liberado del pecado, a pesar de mi continuo. recuerdo. Mis hijos, este es el momento de su purificaci\u00f3n y tienes que vivirla con plena aceptaci\u00f3n. Ni\u00f1os, por favor, todav\u00eda toco la tierra porque quiero salvarte. Vives mis mensajes con humildad, oraci\u00f3n y hermandad, ser\u00e1s como el peque\u00f1o descanso, que permaneci\u00f3 cerca de mi Jes\u00fas, s\u00e9 ap\u00f3stoles y tendr\u00e1 el coraje de la fe. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n. Estar\u00e9 contigo hasta el final de la oraci\u00f3n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, merci d'\u00eatre \u00e0 genoux dans la pri\u00e8re. Mes enfants, attendent l'avertissement, qui est plus proche que vous ne le pensez, mais l'attendez avec une grande joie, l'amour de Dieu vous montrera des choses merveilleuses, ceux qui auront peur, c'est parce qu'ils ne se sont pas encore lib\u00e9r\u00e9s du p\u00e9ch\u00e9, malgr\u00e9 mon appel continu. Mes enfants, c'est le moment de votre purification et vous devez le vivre avec toute l'acceptation. Enfants, s'il vous pla\u00eet, je touche toujours la terre parce que je veux que vous soyez sauv\u00e9. Vous vivez mes messages avec humilit\u00e9, pri\u00e8re et fraternit\u00e9, vous serez comme le petit reste, qui est rest\u00e9 proche de mon J\u00e9sus, soyez des ap\u00f4tres et ayez le courage de la foi. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen. Je serai avec vous jusqu'\u00e0 la fin de la pri\u00e8re.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, grazie per aver piegato le ginocchia durante la preghiera. Figli, attendete l\u2019Avvertimento ,che \u00e8 pi\u00f9 vicino di quanto voi pensiate, ma attendetelo con grande gioia, l\u2019amore di Dio vi far\u00e0 vedere cose meravigliose, chi avr\u00e0 paura \u00e8 perch\u00e9 non si \u00e8 ancora liberato dal peccato, nonostante il mio continuo richiamo. Figli miei, questo \u00e8 il momento della vostra purificazione e dovete viverla con accettazione piena. Figli, vi prego, Io tocco ancora la terra perch\u00e9 vi voglio salvi. voi vivete i miei messaggi con umilt\u00e0, preghiera e fratellanza, sarete come il piccolo resto, che rimase vicino al mio Ges\u00f9, siate apostoli e abbiate il coraggio della fede. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen. Sar\u00f2 con voi fino alla fine della preghiera.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce ukl\u0119kli\u015bcie do modlitwy. Dzieci moje, oczekujcie Ostrze\u017cenia, kt\u00f3re jest bli\u017cej, ni\u017c my\u015blicie, oczekujcie go z wielk\u0105 rado\u015bci\u0105, mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 Bo\u017ca sprawi, \u017ce zobaczycie cudowne rzeczy, ba\u0107 b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 ci, kt\u00f3rzy jeszcze nie uwolnili si\u0119 od grzechu, mimo moich nieustannych wezwa\u0144. Moje dzieci, to jest czas waszego oczyszczenia i musicie go prze\u017cy\u0107 z pe\u0142n\u0105 akceptacj\u0105. Dzieci moje, b\u0142agam was, wci\u0105\u017c przebywam na ziemi, bo chc\u0119, aby\u015bcie byli zbawieni. \u017byj\u0105c moimi or\u0119dziami w pokorze, modlitwie i braterstwie, b\u0119dziecie jak ta ma\u0142a resztka, kt\u00f3ra pozosta\u0142a blisko mojego Jezusa, b\u0119dziecie aposto\u0142ami i b\u0119dziecie mieli odwag\u0119 wiary. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen. B\u0119d\u0119 z wami a\u017c do ko\u0144ca modlitwy.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, obrigado por ajoelhar -se em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, aguardam o aviso, que \u00e9 mais pr\u00f3ximo do que voc\u00ea pensa, mas aguarda com grande alegria, o amor de Deus mostrar\u00e1 coisas maravilhosas, aqueles que ter\u00e3o medo \u00e9 porque ainda n\u00e3o se libertaram do pecado, apesar do meu chamado cont\u00ednuo. Meus filhos, este \u00e9 o momento da sua purifica\u00e7\u00e3o e voc\u00ea deve viver com total aceita\u00e7\u00e3o. Filhos, por favor, eu ainda toco a terra porque quero que voc\u00ea seja salvo. Voc\u00ea vive minhas mensagens com humildade, ora\u00e7\u00e3o e irmandade, voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 como o pequeno remanescente, que ficou perto de meu Jesus, ser ap\u00f3stolos e ter a coragem da f\u00e9. Agora deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m. Estarei com voc\u00ea at\u00e9 o fim da ora\u00e7\u00e3o.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u8dea\u4e0b\u7948\u7977\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7b49\u5f85\u8b66\u544a\uff0c\u5b83\u6bd4\u60a8\u60f3\u8c61\u7684\u8981\u8fd1\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u4ee5\u6781\u5927\u7684\u559c\u60a6\u7b49\u5f85\u7740\u5b83\uff0c\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u7231\u5c06\u5411\u60a8\u5c55\u793a\u7f8e\u5999\u7684\u4e8b\u7269\uff0c\u90a3\u4e9b\u4f1a\u5bb3\u6015\u7684\u4eba\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u4eec\u5c1a\u672a\u5c1a\u672a\u4ece\u7f6a\u6076\u4e2d\u89e3\u8131\u51fa\u6765\uff0c\u5c3d\u7ba1\u6211\u6301\u7eed\u4e86\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u60a8\u51c0\u5316\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\uff0c\u60a8\u5fc5\u987b\u5b8c\u5168\u63a5\u53d7\u5b83\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8bf7\uff0c\u6211\u4ecd\u7136\u89e6\u6478\u5730\u7403\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u5e0c\u671b\u4f60\u5f97\u6551\u3002\u60a8\u4ee5\u8c26\u5351\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u548c\u5144\u5f1f\u60c5\u8c0a\u6765\u5b9e\u73b0\u6211\u7684\u4fe1\u606f\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u5c31\u50cf\u90a3\u4e2a\u9760\u8fd1\u6211\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u5c0f\u6b8b\u4f59\u7269\uff0c\u662f\u4f7f\u5f92\uff0c\u6709\u4fe1\u4ef0\u7684\u52c7\u6c14\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7ed9\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u3002\u6211\u4f1a\u548c\u4f60\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\uff0c\u76f4\u5230\u7948\u7977\u7ed3\u675f\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":4,"month_string":"June","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My child, despite My tears, you continue to live in indifference, even My beloved children do not have the humility of silence and contemplation. My children, I weep because I know what is coming soon and you continue to live as if you do not know the truth. My children, in the Church, blood will be shed. Pray for the powerful because they want to bring you to death. The subterranean earth will heat up so much that even many fish in the sea will die. My children, return to God, your only salvation, and be converted. Now I bless you, in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Mein Kind leben trotz meiner Tr\u00e4nen weiterhin in Gleichg\u00fcltigkeit, selbst meine geliebten Kinder haben nicht die Demut von Stille und Kontemplation. Meine Kinder, ich weine, weil ich wei\u00df, was bald kommt, und Sie leben weiterhin so, als ob Sie die Wahrheit nicht kennen. Meine Kinder in der Kirche werden Blut vergossen. Bete f\u00fcr die M\u00e4chtigen, weil sie dich zum Tode bringen wollen. Die unterirdische Erde wird so sehr auferstehen, dass selbst viele Fische im Meer sterben werden. Meine Kinder kehren zu Gott zur\u00fcck, Ihre einzige Erl\u00f6sung, und werden Sie konvertiert. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mi hija, a pesar de mis l\u00e1grimas, contin\u00faa viviendo en indiferencia, incluso mis hijos favoritos no tienen la humildad del silencio y la contemplaci\u00f3n. Hijos, lloro porque s\u00e9 lo que vendr\u00e1 en breve y contin\u00faas viviendo como si no supieras la verdad. Mis hijos, en la iglesia, ser\u00e1n viernes de sangre. Ore por los poderosos porque quieren llevarte a la muerte. El sustrato de la tierra se calentar\u00e1 tanto que muchos peces del mar morir\u00e1n. Mis hijos, vuelven a Dios, su \u00fanica salvaci\u00f3n y converso. Ahora los bendiga, en el nombre del Padre, del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mon enfant, malgr\u00e9 mes larmes, vous continuez \u00e0 vivre dans l'indiff\u00e9rence, m\u00eame mes enfants bien-aim\u00e9s n'ont pas l'humilit\u00e9 du silence et de la contemplation. Mes enfants, je pleure parce que je sais ce qui arrive bient\u00f4t et vous continuez \u00e0 vivre comme si vous ne connaissiez pas la v\u00e9rit\u00e9. Mes enfants, dans l'\u00e9glise, le sang seront vers\u00e9s. Priez pour les puissants car ils veulent vous faire m'emp\u00eacher de mort. La terre souterraine chauffera tellement que m\u00eame de nombreux poissons dans la mer mourront. Mes enfants, retournez \u00e0 Dieu, votre seul salut, et \u00eatre converti. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figlia mia, nonostante le mie lacrime, continuate a vivere nell\u2019indifferenza, anche i miei figli prediletti non hanno l\u2019umilt\u00e0 del silenzio e della contemplazione. Figli, piango perch\u00e9 Io so cosa arriver\u00e0 a breve e voi continuate a vivere come se non conosceste la verit\u00e0. Figli miei, nella Chiesa, sar\u00e0 versato sangue. Pregate per i potenti perch\u00e9 vogliono portarvi alla morte. Il substrato della terra si riscalder\u00e0 cos\u00ec tanto, che anche molti pesci del mare moriranno. Figli miei, tornate a Dio, vostra unica salvezza e convertitevi. Ora vi benedico, nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moje dziecko, mimo moich \u0142ez nadal \u017cyjesz w oboj\u0119tno\u015bci, nawet moje ukochane dzieci nie maj\u0105 pokory milczenia i kontemplacji. Dzieci moje, p\u0142acz\u0119, bo wiem, co wkr\u00f3tce nadejdzie, a wy nadal \u017cyjecie tak, jakby\u015bcie nie znali prawdy. Dzieci moje, w Ko\u015bciele poleje si\u0119 krew. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za w\u0142adc\u00f3w, bo oni chc\u0105 was doprowadzi\u0107 do \u015bmierci. Wn\u0119trze Ziemi rozgrzeje si\u0119 tak bardzo, \u017ce zginie nawet wiele ryb w morzu. Moje dzieci, powr\u00f3\u0107cie do Boga, waszego jedynego ratunku, i nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119. Teraz ja was b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meu filho, apesar das minhas l\u00e1grimas, voc\u00ea continua vivendo em indiferen\u00e7a, mesmo meus filhos amados n\u00e3o t\u00eam a humildade de sil\u00eancio e contempla\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, eu choro porque sei o que est\u00e1 chegando em breve e voc\u00ea continua vivendo como se n\u00e3o soubesse a verdade. Meus filhos, na igreja, o sangue ser\u00e1 derramado. Ore pelos poderosos porque eles querem lev\u00e1 -lo \u00e0 morte. A terra subterr\u00e2nea esquenta tanto que at\u00e9 muitos peixes no mar morrer\u00e3o. Meus filhos, voltam a Deus, sua \u00fanica salva\u00e7\u00e3o e se convertem. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo, em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5c3d\u7ba1\u6211\u7684\u773c\u6cea\uff0c\u60a8\u4ecd\u4f1a\u4fdd\u6301\u51b7\u6f20\u751f\u6d3b\uff0c\u5373\u4f7f\u6211\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4e5f\u6ca1\u6709\u6c89\u9ed8\u548c\u6c89\u601d\u7684\u8c26\u5351\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u54ed\u6ce3\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u77e5\u9053\u5373\u5c06\u53d1\u751f\u7684\u4e8b\u60c5\uff0c\u60a8\u7ee7\u7eed\u751f\u6d3b\uff0c\u597d\u50cf\u60a8\u4e0d\u77e5\u9053\u771f\u76f8\u4e00\u6837\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u5728\u6559\u5802\u91cc\u4f1a\u6d41\u8840\u3002\u4e3a\u5f3a\u5927\u7684\u4eba\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u4eec\u60f3\u8ba9\u60a8\u6b7b\u4ea1\u3002\u5730\u4e0b\u5730\u7403\u4f1a\u52a0\u70ed\u5f97\u5982\u6b64\u4e4b\u591a\uff0c\u4ee5\u81f3\u4e8e\u5373\u4f7f\u662f\u6d77\u4e2d\u7684\u8bb8\u591a\u9c7c\u4e5f\u4f1a\u6b7b\u4ea1\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u56de\u5230\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u60a8\u552f\u4e00\u7684\u6551\u8d4e\uff0c\u5e76\u5f97\u5230converted\u4f9d\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":6,"month_string":"June","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart: I bless you with my love, I bless you with my fiat. Children, I call you to convert. Some ask themselves: how do I convert? You must decide to turn away from sin, from all that corrupts your spiritual and physical senses, your mind, your thoughts and all that hardens your heart. You must make a firm decision, a firm purpose to amend the falls you may have in detachment from the worldly, from the sinful and from improper habits. The tyranny of the human self is strong when it has been allowed to take the reins of the cravings of the flesh and the senses. Convert by turning away from that which corrupts you and leads you to join the low and lower where the devil moves. Sin leads you to deny yourselves of my Divine Son and this is very serious, for the result is to deny yourselves eternal salvation, if you do not repent. Sin is to enter the dangerous terrain of the forbidden and improper where the soul suffers. You possess free will and I see so many of my children constantly falling into the same sin out of foolishness, they say: 'I am free, freedom is mine', and thus they sink into the nauseating waters of sin, from which they do not come out because of pride, because of the bad use of free will. Convert! Think about how you are, what you do, how you react, how you are with your brothers, how you act and how you act. Children, humanity is in danger and without conversion you are easy prey to evil. Great changes are coming! Modernisms arrive that destroy the spirituality of my children, leading them to betray my son. There are so many who feel they are wise that they end up being foolish and falling into the vile. There is an urgent need for change in humanity so that they are not deceived. The human creature is in constant conversion with the urgency to be constantly washed of sin. I call you as the first time to strengthen yourselves as the people of my son with fasting, prayer, the Eucharist and fraternity. As a Mother I would like to speak to you only of the greatness of heaven, but at this moment I must speak of what is approaching and can lead you to fall. In this 'already' you must change and prepare yourselves to be totally new creatures. Violence is increasing in the face of the dissent of humanity, generating chaos in one country or another. That is why I call you to adore my Divine Son, to pray and to be fraternal. You will not succeed in giving what you do not carry within. My children, you need to live in adoration of my Son so that you may pass this on to your brothers and sisters before it is too late. Beloved people of my Son, this is the time to raise your hearts to my Son, separating yourselves from my Son prevents you from discerning. More illnesses are coming which are not Divine Will, but of misused science. Pray and use what has been indicated to you. Be fraternal and do not allow strife.... Unity is urgent. He who lives in strife will find himself alone before the danger of evil. I bless you with my love, come into my womb. I remain with the people of my Son. Do not fear, I protect you. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca: B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moim fiat. Dzieci, wzywam was do nawr\u00f3cenia. Niekt\u00f3rzy zadaj\u0105 sobie pytanie: jak mam si\u0119 nawr\u00f3ci\u0107? Musicie zdecydowa\u0107 si\u0119 na odwr\u00f3cenie si\u0119 od grzechu, od wszystkiego, co deprawuje wasze duchowe i fizyczne zmys\u0142y, wasz umys\u0142, wasze my\u015bli i wszystko, co zatwardza wasze serce. Musisz podj\u0105\u0107 stanowcz\u0105 decyzj\u0119, stanowczy cel, aby zmieni\u0107 upadki, kt\u00f3re mo\u017cesz mie\u0107 w oderwaniu od tego, co \u015bwiatowe, od tego, co grzeszne i od niew\u0142a\u015bciwych nawyk\u00f3w. Tyrania ludzkiego \"ja\" jest silna, gdy pozwolono jej przej\u0105\u0107 kontrol\u0119 nad pragnieniami cia\u0142a i zmys\u0142\u00f3w. Nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119, odwracaj\u0105c si\u0119 od tego, co was deprawuje i prowadzi do przy\u0142\u0105czenia si\u0119 do tego, co niskie i ni\u017csze, gdzie porusza si\u0119 diabe\u0142. Grzech prowadzi was do zaparcia si\u0119 mojego Boskiego Syna, a to jest bardzo powa\u017cne, bo skutkiem tego jest zaparcie si\u0119 wiecznego zbawienia, je\u015bli nie b\u0119dziecie pokutowa\u0107. Grzech to wej\u015bcie na niebezpieczny teren tego, co zakazane i niew\u0142a\u015bciwe, gdzie dusza cierpi. Posiadacie woln\u0105 wol\u0119 i widz\u0119, jak tak wiele Moich dzieci z g\u0142upoty popada ci\u0105gle w ten sam grzech, m\u00f3wi\u0105: \"Jestem wolny, wolno\u015b\u0107 jest moja\" i w ten spos\u00f3b pogr\u0105\u017caj\u0105 si\u0119 w md\u0142awych wodach grzechu, z kt\u00f3rych nie wychodz\u0105 z powodu pychy, z powodu z\u0142ego u\u017cycia wolnej woli. Nawr\u00f3\u0107 si\u0119! Zastan\u00f3w si\u0119, jaki jeste\u015b, co robisz, jak reagujesz, jak jeste\u015b z bra\u0107mi, jak post\u0119pujesz i jak si\u0119 zachowujesz. Dzieci, ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest w niebezpiecze\u0144stwie, a bez nawr\u00f3cenia jeste\u015bcie \u0142atwym \u0142upem dla z\u0142a. Nadchodz\u0105 wielkie zmiany! Przybywaj\u0105 modernizmy, kt\u00f3re niszcz\u0105 duchowo\u015b\u0107 moich dzieci, prowadz\u0105c je do zdrady mojego Syna. Jest tak wielu, kt\u00f3rzy uwa\u017caj\u0105 si\u0119 za m\u0105drych, \u017ce w ko\u0144cu s\u0105 g\u0142upi i popadaj\u0105 w pod\u0142o\u015b\u0107. Istnieje pilna potrzeba zmiany w ludzko\u015bci, aby nie zosta\u0142a oszukana. Stworzenie ludzkie jest w ci\u0105g\u0142ym nawr\u00f3ceniu z piln\u0105 potrzeb\u0105 ci\u0105g\u0142ego obmywania z grzechu. Wzywam was po raz pierwszy do umocnienia si\u0119 jako lud mojego Syna postem, modlitw\u0105, Eucharysti\u0105 i braterstwem. Jako Matka chcia\u0142abym m\u00f3wi\u0107 wam tylko o wielko\u015bci Nieba, ale w tej chwili musz\u0119 m\u00f3wi\u0107 o tym, co si\u0119 zbli\u017ca i mo\u017ce doprowadzi\u0107 was do upadku. W tym \"ju\u017c\" musicie si\u0119 zmieni\u0107 i przygotowa\u0107 si\u0119 do bycia zupe\u0142nie nowymi stworzeniami. Przemoc wzrasta wobec niezgody ludzko\u015bci, wywo\u0142uj\u0105c chaos w tym czy innym kraju. Dlatego wzywam was do adorowania mojego Boskiego Syna, do modlitwy i do braterstwa. Nie uda wam si\u0119 da\u0107 tego, czego nie nosicie w sobie. Moje dzieci, musicie \u017cy\u0107 w adoracji mojego Syna, aby\u015bcie mogli przekaza\u0107 to swoim braciom i siostrom, zanim b\u0119dzie za p\u00f3\u017ano. Umi\u0142owany ludzie mojego Syna, to jest czas, aby podnie\u015b\u0107 wasze serca do mojego Syna, oddzielenie si\u0119 od mojego Syna uniemo\u017cliwia wam rozeznanie. Nadchodzi wi\u0119cej chor\u00f3b, kt\u00f3re nie s\u0105 Bosk\u0105 Wol\u0105, ale \u017ale u\u017cyt\u0105 nauk\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 i korzystajcie z tego, co zosta\u0142o wam wskazane. B\u0105d\u017acie braterscy i nie dopuszczajcie do spor\u00f3w.... Jedno\u015b\u0107 jest pilna. Kto \u017cyje w sporze, znajdzie si\u0119 sam przed niebezpiecze\u0144stwem z\u0142a. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, przyjd\u017acie na moje \u0142ono. Pozostaj\u0119 z ludem mojego Syna. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, ja was chroni\u0119. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":7,"month_string":"June","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, the Church of Peter will also be much attacked from within, how many are the traitors! even among those who were called to vocational ministry but are now betraying my Son. My children, the war will continue and will take many countries, pray for France and Italy, they will be the ones who will suffer many losses.  Pray for America, for a good part of it will be wiped out. Children, I ask you to always look at God's light, even when everything will be more difficult, never lose hope. Pray for those whose hearts are closed, that they may be saved during the Warning, the times are getting closer. Pray, for even the worst of sinners may be saved before the King of kings. Children, be careful, famine will spread quickly, as will other coming diseases. Children, never barter your souls for a piece of bread, listen to my words. My children, all this pain will stop, but now we need your courage as soldiers of light shouting the truth, never be afraid, I am here to protect you. Watch the weather changes, from strong heat there will be strong cold, from tornadoes there will be strong hail, get used to the changes, for they will be manifold. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, die Kirche von Peter, wird auch von innen sehr angegriffen, wie viele sind die Verr\u00e4ter! Sogar unter denjenigen, die zum Berufsministerium gerufen wurden, aber jetzt meinen Sohn verraten. Meine Kinder, der Krieg wird fortgesetzt und viele L\u00e4nder nehmen, f\u00fcr Frankreich und Italien beten, sie werden diejenigen sein, die viele Verluste erleiden. Bete f\u00fcr Amerika, f\u00fcr einen Gro\u00dfteil davon wird es ausgel\u00f6scht. Kinder, ich bitte Sie, immer Gottes Licht zu betrachten, auch wenn alles schwieriger wird, niemals die Hoffnung verlieren. Beten Sie f\u00fcr diejenigen, deren Herzen geschlossen sind, damit sie w\u00e4hrend der Warnung gerettet werden k\u00f6nnen. Die Zeiten kommen sich n\u00e4her. Beten Sie, denn selbst die schlimmsten S\u00fcnder k\u00f6nnen vor dem K\u00f6nig der K\u00f6nige gerettet werden. Kinder, sei vorsichtig, die Hungersnot wird sich schnell ausbreiten, ebenso wie andere kommende Krankheiten. Kinder, tauschte niemals deine Seelen f\u00fcr ein St\u00fcck Brot, h\u00f6r auf meine Worte. Meine Kinder, all diese Schmerzen werden aufh\u00f6ren, aber jetzt brauchen wir Ihren Mut als Lichtsoldaten, die die Wahrheit schreien, haben Sie niemals Angst, ich bin hier, um Sie zu besch\u00fctzen. Beobachten Sie, wie sich die Wetter\u00e4nderungen durch starke Hitze \u00e4ndern, es wird stark kalt sein, von Tornados wird starker Hagel geben, sich an die Ver\u00e4nderungen gew\u00f6hnt, denn sie werden vielf\u00e4ltig sein. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, la Iglesia de Pietro tambi\u00e9n estar\u00e1n muy apegados desde el interior, \u00a1cu\u00e1ntos traidores son! Incluso entre los que han sido llamados a la vocaci\u00f3n, pero que ahora traicionan a mi hijo. Los ni\u00f1os, la guerra continuar\u00e1 y tomar\u00e1n muchos pa\u00edses, rezar\u00e1n por Francia e Italia, ser\u00e1n aquellos que sufren muchas p\u00e9rdidas. Ore por Am\u00e9rica, porque una buena parte ser\u00e1 cancelada. Ni\u00f1os, les pido que siempre miren la luz de Dios, incluso cuando todo es m\u00e1s dif\u00edcil, nunca pierda la esperanza. Ore por aquellos que tienen corazones cerrados, para que puedan salvarse durante la advertencia, los tiempos se est\u00e1n acercando. Ore, porque incluso lo peor de los pecadores podr\u00eda salvarse frente al rey de los reyes, ten cuidado, la hambruna se extender\u00e1 r\u00e1pidamente, as\u00ed como otras enfermedades. Ni\u00f1os, nunca intercambian tu alma por un pedazo de pan, escuchen mis palabras. Mis hijos, todo este dolor se detendr\u00e1, pero ahora necesitamos su coraje de soldados de luz que gritan la verdad, nunca tienes miedo, estoy aqu\u00ed para protegerte. Mire las variaciones clim\u00e1ticas, con un calor fuerte que habr\u00e1 un resfriado fuerte, desde el Tornadi, pasar\u00e1 a la fuerte granizo, se acostumbrar\u00e1 a los cambios, porque ser\u00e1n m\u00faltiples. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, l'\u00e9glise de Peter seront \u00e9galement tr\u00e8s attaqu\u00e9s de l'int\u00e9rieur, combien sont les tra\u00eetres! M\u00eame parmi ceux qui ont \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9s au minist\u00e8re professionnel mais trahissent maintenant mon fils. Mes enfants, la guerre continueront et prendront de nombreux pays, prieront pour la France et l'Italie, ce seront eux qui subiront de nombreuses pertes. Priez pour l'Am\u00e9rique, pour une bonne partie de cela sera an\u00e9anti. Enfants, je vous demande de toujours regarder la lumi\u00e8re de Dieu, m\u00eame lorsque tout sera plus difficile, ne perdez jamais espoir. Priez pour ceux dont le c\u0153ur est ferm\u00e9, afin qu'ils soient sauv\u00e9s pendant l'avertissement, les temps se rapprochent. Priez, m\u00eame pour le pire des p\u00e9cheurs, il peut \u00eatre sauv\u00e9 devant le roi des rois. Enfants, soyez prudent, la famine se propagera rapidement, tout comme les autres maladies \u00e0 venir. Enfants, ne troctez jamais vos \u00e2mes pour un morceau de pain, \u00e9coutez mes mots. Mes enfants, toute cette douleur s'arr\u00eateront, mais maintenant nous avons besoin de votre courage en tant que soldats de lumi\u00e8re criant la v\u00e9rit\u00e9, n'ayez jamais peur, je suis ici pour vous prot\u00e9ger. Regardez les changements m\u00e9t\u00e9orologiques, \u00e0 feu fort, il y aura un fort froid, des tornades il y aura une forte gr\u00eale, s'habituera aux changements, car ils seront multiples. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, la Chiesa Di Pietro sar\u00e0 molto attaccata anche dall\u2019interno, quanti sono i traditori! anche tra coloro che sono stati chiamati alla vocazione, ma che adesso tradiscono mio Figlio. Figli, la guerra continuer\u00e0 e prender\u00e0 molti paesi, pregate per la Francia e per l\u2019Italia, saranno coloro che subiranno molte perdite.  Pregate per l\u2019America, perch\u00e9 sar\u00e0 cancellata una buona parte di essa. Figli, vi chiedo di guardare sempre la luce di Dio, anche quando tutto sar\u00e0 pi\u00f9 difficile, non perdete mai la speranza. Pregate per coloro che hanno i cuori chiusi, affinch\u00e9 possano essere salvati durante l\u2019Avvertimento, i tempi sono sempre pi\u00f9 vicini. Pregate, perch\u00e9 anche i peggiori dei peccatori potrebbero salvarsi davanti al Re dei Re. Figli, fate attenzione, la carestia si diffonder\u00e0 velocemente, cos\u00ec come altre malattie in arrivo. Figli, non barattate mai la vostra anima per un pezzo di pane, ascoltate le mie parole. Figli miei, tutto questo dolore smetter\u00e0, ma adesso abbiamo bisogno del vostro coraggio di soldati di luce che urlano la verit\u00e0, non abbiate mai paura, Io sono qui per proteggervi. Guardate le variazioni climatiche, dal forte caldo ci sar\u00e0 un forte freddo, dai tornadi si passer\u00e0 alla forte grandine, abituatevi ai cambiamenti, perch\u00e9 saranno molteplici. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen","text_pl":"Dzieci moje, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 Piotrowy b\u0119dzie r\u00f3wnie\u017c mocno atakowany od wewn\u0105trz, jak wielu jest zdrajc\u00f3w, nawet w\u015br\u00f3d tych, kt\u00f3rzy zostali powo\u0142ani, a teraz zdradzaj\u0105 mojego Syna. Dzieci moje, wojna b\u0119dzie trwa\u0142a i zajmie wiele kraj\u00f3w, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Francj\u0119 i W\u0142ochy, to one ponios\u0105 wiele strat. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ameryk\u0119, bo zostanie zmieciona z powierzchni ziemi. Dzieci moje, prosz\u0119 was, aby\u015bcie zawsze patrzyli na Bo\u017ce \u015awiat\u0142o, nawet gdy wszystko b\u0119dzie trudniejsze, nigdy nie tra\u0107cie nadziei. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za tych, kt\u00f3rych serca s\u0105 zamkni\u0119te, aby zostali zbawieni w czasie Ostrze\u017cenia, bo czasy si\u0119 zbli\u017caj\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, aby nawet najgorsi grzesznicy mogli zosta\u0107 zbawieni przed Kr\u00f3lem kr\u00f3l\u00f3w. Dzieci, strze\u017ccie si\u0119, g\u0142\u00f3d b\u0119dzie si\u0119 szybko rozprzestrzenia\u0142, podobnie jak inne nadchodz\u0105ce choroby. Moje dzieci, nie przehandlujcie waszych dusz za kawa\u0142ek chleba, s\u0142uchajcie moich s\u0142\u00f3w. Moje dzieci, ca\u0142y ten b\u00f3l si\u0119 sko\u0144czy, ale teraz potrzebujemy waszej odwagi jako \u017co\u0142nierzy \u015bwiat\u0142a, kt\u00f3rzy wykrzykuj\u0105 prawd\u0119, nigdy si\u0119 nie b\u00f3jcie, jestem tu, aby was chroni\u0107. Obserwuj zmiany klimatyczne: od silnych upa\u0142\u00f3w do silnego zimna, od tornad do silnego gradu, przyzwyczajaj si\u0119 do zmian, bo b\u0119dzie ich wiele. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, a Igreja de Pedro tamb\u00e9m ser\u00e3o muito atacados por dentro, quantos s\u00e3o os traidores! Mesmo entre os que foram chamados ao minist\u00e9rio profissional, mas agora est\u00e3o traindo meu filho. Meus filhos, a guerra continuar\u00e1 e levar\u00e1 muitos pa\u00edses, orar\u00e3o pela Fran\u00e7a e pela It\u00e1lia, ser\u00e3o os que sofrer\u00e3o muitas perdas. Ore pela Am\u00e9rica, pois boa parte disso ser\u00e1 eliminada. Filhos, pe\u00e7o que voc\u00ea sempre olhe para a luz de Deus, mesmo quando tudo ser\u00e1 mais dif\u00edcil, nunca perca a esperan\u00e7a. Ore por aqueles cujos cora\u00e7\u00f5es est\u00e3o fechados, para que possam ser salvos durante o aviso, os tempos est\u00e3o se aproximando. Ore, pois mesmo os piores dos pecadores podem ser salvos diante do rei dos reis. Crian\u00e7as, tenha cuidado, a fome se espalhar\u00e1 rapidamente, assim como outras doen\u00e7as pr\u00f3ximas. Filhos, nunca trocam suas almas por um peda\u00e7o de p\u00e3o, ou\u00e7a minhas palavras. Meus filhos, toda essa dor vai parar, mas agora precisamos da sua coragem como soldados de luz gritando a verdade, nunca tenha medo, estou aqui para proteg\u00ea -lo. Observe as mudan\u00e7as clim\u00e1ticas, do calor forte, haver\u00e1 um frio forte, de tornados, haver\u00e1 granizo forte, se acostumar com as mudan\u00e7as, pois elas ser\u00e3o m\u00faltiplas. Agora deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5f7c\u5f97\u6559\u5802\u4e5f\u5c06\u4ece\u5185\u90e8\u53d7\u5230\u5f88\u591a\u653b\u51fb\uff0c\u53db\u5f92\u6709\u591a\u5c11\uff01\u5373\u4f7f\u5728\u90a3\u4e9b\u88ab\u53ec\u5524\u5230\u804c\u4e1a\u4e8b\u5de5\u4f46\u73b0\u5728\u80cc\u53db\u6211\u513f\u5b50\u7684\u4eba\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6218\u4e89\u5c06\u7ee7\u7eed\u5e76\u5e26\u8d70\u8bb8\u591a\u56fd\u5bb6\uff0c\u4e3a\u6cd5\u56fd\u548c\u610f\u5927\u5229\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u5c06\u662f\u5c06\u906d\u53d7\u8bb8\u591a\u635f\u5931\u7684\u56fd\u5bb6\u3002\u4e3a\u7f8e\u56fd\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5176\u4e2d\u7684\u5f88\u5927\u4e00\u90e8\u5206\u5c06\u88ab\u6d88\u706d\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u8981\u4f60\u603b\u662f\u770b\u7740\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u5149\uff0c\u5373\u4f7f\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u4f1a\u66f4\u52a0\u56f0\u96be\uff0c\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u4f1a\u5931\u53bb\u5e0c\u671b\u3002\u4e3a\u90a3\u4e9b\u5c01\u95ed\u5fc3\u7075\u7684\u4eba\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5728\u8b66\u544a\u671f\u95f4\u53ef\u4ee5\u4fdd\u5b58\u4ed6\u4eec\uff0c\u65f6\u4ee3\u8d8a\u6765\u8d8a\u8fd1\u3002\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5373\u4f7f\u662f\u6700\u7cdf\u7cd5\u7684\u7f6a\u4eba\uff0c\u4e5f\u53ef\u4ee5\u5c06\u5176\u4fdd\u5b58\u5728\u56fd\u738b\u56fd\u738b\u9762\u524d\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u8981\u5c0f\u5fc3\uff0c\u9965\u8352\u4f1a\u50cf\u5176\u4ed6\u5373\u5c06\u5230\u6765\u7684\u75be\u75c5\u4e00\u6837\u8fc5\u901f\u4f20\u64ad\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u8981\u628a\u4f60\u7684\u7075\u9b42\u6362\u6210\u4e00\u5757\u9762\u5305\uff0c\u542c\u6211\u7684\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6240\u6709\u8fd9\u4e9b\u75db\u82e6\u90fd\u4f1a\u505c\u6b62\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4eec\u9700\u8981\u60a8\u7684\u52c7\u6c14\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u58eb\u5175\u558a\u7740\u771f\u76f8\uff0c\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u6211\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u4fdd\u62a4\u60a8\u3002\u89c2\u770b\u5929\u6c14\u53d8\u5316\uff0c\u4ece\u6d53\u70c8\u7684\u70ed\u91cf\u4e2d\u4f1a\u6709\u5f3a\u70c8\u7684\u611f\u5192\uff0c\u9f99\u5377\u98ce\u5c06\u6709\u5f3a\u70c8\u7684\u51b0\u96f9\uff0c\u4e60\u60ef\u53d8\u5316\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5b83\u4eec\u5c06\u662f\u591a\u79cd\u591a\u6837\u7684\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7ed9\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":11,"month_string":"June","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. Beloved children, pray for the Church, for many bishops are against each other because of power. Communism is advancing, it will also enter the Church and you still do not understand.  Many of my children will come from everywhere, because the famine is advancing. America will make the news. My children, you have free will, but you are using it very badly and it does not mean doing whatever you want even sinning, feed yourselves on the Holy Gospel and the Eucharist. My children, I now bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Geliebte Kinder beten f\u00fcr die Kirche, denn viele Bisch\u00f6fe sind wegen Macht gegeneinander. Der Kommunismus f\u00e4hrt vor, er wird auch in die Kirche eintreten und Sie verstehen immer noch nicht. Viele meiner Kinder werden von \u00fcberall kommen, weil die Hungersnot vorrang. Amerika wird die Nachrichten machen. Meine Kinder, Sie haben einen freien Willen, aber Sie verwenden ihn sehr schlecht und es bedeutet nicht, dass Sie das tun, was Sie auch s\u00fcndigen m\u00f6chten, sich auf das heilige Evangelium und die Eucharistie f\u00fcttern. Meine Kinder, ich segne dich jetzt im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Amados a los ni\u00f1os, rezan por la iglesia, porque muchos obispos est\u00e1n uno contra el otro por el poder. El comunismo avanza, tambi\u00e9n entrar\u00e1 en la iglesia y a\u00fan no lo entiende. Muchos de mis hijos vendr\u00e1n de todos los lugares, porque la hambruna avanza. Estados Unidos har\u00e1 que la gente hable de s\u00ed misma. Mis hijos, tienes libre albedr\u00edo, pero lo est\u00e1s usando muy mal y no significa hacer todo lo que quieres pecar, alimentar el Santo Evangelio y la Eucarist\u00eda. Ni\u00f1os, ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Les enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, prient pour l'\u00e9glise, car de nombreux \u00e9v\u00eaques sont les uns contre les autres \u00e0 cause du pouvoir. Le communisme avance, il entrera \u00e9galement dans l'\u00e9glise et vous ne comprenez toujours pas. Beaucoup de mes enfants viendront de partout, car la famine avance. L'Am\u00e9rique fera la nouvelle. Mes enfants, vous avez le libre arbitre, mais vous l'utilisez tr\u00e8s mal et cela ne signifie pas faire ce que vous voulez m\u00eame p\u00e9cher, vous nourrir du Saint \u00c9vangile et de l'Eucharistie. Mes enfants, je vous b\u00e9nis maintenant au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli amati, pregate per la Chiesa, perch\u00e9 molti vescovi sono uno contro l\u2019altro a causa del potere. Il comunismo sta avanzando, entrer\u00e0 anche nella Chiesa e voi ancora non capite.  Molti dei miei figli arriveranno da ogni luogo, perch\u00e9 la carestia avanza. L\u2019America far\u00e0 parlare di s\u00e9. Figli miei, voi avete il libero arbitrio, ma lo state usando molto male e non significa far tutto ci\u00f2 che si vuole anche peccando, cibatevi del Santo Vangelo e dell\u2019Eucaristia. Figli, ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, poniewa\u017c wielu biskup\u00f3w z \u017c\u0105dzy w\u0142adzy wyst\u0119puje przeciwko sobie. Komunizm post\u0119puje, wkroczy tak\u017ce do Ko\u015bcio\u0142a, a wy nadal tego nie rozumiecie. Wiele z moich dzieci przyb\u0119dzie ze wszystkich stron, poniewa\u017c g\u0142\u00f3d jest coraz wi\u0119kszy. Ameryka da o sobie zna\u0107. Dzieci moje, macie woln\u0105 wol\u0119, ale bardzo \u017ale z niej korzystacie - nie polega ona na post\u0119powaniu wed\u0142ug w\u0142asnego uznania, cz\u0119sto prowadz\u0105cego do grzechu, lecz na karmieniu si\u0119 \u015bwi\u0119t\u0105 Ewangeli\u0105 i Eucharysti\u0105. Dzieci moje, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was teraz w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Crian\u00e7as amadas, orem pela igreja, pois muitos bispos est\u00e3o um contra o outro por causa do poder. O comunismo est\u00e1 avan\u00e7ando, tamb\u00e9m entrar\u00e1 na igreja e voc\u00ea ainda n\u00e3o entende. Muitos dos meus filhos vir\u00e3o de todos os lugares, porque a fome est\u00e1 avan\u00e7ando. A Am\u00e9rica far\u00e1 as not\u00edcias. Meus filhos, voc\u00ea tem livre arb\u00edtrio, mas voc\u00ea o est\u00e1 usando muito mal e isso n\u00e3o significa fazer o que quiser, mesmo pecar, alimente -se com o Santo Evangelho e a Eucaristia. Meus filhos, agora eu aben\u00e7oo voc\u00ea em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u8bb8\u591a\u4e3b\u6559\u7531\u4e8e\u6743\u529b\u800c\u5f7c\u6b64\u53cd\u5bf9\u3002\u5171\u4ea7\u4e3b\u4e49\u6b63\u5728\u53d1\u5c55\uff0c\u5b83\u4e5f\u5c06\u8fdb\u5165\u6559\u4f1a\uff0c\u60a8\u4ecd\u7136\u4e0d\u4e86\u89e3\u3002\u6211\u7684\u8bb8\u591a\u5b69\u5b50\u90fd\u4f1a\u6765\u81ea\u4efb\u4f55\u5730\u65b9\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u9965\u8352\u6b63\u5728\u53d1\u5c55\u3002\u7f8e\u56fd\u5c06\u53d1\u5e03\u65b0\u95fb\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u60a8\u6709\u81ea\u7531\u610f\u5fd7\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u60a8\u975e\u5e38\u7cdf\u7cd5\u5730\u4f7f\u7528\u5b83\uff0c\u8fd9\u5e76\u4e0d\u610f\u5473\u7740\u8981\u505a\u4efb\u4f55\u60a8\u60f3\u72af\u7f6a\u7684\u4e8b\u60c5\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u517b\u6d3b\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u798f\u97f3\u548c\u5723\u4f53\u5723\u4e8b\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u73b0\u5728\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":11,"month_string":"June","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My children, I am so tired, but so tired, too much wickedness. Here is the time of the antichrist, he will always tease you. My children, do not be hypocrites, love me, really love each other and forgive. The dark night is coming, those who will be with me will be with me forever. I put you in your places and my counting begins now; you are not ready yet but unless you have abandoned all that is of the world, you will never be able to enter my Kingdom. Pray children, pray much. My traitors, in My Church, continue to inflict Me, continue to harm Me, they are fighting for power, they have not understood that I am the only One who can decide all actions. Ah! this free choice how they are playing it. Oh! My daughter, you must be more tenacious, be tougher, explain to them that the times are over, but do not grieve because I am with you. They do not believe My prophecies and My Mother's prophecies, they do not believe, but how will they do when the dark night comes and all is fulfilled, whom will they ask for help? So many will convert, but so many will die, they will be afraid, they have not understood that I am your everything, your God. I am here and I am watching you, listening to you and scanning your hearts. My children, be like brothers, be united, give comfort to those in need, comfort each other, huddle together as one family in my name, but you must stand together, soon the worst will come, but do you not understand that without me all will be lost? I bless you, think, reflect and meditate on my words! I bless you children, be warriors, never get down, my Holy Spirit will enter each of you to be stronger, to give you strength and peace. I love you all, one by one. I bless you, always, in the name of the Father, in my Most Holy Name and the Holy Spirit. My children, I give you a caress as you pass, one by one, you will feel the breath of the Spirit and understand that I am here.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, ich bin so m\u00fcde, aber so m\u00fcde, zu viel Bosheit. Hier ist die Zeit des Antichristen, er wird Sie immer \u00e4rgern. Meine Kinder, sind keine Heuchler, lieben mich, lieben sich wirklich und vergib. Die dunkle Nacht kommt, diejenigen, die mit mir sein werden, werden f\u00fcr immer bei mir sein. Ich habe dich an deine Orte gesetzt und mein Z\u00e4hlen beginnt jetzt; Sie sind noch nicht bereit, aber wenn Sie nicht alles aufgegeben haben, was von der Welt ist, werden Sie niemals in mein K\u00f6nigreich eintreten k\u00f6nnen. Bete Kinder, bete viel. Meine Verr\u00e4ter in meiner Kirche verursachen mich weiterhin, schaden mir weiterhin, sie k\u00e4mpfen um Macht, sie haben nicht verstanden, dass ich der einzige bin, der alle Aktionen entscheiden kann. Ah! Diese kostenlose Wahl, wie sie es spielen. Oh! Meine Tochter, du musst hartn\u00e4ckiger sein, h\u00e4rter sein, ihnen erkl\u00e4ren, dass die Zeiten vorbei sind, aber nicht trauern, weil ich bei dir bin. Sie glauben nicht, dass meine Prophezeiungen und die Prophezeiungen meiner Mutter nicht glauben, aber wie werden sie es tun, wenn die dunkle Nacht kommt und alles erf\u00fcllt ist, wen werden sie um Hilfe bitten? So viele werden konvertieren, aber so viele werden sterben, sie werden Angst haben, sie haben nicht verstanden, dass ich dein Alles bin, dein Gott. Ich bin hier und beobachte dich, h\u00f6re dir zu und scanne deine Herzen. Meine Kinder, seien wie Br\u00fcder, sind vereint, tr\u00f6sten den Bed\u00fcrftigen, tr\u00f6sten sich gegenseitig, dr\u00e4ngeln Sie sich als eine Familie in meinem Namen, aber Sie m\u00fcssen zusammen stehen, bald wird der Schlimmste kommen, aber verstehen Sie das nicht ohne mich Alles wird verloren gehen? Ich segne dich, denke, reflektiere und meditiere \u00fcber meine Worte! Ich segne dich, Kinder, sei Krieger, stieg niemals runter, mein Heiliger Geist wird in jeden von euch eintreten, um st\u00e4rker zu sein, um dir Kraft und Frieden zu geben. Ich liebe euch alle nacheinander.Ich segne dich immer im Namen des Vaters in meinem heiligsten Namen und des Heiligen Geistes. Meine Kinder, ich gebe dir eine Liebkosung, w\u00e4hrend du nacheinander vorbeikommst, du wirst den Atem des Geistes sp\u00fcren und verstehen, dass ich hier bin.","text_es":"Mis hijos, estoy tan cansado, pero tan cansado, demasiada maldad. Aqu\u00ed est\u00e1 el momento del Anticristo, \u00e9l siempre te burlar\u00e1 de ti. Mis hijos, no sean hip\u00f3critas, \u00e1mame, \u00e1mame a ti mismo y perd\u00f3nate a ti mismo. La noche oscura est\u00e1 llegando, quien estar\u00e1 conmigo ser\u00e1 para siempre. Te pongo en tus lugares y ahora comienzo mi cuenta; Todav\u00eda no est\u00e1s listo, pero, si no has abandonado todo lo que est\u00e1 en el mundo, nunca puedes entrar en mi reino. Ore a los ni\u00f1os, reza mucho. Mis traidores, en mi iglesia, contin\u00faan infligi\u00e9ndome, contin\u00faan lastim\u00e1ndome, est\u00e1n luchando por el poder, no han entendido que yo sea el \u00fanico que pueda decidir sobre todas las acciones. \u00a1Ah! Esta libre elecci\u00f3n como si lo estuvieran jugando. \u00a1Vaya! Mi hija, tienes que ser m\u00e1s tenaz, ser m\u00e1s dif\u00edcil, expl\u00edcales que los tiempos han terminado, pero no para estar triste porque estoy contigo. No creen en mis profec\u00edas y en las de mi madre, no creen, pero c\u00f3mo lo har\u00e1n cuando llegue la noche oscura y todo se lograr\u00e1, \u00bfqui\u00e9n pedir\u00e1 ayuda? Muchos se convertir\u00e1n, pero muchos morir\u00e1n, tendr\u00e1n miedo, no han entendido que yo soy tu todo, tu Dios. Estoy aqu\u00ed y te miro, te escucho y sacud\u00ed tus corazones.Mis hijos, sean como hermanos, est\u00e9n unidos, dan consuelo a aquellos que se necesitan, consuelan unos a otros, se apriden como una sola familia a mi nombre, pero tienes que estar unidos, pronto vendr\u00e1 lo peor, pero no entiendes que sin m\u00ed ser\u00e1 todo perdido? \u00a1Te bendigo, pienso, reflexiono y medito en mis palabras! Bendices a los ni\u00f1os, seas guerreros, nunca te rompes, mi Esp\u00edritu Santo entrar\u00e1 a cada uno de ustedes para ser m\u00e1s fuertes, para darte fuerza y \u200b\u200bpaz. Los amo a todos, uno por uno. Te bendices, siempre, en el nombre del Padre, en mi Santo Nombre y el Esp\u00edritu Santo. Mis hijos, les doy una caricia que pasa, uno por uno, sentir\u00e1s el aliento del esp\u00edritu y entender\u00e1s que estoy aqu\u00ed.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, je suis tellement fatigu\u00e9, mais tellement fatigu\u00e9, trop de m\u00e9chancet\u00e9. Voici le moment de l'Ant\u00e9christ, il vous taquinera toujours. Mes enfants, ne soyez pas hypocrites, aiment-moi, s'aiment vraiment et pardonnent. La nuit noire arrive, ceux qui seront avec moi seront avec moi pour toujours. Je vous ai mis \u00e0 votre place et mon comptage commence maintenant; Vous n'\u00eates pas encore pr\u00eat, mais \u00e0 moins que vous n'ayez abandonn\u00e9 tout ce qui est du monde, vous ne pourrez jamais entrer dans mon royaume. Priez les enfants, priez beaucoup. Mes tra\u00eetres, dans mon \u00e9glise, continuent de m'infliger, continuent de me faire du mal, ils se battent pour le pouvoir, ils n'ont pas compris que je suis le seul \u00e0 pouvoir d\u00e9cider toutes les actions. Ah! Ce libre choix comment ils jouent. Oh! Ma fille, vous devez \u00eatre plus tenace, \u00eatre plus difficile, expliquez-leur que les temps sont termin\u00e9s, mais ne pleurent pas parce que je suis avec vous. Ils ne croient pas mes proph\u00e9ties et les proph\u00e9ties de ma m\u00e8re, ils ne croient pas, mais comment feront-ils lorsque la nuit sombre arrivera et que tout sera accompli, qui demanderont-ils de l'aide? Beaucoup convertiront, mais tant de gens mourront, ils auront peur, ils n'ont pas compris que je suis tout votre Dieu. Je suis ici et je vous regarde, vous \u00e9coute et scanne vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, soyez comme des fr\u00e8res, soyez unis, rendez le r\u00e9confort \u00e0 ceux qui en ont besoin, r\u00e9confortez-vous, se blottissent ensemble en une seule famille en mon nom, mais vous devez vous tenir ensemble, bient\u00f4t le pire viendra, mais ne comprenez-vous pas cela sans moi Tout sera perdu? Je vous b\u00e9nis, pensez, r\u00e9fl\u00e9chissez et m\u00e9dite sur mes mots! Je vous b\u00e9nis les enfants, soyez des guerriers, ne descendez jamais, mon Saint-Esprit entrera chacun de vous pour \u00eatre plus fort, pour vous donner de la force et de la paix. Je t'aime tous, un par un.Je vous b\u00e9nis, toujours, au nom du P\u00e8re, dans mon plus saint nom et le Saint-Esprit. Mes enfants, je vous donne une caresse pendant que vous passez, un par un, vous ressentirez le souffle de l'esprit et vous comprendrez que je suis ici.","text_it":"Figli miei, sono cos\u00ec stanco, ma cos\u00ec stanco, troppa cattiveria. Ecco questo \u00e8 il momento dell\u2019anticristo, vi stuzzicher\u00e0 sempre. Figli miei, non siate ipocriti, amatemi, amatevi per davvero e perdonate. La notte buia sta arrivando, chi sar\u00e0 con me lo sar\u00e0 per sempre. Io vi metto ai vostri posti e inizia ora la mia conta; voi non siete pronti ancora ma, se non avrete abbandonato tutto ci\u00f2 che \u00e8 del mondo, non potrete mai entrare nel mio Regno. Pregate figli, pregate tanto. I miei traditori, nella mia Chiesa, continuano ad infliggermi, continuano a farmi del male, stanno lottando per il potere, non hanno capito che Io sono l\u2019unico che pu\u00f2 decidere di tutte le azioni. Ah! questa libera scelta come se la stanno giocando. Oh! Figlia mia, devi essere pi\u00f9 tenace, sii pi\u00f9 dura, spiega loro che i tempi sono finiti, ma non rattristarti perch\u00e9 Io sono con te. Non credono alle mie profezie e a quelle di mia Madre, non credono, ma come faranno quando arriver\u00e0 la notte buia e tutto sar\u00e0 compiuto, a chi chiederanno aiuto? Tanti si convertiranno, ma tanti moriranno, avranno paura, non hanno capito che Io sono il vostro tutto, il vostro Dio. Io sono qui e vi guardo, vi ascolto e scruto i vostri cuori. Figli miei, siate come fratelli, siate uniti, date conforto a chi ha bisogno, confortatevi a vicenda, stringetevi come un\u2019unica famiglia nel mio nome, ma dovete stare uniti, presto arriver\u00e0 il peggio, ma non capite che senza di me sar\u00e0 tutto perduto? Vi benedico, pensate, riflettete e meditate le mie parole! Vi benedico figli, siate guerrieri, non abbattetevi mai, il mio Spirito Santo entrer\u00e0 in ognuno di voi per essere pi\u00f9 forti, per darvi la forza e la pace. Vi amo tutti, uno per uno. Vi benedico, sempre, nel nome del Padre, nel mio Santissimo Nome e dello Spirito Santo. Figli miei, vi do una carezza passando, uno per uno, sentirete il soffio dello Spirito e capirete che Io sono qui.","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, jestem tak zm\u0119czony, tak zm\u0119czony, zbyt wiele niegodziwo\u015bci. To jest czas antychrysta, on zawsze b\u0119dzie wam przeszkadza\u0142. Moje dzieci, nie b\u0105d\u017acie hipokrytami, kochajcie mnie, kochajcie siebie naprawd\u0119 i przebaczajcie. Nadchodzi noc ciemna, ci, kt\u00f3rzy b\u0119d\u0105 ze Mn\u0105, b\u0119d\u0105 ze Mn\u0105 na zawsze. Umie\u015bci\u0142em was na waszych miejscach i teraz zaczyna si\u0119 moje odliczanie; nie jeste\u015bcie jeszcze gotowi, ale je\u015bli nie porzucili\u015bcie wszystkiego, co jest ze \u015bwiata, nigdy nie b\u0119dziecie mogli wej\u015b\u0107 do mojego Kr\u00f3lestwa. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 mocno. Zdrajcy, w moim Ko\u015bciele, nadal mnie atakuj\u0105, nadal mnie krzywdz\u0105, walcz\u0105 o w\u0142adz\u0119, nie zrozumieli, \u017ce tylko ja mog\u0119 decydowa\u0107 o wszystkich dzia\u0142aniach. Ach! Ten wolny wyb\u00f3r, jak oni to rozgrywaj\u0105. C\u00f3rko moja, musisz by\u0107 wytrwalsza, mocniejsza, wyt\u0142umacz im, \u017ce te czasy si\u0119 sko\u0144czy\u0142y, ale nie smu\u0107 si\u0119, bo Ja jestem z tob\u0105. Nie wierz\u0105 w moje proroctwa i proroctwa mojej Matki, nie wierz\u0105, ale jak post\u0105pi\u0105, gdy nadejdzie ciemna noc i wszystko si\u0119 spe\u0142ni, do kogo zwr\u00f3c\u0105 si\u0119 o pomoc? Wielu si\u0119 nawr\u00f3ci, ale wielu umrze, b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 ba\u0107, nie zrozumieli, \u017ce Ja jestem waszym Wszystkim, waszym Bogiem. Jestem tu i patrz\u0119 na was, s\u0142ucham was i badam wasze serca. Dzieci moje, b\u0105d\u017acie jak bracia, b\u0105d\u017acie zjednoczeni, dawajcie pociech\u0119 potrzebuj\u0105cym, pocieszajcie si\u0119 nawzajem, tulcie si\u0119 do siebie jak jedna rodzina w moje imi\u0119, ale musicie by\u0107 zjednoczeni, wkr\u00f3tce nadejdzie najgorsze, ale czy nie rozumiecie, \u017ce beze mnie wszystko b\u0119dzie stracone? B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, my\u015blcie, rozwa\u017cajcie i medytujcie nad moimi s\u0142owami! B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, moje dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie wojownikami, nigdy nie dajcie si\u0119 pokona\u0107, m\u00f3j Duch \u015awi\u0119ty wejdzie w ka\u017cdego z was, aby\u015bcie byli silniejsi, aby da\u0107 wam si\u0142\u0119 i pok\u00f3j. Kocham was wszystkich. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was zawsze w imi\u0119 Ojca, w moje Naj\u015bwi\u0119tsze Imi\u0119 i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego. Moje dzieci, gdy b\u0119dziecie przechodzi\u0107, przytul\u0119 ka\u017cdego z was, poczujecie tchnienie Ducha i zrozumiecie, \u017ce jestem tutaj.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, estou t\u00e3o cansado, mas t\u00e3o cansado, muita maldade. Aqui est\u00e1 a hora do Anticristo, ele sempre o provocar\u00e1. Meus filhos, n\u00e3o s\u00e3o hip\u00f3critas, me amam, realmente se amam e perdoam. A noite sombria est\u00e1 chegando, aqueles que estar\u00e3o comigo estar\u00e3o comigo para sempre. Eu coloquei voc\u00ea em seus lugares e minha contagem come\u00e7a agora; Voc\u00ea ainda n\u00e3o est\u00e1 pronto, mas, a menos que tenha abandonado tudo o que \u00e9 do mundo, nunca poder\u00e1 entrar no meu reino. Ore para crian\u00e7as, ore muito. Meus traidores, em minha igreja, continuam a me infligir, continuam a me prejudicar, est\u00e3o lutando pelo poder, eles n\u00e3o entenderam que eu sou o \u00fanico que pode decidir todas as a\u00e7\u00f5es. Ah! Esta escolha livre como eles est\u00e3o jogando. Oh! Minha filha, voc\u00ea deve ser mais tenaz, ser mais dif\u00edcil, explicar a eles que os tempos acabaram, mas n\u00e3o sofrem porque estou com voc\u00ea. Eles n\u00e3o acreditam nas minhas profecias e profecias de minha m\u00e3e, n\u00e3o acreditam, mas como eles se sair\u00e3o quando a noite escura chegar e tudo for cumprido, a quem pedir\u00e3o ajuda? Muitos se converter\u00e3o, mas muitos morrer\u00e3o, ter\u00e3o medo, n\u00e3o entenderam que eu sou seu tudo, seu Deus. Estou aqui e estou te observando, ouvindo voc\u00ea e examinando seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, sejam como irm\u00e3os, se unam, d\u00e3o conforto aos que precisam, confortem -se, se amontoam como uma fam\u00edlia em meu nome, mas voc\u00ea deve ficar juntos, em breve o pior vir\u00e1, mas voc\u00ea n\u00e3o entende isso sem mim Tudo ser\u00e1 perdido? Eu te aben\u00e7oo, pense, reflita e medite em minhas palavras! Eu aben\u00e7oo voc\u00eas, filhos, sejam guerreiros, nunca descendo, meu Esp\u00edrito Santo entrar\u00e1 em cada um de voc\u00eas para ser mais forte, para lhe dar for\u00e7a e paz. Eu amo todos voc\u00eas, um por um.Eu te aben\u00e7oo, sempre, em nome do Pai, no meu nome mais santo e no Esp\u00edrito Santo. Meus filhos, eu te dou uma car\u00edcia \u00e0 medida que voc\u00ea passa, um a um, voc\u00ea sentir\u00e1 o sopro do esp\u00edrito e entender\u00e1 que estou aqui.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u5f88\u7d2f\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u592a\u7d2f\u4e86\uff0c\u592a\u90aa\u6076\u4e86\u3002\u8fd9\u662f\u654c\u57fa\u7763\u8005\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\uff0c\u4ed6\u5c06\u6c38\u8fdc\u53d6\u7b11\u4f60\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u505a\u4f2a\u541b\u5b50\uff0c\u7231\u6211\uff0c\u771f\u7684\u5f7c\u6b64\u76f8\u7231\uff0c\u5bbd\u6055\u3002\u6f06\u9ed1\u7684\u591c\u665a\u5373\u5c06\u5230\u6765\uff0c\u90a3\u4e9b\u4f1a\u548c\u6211\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u7684\u4eba\u5c06\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0e\u6211\u540c\u5728\u3002\u6211\u628a\u4f60\u653e\u5728\u4f60\u7684\u4f4d\u7f6e\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u8ba1\u6570\u73b0\u5728\u5f00\u59cb\u4e86\u3002\u60a8\u8fd8\u6ca1\u6709\u51c6\u5907\u597d\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u9664\u975e\u60a8\u653e\u5f03\u4e86\u6240\u6709\u4e16\u754c\uff0c\u5426\u5219\u60a8\u5c06\u6c38\u8fdc\u65e0\u6cd5\u8fdb\u5165\u6211\u7684\u738b\u56fd\u3002\u7948\u7977\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u5f88\u591a\u3002\u6211\u7684\u53db\u5f92\u5728\u6211\u7684\u6559\u4f1a\u4e2d\u7ee7\u7eed\u9020\u6210\u6211\u7684\u884c\u4e3a\uff0c\u7ee7\u7eed\u4f24\u5bb3\u6211\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u6b63\u5728\u4e89\u53d6\u6743\u529b\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e0d\u660e\u767d\u6211\u662f\u552f\u4e00\u53ef\u4ee5\u51b3\u5b9a\u6240\u6709\u884c\u52a8\u7684\u4eba\u3002\u554a!\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u73a9\u6cd5\u5982\u4f55\u3002\u54e6\uff01\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u4f60\u5fc5\u987b\u66f4\u52a0\u987d\u5f3a\uff0c\u66f4\u575a\u5f3a\uff0c\u5411\u4ed6\u4eec\u89e3\u91ca\u65f6\u4ee3\u5df2\u7ecf\u8fc7\u53bb\u4e86\uff0c\u4f46\u4e0d\u8981\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u548c\u4f60\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u800c\u611f\u5230\u60b2\u4f24\u3002\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e0d\u76f8\u4fe1\u6211\u7684\u9884\u8a00\u548c\u6211\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u9884\u8a00\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e0d\u76f8\u4fe1\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u5f53\u9ed1\u6697\u7684\u591c\u665a\u5230\u6765\u5e76\u4e14\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u5f97\u5230\u6ee1\u8db3\u65f6\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u5982\u4f55\u5bfb\u6c42\u5e2e\u52a9\uff1f\u8fd9\u4e48\u591a\u4eba\u4f1aconvert\u4f9d\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u5f88\u591a\u4eba\u4f1a\u6b7b\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e0d\u660e\u767d\u6211\u662f\u4f60\u7684\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u4f60\u7684\u4e0a\u5e1d\u3002\u6211\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\uff0c\u6211\u5728\u770b\u7740\u4f60\uff0c\u542c\u4f60\u8bf4\u5e76\u626b\u63cf\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u50cf\u5144\u5f1f\u4e00\u6837\uff0c\u56e2\u7ed3\u8d77\u6765\uff0c\u4e3a\u6709\u9700\u8981\u7684\u4eba\u611f\u5230\u5b89\u6170\uff0c\u4e92\u76f8\u5b89\u6170\uff0c\u4ee5\u6211\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u6324\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u4f60\u5fc5\u987b\u7ad9\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\uff0c\u5f88\u5feb\uff0c\u6700\u7cdf\u7cd5\u7684\u60c5\u51b5\u5c31\u4f1a\u5230\u6765\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u4f60\u4e0d\u660e\u767d\u6ca1\u6709\u6211\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u4f1a\u4e22\u5931\u5417\uff1f\u6211\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u601d\u8003\uff0c\u53cd\u601d\u548c\u51a5\u60f3\u6211\u7684\u8bdd\uff01\u6211\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6210\u4e3a\u6218\u58eb\uff0c\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u4f1a\u4e0b\u6765\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5723\u7075\u5c06\u8fdb\u5165\u4f60\u4eec\u6bcf\u4e2a\u4eba\uff0c\u4ee5\u4f7f\u60a8\u66f4\u52a0\u575a\u5f3a\uff0c\u7ed9\u60a8\u529b\u91cf\u4e0e\u548c\u5e73\u3002\u6211\u7231\u4f60\u4eec\uff0c\u4e00\u4e2a\u4eba\u4e00\u4e2a\u3002\u6211\u603b\u662f\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u4ee5\u6211\u6700\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u540d\u5b57\u548c\u5723\u7075\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5f53\u4f60\u901a\u8fc7\u65f6\uff0c\u6211\u7ed9\u4f60\u4e00\u4e2a\u7231\u629a\u7684\u4eba\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u611f\u53d7\u5230\u7cbe\u795e\u7684\u547c\u5438\uff0c\u5e76\u4e86\u89e3\u6211\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":12,"month_string":"June","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: live under the Divine Will, so the work and act will be according to the provisions of our King and not to the provisions of the worldly powers. As prince of the celestial legions, I ask you to surrender all your work and actions at every moment to our King and Lord Jesus Christin reparation for the offenses of humanity and for the salvation of souls. The more that join this offering, the stronger and higher the wall is and the more resistant it is to the attacks of the devil. They are happy to know in advance what heaven expects and desires from its children... They are happy to know where they should conduct themselves and pray for it, thus they remain within the Divine Will. When the moment shortens, evil becomes more present and visible within humanity in various ways. This has happened in the history of mankind. At this time, the devil and his minions have embedded themselves within the institutions of society, blackening them and giving them a turn far removed from the divine will. As prince of the celestial legions, I call on you to unite in prayer so that the intensity of the great earthquake that will soon occur on earth, at the points where great tectonic faults converge, may be reduced. I call you to pray the holy rosary for 7 days and to worship our King and Lord Jesus Christ present in the most blessed sacrament of the altar. These acts of love are offered by: all mankind blinded by the devil, by human creature\u2019s sick in body or spirit and for faith to be firm in each child of God. This way of praying will combat evil and will unite the children of God in brotherhood, strengthening faith and trust in Divine Protection. Beloved children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: to you I speak, to you who have heard and have closed your ears like the majority of humanity, to you who have been instructed by the Kingdom of God and refuse to understand, I\u2019m talking to you... They are faced with the scourge of food, economic, love of neighbour, charity and lack of faith. Urge children of our Queen and Mother! It urges that the people of God be prepared in the spirit and in the material. The big countries will be crucified and the small countries will suffer. They must store according to the possibilities of each one, they must be discreet so that they do not fall prey to the wolves. Pray people of God, pray for Argentina, the agitation of society arrives, its soil is shaken. Pray people of God, pray for Chile, its soil shakes strongly. Pray for Central America, it shakes, pray. Pray for the unfortunate events in the United States. Pray children of God, pray for Japan, its soil shakes. Pray people of God, pray for Spain, it is shaken. Pray people of God, France is gripped by terror. Pray people of God, pray for all humanity so that faith prevails and fear does not take hold of any child of the people of God. With my sword raised, I rout the minions of evil and protect the people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ as I have been ordered. Continue in unity, without going back, praying, children, praying, without harming your neighbour and being messengers of love. I bless you, protect you and summon you in the love of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Saint Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: \u017cyj zgodnie z Wol\u0105 Bo\u017c\u0105, aby praca i dzia\u0142anie by\u0142y zgodne z postanowieniami naszego Kr\u00f3la, a nie z postanowieniami pot\u0119g \u015bwiatowych. Jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 legion\u00f3w niebieskich prosz\u0119 was, aby\u015bcie w ka\u017cdej chwili oddawali wszystkie swoje prace i dzia\u0142ania naszemu Kr\u00f3lowi i Panu Jezusowi Chrystusowi w zado\u015b\u0107uczynieniu za przewinienia ludzko\u015bci i dla zbawienia dusz. Im wi\u0119cej os\u00f3b przy\u0142\u0105czy si\u0119 do tego ofiarowania, tym silniejszy i wy\u017cszy jest mur i tym bardziej odporny na ataki diab\u0142a. Ciesz\u0105 si\u0119, \u017ce z g\u00f3ry wiedz\u0105, czego niebo oczekuje i pragnie od swoich dzieci... Ciesz\u0105 si\u0119, \u017ce wiedz\u0105, gdzie powinni si\u0119 zachowa\u0107 i modl\u0105 si\u0119 o to, w ten spos\u00f3b pozostaj\u0105 w obr\u0119bie Woli Bo\u017cej. Gdy moment si\u0119 skraca, z\u0142o staje si\u0119 obecne i widoczne w ludzko\u015bci na r\u00f3\u017cne sposoby. Tak dzia\u0142o si\u0119 w historii ludzko\u015bci. W obecnym czasie diabe\u0142 i jego s\u0142ugusy osadzili si\u0119 w instytucjach spo\u0142ecznych, zaciemniaj\u0105c je i nadaj\u0105c im obr\u00f3t daleki od Boskiej woli. Jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 niebia\u0144skich legion\u00f3w wzywam was do zjednoczenia si\u0119 w modlitwie, aby zmniejszy\u0107 intensywno\u015b\u0107 wielkiego trz\u0119sienia ziemi, kt\u00f3re wkr\u00f3tce nast\u0105pi na ziemi, w punktach, gdzie zbiegaj\u0105 si\u0119 wielkie uskoki tektoniczne. Wzywam was do odmawiania przez 7 dni r\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ca \u015bwi\u0119tego i oddawania czci naszemu Kr\u00f3lowi i Panu Jezusowi Chrystusowi obecnemu w naj\u015bwi\u0119tszym sakramencie o\u0142tarza. Te akty mi\u0142o\u015bci ofiaruj\u0119: za ca\u0142\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107 za\u015blepion\u0105 przez diab\u0142a, za ludzkie stworzenia chore na ciele lub duchu oraz za wiar\u0119, aby by\u0142a mocna w ka\u017cdym dziecku Bo\u017cym. Ten spos\u00f3b modlitwy zwalczy z\u0142o i zjednoczy dzieci Bo\u017ce w braterstwie, umacniaj\u0105c wiar\u0119 i ufno\u015b\u0107 w Bo\u017c\u0105 Opiek\u0119. Umi\u0142owane dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: do was m\u00f3wi\u0119, do was, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0142yszeli\u015bcie i zamkn\u0119li\u015bcie uszy jak wi\u0119kszo\u015b\u0107 ludzko\u015bci, do was, kt\u00f3rzy zostali\u015bcie pouczeni o Kr\u00f3lestwie Bo\u017cym i odmawiacie zrozumienia, m\u00f3wi\u0119 do was... Stoj\u0105 przed nimi plagi \u017cywno\u015bciowe, ekonomiczne, mi\u0142o\u015bci bli\u017aniego, mi\u0142osierdzia i braku wiary. Przynagla dzieci naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki! Wzywa, aby lud Bo\u017cy by\u0142 przygotowany duchowo i materialnie. Wielkie kraje zostan\u0105 ukrzy\u017cowane, a ma\u0142e kraje b\u0119d\u0105 cierpie\u0107. Musz\u0105 magazynowa\u0107 wed\u0142ug mo\u017cliwo\u015bci ka\u017cdego z nich, musz\u0105 by\u0107 dyskretne, aby nie pa\u015b\u0107 ofiar\u0105 wilk\u00f3w. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludzie Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Argentyn\u0119, nadchodzi wzburzenie spo\u0142ecze\u0144stwa, jej ziemia jest wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119ta. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Chile, jego ziemia mocno si\u0119 trz\u0119sie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ameryk\u0119 \u015arodkow\u0105, ona si\u0119 trz\u0119sie, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za niefortunne wydarzenia w Stanach Zjednoczonych. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci Bo\u017ce, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Japoni\u0119, jej ziemia si\u0119 trz\u0119sie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Hiszpani\u0119, ona jest wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119ta. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludu Bo\u017cy, Francja jest ogarni\u0119ta terrorem. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za ca\u0142\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107, aby wiara zwyci\u0119\u017cy\u0142a i strach nie ogarn\u0105\u0142 \u017cadnego dziecka ludu Bo\u017cego. Z podniesionym mieczem rozprawiam si\u0119 ze s\u0142ugami z\u0142a i chroni\u0119 lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, jak mi nakazano. Trwajcie w jedno\u015bci, bez cofania si\u0119, modl\u0105c si\u0119, dzieci, modl\u0105c si\u0119, nie krzywdz\u0105c bli\u017aniego i b\u0119d\u0105c pos\u0142a\u0144cami mi\u0142o\u015bci. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, chroni\u0119 i przyzywam w mi\u0142o\u015bci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":14,"month_string":"June","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts.  My children, how beautiful you are when you kneel in prayer. Listen to what I have to say, do not be distracted by my messages, remember that they are for the salvation of mankind. You have eyes to look but do not see, ears to listen and do not hear. My children, pray for France, she will suffer much. Convert!!!  Now I leave you with my motherly blessing, in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, wie sch\u00f6n du bist, wenn du im Gebet knien. H\u00f6ren Sie sich an, was ich zu sagen habe, lassen Sie sich nicht von meinen Nachrichten abgelenkt, denken Sie daran, dass sie f\u00fcr die Errettung der Menschheit sind. Sie haben Augen zu schauen, sehen aber nicht, Ohren zuzuh\u00f6ren und nicht zu h\u00f6ren. Meine Kinder, beten f\u00fcr Frankreich, sie wird viel leiden. Konvertieren!!! Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen, im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Ni\u00f1os, ya que eres hermosa cuando te arrodillas en oraci\u00f3n. Escucha lo que tengo que decirte, no te distraigas de mis mensajes, recuerda que son para la salvaci\u00f3n de la humanidad. Tienes ojos para mirar, pero no ves, o\u00eddos para escuchar y no escuchar. Mis hijos, rezan por Francia, sufrir\u00e1n mucho. Convertir !! Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna, en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, comme vous \u00eates belle lorsque vous vous agenouillez dans la pri\u00e8re. \u00c9coutez ce que j'ai \u00e0 dire, ne soyez pas distrait par mes messages, n'oubliez pas qu'ils sont pour le salut de l'humanit\u00e9. Vous avez des yeux \u00e0 regarder mais ne voyez pas, les oreilles \u00e0 \u00e9couter et n'entendez pas. Mes enfants, prient pour la France, elle souffrira beaucoup. Convertir!!! Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore.  Figli, come siete belli quando vi inginocchiate nella preghiera. Ascoltate ci\u00f2 che ho da dirvi, non distraetevi dai miei messaggi, ricordate che sono per la salvezza dell\u2019umanit\u00e0. Avete occhi per guardare, ma non vedete, orecchie per ascoltare e non udite. Figli miei, pregate per la Francia, patir\u00e0 molto. Convertitevi!!  Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna, nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Dzieci moje, jak\u017ce jeste\u015bcie pi\u0119kne, gdy kl\u0119kacie do modlitwy. S\u0142uchajcie tego, co mam wam do powiedzenia, nie roztrz\u0105sajcie moich or\u0119dzi, pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce s\u0105 one dla zbawienia ludzko\u015bci. Macie oczy do patrzenia, ale nie widzicie, uszy do s\u0142uchania, a nie s\u0142yszycie. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Francj\u0119, bo ona b\u0119dzie wiele cierpie\u0107. Nawr\u00f3\u0107 si\u0119! Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem, w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, como voc\u00ea \u00e9 linda quando voc\u00ea se ajoelha em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Ou\u00e7a o que tenho a dizer, n\u00e3o se distraia com minhas mensagens, lembre -se de que elas s\u00e3o pela salva\u00e7\u00e3o da humanidade. Voc\u00ea tem olhos para olhar, mas n\u00e3o v\u00ea, ouvidos para ouvir e n\u00e3o ouvir. Meus filhos, oram pela Fran\u00e7a, ela sofrer\u00e1 muito. Converter!!! Agora deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna, em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5f53\u4f60\u8dea\u4e0b\u7948\u7977\u65f6\uff0c\u4f60\u591a\u4e48\u7f8e\u4e3d\u3002\u542c\u6211\u8bf4\u7684\u8bdd\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u88ab\u6211\u7684\u4fe1\u606f\u5206\u6563\u6ce8\u610f\u529b\uff0c\u8bf7\u8bb0\u4f4f\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u662f\u4e3a\u4e86\u62ef\u6551\u4eba\u7c7b\u3002\u60a8\u6709\u773c\u775b\u53ef\u4ee5\u770b\uff0c\u4f46\u770b\u4e0d\u5230\uff0c\u8033\u6735\u542c\uff0c\u542c\u4e0d\u5230\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e3a\u6cd5\u56fd\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5979\u4f1a\u906d\u53d7\u5f88\u591a\u75db\u82e6\u3002\u5151\u6362\uff01\uff01\uff01\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7ed9\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":18,"month_string":"June","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: receive the blessing that our King constantly showers upon each one. You are beloved of our Queen and Mother of the End Times.... You are so beloved that her Divine Son sends his Angel of Peace to accompany you, to open the way for you and to keep you attentive to the Law of God so that you will not be lost. Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ with love, faith and obedience have come to my call of the seven days of prayer for the good of humanity. They forget that without prayer the human creature is empty. Without prayer with the heart and soul, the creature is hesitant before the temptations of evil, being easy prey to the devil and his machinations. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: fraternity among the children of God is paramount and unity is necessary in the face of the onslaught of evil that desires to destroy and separate the works of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Human creatures call themselves bearers of 'divine gifts' in order to divide the children of God so that they may stray from the true path. Our King and Lord Jesus Christ calls you to unity. Understand that what is coming is not a time of rain or wind or darkness or trembling? You have failed to digest that what is coming are the strongest trials and the strongest shocks that humanity has faced in this generation. How can we bring them to understand with reason and spirit that what is coming is written! It is not the end of the world, no! What will they do when faced with these moments they look at themselves and see that they despised the truth, did not believe it and did not prepare themselves in the spirit nor in what heaven has indicated to them! Do you expect long times? You are wrong. Do not fall into the clutches of evil at this most critical time for mankind! Famine is spreading and with it a shortage of the essentials for the human creature. The economy falls in the world and man enters into chaos in the absence of the money god to whom they have given their security. Children of our Queen and Mother of the last times, the wheat will be separated from the tares and the tares will persecute the wheat. Do not fear, after the trial, the wheat will rise again with greater strength, it will be enlightened by the love of its King and Lord Jesus Christ. Be on your spiritual alert! Watch the wolves in sheep's clothing lead the people of God into the spiritual abyss and accept it with such weakness and coldness that you may wake up as part of the tares. The children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ must be spiritual in order not to be deceived. When mourning enters the House of God, they must maintain spiritual fortitude and not be led astray. That is what the devil desires, that the sheep be scattered. Do not allow it. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: pray, pray in the face of despair, uprisings and persecution. Pray, pray people of God that human creatures will heed my call to prayer. Pray people of God, pray for Mexico, its soil is shaking with force. Pray, people of God, pray for the conversion of humanity and for all human creatures to accept as Mother the one who is the Mother of the word. Without fear, continue with firm steps and in haste. Continue to hope without despairing, but trusting in the Trinitarian Will. You are loved; therefore, I bring you words of eternal life calling you to conversion. Come! Enter the true path, the one that leads you to the encounter with our King and Lord Jesus Christ. I protect you; I bless you. Do not fall prey to fear. My heavenly legions keep you protected. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: przyjmijcie b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo, kt\u00f3re nasz Kr\u00f3l nieustannie zsy\u0142a na ka\u017cdego. Jeste\u015bcie umi\u0142owani przez nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119 Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych.... Jeste\u015bcie tak umi\u0142owani, \u017ce Jej Boski Syn posy\u0142a swojego Anio\u0142a Pokoju, aby wam towarzyszy\u0142, aby otwiera\u0142 wam drog\u0119 i aby\u015bcie byli uwa\u017cni na Prawo Bo\u017ce, aby\u015bcie si\u0119 nie zgubili. Umi\u0142owany lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, wiar\u0105 i pos\u0142usze\u0144stwem przyszed\u0142 na moje wezwanie siedmiu dni modlitwy dla dobra ludzko\u015bci. Zapomnieli, \u017ce bez modlitwy stworzenie ludzkie jest puste. Bez modlitwy sercem i dusz\u0105, stworzenie waha si\u0119 przed pokusami z\u0142a, b\u0119d\u0105c \u0142atwym \u0142upem diab\u0142a i jego machinacji. Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: braterstwo w\u015br\u00f3d dzieci Bo\u017cych jest najwa\u017cniejsze i jedno\u015b\u0107 jest konieczna w obliczu naporu z\u0142a, kt\u00f3re pragnie zniszczy\u0107 i rozdzieli\u0107 dzie\u0142a naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Ludzkie stworzenia nazywaj\u0105 si\u0119 nosicielami \"boskich dar\u00f3w\", aby podzieli\u0107 dzieci Bo\u017ce, by mog\u0142y zboczy\u0107 z prawdziwej drogi. Nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus wzywa was do jedno\u015bci. Zrozumcie, \u017ce to, co nadchodzi, nie jest czasem deszczu ani wiatru, ani ciemno\u015bci, ani dr\u017cenia? Nie przetrawili\u015bcie tego, \u017ce to, co nadchodzi, to najsilniejsze pr\u00f3by i najsilniejsze wstrz\u0105sy, jakie spotka\u0142y ludzko\u015b\u0107 w tym pokoleniu. Jak mo\u017cemy doprowadzi\u0107 ich do zrozumienia rozumem i duchem, \u017ce to, co nadchodzi, jest napisane! To nie jest koniec \u015bwiata, nie! Co zrobi\u0105, gdy w obliczu tych chwil spojrz\u0105 na siebie i zobacz\u0105, \u017ce wzgardzili prawd\u0105, nie uwierzyli jej i nie przygotowali si\u0119 w duchu ani w tym, co wskaza\u0142o im niebo! Czy spodziewacie si\u0119 d\u0142ugich czas\u00f3w? Jeste\u015bcie w b\u0142\u0119dzie. Nie wpadnijcie w szpony z\u0142a w tym najbardziej krytycznym dla ludzko\u015bci czasie! Rozprzestrzenia si\u0119 g\u0142\u00f3d, a wraz z nim niedob\u00f3r podstawowych rzeczy dla ludzkiego stworzenia. Na \u015bwiecie upada gospodarka i cz\u0142owiek wchodzi w chaos pod nieobecno\u015b\u0107 boga pieni\u0105dza, kt\u00f3remu oddali swoje bezpiecze\u0144stwo. Dzieci naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki czas\u00f3w ostatecznych, pszenica b\u0119dzie oddzielona od k\u0105kolu, a k\u0105kol b\u0119dzie prze\u015bladowa\u0142 pszenic\u0119. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, po pr\u00f3bie pszenica powstanie ponownie z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 si\u0142\u0105, b\u0119dzie o\u015bwiecona mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 swojego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. B\u0105d\u017acie w swojej duchowej czujno\u015bci! Obserwujcie, jak wilki w owczej sk\u00f3rze prowadz\u0105 lud Bo\u017cy w duchow\u0105 otch\u0142a\u0144 i przyjmuj\u0105 j\u0105 z tak\u0105 s\u0142abo\u015bci\u0105 i ozi\u0119b\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, \u017ce mo\u017cecie obudzi\u0107 si\u0119 jako cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 k\u0105kolu. Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa musz\u0105 by\u0107 duchowe, aby nie da\u0107 si\u0119 zwie\u015b\u0107. Kiedy \u017ca\u0142oba wchodzi do Domu Bo\u017cego, musz\u0105 zachowa\u0107 duchowy hart ducha i nie da\u0107 si\u0119 sprowadzi\u0107 na manowce. To jest to, czego diabe\u0142 pragnie, aby owce by\u0142y rozproszone. Nie pozw\u00f3lcie na to. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: m\u00f3dl si\u0119, m\u00f3dl si\u0119 w obliczu rozpaczy, powsta\u0144 i prze\u015bladowa\u0144. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludzie Bo\u017cy, aby ludzkie stworzenia wys\u0142ucha\u0142y mojego wezwania do modlitwy. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Meksyk, jego ziemia dr\u017cy z si\u0142\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 o nawr\u00f3cenie ludzko\u015bci i o to, aby wszystkie stworzenia ludzkie przyj\u0119\u0142y za Matk\u0119 T\u0119, kt\u00f3ra jest Matk\u0105 S\u0142owa. Bez l\u0119ku, kontynuujcie zdecydowanymi krokami i z po\u015bpiechem. Trwajcie w nadziei, nie rozpaczaj\u0105c, lecz ufaj\u0105c w Wol\u0119 Trynitarn\u0105. Jeste\u015bcie kochani; dlatego przynosz\u0119 wam s\u0142owa \u017cycia wiecznego wzywaj\u0105ce was do nawr\u00f3cenia. Przyjd\u017acie! Wejd\u017a na prawdziw\u0105 drog\u0119, t\u0119, kt\u00f3ra prowadzi ci\u0119 do spotkania z naszym Kr\u00f3lem i Panem Jezusem Chrystusem. Chroni\u0119 was; b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Nie padnijcie ofiar\u0105 strachu. Moje niebia\u0144skie legiony strzeg\u0105 ci\u0119. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":21,"month_string":"June","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for being here in prayer and for bending your knees. Daughter, you have to tell the priests that their confusion is between the heart and the mouth, so they are bringing confusion among My children and they still do not understand that the Transubstantiation of the bread and wine, happens with the Consecration and the descent of the Holy Spirit who transforms into Body and Blood and Divinity. My children, pray much, for the earth is a vast desert and where there will be water, it will cause much damage. Children, my angels sing their lament because my Son Jesus is torn with pain, pray and love my Jesus and remember that he died for you and to free you from sin. The Bishop of Rome will be attacked by the very people who support him. Now I bless you, in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie hier im Gebet sind und sich die Knie beugen. Tochter, man muss den Priestern sagen, dass ihre Verwirrung zwischen Herz und Mund ist, also bringen sie Verwirrung unter meinen Kindern und verstehen immer noch nicht, dass die Transsubstantiation von Brot und Wein mit der Weihe und dem Abstieg der Fall ist Der Heilige Geist, der sich in K\u00f6rper, Blut und G\u00f6ttlichkeit verwandelt. Meine Kinder beten viel, denn die Erde ist eine riesige W\u00fcste und wo es Wasser gibt, wird es viel Schaden verursachen. Kinder, meine Engel singen ihre Klage, weil mein Sohn Jesus vor Schmerz gerissen ist, beten und lieben meinen Jesus und denken Sie daran, dass er f\u00fcr Sie gestorben ist und Sie von der S\u00fcnde befreien. Der Bischof von Rom wird von genau den Menschen angegriffen, die ihn unterst\u00fctzen. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por haber doblado las rodillas. Hija, debes decirle a los sacerdotes que su confusi\u00f3n es entre el coraz\u00f3n y la boca, por lo que est\u00e1n trayendo la confusi\u00f3n entre mis hijos y a\u00fan no entienden que la transubstanciaci\u00f3n del pan y el vino tiene lugar con la consagraci\u00f3n y el descenso de la santa. Esp\u00edritu que se transforma en cuerpo, sangre y divinidad. Mis hijos, rezan mucho, porque la tierra es un desierto inmenso y donde habr\u00e1 agua, esto causar\u00e1 mucho da\u00f1o. Ni\u00f1os, mis \u00e1ngeles cantan su lamento porque mi hijo Jes\u00fas est\u00e1 desgarrado por el dolor, rezan y aman a mi Jes\u00fas y recuerda que muri\u00f3 por ti y para deshacerse del pecado. El obispo de Roma ser\u00e1 atacado por quienes lo apoyan. Ahora los bendiga, en el nombre del Padre, del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re et d'avoir pli\u00e9 vos genoux. Fille, vous devez dire aux pr\u00eatres que leur confusion est entre le c\u0153ur et la bouche, alors ils apportent de la confusion parmi mes enfants et ils ne comprennent toujours pas que la transubstanciation du pain et du vin, se produit avec la cons\u00e9cration et la descente de la descente de Le Saint-Esprit qui se transforme en corps, sang et divinit\u00e9. Mes enfants, prient beaucoup, car la terre est un vaste d\u00e9sert et l\u00e0 o\u00f9 il y aura de l'eau, cela causera beaucoup de d\u00e9g\u00e2ts. Enfants, mes anges chantent leur lamentation parce que mon fils J\u00e9sus est d\u00e9chir\u00e9 de douleur, prie et aime mon J\u00e9sus et se souviens qu'il est mort pour vous et de vous lib\u00e9rer du p\u00e9ch\u00e9. L'\u00e9v\u00eaque de Rome sera attaqu\u00e9 par les personnes m\u00eames qui le soutiennent. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia.  Figlia, devi dire ai sacerdoti che la loro confusione \u00e8 tra il cuore e la bocca, cos\u00ec stanno portando la confusione tra i miei figli e ancora non capiscono che la transustanziazione del pane e del vino, avviene con la Consacrazione e la discesa dello Spirito Santo che trasforma in corpo e sangue e divinit\u00e0. Figli miei, pregate tanto, perch\u00e9 la terra \u00e8 un deserto immenso e dove ci sar\u00e0 l\u2019acqua, questa causer\u00e0 molti danni. Figli, i miei angeli cantano il loro lamento perch\u00e9 mio Figlio Ges\u00f9 \u00e8 straziato dal dolore, pregate e amate il mio Ges\u00f9 e ricordate che \u00e8 morto per voi e per liberarvi dal peccato. Il Vescovo di Roma sar\u00e0 attaccato proprio da coloro che lo sostengono. Ora vi benedico, nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj na modlitwie i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie. C\u00f3rko, musisz powiedzie\u0107 ksi\u0119\u017com, \u017ce ich zam\u0119t jest mi\u0119dzy sercem a ustami, dlatego wprowadzaj\u0105 zam\u0119t w\u015br\u00f3d moich dzieci i nadal nie rozumiej\u0105, \u017ce Przeistoczenie chleba i wina dokonuje si\u0119 podczas konsekracji i zst\u0105pienia Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, kt\u00f3ry przemienia je w Cia\u0142o i Krew i B\u00f3stwo. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 mocno, bo ziemia jest ogromn\u0105 pustyni\u0105 i tam, gdzie jest woda, wyrz\u0105dzi ona wiele szk\u00f3d. Moje dzieci, moi anio\u0142owie \u015bpiewaj\u0105 sw\u00f3j lament, poniewa\u017c m\u00f3j Syn Jezus jest rozdarty b\u00f3lem, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 i kochajcie mojego Jezusa i pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce umar\u0142 za was, aby uwolni\u0107 was od grzechu. Biskup Rzymu b\u0119dzie atakowany w\u0142a\u015bnie przez tych, kt\u00f3rzy go popieraj\u0105. Teraz ja was b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por dobrar os joelhos. Filha, voc\u00ea deve dizer aos padres que a confus\u00e3o deles est\u00e1 entre o cora\u00e7\u00e3o e a boca, ent\u00e3o eles est\u00e3o trazendo confus\u00e3o entre meus filhos e eles ainda n\u00e3o entendem que a transubstancia\u00e7\u00e3o do p\u00e3o e do vinho acontece com a consagra\u00e7\u00e3o e a descida de O Esp\u00edrito Santo que se transforma em corpo, sangue e divindade. Meus filhos, oram muito, pois a terra \u00e9 um vasto deserto e onde haver\u00e1 \u00e1gua, causar\u00e1 muitos danos. Filhos, meus anjos cantam seu lamento porque meu filho Jesus est\u00e1 rasgado de dor, ore e ame meu Jesus e lembre -se de que ele morreu por voc\u00ea e para libert\u00e1 -lo do pecado. O bispo de Roma ser\u00e1 atacado pelas mesmas pessoas que o apoiam. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo, em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\u5e76\u5f2f\u8170\u3002\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u60a8\u5fc5\u987b\u544a\u8bc9\u7267\u5e08\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u6df7\u4e71\u662f\u5728\u5fc3\u810f\u548c\u5634\u4e4b\u95f4\u5723\u7075\u8f6c\u53d8\u4e3a\u8eab\u4f53\uff0c\u8840\u6db2\u548c\u795e\u6027\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u5f88\u591a\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5730\u7403\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u5e7f\u9614\u7684\u6c99\u6f20\uff0c\u90a3\u91cc\u4f1a\u6709\u6c34\uff0c\u8fd9\u4f1a\u9020\u6210\u5f88\u5927\u7684\u7834\u574f\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5929\u4f7f\u5531\u7740\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u54c0\u53f9\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u88ab\u75db\u82e6\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u548c\u7231\u6211\u7684\u8036\u7a23\u6495\u88c2\uff0c\u5e76\u8bb0\u4f4f\u4ed6\u4e3a\u4f60\u800c\u6b7b\uff0c\u4f7f\u4f60\u6446\u8131\u7f6a\u6076\u3002\u7f57\u9a6c\u4e3b\u6559\u5c06\u53d7\u5230\u652f\u6301\u4ed6\u7684\u4eba\u7684\u653b\u51fb\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":23,"month_string":"June","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: receive from the Sacred Hearts blessing and fortitude for those who wish to accept them. A great part of humanity remains inert in the light of the calls of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. These calls will regain value in human memory when the events which have been enumerated unfold one after the other in front of humanity. Humanity's disobedience is the weapon of the devil with which he succeeds in making man rise up against the most Holy Trinity. In these times, disobedience will be almost total. Man does not wish to be subject to anything and proclaims his free will, leading him to sink into his vanity, pride and liberalism. I have to tell you that whoever does not change their works and actions in the direction of fraternity, will fall prey to darkness. Pride, selfishness, arrogance and superiority are small tentacles with which the devil is causing excessive damage and I, as prince of the armies of heaven, will not allow the people of my King and Lord Jesus Christ to be undermined. The Holy Spirit pours out his gifts and virtues on the humble so that they would preach the word, not on the proud so that they would exalt their free will. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, the day of prayer that I requested of you has reached the paternal throne like precious incense. I must share with you that each day of prayer has been completely pleasing to God and has succeeded in attenuating to some extent the great earthquake that humanity is going to suffer. Without wishing to upset you, I must tell you that the coming events will occur one after another without respite. Earthquakes will be of greater intensity, causing the earth to lose its compact state and high mountains to collapse. People of our lord and king Jesus Christ, the country represented by the bear will react unexpectedly, causing the world to remain anxious, and making some countries react hastily. When you hear an unknown rumbling, do not leave your homes or places where you are; do not leave until you receive orders to move. If a strong and unknown glow appears, do not look at it; on the contrary, keep your head to the ground and do not look until the glow disappears, and do not move from the place where you are. Store food inside your homes, without forgetting water, blessed grapes, the sacramentals and what is necessary for the small altar that at a certain moment you were asked to prepare in your homes. Attention, beloved people of God, attention. Remain attentive to the persistence of evil that wants to make you fall. Do not succumb! I defend you with my sword. Do not fear. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: przyjmij od Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszych Serc b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo i m\u0119stwo dla tych, kt\u00f3rzy zechc\u0105 je przyj\u0105\u0107. Wielka cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 ludzko\u015bci pozostaje oboj\u0119tna wobec wezwa\u0144 naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Wezwania te odzyskaj\u0105 warto\u015b\u0107 w pami\u0119ci ludzkiej, gdy wydarzenia, kt\u00f3re zosta\u0142y wyliczone, b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 rozwija\u0107 jedno po drugim przed ludzko\u015bci\u0105. Niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwo ludzko\u015bci jest broni\u0105 diab\u0142a, za pomoc\u0105 kt\u00f3rej udaje mu si\u0119 sk\u0142oni\u0107 cz\u0142owieka do powstania przeciwko Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej. W tych czasach niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwo b\u0119dzie prawie ca\u0142kowite. Cz\u0142owiek nie chce by\u0107 niczemu poddany i g\u0142osi swoj\u0105 woln\u0105 wol\u0119, co prowadzi go do pogr\u0105\u017cenia si\u0119 w swojej pr\u00f3\u017cno\u015bci, pychy i liberalizmu. Musz\u0119 wam powiedzie\u0107, \u017ce kto nie zmieni swoich uczynk\u00f3w i dzia\u0142a\u0144 w kierunku braterstwa, padnie ofiar\u0105 ciemno\u015bci. Pycha, egoizm, arogancja i wy\u017cszo\u015b\u0107 to ma\u0142e macki, kt\u00f3rymi diabe\u0142 wyrz\u0105dza nadmierne szkody, a ja, jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 wojsk niebieskich, nie pozwol\u0119, aby lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa by\u0142 podkopywany. Duch \u015awi\u0119ty wylewa swoje dary i cnoty na pokornych, aby g\u0142osili s\u0142owo, a nie na dumnych, aby wywy\u017cszali swoj\u0105 woln\u0105 wol\u0119. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, dzie\u0144 modlitwy, o kt\u00f3ry was prosi\u0142em, dotar\u0142 do ojcowskiego tronu jak cenne kadzid\u0142o. Musz\u0119 si\u0119 z wami podzieli\u0107, \u017ce ka\u017cdy dzie\u0144 modlitwy by\u0142 ca\u0142kowicie mi\u0142y Bogu i uda\u0142o si\u0119 w pewnym stopniu z\u0142agodzi\u0107 wielkie trz\u0119sienie ziemi, kt\u00f3re czeka ludzko\u015b\u0107. Nie chc\u0105c was zasmuci\u0107, musz\u0119 wam powiedzie\u0107, \u017ce nadchodz\u0105ce wydarzenia b\u0119d\u0105 nast\u0119powa\u0142y jedno po drugim bez przerwy. Trz\u0119sienia ziemi b\u0119d\u0105 mia\u0142y wi\u0119ksz\u0105 intensywno\u015b\u0107, powoduj\u0105c, \u017ce ziemia straci sw\u00f3j zwarty stan, a wysokie g\u00f3ry zawal\u0105 si\u0119. Ludu naszego pana i kr\u00f3la Jezusa Chrystusa, kraj reprezentowany przez nied\u017awiedzia zareaguje niespodziewanie, powoduj\u0105c, \u017ce \u015bwiat pozostanie niespokojny, a niekt\u00f3re kraje zareaguj\u0105 pospiesznie. Gdy us\u0142yszycie nieznane dudnienie, nie opuszczajcie swoich dom\u00f3w ani miejsc, w kt\u00f3rych jeste\u015bcie; nie wychod\u017acie, dop\u00f3ki nie otrzymacie rozkazu, by si\u0119 ruszy\u0107. Je\u015bli pojawi si\u0119 silna i nieznana \u0142una, nie patrzcie na ni\u0105, przeciwnie, trzymajcie g\u0142ow\u0119 przy ziemi i nie patrzcie, a\u017c \u0142una zniknie, i nie ruszajcie si\u0119 z miejsca, w kt\u00f3rym jeste\u015bcie. Przechowujcie \u017cywno\u015b\u0107 wewn\u0105trz waszych dom\u00f3w, nie zapominaj\u0105c o wodzie, pob\u0142ogos\u0142awionych winogronach, sakramentaliach i tym, co jest potrzebne do ma\u0142ego o\u0142tarza, o kt\u00f3rego przygotowanie w pewnej chwili poproszono was w waszych domach. Uwaga, umi\u0142owany ludu Bo\u017cy, uwaga. Pozosta\u0144cie uwa\u017cni na up\u00f3r z\u0142a, kt\u00f3re chce was doprowadzi\u0107 do upadku. Nie ulegajcie! Ja broni\u0119 was moim mieczem. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":25,"month_string":"June","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. Beloved children, in these special times never abandon prayer and become aware of the graces that descend upon you and always be grateful. My children, you are beloved in my eyes and before Our Father. This is the reason for the apparitions throughout the world so that you may be warned of the dangers you run if you abandon God. My children, be grateful and have respect for the prophets who have been called to the mission, they lead the Church, that is you all.  The Church is not only made up of temples, Jesus Himself at times, tore down the walls. My children, these are also times of grace and many you will see coming down, they will serve to open the eyes of those who do not believe, that heaven is united to earth and Jesus is close to each of you. Pray for Spain. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Geliebte Kinder geben in diesen besonderen Zeiten nie das Gebet auf und werden sich der Gnaden bewusst, die auf Sie herabsteigen und immer dankbar sind. Meine Kinder, du bist in meinen Augen und vor unserem Vater geliebt. Dies ist der Grund f\u00fcr die Erscheinungen auf der ganzen Welt, damit Sie vor den Gefahren gewarnt werden, die Sie durchlaufen, wenn Sie Gott verlassen. Meine Kinder, seien dankbar und haben Respekt vor den Propheten, die zur Mission gerufen wurden, sie f\u00fchren die Kirche an, das sind Sie alle. Die Kirche besteht nicht nur aus Tempeln, Jesus selbst, riss die Mauern ab. Meine Kinder, das sind auch Zeiten der Gnade, und viele, die Sie herunterkommen sehen, sie werden dazu dienen, die Augen derer zu \u00f6ffnen, die nicht glauben, dass der Himmel mit der Erde vereint ist und Jesus jedem von Ihnen nahe steht. Bete f\u00fcr Spanien. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Los ni\u00f1os amados, en estos tiempos particulares, nunca abandonan la oraci\u00f3n y se dan cuenta de las gracias que descienden sobre usted y siempre gracias. Mis hijos, ustedes son un favorito en mis ojos y frente a nuestro padre. Esta es la raz\u00f3n de las apariciones en todo el mundo para que se le advierta sobre los peligros que corres si abandona a Dios. Ni\u00f1os, gracias y respeto a los profetas que han sido llamados a la misi\u00f3n, gu\u00edan a la Iglesia, es decir, es, es decir, es decir, es decir, es decir, es decir, es decir Todos ustedes. La iglesia no solo est\u00e1 hecha por los templos, a veces Jes\u00fas, a veces, derribaba las paredes. Mis hijos, estos tambi\u00e9n son los tiempos de gracia y muchos los ver\u00e1n descender, tendr\u00e1n que abrir los ojos a aquellos que no creen, que el cielo se combina con la tierra y Jes\u00fas est\u00e1 cerca de cada uno de ustedes. Ore por Espa\u00f1a. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Les enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, en ces temps sp\u00e9ciaux n'abandonnent jamais la pri\u00e8re et ne prennent conscience des gr\u00e2ces qui vous descendent et qui vous sont toujours reconnaissantes. Mes enfants, vous \u00eates aim\u00e9 dans mes yeux et avant notre p\u00e8re. C'est la raison des apparitions du monde entier afin que vous puissiez \u00eatre averti des dangers que vous courez si vous abandonnez Dieu. Mes enfants, soyez reconnaissants et respectant les proph\u00e8tes qui ont \u00e9t\u00e9 appel\u00e9s \u00e0 la mission, ils dirigent l'\u00e9glise, c'est vous tous. L'\u00c9glise n'est pas seulement compos\u00e9e de temples, J\u00e9sus lui-m\u00eame parfois, a d\u00e9truit les murs. Mes enfants, ce sont aussi des moments de gr\u00e2ce et beaucoup que vous verrez descendre, ils serviront \u00e0 ouvrir les yeux de ceux qui ne croient pas, que le ciel est uni \u00e0 la Terre et que J\u00e9sus est proche de chacun de vous. Priez pour l'Espagne. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli amati, in questi tempi particolari non abbandonate mai la preghiera e accorgetevi delle grazie che scendono su di voi e ringraziate sempre. Figli miei, voi siete prediletti ai miei occhi e davanti al Padre Nostro. Questo \u00e8 il motivo delle apparizioni in tutto il mondo affinch\u00e9 siate avvertiti dei pericoli che correte se abbandonate Dio. Figli, ringraziate e abbiate rispetto per i profeti che sono stati chiamati alla missione, essi guidano la Chiesa, cio\u00e8 voi tutti.  La Chiesa non \u00e8 solo fatta da templi, Ges\u00f9 stesso a volte, ha abbattuto le mura. Figli miei, questi sono anche i tempi di grazia e tante ne vedrete scendere, serviranno per far aprire gli occhi a chi non crede, che il cielo \u00e8 unito alla terra e Ges\u00f9 \u00e8 vicino a ognuno di voi.  Pregate per la Spagna. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, w tych szczeg\u00f3lnych czasach nigdy nie rezygnujcie z modlitwy i b\u0105d\u017acie \u015bwiadomi \u0142ask, kt\u00f3re na was zst\u0119puj\u0105 i zawsze b\u0105d\u017acie wdzi\u0119czni. Moje dzieci, jeste\u015bcie uprzywilejowani w moich oczach i przed Naszym Ojcem. Objawienia na ca\u0142ym \u015bwiecie odbywaj\u0105 si\u0119 po to, by was ostrzec przed niebezpiecze\u0144stwami, na kt\u00f3re nara\u017cacie si\u0119, je\u015bli porzucacie Boga. Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kujcie i miejcie szacunek dla prorok\u00f3w, kt\u00f3rzy zostali powo\u0142ani do misji, prowadz\u0105 Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, czyli was wszystkich. Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 to nie tylko \u015bwi\u0105tynie, sam Jezus niekiedy burzy\u0142 mury. Moje dzieci, to jest r\u00f3wnie\u017c czas \u0142aski i zobaczycie, jak wiele ich sp\u0142ynie, pos\u0142u\u017c\u0105 one do otwarcia oczu tym, kt\u00f3rzy nie wierz\u0105, \u017ce Niebo jest zjednoczone z ziemi\u0105, a Jezus jest blisko ka\u017cdego z was. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Hiszpani\u0119. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Crian\u00e7as amadas, nesses tempos especiais, nunca abandonam a ora\u00e7\u00e3o e tomam consci\u00eancia das gra\u00e7as que descem sobre voc\u00ea e sempre s\u00e3o agradecidas. Meus filhos, voc\u00ea \u00e9 amado aos meus olhos e diante de nosso pai. Esta \u00e9 a raz\u00e3o das apari\u00e7\u00f5es em todo o mundo, para que voc\u00ea seja avisado dos perigos que corre se abandonar Deus. Meus filhos, sejam gratos e respeitem os profetas que foram chamados para a miss\u00e3o, eles lideram a igreja, s\u00e3o todos voc\u00eas. A igreja n\u00e3o \u00e9 apenas composta de templos, \u00e0s vezes, o pr\u00f3prio Jesus, derrubou os muros. Meus filhos, esses tamb\u00e9m s\u00e3o momentos de gra\u00e7a e muitos que voc\u00ea ver\u00e1 descendo, eles servir\u00e3o para abrir os olhos daqueles que n\u00e3o acreditam, que o c\u00e9u est\u00e1 unido \u00e0 terra e Jesus est\u00e1 pr\u00f3ximo de cada um de voc\u00eas. Ore pela Espanha. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5728\u8fd9\u4e9b\u7279\u6b8a\u65f6\u671f\uff0c\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u4f1a\u653e\u5f03\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u610f\u8bc6\u5230\u964d\u4e34\u5728\u4f60\u8eab\u4e0a\u7684\u6069\u5178\uff0c\u5e76\u6c38\u8fdc\u611f\u6fc0\u4e0d\u5c3d\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4f60\u5728\u6211\u7684\u773c\u4e2d\u548c\u7236\u4eb2\u9762\u524d\u88ab\u7231\u3002\u8fd9\u5c31\u662f\u5168\u4e16\u754c\u9020\u6210\u5e7b\u5f71\u7684\u539f\u56e0\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u60a8\u653e\u5f03\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u60a8\u53ef\u80fd\u4f1a\u88ab\u8b66\u544a\u60a8\u9047\u5230\u7684\u5371\u9669\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8981\u611f\u6fc0\uff0c\u5e76\u5c0a\u91cd\u88ab\u53ec\u5524\u5230\u4efb\u52a1\u7684\u5148\u77e5\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u5e26\u9886\u6559\u4f1a\uff0c\u5c31\u662f\u4f60\u4eec\u3002\u6559\u4f1a\u4e0d\u4ec5\u7531\u5bfa\u5e99\u7ec4\u6210\uff0c\u6709\u65f6\u8036\u7a23\u672c\u4eba\u4e5f\u6495\u4e0b\u4e86\u5899\u58c1\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e9b\u4e5f\u662f\u6069\u5178\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u60a8\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u7684\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u5c06\u7741\u5f00\u90a3\u4e9b\u4e0d\u76f8\u4fe1\u7684\u4eba\u7684\u773c\u775b\uff0c\u5929\u5802\u4e0e\u5730\u7403\u8054\u5408\uff0c\u8036\u7a23\u4e0e\u4f60\u4eec\u6bcf\u4e2a\u4eba\u90fd\u5f88\u4eb2\u5bc6\u3002\u4e3a\u897f\u73ed\u7259\u7948\u7977\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":28,"month_string":"June","author":"Holy Father","text_en":"Dear children, I your Father, desire that each of you remember that I am often where you are. I know all your needs and all that you desire, how I wish to see you come to Me with trust and love! Do not be enticed by vices that lead to total ruin. My children, love for you is so great that I do not feel a joy equal to that of being among men. Behold, I say to those who are in a state of sin: do not ignore this call of love, otherwise I will not be able to enter you; I would like you to beware of sin. I look at you, yet you ignore that I am here and call you with My great joy, I would always like to be beside you with the hope that one day you will return to Your Father, it would be a beautiful act of love. I am the living spring, I would like to be for you the joy without end, My Son Jesus is in Me and I am in Him and our Love which is the Holy Spirit holds us together. Come and drink in this spring and your joy will be so great until eternity. Do not be indifferent to this love, only then will you be blessed, believe this truth. Take advantage of these hard times, follow the Scriptures and especially the Ten Commandments. Children, call me by the name 'Father' even once and you will have the assurance of eternal life. I say to you sons, who are working for My Glory and striving to make Me known and loved, that your reward will be great and you will have much more in eternity. To you my priest sons, I urge you to make known this Fatherly love that I have for all of you in particular, you must work so that my will may be done, do not waste your time with the things of the world and do not be inactive, but make known my power, I only desire to be loved, and to you who are not doing my will at this time, I say, Woe! I address My children, speak of Me, do not reject Me, I do not want sacrifices, I want love and respect. Look at the Crucifix, the Blessed Sacrament, the Sacred Scriptures, so that you may understand to what extent I have loved you and if families would love me more, know me more, invoke me more, I will give them my peace, my Mercy and I will be your all that will suffice for everything, do not reject this joy I would like you to enjoy this light that will illuminate your life. Now I bless you children in the name of the Most Holy Trinity.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, ich dein Vater, w\u00fcnsche dir, dass jeder von euch daran erinnert, dass ich oft dort bin, wo du bist. Ich kenne alle deine Bed\u00fcrfnisse und alles, was du willst, wie ich dich mit Vertrauen und Liebe zu mir kommen m\u00f6chte! Lassen Sie sich nicht von Laster verleihen, die zu totalem Ruin f\u00fchren. Meine Kinder, Liebe zu dir, ist so gro\u00df, dass ich keine Freude f\u00fchle, die der von M\u00e4nnern ist. Siehe, ich sage zu denen, die sich in einem Zustand der S\u00fcnde befinden: Ignoriere diesen Ruf der Liebe nicht, sonst werde ich dich nicht betreten k\u00f6nnen. Ich m\u00f6chte, dass Sie sich vor der S\u00fcnde h\u00fcten. Ich schaue dich an, aber du ignorierst, dass ich hier bin und dich mit meiner gro\u00dfen Freude anrufe. Ich w\u00fcrde immer gerne neben dir sein, in der Hoffnung, dass du eines Tages zu deinem Vater zur\u00fcckkehren wirst, es w\u00e4re ein wundersch\u00f6ner Akt der Liebe. Ich bin der lebende Fr\u00fchling, ich m\u00f6chte f\u00fcr dich die Freude ohne Ende sein, mein Sohn Jesus ist in mir und ich bin in ihm und unsere Liebe, die der Heilige Geist ist, h\u00e4lt uns zusammen. Komm und trinke im Fr\u00fchling und deine Freude wird bis zur Ewigkeit so gro\u00df. Seien Sie dieser Liebe nicht gleichg\u00fcltig, nur dann werden Sie gesegnet sein, glauben Sie dieser Wahrheit. Nutzen Sie diese schweren Zeiten, folgen Sie den heiligen Schriften und insbesondere den zehn Geboten. Kinder, nennen Sie mich auch einmal den Namen \"Vater\" und Sie werden die Gewissheit des ewigen Lebens haben. Ich sage Ihnen S\u00f6hnen, die f\u00fcr meinen Ruhm arbeiten und mich bem\u00fchen, mich zu kennen und zu geliebt, dass Ihre Belohnung gro\u00dfartig sein wird und Sie viel mehr in der Ewigkeit haben werden.F\u00fcr Sie, meine Priester -S\u00f6hne Sei inaktiv, aber mach meine Macht bekannt, ich m\u00f6chte nur geliebt werden, und f\u00fcr dich, die meinen Willen zu diesem Zeitpunkt nicht tun, sage ich, Weh! Ich spreche meine Kinder an, spreche von mir, lehne mich nicht ab, ich will keine Opfer, ich will Liebe und Respekt. Schauen Sie sich das Kruzifix, das gesegnete Sakrament, die heiligen Schriften an, damit Sie verstehen, inwieweit ich Sie geliebt habe und ob Familien mich mehr lieben w\u00fcrden, mich mehr kennen, mich mehr berufen, ich werde ihnen meinen Frieden geben, meine Barmherzigkeit Und ich werde dein alles sein, was f\u00fcr alles ausreicht, lehne diese Freude nicht ab. Ich m\u00f6chte, dass Sie dieses Licht genie\u00dfen, das Ihr Leben beleuchtet. Jetzt segne ich dich Kinder im Namen der heiligsten Dreifaltigkeit.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, yo tu padre, deseo que cada uno de ustedes recuerde que a menudo estoy donde est\u00e1s. \u00a1Conozco todas sus necesidades y todo lo que quieras, cu\u00e1nto me gustar\u00eda verte venir a m\u00ed con confianza y amor! No se adjunte por los vicios que conducen a la ruina total. Ni\u00f1os, el amor por ti es tan bueno que no siento una alegr\u00eda igual a la de estar entre los hombres. Aqu\u00ed, le digo a aquellos que est\u00e1n en un estado de pecado: no ignore este llamado de amor, de lo contrario no podr\u00e9 entrar en usted, me gustar\u00eda que lo mire desde el pecado. Te miro, pero ignor\u00e9 que estoy aqu\u00ed y te llamo con mi gran alegr\u00eda, siempre me gustar\u00eda estar a tu lado con la esperanza de que alg\u00fan d\u00eda regreses con tu padre, ser\u00eda un hermoso acto de amor. . Soy la fuente viviente, me gustar\u00eda ser para ti la alegr\u00eda interminable, mi hijo Jes\u00fas est\u00e1 en m\u00ed y estoy en \u00e9l y nuestro amor, que es el Esp\u00edritu Santo, nos mantiene unidos. Ven y bebe en esta fuente y tu alegr\u00eda ser\u00e1 genial para la eternidad. No seas indiferente a este amor, solo que de esta manera ser\u00e1s bendecido, crea esta verdad. Aproveche estos tiempos dif\u00edciles, siga los escritos y, sobre todos, los diez mandamientos. Ni\u00f1os, ll\u00e1mame con el nombre 'Padre' incluso una vez y tendr\u00e1s la certeza de la vida eterna. Les digo a los ni\u00f1os, que est\u00e1n trabajando en mi gloria y se comprometen a darme a conocer y ser amados, que su recompensa ser\u00e1 excelente y que tendr\u00e1 mucho m\u00e1s en la eternidad.Para ustedes mis hijos sacerdotes, le insto a que sepa este amor paternal que tengo por todos ustedes en particular, deben trabajar para que mi voluntad se d\u00e9 cuenta, no pierda el tiempo con las cosas del mundo y no est\u00e9 inactiva. , pero h\u00e1game saber la m\u00eda Potenza, solo quiero ser amado, y para ustedes que en este momento no est\u00e1n haciendo mi voluntad, digo: \u00a1problemas! Me dirijo a mis hijos, hablo de m\u00ed, no me rechace, no quiero sacrificios, quiero amor y respeto. Mira el crucifijo, el Sagrado Sacramento, las Sagradas Escrituras, para que puedas entender cu\u00e1n lejos te amaba y si las familias me amaban m\u00e1s, me conoc\u00edan m\u00e1s, me invocaban m\u00e1s, les dar\u00eda mi paz, la misericordia y la misericordia y la misericordia. Ser\u00e9 tu todo lo que ser\u00e1 suficiente para todo, no rechace esta alegr\u00eda, me gustar\u00eda hacerte disfrutar de esta luz que iluminar\u00e1 tu vida. Ahora los bendiga hijos en nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, je suis votre p\u00e8re, je d\u00e9sire que chacun de vous se souvienne que je suis souvent l\u00e0 o\u00f9 vous \u00eates. Je connais tous vos besoins et tout ce que vous d\u00e9sirez, comment je souhaite vous voir venir \u00e0 moi avec confiance et amour! Ne soyez pas attir\u00e9 par des vices qui conduisent \u00e0 une ruine totale. Mes enfants, l'amour pour toi sont si grands que je ne ressens pas une joie \u00e9gale \u00e0 celle parmi les hommes. Voici, je dis \u00e0 ceux qui sont dans un \u00e9tat de p\u00e9ch\u00e9: n'ignorez pas cet appel d'amour, sinon je ne pourrai pas vous entrer; J'aimerais que vous vous m\u00e9tituez du p\u00e9ch\u00e9. Je te regarde, pourtant tu ignore que je suis ici et t'appelle avec ma grande joie, j'aimerais toujours \u00eatre \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 de toi avec l'espoir qu'un jour tu retournera \u00e0 ton p\u00e8re, ce serait un bel acte d'amour. Je suis le printemps vivant, je voudrais \u00eatre pour toi la joie sans fin, mon fils J\u00e9sus est en moi et je suis en lui et notre amour qui est le Saint-Esprit nous tient ensemble. Venez boire ce printemps et votre joie sera si grande jusqu'\u00e0 l'\u00e9ternit\u00e9. Ne soyez pas indiff\u00e9rent \u00e0 cet amour, seulement alors vous serez b\u00e9ni, croyez cette v\u00e9rit\u00e9. Profitez de ces moments difficiles, suivez les \u00c9critures et surtout les dix commandements. Enfants, appelez-moi par le nom \u00abp\u00e8re\u00bb m\u00eame une fois et vous aurez l'assurance de la vie \u00e9ternelle. Je vous dis des fils, qui travaillent pour ma gloire et s'efforcent de me faire conna\u00eetre et aimer, que votre r\u00e9compense sera formidable et que vous aurez beaucoup plus dans l'\u00e9ternit\u00e9.\u00c0 vous mes fils pr\u00eatres, je vous exhorte \u00e0 faire conna\u00eetre cet amour paternel que j'ai pour vous tous en particulier, vous devez travailler pour que ma volont\u00e9 soit fait, ne perdez pas votre temps avec les choses du monde et ne pas Soyez inactif, mais fais conna\u00eetre mon pouvoir, je d\u00e9sire seulement \u00eatre aim\u00e9, et pour toi qui ne fait pas ma volont\u00e9 pour le moment, je dis, malheur! Je m'adresse \u00e0 mes enfants, je parle de moi, ne me rejette pas, je ne veux pas de sacrifices, je veux l'amour et le respect. Regardez le crucifix, le Saint-Sacrement, les \u00c9critures sacr\u00e9es, afin que vous puissiez comprendre dans quelle mesure je vous ai aim\u00e9 et si les familles m'aiment plus, me connais plus, m'invoque plus, je leur donnerai ma paix, ma mis\u00e9ricorde Et je serai votre tout ce qui suffira pour tout, ne rejettez pas cette joie, j'aimerais que vous appr\u00e9ciez cette lumi\u00e8re qui illuminera votre vie. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis les enfants au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9.","text_it":"Cari figli, Io vostro Padre, desidero che ognuno di voi si ricordi che Io spesso sono dove siete voi. Io conosco tutti i vostri bisogni e tutto ci\u00f2 che voi desiderate, quanto vorrei vedervi venire a me con fiducia e amore!  Non fatevi allettare dai vizi che conducono alla rovina totale. Figli, l\u2019amore per voi \u00e8 cos\u00ec grande che Io non provo una gioia pari a quella di essere tra gli uomini. Ecco, Io dico a coloro che sono in stato di peccato: non ignorate questa chiamata d\u2019amore, altrimenti non potr\u00f2 entrare in voi, vorrei che voi vi guardaste dal peccato. Vi guardo, eppure ignorate che Io sono qui e vi chiamo con la mia grande gioia, vorrei sempre stare accanto a voi con la speranza che un giorno tornerete dal Padre Vostro, sarebbe un bellissimo atto di amore. Io sono la sorgente viva, vorrei essere per voi la gioia senza fine, Mio Figlio Ges\u00f9 \u00e8 in me e Io sono in Lui e il nostro amore che \u00e8 lo Spirito Santo ci tiene uniti. Venite e abbeveratevi in questa sorgente e la vostra gioia sar\u00e0 cos\u00ec grande fino all\u2019eternit\u00e0. Non siate indifferenti a questo amore, solo cos\u00ec sarete benedetti, credete a questa verit\u00e0. Approfittate di questi duri tempi, seguite le Scritture e soprattutto i dieci comandamenti. Figli, chiamatemi con il nome 'Padre' anche una sola volta e avrete la certezza della vita eterna. Dico a voi figli, che state lavorando per la mia Gloria e vi impegnate a farmi conoscere e ad amare, che la vostra ricompensa sar\u00e0 grande e avrete molto di pi\u00f9 nell\u2019eternit\u00e0. A voi miei figli sacerdoti, Io vi esorto a far conoscere questo amore Paterno che nutro per tutti voi in particolare, dovete lavorare affinch\u00e9 la mia volont\u00e0 si realizzi, non perdete tempo con le cose del mondo e non siate inattivi, ma fate conoscere la mia potenza, Io desidero solo essere amato, e a voi che in questo momento non state facendo la mia volont\u00e0, dico: Guai!  Mi rivolgo ai miei bambini, parlate di me, non respingetemi, Io non voglio sacrifici, voglio amore e rispetto. Guardate il crocifisso, il Santissimo Sacramento, le sacre scritture, affinch\u00e9 possiate capire fino a che punto vi ho amati e se le famiglie mi amassero di pi\u00f9, mi conoscessero di pi\u00f9, mi invocassero di pi\u00f9, Io donerei loro la mia pace, la mia Misericordia ed Io sar\u00f2 il vostro tutto che vi baster\u00e0 per tutto, non rifiutate questa gioia vorrei farvi godere di questa luce che illuminer\u00e0 la vostra vita. Ora vi benedico figli nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, Ja, wasz Ojciec, pragn\u0119, aby ka\u017cdy z was pami\u0119ta\u0142, \u017ce jestem tam, gdzie wy. Znam wszystkie wasze potrzeby i pragnienia, jak\u017ce chcia\u0142bym, aby\u015bcie przyszli do mnie z ufno\u015bci\u0105 i mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105! Nie daj si\u0119 omami\u0107 pokusom, kt\u00f3re prowadz\u0105 do ca\u0142kowitej ruiny. Moje dzieci, moja mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do was jest tak wielka, \u017ce nie odczuwam rado\u015bci r\u00f3wnej tej, jak\u0105 daje przebywanie w\u015br\u00f3d ludzi. Oto m\u00f3wi\u0119 do tych, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0105 w stanie grzechu: nie ignorujcie tego wezwania mi\u0142o\u015bci, inaczej nie b\u0119d\u0119 m\u00f3g\u0142 przyj\u015b\u0107 do was; chcia\u0142bym, aby\u015bcie strzegli si\u0119 grzechu. Patrz\u0119 na ciebie, a jednak ignorujesz, \u017ce jestem tu i wo\u0142am ci\u0119 z moj\u0105 wielk\u0105 rado\u015bci\u0105, chcia\u0142bym zawsze by\u0107 blisko ciebie z nadziej\u0105, \u017ce kiedy\u015b wr\u00f3cisz do Ojca, to by\u0142by pi\u0119kny akt mi\u0142o\u015bci. Jestem \u017cywym \u017ar\u00f3d\u0142em, pragn\u0119 by\u0107 dla was rado\u015bci\u0105 bez ko\u0144ca, M\u00f3j Syn Jezus jest we mnie, a ja w Nim, a nasza mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, kt\u00f3r\u0105 jest Duch \u015awi\u0119ty, utrzymuje nas w jedno\u015bci. Przyjd\u017a i pij z tego \u017ar\u00f3d\u0142a, a twoja rado\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dzie tak wielka a\u017c do wieczno\u015bci. Nie b\u0105d\u017a oboj\u0119tny na t\u0119 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, tylko wtedy b\u0119dziesz b\u0142ogos\u0142awionym, uwierz w t\u0119 prawd\u0119. Wykorzystaj te trudne czasy, kieruj si\u0119 Pismem \u015awi\u0119tym, a zw\u0142aszcza dziesi\u0119cioma przykazaniami. Moje dzieci, nazwijcie mnie cho\u0107 raz imieniem 'Ojciec', a b\u0119dziecie mieli pewno\u015b\u0107 \u017cycia wiecznego. M\u00f3wi\u0119 wam synowie, kt\u00f3rzy pracujecie dla mojej Chwa\u0142y i d\u0105\u017cycie do tego, abym by\u0142 znany i kochany, \u017ce wasza nagroda b\u0119dzie wielka i b\u0119dziecie mieli o wiele wi\u0119cej w wieczno\u015bci. Was, moi synowie kap\u0142ani, wzywam, aby\u015bcie ujawnili t\u0119 ojcowsk\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, kt\u00f3r\u0105 darz\u0119 was wszystkich. W szczeg\u00f3lno\u015bci musicie pracowa\u0107, aby spe\u0142ni\u0142a si\u0119 moja wola, nie tra\u0107cie czasu na sprawy tego \u015bwiata i nie b\u0105d\u017acie bezczynni, ale ujawnijcie moj\u0105 moc, pragn\u0119 tylko by\u0107 kochanym, a wam, kt\u00f3rzy w tym czasie nie wype\u0142niacie mojej woli, m\u00f3wi\u0119: Biada! Zwracam si\u0119 do moich dzieci, m\u00f3wcie o mnie, nie odrzucajcie mnie, nie chc\u0119 ofiar, chc\u0119 mi\u0142o\u015bci i szacunku. Patrzcie na krucyfiks, na Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszy Sakrament, w Pismo \u015awi\u0119te, aby\u015bcie zrozumieli, do jakiego stopnia was umi\u0142owa\u0142em i je\u015bli rodziny b\u0119d\u0105 Mnie bardziej kocha\u0107, bardziej poznawa\u0107, bardziej powo\u0142ywa\u0107 si\u0119 na Mnie, to Ja dam im m\u00f3j Pok\u00f3j, moje Mi\u0142osierdzie i b\u0119d\u0119 waszym wszystkim, co wystarczy na wszystko, nie odrzucajcie tej rado\u015bci, chcia\u0142bym, aby\u015bcie cieszyli si\u0119 tym \u015bwiat\u0142em, kt\u00f3re roz\u015bwietli wasze \u017cycie. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was dzieci w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej.","text_pt":"Queridos filhos, seu pai, desejo que cada um de voc\u00eas se lembre de que eu estou muitas vezes onde est\u00e1. Conhe\u00e7o todas as suas necessidades e tudo o que voc\u00ea deseja, como desejo ver voc\u00ea venha a mim com confian\u00e7a e amor! N\u00e3o seja atra\u00eddo por v\u00edcios que levam \u00e0 ru\u00edna total. Meus filhos, o amor por voc\u00ea \u00e9 t\u00e3o grande que n\u00e3o sinto uma alegria igual \u00e0 de estar entre os homens. Eis que eu digo \u00e0queles que est\u00e3o em um estado de pecado: n\u00e3o ignore esse chamado de amor, caso contr\u00e1rio, n\u00e3o poderei entrar em voc\u00ea; Eu gostaria que voc\u00ea tome cuidado com o pecado. Eu olho para voc\u00ea, mas voc\u00ea ignora que estou aqui e ligo para voc\u00ea com minha grande alegria, eu sempre gostaria de estar ao seu lado com a esperan\u00e7a de que um dia voc\u00ea retorne ao seu pai, seria um belo ato de amor. Eu sou a primavera viva, gostaria de ser para voc\u00ea a alegria sem fim, meu filho Jesus est\u00e1 em mim e estou nele e nosso amor, que \u00e9 o Esp\u00edrito Santo nos mant\u00e9m unidos. Venha e beba nesta primavera e sua alegria ser\u00e1 t\u00e3o grande at\u00e9 a eternidade. N\u00e3o seja indiferente a esse amor, s\u00f3 ent\u00e3o voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 aben\u00e7oado, acredite nessa verdade. Aproveite esses tempos dif\u00edceis, siga as escrituras e especialmente os dez mandamentos. Filhos, me chame com o nome de 'Pai' mesmo uma vez e voc\u00ea ter\u00e1 a garantia da vida eterna. Eu digo a voc\u00eas filhos, que est\u00e3o trabalhando para minha gl\u00f3ria e se esfor\u00e7ando para me fazer conhecido e amado, que sua recompensa ser\u00e1 \u00f3tima e voc\u00ea ter\u00e1 muito mais na eternidade.Para voc\u00ea, meus filhos sacerdotes, pe\u00e7o que voc\u00ea divulgue esse amor paternal que tenho para todos voc\u00eas em particular, voc\u00ea deve trabalhar para que minha vontade seja feita, n\u00e3o perca seu tempo com as coisas do mundo e n\u00e3o Seja inativo, mas fa\u00e7a conhecido meu poder, eu s\u00f3 desejo ser amado, e para voc\u00ea que n\u00e3o est\u00e1 fazendo minha vontade neste momento, eu digo, ai! Eu me dirigi aos meus filhos, falo de mim, n\u00e3o me rejeite, n\u00e3o quero sacrif\u00edcios, quero amor e respeito. Olhe para o crucifixo, o Sant\u00edssimo Sacramento, as Escrituras Sagradas, para que voc\u00ea possa entender at\u00e9 que ponto eu te amei e se as fam\u00edlias me amassem mais, me conhecerem mais, invocar\u00e3o mais, darei a eles a minha paz, minha miseric\u00f3rdia E eu serei o seu tudo o que ser\u00e1 suficiente para tudo, n\u00e3o rejeite essa alegria. Gostaria que voc\u00ea apreciasse essa luz que iluminar\u00e1 sua vida. Agora eu aben\u00e7oo voc\u00eas, filhos em nome da Trindade mais Santa.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u662f\u4f60\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u5e0c\u671b\u4f60\u4eec\u6bcf\u4e2a\u4eba\u90fd\u8bb0\u5f97\u6211\u7ecf\u5e38\u5728\u4f60\u8eab\u8fb9\u3002\u6211\u77e5\u9053\u60a8\u7684\u6240\u6709\u9700\u6c42\u4ee5\u53ca\u60a8\u60f3\u8981\u7684\u6240\u6709\u9700\u6c42\uff0c\u6211\u5e0c\u671b\u5982\u4f55\u770b\u5230\u60a8\u4fe1\u4efb\u548c\u7231\u5fc3\uff01\u4e0d\u8981\u88ab\u5bfc\u81f4\u5f7b\u5e95\u7834\u574f\u7684\u6076\u4e60\u6240\u5438\u5f15\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5bf9\u4f60\u7684\u7231\u662f\u5982\u6b64\u4e4b\u5927\uff0c\u4ee5\u81f3\u4e8e\u6211\u6ca1\u6709\u50cf\u5728\u7537\u4eba\u4e2d\u7684\u90a3\u6837\u7684\u5feb\u4e50\u3002\u770b\u54ea\uff0c\u6211\u5bf9\u90a3\u4e9b\u5904\u4e8e\u7f6a\u6076\u72b6\u6001\u7684\u4eba\u8bf4\uff1a\u4e0d\u8981\u5ffd\u7565\u8fd9\u79cd\u7231\u7684\u547c\u5524\uff0c\u5426\u5219\u6211\u5c06\u65e0\u6cd5\u8fdb\u5165\u60a8\uff1b\u6211\u5e0c\u671b\u4f60\u8981\u5f53\u5fc3\u7f6a\u3002\u6211\u770b\u7740\u4f60\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u4f60\u5ffd\u7565\u4e86\u6211\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\uff0c\u4ee5\u6211\u7684\u559c\u60a6\u6253\u7535\u8bdd\u7ed9\u4f60\uff0c\u6211\u603b\u662f\u60f3\u5728\u4f60\u8eab\u8fb9\uff0c\u5e0c\u671b\u6709\u4e00\u5929\u4f60\u80fd\u56de\u5230\u4f60\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\u8eab\u8fb9\uff0c\u8fd9\u5c06\u662f\u4e00\u79cd\u7f8e\u4e3d\u7684\u7231\u60c5\u884c\u4e3a\u3002\u6211\u662f\u6d3b\u7740\u7684\u6625\u5929\uff0c\u6211\u60f3\u4e3a\u4f60\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ec8\u7ed3\u7684\u559c\u60a6\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u5728\u6211\u91cc\u9762\uff0c\u6211\u5728\u4ed6\u91cc\u9762\uff0c\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u7231\u662f\u5723\u7075\u5c06\u6211\u4eec\u56e2\u7ed3\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u3002\u5728\u4eca\u5e74\u6625\u5929\u6765\u559d\u9152\uff0c\u76f4\u5230\u6c38\u6052\uff0c\u60a8\u7684\u559c\u60a6\u5c06\u662f\u5982\u6b64\u4e4b\u5927\u3002\u4e0d\u8981\u5bf9\u8fd9\u79cd\u7231\u6f20\u4e0d\u5173\u5fc3\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u90a3\u65f6\uff0c\u60a8\u624d\u4f1a\u53d7\u5230\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u76f8\u4fe1\u8fd9\u4e2a\u771f\u7406\u3002\u5229\u7528\u8fd9\u4e9b\u8270\u96be\u65f6\u671f\uff0c\u9075\u5faa\u5723\u7ecf\uff0c\u5c24\u5176\u662f\u5341\u8beb\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u751a\u81f3\u4e00\u6b21\u4ee5\u201c\u7236\u4eb2\u201d\u7684\u540d\u5b57\u79f0\u547c\u6211\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u62e5\u6709\u6c38\u751f\u7684\u4fdd\u8bc1\u3002\u6211\u5bf9\u60a8\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8bf4\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e3a\u6211\u7684\u8363\u8000\u800c\u52aa\u529b\uff0c\u52aa\u529b\u4f7f\u6211\u77e5\u9053\u548c\u88ab\u7231\uff0c\u60a8\u7684\u5956\u52b1\u5c06\u662f\u4f1f\u5927\u7684\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u62e5\u6709\u66f4\u591a\u7684\u6c38\u6052\u3002\u6211\u7684\u7267\u5e08\u513f\u5b50\u5bf9\u4f60\u6765\u8bf4\uff0c\u6211\u6566\u4fc3\u4f60\u77e5\u9053\u6211\u5bf9\u4f60\u4eec\u6240\u6709\u4eba\u7684\u8fd9\u79cd\u7236\u4eb2\u7684\u7231\u4fdd\u6301\u4e0d\u6d3b\u8dc3\uff0c\u4f46\u8981\u77e5\u9053\u6211\u7684\u529b\u91cf\uff0c\u6211\u53ea\u60f3\u88ab\u7231\uff0c\u800c\u5bf9\u4e8e\u90a3\u4e9b\u76ee\u524d\u6ca1\u6709\u505a\u6211\u7684\u9057\u5631\u7684\u4f60\uff0c\u6211\u8bf4\uff0c\u7978\uff01\u6211\u5411\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u8bb2\u8bdd\uff0c\u8bf4\u6211\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u62d2\u7edd\u6211\uff0c\u6211\u4e0d\u60f3\u727a\u7272\uff0c\u6211\u60f3\u8981\u7231\u548c\u5c0a\u91cd\u3002\u770b\u770b\u8036\u7a23\u53d7\u96be\u50cf\uff0c\u6709\u798f\u7684\u5723\u793c\uff0c\u795e\u5723\u7684\u7ecf\u6587\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u60a8\u53ef\u4ee5\u7406\u89e3\u6211\u5728\u591a\u5927\u7a0b\u5ea6\u4e0a\u7231\u4f60\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u5bb6\u4eba\u4f1a\u66f4\u591a\u5730\u7231\u6211\uff0c\u4e86\u89e3\u6211\u66f4\u591a\uff0c\u66f4\u591a\u5730\u5524\u8d77\u6211\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u7ed9\u4ed6\u4eec\u6211\u7684\u548c\u5e73\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u601c\u60af\u6211\u5c06\u6210\u4e3a\u60a8\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u8db3\u4ee5\u6ee1\u8db3\u4e00\u5207\u7684\u4e00\u5207\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u62d2\u7edd\u8fd9\u79cd\u559c\u60a6\uff0c\u6211\u5e0c\u671b\u60a8\u4eab\u53d7\u8fd9\u79cd\u5149\u660e\u60a8\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\u7684\u5149\u8292\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u6700\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u60a8\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":6,"day":29,"month_string":"June","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people: I bless you with my Heart, I bless you with my Love. My people, you are my beloved children and I share my word with you so that you may prepare yourselves in the spirit. I desire that you convert and be fraternal; that is what I desire, that you be one heart united to that of my Mother. My people, at this moment, ask the Holy Spirit for discernment at every moment. Many human creatures, confused by the human ego that is filled with pride, wish to move away from where I have called them and it is not right. This moment is a time of prevention and at the same time a time of choice: prevention so that they do not go astray on other paths and of choice so that with my Holy Spirit they may be able to discern and stand firmly with me. They need to work in my vineyard so that, with my same love, they may wait for my Angel of Peace, who is in my house waiting for me to send him to my people. That is why no creature has ever seen him face to face. My Angel of Peace will arrive after the antichrist appears and I do not wish you to confuse him with him. My people, it is very important that you be cautious.... My Angel of Peace is neither Elijah nor Enoch, he is not an Archangel, he is my mirror of love to fill with my love every human creature who needs it. The devil has left very few of his own in hell. Most are on earth, doing his work against souls, his war is spiritual against those who remain with me. The war is spiritual, but at the same time it harms them, elevating and sickening their human ego, making them feel proud, arrogant, that they know everything, that they are indispensable where they are so that their brothers admire them and that is not good. When you are not humble, the devil declares himself the winner. My people, listen to me! It is important for you to sow humility in your hearts so that your minds and thoughts may speak of what you carry within. This is the era of the third Fiat, the era where evil is in battle against my Mother's children. The fire of ungodliness advances, the powers go on to show their power and their fury against the little ones, whom my beloved St. Michael the Archangel will defend. My children must remain prepared to face the famine that already lingers over humanity. Shortages will be severe, the climate in some countries will be extremely hot and in others extremely cold. Nature rebels against the sin of the human creature. The climate will constantly vary and the elements will rush against human creatures. Prepare yourselves! The soul must be a lamp that illuminates in the face of the darkness that the earth will suffer for a few hours. Without fear, trusting in my protection, continue to comply with all that I ask of you so that you may be victorious. Without fear! I am your god. I carry you in my Sacred Heart and you are my great treasure. I bless you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moim Sercem, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 Mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, jeste\u015bcie moimi umi\u0142owanymi dzie\u0107mi i dziel\u0119 si\u0119 z wami moim s\u0142owem, aby\u015bcie mogli przygotowa\u0107 si\u0119 w duchu. Pragn\u0119, aby\u015bcie si\u0119 nawr\u00f3cili i byli braterscy; tego w\u0142a\u015bnie pragn\u0119, aby\u015bcie byli jednym sercem zjednoczeni z sercem mojej Matki. M\u00f3j lud w tej chwili prosi Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego o rozeznanie w ka\u017cdej chwili. Wiele ludzkich stworze\u0144, zdezorientowanych przez ludzkie ego, kt\u00f3re jest przepe\u0142nione pych\u0105, chce oddali\u0107 si\u0119 od miejsca, do kt\u00f3rego ich powo\u0142a\u0142em, a to nie jest s\u0142uszne. Ten moment jest czasem prewencji i jednocze\u015bnie czasem wyboru: prewencji, aby nie zb\u0142\u0105dzili na inne drogi i wyboru, aby dzi\u0119ki mojemu \u015awi\u0119temu Duchowi mogli rozezna\u0107 i stan\u0105\u0107 mocno przy Mnie. Musz\u0105 pracowa\u0107 w mojej winnicy, aby z t\u0105 sam\u0105 moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 oczekiwa\u0107 na mojego Anio\u0142a Pokoju, kt\u00f3ry jest w moim domu i czeka, a\u017c go po\u015bl\u0119 do mojego ludu. Dlatego \u017cadne stworzenie nie widzia\u0142o go nigdy twarz\u0105 w twarz. M\u00f3j Anio\u0142 Pokoju przyb\u0119dzie po pojawieniu si\u0119 antychrysta i nie \u017cycz\u0119 sobie, aby\u015bcie go z nim pomylili. M\u00f3j ludu, bardzo wa\u017cne jest, aby\u015bcie byli ostro\u017cni.... M\u00f3j Anio\u0142 Pokoju nie jest ani Eliaszem, ani Enochem, nie jest Archanio\u0142em, jest moim zwierciad\u0142em mi\u0142o\u015bci, aby nape\u0142ni\u0107 moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 ka\u017cde ludzkie stworzenie, kt\u00f3re tego potrzebuje. Diabe\u0142 pozostawi\u0142 w piekle bardzo niewielu swoich. Wi\u0119kszo\u015b\u0107 jest na ziemi, wykonuj\u0105c swoj\u0105 prac\u0119 przeciwko duszom, jego wojna jest duchowa przeciwko tym, kt\u00f3rzy pozostaj\u0105 ze mn\u0105. Wojna ta jest duchowa, ale jednocze\u015bnie szkodzi im, wywy\u017cszaj\u0105c i choruj\u0105c ich ludzkie ego, sprawiaj\u0105c, \u017ce czuj\u0105 si\u0119 dumni, aroganccy, \u017ce wiedz\u0105 wszystko, \u017ce s\u0105 niezb\u0119dni tam, gdzie s\u0105, aby ich bracia ich podziwiali, a to nie jest dobre. Kiedy nie jeste\u015b pokorny, diabe\u0142 og\u0142asza si\u0119 zwyci\u0119zc\u0105. M\u00f3j ludu, pos\u0142uchaj mnie! Wa\u017cne jest, aby\u015bcie zasiali pokor\u0119 w waszych sercach, aby wasze umys\u0142y i my\u015bli m\u00f3wi\u0142y o tym, co nosicie w sobie. Jest to epoka trzeciego Fiat, epoka, w kt\u00f3rej z\u0142o prowadzi walk\u0119 z dzie\u0107mi mojej Matki. Ogie\u0144 bezbo\u017cno\u015bci post\u0119puje, moce id\u0105 dalej, aby pokaza\u0107 swoj\u0105 moc i swoj\u0105 furi\u0119 przeciwko ma\u0142ym, kt\u00f3rych b\u0119dzie broni\u0142 m\u00f3j ukochany \u015bw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Moje dzieci musz\u0105 pozosta\u0107 przygotowane do stawienia czo\u0142a g\u0142odowi, kt\u00f3ry ju\u017c zalega nad ludzko\u015bci\u0105. Niedobory b\u0119d\u0105 dotkliwe, klimat w niekt\u00f3rych krajach b\u0119dzie niezwykle gor\u0105cy, a w innych niezwykle zimny. Natura buntuje si\u0119 przeciwko grzechowi ludzkiego stworzenia. Klimat b\u0119dzie si\u0119 stale zmienia\u0142, a \u017cywio\u0142y b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 spieszy\u0107 przeciwko ludzkim stworzeniom. Przygotujcie si\u0119! Dusza musi by\u0107 lamp\u0105, kt\u00f3ra o\u015bwieca w obliczu ciemno\u015bci, jakich przez kilka godzin dozna ziemia. Bez l\u0119ku, ufaj\u0105c w moj\u0105 opiek\u0119, nadal wype\u0142niajcie wszystko, o co was prosz\u0119, aby\u015bcie mogli odnie\u015b\u0107 zwyci\u0119stwo. Bez l\u0119ku! Ja jestem waszym Bogiem. Nosz\u0119 ci\u0119 w moim Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszym Sercu i jeste\u015b moim wielkim skarbem. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 ci\u0119. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":3,"month_string":"July","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear precious children to my heart and Jesus' heart, thank you for being here in prayer and for bending your knees. I look at these little ones in prayer and how I wish you too were like them with pure hearts! Remember what Jesus said: the little ones will enter my Kingdom. My children, I beseech you, it will be worse than the universal flood if you do not convert, I do not want to put fear in you but to warn you, return to God with folded hands, bending your knees and with your heart and soul turned to the only Savior, and then live in eternity in heaven. Children, there will be earthquakes, droughts and cloudbursts, in the Church, evil and the evil one has entered and is without my Son anymore. Look around you, for you will no longer recognize your brothers and sisters. I ask you for prayers, fasting and brotherly love. Now I bless you, in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen. Many graces will descend on you today, witness!","text_de":"Liebe kostbare Kinder in meinem Herzen und das Herz Jesu, danke, dass du hier im Gebet bist und dir die Knie beugt hast. Ich schaue mir diese Kleinen im Gebet an und wie ich dir auch w\u00fcnsche, dass sie wie sie mit reinem Herzen w\u00e4ren! Denken Sie daran, was Jesus gesagt hat: Die Kleinen werden in mein Reich betreten. Meine Kinder, ich bitte Sie, es wird schlechter sein als die universelle Flut, wenn Sie nicht konvertieren, ich m\u00f6chte Ihnen keine Angst geben, sondern Sie warnen, mit gefalteten H\u00e4nden zu Gott zur\u00fcckkehren, die Knie und mit Ihrem Herzen und mit Ihrem Herzen und mit Ihrem Herzen und mit Ihrem Herzen biegen Die Seele wandte sich dem einzigen Erl\u00f6ser und lebte dann in der Ewigkeit im Himmel. Kinder, es wird Erdbeben, D\u00fcrren und Wolkenbursts in der Kirche, das B\u00f6se und das B\u00f6se, das man betreten hat und ohne meinen Sohn ist. Schau dich um, denn du wirst deine Br\u00fcder und Schwestern nicht mehr erkennen. Ich bitte Sie um Gebete, Fasten und br\u00fcderliche Liebe. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen. Viele Gnaden werden heute auf Sie herabsteigen, Zeugen!","text_es":"Queridos ni\u00f1os preciosos a mi coraz\u00f3n y al de Jes\u00fas, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por haber doblado las rodillas. \u00a1Miro a estos peque\u00f1os en oraci\u00f3n y c\u00f3mo me gustar\u00eda que estuvieran como lo estaban con corazones puros! Recuerda lo que dijo Jes\u00fas: los peque\u00f1os entrar\u00e1n en mi reino. Mis hijos, les ruego, ser\u00e1 peor que la inundaci\u00f3n universal si no se convierten, no quiero asustarme a s\u00ed mismo, sino advertirle, regrese a Dios con las manos en el llegado, doblando las rodillas y con el El coraz\u00f3n y el alma dirigidos al \u00fanico Salvador, porque entonces viven en la eternidad en el para\u00edso. Ni\u00f1os, habr\u00e1 terremotos, sequ\u00edas y tormentas, en la iglesia, el mal y el mal ha entrado y no tiene m\u00e1s mi hijo. Mire a su alrededor, porque ya no reconocer\u00e1 a sus hermanos. Te pido oraciones, ayuno y amor fraternal. Ahora los bendiga, en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo. \u00a1Hoy muchas gracias pasar\u00e1n a ti, testificar\u00e1n!","text_fr":"Chers enfants pr\u00e9cieux \u00e0 mon c\u0153ur et au c\u0153ur de J\u00e9sus, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re et d'avoir pli\u00e9 vos genoux. Je regarde ces petits dans la pri\u00e8re et comment je vous souhaite aussi, ils \u00e9taient comme des c\u0153urs purs! Rappelez-vous ce que J\u00e9sus a dit: les petits entreront dans mon royaume. Mes enfants, je vous en supplie, ce sera pire que l'inondation universelle si vous ne vous convertiz pas, je ne veux pas mettre la peur en vous mais pour vous avertir, retourner \u00e0 Dieu avec les mains pli\u00e9es, plier les genoux et avec votre c\u0153ur et L'\u00e2me se tourna vers le seul Sauveur, puis vivent dans l'\u00e9ternit\u00e9 dans le ciel. Enfants, il y aura des tremblements de terre, des s\u00e9cheresses et des explosions de nuages, dans l'\u00e9glise, le mal et le mal entr\u00e9 et est sans mon fils. Regardez autour de vous, car vous ne reconna\u00eetrez plus vos fr\u00e8res et s\u0153urs. Je vous demande des pri\u00e8res, du je\u00fbne et de l'amour fraternel. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen. De nombreuses gr\u00e2ces vous descendent aujourd'hui, t\u00e9moin!","text_it":"Cari figli preziosi al mio cuore e a quello di Ges\u00f9, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia. Guardo questi piccoli in preghiera e come vorrei che anche voi foste cos\u00ec come loro con i cuori puri! Ricordate cosa ha detto Ges\u00f9: i piccoli entreranno nel mio Regno. Figli miei, vi supplico, sar\u00e0 peggio del diluvio universale se voi non vi convertite, non voglio mettervi paura ma avvertirvi, tornate a Dio con le mani giunte, piegando le ginocchia e con il cuore e l\u2019anima rivolti all\u2019unico Salvatore, per poi vivere nell\u2019eternit\u00e0 in paradiso. Figli, ci saranno terremoti, siccit\u00e0 e nubifragi, nella Chiesa, \u00e8 entrato il male e il maligno ed \u00e8 senza pi\u00f9 mio Figlio. Guardatevi intorno, perch\u00e9 non riconoscerete pi\u00f9 i vostri fratelli. Vi chiedo preghiere, digiuno e amore fraterno. Ora vi benedico, nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo amen. Oggi scenderanno molte grazie su di voi, testimoniate!","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, najdro\u017csze mojemu sercu i Sercu Jezusa, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tu na modlitwie i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie. Patrz\u0119 na te male\u0144stwa w modlitwie i jak\u017ce pragn\u0119, aby\u015bcie i wy byli jak one o czystych sercach! Pami\u0119tajcie, co powiedzia\u0142 Jezus: mali wejd\u0105 do mojego Kr\u00f3lestwa. Moje dzieci, prosz\u0119 was, je\u015bli si\u0119 nie nawr\u00f3cicie, przyjdzie co\u015b gorszego ni\u017c powszechny potop, nie chc\u0119 was przerazi\u0107, chc\u0119 was ostrzec, wr\u00f3\u0107cie do Boga ze z\u0142o\u017conymi r\u0119kami, zginaj\u0105c kolana, z sercem i dusz\u0105 zwr\u00f3con\u0105 do jedynego Zbawiciela, aby potem \u017cy\u0107 w wieczno\u015bci w raju. Moje dzieci, b\u0119d\u0105 trz\u0119sienia ziemi, susze i oberwania chmury, do Ko\u015bcio\u0142a wesz\u0142o z\u0142o i szatan, a mojego Syna ju\u017c nie ma. Rozejrzyjcie si\u0119 wok\u00f3\u0142 siebie, bo nie rozpoznacie ju\u017c swoich braci. Prosz\u0119 Was o modlitwy, post i mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 bratersk\u0105. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen. Wiele \u0142ask zst\u0105pi dzi\u015b na Ciebie, \u015bwiadku!","text_pt":"Caros filhos preciosos para o meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o e o cora\u00e7\u00e3o de Jesus, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por dobrar os joelhos. Eu olho para esses pequeninos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e como eu desejo que voc\u00ea tamb\u00e9m fosse como eles com cora\u00e7\u00f5es puros! Lembre -se do que Jesus disse: os pequenos entrar\u00e3o no meu reino. Meus filhos, eu suporto voc\u00ea, ser\u00e1 pior do que a inunda\u00e7\u00e3o universal, se voc\u00ea n\u00e3o se converter, n\u00e3o quero colocar medo em voc\u00ea, mas para avis\u00e1 -lo, voltar a Deus com as m\u00e3os dobradas, dobrando os joelhos e com seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o e A alma virou -se para o \u00fanico salvador e depois vive na eternidade no c\u00e9u. Filhos, haver\u00e1 terremotos, secas e explos\u00f5es de nuvens, na igreja, mal e o maligno entrou e fica mais sem meu filho. Olhe ao seu redor, pois voc\u00ea n\u00e3o reconhecer\u00e1 mais seus irm\u00e3os e irm\u00e3s. Pe\u00e7o ora\u00e7\u00f5es, jejum e amor fraternal. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo, em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m. Muitas gra\u00e7as v\u00e3o descer sobre voc\u00ea hoje, testemunhar!","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b9d\u8d35\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\u548c\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\u5e76\u5f2f\u8170\u3002\u6211\u770b\u7740\u8fd9\u4e9b\u5c0f\u5b69\u5b50\u5728\u7948\u7977\u4e2d\uff0c\u6211\u5e0c\u671b\u4f60\u4e5f\u50cf\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e00\u6837\u50cf\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e00\u6837\u50cf\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e00\u6837\uff01\u8bb0\u4f4f\u8036\u7a23\u8bf4\u7684\u8bdd\uff1a\u5c0f\u5b69\u5b50\u4f1a\u8fdb\u5165\u6211\u7684\u738b\u56fd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u6073\u6c42\u4f60\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u4e0d\u8f6c\u6362\uff0c\u90a3\u5c06\u6bd4\u666e\u904d\u7684\u6d2a\u6c34\u66f4\u7cdf\u7cd5\u7075\u9b42\u8f6c\u5411\u552f\u4e00\u7684\u6551\u4e3b\uff0c\u7136\u540e\u751f\u6d3b\u5728\u5929\u5802\u4e2d\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5728\u6559\u5802\u91cc\uff0c\u4f1a\u6709\u5730\u9707\uff0c\u5e72\u65f1\u548c\u4e91\u7206\uff0c\u90aa\u6076\u548c\u90aa\u6076\u7684\u4eba\u8fdb\u5165\u4e86\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u3002\u73af\u987e\u56db\u5468\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u60a8\u5c06\u4e0d\u518d\u8ba4\u8bc6\u60a8\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\u59d0\u59b9\u3002\u6211\u8bf7\u60a8\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u7981\u98df\u548c\u5144\u5f1f\u822c\u7684\u7231\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002\u4eca\u5929\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u6069\u5178\u5c06\u4e0b\u964d\u5230\u60a8\u8eab\u4e0a\uff0c\u89c1\u8bc1\uff01","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":5,"month_string":"July","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children, thank you for being here in prayer and for answering my call in your hearts. My children, always be united, make reparation for all the horrors that are all over the earth, reciting the Litany of the Most Precious Blood of Jesus. My children, look at the changes that are on earth, but the spiritual ones will also be great, get used to these changes, for nothing will return as before. My children, pray, for America's head of state will be strongly attacked. I still come to give you a caress, I would like to comfort you in this unhealthy and perverse world. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Geliebte Kinder, danke, dass du hier im Gebet bist und meinen Anruf in deinen Herzen beantwortet hast. Meine Kinder, sind immer vereint, machen sich f\u00fcr alle Schrecken auf der ganzen Welt wieder auf und rezitieren die Litanei des kostbarsten Blutes Jesu. Meine Kinder schauen sich die Ver\u00e4nderungen an, die auf der Erde sind, aber die spirituellen werden auch gro\u00dfartig sein, gew\u00f6hnen sich an diese Ver\u00e4nderungen, denn nichts wird wie zuvor zur\u00fcckkehren. Meine Kinder, beten, f\u00fcr Amerikas Staatsoberhaupt wird stark angegriffen. Ich komme immer noch, um dir einen Liebkosung zu geben, ich m\u00f6chte dich in dieser ungesunden und perversen Welt tr\u00f6sten. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Amados hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por haber respondido mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, siempre se unen, reparan todos los horrores que est\u00e1n en toda la tierra, recitando la corona de la preciosa sangre de Jes\u00fas. Mis hijos, miran los cambios que est\u00e1n en la tierra, pero tambi\u00e9n los espirituales ser\u00e1n grandes, Acostarse a estos cambios, porque nada volver\u00e1 como antes. Ni\u00f1os, rezan, porque el Jefe de Estado de Am\u00e9rica estar\u00e1 fuertemente apegado. Todav\u00eda vengo a darte una caricia, me gustar\u00eda consolarte en este mundo poco saludable y perverso. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re et d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, toujours unis, font la r\u00e9paration de toutes les horreurs qui sont partout sur la terre, r\u00e9citant la litanie du sang le plus pr\u00e9cieux de J\u00e9sus. Mes enfants, regardez les changements qui sont sur Terre, mais les spirituels seront \u00e9galement formidables, s'habitueront \u00e0 ces changements, car rien ne reviendra comme avant. Mes enfants, prient, pour le chef de l'\u00c9tat am\u00e9ricain seront fortement attaqu\u00e9s. Je viens toujours vous donner une caresse, je voudrais vous r\u00e9conforter dans ce monde malsain et pervers. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli amati, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, siate sempre uniti, riparate per tutti gli orrori che ci sono su tutta la terra, recitando la corona del preziosissimo sangue di Ges\u00f9. Figli miei, guardate i cambiamenti che sono sulla terra, ma anche quelli spirituali saranno grandi, abituatevi a questi cambiamenti, perch\u00e9 niente torner\u00e0 come prima. Figli, pregate, perch\u00e9 il capo di Stato dell\u2019America sar\u00e0 fortemente attaccato. Io vengo ancora per darvi una carezza, vorrei confortarvi in questo mondo malsano e perverso. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tu na modlitwie i \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, zawsze b\u0105d\u017acie zjednoczeni, czy\u0144cie zado\u015b\u0107 za wszystkie okropno\u015bci, kt\u00f3re s\u0105 na ziemi, odmawiaj\u0105c Koronk\u0119 do Najdro\u017cszej Krwi Pana Jezusa. Moje dzieci, patrzcie na zmiany, kt\u00f3re zachodz\u0105 na ziemi, tak\u017ce te duchowe b\u0119d\u0105 wielkie, przyzwyczajajcie si\u0119 do tych zmian, bo nic nie b\u0119dzie ju\u017c jak dawniej. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, bo g\u0142owa pa\u0144stwa ameryka\u0144skiego b\u0119dzie mocno atakowana. Przychodz\u0119 ponownie, aby ci\u0119 przytuli\u0107, pragn\u0119 Ci\u0119 pocieszy\u0107 w tym niezdrowym i przewrotnym \u015bwiecie. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Filhos Amados, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por atender meu chamado em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, sempre est\u00e3o unidos, fazem repara\u00e7\u00e3o por todos os horrores que est\u00e3o por toda a terra, recitando a litania do sangue mais precioso de Jesus. Meus filhos, olhem para as mudan\u00e7as que est\u00e3o na Terra, mas as espirituais tamb\u00e9m ser\u00e3o \u00f3timas, se acostumar\u00e3o com essas mudan\u00e7as, pois nada retornar\u00e1 como antes. Meus filhos, oram, pelo que o chefe de estado da Am\u00e9rica ser\u00e1 fortemente atacado. Eu ainda vim para lhe dar uma car\u00edcia, gostaria de confort\u00e1 -lo neste mundo prejudicial e perverso. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u63a5\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u6c38\u8fdc\u56e2\u7ed3\u4e00\u81f4\uff0c\u4e3a\u904d\u5e03\u5927\u5730\u7684\u6240\u6709\u6050\u6016\u7edf\u6cbb\uff0c\u6717\u8bf5\u8036\u7a23\u6700\u5b9d\u8d35\u7684\u8840\u7edf\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u770b\u770b\u5730\u7403\u4e0a\u7684\u53d8\u5316\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u7cbe\u795e\u4e0a\u7684\u53d8\u5316\u4e5f\u4f1a\u5f88\u68d2\uff0c\u4e60\u60ef\u4e86\u8fd9\u4e9b\u53d8\u5316\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ec0\u4e48\u90fd\u4e0d\u4f1a\u50cf\u4ee5\u524d\u90a3\u6837\u56de\u6765\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4e3a\u7f8e\u56fd\u7684\u56fd\u5bb6\u5143\u9996\u53d7\u5230\u5f3a\u70c8\u653b\u51fb\u3002\u6211\u4ecd\u7136\u6765\u7ed9\u4f60\u4e00\u4e2a\u7231\u629a\uff0c\u6211\u60f3\u5728\u8fd9\u4e2a\u4e0d\u5065\u5eb7\u548c\u4e0d\u5065\u5eb7\u7684\u4e16\u754c\u4e2d\u5b89\u6170\u4f60\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":9,"month_string":"July","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"I come in the name of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. I am sent to give you the word of our King. Mankind will know what the spiritual battle is and will regret not having believed. My angelic legions are over all human creatures to assist, help and guard them if they ask us to do so. At this moment human creatures do not see, do not hear, do not believe.... The mind is occupied in the mundane and the heart has been usurped by idols, fanaticisms and mainly by the conceited 'ego' that they possess. They do not love life, the sacred gift of God for humanity. One or the other will be astonished by the continuous atmospheric phenomena that will increase all over the earth. The bear awakens fierce, without being expected by the rest of humanity; he will give a thrust and a crown will roll. One and another sign is received by mankind and unheeded it continues in its pleasures until it rains fire from heaven and understands that the warnings are not in vain. God's people, it seems that you continue to live as usual, but this is not so. Be prepared! I will ask you again and again, to the point of exhaustion... The horsemen of the apocalypse sweep across heaven and their roar is heard all over the earth. Human creatures do not know what it is, but listen to them without knowing where the trumpet sounds come from. Pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, pray for Canada will be scourged. Pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, London will be attacked with desires to conquer you. Pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, Brazil will be scourged by the rains heavily before it becomes a land of provision. Pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, Argentina will taste the gall of pain. Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, famine advances mercilessly, war widens, disease runs over the earth and soon reaches my beloved children. The people of God will migrate to South America, will migrate to Central America in search of a place to dwell in the midst of war. Beloveds of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: Humanity will go out of control... And out of the church come new rules; some approve, some do not. The schism is drawing nearer and nearer. Creation is the home of human creatures and they must restore it to the order in which it was created. The animal kingdom, the vegetable kingdom and the mineral kingdom need their home to be restored as God created it. You people of our King and Lord must not fear, on the contrary, faith must abound in each one of you. My celestial legions will come to your aid. You are children of the creator of heaven and earth... Do not forget it! Call upon our Queen and Mother: hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Have a blessed palm, do not forget it. I bless you with my heavenly legions. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Przychodz\u0119 w imieniu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Jestem pos\u0142any, aby przekaza\u0107 wam s\u0142owo naszego Kr\u00f3la. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 pozna, czym jest walka duchowa i b\u0119dzie \u017ca\u0142owa\u0107, \u017ce nie uwierzy\u0142a. Moje anielskie legiony s\u0105 nad wszystkimi ludzkimi stworzeniami, aby je wspomaga\u0107, pomaga\u0107 i strzec, je\u015bli nas o to poprosz\u0105. W tej chwili ludzkie stworzenia nie widz\u0105, nie s\u0142ysz\u0105, nie wierz\u0105.... Umys\u0142 zaj\u0119ty jest przyziemno\u015bci\u0105, a serce zosta\u0142o uzurpowane przez bo\u017cki, fanatyzmy, a g\u0142\u00f3wnie przez zarozumia\u0142e \"ego\", kt\u00f3re posiadaj\u0105. Nie kochaj\u0105 \u017cycia, \u015bwi\u0119tego daru Boga dla ludzko\u015bci. Jeden czy drugi b\u0119dzie zdumiony ci\u0105g\u0142ymi zjawiskami atmosferycznymi, kt\u00f3re nasil\u0105 si\u0119 na ca\u0142ej ziemi. Nied\u017awied\u017a przebudzi si\u0119 zawzi\u0119cie, nie b\u0119d\u0105c oczekiwanym przez reszt\u0119 ludzko\u015bci; da pchni\u0119cie i potoczy si\u0119 korona. Jeden i drugi znak odbiera ludzko\u015b\u0107 i nie s\u0142uchana trwa w swoich przyjemno\u015bciach, a\u017c do momentu, gdy spadnie deszcz ognia z nieba i zrozumie, \u017ce ostrze\u017cenia nie s\u0105 daremne. Ludu Bo\u017cy, wydaje si\u0119, \u017ce dalej \u017cyjecie jak zwykle, ale tak nie jest. B\u0105d\u017acie przygotowani! B\u0119d\u0119 was pyta\u0142 raz po raz, a\u017c do wyczerpania... Je\u017ad\u017acy apokalipsy przetaczaj\u0105 si\u0119 przez niebo, a ich ryk s\u0142ycha\u0107 na ca\u0142ej ziemi. Stworzenia ludzkie nie wiedz\u0105, co to jest, ale s\u0142uchaj\u0105 ich, nie wiedz\u0105c, sk\u0105d pochodz\u0105 d\u017awi\u0119ki tr\u0105b. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Kanad\u0119 b\u0119dzie biczowana. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, Londyn b\u0119dzie atakowany z pragnieniami zdobycia Was. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, Brazylia b\u0119dzie biczowana przez deszcze mocno, zanim stanie si\u0119 ziemi\u0105 zaopatrzenia. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, Argentyna zakosztuje \u017c\u00f3\u0142ci b\u00f3lu. Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, g\u0142\u00f3d post\u0119puje bezlito\u015bnie, wojna si\u0119 rozszerza, choroby przebiegaj\u0105 po ziemi i wkr\u00f3tce dosi\u0119gn\u0105 moje umi\u0142owane dzieci. Lud Bo\u017cy b\u0119dzie migrowa\u0142 do Ameryki Po\u0142udniowej, b\u0119dzie migrowa\u0142 do Ameryki \u015arodkowej w poszukiwaniu miejsca zamieszkania po\u015br\u00f3d wojny. Umi\u0142owani naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Ludzko\u015b\u0107 wymknie si\u0119 spod kontroli... A z Ko\u015bcio\u0142a wychodz\u0105 nowe zasady; jedni je aprobuj\u0105, inni nie. Schizma jest coraz bli\u017csza. Stworzenie jest domem ludzkich istot i musz\u0105 one przywr\u00f3ci\u0107 je do porz\u0105dku, w jakim zosta\u0142y stworzone. Kr\u00f3lestwo zwierz\u0105t, kr\u00f3lestwo ro\u015blin i kr\u00f3lestwo minera\u0142\u00f3w potrzebuj\u0105, aby ich dom zosta\u0142 przywr\u00f3cony tak, jak B\u00f3g go stworzy\u0142. Wy, ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana, nie mo\u017cecie si\u0119 l\u0119ka\u0107, przeciwnie, wiara musi obfitowa\u0107 w ka\u017cdym z was. Moje niebia\u0144skie legiony przyjd\u0105 wam z pomoc\u0105. Jeste\u015bcie dzie\u0107mi Stw\u00f3rcy nieba i ziemi... Nie zapominajcie o tym! Wzywajcie nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119: niech \u017cyje Maryja najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Miejcie b\u0142ogos\u0142awion\u0105 palm\u0119, nie zapominajcie o tym. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moimi niebia\u0144skimi legionami. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":9,"month_string":"July","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My dear children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, have the courage to make your choice now because your life will depend on it, the closer you come to the light the more enlightened you will be, the closer you come to evil the more easily the devil will engulf you. My children, choose God forever, please My children, continue to hold prayer cenacles, open your hearts and your homes and I will bless you and I will always be with you to guide you. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen. ","text_de":"Meine lieben Kinder, danke, dass du auf meinen Anruf in deinem Herzen geantwortet hast. Meine Kinder haben den Mut, jetzt Ihre Wahl zu treffen, denn Ihr Leben wird davon abh\u00e4ngen, je n\u00e4her Sie ans Licht kommen, desto aufgekl\u00e4rter werden Sie, je n\u00e4her Sie dem B\u00f6sen kommen, desto leichter wird der Teufel Sie verschlingen. Meine Kinder, w\u00e4hlen Sie Gott f\u00fcr immer, bitte, meine Kinder, halten Sie weiterhin Gebetszenakeln, \u00f6ffnen Sie Ihre Herzen und Ihre H\u00e4user und ich werde Sie segnen und ich werde immer mit Ihnen sein, um Sie zu f\u00fchren. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, tengan el coraje de hacer su elecci\u00f3n ahora, porque en esto su vida depender\u00e1, cuanto m\u00e1s se acerque a la luz, m\u00e1s se iluminar\u00e1, m\u00e1s se acercar\u00e1 al mal, m\u00e1s el diablo se endurecer\u00e1 f\u00e1cilmente. Mis hijos, eligen a Dios para siempre, complacen a mis hijos, sigan cenando la oraci\u00f3n, abre sus corazones y hogares y los bendecir\u00e9 y siempre estar\u00e9 contigo para guiarte. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, ont le courage de faire votre choix maintenant parce que votre vie d\u00e9pendra de celle-ci, plus vous vous rapprochez de la lumi\u00e8re, plus vous serez \u00e9clair\u00e9, plus vous vous rapprochez du mal, plus le diable vous engloutira. Mes enfants, choisissez Dieu pour toujours, s'il vous pla\u00eet mes enfants, continuez \u00e0 tenir des cenacles de pri\u00e8re, ouvrez vos c\u0153urs et vos maisons et je vous b\u00e9nirai et je serai toujours avec vous pour vous guider. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, abbiate il coraggio di fare la vostra scelta ora, perch\u00e9 da ci\u00f2 dipender\u00e0 la vostra vita, pi\u00f9 vi avvicinerete alla luce \u00e8 pi\u00f9 sarete illuminati, pi\u00f9 vi avvicinerete al male e pi\u00f9 il demonio vi fagociter\u00e0 facilmente. Figli miei, scegliete Dio per sempre, vi prego bambini miei, continuate a fare cenacoli di preghiera, aprite i vostri cuori e le vostre case ed Io vi benedir\u00f2 e sar\u00f2 sempre con voi per guidarvi. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen. ","text_pl":"Moje drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, miejcie odwag\u0119 dokona\u0107 teraz wyboru, bo od tego b\u0119dzie zale\u017ca\u0142o wasze \u017cycie, im bardziej zbli\u017cycie si\u0119 do \u015bwiat\u0142a, tym bardziej b\u0119dziecie o\u015bwieceni, im bardziej zbli\u017cycie si\u0119 do z\u0142a, tym \u0142atwiej diabe\u0142 was poch\u0142onie. Moje dzieci, wybierzcie Boga na zawsze, prosz\u0119 moje dzieci, tw\u00f3rzcie nadal kr\u0119gi modlitewne, otw\u00f3rzcie swoje serca i swoje domy, a ja wam pob\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 i zawsze b\u0119d\u0119 z wami, aby was prowadzi\u0107. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus queridos filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, t\u00eam a coragem de fazer sua escolha agora, porque sua vida depender\u00e1 disso, quanto mais perto voc\u00ea chegar \u00e0 luz, mais esclarecida estar\u00e1, quanto mais perto voc\u00ea se aproximar, mais facilmente o diabo o envolver\u00e1. Meus filhos, escolha Deus para sempre, por favor meus filhos, continue segurando cen\u00e1culos de ora\u00e7\u00e3o, abra seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e suas casas e eu o aben\u00e7oarei e sempre estarei com voc\u00ea para gui\u00e1 -lo. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6709\u52c7\u6c14\u73b0\u5728\u505a\u51fa\u9009\u62e9\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u60a8\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\u5c06\u53d6\u51b3\u4e8e\u5b83\uff0c\u60a8\u63a5\u8fd1\u5149\u7ebf\u7684\u8d8a\u8fd1\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u8d8a\u542f\u53d1\uff0c\u60a8\u8d8a\u63a5\u8fd1\u90aa\u6076\uff0c\u9b54\u9b3c\u5c31\u4f1a\u8d8a\u6765\u8d8a\u5bb9\u6613\u541e\u566c\u60a8\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6c38\u8fdc\u9009\u62e9\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u8bf7\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7ee7\u7eed\u6301\u6709\u7948\u7977\u7684\u5ff5\u5934\uff0c\u655e\u5f00\u5fc3hearts\u548c\u60a8\u7684\u623f\u5c4b\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u795d\u798f\u60a8\uff0c\u6211\u5c06\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0e\u60a8\u4e00\u8d77\u6307\u5bfc\u60a8\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":12,"month_string":"July","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart, I charge you to pray, each of you individually, because each person knows what to ask and what to give. Beloved people of my Son, the days are shortening and my true children are becoming fewer and fewer. Man feels that he is God and has taken power over man himself in order to destroy himself. Human beings will commit very grave sin. Children, you know about so much that is already upon humanity, and yet you do not change... Children, so much has been made known to you, not in order to terrify you, but so that you would prepare spiritually, and yet you do not change... Only those who remain in my Son will retain their sanity regarding what has been taken for a personal god: money. Having clung to the god of the world, you will feel lost without economic support. Faced with the fall of the economy, people will turn to what is offered to you and will fall into the hands of the antichrist. The microchip in the bodies of my children is the seal for being be able to buy and sell, in exchange for losing eternal life, in order to feel that material security to which you are so accustomed. Do not lose your soul! How my Son grieves because of it! How my Son grieves! People of my Son, once the microchip is implanted in you, they will dominate your minds, ruling over you so that you would work and act as the power of evil commands you. My Son does not offer power on earth and does not offer domination over your brothers and sisters... My Son shed his blood for each one of you, he redeemed you from sin and gave you eternal life for those who desire it. Children of my Heart, the earth will shake forcefully; the wind will blow as it has never blown before and ice with fall in the midst of the heat of the tropics... The moon is tinged with red and the signs will not stop, neither in the firmament nor on earth, and yet the people of my Son continue to be blindfolded, immersed in banality, without opening their eyes. My children lose their faith at the slightest word they do not like to hear or read, but whatever offers spiritual independence reinforces them. They submit to the devil so passively that they do not discern what an event means on the path of the plans about which this mother has spoken in advance. My Son's Church is shrinking and only those who discern what is to come will know what is happening with each event. Pray and pray, discern, prepare, bend your knees. My maternal heart is open to receive you: come, enter into my heart and I will lead you to my Divine Son. I love you; I bless you; I protect you. Do not be afraid. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca, zobowi\u0105zuj\u0119 was do modlitwy, ka\u017cdego z was indywidualnie, bo ka\u017cdy wie, o co ma prosi\u0107 i co da\u0107. Umi\u0142owany ludu mojego Syna, dni si\u0119 skracaj\u0105, a moich prawdziwych dzieci jest coraz mniej. Cz\u0142owiek uwa\u017ca, \u017ce jest Bogiem i przej\u0105\u0142 w\u0142adz\u0119 nad samym cz\u0142owiekiem, aby zniszczy\u0107 siebie. Cz\u0142owiek b\u0119dzie pope\u0142nia\u0142 bardzo ci\u0119\u017cki grzech. Dzieci, wiecie o tak wielu rzeczach, kt\u00f3re ju\u017c s\u0105 na ludzko\u015bci, a jednak nie zmieniacie si\u0119... Dzieci, tak wiele zosta\u0142o wam powiedziane, nie po to, aby was przerazi\u0107, ale po to, aby\u015bcie si\u0119 przygotowali duchowo, a jednak nie zmieniacie si\u0119... Tylko ci, kt\u00f3rzy pozostaj\u0105 w moim Synu, zachowaj\u0105 rozs\u0105dek w odniesieniu do tego, co zosta\u0142o wzi\u0119te za boga osobistego: pieni\u0119dzy. Przylgn\u0105wszy do boga tego \u015bwiata, poczujecie si\u0119 zagubieni bez wsparcia ekonomicznego. W obliczu upadku gospodarki, ludzie zwr\u00f3c\u0105 si\u0119 ku temu, co jest wam oferowane i wpadn\u0105 w r\u0119ce antychrysta. Mikrochip w cia\u0142ach moich dzieci jest piecz\u0119ci\u0105, aby m\u00f3c kupowa\u0107 i sprzedawa\u0107, w zamian za utrat\u0119 \u017cycia wiecznego, aby poczu\u0107 to materialne bezpiecze\u0144stwo, do kt\u00f3rego jeste\u015bcie tak przyzwyczajeni. Nie tra\u0107cie swojej duszy! Jak\u017ce m\u00f3j Syn smuci si\u0119 z tego powodu! Jak\u017ce smuci si\u0119 m\u00f3j Syn! Ludu mojego Syna, po wszczepieniu wam mikrochipa, zdominuj\u0105 wasze umys\u0142y, rz\u0105dz\u0105c wami, aby\u015bcie pracowali i dzia\u0142ali tak, jak nakazuje wam moc z\u0142a. M\u00f3j Syn nie oferuje w\u0142adzy na ziemi i nie oferuje dominacji nad waszymi bra\u0107mi i siostrami... M\u00f3j Syn przela\u0142 swoj\u0105 krew za ka\u017cdego z was, odkupi\u0142 was od grzechu i da\u0142 \u017cycie wieczne dla tych, kt\u00f3rzy go pragn\u0105. Dzieci mojego Serca, ziemia zatrz\u0119sie si\u0119 z si\u0142\u0105; wiatr b\u0119dzie wia\u0142 jak nigdy dot\u0105d i l\u00f3d spadnie po\u015br\u00f3d upa\u0142\u00f3w tropik\u00f3w... Ksi\u0119\u017cyc zabarwia si\u0119 na czerwono i znaki nie ustan\u0105 ani na firmamencie, ani na ziemi, a jednak lud mojego Syna trwa w za\u015blepieniu, zanurzony w banale, nie otwieraj\u0105c oczu. Moje dzieci trac\u0105 wiar\u0119 przy najmniejszym s\u0142owie, kt\u00f3rego nie lubi\u0105 s\u0142ysze\u0107 lub czyta\u0107, ale cokolwiek oferuje duchow\u0105 niezale\u017cno\u015b\u0107, wzmacnia je. Poddaj\u0105 si\u0119 diab\u0142u tak biernie, \u017ce nie rozeznaj\u0105, co dane wydarzenie oznacza na drodze plan\u00f3w, o kt\u00f3rych ta matka z g\u00f3ry m\u00f3wi\u0142a. Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 Mojego Syna kurczy si\u0119 i tylko ci, kt\u00f3rzy rozeznaj\u0105, co ma nadej\u015b\u0107, b\u0119d\u0105 wiedzieli, co si\u0119 dzieje z ka\u017cdym wydarzeniem. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 i m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, rozeznawajcie, przygotowujcie si\u0119, zginajcie kolana. Moje matczyne serce jest otwarte, aby was przyj\u0105\u0107: przyjd\u017acie, wejd\u017acie do mojego serca, a ja was poprowadz\u0119 do mojego Boskiego Syna. Kocham was; b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was; chroni\u0119 was. Nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":15,"month_string":"July","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"Beloved one, daughter and sister, write to the world. Today, worse than the virus you have so feared is the lust, wickedness, confusion and selfishness that are rampant in the hearts and minds of this humanity. The apostasy reigns because my anointed ones do not believe in the existence of Satan and his tricks, they do not speak of the sin that is tearing them apart, passing it off as ordinary. I will come to divide good from evil, return to Me, before it is too late, you no longer follow My teachings, tolerate evil and bow your heads to it. Those who pass laws against those of My Father will be vomited up and feel the burning of eternal fire. The chastisements will be for the purification of this perverse humanity. Make your choice, I tell you this, so that you may be aware. Wake up, for the time is over, many reject my Mercy, yet, I have shown them miracles, but they are blind and deaf. I say to the politicians: in the name of God, stop now! I will destroy your plans, only I, can decide the end of man, your satanic plans will be swept away, together with you, My Father's justice will thunder so loudly that the whole universe will tremble. Those who follow God's laws shall not fear, but rejoice, for God's kingdom is at hand. Peace be with you, Amen.","text_de":"Geliebte, Tochter und Schwester, schreiben in die Welt. Heute ist schlimmer als das Virus, das Sie so gef\u00fcrchtet haben, die Lust, Bosheit, Verwirrung und Selbstsucht, die in den Herzen und Geist dieser Menschheit weit verbreitet sind. Der Abfallgr\u00fcn herrscht, weil meine Gesalbten nicht an die Existenz von Satan und seinen Tricks glauben, sie sprechen nicht von der S\u00fcnde, die sie auseinander rei\u00dft und sie als gew\u00f6hnlich abgibt. Ich werde kommen, um das Gut vom B\u00f6sen zu teilen, zu mir zur\u00fcckzukehren, bevor es zu sp\u00e4t ist, folgen Sie nicht mehr meinen Lehren, tolerieren das B\u00f6se und verneigen Sie Ihre K\u00f6pfe. Diejenigen, die Gesetze gegen die meines Vaters verabschieden, werden sich erbrochen und sp\u00fcren das Verbrennen ewiger Feuer. Die Z\u00fcchter werden f\u00fcr die Reinigung dieser perversen Menschheit dienen. Treffen Sie Ihre Wahl, ich sage Ihnen das, damit Sie sich vielleicht bewusst sind. Wach auf, f\u00fcr die Zeit ist vorbei, viele lehnen meine Barmherzigkeit ab, aber ich habe ihnen Wunder gezeigt, aber sie sind blind und taub. Ich sage zu den Politikern: Im Namen Gottes h\u00f6r jetzt auf! Ich werde deine Pl\u00e4ne zerst\u00f6ren, nur ich kann das Ende des Menschen entscheiden, deine satanischen Pl\u00e4ne werden zusammen mit dir weggefegt, die Gerechtigkeit meines Vaters wird so laut donnern, dass das ganze Universum zittern wird. Diejenigen, die Gottes Gesetzen folgen, werden sich nicht f\u00fcrchten, sondern freuen sich, denn Gottes Reich ist zur Hand. Friede sei mit dir, Amen.","text_es":"Mi ser querido, hija y hermana, escriben al mundo. Hoy, lo peor que el virus que has temido tanto, es la lujuria, la malicia, la confusi\u00f3n y el ego\u00edsmo los que se est\u00e1n propagando en el coraz\u00f3n y la mente de esta humanidad. Apostlesia reina porque mi gente consagrada no cree en la existencia de Satan\u00e1s y sus trucos, no hablan del pecado que rasgo, haciendo que el pecado pase, como administraci\u00f3n ordinaria. Vendr\u00e9 a dividir el bien del mal, volver a m\u00ed, antes de que sea demasiado tarde, ya no seguir\u00e1s mis ense\u00f1anzas, tolerar\u00e1s el mal y se inclina sobre la cabeza hacia \u00e9l. Aquellos que aprueben las leyes contra las de mi padre, ser\u00e1n vomitados y sentir\u00e1n la quema del fuego eterno. Los castigos ser\u00e1n por la purificaci\u00f3n de esta humanidad perversa. Haga su elecci\u00f3n, le digo esto, para que est\u00e9 consciente. Despierta, porque ha terminado el tiempo, muchos rechazan mi misericordia, sin embargo, les he mostrado los milagros, pero son ciegos y sordos. Le digo a los pol\u00edticos: en nombre de Dios, \u00a1det\u00e9ngase ahora! Destruir\u00e9 tus planes, solo yo, puedo decidir el fin del hombre, tus proyectos sat\u00e1nicos ser\u00e1n barridos, junto con ti, la justicia de mi padre truenar\u00e1 tan fuerte que el universo temblar\u00e1. Aquellos que siguen las leyes de Dios no tendr\u00e1n que temer, sino exultar, porque el reino de Dios est\u00e1 cerca. La paz sea contigo, am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Un bien-aim\u00e9, sa fille et sa s\u0153ur, \u00e9crivent au monde. Aujourd'hui, pire que le virus que vous avez si craint, c'est la luxure, la m\u00e9chancet\u00e9, la confusion et l'\u00e9go\u00efsme qui s\u00e9vitent dans le c\u0153ur et l'esprit de cette humanit\u00e9. L'apostasie r\u00e8gne parce que mes oints ne croient pas \u00e0 l'existence de Satan et de ses astuces, ils ne parlent pas du p\u00e9ch\u00e9 qui les d\u00e9chire, le faisant passer comme ordinaire. Je viendrai pour diviser le bien du mal, retourner \u00e0 moi, avant qu'il ne soit trop tard, vous ne suivez plus mes enseignements, tol\u00e9rez le mal et vous inclinez la t\u00eate. Ceux qui adoptent des lois contre ceux de mon p\u00e8re seront vomis et ressentiront l'incendie du feu \u00e9ternel. Les ch\u00e2timents seront pour la purification de cette humanit\u00e9 perverse. Faites votre choix, je vous le dis, afin que vous puissiez \u00eatre conscient. R\u00e9veillez-vous, pour le moment est termin\u00e9, beaucoup rejettent ma mis\u00e9ricorde, mais je leur ai montr\u00e9 des miracles, mais ils sont aveugles et sourds. Je dis aux politiciens: au nom de Dieu, arr\u00eatez-vous maintenant! Je d\u00e9truirai vos plans, seulement moi, je peux d\u00e9cider de la fin de l'homme, vos plans sataniques seront emport\u00e9s, avec vous, la justice de mon p\u00e8re tonnera si fort que l'univers entier tremblera. Ceux qui suivent les lois de Dieu ne craignent pas, mais se r\u00e9jouissent, car le royaume de Dieu est \u00e0 port\u00e9e de main. La paix soit avec toi, amen.","text_it":"Amata mia, figlia e sorella, scrivi al mondo. Oggi, peggiore del virus che avete tanto temuto, \u00e8 la lussuria, la cattiveria, la confusione e l\u2019egoismo che stanno dilagando nel cuore e nella mente di questa umanit\u00e0. L \u2018apostasia regna perch\u00e9 i miei consacrati non credono all\u2019esistenza di satana e alle sue astuzie, non parlano del peccato che dilania, facendo passare il peccato, come ordinaria amministrazione. Io verr\u00f2 a dividere il bene dal male, tornate a Me, prima che sia troppo tardi, voi non seguite pi\u00f9 i miei insegnamenti, tollerate il male e chinate il capo ad esso. Coloro che approveranno le leggi contro quelle del Padre mio, saranno vomitati e sentiranno il bruciore del fuoco eterno. I castighi saranno per la purificazione di questa umanit\u00e0 perversa. Fate la vostra scelta, vi dico ci\u00f2, affinch\u00e9 siate consapevoli. Svegliatevi, perch\u00e9 il tempo \u00e8 finito, molti rifiutano la mia Misericordia, eppure, ho mostrato loro i miracoli, ma sono ciechi e sordi. Io dico ai politici: in nome di Dio, fermatevi ora! Distrugger\u00f2 i vostri piani, solo Io, posso decidere la fine dell\u2019uomo, i vostri progetti satanici saranno spazzati via, insieme a voi, la giustizia del Padre mio tuoner\u00e0 cos\u00ec forte che l\u2019universo tutto tremer\u00e0. Coloro che seguono le leggi di Dio non dovranno temere, ma esultare, perch\u00e9 il regno di Dio \u00e8 vicino. La pace sia con voi, amen.","text_pl":"Moja ukochana c\u00f3rko i siostro, napisz to \u015bwiatu. Dzi\u015b gorsze od wirusa, kt\u00f3rego tak si\u0119 obawiali\u015bcie, s\u0105 \u017c\u0105dza, niegodziwo\u015b\u0107, zamieszanie i samolubstwo, kt\u00f3re szalej\u0105 w sercach i umys\u0142ach tej ludzko\u015bci. Apostazja panuje, poniewa\u017c Moi konsekrowani nie wierz\u0105 w istnienie szatana i jego podst\u0119p\u00f3w, nie m\u00f3wi\u0105 o grzechu, kt\u00f3ry pustoszy, przemilczaj\u0105c go jako co\u015b normalnego. Przyjd\u0119, aby oddzieli\u0107 dobro od z\u0142a, wr\u00f3\u0107cie do Mnie, zanim b\u0119dzie za p\u00f3\u017ano, nie stosujecie ju\u017c Moich nauk, tolerujecie z\u0142o i chylicie przed nim g\u0142owy. Ci, kt\u00f3rzy wydaj\u0105 prawa sprzeczne z prawami Mojego Ojca, zostan\u0105 zwymiotowani i odczuj\u0105 palenie wiecznego ognia. Kary b\u0119d\u0105 dla oczyszczenia tej przewrotnej ludzko\u015bci. Dokonaj wyboru, m\u00f3wi\u0119 do ciebie, aby\u015b by\u0142 \u015bwiadomy. Obud\u017acie si\u0119, bo czas si\u0119 sko\u0144czy\u0142, wielu odrzuca Moje Mi\u0142osierdzie, a przecie\u017c pokaza\u0142em im cuda, ale s\u0105 \u015blepi i g\u0142usi. M\u00f3wi\u0119 do polityk\u00f3w: w imi\u0119 Boga, przesta\u0144cie ju\u017c! Zniszcz\u0119 wasze plany, tylko Ja, mog\u0119 zadecydowa\u0107 o ko\u0144cu cz\u0142owieka, wasze szata\u0144skie plany zostan\u0105 zmiecione, razem z wami. Sprawiedliwo\u015b\u0107 mojego Ojca zagrzmi tak g\u0142o\u015bno, \u017ce zadr\u017cy ca\u0142y wszech\u015bwiat. Ci, kt\u00f3rzy przestrzegaj\u0105 praw Bo\u017cych, nie b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 l\u0119ka\u0107, lecz radowa\u0107, bo bliskie jest Kr\u00f3lestwo Bo\u017ce. Pok\u00f3j niech b\u0119dzie z wami, Amen.","text_pt":"Amado, filha e irm\u00e3, escreva para o mundo. Hoje, pior do que o v\u00edrus que voc\u00ea tanto temia, \u00e9 a lux\u00faria, a maldade, a confus\u00e3o e o ego\u00edsmo que s\u00e3o desenfreados nos cora\u00e7\u00f5es e mentes dessa humanidade. A apostasia reina porque meus ungidos n\u00e3o acreditam na exist\u00eancia de Satan\u00e1s e seus truques, eles n\u00e3o falam do pecado que os est\u00e1 destruindo, passando -o como comum. Vou dividir o bem do mal, voltar para mim, antes que seja tarde demais, voc\u00ea n\u00e3o segue mais meus ensinamentos, tolera o mal e inclina sua cabe\u00e7a a ele. Aqueles que aprovam leis contra os de meu pai ser\u00e3o vomitados e sentir\u00e3o a queima do fogo eterno. Os castimentos ser\u00e3o para a purifica\u00e7\u00e3o dessa humanidade perversa. Fa\u00e7a sua escolha, eu digo isso, para que voc\u00ea esteja ciente. Acorde, para o tempo acabou, muitos rejeitam minha miseric\u00f3rdia, mas mostrei milagres, mas s\u00e3o cegos e surdos. Eu digo aos pol\u00edticos: em nome de Deus, pare agora! Destruirei seus planos, somente eu posso decidir o fim do homem, seus planos sat\u00e2nicos ser\u00e3o varridos, juntamente com voc\u00ea, a justi\u00e7a de meu pai trovejar\u00e1 t\u00e3o alto que todo o universo tremer\u00e1. Aqueles que seguem as leis de Deus n\u00e3o ter\u00e3o medo, mas se alegrem, pois o reino de Deus est\u00e1 pr\u00f3ximo. A paz esteja com voc\u00ea, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u4e00\u4e2a\uff0c\u5973\u513f\u548c\u59d0\u59d0\uff0c\u5199\u4fe1\u7ed9\u4e16\u754c\u3002\u5982\u4eca\uff0c\u6bd4\u60a8\u5982\u6b64\u6050\u60e7\u7684\u75c5\u6bd2\u66f4\u7cdf\u7cd5\u7684\u662f\uff0c\u5728\u8fd9\u79cd\u4eba\u7c7b\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u548c\u601d\u60f3\u4e2d\u7316ramp\u7684\u6b32\u671b\uff0c\u90aa\u6076\uff0c\u6df7\u4e71\u548c\u81ea\u79c1\u3002\u53db\u6559\u4e4b\u738b\u4e4b\u6240\u4ee5\u7edf\u6cbb\uff0c\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u53d7\u818f\u7684\u4eba\u4e0d\u76f8\u4fe1\u6492\u65e6\u7684\u5b58\u5728\u53ca\u5176\u7a8d\u95e8\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u4ed6\u4eec\u6ca1\u6709\u8bf4\u51fa\u6b63\u5728\u6495\u88c2\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u7f6a\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u50cf\u666e\u901a\u7684\u90a3\u6837\u5c06\u5176\u62c6\u5f00\u3002\u6211\u4f1a\u4ece\u90aa\u6076\u4e2d\u5206\u5f00\u5584\uff0c\u56de\u5230\u6211\u8eab\u4e0a\uff0c\u5728\u4e3a\u65f6\u5df2\u665a\u4e4b\u524d\uff0c\u60a8\u4e0d\u518d\u9075\u5faa\u6211\u7684\u6559s\uff0c\u5fcd\u53d7\u90aa\u6076\u5e76\u4f4e\u4e0b\u5934\u3002\u90a3\u4e9b\u901a\u8fc7\u6cd5\u5f8b\u5bf9\u6211\u7236\u4eb2\u7684\u6cd5\u5f8b\u7684\u4eba\u5c06\u88ab\u5455\u5410\uff0c\u5e76\u611f\u5230\u6c38\u6052\u7684\u71c3\u70e7\u3002\u5b97\u6559\u5c06\u662f\u4e3a\u4e86\u51c0\u5316\u8fd9\u79cd\u4e0d\u6b63\u5f53\u7684\u4eba\u7c7b\u3002\u505a\u51fa\u9009\u62e9\uff0c\u6211\u544a\u8bc9\u4f60\uff0c\u8fd9\u6837\u60a8\u5c31\u53ef\u4ee5\u77e5\u9053\u3002\u9192\u6765\u4e86\uff0c\u5f53\u65f6\u5df2\u7ecf\u7ed3\u675f\u4e86\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u62d2\u7edd\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u601c\u60af\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\uff0c\u6211\u5411\u4ed6\u4eec\u5c55\u793a\u4e86\u5947\u8ff9\uff0c\u4f46\u4ed6\u4eec\u662f\u76f2\u76ee\u7684\u804b\u54d1\u4eba\u3002\u6211\u5bf9\u653f\u6cbb\u5bb6\u8bf4\uff1a\u4ee5\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u540d\u4e49\uff0c\u7acb\u5373\u505c\u6b62\uff01\u6211\u5c06\u6467\u6bc1\u60a8\u7684\u8ba1\u5212\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u6211\u53ef\u4ee5\u51b3\u5b9a\u4eba\u7684\u7ec8\u7ed3\uff0c\u60a8\u7684\u6492\u65e6\u8ba1\u5212\u5c06\u88ab\u626b\u9664\uff0c\u4e0e\u60a8\u4e00\u8d77\uff0c\u6211\u7236\u4eb2\u7684\u6b63\u4e49\u4f1a\u5927\u58f0\u96f7\u58f0\uff0c\u4ee5\u81f3\u4e8e\u6574\u4e2a\u5b87\u5b99\u90fd\u4f1a\u98a4\u6296\u3002\u90a3\u4e9b\u9075\u5faa\u4e0a\u5e1d\u5f8b\u6cd5\u7684\u4eba\u4e0d\u4f1a\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u4e3a\u4e86\u6b22\u6b23\u9f13\u821e\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u738b\u56fd\u5728\u573a\u3002\u548c\u5e73\u4e0e\u4f60\u540c\u5728\uff0c\u963f\u4eec\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":16,"month_string":"July","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for being here in prayer and for bending your knees. My children, Italy will pay dearly for the decisions of politicians. Volcanoes will erupt, watch the events that will happen on earth so that you may believe and return to God. Beloved children, soon Satan's chain will be stronger, do not accept what is most dangerous that they will propose to you, they want to take your minds and manipulate you, beware!!! Children, always have your eyes fixed toward the light, that light that you will see and that will give you peace and love, the light that will transform you to live only for good. I love you children and bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie hier im Gebet sind und sich die Knie beugen. Meine Kinder, Italien, wird teuer f\u00fcr die Entscheidungen von Politikern zahlen. Vulkane werden ausbrechen, beobachten die Ereignisse, die auf Erden passieren, damit Sie glauben und zu Gott zur\u00fcckkehren. Geliebte Kinder, bald wird Satans Kette st\u00e4rker sein, akzeptieren nicht, was sie am gef\u00e4hrlichsten sind, was sie Ihnen vorschlagen, sie wollen Ihre Gedanken nehmen und Sie manipulieren, achten Sie auf !!! Kinder, haben Ihre Augen immer auf das Licht gerichtet, das Licht, das Sie sehen werden und das Ihnen Frieden und Liebe gibt, das Licht, das Sie dazu ver\u00e4ndert, nur zum Guten zu leben. Ich liebe dich Kinder und segne dich im Namen der heiligsten Dreifaltigkeit, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por haber doblado las rodillas. Mis hijos, Italia, pagar\u00e1n las decisiones de los pol\u00edticos. Los volcanes erupcionar\u00e1n, analizar\u00e1n los eventos que suceder\u00e1n en la tierra, para que pueda creer y regresar a Dios. Amados ni\u00f1os, pronto la cadena de Satan\u00e1s ser\u00e1 m\u00e1s fuerte, no aceptar\u00e1 lo que m\u00e1s peligroso le ofrecer\u00e1, quieren tomar su mentes y manipularte, atenci\u00f3n !! Ni\u00f1os, siempre ten una mirada fija hacia la luz, esa luz que ver\u00e1s y que te dar\u00e1n paz y amor, la luz que te transformar\u00e1 para vivir solo para el bien. Te amo hijos y te bendigo en el nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Am\u00e9n","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re et d'avoir pli\u00e9 vos genoux. Mes enfants, l'Italie paiera cher pour les d\u00e9cisions des politiciens. Les volcans \u00e9clateront, regarderont les \u00e9v\u00e9nements qui se produiront sur Terre afin que vous puissiez croire et retourner \u00e0 Dieu. Les enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, la cha\u00eene de Satan sera bient\u00f4t plus forte, n'acceptera pas ce qui est le plus dangereux qu'ils vous proposeront, ils veulent vous prendre l'esprit et vous manipuler, attention !!! Les enfants, ont toujours les yeux fix\u00e9s vers la lumi\u00e8re, cette lumi\u00e8re que vous verrez et qui vous donnera la paix et l'amour, la lumi\u00e8re qui vous transformera pour vivre uniquement pour de bon. Je vous aime les enfants et vous b\u00e9nisse au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia. Figli miei, l\u2019Italia pagher\u00e0 a caro prezzo le decisioni dei politici. I vulcani erutteranno, guardate gli eventi che accadranno sulla terra, affinch\u00e9 possiate credere e tornare a Dio. Figli amati, presto la catena di satana sar\u00e0 pi\u00f9 forte, non accettate ci\u00f2 che di pi\u00f9 pericoloso vi proporranno, vogliono prendere le vostre menti e manipolarvi, attenzione!! Figli, abbiate sempre lo sguardo fisso verso la luce, quella luce che vedrete e che vi dar\u00e0 pace e amore, la luce che vi trasformer\u00e0 per vivere solo per il bene. Vi amo figli e vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, amen","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tu na modlitwie i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie. Moje dzieci, W\u0142ochy drogo zap\u0142ac\u0105 za decyzje polityk\u00f3w. Wybuchn\u0105 wulkany, obserwujcie wydarzenia, kt\u00f3re b\u0119d\u0105 mia\u0142y miejsce na ziemi, aby\u015bcie mogli uwierzy\u0107 i wr\u00f3ci\u0107 do Boga. Ukochane dzieci, wkr\u00f3tce sieci szatana b\u0119d\u0105 silniejsze, nie zgadzajcie si\u0119 na to, co jest najbardziej niebezpieczne, chc\u0105 zaw\u0142adn\u0105\u0107 waszymi umys\u0142ami i manipulowa\u0107 wami, uwa\u017cajcie! Moje dzieci, miejcie zawsze wzrok utkwiony w \u015bwiat\u0142o, to \u015bwiat\u0142o, kt\u00f3re zobaczycie i kt\u00f3re da wam pok\u00f3j i mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, \u015bwiat\u0142o, kt\u00f3re was przemieni, aby\u015bcie \u017cyli tylko dla dobra. Kocham was dzieci i b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por dobrar os joelhos. Meus filhos, It\u00e1lia, pagar\u00e3o caro pelas decis\u00f5es dos pol\u00edticos. Os vulc\u00f5es ir\u00e3o erup\u00e7\u00e3o, assistem aos eventos que acontecer\u00e3o na Terra para que voc\u00ea possa acreditar e retornar a Deus. Crian\u00e7as amadas, em breve a cadeia de Satan\u00e1s ser\u00e1 mais forte, n\u00e3o aceita o que \u00e9 mais perigoso que elas propor\u00e3o a voc\u00ea, elas querem levar suas mentes e manipul\u00e1 -lo, cuidado !!! As crian\u00e7as, sempre t\u00eam os olhos fixos em dire\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e0 luz, aquela luz que voc\u00ea ver\u00e1 e que lhe dar\u00e1 paz e amor, a luz que o transformar\u00e1 para viver apenas para sempre. Eu te amo filhos e aben\u00e7oe voc\u00ea em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\u5e76\u5f2f\u8170\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u610f\u5927\u5229\u5c06\u4e3a\u653f\u5ba2\u7684\u51b3\u5b9a\u4ed8\u51fa\u9ad8\u6602\u7684\u4ee3\u4ef7\u3002\u706b\u5c71\u5c06\u7206\u53d1\uff0c\u89c2\u5bdf\u5c06\u5728\u5730\u7403\u4e0a\u53d1\u751f\u7684\u4e8b\u4ef6\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u60a8\u76f8\u4fe1\u5e76\u8fd4\u56de\u4e0a\u5e1d\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5f88\u5feb\u6492\u65e6\u7684\u8fde\u9501\u5e97\u5c06\u53d8\u5f97\u66f4\u52a0\u7262\u56fa\uff0c\u4e0d\u63a5\u53d7\u4ed6\u4eec\u5c06\u5411\u60a8\u63d0\u51fa\u7684\u6700\u5371\u9669\u7684\u4e1c\u897f\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u60f3\u52a8\u5fc3\u60a8\u7684\u601d\u60f3\u5e76\u64cd\u7eb5\u60a8\uff0c\u8981\u5f53\u5fc3\uff01\uff01\uff01\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u603b\u662f\u628a\u773c\u775b\u76ef\u7740\u5149\uff0c\u60a8\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u7684\u5149\u660e\uff0c\u8fd9\u5c06\u4f7f\u60a8\u548c\u5e73\u4e0e\u7231\uff0c\u5149\u660e\u4f1a\u6539\u53d8\u60a8\u7684\u5149\u660e\u3002\u6211\u7231\u4f60\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4ee5\u6700\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":18,"month_string":"July","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people, receive my blessing. I bless your spiritual body, your physical body and all of your organs.... I bless family ties... I bless respect, unity and truth.... I bless charity and honesty.... I bless the parents and the children... I bless every home... I bless the mind and the thought.... I bless every word so that everything that comes to you and goes out from you may be for the good of the soul and for your salvation. You are free my children, free to serve in my vineyard, free to love me and to love my most holy Mother. You have free will so that each one may decide whether or not to follow me. Within that freedom, each one possesses the gift of discernment by which each one in particular knows that in order to stand firm in the spiritual life he must know the foundations that make the structure strong and firm. The foundations of my house are written with the Love of my Father, with my blood and with my Holy Spirit. I have stayed with my children to nourish them and to walk my path; I have given them my Mother so that they may love her and the divine aids so that they may not remain alone. My children are recognized by their love for their neighbour, by their fraternity among themselves, that is the sign that they are my children. My people, the spiritual battle is getting hotter, the power of evil has released its rider on humanity bringing the scourges of nature, famine, disease and the fall of the economy advancing from country to country, with the purpose of bringing forth wrath in my children so that they may be aggressors and thieves. You continue not to understand, my beloved people, that the human creature who lives far from me is prey to evil. Those who are weak in not receiving me, those who do not amend their way of sin, of pride, of disobedience, of concupiscence, are in grave danger of falling prey to evil, of becoming the servants of evil and of condemning themselves. Pride, the great evil of man, at this very moment is a great danger for the soul, because it opens the doors more than before to Satan. You must live each moment in order to grow spiritually, not so that evil may lead you away from me. Spiritual life my children is not static, you must constantly call upon me so that I may work and act in and with you. I am not a stranger, 'I am your God' and I love you, I seek you in every way so that you may come to me, I do not wish you to be lost. Heed my calls, do not let them pass you by. If you would see how much you are approaching, you would change right now, without hesitation. My people are hard and that is why they live such great trials. A new virus appears... I call you to use the plant called fumaria officinalis l. In its stems, flowers and leaves, marigold for the skin, and garlic. Without fear trust in my love for my people, I have already mentioned to you that humanity will change, the war expands. My children, I warn you to come closer to me and to initiate conversion. Invite me to remain in you, so that you turn away from sin. Each one of you is my great treasure.... Call me and do not separate yourselves from me. I love you, enter into my heart. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, przyjmij moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 wasze cia\u0142o duchowe, wasze cia\u0142o fizyczne i wszystkie wasze organy.... B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 wi\u0119zi rodzinne... B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 szacunek, jedno\u015b\u0107 i prawd\u0119.... B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 dobroczynno\u015b\u0107 i uczciwo\u015b\u0107.... B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 rodzic\u00f3w i dzieci... B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 ka\u017cdy dom... B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 umys\u0142 i my\u015bli.... B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 ka\u017cde s\u0142owo, aby wszystko, co do was przychodzi i od was wychodzi, by\u0142o dla dobra duszy i dla waszego zbawienia. Jeste\u015bcie wolni moje dzieci, wolni, by s\u0142u\u017cy\u0107 w mojej winnicy, wolni, by kocha\u0107 Mnie i kocha\u0107 moj\u0105 naj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105 Matk\u0119. Macie woln\u0105 wol\u0119, aby ka\u017cdy m\u00f3g\u0142 zdecydowa\u0107, czy chce i\u015b\u0107 za mn\u0105, czy nie. W ramach tej wolno\u015bci ka\u017cdy posiada dar rozeznania, dzi\u0119ki kt\u00f3remu ka\u017cdy w szczeg\u00f3lno\u015bci wie, \u017ce aby wytrwa\u0107 w \u017cyciu duchowym musi pozna\u0107 fundamenty, kt\u00f3re czyni\u0105 budowl\u0119 mocn\u0105 i trwa\u0142\u0105. Fundamenty mojego domu s\u0105 napisane Mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 mojego Ojca, moj\u0105 Krwi\u0105 i moim Duchem \u015awi\u0119tym. Zosta\u0142em z moimi dzie\u0107mi, aby je karmi\u0107 i aby sz\u0142y moj\u0105 drog\u0105; da\u0142em im moj\u0105 Matk\u0119, aby j\u0105 kocha\u0142y i boskie pomoce, aby nie pozosta\u0142y same. Moje dzieci poznaje si\u0119 po mi\u0142o\u015bci do bli\u017aniego, po braterstwie mi\u0119dzy sob\u0105, to jest znak, \u017ce s\u0105 moimi dzie\u0107mi. M\u00f3j lud, walka duchowa staje si\u0119 coraz gor\u0119tsza, moc z\u0142a wypu\u015bci\u0142a swojego je\u017ad\u017aca na ludzko\u015b\u0107 przynosz\u0105c plagi natury, g\u0142\u00f3d, choroby i upadek gospodarki post\u0119puj\u0105cy od kraju do kraju, w celu wywo\u0142ania gniewu w moich dzieciach, aby by\u0142y agresorami i z\u0142odziejami. Nadal nie rozumiecie, m\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludzie, \u017ce stworzenie ludzkie, kt\u00f3re \u017cyje z dala ode Mnie, jest ofiar\u0105 z\u0142a. Ci, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0105 s\u0142abi i nie przyjmuj\u0105 mnie, ci, kt\u00f3rzy nie zmieniaj\u0105 swojej drogi grzechu, pychy, niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwa, rozwi\u0105z\u0142o\u015bci, s\u0105 w powa\u017cnym niebezpiecze\u0144stwie, \u017ce padn\u0105 ofiar\u0105 z\u0142a, \u017ce stan\u0105 si\u0119 s\u0142ugami z\u0142a i \u017ce sami si\u0119 pot\u0119pi\u0105. Pycha, wielkie z\u0142o cz\u0142owieka, w tej w\u0142a\u015bnie chwili jest wielkim niebezpiecze\u0144stwem dla duszy, bo otwiera drzwi szatanowi bardziej ni\u017c przedtem. Musicie \u017cy\u0107 ka\u017cd\u0105 chwil\u0105, aby wzrasta\u0107 duchowo, a nie po to, aby z\u0142o mog\u0142o was odci\u0105gn\u0105\u0107 ode Mnie. \u017bycie duchowe moje dzieci nie jest statyczne, musicie stale mnie wzywa\u0107, abym m\u00f3g\u0142 pracowa\u0107 i dzia\u0142a\u0107 w was i z wami. Nie jestem obcy, \"Ja jestem twoim Bogiem\" i kocham ci\u0119, szukam ci\u0119 na wszelkie sposoby, aby\u015b m\u00f3g\u0142 przyj\u015b\u0107 do mnie, nie chc\u0119, aby\u015b si\u0119 zgubi\u0142. S\u0142uchajcie moich wezwa\u0144, nie pozw\u00f3lcie, aby was omin\u0119\u0142y. Gdyby\u015bcie zobaczyli, jak bardzo si\u0119 zbli\u017cacie, zmieniliby\u015bcie si\u0119 ju\u017c teraz, bez wahania. M\u00f3j lud jest twardy i dlatego prze\u017cywa tak wielkie pr\u00f3by. Pojawia si\u0119 nowy wirus... Wzywam was do stosowania ro\u015bliny o nazwie fumaria officinalis l. W jej \u0142odygach, kwiatach i li\u015bciach, nagietka na sk\u00f3r\u0119 i czosnku. Bez obaw ufajcie w moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do mojego ludu, wspomina\u0142em wam ju\u017c, \u017ce ludzko\u015b\u0107 si\u0119 zmieni, wojna si\u0119 rozszerza. Moje dzieci, ostrzegam was, aby\u015bcie zbli\u017cyli si\u0119 do Mnie i zainicjowali nawr\u00f3cenie. Zach\u0119cajcie mnie do pozostania w was, aby\u015bcie odwr\u00f3cili si\u0119 od grzechu. Ka\u017cdy z was jest moim wielkim skarbem.... Wzywajcie mnie i nie oddzielajcie si\u0119 ode mnie. Kocham was, wejd\u017acie do mojego serca. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":19,"month_string":"July","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for being here in prayer and for bending your knees. Children, I, your Mother will be your comfort together with my Son Jesus. My children, why are you surprised, my Son was also persecuted, you will be too. My children, you will be much attacked by evil, but listen to my words, be strong in prayer, be soldiers of light, remove fear from your hearts and minds and believe in Jesus who will save all his faithful brothers and sisters, be light for this world of darkness and when you are in despondency call upon me and I will be with you. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie hier im Gebet sind und sich die Knie beugen. Kinder, ich, deine Mutter wird dein Trost zusammen mit meinem Sohn Jesus sein. Meine Kinder, warum bist du \u00fcberrascht, mein Sohn wurde auch verfolgt, du wirst es auch sein. Meine Kinder, du wirst viel vom B\u00f6sen angegriffen sein, aber h\u00f6r auf meine Worte, sei stark im Gebet, sei Soldaten des Lichts, entfernen F\u00fcr diese Welt der Dunkelheit und wenn Sie in Verzweiflung sind, rufen Sie mich an und ich werde bei Ihnen sein. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por haber doblado las rodillas. Hijos, yo, tu madre, ser\u00e9 tu consuelo con mi hijo Jes\u00fas. Ni\u00f1os, porque est\u00e1s sorprendido, mi hijo tambi\u00e9n ha sido perseguido, t\u00fa tambi\u00e9n lo ser\u00e1s. Mis hijos, ser\u00e1n muy atacados por el mal, pero escuchen mis palabras, sean fuertes en oraci\u00f3n, sean soldados de luz, eliminan el miedo de su coraz\u00f3n y de sus mentes y crean en Jes\u00fas que salvar\u00e1 a todos sus fieles hermanos, se La luz para este mundo de la oscuridad y cuando est\u00e9s desesperado me invoquen y estar\u00e9 contigo. Ahora te bendiga en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re et d'avoir pli\u00e9 vos genoux. Enfants, moi, ta m\u00e8re sera ton r\u00e9confort avec mon fils J\u00e9sus. Mes enfants, pourquoi \u00eates-vous surpris, mon fils a \u00e9galement \u00e9t\u00e9 pers\u00e9cut\u00e9, vous le serez aussi. Mes enfants, vous serez tr\u00e8s attaqu\u00e9 par le mal, mais \u00e9coutez mes paroles, soyez fort dans la pri\u00e8re, soyez des soldats de lumi\u00e8re, retirez la peur de votre c\u0153ur et de votre esprit et croire en J\u00e9sus qui sauvera tous ses fid\u00e8les fr\u00e8res et s\u0153urs, \u00eatre l\u00e9ger Pour ce monde des t\u00e9n\u00e8bres et lorsque vous \u00eates dans le d\u00e9couragement, appelez-moi et je serai avec vous. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia. Figli, Io, vostra Madre sar\u00f2 il vostro conforto insieme a mio Figlio Ges\u00f9. Figli, perch\u00e9 vi meravigliate, anche mio Figlio \u00e8 stato perseguitato, lo sarete anche voi. Figli miei, sarete molto attaccati dal male, ma ascoltate le mie parole, siate forti nella preghiera, siate soldati di luce, togliete la paura dal vostro cuore e dalle vostre menti e credete in Ges\u00f9 che salver\u00e0 tutti i suoi fratelli fedeli, siate luce per questo mondo di tenebre e quando sarete nello sconforto invocatemi ed Io sar\u00f2 con voi. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tu na modlitwie i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie. Moje dzieci, Ja, wasza Matka, b\u0119d\u0119 wasz\u0105 pociech\u0105 razem z moim Synem Jezusem. Dzieci moje, czemu si\u0119 dziwicie, m\u00f3j Syn by\u0142 prze\u015bladowany, wy te\u017c b\u0119dziecie prze\u015bladowani. Moje dzieci, b\u0119dziecie mocno atakowani przez z\u0142o, ale s\u0142uchajcie moich s\u0142\u00f3w, b\u0105d\u017acie mocni w modlitwie, b\u0105d\u017acie \u017co\u0142nierzami \u015bwiat\u0142a, usu\u0144cie strach z waszych serc i umys\u0142\u00f3w i wierzcie w Jezusa, kt\u00f3ry uratuje wszystkich swoich wiernych braci i siostry, b\u0105d\u017acie \u015bwiat\u0142em dla tego \u015bwiata ciemno\u015bci, a gdy b\u0119dziecie w rozpaczy, wzywajcie mnie, a ja b\u0119d\u0119 z wami. A teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por dobrar os joelhos. Filhos, eu, sua m\u00e3e ser\u00e1 seu conforto junto com meu filho Jesus. Meus filhos, por que voc\u00ea est\u00e1 surpreso, meu filho tamb\u00e9m foi perseguido, voc\u00ea tamb\u00e9m estar\u00e1. Meus filhos, voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 muito atacado pelo mal, mas ou\u00e7a minhas palavras, seja forte em ora\u00e7\u00e3o, seja soldados de luz, remova o medo de seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e mentes e acredite em Jesus que salvar\u00e3o todos os seus irm\u00e3os e irm\u00e3s fi\u00e9is, sejam leves Para este mundo das trevas e quando voc\u00ea estiver em des\u00e2nimo, me chama e estarei com voc\u00ea. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\u5e76\u5f2f\u8170\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\uff0c\u4f60\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u5c06\u4e0e\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u4e00\u8d77\u611f\u5230\u5b89\u6170\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4f60\u4e3a\u4ec0\u4e48\u611f\u5230\u60ca\u8bb6\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u4e5f\u53d7\u5230\u4e86\u8feb\u5bb3\uff0c\u4f60\u4e5f\u4f1a\u53d7\u5230\u8feb\u5bb3\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4f60\u4f1a\u53d7\u5230\u90aa\u6076\u7684\u653b\u51fb\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u542c\u6211\u7684\u8bdd\uff0c\u5728\u7948\u7977\u4e2d\u575a\u5f3a\uff0c\u6210\u4e3a\u5149\u660e\u7684\u58eb\u5175\uff0c\u4ece\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u6d88\u9664\u6050\u60e7\uff0c\u76f8\u4fe1\u8036\u7a23\uff0c\u8036\u7a23\u5c06\u62ef\u6551\u4ed6\u6240\u6709\u5fe0\u5b9e\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\u59d0\u59b9\uff0c\u6210\u4e3a\u5149\u660e\u5bf9\u4e8e\u8fd9\u4e2a\u9ed1\u6697\u7684\u4e16\u754c\uff0c\u5f53\u60a8\u611f\u5230\u6cae\u4e27\u65f6\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u548c\u60a8\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":23,"month_string":"July","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for being here in prayer and for answering my call in your hearts. My children, this is the time of injustice, be humble and do penance. My children, the Bishopric of Rome is in serious difficulty, pray for the priests, the Church is and always will be one and holy, but some souls who dwell in it will be taken by evil.  Come here to this place blessed by the Father and drink in the fountain of my Son Jesus.  My children, hurricanes will increase, soon there will be an attack by evil, please believe my words. My children, my Son will divide the evil from the good, you continue in prayer, times will get harder and harder, new viruses will arise, your freedom hangs in the balance. Be warriors of light. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie hier im Gebet sind und meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen beantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, dies ist die Zeit der Ungerechtigkeit, seien Sie dem\u00fctig und tun Bu\u00dfe. Meine Kinder, das Bistum Roms, ist in ernsthaften Schwierigkeiten, beten f\u00fcr die Priester, die Kirche ist und wird immer ein und heilig sein, aber einige Seelen, die darin wohnen, werden vom B\u00f6sen genommen. Komm hierher an diesen Ort, der vom Vater gesegnet und im Brunnen meines Sohnes Jesus gesegnet ist. Meine Kinder, Hurrikane werden zunehmen, bald wird es einen Angriff von B\u00f6se geben, bitte glauben Sie meinen Worten. Meine Kinder, mein Sohn wird das B\u00f6se aus dem Guten teilen, Sie werden im Gebet fortgesetzt, Zeiten werden immer h\u00e4rter, neue Viren werden entstehen, Ihre Freiheit h\u00e4ngt im Gleichgewicht. Lichtkrieger sein. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por haber respondido mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Los ni\u00f1os, este es el momento de la injusticia, sean humildes y hacen penitencia. Hijos, el obispado de Roma tiene serias dificultades, rez\u00f3 por los sacerdotes, la iglesia es y siempre ser\u00e1 una y santa, pero algunas almas que viven en \u00e9l ser\u00e1n tomadas por el mal. Ven aqu\u00ed, en este lugar bendecido por el Padre y la bebida en la fuente de mi hijo Jes\u00fas. Mis hijos, los huracanes aumentar\u00e1n, pronto habr\u00e1 un ataque de la obra del mal, por favor, cree en mis palabras. Mis hijos, mi hijo dividir\u00e1 el mal del bien, contin\u00faa en oraci\u00f3n, los tiempos ser\u00e1n cada vez m\u00e1s duros, aparecer\u00e1n nuevos virus, su libertad est\u00e1 en equilibrio. Ser guerreros de la luz. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re et d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, c'est le moment de l'injustice, \u00eatre humble et faire p\u00e9nitence. Mes enfants, l'\u00e9v\u00each\u00e9 de Rome sont tr\u00e8s en difficult\u00e9, prient pour les pr\u00eatres, l'\u00e9glise est et sera toujours une et sainte, mais certaines \u00e2mes qui y habitent seront prises par le mal. Venez ici dans cet endroit b\u00e9ni par le P\u00e8re et buvez dans la fontaine de mon Fils J\u00e9sus. Mes enfants, les ouragans augmenteront, bient\u00f4t il y aura une attaque du mal, croyez-le bien, croyez mes paroles. Mes enfants, mon fils divisera le mal du bien, vous continuez dans la pri\u00e8re, les temps deviendront de plus en plus difficiles, de nouveaux virus surgiront, votre libert\u00e9 est en jeu. Soyez des guerriers de la lumi\u00e8re. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, questo \u00e8 il tempo dell\u2019ingiustizia, siate umili e fate penitenza. Figli, il Vescovato di Roma \u00e8 in seria difficolt\u00e0, pregate per i sacerdoti, la Chiesa \u00e8 e sar\u00e0 sempre una e santa, ma alcune anime che abitano in essa verranno prese dal male.  Venite qui, in questo luogo benedetto dal Padre e abbeveratevi nella fonte di mio Figlio Ges\u00f9.  Figli miei, gli uragani aumenteranno, presto ci sar\u00e0 un attentato per opera del male, vi prego, credete alle mie parole. Figli miei, mio Figlio divider\u00e0 il male dal bene, voi continuate nella preghiera, i tempi saranno sempre pi\u00f9 duri, nuovi virus si affacceranno, la vostra libert\u00e0 \u00e8 in bilico. Siate Guerrieri di luce. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tu na modlitwie i \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, to jest czas niesprawiedliwo\u015bci, b\u0105d\u017acie pokorni i czy\u0144cie pokut\u0119. Moje dzieci, Biskupstwo Rzymu prze\u017cywa powa\u017cne trudno\u015bci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za kap\u0142an\u00f3w, Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 jest i zawsze b\u0119dzie jeden i \u015bwi\u0119ty, ale niekt\u00f3re dusze w nim \u017cyj\u0105ce zostan\u0105 porwane przez z\u0142o. Przyjd\u017acie tutaj, na to miejsce pob\u0142ogos\u0142awione przez Ojca i pijcie ze \u017ar\u00f3d\u0142a Mojego Syna Jezusa. Moje dzieci, huragany b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 nasila\u0107, wkr\u00f3tce nast\u0105pi atak z\u0142a, b\u0142agam was, uwierzcie w moje s\u0142owa. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3j Syn rozdzieli z\u0142o od dobra, wy trwajcie w modlitwie, czasy b\u0119d\u0105 coraz trudniejsze, pojawi\u0105 si\u0119 nowe wirusy, wasza wolno\u015b\u0107 wisi na w\u0142osku. B\u0105d\u017acie wojownikami \u015bwiat\u0142a. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por atender minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, este \u00e9 o momento da injusti\u00e7a, seja humilde e faz penit\u00eancia. Meus filhos, o bispado de Roma est\u00e1 em dificuldade, ore pelos padres, a Igreja \u00e9 e sempre ser\u00e1 uma e santo, mas algumas almas que habitam nela ser\u00e3o levadas pelo mal. Venha aqui para este lugar aben\u00e7oado pelo Pai e beba na fonte do meu filho Jesus. Meus filhos, os furac\u00f5es aumentar\u00e3o, em breve haver\u00e1 um ataque pelo mal, por favor, acredite nas minhas palavras. Meus filhos, meu filho dividir\u00e1 o mal do bem, voc\u00ea continua em ora\u00e7\u00e3o, os tempos ficar\u00e3o cada vez mais dif\u00edceis, novos v\u00edrus surgir\u00e3o, sua liberdade pendura no equil\u00edbrio. Ser guerreiros da luz. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u63a5\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u4e0d\u516c\u6b63\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\uff0c\u8981\u8c26\u865a\u5e76pen\u6094\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7f57\u9a6c\u7684\u4e3b\u6559\u5728\u4e25\u91cd\u7684\u56f0\u96be\u4e2d\uff0c\u4e3a\u795e\u7236\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u200b\u200b\u6559\u4f1a\u662f\u5e76\u4e14\u6c38\u8fdc\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u4eba\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u6709\u4e9b\u4f4f\u5728\u5176\u4e2d\u7684\u7075\u9b42\u5c06\u88ab\u90aa\u6076\u5e26\u8d70\u3002\u6765\u8fd9\u91cc\u6765\u5230\u7236\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u7684\u5730\u65b9\uff0c\u5728\u6211\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u6cc9\u6e90\u4e2d\u559d\u9152\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u98d3\u98ce\u5c06\u589e\u52a0\uff0c\u5f88\u5feb\u5c31\u4f1a\u906d\u53d7\u90aa\u6076\u7684\u653b\u51fb\uff0c\u8bf7\u76f8\u4fe1\u6211\u7684\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u4f1a\u5c06\u90aa\u6076\u4e0e\u5584\u826f\u5206\u5f00\uff0c\u60a8\u7ee7\u7eed\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u65f6\u4ee3\u5c06\u53d8\u5f97\u8d8a\u6765\u8d8a\u56f0\u96be\uff0c\u65b0\u75c5\u6bd2\u4f1a\u51fa\u73b0\uff0c\u60a8\u7684\u81ea\u7531\u60ac\u800c\u672a\u51b3\u3002\u6210\u4e3a\u5149\u7684\u6218\u58eb\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":24,"month_string":"July","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved people of my Son, beloved children, I draw near to each of my own to offer you my hands at this moment of blindness, when the evil oppressor of souls has sent his emissaries to blindfold as many as possible. Maintain your constant practice of God\u2019s Law, of the sacraments, of the beatitudes and other pious goals. Not giving the enemy respite, my Son\u2019s people must constantly grow in the spiritual life in order to go deeper and to be more closely united to my divine son. Practice the corporal and spiritual works of mercy so that you would aspire to the good and not fall prey to those who wish to blindfold you so that you would not fulfil them, would not act in the good and so that your hearts would be hardened. Be assured that every act of love for your neighbour and for love of God is a wellspring of blessings for you, even if you do not ask for them. My children are those who within themselves recognize that they are sinners, who are humble, meek of heart and who deeply love my divine son above all else. Children, fight evil with good - it is the good that should flourish in you at this time; even if you are viewed with indifference and rejection, this leads you to become more like my Divine Son. People of my Son, war is progressing and humanity does not see it\u2026. Pray, people of my Son: war is positioning itself to pounce forcefully and unexpectedly. Pray, people of my Son, pray: a new plague will be the cry of the powerful. Homes will again become shelters for their inhabitants and borders will be closed. Pray, people of my Son, pray; you will be offered the mark when you are hungry. Refuse! Children, nature will be modified by the powers in their struggle for supremacy: some will modify the climate and others the tectonic faults. Not everything that happens is the work of nature. Remain attentive: do not forget that the sun is doing damage to the earth, exacerbating suffering. Pray, a powerful person will fall in a political betrayal; he will be killed and there will be chaos on earth. People of my Son, communism is advancing and world hunger is one of its great weapons. The church of my Son is in shadow\u2026. My Son\u2019s church is undergoing persecution in small countries, which will later progress to the great nations. Do not lose faith; continue being faithful to my Divine Son. You are heading towards the purification and some of my children are becoming tired and overwhelmed by the wait, and yet they continue in constant expectation, as in the depths of their hearts they hear: 'you must bear fruit for eternal life\u201d. I am the mother of humanity and I suffer because of the foolishness of so many of my children who, having been called to be lighted lamps, have become conceited and do not illuminate their surroundings, becoming mixed with the things of the world. Children, come to me and walk towards the true way, led by my hand. Come to me and I will lead you to my divine son. Give me your hands without fear and be ready to walk without looking sideways, but only towards my Son. I bless you, beloved children; do not fear. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany ludu mojego Syna, umi\u0142owane dzieci, zbli\u017cam si\u0119 do ka\u017cdego z moich, aby ofiarowa\u0107 wam moje r\u0119ce w tej chwili za\u015blepienia, kiedy z\u0142y ciemi\u0119zca dusz wys\u0142a\u0142 swoich emisariuszy, aby o\u015blepi\u0107 jak najwi\u0119cej. Zachowujcie sta\u0142e praktykowanie Prawa Bo\u017cego, sakrament\u00f3w, b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stw i innych pobo\u017cnych cel\u00f3w. Nie daj\u0105c wrogowi wytchnienia, lud mojego Syna musi stale wzrasta\u0107 w \u017cyciu duchowym, aby zej\u015b\u0107 g\u0142\u0119biej i by\u0107 \u015bci\u015blej zjednoczonym z moim Boskim Synem. Praktykujcie cielesne i duchowe uczynki mi\u0142osierdzia, aby\u015bcie d\u0105\u017cyli do dobra i nie padli ofiar\u0105 tych, kt\u00f3rzy chc\u0105 was za\u015blepi\u0107, aby\u015bcie ich nie spe\u0142niali, nie post\u0119powali w dobru i aby wasze serca by\u0142y zatwardzia\u0142e. B\u0105d\u017acie pewni, \u017ce ka\u017cdy akt mi\u0142o\u015bci do bli\u017aniego i mi\u0142o\u015bci do Boga jest dla was \u017ar\u00f3d\u0142em b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stw, nawet je\u015bli o nie nie prosicie. Moimi dzie\u0107mi s\u0105 ci, kt\u00f3rzy w sobie uznaj\u0105, \u017ce s\u0105 grzesznikami, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0105 pokorni, cisi w sercu i kt\u00f3rzy g\u0142\u0119boko kochaj\u0105 mojego Boskiego Syna ponad wszystko. Dzieci, zwalczajcie z\u0142o dobrem - to w\u0142a\u015bnie dobro powinno w was rozkwita\u0107 w tym czasie; nawet je\u015bli jeste\u015bcie postrzegani z oboj\u0119tno\u015bci\u0105 i odrzuceniem, prowadzi to do tego, \u017ce stajecie si\u0119 bardziej podobni do mojego Boskiego Syna. Ludu mojego Syna, wojna post\u0119puje, a ludzko\u015b\u0107 tego nie widzi.... M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu mojego Syna: wojna ustawia si\u0119, aby zaatakowa\u0107 z si\u0142\u0105 i niespodziewanie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu mojego Syna, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: nowa plaga b\u0119dzie krzykiem pot\u0119\u017cnych. Domy zn\u00f3w stan\u0105 si\u0119 schronami dla ich mieszka\u0144c\u00f3w, a granice zostan\u0105 zamkni\u0119te. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu mojego Syna, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119; zostanie wam zaproponowany znak, gdy b\u0119dziecie g\u0142odni. Odmawiajcie! Dzieci, przyroda b\u0119dzie modyfikowana przez mocarstwa w ich walce o supremacj\u0119: jedni b\u0119d\u0105 modyfikowa\u0107 klimat, a inni uskoki tektoniczne. Nie wszystko, co si\u0119 dzieje, jest dzie\u0142em natury. B\u0105d\u017acie uwa\u017cni: nie zapominajcie, \u017ce s\u0142o\u0144ce wyrz\u0105dza szkody na ziemi, pog\u0142\u0119biaj\u0105c cierpienie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, pot\u0119\u017cna osoba upadnie w wyniku zdrady politycznej; zostanie zabita i na ziemi zapanuje chaos. Ludzie mojego Syna, komunizm post\u0119puje, a g\u0142\u00f3d na \u015bwiecie jest jedn\u0105 z jego wielkich broni. Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 mojego Syna jest w cieniu.... Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 mojego Syna prze\u017cywa prze\u015bladowania w ma\u0142ych krajach, kt\u00f3re p\u00f3\u017aniej przejd\u0105 na wielkie narody. Nie tra\u0107cie wiary; nadal b\u0105d\u017acie wierni mojemu Boskiemu Synowi. Zmierzacie w kierunku oczyszczenia i niekt\u00f3re z moich dzieci staj\u0105 si\u0119 zm\u0119czone i przyt\u0142oczone oczekiwaniem, a jednak trwaj\u0105 w ci\u0105g\u0142ym oczekiwaniu, gdy\u017c w g\u0142\u0119bi serca s\u0142ysz\u0105: \"musicie przynie\u015b\u0107 owoc na \u017cycie wieczne\". Jestem Matk\u0105 ludzko\u015bci i cierpi\u0119 z powodu g\u0142upoty tak wielu moich dzieci, kt\u00f3re powo\u0142ane do bycia zapalonymi lampami, sta\u0142y si\u0119 zarozumia\u0142e i nie o\u015bwietlaj\u0105 swojego otoczenia, mieszaj\u0105c si\u0119 z rzeczami tego \u015bwiata. Dzieci, przyjd\u017acie do mnie i pod\u0105\u017cajcie ku prawdziwej drodze, prowadzeni moj\u0105 r\u0119k\u0105. Przyjd\u017acie do mnie, a ja was poprowadz\u0119 do mojego Boskiego Syna. Podajcie mi wasze r\u0119ce bez l\u0119ku i b\u0105d\u017acie gotowi i\u015b\u0107 bez ogl\u0105dania si\u0119 na boki, ale tylko w kierunku mojego Syna. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, umi\u0142owane dzieci; nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":24,"month_string":"July","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Children, thank you for being here in prayer, I bless this house, for like the first Christians there is prayer and sharing. Prepare your shelters, for the persecution of Christians has begun, but you need not fear. (Galatians 6 -7\/9) 'Make no mistake: God is not mocked, for a person will reap only what he sows, because the one who sows for his flesh will reap corruption from the flesh, but the one who sows for the spirit will reap eternal life from the spirit. Let us not grow tired of doing good, for in due time we shall reap our harvest, if we do not give up. So then, while we have the opportunity, let us do good to all, but especially to those who belong to the family of the faith'. Now I bless you and leave my peace in your hearts, Amen.","text_de":"Kinder, danke, dass du hier im Gebet bist, ich segne dieses Haus, denn wie die ersten Christen gibt es Gebet und Teilen. Bereiten Sie Ihre Unterk\u00fcnfte vor, denn die Verfolgung von Christen hat begonnen, aber Sie m\u00fcssen keine Angst haben. (Galater 6 -7\/9) 'Machen Der Geist wird das ewige Leben aus dem Geist ernten. Lassen Sie uns nicht satt, Gutes zu tun, denn zu gegebener Zeit werden wir unsere Ernte ernten, wenn wir nicht aufgeben. Also, w\u00e4hrend wir die Gelegenheit dazu haben, lassen Sie uns allen gut tun, insbesondere zu denen, die zur Familie des Glaubens angeh\u00f6ren. Jetzt segne ich dich und verlasse meinen Frieden in deinen Herzen, Amen.","text_es":"Ni\u00f1os, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n, bendigo esta casa, porque como los primeros cristianos hay oraci\u00f3n y compartir. Prepare sus refugios, porque la persecuci\u00f3n de los cristianos ha comenzado, pero no tiene que temer. (G\u00e1latas 6-7\/9) 'No obtienes ilusiones; No podemos hacer un juego de Dios. Todos recolectar\u00e1n lo que \u00e9l habr\u00e1 sembrado. Aquellos que sembren en su carne, de la carne recolectar\u00e1n corrupci\u00f3n; Aquellos que sembran en esp\u00edritu, del Esp\u00edritu recolectar\u00e1n la vida eterna. Y no nos cansemos de hacer el bien; De hecho, si no nos damos por vencidos, en ese momento cosecharemos. Entonces, dado que tenemos la oportunidad, operamos el bien hacia todos, especialmente hacia los hermanos en la fe. Ahora te bendigo y dejar\u00e9 mi paz en tus corazones, am\u00e9n","text_fr":"Enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re, je b\u00e9nis cette maison, car comme les premiers chr\u00e9tiens l\u00e0-bas, il y a la pri\u00e8re et le partage. Pr\u00e9parez vos abris, car la pers\u00e9cution des chr\u00e9tiens a commenc\u00e9, mais vous n'avez pas besoin de craindre. (Galates 6 -7\/9) \u00abNe vous y trompez pas: Dieu n'est pas moqu\u00e9, car une personne ne r\u00e9coltera que ce qu'il s\u00e8de, parce que celui qui seme L'esprit r\u00e9coltera la vie \u00e9ternelle de l'Esprit. Ne nous lassons pas de faire du bien, car en temps voulu, nous r\u00e9colterons notre r\u00e9colte, si nous n'abandonnons pas. Alors, alors que nous en avons l'occasion, faisons du bien \u00e0 tous, mais surtout \u00e0 ceux qui appartiennent \u00e0 la famille de la foi \u00bb. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis et laisse ma paix dans vos c\u0153urs, Amen.","text_it":"Figli, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera, Io benedico questa casa, perch\u00e9 come i primi cristiani vi \u00e8 la preghiera e la condivisione. Preparate i vostri rifugi, perch\u00e9 la persecuzione dei cristiani ha avuto inizio, ma voi non dovete temere. (Galati 6 -7\/9)  'Non vi fate illusioni; non ci si pu\u00f2 prendere gioco di Dio. Ciascuno raccoglier\u00e0 quello che avr\u00e0 seminato. Chi semina nella sua carne, dalla carne raccoglier\u00e0 corruzione; chi semina nello Spirito, dallo Spirito raccoglier\u00e0 vita eterna. E non stanchiamoci di fare il bene; se infatti non desistiamo, a suo tempo mieteremo. Poich\u00e9 dunque ne abbiamo l\u2019occasione, operiamo il bene verso tutti, soprattutto verso i fratelli nella Fede.'  Ora vi benedico e lascer\u00f2 la mia pace nei vostri cuori, amen","text_pl":"Dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tu na modlitwie, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 ten dom, bo jak u pierwszych chrze\u015bcijan jest tu modlitwa i dzielenie si\u0119. Przygotujcie swoje schronienia, bo rozpocz\u0119\u0142o si\u0119 prze\u015bladowanie chrze\u015bcijan, ale nie musicie si\u0119 obawia\u0107. (Galat\u00f3w 6 -7\/9) 'Nie \u0142ud\u017acie si\u0119: B\u00f3g nie dozwoli z siebie szydzi\u0107. A co cz\u0142owiek sieje, to i \u017c\u0105\u0107 b\u0119dzie: kto sieje w ciele swoim, jako plon cia\u0142a zbierze zag\u0142ad\u0119; kto sieje w duchu, jako plon ducha zbierze \u017cycie wieczne. W czynieniu dobrze nie ustawajmy, bo gdy pora nadejdzie, b\u0119dziemy zbiera\u0107 plony, o ile w pracy nie ustaniemy. A zatem, dop\u00f3ki mamy czas, czy\u0144my dobrze wszystkim, a zw\u0142aszcza naszym braciom w wierze'.  Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was i zostawiam m\u00f3j pok\u00f3j w waszych sercach, Amen.","text_pt":"Filhos, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o, aben\u00e7oo esta casa, pois, como os primeiros crist\u00e3os, h\u00e1 ora\u00e7\u00e3o e compartilhamento. Prepare seus abrigos, para a persegui\u00e7\u00e3o aos crist\u00e3os, come\u00e7ou, mas voc\u00ea n\u00e3o precisa temer. (G\u00e1latas 6 -7\/9) 'N\u00e3o se engane: Deus n\u00e3o \u00e9 ridicularizado, pois uma pessoa colher\u00e1 apenas o que ela semeia, porque quem semeia por sua carne colher\u00e1 a corrup\u00e7\u00e3o da carne, mas quem semeia para o O Esp\u00edrito colher\u00e1 a vida eterna do Esp\u00edrito. N\u00e3o nos cansemos de fazer o bem, pois no devido tempo colheremos nossa colheita, se n\u00e3o desistirmos. Ent\u00e3o, embora tenhamos a oportunidade, vamos fazer o bem a todos, mas especialmente para aqueles que pertencem \u00e0 fam\u00edlia da f\u00e9 '. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo e deixo minha paz em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u6211\u795d\u798f\u8fd9\u6240\u623f\u5b50\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5c31\u50cf\u7b2c\u4e00\u6279\u57fa\u7763\u5f92\u4e00\u6837\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u548c\u5206\u4eab\u3002\u51c6\u5907\u5e87\u62a4\u6240\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5bf9\u57fa\u7763\u5f92\u7684\u8feb\u5bb3\u5df2\u7ecf\u5f00\u59cb\uff0c\u4f46\u60a8\u4e0d\u5fc5\u62c5\u5fc3\u3002 \uff08\u52a0\u62c9\u592a\u4e666 -7\/9\uff09'\u6beb\u65e0\u7591\u95ee\uff1a\u6ca1\u6709\u5632\u7b11\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4e00\u4e2a\u4eba\u53ea\u4f1a\u6536\u83b7\u4ed6\u64ad\u79cd\u7684\u4e1c\u897f\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u64ad\u4e0b\u8089\u7684\u4eba\u4f1a\u4ece\u8089\u4f53\u4e0a\u8d5a\u94b1\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u64ad\u79cd\u7684\u4eba\u7cbe\u795e\u5c06\u4ece\u5723\u7075\u4e2d\u83b7\u5f97\u6c38\u751f\u3002\u8ba9\u6211\u4eec\u4e0d\u8981\u538c\u5026\u505a\u597d\u4e8b\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u6211\u4eec\u4e0d\u653e\u5f03\uff0c\u6211\u4eec\u5c06\u6536\u83b7\u6536\u6210\u3002\u56e0\u6b64\uff0c\u5728\u6211\u4eec\u6709\u673a\u4f1a\u7684\u540c\u65f6\uff0c\u8ba9\u6211\u4eec\u5bf9\u6240\u6709\u4eba\u505a\u597d\u4e8b\uff0c\u5c24\u5176\u662f\u5bf9\u90a3\u4e9b\u5c5e\u4e8e\u4fe1\u4ef0\u5bb6\u5ead\u7684\u4eba\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u628a\u6211\u7684\u548c\u5e73\u7559\u5728\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\uff0c\u963f\u4eec\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":30,"month_string":"July","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people, I love you; I guide you and gather you as a shepherd of souls. Beloved people of my heart: I come with my love to bless you and offer you my cross of glory and majesty. My children, I continue to suffer for each one of you, I see you moving further and further away from my fold submerged in false doctrines because you do not recognize me. My people accept what is sinful, false and shameful; they accept what is wrong and become familiar with evil. I call them to conversion! It is the exact moment for them not to be guided by their own interests, but by those of my house. It is the time of the signs that anticipate the warning and my people continue without examining themselves, without going within themselves and without looking at themselves without masks. My children act outside of my love. Far from the actions and actions of a true Christian, they allow themselves to be attracted by those who, knowing me, despise me and seek their own interests and not mine. Human miseries have led them to taste the sinful, loving earthly power, going so far as to submerge my church in darkness and silencing the altars of the eucharistic sacrifice with a sledgehammer. Oh, moment of pain! I suffer over and over again.... And my blinded people look at themselves, despise humility and with great pride feed their conceited and spoiled 'ego'. I have given you so much, children! So much have you lost through sober by until, without finding contentment or spiritual fulfilment, you prostrate yourselves again before me, so that I may free you from so much gangrene that you have let fall upon what is mine! Pray my people, pray, pray, my justice arrives for what is my property. Pray my people, pray the city of lights is extinguished, the noise is silenced and my children cry out. Pray my people, pray for Argentina, it suffers before the astonished humanity. Pray, my people, pray, nature acts with greater force. My enemies rise against my children. Without fear continue with faith, my angelic legions will make the oppressors flee. My people, human pride and foolishness must be banished in preparation for putting to fight the detainers that live within each of you. Surrender yourselves to me without human resistance, thus I will be all in you and you will be my contentment. Hurry children, get rid of so many rags that prevent you from walking towards me.... Be love, fraternity, charity, forgiveness, hope and each one of you be the support of your brother. Fulfil the commandments, love the sacraments, be reconciled with me and receive me with love for those who do not love me. This is how you will be my contentment; this is how my children work and act in order to taste my love and for my love to be in you a sign of my presence. I bless you and strengthen you. My people, without fear, continue to hold my hand and the hand of my mother. My heart beats for each one of you. I love you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, kocham was; prowadz\u0119 was i gromadz\u0119 jako pasterz dusz. Umi\u0142owany ludu mojego serca: Przychodz\u0119 z moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, aby was b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0107 i ofiarowa\u0107 wam m\u00f3j krzy\u017c chwa\u0142y i majestatu. Moje dzieci, nadal cierpi\u0119 za ka\u017cdego z was, widz\u0119 jak coraz bardziej oddalacie si\u0119 od mojej owczarni zanurzeni w fa\u0142szywych doktrynach, poniewa\u017c nie rozpoznajecie mnie. M\u00f3j lud przyjmuje to, co grzeszne, fa\u0142szywe i haniebne; przyjmuje to, co z\u0142e i oswaja si\u0119 ze z\u0142em. Wzywam ich do nawr\u00f3cenia! Jest to dok\u0142adny moment, aby nie kierowali si\u0119 w\u0142asnym interesem, ale interesem mojego domu. Jest to czas znak\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re uprzedzaj\u0105 ostrze\u017cenie, a m\u00f3j lud trwa bez badania siebie, bez wchodzenia w siebie i bez patrzenia na siebie bez masek. Moje dzieci dzia\u0142aj\u0105 poza moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Daleko od czyn\u00f3w i dzia\u0142a\u0144 prawdziwego chrze\u015bcijanina, pozwalaj\u0105 si\u0119 przyci\u0105ga\u0107 tym, kt\u00f3rzy znaj\u0105c Mnie, gardz\u0105 Mn\u0105 i szukaj\u0105 w\u0142asnych interes\u00f3w, a nie moich. Ludzkie nieszcz\u0119\u015bcia doprowadzi\u0142y ich do tego, \u017ce zakosztowali grzesznej, kochaj\u0105cej ziemskiej w\u0142adzy, posuwaj\u0105c si\u0119 tak daleko, \u017ce pogr\u0105\u017cyli M\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 w ciemno\u015bciach i uciszyli o\u0142tarze eucharystycznej ofiary m\u0142otem kowalskim. O, chwilo b\u00f3lu! Cierpi\u0119 wci\u0105\u017c na nowo.... A m\u00f3j za\u015blepiony lud patrzy na siebie, gardzi pokor\u0105 i z wielk\u0105 pych\u0105 karmi swoje zarozumia\u0142e i zepsute \"ego\". Tak wiele wam da\u0142em, dzieci! Tak wiele utracili\u015bcie przez trze\u017awo\u015b\u0107, a\u017c nie znajduj\u0105c zadowolenia ani duchowego spe\u0142nienia, ponownie k\u0142aniali\u015bcie si\u0119 przede mn\u0105, abym uwolni\u0142 was od tak wielkiej gangreny, kt\u00f3r\u0105 pozwolili\u015bcie, aby spad\u0142a na to, co moje! M\u00f3dl si\u0119 m\u00f3j ludu, m\u00f3dl si\u0119, m\u00f3dl si\u0119, aby moja sprawiedliwo\u015b\u0107 dotar\u0142a do tego, co jest moj\u0105 w\u0142asno\u015bci\u0105. M\u00f3dl si\u0119 m\u00f3j ludu, m\u00f3dl si\u0119, aby miasto \u015bwiate\u0142 zgas\u0142o, aby ucich\u0142 ha\u0142as i aby moje dzieci p\u0142aka\u0142y. M\u00f3dl si\u0119 m\u00f3j ludu, m\u00f3dl si\u0119 za Argentyn\u0119, cierpi ona przed zdumion\u0105 ludzko\u015bci\u0105. M\u00f3dl si\u0119, m\u00f3j ludu, m\u00f3dl si\u0119, natura dzia\u0142a z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 si\u0142\u0105. Moi wrogowie powstaj\u0105 przeciwko moim dzieciom. Bez strachu trwajcie z wiar\u0105, moje anielskie legiony sprawi\u0105, \u017ce ciemi\u0119\u017cyciele uciekn\u0105. M\u00f3j ludu, ludzka duma i g\u0142upota musz\u0105 zosta\u0107 wygnane, aby przygotowa\u0107 si\u0119 do walki z wi\u0119\u017aniami, kt\u00f3rzy \u017cyj\u0105 w ka\u017cdym z was. Poddajcie si\u0119 mi bez ludzkiego oporu, w ten spos\u00f3b b\u0119d\u0119 ca\u0142y w was, a wy b\u0119dziecie moj\u0105 satysfakcj\u0105. Pospieszcie si\u0119 dzieci, pozb\u0105d\u017acie si\u0119 tylu \u0142achman\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re przeszkadzaj\u0105 wam i\u015b\u0107 ku mnie.... B\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, braterstwem, mi\u0142osierdziem, przebaczeniem, nadziej\u0105 i ka\u017cdy z was niech b\u0119dzie podpor\u0105 swojego brata. Wype\u0142niajcie przykazania, kochajcie sakramenty, b\u0105d\u017acie pojednani ze Mn\u0105 i przyjmujcie Mnie z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 za tych, kt\u00f3rzy Mnie nie kochaj\u0105. Tak b\u0119dziecie moim zadowoleniem; tak pracuj\u0105 i dzia\u0142aj\u0105 moje dzieci, aby zakosztowa\u0107 mojej mi\u0142o\u015bci i aby moja mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 by\u0142a w was znakiem mojej obecno\u015bci. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was i umacniam. M\u00f3j lud, bez l\u0119ku, nadal trzymaj moj\u0105 r\u0119k\u0119 i r\u0119k\u0119 mojej Matki. Moje serce bije dla ka\u017cdego z was. Kocham was. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":7,"day":30,"month_string":"July","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for answering my call in your hearts and for bending your knees in prayer. My children, soon you will find yourselves in a very difficult time, more than you imagine. My children, be united and listen to the words of a loving Mother, the antichrist is acting, you will reach the point where you will not be able to buy anything without his permission, stock up and do not be reckless. Beloved children, pray for priests, Satan is acting, he will have everything sacred removed, starting with tabernacles and priestly robes, saying you are all the same. The consecrated faithful, they will suffer a lot, but Jesus and I will be near. Children, please love one another and unite in God's love, only then will you be victorious. New illnesses will arise, just a little longer and you will still be in your prisons. Children, economic disaster is near, help one another, call on Me and I will be with you. I love you children, pray, pray, pray much.  Now I bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass du meinen Anruf in deinen Herzen beantwortet hast und deine Knie im Gebet beugt hast. Meine Kinder, bald werden Sie sich in einer sehr schwierigen Zeit befinden, mehr als Sie sich vorstellen. Meine Kinder, sind vereint und h\u00f6ren auf die Worte einer liebevollen Mutter, der Antichrist, du wirst den Punkt erreichen, an dem du ohne seine Erlaubnis nichts kaufen kannst, um etwas zu versorgen und nicht r\u00fccksichtslos zu sein. Geliebte Kinder, beten f\u00fcr Priester, Satan handelt, er wird alles heilige Entfernung haben, beginnend mit Tabernakeln und priesterlichen Gew\u00e4ndern und sagen, dass Sie alle gleich sind. Die geweihten Gl\u00e4ubigen werden viel leiden, aber Jesus und ich werden in der N\u00e4he sein. Kinder, bitte lieben und vereinen Sie sich in Gottes Liebe, nur dann werden Sie siegreich sein. Neue Krankheiten werden auftreten, nur ein bisschen l\u00e4nger und Sie werden immer noch in Ihren Gef\u00e4ngnissen sein. Kinder, wirtschaftliche Katastrophe ist in der N\u00e4he, helfen sich gegenseitig, rufen Sie mich an und ich werde bei Ihnen sein. Ich liebe dich Kinder, bete, bete, bete viel. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen der heiligsten Dreifaltigkeit, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n y por haber doblado las rodillas en oraci\u00f3n. Ni\u00f1os, pronto te encontrar\u00e1s en un momento muy dif\u00edcil, m\u00e1s de lo que imaginas. Mis hijos, se unen y escuchen las palabras de una madre amorosa, el Anticristo est\u00e1 actuando, llegar\u00e1 al punto de que ya no se puede comprar nada sin su permiso, hacer acciones y no ser ligeros. Amados hijos, rezaron por los sacerdotes, Satan\u00e1s est\u00e1 actuando, har\u00e1 todo lo que es sagrado, comenzando desde los tabern\u00e1culos y la disfraz sacerdotal, diciendo que todos son iguales. Los fieles consagrados sufrir\u00e1n mucho, pero Jes\u00fas y yo estaremos cerca. Los ni\u00f1os, por favor, se aman y se unen al amor de Dios, solo de esta manera estar\u00e1n ganando. Aparecer\u00e1n nuevas enfermedades, todav\u00eda peque\u00f1as y a\u00fan estar\u00e1s en tus prisiones. Los ni\u00f1os, el desastre econ\u00f3mico est\u00e1 cerca, se ayudan mutuamente, me invocan y yo estar\u00e9 contigo. Los amo hijos, rezo, rezo, reza mucho. Ahora te bendiga en el nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs et d'avoir pli\u00e9 vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re. Mes enfants, vous vous retrouverez bient\u00f4t dans une p\u00e9riode tr\u00e8s difficile, plus que vous ne l'imaginez. Mes enfants, soyez unis et \u00e9coutez les paroles d'une m\u00e8re aimante, l'Ant\u00e9christ agit, vous atteindrez le point o\u00f9 vous ne pourrez rien acheter sans sa permission, faire le plein et ne pas \u00eatre t\u00e9m\u00e9raire. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, prier pour les pr\u00eatres, Satan agit, il fera enlever tout le sacr\u00e9, en commen\u00e7ant par les tabernacles et les robes sacerdotales, disant que vous \u00eates tous pareils. Les fid\u00e8les consacr\u00e9s, ils souffriront beaucoup, mais J\u00e9sus et moi serons proches. Enfants, s'il vous pla\u00eet, s'aimez-vous les uns les autres et s'unissent dans l'amour de Dieu, seulement alors vous serez victorieux. De nouvelles maladies surgiront, juste un peu plus longtemps et vous serez toujours dans vos prisons. Enfants, une catastrophe \u00e9conomique est proche, s'entraider, m'appeler et je serai avec vous. Je t'aime les enfants, priez, priez, priez beaucoup. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore e per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia nella preghiera. Figli, presto vi ritroverete in un tempo molto difficile, pi\u00f9 di quanto immaginate. Figli miei, siate uniti e ascoltate le parole di una Madre amorevole, l\u2019anticristo sta agendo, arriverete al punto che non potrete pi\u00f9 acquistare nulla senza il suo permesso, fate scorte e non siate leggeri. Figli amati, pregate per i sacerdoti, satana sta agendo, far\u00e0 togliere tutto ci\u00f2 che \u00e8 sacro, iniziando dai tabernacoli e dalle vesti sacerdotali, dicendo che siete tutti uguali. I consacrati fedeli, soffriranno molto, ma Ges\u00f9 ed Io saremo vicini. Figli, vi prego, amatevi l\u2019un l\u2019altro e unitevi nell\u2019amore di Dio, solo cos\u00ec sarete vincenti. Malattie nuove si affacceranno, ancora poco e sarete ancora nelle vostre prigioni. Figli, il disastro economico \u00e8 vicino, aiutatevi l\u2019un l\u2019altro, invocatemi ed Io sar\u00f2 con voi. Vi amo figli, pregate, pregate, pregate tanto.  Ora vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach i \u017ce kl\u0119kacie do modlitwy. Moje dzieci, wkr\u00f3tce znajdziecie si\u0119 w bardzo trudnym czasie, trudniejszym ni\u017c sobie wyobra\u017cacie. Moje dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie zjednoczeni i s\u0142uchajcie s\u0142\u00f3w kochaj\u0105cej Matki, antychryst dzia\u0142a, dojdzie do tego, \u017ce nie b\u0119dziecie mogli ju\u017c nic kupi\u0107 bez jego zgody, r\u00f3bcie zapasy i nie b\u0105d\u017acie lekkomy\u015blni. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za kap\u0142an\u00f3w, szatan dzia\u0142a, usunie wszystko, co \u015bwi\u0119te, zaczynaj\u0105c od tabernakulum i szat kap\u0142a\u0144skich, m\u00f3wi\u0105c, \u017ce wszyscy jeste\u015bcie tacy sami. Wierni konsekrowani, b\u0119d\u0105 wiele cierpie\u0107, ale Jezus i ja b\u0119dziemy blisko. Moje dzieci, b\u0142agam was, kochajcie si\u0119 wzajemnie i jednoczcie si\u0119 w mi\u0142o\u015bci Boga, tylko w ten spos\u00f3b odniesiecie zwyci\u0119stwo. Powstan\u0105 nowe choroby, jeszcze tylko chwila i zn\u00f3w b\u0119dziecie w swoich wi\u0119zieniach. Dzieci, katastrofa ekonomiczna jest bliska, pomagajcie sobie nawzajem, przyzywajcie mnie, a ja b\u0119d\u0119 z wami. Kocham was dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 mocno. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por atender meu chamado em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e por dobrar os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, em breve voc\u00eas se encontrar\u00e3o em um momento muito dif\u00edcil, mais do que voc\u00ea imagina. Meus filhos, se uniram e ouvem as palavras de uma m\u00e3e amorosa, o Anticristo est\u00e1 agindo, voc\u00ea chegar\u00e1 ao ponto em que n\u00e3o poder\u00e1 comprar nada sem a permiss\u00e3o dele, estocar e n\u00e3o ser\u00e1 imprudente. Crian\u00e7as amadas, orem por padres, Satan\u00e1s est\u00e1 agindo, ele ter\u00e1 tudo o que \u00e9 sagrado removido, come\u00e7ando com tabern\u00e1culos e vestes sacerdotais, dizendo que voc\u00ea \u00e9 todos iguais. Os fi\u00e9is consagrados, eles sofrer\u00e3o muito, mas Jesus e eu estaremos pr\u00f3ximos. Filhos, por favor, se amem e se unem no amor de Deus, s\u00f3 ent\u00e3o voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 vitorioso. Novas doen\u00e7as surgir\u00e3o, apenas um pouco mais e voc\u00ea ainda estar\u00e1 nas suas pris\u00f5es. Crian\u00e7as, o desastre econ\u00f4mico est\u00e1 pr\u00f3ximo, ajudam -se, me chamam e estarei com voc\u00ea. Eu te amo filhos, ore, ore, ore muito. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u5fc3\u4e2d\u63a5\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\uff0c\u5e76\u5c48\u670d\u4e8e\u7948\u7977\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5f88\u5feb\u60a8\u4f1a\u5728\u975e\u5e38\u56f0\u96be\u7684\u65f6\u671f\u53d1\u73b0\u81ea\u5df1\uff0c\u6bd4\u60a8\u60f3\u8c61\u7684\u8981\u591a\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u56e2\u7ed3\u4e00\u81f4\uff0c\u542c\u53d6\u4e00\u4e2a\u5145\u6ee1\u7231\u5fc3\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u8bdd\uff0c\u654c\u57fa\u7763\u7684\u8868\u6f14\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u65e0\u6cd5\u5728\u672a\u7ecf\u4ed6\u7684\u5141\u8bb8\u7684\u60c5\u51b5\u4e0b\u8d2d\u4e70\u4efb\u4f55\u4e1c\u897f\uff0c\u5e93\u5b58\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u9c81ck\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e3a\u796d\u53f8\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u6492\u65e6\u7684\u8868\u6f14\uff0c\u4ed6\u5c06\u628a\u4e00\u5207\u795e\u5723\u7684\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u5220\u9664\uff0c\u4ece\u5973\u5893\u548c\u7267\u5e08\u957f\u888d\u5f00\u59cb\uff0c\u8bf4\u4f60\u90fd\u662f\u4e00\u6837\u7684\u3002\u5949\u732e\u7684\u5fe0\u5b9e\u8005\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u906d\u53d7\u5f88\u591a\u75db\u82e6\uff0c\u4f46\u8036\u7a23\u548c\u6211\u5c06\u4f1a\u9644\u8fd1\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8bf7\u5f7c\u6b64\u76f8\u7231\uff0c\u5e76\u56e2\u7ed3\u4e8e\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u7231\u4e2d\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u8fd9\u6837\uff0c\u60a8\u624d\u80fd\u80dc\u5229\u3002\u65b0\u75be\u75c5\u5c06\u51fa\u73b0\uff0c\u53ea\u4f1a\u66f4\u957f\u4e00\u70b9\uff0c\u60a8\u4ecd\u7136\u4f1a\u5728\u76d1\u72f1\u4e2d\u3002\u513f\u7ae5\uff0c\u7ecf\u6d4e\u707e\u96be\u5373\u5c06\u5230\u6765\uff0c\u4e92\u76f8\u5e2e\u52a9\uff0c\u62dc\u8bbf\u6211\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u548c\u4f60\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u3002\u6211\u7231\u4f60\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u5f88\u591a\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u6700\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":3,"month_string":"August","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear blessed children, thank you for being here and answering My call in your hearts. Children, rejoice because the coming of Jesus is near, open your hearts, I am here to touch the earth to bring love into your lives and prepare you for the most beautiful day, to see my Jesus coming on a cloud from heaven. Believe in Christ Jesus, the only deep Love and Redeemer. Beloved children, be ready and I will put you in the front row to enjoy the wonder. My children, love and praise Jesus, your Savior who will come to give you the earth cleansed of evil and to give you a land where everything will be new. Now I bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, Amen. Today many graces will descend upon you, witness!","text_de":"Liebe gesegnete Kinder, danke, dass du hier bist und meinen Anruf in deinen Herzen beantwortet hast. Kinder, freut sich, denn das Kommen Jesu ist nahe, \u00f6ffne deine Herzen, ich bin hier, um die Erde zu ber\u00fchren, um Liebe in dein Leben zu bringen und dich auf den sch\u00f6nsten Tag vorzubereiten, um zu sehen, wie mein Jesus auf eine Wolke aus dem Himmel kommt. Glaube an Christus Jesus, die einzige tiefe Liebe und Erl\u00f6ser. Geliebte Kinder, seien Sie bereit und ich werde Sie in die erste Reihe bringen, um das Wunder zu genie\u00dfen. Meine Kinder, lieben und loben Jesus, dein Erretter, der kommen wird, um dir die Erde zu geben, die vom B\u00f6sen gereinigt wird, und dir ein Land zu geben, in dem alles neu sein wird. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen der heiligsten Dreifaltigkeit, Amen. Heute werden viele Gnaden auf Sie herabsteigen, Zeugen!","text_es":"Cari figli benedetti, grazie per essere qui e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, gioite perch\u00e9 la venuta di Ges\u00f9 \u00e8 vicina, aprite i vostri cuori, Io sono qui a toccare la terra per portare l\u2019amore nelle vostre vite e prepararvi al giorno pi\u00f9 bello, vedere il mio Ges\u00f9 arrivare su una nube dal cielo. Credete in Cristo Ges\u00f9, unico profondo amore e Redentore. Figli amati, siate pronti ed Io vi metter\u00f2 in prima fila per godere la meraviglia. Figli miei, amate e lodate Ges\u00f9, vostro Salvatore che verr\u00e0 a donarvi la terra purificata dal male e per darvi una terra dove tutto sar\u00e0 nuovo. Ora vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, amen. Oggi tante le grazie scenderanno su di voi, testimoniate!!","text_fr":"Chers enfants b\u00e9nis, merci d'\u00eatre ici et de r\u00e9pondre \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Enfants, r\u00e9jouissez-vous parce que la venue de J\u00e9sus est proche, ouvre vos c\u0153urs, je suis ici pour toucher la terre pour apporter l'amour dans votre vie et vous pr\u00e9parer \u00e0 la plus belle journ\u00e9e, voir mon J\u00e9sus venir sur un nuage du ciel. Croyez en J\u00e9sus-Christ, le seul amour profond et r\u00e9dempteur. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, soyez pr\u00eat et je vous mettrai au premier rang pour profiter de l'\u00e9merveillement. Mes enfants, aiment et louent J\u00e9sus, votre Sauveur qui viendra vous donner la terre nettoy\u00e9e du mal et vous donner une terre o\u00f9 tout sera nouveau. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9, Amen. Aujourd'hui, de nombreuses gr\u00e2ces vous descendent, t\u00e9moigne!","text_it":"Cari figli benedetti, grazie per essere qui e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, gioite perch\u00e9 la venuta di Ges\u00f9 \u00e8 vicina, aprite i vostri cuori, Io sono qui a toccare la terra per portare l\u2019amore nelle vostre vite e prepararvi al giorno pi\u00f9 bello, vedere il mio Ges\u00f9 arrivare su una nube dal cielo. Credete in Cristo Ges\u00f9, unico profondo amore e Redentore. Figli amati, siate pronti ed Io vi metter\u00f2 in prima fila per godere la meraviglia. Figli miei, amate e lodate Ges\u00f9, vostro Salvatore che verr\u00e0 a donarvi la terra purificata dal male e per darvi una terra dove tutto sar\u00e0 nuovo. Ora vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, amen. Oggi tante le grazie scenderanno su di voi, testimoniate!!","text_pl":"Drogie b\u0142ogos\u0142awione dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj i \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, radujcie si\u0119, bo przyj\u015bcie Jezusa jest bliskie, otw\u00f3rzcie swoje serca, jestem tutaj, aby poruszy\u0107 ziemi\u0119, aby wnie\u015b\u0107 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do waszego \u017cycia i przygotowa\u0107 was na najpi\u0119kniejszy dzie\u0144, aby zobaczy\u0107 mojego Jezusa przybywaj\u0105cego na ob\u0142oku z nieba. Uwierz w Jezusa Chrystusa, jedyn\u0105 g\u0142\u0119bok\u0105 Mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 i Odkupiciela. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie gotowi, a Ja postawi\u0119 was w pierwszym rz\u0119dzie, aby\u015bcie mogli cieszy\u0107 si\u0119 tym cudem. Moje dzieci, kochajcie i chwalcie Jezusa, waszego Zbawiciela, kt\u00f3ry przyjdzie, aby da\u0107 wam ziemi\u0119 oczyszczon\u0105 ze z\u0142a i da\u0107 wam ziemi\u0119, w kt\u00f3rej wszystko b\u0119dzie nowe. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, Amen. Dzi\u015b wiele \u0142ask zst\u0105pi na was, b\u0105d\u017acie ich \u015bwiadkami!","text_pt":"Caros filhos aben\u00e7oados, obrigado por estar aqui e atender minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Os filhos, alegrem -se porque a vinda de Jesus est\u00e1 pr\u00f3xima, abre seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es, estou aqui para tocar a terra para trazer amor em suas vidas e prepar\u00e1 -lo para o dia mais bonito, para ver meu Jesus vindo em uma nuvem do c\u00e9u. Acredite em Cristo Jesus, o \u00fanico amor profundo e redentor. Crian\u00e7as amadas, estejam prontas e eu o colocarei na primeira fila para aproveitar a maravilha. Meus filhos, amor e louvar a Jesus, seu Salvador, que vir\u00e1 para lhe dar a terra limpa do mal e para lhe dar uma terra onde tudo ser\u00e1 novo. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Am\u00e9m. Hoje, muitas gra\u00e7as descerem sobre voc\u00ea, testemunham!","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u795d\u798f\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u5e76\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u63a5\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u5f88\u9ad8\u5174\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u6765\u4e34\u5373\u5c06\u5230\u6765\uff0c\u655e\u5f00\u5fc3hearts\uff0c\u6211\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u89e6\u6478\u5730\u7403\uff0c\u5c06\u7231\u5e26\u5165\u60a8\u7684\u751f\u6d3b\uff0c\u5e76\u4e3a\u60a8\u505a\u597d\u6700\u7f8e\u4e3d\u7684\u4e00\u5929\uff0c\u770b\u5230\u6211\u7684\u8036\u7a23\u4ece\u5929\u4e0a\u7b3c\u7f69\u7740\u4e4c\u4e91\u3002\u76f8\u4fe1\u57fa\u7763\u8036\u7a23\uff0c\u552f\u4e00\u7684\u6df1\u7231\u548c\u6551\u8d4e\u8005\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u51c6\u5907\u597d\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u628a\u4f60\u653e\u5728\u524d\u6392\u4eab\u53d7\u5947\u8ff9\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7231\u548c\u8d5e\u7f8e\u8036\u7a23\uff0c\u60a8\u7684\u6551\u4e3b\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4f1a\u6765\u7ed9\u60a8\u90aa\u6076\u7684\u5730\u7403\uff0c\u5e76\u7ed9\u60a8\u4e00\u7247\u65b0\u7684\u571f\u5730\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u6700\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002\u4eca\u5929\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u6069\u5178\u4f1a\u964d\u4e34\u5728\u4f60\u8eab\u4e0a\uff0c\u89c1\u8bc1\uff01","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":7,"month_string":"August","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people, with my love I bless you constantly and I call you to love me so that you may live in my Love and give love to your brothers. Without love you are like dry trees that do not bear fruit, their leaves fall off and they do not bear fruit. So is he who refuses my love, he is like the dry tree. Therefore, I call you to conversion and to ask my holy spirit for the gift of love so that you may be that crystalline water, that fruit which is a testimony of those who work and act in my will. My children, the gift of life must be a constant act of gratitude to me and therefore you must refuse to offend me. My children, looking at the daily events in which the tentacles of evil advance, among them with great firmness: war, persecution of my people and disease, you must change your actions and cooperate in the plan of salvation which is that all my children be saved. How do they cooperate? By being lovers of my will, you will find joy in being my children, even if you face whatever comes your way. My will is that all be saved, instead my children move away from me more and more without interest, without believing in what I tell them until they will face events without having decided to grow spiritually, without obeying me and without deciding to enter into sacred scripture to know me. This generation mocks me, my Mother, my cross and my consecrated ones who work and act in my will. This generation does not understand the moment in which it lives because it does not love me and does not believe. This generation rejects my peace, is content to submerge itself in what causes confrontations, rebellions, conflicts and strife because this is the environment in which Satan finds himself and envelops them in all that noise that does not allow peace, love, tranquillity, discernment, donation and my love to reign in the interior of my children. Therefore, exposed to the inclemencies of evil, they walk on wrong paths that lead them to be unbelievers, to not love their neighbour, to taste pride and vainglory looking at their brothers so small, who do not take them into account. My beloved people, how proudly they live! How much pride they carry with them and for that reason they do not obey me! I have entrusted so many of my people to work in my vineyard and they do not accept or despise me again and again, leading me to knock on other doors where humility and love for me reigns. I offer myself and am despised... I knock at the door of my children's hearts and I must withdraw without being attended to until they need me on behalf of the human creature and when in need, they look for me. My people, make haste, come to my Heart! Humanity has become indifferent to its own brethren and reacts violently to the slightest problem. Humanity is burning with intolerance, with lack of love and Satan is taking advantage of this to graft onto you his poison which multiplies this indifference, this mockery and this violence. Be converted, do not be afraid of conversion! Thus, you will find peace and you will look at all that happens without fear with the certainty that I am with my people. The war is dispersed in various hotbeds of tension. This is the strategy of the powers to attack without warning, without being seen. Food and medicine are becoming more expensive all over the earth. The powerful nations believe they possess what the rest of humanity will lack and they do not. The great nations have been plundered before. My people, you hear the roar of war in the Balkans, treachery and death comes to these lands. The struggles now and hereafter will be for water, which will become too scarce. The human creature has despised it and the high temperatures evaporate it. Pray for India my children, it suffers from encroachment and nature. Pray my children, pray, Argentina falls and her people rebel. Pray my children, pray for Chile suffers from nature. Pray my children, Indonesia shudders and is reduced by water. Pray my children, pray for America and Russia, they spread conflicts. My beloved people, wake up, it is necessary for you to be cautious, without warning the fights flare up and my children will be strangers in foreign lands. Be cautious. Pray, prayer with the heart is necessary. I protect you; I ask you to convert, I bless you. Each of my children must reason. Do not fear my people, increase your faith. Do not fear, I am with you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was nieustannie i wzywam was do kochania mnie, aby\u015bcie \u017cyli w mojej Mi\u0142o\u015bci i dawali mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 swoim braciom. Bez mi\u0142o\u015bci jeste\u015bcie jak suche drzewa, kt\u00f3re nie przynosz\u0105 owoc\u00f3w, ich li\u015bcie opadaj\u0105 i nie przynosz\u0105 owoc\u00f3w. Tak samo ten, kto odrzuca moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, jest jak suche drzewo. Dlatego wzywam was do nawr\u00f3cenia i do proszenia mojego \u015bwi\u0119tego ducha o dar mi\u0142o\u015bci, aby\u015bcie byli t\u0105 krystaliczn\u0105 wod\u0105, tym owocem, kt\u00f3ry jest \u015bwiadectwem tych, kt\u00f3rzy pracuj\u0105 i dzia\u0142aj\u0105 w mojej woli. Moje dzieci, dar \u017cycia musi by\u0107 nieustannym aktem wdzi\u0119czno\u015bci wobec mnie i dlatego musicie odm\u00f3wi\u0107 obra\u017cania mnie. Moje dzieci, patrz\u0105c na codzienne wydarzenia, w kt\u00f3rych macki z\u0142a posuwaj\u0105 si\u0119 naprz\u00f3d, a w\u015br\u00f3d nich z wielk\u0105 stanowczo\u015bci\u0105: wojna, prze\u015bladowanie mojego ludu i choroby, musicie zmieni\u0107 swoje post\u0119powanie i wsp\u00f3\u0142pracowa\u0107 w planie zbawienia, kt\u00f3ry polega na tym, aby wszystkie moje dzieci zosta\u0142y zbawione. W jaki spos\u00f3b wsp\u00f3\u0142pracuj\u0105? B\u0119d\u0105c mi\u0142uj\u0105cymi moj\u0105 wol\u0119, znajdziecie rado\u015b\u0107 z tego, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie moimi dzie\u0107mi, nawet je\u015bli zmierzycie si\u0119 z tym, co stanie na waszej drodze. Moj\u0105 wol\u0105 jest, aby wszyscy zostali zbawieni, natomiast moje dzieci oddalaj\u0105 si\u0119 ode mnie coraz bardziej bez zainteresowania, bez wiary w to, co im m\u00f3wi\u0119, a\u017c stan\u0105 w obliczu wydarze\u0144, nie decyduj\u0105c si\u0119 na wzrost duchowy, nie b\u0119d\u0105c mi pos\u0142usznymi i nie decyduj\u0105c si\u0119 na wej\u015bcie do Pisma \u015awi\u0119tego, aby mnie pozna\u0107. To pokolenie szydzi ze Mnie, z Mojej Matki, z Mojego Krzy\u017ca i z Moich konsekrowanych, kt\u00f3rzy pracuj\u0105 i dzia\u0142aj\u0105 zgodnie z Moj\u0105 wol\u0105. To pokolenie nie rozumie chwili, w kt\u00f3rej \u017cyje, poniewa\u017c nie kocha Mnie i nie wierzy. To pokolenie odrzuca m\u00f3j pok\u00f3j, zadowala si\u0119 zanurzeniem w tym, co wywo\u0142uje konfrontacje, bunty, konflikty i spory, bo w takim \u015brodowisku znajduje si\u0119 szatan i otacza je tym ca\u0142ym ha\u0142asem, kt\u00f3ry nie pozwala, aby we wn\u0119trzu moich dzieci panowa\u0142 pok\u00f3j, mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, spok\u00f3j, rozeznanie, darowanie i moja mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107. Dlatego nara\u017ceni na dzia\u0142anie z\u0142a, chodz\u0105 po z\u0142ych drogach, kt\u00f3re prowadz\u0105 ich do bycia niewiernymi, do niekochania bli\u017aniego, do smakowania pychy i pr\u00f3\u017cno\u015bci patrz\u0105c na swoich braci tak ma\u0142ych, kt\u00f3rzy nie licz\u0105 si\u0119 z nimi. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, jak\u017ce dumnie \u017cyj\u0105! Jak wiele dumy nosz\u0105 ze sob\u0105 i z tego powodu nie s\u0105 Mi pos\u0142uszni! Powierzy\u0142em tylu moim ludziom prac\u0119 w mojej winnicy, a oni nie przyjmuj\u0105 lub pogardzaj\u0105 mn\u0105 wci\u0105\u017c na nowo, prowadz\u0105c mnie do pukania do innych drzwi, gdzie panuje pokora i mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do mnie. Ofiarowuj\u0119 siebie i jestem wzgardzony... Pukam do drzwi serc Moich dzieci i musz\u0119 si\u0119 wycofa\u0107, nie b\u0119d\u0105c obs\u0142ugiwanym, dop\u00f3ki nie potrzebuj\u0105 Mnie w imieniu ludzkiego stworzenia, a kiedy s\u0105 w potrzebie, szukaj\u0105 Mnie. M\u00f3j ludu, pospiesz si\u0119, przyjd\u017a do mojego Serca! Ludzko\u015b\u0107 sta\u0142a si\u0119 oboj\u0119tna na swoich braci i reaguje gwa\u0142townie na najmniejszy problem. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 p\u0142onie nietolerancj\u0105, brakiem mi\u0142o\u015bci i szatan wykorzystuje to, aby zaszczepi\u0107 wam swoj\u0105 trucizn\u0119, kt\u00f3ra pomna\u017ca t\u0119 oboj\u0119tno\u015b\u0107, to szyderstwo i t\u0119 przemoc. Nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119 nawr\u00f3cenia! W ten spos\u00f3b znajdziecie pok\u00f3j i b\u0119dziecie patrze\u0107 na wszystko, co si\u0119 dzieje bez l\u0119ku z pewno\u015bci\u0105, \u017ce jestem z moim ludem. Wojna jest rozproszona w r\u00f3\u017cnych punktach zapalnych. Taka jest strategia mocarstw, aby atakowa\u0107 bez ostrze\u017cenia, bez widoczno\u015bci. Na ca\u0142ej ziemi dro\u017ceje \u017cywno\u015b\u0107 i lekarstwa. Pot\u0119\u017cne narody uwa\u017caj\u0105, \u017ce posiadaj\u0105 to, czego b\u0119dzie brakowa\u0142o reszcie ludzko\u015bci, a tak nie jest. Wielkie narody by\u0142y ju\u017c wcze\u015bniej pl\u0105drowane. M\u00f3j ludu, s\u0142yszysz ryk wojny na Ba\u0142kanach, zdrada i \u015bmier\u0107 przychodzi na te ziemie. Walki teraz i w przysz\u0142o\u015bci b\u0119d\u0105 o wod\u0119, kt\u00f3ra stanie si\u0119 zbyt rzadka. Ludzkie stworzenie wzgardzi\u0142o ni\u0105, a wysokie temperatury powoduj\u0105 jej wyparowanie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Indie Moje dzieci, cierpi\u0105 one z powodu ingerencji i natury. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, Argentyna upada i jej lud si\u0119 buntuje. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Chile, cierpi z powodu natury. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, Indonezja dr\u017cy i jest zmniejszona przez wod\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ameryk\u0119 i Rosj\u0119, one szerz\u0105 konflikty. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludzie, obud\u017acie si\u0119, konieczne jest, aby\u015bcie byli ostro\u017cni, bez ostrze\u017cenia walki wybuchaj\u0105 i moje dzieci b\u0119d\u0105 obcymi na obcej ziemi. B\u0105d\u017acie ostro\u017cni. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, konieczna jest modlitwa sercem. Chroni\u0119 was; prosz\u0119 was o nawr\u00f3cenie, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Ka\u017cde z moich dzieci musi rozumowa\u0107. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119 m\u00f3j ludu, zwi\u0119kszajcie swoj\u0105 wiar\u0119. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, jestem z wami. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":9,"month_string":"August","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, humanity is in the brink, please children, return to God and His laws, He is merciful and if you ask for forgiveness, He will grant it. My children, wars will begin, they will end, but then they will continue, pray, for you are running out of time, let your speech be, yes yes, no no. I keep coming to you to instruct you and you often turn away. My children, believe my words so that you may be prepared, your path will be rather arduous and impassable, but whoever has the Holy Rosary as an anchor will be saved. Children, follow the Ten Commandments, look to my Son and there you will see the light. Children, there will be a strong earthquake, cloudbursts all the time, but I ask you to pray under the cross of my Son and you and your families will be Blessed. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, die Menschheit ist am Rande, bitte Kinder, kehren zu Gott und zu seinen Gesetzen zur\u00fcck, er ist barmherzig und wenn Sie um Vergebung bitten, wird er es gew\u00e4hren. Meine Kinder, Kriege werden beginnen, sie werden enden, aber dann werden sie weitermachen, beten, denn Ihnen geht die Zeit aus, lassen Sie Ihre Rede sein, ja, nein nein. Ich komme immer wieder zu Ihnen, um Sie zu unterweisen, und Sie wenden sich oft ab. Meine Kinder, glauben meine Worte, damit Sie vorbereitet sind, Ihr Weg wird ziemlich m\u00fchsam und unpassierbar sein, aber wer auch immer den heiligen Rosenkranz als Anker hat, wird gerettet. Kinder, folgen Sie den zehn Geboten, schauen Sie zu meinem Sohn und dort sehen Sie das Licht. Kinder, es wird st\u00e4ndig ein starkes Erdbeben geben, Cloudbursts, aber ich bitte Sie, unter dem Kreuz meines Sohnes zu beten, und Sie und Ihre Familien werden gesegnet. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Hijos m\u00edos, gracias por responder a mi llamada en vuestros corazones. Hijos m\u00edos, la humanidad est\u00e1 al borde, por favor hijos, volved a Dios y a sus leyes, \u00c9l es misericordioso y si ped\u00eds perd\u00f3n, os lo conceder\u00e1. Hijos m\u00edos, las guerras comenzar\u00e1n, terminar\u00e1n, pero luego continuar\u00e1n, rezad, porque se os acaba el tiempo, que vuestro discurso sea, s\u00ed s\u00ed, no no. Sigo viniendo a vosotros para instruiros y a menudo os apart\u00e1is. Hijos m\u00edos, creed en mis palabras para que est\u00e9is preparados, vuestro camino ser\u00e1 bastante arduo e intransitable, pero quien tenga el Santo Rosario como ancla se salvar\u00e1. Hijos, seguid los Diez Mandamientos, mirad a mi Hijo y all\u00ed ver\u00e9is la luz. Hijos, habr\u00e1 un fuerte terremoto, chaparrones todo el tiempo, pero os pido que rec\u00e9is bajo la cruz de mi Hijo y ser\u00e9is bendecidos vosotros y vuestras familias. Ahora os bendigo en el nombre del Padre y del Hijo y del Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, l'humanit\u00e9 est au bord du bord, s'il vous pla\u00eet les enfants, retournent \u00e0 Dieu et \u00e0 ses lois, il est mis\u00e9ricordieux et si vous demandez le pardon, il l'accordera. Mes enfants, les guerres commenceront, ils prendront fin, mais ensuite ils continueront, prieront, car vous manquez de temps, laissez votre discours \u00eatre, oui, oui non non. Je continue de venir vers vous pour vous instruire et vous vous d\u00e9tournez souvent. Mes enfants, croyez mes mots afin que vous soyez pr\u00eat, votre chemin sera plut\u00f4t ardu et impraticable, mais celui qui a le Saint Rosaire comme ancre sera sauv\u00e9. Enfants, suivez les dix commandements, regardez mon fils et vous verrez la lumi\u00e8re. Enfants, il y aura tout le temps un tremblement de terre fort, les nuages, mais je vous demande de prier sous la croix de mon fils et vous et vos familles vous serez b\u00e9nie. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, l\u2019umanit\u00e0 \u00e8 in bilico, vi prego figli, tornate a Dio e alle sue leggi, Lui \u00e8 misericordioso e se chiederete il perdono, ve lo conceder\u00e0. Figli miei, le guerre inizieranno, finiranno, ma poi continueranno, pregate, perch\u00e9 non avete pi\u00f9 tempo, che il vostro parlare sia, si si, no no. Continuo a venire a voi per istruirvi e spesso vi girate dall\u2019altra parte. Figli miei, credete alle mie parole affinch\u00e9 siate preparati, il vostro cammino sar\u00e0 piuttosto arduo e impervio, ma chi avr\u00e0 come \u00e0ncora il Santo Rosario, sar\u00e0 salvato. Figli, seguite i dieci comandamenti, guardate mio Figlio e l\u00ec vedrete la luce. Figli, ci sar\u00e0 un forte terremoto, nubifragi in continuazione, ma Io vi chiedo di pregare sotto la croce di mio Figlio e sarete Benedetti voi e le vostre famiglie. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo. amen.","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest w zawieszeniu, b\u0142agam was dzieci, powr\u00f3\u0107cie do Boga i Jego praw, On jest mi\u0142osierny i je\u015bli poprosicie o przebaczenie, On go udzieli. Moje dzieci, wojny b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 zaczyna\u0107, b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 ko\u0144czy\u0107, ale potem b\u0119d\u0105 trwa\u0107, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, bo nie macie ju\u017c czasu, niech wasza mowa b\u0119dzie: tak tak, nie nie. Ci\u0105gle przychodz\u0119 do was, aby was pouczy\u0107, a wy cz\u0119sto si\u0119 odwracacie. Moje dzieci, wierzcie moim s\u0142owom, aby\u015bcie byli przygotowani, wasza droga b\u0119dzie raczej uci\u0105\u017cliwa i nieprzejezdna, ale kto ma R\u00f3\u017caniec \u015awi\u0119ty jako kotwic\u0119, ten b\u0119dzie uratowany. Moje dzieci, przestrzegajcie Dziesi\u0119ciu Przykaza\u0144, patrzcie w stron\u0119 mojego Syna, a tam zobaczycie \u015bwiat\u0142o. Dzieci, ca\u0142y czas b\u0119d\u0105 silne trz\u0119sienia ziemi, oberwania chmur, ale prosz\u0119 was o modlitw\u0119 pod Krzy\u017cem mojego Syna, a wy i wasze rodziny b\u0119d\u0105 b\u0142ogos\u0142awione. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, a humanidade est\u00e1 \u00e0 beira, por favor, os filhos, voltem a Deus e suas leis, ele \u00e9 misericordioso e, se voc\u00ea pedir perd\u00e3o, ele conceder\u00e1 isso. Meus filhos, as guerras come\u00e7ar\u00e3o, eles terminar\u00e3o, mas depois continuar\u00e3o, orando, pois voc\u00ea est\u00e1 ficando sem tempo, deixe seu discurso estar, sim sim, n\u00e3o n\u00e3o. Eu continuo vindo at\u00e9 voc\u00ea para instru\u00ed -lo e voc\u00ea costuma se afastar. Meus filhos, acreditam nas minhas palavras para que voc\u00ea esteja preparado, seu caminho ser\u00e1 bastante \u00e1rduo e intransit\u00e1vel, mas quem tiver o Santo Ros\u00e1rio como \u00e2ncora ser\u00e1 salvo. Filhos, siga os dez mandamentos, olhe para meu filho e l\u00e1 voc\u00ea ver\u00e1 a luz. Filhos, haver\u00e1 um forte terremoto, nuvem explos\u00f5es o tempo todo, mas pe\u00e7o que voc\u00ea ore sob a cruz de meu filho e voc\u00ea e suas fam\u00edlias ser\u00e3o aben\u00e7oadas. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4eba\u7c7b\u5728\u8fb9\u7f18\uff0c\u8bf7\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u56de\u5230\u4e0a\u5e1d\u548c\u4ed6\u7684\u5f8b\u6cd5\u4e0a\uff0c\u4ed6\u662f\u4ec1\u6148\u7684\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u60a8\u8981\u6c42\u5bbd\u6055\uff0c\u4ed6\u4f1a\u6388\u4e88\u5b83\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6218\u4e89\u5c06\u5f00\u59cb\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u5c06\u7ed3\u675f\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u968f\u540e\u4ed6\u4eec\u5c06\u7ee7\u7eed\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u60a8\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\u6ca1\u65f6\u95f4\uff0c\u8ba9\u60a8\u7684\u6f14\u8bb2\u662f\uff0c\u662f\uff0c\u662f\uff0c\u5426\u3002\u6211\u4e00\u76f4\u6765\u627e\u4f60\u6307\u5bfc\u4f60\uff0c\u4f60\u7ecf\u5e38\u8f6c\u8eab\u79bb\u5f00\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u76f8\u4fe1\u6211\u7684\u8bdd\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fbf\u60a8\u53ef\u4ee5\u505a\u597d\u51c6\u5907\uff0c\u60a8\u7684\u9053\u8def\u5c06\u76f8\u5f53\u8270\u5de8\u4e14\u65e0\u6cd5\u901a\u884c\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u4efb\u4f55\u62e5\u6709\u5723\u5ff5\u73e0\u4f5c\u4e3a\u951a\u7684\u4eba\u90fd\u5c06\u5f97\u6551\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8ddf\u968f\u5341\u8beb\uff0c\u770b\u6211\u513f\u5b50\uff0c\u5728\u90a3\u91cc\u4f60\u4f1a\u770b\u5230\u5149\u660e\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5c06\u4e00\u76f4\u53d1\u751f\u5f3a\u70c8\u7684\u5730\u9707\uff0c\u4e91\u7206\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\u8981\u6c42\u60a8\u5728\u513f\u5b50\u7684\u5341\u5b57\u67b6\u4e0b\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u60a8\u548c\u60a8\u7684\u5bb6\u4eba\u5c06\u53d7\u5230\u795d\u798f\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":11,"month_string":"August","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart, you are my great treasure and my heart beats fast with love for each one of you. Like the river that follows its course and flows at some point to its mouth, so each of you, children, have been created by the eternal father to be co-heirs with my Son of eternal life. My Son's people, the worldly contaminates you constantly, therefore you must continually strengthen yourselves with the Sacred Scriptures, going to the sacrament of reconciliation and going to receive my Divine Son in the eucharistic sacrament. At this time mankind is preoccupied with the care of the physical body, leaving aside the care of the spirit. They worship the physical body so much and have left my Son aside, they have banished him, they despise him: They do not know him and they do not love him.... They fabricate a personal relationship, without the consent of my Son, separating themselves from the Church.... They fabricate their own spirituality and in their own way, they fabricate a personal relationship with my Divine Son to hide the rebellion and pride that some of my children hide. The human creature must be fraternal and live in community, as my Son commands. Fraternity would achieve less strife, envy, discord, selfishness, less desire for appropriation by the great powers and there would be less fighting. Children, it is human foolishness that at this moment is leading all mankind to fall into the precipice of oblivion; yes, the oblivion that is leading mankind to where it will not be able to stop the war. The advanced arms race is at this moment the major objective of the powers and the possession of armaments is the objective of some small nations, which are satellites of communism and at this moment are preparing to be delegates of communism in their regions. Just as other powers embrace a number of countries and provide them with armaments for the supposed purpose of defines in countries that do not possess weapons. My Divine Son condemns both positions. The present war generates a great disaster and will generate the great disaster of humanity and of the earth, leaving it inert. This is how a great part of my children live, with their hearts empty of God, in total aridity, being aimless wanderers in an agonizing state and refusing to be healed. Thus, those who do not convert even at the last moment, will be copies of the devastation in which the earth will be left, after the determination of some power to initiate the devastation of humanity by launching weapons from hell itself. My Son's people must not be complicit in these acts so condemned by my Divine Son. Pray my children, pray, self-interests of nations generated the war and continue to generate it. Pray my children, pray, do not see nature manifesting its unseen strength as a preamble to what is to come. Pray my children, pray, you are children of the same father, do not ignore the suffering of your brothers and sisters at this time. Pray my children, pray, the church of my Son is deceived, without losing faith continue. Pray my children, pray, one nation and another is involved in war. Beloved children of my heart be doers of the Father's Will, nothing is yours, everything is God's. Scarcity increases, what you possess you will crave as the moment passes. You are astonished to know how nations that seem neutral maintain commitments with powers that, taking advantage of the territory of those countries, control their opponents in war. The folly of man increases the danger of human destruction and the destruction of nature. How the Heart of my Divine Son aches! How is my Son wounded again and again with the disobedience of his children and the obsession to lead all nations together with the antichrist and the powerful of the world! Mankind suffers and will suffer. Each country will protect itself by protecting its borders and almost no country will protect the spiritual salvation of its people. A bomb was detonated... The consequences are not long in coming, without being indifferent, be cautious. From one moment to the next mankind will be plunged into the dreaded third world war. My children, prepare yourselves, keep in prayer for your brothers, who with the passing of time, will go out to the countries of south America to be welcomed. My children, live increasing your inner peace so that the devil does not use you as creatures of scourge for your brothers. It is not enough to appear to be good, you must act and act as my Son commands you and live being witnesses of love, charity, forgiveness, hope and faith. Without fear, always seek the good, give testimony of my Son's love, be creatures of good and preach before you cannot do it. Pray and protect the elderly, give them love in the families and be lamps that light their way. This is the moment. Without fear for what is happening and will happen, surrender to the Holy Trinity that his children will not be abandoned. Let me guide you on the right path, come to me and be meek, be humble and be those children confident that you will never be abandoned. Do not fear: 'am I not here who am your Mother'. My beloved children, I bless you. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca, jeste\u015bcie moim wielkim skarbem i moje serce bije szybko z mi\u0142o\u015bci do ka\u017cdego z was. Jak rzeka, kt\u00f3ra pod\u0105\u017ca swoim biegiem i p\u0142ynie w pewnym momencie do swego uj\u015bcia, tak ka\u017cdy z was, dzieci, zosta\u0142 stworzony przez Ojca Przedwiecznego, aby by\u0107 wsp\u00f3\u0142dziedzicem z moim Synem \u017cycia wiecznego. Ludu mojego Syna, doczesno\u015b\u0107 zanieczyszcza was nieustannie, dlatego musicie nieustannie umacnia\u0107 si\u0119 Pismem \u015awi\u0119tym, przyst\u0119puj\u0105c do sakramentu pojednania i udaj\u0105c si\u0119 na przyj\u0119cie mojego Boskiego Syna w sakramencie eucharystycznym. W obecnym czasie ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest poch\u0142oni\u0119ta trosk\u0105 o cia\u0142o fizyczne, pomijaj\u0105c trosk\u0119 o ducha. Tak bardzo czcz\u0105 cia\u0142o fizyczne, a odeszli od mojego Syna, wygnali Go, gardz\u0105 Nim: Nie znaj\u0105 Go i nie kochaj\u0105.... Fabrykuj\u0105 osobiste relacje, bez zgody mojego Syna, oddzielaj\u0105c si\u0119 od Ko\u015bcio\u0142a.... Fabrykuj\u0105 swoj\u0105 w\u0142asn\u0105 duchowo\u015b\u0107 i na sw\u00f3j spos\u00f3b fabrykuj\u0105 osobist\u0105 relacj\u0119 z moim Boskim Synem, aby ukry\u0107 bunt i pych\u0119, kt\u00f3r\u0105 ukrywaj\u0105 niekt\u00f3re moje dzieci. Ludzkie stworzenie musi by\u0107 braterskie i \u017cy\u0107 we wsp\u00f3lnocie, jak nakazuje m\u00f3j Syn. Dzi\u0119ki braterstwu osi\u0105gn\u0119\u0142oby mniej spor\u00f3w, zawi\u015bci, niezgody, egoizmu, mniej pragnienia zaw\u0142aszczenia przez wielkie moce i by\u0142oby mniej walk. Dzieci, to ludzka g\u0142upota w tej chwili prowadzi ca\u0142\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107 do upadku w przepa\u015b\u0107 zapomnienia; tak, zapomnienia, kt\u00f3re prowadzi ludzko\u015b\u0107 tam, gdzie nie b\u0119dzie w stanie zatrzyma\u0107 wojny. Zaawansowany wy\u015bcig zbroje\u0144 jest w tej chwili g\u0142\u00f3wnym celem mocarstw, a posiadanie zbroje\u0144 jest celem niekt\u00f3rych ma\u0142ych narod\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re s\u0105 satelitami komunizmu i w tej chwili przygotowuj\u0105 si\u0119 do bycia delegatami komunizmu w swoich regionach. Podobnie jak inne mocarstwa obejmuj\u0105 szereg kraj\u00f3w i dostarczaj\u0105 im uzbrojenia w rzekomym celu definiowania w krajach, kt\u00f3re nie posiadaj\u0105 broni. M\u00f3j Boski Syn pot\u0119pia oba stanowiska. Obecna wojna generuje wielk\u0105 katastrof\u0119 i b\u0119dzie generowa\u0107 wielk\u0105 katastrof\u0119 ludzko\u015bci i ziemi, pozostawiaj\u0105c j\u0105 bezw\u0142adn\u0105. Tak \u017cyje wielka cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 moich dzieci, z sercami pustymi od Boga, w ca\u0142kowitej ja\u0142owo\u015bci, b\u0119d\u0105c bezcelowymi w\u0119drowcami w stanie agonalnym i odmawiaj\u0105c uzdrowienia. W ten spos\u00f3b ci, kt\u00f3rzy nie nawr\u00f3c\u0105 si\u0119 nawet w ostatniej chwili, b\u0119d\u0105 kopiami spustoszenia, w jakim zostanie pozostawiona ziemia, po determinacji jakiej\u015b si\u0142y, kt\u00f3ra zainicjuje wyniszczenie ludzko\u015bci przez wystrzelenie broni z samego piek\u0142a. Lud mojego Syna nie mo\u017ce by\u0107 wsp\u00f3\u0142winny tych czyn\u00f3w tak pot\u0119pionych przez mojego Boskiego Syna. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, interes w\u0142asny narod\u00f3w wygenerowa\u0142 wojn\u0119 i nadal j\u0105 generuje. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, nie patrzcie na natur\u0119 manifestuj\u0105c\u0105 swoj\u0105 niewidzialn\u0105 si\u0142\u0119 jako zapowied\u017a tego, co ma nadej\u015b\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, jeste\u015bcie dzie\u0107mi tego samego Ojca, nie ignorujcie cierpienia waszych braci i si\u00f3str w tym czasie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 mojego Syna jest zwiedziony, nie trac\u0105c wiary, trwajcie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, jeden nar\u00f3d i drugi jest zaanga\u017cowany w wojn\u0119. Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego serca b\u0105d\u017acie wykonawcami Woli Ojca, nic nie jest wasze, wszystko jest Bo\u017ce. Wzrasta niedob\u00f3r, to co posiadacie, b\u0119dziecie po\u017c\u0105da\u0107 w miar\u0119 up\u0142ywu chwili. Zdumiewa was fakt, \u017ce narody, kt\u00f3re wydaj\u0105 si\u0119 neutralne, utrzymuj\u0105 zobowi\u0105zania z mocarstwami, kt\u00f3re wykorzystuj\u0105c terytorium tych kraj\u00f3w, kontroluj\u0105 swoich przeciwnik\u00f3w w wojnie. G\u0142upota cz\u0142owieka zwi\u0119ksza niebezpiecze\u0144stwo zniszczenia cz\u0142owieka i zniszczenia przyrody. Jak\u017ce boli Serce mojego Boskiego Syna! Jak\u017ce M\u00f3j Syn jest wci\u0105\u017c na nowo raniony niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwem swoich dzieci i obsesj\u0105 prowadzenia wszystkich narod\u00f3w razem z antychrystem i mo\u017cnymi tego \u015bwiata! Ludzko\u015b\u0107 cierpi i b\u0119dzie cierpie\u0107. Ka\u017cdy kraj b\u0119dzie si\u0119 broni\u0142, chroni\u0105c swoje granice i prawie \u017caden kraj nie b\u0119dzie chroni\u0142 duchowego zbawienia swojego ludu. Zdetonowano bomb\u0119... Konsekwencje nie nadejd\u0105 d\u0142ugo, nie b\u0119d\u0105c oboj\u0119tnym, b\u0105d\u017acie ostro\u017cni. Od jednej chwili do nast\u0119pnej ludzko\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dzie pogr\u0105\u017cona w strasznej trzeciej wojnie \u015bwiatowej. Moje dzieci, przygotujcie si\u0119, trwajcie w modlitwie za waszych braci, kt\u00f3rzy z up\u0142ywem czasu wyjd\u0105 do kraj\u00f3w Ameryki Po\u0142udniowej, aby by\u0107 mile widzianymi. Moje dzieci, \u017cyjcie, zwi\u0119kszaj\u0105c sw\u00f3j wewn\u0119trzny pok\u00f3j, aby diabe\u0142 nie u\u017cywa\u0142 was jako istot biczuj\u0105cych waszych braci. Nie wystarczy wydawa\u0107 si\u0119 dobrym, musicie dzia\u0142a\u0107 i post\u0119powa\u0107 tak, jak nakazuje wam m\u00f3j Syn i \u017cy\u0107 b\u0119d\u0105c \u015bwiadkami mi\u0142o\u015bci, mi\u0142osierdzia, przebaczenia, nadziei i wiary. Bez l\u0119ku szukajcie zawsze dobra, dawajcie \u015bwiadectwo mi\u0142o\u015bci mojego Syna, b\u0105d\u017acie stworzeniami dobra i g\u0142o\u015bcie je, zanim nie b\u0119dziecie mogli tego zrobi\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 i chro\u0144cie osoby starsze, dajcie im mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 w rodzinach i b\u0105d\u017acie lampami, kt\u00f3re o\u015bwietlaj\u0105 ich drog\u0119. To jest ta chwila. Bez l\u0119ku o to, co si\u0119 dzieje i b\u0119dzie si\u0119 dzia\u0142o, poddajcie si\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej, \u017ce Jego dzieci nie zostan\u0105 opuszczone. Pozw\u00f3lcie, abym was poprowadzi\u0142 w\u0142a\u015bciw\u0105 drog\u0105, przyjd\u017acie do mnie i b\u0105d\u017acie cisi, pokorni i b\u0105d\u017acie tymi dzie\u0107mi pewnymi, \u017ce nigdy nie b\u0119dziecie opuszczeni. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119: \"czy\u017c nie jestem tu, kt\u00f3ra jestem wasz\u0105 Matk\u0105\". Moje ukochane dzieci, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":13,"month_string":"August","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children, thank you for being here, I have called you and you have responded in your hearts. Children, pray because the time of purification is upon you, pray for the Church and for the youth because their souls are being lost. Look at the movements of the Earth, they are all signs for you. My children, pray with your hearts, not only with words as the Pagans did, your prayers be full of love for my Divine Son, only in this way can you alleviate our sufferings. Now I bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, Amen.","text_de":"Geliebte Kinder, danke, dass du hier bist, ich habe dich angerufen und du hast in deinen Herzen geantwortet. Kinder, beten, weil die Zeit der Reinigung auf dir liegt, beten f\u00fcr die Kirche und f\u00fcr die Jugend, weil ihre Seelen verloren gehen. Schauen Sie sich die Bewegungen der Erde an, sie sind alle Zeichen f\u00fcr Sie. Meine Kinder beten mit Ihren Herzen, nicht nur mit Worten wie die Heiden, Ihre Gebete sind voller Liebe zu meinem g\u00f6ttlichen Sohn, nur auf diese Weise k\u00f6nnen Sie unsere Leiden lindern. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen der heiligsten Dreifaltigkeit, Amen.","text_es":"Amados hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed, te llam\u00e9 y t\u00fa has respondido en tu coraz\u00f3n. Ni\u00f1os, rezan porque el momento de la purificaci\u00f3n es sobre ti, reza por la iglesia y por los j\u00f3venes porque sus almas se est\u00e1n perdiendo. Mira los movimientos de la Tierra, todos son signos para ti. Mis hijos, rezan con el coraz\u00f3n, no solo con palabras como lo hicieron los paganos, sus oraciones est\u00e1n llenas de amor por mi hijo divino, solo de esta manera puede aliviar nuestros sufrimientos. Ahora te bendiga en el nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, merci d'\u00eatre ici, je vous ai appel\u00e9 et vous avez r\u00e9pondu dans vos c\u0153urs. Enfants, priez parce que le temps de purification est sur vous, priez pour l'\u00e9glise et pour les jeunes parce que leurs \u00e2mes sont perdues. Regardez les mouvements de la terre, ce sont tous des signes pour vous. Mes enfants, prient avec votre c\u0153ur, pas seulement avec des mots comme les pa\u00efens l'ont fait, vos pri\u00e8res sont pleines d'amour pour mon fils divin, seulement de cette mani\u00e8re pouvez-vous att\u00e9nuer nos souffrances. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9, Amen.","text_it":"Figli amati, grazie per essere qui, Io vi ho chiamati e voi avete risposto nel vostro cuore. Figli, pregate perch\u00e9 il tempo della purificazione \u00e8 su di voi, pregate per la Chiesa e per i giovani perch\u00e9 le loro anime si stanno perdendo. Guardate i movimenti della terra, sono tutti segnali per voi. Figli miei, pregate con il cuore, non solo con le parole come facevano i Pagani, le vostre preghiere siano piene d\u2019amore per il mio Divin Figlio, solo cos\u00ec potrete alleviare le nostre sofferenze. Ora vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, amen.","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam za to, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj, wezwa\u0142am was i odpowiedzieli\u015bcie w swoich sercach. Dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, bo czas oczyszczenia jest blisko, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 i za m\u0142odzie\u017c, bo ich dusze s\u0105 zagro\u017cone. Sp\u00f3jrz na ruchy Ziemi, one wszystkie s\u0105 dla ciebie znakami. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 sercem, nie tylko s\u0142owami, jak czynili to poganie, niech wasze modlitwy b\u0119d\u0105 pe\u0142ne mi\u0142o\u015bci do mojego Boskiego Syna, tylko w ten spos\u00f3b mo\u017cecie ul\u017cy\u0107 naszym cierpieniom. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, Amen.","text_pt":"Filhos Amados, obrigado por estar aqui, liguei para voc\u00ea e voc\u00ea respondeu em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Filhos, ore porque o tempo da purifica\u00e7\u00e3o est\u00e1 sobre voc\u00ea, ore pela igreja e pela juventude porque suas almas est\u00e3o sendo perdidas. Olhe para os movimentos da Terra, todos s\u00e3o sinais para voc\u00ea. Meus filhos, orem com seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es, n\u00e3o apenas com as palavras como os pag\u00e3os, suas ora\u00e7\u00f5es est\u00e3o cheias de amor pelo meu Filho Divino, apenas dessa maneira voc\u00ea pode aliviar nossos sofrimentos. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\uff0c\u6211\u6253\u7535\u8bdd\u7ed9\u60a8\uff0c\u60a8\u5728\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7948\u7977\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u51c0\u5316\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\u5230\u4e86\uff0c\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u548c\u9752\u5e74\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u7075\u9b42\u88ab\u8ff7\u5931\u4e86\u3002\u770b\u770b\u5730\u7403\u7684\u52a8\u4f5c\uff0c\u5b83\u4eec\u90fd\u662f\u60a8\u7684\u8ff9\u8c61\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7528\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4e0d\u4ec5\u50cf\u5f02\u6559\u5f92\u90a3\u6837\u7528\u8a00\u8bed\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u60a8\u7684\u7948\u7977\u5145\u6ee1\u4e86\u5bf9\u6211\u795e\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u7684\u7231\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u8fd9\u6837\uff0c\u60a8\u624d\u80fd\u51cf\u8f7b\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u75db\u82e6\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u6700\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":14,"month_string":"August","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear daughter, thank you for answering My call in your heart. My daughter, tomorrow is the feast of My Assumption into Heaven, John was beside me at that moment, he had adorned my little bed with fresh, fragrant flowers. After I fell asleep, a dazzling light invaded the little room, but an even stronger light superimposed itself, making the little room full of little lights that shone with many colors, and here were the angels who lifted me up and brought me to the meeting with My Son Jesus. My daughter, I am still touching the earth to help mankind to convert and love God as I have loved Him, be like Me and carry in your heart the sufferings of these times you are experiencing and those you will experience, know that I will always be beside you to console you. You cannot even imagine how much joy I felt, at the meeting with my Son and that is how I would like your meeting to be when He comes soon. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Tochter, danke, dass du meinen Anruf in deinem Herzen beantwortet hast. Meine Tochter, morgen ist das Fest meiner Annahme in den Himmel, John war in diesem Moment neben mir, er hatte mein kleines Bett mit frischen, duftenden Blumen geschm\u00fcckt. Nachdem ich eingeschlafen war, drang ein schillerndes Licht in den kleinen Raum ein, aber ein noch st\u00e4rkeres Licht \u00fcberlagte sich selbst und lie\u00df den kleinen Raum voller kleiner Lichter, die mit vielen Farben leuchteten mit meinem Sohn Jesus. Meine Tochter, ich ber\u00fchre immer noch die Erde, um der Menschheit zu helfen, Gott zu konvertieren und zu lieben, wie ich ihn geliebt habe, wie ich zu sein und in deinem Herzen die Leiden dieser Zeiten, die du erlebst, und die, die du erleben wirst, wei\u00df, dass ich immer werde Sei neben dir, um dich zu tr\u00f6sten. Sie k\u00f6nnen sich nicht einmal vorstellen, wie viel Freude ich f\u00fchlte, bei dem Treffen mit meinem Sohn und so m\u00f6chte ich, dass Ihr Treffen sein, wenn er bald kommt. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Querida hija, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Mi hija, ma\u00f1ana es la fiesta de mi suposici\u00f3n en el cielo, John en ese momento estaba a mi lado, hab\u00eda adornado mi cama de flores frescas y fragantes. Despu\u00e9s de quedarse dormido, una luz deslumbrante invadi\u00f3 la habitaci\u00f3n, pero una luz a\u00fan m\u00e1s fuerte se superpone, haciendo que el dormitorio lleno de luces que brillaban con muchos colores y aqu\u00ed est\u00e1n los \u00e1ngeles que me criaron y llevaron al encuentro con mi hijo Jes\u00fas. Mi hija, mi hija, Todav\u00eda toco la tierra para ayudar a la humanidad a convertir y amar a Dios, as\u00ed como lo amaba, ser similar a m\u00ed y tra\u00eddo a mi coraz\u00f3n los sufrimientos de estos per\u00edodos que vives y aquellos que vives, saben que siempre estar\u00e9 a tu lado para consolarte. Ni siquiera puedes imaginar cu\u00e1nta alegr\u00eda prob\u00f3, en la reuni\u00f3n con mi hijo y as\u00ed es como desear\u00eda que fuera tu reuni\u00f3n cuando vendr\u00e1 pronto. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Ch\u00e8re fille, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Ma fille, demain est la f\u00eate de mon hypoth\u00e8se dans le ciel, John \u00e9tait \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 de moi \u00e0 ce moment, il avait orn\u00e9 mon petit lit avec des fleurs fra\u00eeches et parfum\u00e9es. Apr\u00e8s que je me suis endormi, une lumi\u00e8re \u00e9blouissante a envahi la petite pi\u00e8ce, mais une lumi\u00e8re encore plus forte se superposait, rendant la petite pi\u00e8ce pleine de petites lumi\u00e8res qui brillaient de nombreuses couleurs, et voici les anges qui m'ont soulev\u00e9 et m'ont amen\u00e9 \u00e0 la r\u00e9union avec mon fils J\u00e9sus. Ma fille, je touche toujours la terre pour aider l'humanit\u00e9 Soyez \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 de vous pour vous consoler. Vous ne pouvez m\u00eame pas imaginer \u00e0 quel point je ressentais de la joie, lors de la rencontre avec mon fils et c'est ainsi que j'aimerais que votre rencontre soit quand il viendra bient\u00f4t. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cara figlia, grazie per avere risposto alla mia chiamata nel tuo cuore. Figlia mia, domani \u00e8 la festa della Mia Assunzione in cielo, Giovanni in quel momento mi era accanto, aveva adornato il mio lettino di fiori freschi e profumati. Dopo essermi addormentata, una luce folgorante ha invaso la stanzetta, ma una luce ancora pi\u00f9 forte si \u00e8 sovrapposta, rendendo la cameretta piena di lucine che brillavano di tanti colori ed ecco gli angeli che mi hanno sollevata e portata all\u2019incontro con mio Figlio Ges\u00f9. Figlia mia, tocco ancora la terra per aiutare l\u2019umanit\u00e0 a convertirsi e amare Dio, cos\u00ec come l\u2019ho amato Io, siate simili a me e portate nel cuore le sofferenze di questi periodi che state vivendo e di quelli che vivrete, sappiate che Io vi sar\u00f2 sempre accanto per consolarvi. Non potete neanche immaginare quanta gioia abbia provato, all\u2019incontro con mio Figlio ed \u00e8 cos\u00ec che vorrei fosse il vostro incontro quando presto Lui arriver\u00e0. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Droga c\u00f3rko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce odpowiedzia\u0142a\u015b na Moje wezwanie w twoim sercu. C\u00f3rko, jutro jest \u015bwi\u0119to Mojego Wniebowzi\u0119cia do Nieba, Jan by\u0142 w tym momencie obok mnie, ozdobi\u0142 moje ma\u0142e \u0142\u00f3\u017cko \u015bwie\u017cymi, pachn\u0105cymi kwiatami. Po tym, jak zasn\u0119\u0142am, do ma\u0142ego pokoju wtargn\u0119\u0142o o\u015blepiaj\u0105ce \u015bwiat\u0142o, ale na\u0142o\u017cy\u0142o si\u0119 na nie jeszcze silniejsze \u015bwiat\u0142o, sprawiaj\u0105c, \u017ce ma\u0142y pok\u00f3j by\u0142 pe\u0142en ma\u0142ych \u015bwiate\u0142ek, kt\u00f3re \u015bwieci\u0142y wieloma kolorami, a anio\u0142owie podnie\u015bli mnie i poprowadzili na spotkanie z moim Synem Jezusem. Moja c\u00f3rko, wci\u0105\u017c przychodz\u0119 na ziemi\u0119, aby pom\u00f3c ludzko\u015bci nawr\u00f3ci\u0107 si\u0119 i pokocha\u0107 Boga tak, jak ja Go pokocha\u0142am, b\u0105d\u017a podobna do mnie i no\u015b w sercu cierpienia tych czas\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re prze\u017cywasz i tych, kt\u00f3re prze\u017cyjesz, wiedz, \u017ce zawsze b\u0119d\u0119 obok ciebie, aby ci\u0119 pocieszy\u0107. Nawet nie wyobra\u017cacie sobie, jak wielk\u0105 rado\u015b\u0107 czu\u0142am, gdy spotka\u0142am mojego Syna i tak chcia\u0142abym, aby wasze spotkanie by\u0142o takie, gdy On przyjdzie wkr\u00f3tce. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Querida filha, obrigado por atender minha chamada em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Minha filha, amanh\u00e3 \u00e9 o banquete da minha suposi\u00e7\u00e3o no c\u00e9u, Jo\u00e3o estava ao meu lado naquele momento, ele adornava minha cama pequena com flores frescas e perfumadas. Depois que adormeci, uma luz deslumbrante invadiu a pequena sala, mas uma luz ainda mais forte se sobreposta, fazendo a pequena sala cheia de pequenas luzes que brilhavam com muitas cores, e aqui estavam os anjos que me levantaram e me trouxeram para a reuni\u00e3o com meu filho Jesus. Minha filha, ainda estou tocando a terra para ajudar Esteja ao seu lado para consolar voc\u00ea. Voc\u00ea n\u00e3o pode nem imaginar quanta alegria me senti, na reuni\u00e3o com meu filho e \u00e9 assim que eu gostaria que sua reuni\u00e3o fosse quando ele vier em breve. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u5fc3\u4e2d\u63a5\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u660e\u5929\u662f\u6211\u5bf9\u5929\u5802\u7684\u5047\u8bbe\u7684\u76db\u5bb4\uff0c\u7ea6\u7ff0\u5f53\u65f6\u5728\u6211\u65c1\u8fb9\uff0c\u4ed6\u7528\u65b0\u9c9c\u7684\u82ac\u82b3\u7684\u82b1\u6735\u88c5\u9970\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u5c0f\u5e8a\u3002\u6211\u5165\u7761\u540e\uff0c\u4e00\u4e2a\u8000\u773c\u7684\u706f\u4fb5\u5165\u4e86\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5c0f\u623f\u95f4\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u751a\u81f3\u66f4\u5f3a\u58ee\u7684\u706f\u53e0\u52a0\u4e86\uff0c\u4f7f\u5c0f\u623f\u95f4\u91cc\u5145\u6ee1\u4e86\u5c0f\u706f\u5149\uff0c\u7167\u4eae\u4e86\u8bb8\u591a\u989c\u8272\uff0c\u8fd9\u91cc\u7684\u5929\u4f7f\u5c06\u6211\u62ac\u8d77\uff0c\u628a\u6211\u5e26\u5230\u4e86\u4f1a\u8bae\u4e0a\u548c\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u6211\u4ecd\u5728\u89e6\u6478\u5730\u7403\uff0c\u4ee5\u5e2e\u52a9\u4eba\u7c7b\u50cf\u6211\u7231\u4ed6\u4e00\u6837convert\u4f9d\u548c\u7231\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u50cf\u6211\u4e00\u6837\uff0c\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u5fcd\u53d7\u60a8\u6240\u7ecf\u5386\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\u7684\u75db\u82e6\uff0c\u60a8\u4f1a\u7ecf\u5386\u7684\u90a3\u4e9b\u4eba\uff0c\u77e5\u9053\u6211\u5c06\u6c38\u8fdc\u5728\u4f60\u65c1\u8fb9\u5b89\u6170\u4f60\u3002\u60a8\u751a\u81f3\u65e0\u6cd5\u60f3\u8c61\u5728\u4e0e\u513f\u5b50\u7684\u4f1a\u8bae\u4e0a\u4f1a\u8bae\u4e0a\u6211\u7684\u559c\u60a6\uff0c\u8fd9\u5c31\u662f\u6211\u5e0c\u671b\u60a8\u5f88\u5feb\u5c31\u4f1a\u5f00\u4f1a\u7684\u65b9\u5f0f\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":15,"month_string":"August","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, as prince of the heavenly host and defender of the mystical body of Christ, I bring you this true and certain word. This people are blessed to have so exalted a Queen, given and received as a Mother at the foot of the Cross. The church on earth celebrates this feast of the assumption of our Queen and Mother with reverence and love. In heaven the hail Mary is heard everywhere as a sign of the love that she who is the Queen and Mother of heaven and earth deserves. She is the Mother of our King and Lord Jesus Christ and Queen and Mother of humanity, she who is the Tabernacle of her Son on earth and sacred fecundity. Divine design decreed that the Sacred Body of the Mother of the word should be assumed into heaven in the hands of the angels, so that the things of earth would not touch her, even at the final moment of her earthly life. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: This loving surrender, this constant 'yes' to the father\u2019s will is what human creatures should possess as filial souls of this most holy Mother, shining like her like the rays of the sun, emanating light towards their brothers and sisters, eradicating the darkness that is advancing upon humanity as evil approaches, anticipating the arrival of the antichrist. And with that arrival you will see conflict in all aspects of human life: a struggle that is mainly a spiritual one, even though those who are the most unbelieving deny it. As the envoy of the most Holy Trinity I affirm that this war is spiritual, even if they are masking it under different guises. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, evil cannot survive when faced by light, which is why, as we approach the climax of the great purification, the struggle is between good and evil, light against darkness. It is divine light that spreads over human beings as the divine sun illuminates all creation. This is the light which always triumphs, although unworthy humanity must purify itself before it reaches the fullness of the divine light. Discern, humanity, faced with those who are scourging your brothers and sisters! Do not be indifferent to the pain of your neighbour. The power that evil has given to some of the powerful who have long since surrendered to its evil tentacles, is tearing the mystical body apart, causing it to suffer the betrayal of some weak members of the mystical body of our King and Lord Jesus Christ and causing it to have new solitary martyrs, but who are not abandoned by Christ, head of the mystical body. How many faithful instruments will the church have at the crucial moment of purification? People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, children of our Queen and Mother: having planned this time that humanity is experiencing, the masonic leaders will not rest until they succeed in involving more and more countries in this war; they will leap out before the eyes of humanity. Pray, people of God, pray for Latin America: weapons are coming, the peoples will be inflamed. Pray, people of God, pray: you will continue to be astonished at the power of nature. Pray, people of God, pray: the shaking of the earth will continue to increase and humanity will suffer. Pray, people of God, pray: the monument to liberty will fall into the sea. Children of God, I call you to examine yourselves internally. You must be fraternal - you must not only respect each other's differences, but be humble in order to forgive one another day by day. Each person must recognize their weaknesses through a deep inner work, and by requesting divine assistance you will overcome them if the creature possesses humility. Pray, pray, receive the Eucharistic Food and humbly enter into what fraternity should be for you. You are the marching column, children of God - the column that does not stop, but strengthens itself in order to continue without faltering. The people of our Queen and Mother should not fear what has been announced, nor the progression of the fulfilment of the prophecies, but they should fear offending the most Holy Trinity, should fear falling into disobedience regarding God\u2019s Law, should fear rivalries and should fear offending their brothers and sisters. Wake up, do not sleep! Offenses are increasing in line with the increase in the lack of charity towards one\u2019s neighbour, and also due to the advance of evil. Wake up from the lethargy in which you are living! Evil takes advantage of those who are asleep in order to take hold of them and to cause discord among the people of God. Remain attentive to alliances between countries: this is an alert for humanity. Beloved children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, do not wait for heaven to reveal to you details of what it allows you to know so that you may prepare, as humanity could fall into chaos before the fulfilment of the prophecies arrives. Signs and signals mark the pace of what has been announced. Be prepared, convert and remain on alert! You are children of God and my legions protect you: do not despair. As the ants gather food for the winter, so you should gather for the winter. If you do not have enough for storage, increase your faith and my legions will provide for you by divine order. People of the Sacred Hearts, do not fear and remain firm in the faith. My legions protect you. Receive my blessing. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 zast\u0119p\u00f3w niebieskich i obro\u0144ca mistycznego cia\u0142a Chrystusa, przynosz\u0119 wam to prawdziwe i pewne s\u0142owo. Ten lud jest b\u0142ogos\u0142awiony, \u017ce ma tak wywy\u017cszon\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105, dan\u0105 i przyj\u0119t\u0105 jako Matka u st\u00f3p Krzy\u017ca. Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 na ziemi obchodzi to \u015bwi\u0119to wcielenia naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki ze czci\u0105 i mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. W niebie wsz\u0119dzie s\u0142ycha\u0107 grad Maryi na znak mi\u0142o\u015bci, na jak\u0105 zas\u0142uguje Ta, kt\u00f3ra jest Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0105 nieba i ziemi. Ona jest Matk\u0105 naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa oraz Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0105 ludzko\u015bci, Ona, kt\u00f3ra jest Tabernakulum swojego Syna na ziemi i \u015bwi\u0119t\u0105 p\u0142odno\u015bci\u0105. Boski plan zadecydowa\u0142, \u017ce \u015awi\u0119te Cia\u0142o Matki S\u0142owa powinno by\u0107 przyj\u0119te do nieba na r\u0119ce anio\u0142\u00f3w, aby rzeczy ziemskie nie dotkn\u0119\u0142y Jej, nawet w ostatniej chwili Jej ziemskiego \u017cycia. Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: To mi\u0142osne poddanie si\u0119, to nieustanne \"tak\" wobec woli Ojca jest tym, co powinny posiada\u0107 stworzenia ludzkie jako synowskie dusze tej naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Matki, ja\u015bniej\u0105ce jak Ona promieniami s\u0142o\u0144ca, emanuj\u0105ce \u015bwiat\u0142em wobec swoich braci i si\u00f3str, wykorzeniaj\u0105ce ciemno\u015bci, kt\u00f3re post\u0119puj\u0105 na ludzko\u015b\u0107 w miar\u0119 zbli\u017cania si\u0119 z\u0142a, przewiduj\u0105c przyj\u015bcie antychrysta. A wraz z tym przyj\u015bciem zobaczycie konflikt we wszystkich aspektach ludzkiego \u017cycia: walk\u0119, kt\u00f3ra jest g\u0142\u00f3wnie walk\u0105 duchow\u0105, nawet je\u015bli ci, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0105 najbardziej niewierz\u0105cy, zaprzeczaj\u0105 temu. Jako wys\u0142annik Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej potwierdzam, \u017ce ta wojna jest duchowa, nawet je\u015bli maskuj\u0105 j\u0105 pod r\u00f3\u017cnymi pozorami. Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, z\u0142o nie mo\u017ce przetrwa\u0107 w obliczu \u015bwiat\u0142a, dlatego te\u017c, gdy zbli\u017camy si\u0119 do punktu kulminacyjnego wielkiego oczyszczenia, walka toczy si\u0119 mi\u0119dzy dobrem a z\u0142em, \u015bwiat\u0142em a ciemno\u015bci\u0105. Jest to boskie \u015bwiat\u0142o, kt\u00f3re rozprzestrzenia si\u0119 nad istotami ludzkimi, tak jak boskie s\u0142o\u0144ce o\u015bwietla ca\u0142e stworzenie. Jest to \u015bwiat\u0142o, kt\u00f3re zawsze triumfuje, chocia\u017c niegodna ludzko\u015b\u0107 musi si\u0119 oczy\u015bci\u0107, zanim osi\u0105gnie pe\u0142ni\u0119 boskiego \u015bwiat\u0142a. Rozeznaj, ludzko\u015bci, w obliczu tych, kt\u00f3rzy biczuj\u0105 twoich braci i siostry! Nie b\u0105d\u017acie oboj\u0119tni na b\u00f3l waszego bli\u017aniego. W\u0142adza, jak\u0105 z\u0142o obdarzy\u0142o niekt\u00f3rych mo\u017cnych, kt\u00f3rzy ju\u017c dawno poddali si\u0119 jego szata\u0144skim mackom, rozrywa cia\u0142o mistyczne, powoduj\u0105c zdrad\u0119 niekt\u00f3rych s\u0142abych cz\u0142onk\u00f3w cia\u0142a mistycznego naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa i przysparzaj\u0105c mu nowych samotnych m\u0119czennik\u00f3w, kt\u00f3rzy jednak nie s\u0105 opuszczeni przez Chrystusa, g\u0142ow\u0119 cia\u0142a mistycznego. Ile wiernych narz\u0119dzi b\u0119dzie mia\u0142 Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 w decyduj\u0105cym momencie oczyszczenia? Ludzie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, dzieci naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki: zaplanowawszy ten czas, kt\u00f3ry prze\u017cywa ludzko\u015b\u0107, przyw\u00f3dcy maso\u0144scy nie spoczn\u0105, dop\u00f3ki nie uda im si\u0119 wci\u0105gn\u0105\u0107 w t\u0119 wojn\u0119 coraz wi\u0119kszej liczby kraj\u00f3w; wyskocz\u0105 na oczach ludzko\u015bci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ameryk\u0119 \u0141aci\u0144sk\u0105: bro\u0144 nadchodzi, ludy zostan\u0105 rozpalone. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: b\u0119dziecie nadal zdumieni pot\u0119g\u0105 natury. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: wstrz\u0105sy ziemi b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 nasila\u0107, a ludzko\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dzie cierpie\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: pomnik wolno\u015bci wpadnie do morza. Dzieci Bo\u017ce, wzywam was do wewn\u0119trznego zbadania siebie. Musicie by\u0107 braterscy - musicie nie tylko szanowa\u0107 wzajemne r\u00f3\u017cnice, ale by\u0107 pokorni, aby dzie\u0144 po dniu przebacza\u0107 sobie nawzajem. Ka\u017cda osoba musi rozpozna\u0107 swoje s\u0142abo\u015bci poprzez g\u0142\u0119bok\u0105 prac\u0119 wewn\u0119trzn\u0105, a prosz\u0105c o bosk\u0105 pomoc pokonacie je, je\u015bli stworzenie posiada pokor\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, przyjmujcie Pokarm Eucharystyczny i z pokor\u0105 wchod\u017acie w to, czym powinno by\u0107 dla was braterstwo. Jeste\u015bcie kolumn\u0105 marszow\u0105, dzieci Bo\u017ce - kolumn\u0105, kt\u00f3ra nie zatrzymuje si\u0119, ale umacnia si\u0119, aby i\u015b\u0107 dalej bez wahania. Lud naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki nie powinien obawia\u0107 si\u0119 tego, co zosta\u0142o og\u0142oszone, ani post\u0119pu w wype\u0142nianiu si\u0119 proroctw, ale powinien obawia\u0107 si\u0119 obra\u017cania Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, powinien obawia\u0107 si\u0119 popadania w niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwo wobec Prawa Bo\u017cego, powinien obawia\u0107 si\u0119 rywalizacji i powinien obawia\u0107 si\u0119 obra\u017cania swoich braci i si\u00f3str. Obud\u017acie si\u0119, nie \u015bpijcie! Przest\u0119pstwa wzrastaj\u0105 wraz ze wzrostem braku mi\u0142o\u015bci wobec bli\u017aniego, a tak\u017ce z powodu post\u0119pu z\u0142a. Obud\u017acie si\u0119 z letargu, w kt\u00f3rym \u017cyjecie! Z\u0142o wykorzystuje tych, kt\u00f3rzy \u015bpi\u0105, aby ich zaw\u0142adn\u0105\u0107 i wywo\u0142a\u0107 niezgod\u0119 w\u015br\u00f3d ludu Bo\u017cego. Zwracajcie uwag\u0119 na sojusze mi\u0119dzy krajami: jest to alarm dla ludzko\u015bci. Umi\u0142owane dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, nie czekajcie, a\u017c niebo ujawni wam szczeg\u00f3\u0142y tego, co pozwala wam wiedzie\u0107, aby\u015bcie mogli si\u0119 przygotowa\u0107, gdy\u017c ludzko\u015b\u0107 mo\u017ce popa\u015b\u0107 w chaos, zanim nadejdzie wype\u0142nienie proroctw. Znaki i sygna\u0142y wyznaczaj\u0105 tempo tego, co zosta\u0142o zapowiedziane. B\u0105d\u017acie przygotowani, nawracajcie si\u0119 i b\u0105d\u017acie czujni! Jeste\u015bcie dzie\u0107mi Boga i moje legiony was chroni\u0105: nie rozpaczajcie. Jak mr\u00f3wki gromadz\u0105 pokarm na zim\u0119, tak wy powinni\u015bcie gromadzi\u0107 na zim\u0119. Je\u015bli nie macie do\u015b\u0107 na przechowanie, pomna\u017cajcie wasz\u0105 wiar\u0119, a moje legiony zrz\u0105dzeniem Bo\u017cym zaopatrz\u0105 was. Ludzie Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszych Serc, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119 i trwajcie mocno w wierze. Moje legiony was chroni\u0105. Przyjmijcie moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":20,"month_string":"August","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear blessed children, thank you for bending your knees in prayer and listening to my call in your heart. My Son has asked you to drink at the foot of the Cross, but many do not seek fresh and blessed waters, but brackish waters. No one or few see all that is happening on earth; heaven sends you signs to pray more, but many continue in their blindness. My children, the desert is advancing and you will be invaded by more brothers. My children, pray for the priests because they are not all shepherds, they do not bring the sheep to the fold. My children, hear and watch, do not be distracted and please convert, it is very urgent. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe gesegnete Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie sich die Knie im Gebet gebeugt und meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen zugeh\u00f6rt haben. Mein Sohn hat Sie gebeten, am Fu\u00dfe des Kreuzes zu trinken, aber viele suchen keine frischen und gesegneten Gew\u00e4sser, sondern brackiges Wasser. Niemand oder nur wenige sehen alles, was auf Erden geschieht; Der Himmel schickt dir Zeichen, um mehr zu beten, aber viele weiterhin blind. Meine Kinder, die W\u00fcste rechnet vor und Sie werden von mehr Br\u00fcdern eingedrungen. Meine Kinder beten f\u00fcr die Priester, weil sie nicht alle Hirten sind, sie bringen die Schafe nicht in die Falte. Meine Kinder h\u00f6ren und beobachten, nicht abgelenkt und bitte konvertieren, es ist sehr dringend. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Estimados ni\u00f1os de Benedetti, gracias por doblar las rodillas en oraci\u00f3n y por haber escuchado mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mi hijo te pidi\u00f3 que te abandonara al pie de la cruz, pero muchos no buscan aguas frescas y bendecidas, sino aguas salobres. Ninguno o pocos ven todo lo que sucede en la tierra, el cielo te env\u00eda las se\u00f1ales para rezar m\u00e1s, pero muchos contin\u00faan en su ceguera. Mis hijos, el desierto avanza y ser\u00e1n invadidos por otros hermanos. Ni\u00f1os, rezan por los sacerdotes porque no todos son pastores, no traen ovejas al redil. Los ni\u00f1os, escuchan y miran, no se distraen y se conviertan, es muy urgente. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants b\u00e9nis, merci d'avoir pli\u00e9 vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re et d'\u00e9couter mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mon fils vous a demand\u00e9 de boire au pied de la croix, mais beaucoup ne cherchent pas des eaux fra\u00eeches et b\u00e9nies, mais des eaux saum\u00e2tres. Personne ou peu ne voient tout ce qui se passe sur Terre; Le ciel vous envoie des signes pour prier plus, mais beaucoup continuent dans leur c\u00e9cit\u00e9. Mes enfants, le d\u00e9sert avance et vous serez envahi par plus de fr\u00e8res. Mes enfants, prient pour les pr\u00eatres parce qu'ils ne sont pas tous des bergers, ils n'apportent pas les moutons au giron. Mes enfants, entendent et regardent, ne sont pas distraits et veuillez convertir, c'est tr\u00e8s urgent. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli Benedetti, grazie per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia nella preghiera e per aver ascoltato la mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Mio Figlio vi ha chiesto di abbeverarvi ai piedi della croce, ma molti non cercano acque dolci e benedette, ma acque salmastre. Nessuno o pochi vedono tutto ci\u00f2 che accade sulla terra, il cielo vi invia i segnali per pregare di pi\u00f9, ma molti continuano nella loro cecit\u00e0. Figli miei, il deserto avanza e sarete invasi da altri fratelli. Figli, pregate per i sacerdoti perch\u00e9 non sono tutti pastori, non portano le pecore all\u2019ovile. Figli, udite e guardate, non siate distratti e vi prego convertitevi, \u00e8 molto urgente. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie b\u0142ogos\u0142awione dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie do modlitwy i \u017ce pos\u0142uchali\u015bcie mojego wezwania w waszych sercach. M\u00f3j Syn prosi\u0142 was o picie u st\u00f3p Krzy\u017ca, ale wielu nie szuka \u015bwie\u017cych i b\u0142ogos\u0142awionych w\u00f3d, ale w\u00f3d s\u0142onych. Niewielu jest w stanie zobaczy\u0107 wszystko, co si\u0119 dzieje na ziemi. Niebo zsy\u0142a wam znaki, aby\u015bcie si\u0119 mocniej modlili, ale wielu trwa w swojej \u015blepocie. Moje dzieci, pustynia przybli\u017ca si\u0119 i zostaniecie najechani przez innych braci. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za kap\u0142an\u00f3w, bo nie wszyscy s\u0105 pasterzami, nie wszyscy wprowadzaj\u0105 owce do owczarni. Moje dzieci, s\u0142uchajcie i patrzcie, nie rozpraszajcie si\u0119 i prosz\u0119 o nawr\u00f3cenie, to bardzo pilne. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos aben\u00e7oados, obrigado por dobrar os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e ouvir minha chamada em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meu filho pediu que voc\u00ea bebesse no p\u00e9 da cruz, mas muitos n\u00e3o procuram \u00e1guas frescas e aben\u00e7oadas, mas \u00e1guas salobras. Ningu\u00e9m v\u00ea tudo o que est\u00e1 acontecendo na terra; O c\u00e9u envia sinais para orar mais, mas muitos continuam em sua cegueira. Meus filhos, o deserto est\u00e1 avan\u00e7ando e voc\u00ea ser\u00e1 invadido por mais irm\u00e3os. Meus filhos, oram pelos sacerdotes porque nem todos s\u00e3o pastores, eles n\u00e3o trazem as ovelhas para o dobro. Meus filhos, ouvem e assista, n\u00e3o se distraem e convertem, \u00e9 muito urgente. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u795d\u798f\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5c48\u670d\u4e8e\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5e76\u542c\u6211\u200b\u200b\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8981\u6c42\u60a8\u5728\u5341\u5b57\u67b6\u7684\u811a\u4e0b\u559d\u9152\uff0c\u4f46\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u4e0d\u5bfb\u6c42\u65b0\u9c9c\u800c\u6709\u798f\u7684\u6c34\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u54b8\u6c34\u3002\u6ca1\u6709\u4eba\u770b\u5230\u5730\u7403\u4e0a\u53d1\u751f\u7684\u4e00\u5207\u3002\u5929\u5802\u5411\u60a8\u53d1\u9001\u8ff9\u8c61\uff0c\u4ee5\u7948\u7977\u66f4\u591a\uff0c\u4f46\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u4ecd\u5728\u5931\u660e\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6c99\u6f20\u6b63\u5728\u524d\u8fdb\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u88ab\u66f4\u591a\u5144\u5f1f\u5165\u4fb5\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e3a\u796d\u53f8\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e0d\u662f\u6240\u6709\u7267\u7f8a\u4eba\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e0d\u4f1a\u628a\u7ef5\u7f8a\u6298\u53e0\u8d77\u6765\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u542c\u548c\u89c2\u770b\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5206\u5fc3\uff0c\u8bf7\u8f6c\u6362\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u975e\u5e38\u7d27\u6025\u7684\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":22,"month_string":"August","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved children, receive my blessing from my most Sacred Heart. You are my people... Whom I love and desire to rescue. My beloved people, I invite you to come with me. Just as the river is a single flow and all the tributaries that derive from the main river carry the same water giving life to all that is beside it, so my children must give what they carry inside: love for me and take it to their brothers and sisters every moment of their lives. Without fear, be tireless and continue on the sure path that leads you to me. The personal encounter with me is a primordial need for each of my children. My children, do not disperse, keep yourselves in unity. Events mark the course of what is to come. You must keep in mind that several events can happen in one day and thus shorten the line of the moment. Prepare for the Warning, examine yourselves inwardly, be humble, fulfil what I call you to fulfil and accept my word with love. The advance of the war continues, that war that you do not see, that war that has awakened the moment of the great blackout, that war that will soon bring down the world economy, that war that has been planned and directed by the interests of the elite and that will then go out to impose its laws, its government, its economy, its religion and its education on the peoples. Pray my children, pray for Central America, the suffering comes with the shaking of the earth. Pray children, pray, pray, the new disease is very serious and contagious to the point of being deadly. Protect your immune system and have the calendula cream and moringa ready for them to take. Pray children, pray the Vatican marks the approaching moment. Italy, how much you will suffer! France, how I grieve for this beloved country! My beloved, my people, the volcanoes enter into greater activity, the intensity is strong and my children suffer. My people, the convulsion is growing. See how much humanity is agitated, motivated by evil and creating conflicts. See how my people suffer as they cling to false man-made gods. Children, a leader holds world aspirations to preside over the one government and for this reason a great and strong battle will be fought. My house is compromised... My children feel desperate, yet it is not so, 'I am that I am' and I do not leave them alone. Attentive, my children, attentive! Do not fall prey to fear, be discerning, do not anticipate the variants of illnesses, it is not necessary to hurry. Have firm faith. My love is for each of you. My children, you are at a time when the devil is pouncing against my people. You will suffer, but you will never be defeated because I am with my people. I bless you; my love is powerful. Love my Mother without fear. My blessing is in each one. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Moje ukochane dzieci, przyjmijcie moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo od mojego naj\u015bwi\u0119tszego Serca. Jeste\u015bcie moim ludem... kt\u00f3ry kocham i pragn\u0119 ratowa\u0107. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, zach\u0119cam was, aby\u015bcie poszli ze mn\u0105. Tak jak rzeka jest jednym strumieniem i wszystkie dop\u0142ywy, kt\u00f3re odchodz\u0105 od g\u0142\u00f3wnej rzeki, nios\u0105 t\u0119 sam\u0105 wod\u0119, daj\u0105c \u017cycie wszystkiemu, co jest obok, tak moje dzieci musz\u0105 da\u0107 to, co nosz\u0105 w sobie: mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do mnie i zanie\u015b\u0107 j\u0105 swoim braciom i siostrom w ka\u017cdej chwili swojego \u017cycia. Bez l\u0119ku b\u0105d\u017acie niestrudzeni i pod\u0105\u017cajcie dalej pewn\u0105 drog\u0105, kt\u00f3ra prowadzi was do Mnie. Osobiste spotkanie ze mn\u0105 jest pierwotn\u0105 potrzeb\u0105 ka\u017cdego z moich dzieci. Moje dzieci, nie rozpraszajcie si\u0119, zachowujcie si\u0119 w jedno\u015bci. Wydarzenia wyznaczaj\u0105 kierunek tego, co ma nast\u0105pi\u0107. Musicie pami\u0119ta\u0107, \u017ce w jednym dniu mo\u017ce si\u0119 wydarzy\u0107 kilka wydarze\u0144 i w ten spos\u00f3b skr\u00f3ci\u0107 lini\u0119 chwili. Przygotujcie si\u0119 na Ostrze\u017cenie, badajcie si\u0119 wewn\u0119trznie, b\u0105d\u017acie pokorni, wype\u0142niajcie to, do czego was wzywam i przyjmujcie moje s\u0142owo z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Post\u0119p wojny trwa, tej wojny, kt\u00f3rej nie widzicie, tej wojny, kt\u00f3ra obudzi\u0142a moment wielkiego zaciemnienia, tej wojny, kt\u00f3ra wkr\u00f3tce doprowadzi do upadku gospodarki \u015bwiatowej, tej wojny, kt\u00f3ra zosta\u0142a zaplanowana i wyre\u017cyserowana przez interesy elit i kt\u00f3ra nast\u0119pnie wyjdzie, aby narzuci\u0107 ludom swoje prawa, sw\u00f3j rz\u0105d, swoj\u0105 gospodark\u0119, swoj\u0105 religi\u0119 i swoj\u0105 edukacj\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ameryk\u0119 \u015arodkow\u0105, cierpienie przychodzi wraz ze wstrz\u0105sem ziemi. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, nowa choroba jest bardzo powa\u017cna i zara\u017aliwa do tego stopnia, \u017ce jest \u015bmiertelna. Chro\u0144cie sw\u00f3j system odporno\u015bciowy i miejcie przygotowany krem z nagietka i moringi, aby mogli je przyjmowa\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, aby Watykan zaznaczy\u0142 zbli\u017caj\u0105c\u0105 si\u0119 chwil\u0119. W\u0142ochy, jak bardzo b\u0119dziecie cierpie\u0107! Francjo, jak\u017ce smuc\u0119 si\u0119 z powodu tego ukochanego kraju! Moi umi\u0142owani, m\u00f3j lud, wulkany wchodz\u0105 w wi\u0119ksz\u0105 aktywno\u015b\u0107, intensywno\u015b\u0107 jest silna i moje dzieci cierpi\u0105. M\u00f3j ludu, konwulsja narasta. Zobaczcie, jak bardzo ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest wzburzona, motywowana przez z\u0142o i tworz\u0105ca konflikty. Zobaczcie, jak m\u00f3j lud cierpi, gdy trzyma si\u0119 fa\u0142szywych bog\u00f3w stworzonych przez cz\u0142owieka. Dzieci, przyw\u00f3dca ma \u015bwiatowe aspiracje, aby przewodniczy\u0107 jednemu rz\u0105dowi i z tego powodu b\u0119dzie toczy\u0107 si\u0119 wielka i silna walka. M\u00f3j dom jest zagro\u017cony... Moje dzieci czuj\u0105 si\u0119 zrozpaczone, ale tak nie jest, \"Ja jestem, kt\u00f3ry jestem\" i nie zostawiam ich samych. Uwa\u017cni, moje dzieci, uwa\u017cni! Nie padajcie ofiar\u0105 strachu, b\u0105d\u017acie rozeznani, nie przewidujcie wariant\u00f3w chor\u00f3b, nie trzeba si\u0119 spieszy\u0107. Miejcie mocn\u0105 wiar\u0119. Moja mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 jest dla ka\u017cdego z was. Moje dzieci, jeste\u015bcie w czasie, kiedy diabe\u0142 rzuca si\u0119 na m\u00f3j lud. B\u0119dziecie cierpie\u0107, ale nigdy nie zostaniecie pokonani, poniewa\u017c Ja jestem z moim ludem. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was; moja mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 jest pot\u0119\u017cna. Kochajcie moj\u0105 Matk\u0119 bez l\u0119ku. Moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo jest w ka\u017cdym z nich. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":23,"month_string":"August","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, pray, pray much, for the world is in great danger, humanity is in great danger, even the Church is closing its doors.  My children, soon a schism will shake the Church of Rome, shrouded in darkness. My children, remember that I am here every day together with my Jesus, do not fear because you will always have our comfort when you invoke our names. My children, pray especially for France, for she has lost her faith, the signs sent from heaven will be very strong and evident. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie in Ihren Herzen auf meinen Anruf geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder beten, beten hart, denn die Welt ist in gro\u00dfer Gefahr, die Menschheit ist in gro\u00dfer Gefahr, sogar die Kirche schlie\u00dft ihre T\u00fcr. Meine Kinder, bald wird Schisma die r\u00f6mische Kirche sch\u00fctteln, in der Dunkelheit geh\u00fcllt. Meine Kinder, denken Sie daran, dass ich jeden Tag mit meinem Jesus hier bin, haben Sie keine Angst, weil wir Sie immer tr\u00f6sten, wenn Sie unsere Namen nennen. Meine Kinder beten besonders f\u00fcr Frankreich, weil sie den Glauben verloren hat, die Zeichen, die vom Himmel geschickt wurden, werden sehr stark und sichtbar sein. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, rezan, rezan mucho, porque el mundo est\u00e1 en gran peligro, la humanidad est\u00e1 en gran peligro, la iglesia tambi\u00e9n cierra las puertas. Mis hijos, pronto un cisma har\u00e1 temblar la Iglesia de Roma, rodeada de la oscuridad. Mis hijos, recuerdan que estoy aqu\u00ed todos los d\u00edas junto con mi Jes\u00fas, no tengan miedo porque siempre tendr\u00e1s nuestra comodidad cuando invocas nuestros nombres. Los ni\u00f1os, rezaron en particular por Francia, porque ha perdido la fe, las se\u00f1ales enviadas desde el cielo ser\u00e1n muy fuertes y evidentes. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci dans vos c\u0153urs, vous avez r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel. Mes enfants, priez, priez dur, parce que le monde est en grand danger, l'humanit\u00e9 est en grand danger, m\u00eame l'\u00e9glise ferme sa porte. Mes enfants, bient\u00f4t le schisme, secouera l'\u00e9glise romaine, envelopp\u00e9e d'obscurit\u00e9. Mes enfants, rappelez-vous que je suis ici avec mon J\u00e9sus tous les jours, n'ayez pas peur car nous vous r\u00e9conforterons toujours lorsque vous appellerez nos noms. Mes enfants, prient surtout pour la France, car elle a perdu la foi, les panneaux envoy\u00e9s du ciel seront tr\u00e8s forts et visibles. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, pregate, pregate tanto, perch\u00e9 il mondo \u00e8 in grande pericolo, l\u2019umanit\u00e0 \u00e8 in grande pericolo, anche la Chiesa chiude le porte.  Figli miei, presto uno scisma far\u00e0 tremare la Chiesa di Roma, avvolta dalle tenebre. Figli miei, ricordate che Io sono qui tutti i giorni insieme al mio Ges\u00f9, non temete perch\u00e9 avrete sempre il nostro conforto, quando invocherete i nostri nomi.  Figli, pregate in particolare per la Francia, perch\u00e9 ha perso la fede, i segnali inviati dal cielo saranno molto forti ed evidenti. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce w waszych sercach odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 mocno, bo \u015bwiat jest w wielkim niebezpiecze\u0144stwie, ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest w wielkim niebezpiecze\u0144stwie, nawet Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 zamyka swoje drzwi. Moje dzieci, wkr\u00f3tce schizma wstrz\u0105\u015bnie Ko\u015bcio\u0142em Rzymskim, owianym ciemno\u015bci\u0105. Moje dzieci, pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce jestem tu codziennie z moim Jezusem, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, bo zawsze was pocieszymy, gdy b\u0119dziecie przywo\u0142ywa\u0107 nasze imiona. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 szczeg\u00f3lnie za Francj\u0119, poniewa\u017c straci\u0142a wiar\u0119, znaki wysy\u0142ane z nieba b\u0119d\u0105 bardzo silne i widoczne. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado em que em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es voc\u00ea respondeu \u00e0 minha liga\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, orem, orem com for\u00e7a, porque o mundo est\u00e1 em grande perigo, a humanidade est\u00e1 em grande perigo, at\u00e9 a igreja fecha sua porta. Meus filhos, logo o cisma abalar\u00e1 a igreja romana, envolta na escurid\u00e3o. Meus filhos, lembre -se de que estou aqui com meu Jesus todos os dias, n\u00e3o tenha medo, porque sempre o confortaremos quando voc\u00ea chamar nossos nomes. Meus filhos, oram especialmente pela Fran\u00e7a, porque ela perdeu a f\u00e9, os sinais enviados do c\u00e9u ser\u00e3o muito fortes e vis\u00edveis. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\uff0c\u60a8\u5728\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u52aa\u529b\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4e16\u754c\u5904\u4e8e\u6781\u5927\u7684\u5371\u9669\u4e4b\u4e2d\uff0c\u4eba\u7c7b\u5904\u4e8e\u6781\u5927\u7684\u5371\u9669\u4e4b\u4e2d\uff0c\u751a\u81f3\u6559\u4f1a\u90fd\u5173\u95e8\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u5f88\u5feb\u5206\u88c2\u5c06\u6447\u6643\u7f57\u9a6c\u6559\u5802\uff0c\u7b3c\u7f69\u5728\u9ed1\u6697\u4e2d\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8bf7\u8bb0\u4f4f\u6211\u6bcf\u5929\u90fd\u548c\u6211\u7684\u8036\u7a23\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5f53\u60a8\u53eb\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u540d\u5b57\u65f6\uff0c\u6211\u4eec\u5c06\u6c38\u8fdc\u5b89\u6170\u60a8\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u7279\u522b\u4e3a\u6cd5\u56fd\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5979\u5931\u53bb\u4e86\u4fe1\u5fc3\uff0c\u6240\u4ee5\u4ece\u5929\u4e0a\u5bc4\u51fa\u7684\u8ff9\u8c61\u5c06\u975e\u5e38\u5f3a\u70c8\u548c\u53ef\u89c1\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u60a8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":27,"month_string":"August","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for hearing My call in your heart and for bending your knees in prayer. My child, lead My people to God, do not be afraid, I also carried a great burden in My heart, but you will have the grace to be able to be stronger. Pray children, for the nuclear power plants in the East, for danger begins for My children. Pray for the Church and be united in the name of Jesus Christ. My children I touch the earth and walk in my earthly pilgrimage to remove my children from the mud, yet still I see that they reject grace. My child, do not fear, I will always be at your side and bless you all in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass du meinen Anruf in deinem Herzen geh\u00f6rt hast und deine Knie im Gebet beugt hast. Mein Kind, f\u00fchre mein Volk zu Gott, habe keine Angst, ich habe auch eine gro\u00dfe Last in meinem Herzen, aber du wirst die Gnade haben, um st\u00e4rker zu sein. Beten Sie Kinder, f\u00fcr die Kernkraftwerke im Osten, denn f\u00fcr meine Kinder beginnt die Gefahr. Bete f\u00fcr die Kirche und sei im Namen Jesu Christi vereint. Meine Kinder ber\u00fchren die Erde und gehe in meiner irdischen Pilgerreise, um meine Kinder aus dem Schlamm zu entfernen, aber ich sehe trotzdem, dass sie Gnade ablehnen. Mein Kind, f\u00fcrchte nicht, ich werde immer an deiner Seite sein und dich alle im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen, segnen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por escuchar mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n y por haber doblado las rodillas en oraci\u00f3n. Mi hija, llevo a mi pueblo hacia Dios, sin tener miedo, tambi\u00e9n traje un gran peso en mi coraz\u00f3n, pero tendr\u00e1s gracia para ser m\u00e1s fuerte. Ore por los ni\u00f1os, por las centrales nucleares del este, porque el peligro comienza para mis hijos. Ore por la Iglesia y unirse en el nombre de Jesucristo. Mis hijos tocan la tierra y caminan en mi peregrinaci\u00f3n terrenal para sacar a mis hijos del barro, pero a\u00fan as\u00ed veo que rechazan la gracia. Mi hija, no temas, siempre estar\u00e9 a tu lado y los bendecir\u00e9 a todos en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir entendu mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur et d'avoir pli\u00e9 vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re. Mon enfant, dirige mon peuple \u00e0 Dieu, n'ayez pas peur, j'ai \u00e9galement port\u00e9 un grand fardeau dans mon c\u0153ur, mais vous aurez la gr\u00e2ce de pouvoir \u00eatre plus fort. Priez les enfants, pour les centrales nucl\u00e9aires \u00e0 l'est, car le danger commence pour mes enfants. Priez pour l'\u00c9glise et soyez unis au nom de J\u00e9sus-Christ. Mes enfants, je touche la terre et marche dans mon p\u00e8lerinage terrestre pour retirer mes enfants de la boue, mais je vois toujours qu'ils rejettent la gr\u00e2ce. Mon enfant, ne craigne pas, je serai toujours \u00e0 vos c\u00f4t\u00e9s et vous b\u00e9nirai tous au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver ascoltato la mia chiamata nel vostro cuore e per aver piegato le ginocchia nella preghiera. Figlia mia, conduci il mio popolo verso Dio, non aver paura, anche Io portai un grande peso nel mio cuore, ma avrai la grazia per poter essere pi\u00f9 forte. Pregate figli, per le centrali nucleari dell\u2019est, perch\u00e9 inizia il pericolo per i miei figli. Pregate per la Chiesa e siate uniti nel nome di Ges\u00f9 Cristo. Figli miei tocco la terra e cammino nel mio pellegrinaggio terreno per togliere i miei figli dal fango, eppure ancora vedo che rifiutano la grazia. Figlia mia, non temere, Io sar\u00f2 sempre al tuo fianco e vi benedico tutti nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce s\u0142uchacie mojego wo\u0142ania w waszym sercu i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie do modlitwy. Moje dziecko, prowad\u017a m\u00f3j lud ku Bogu, nie b\u00f3j si\u0119, ja te\u017c nosz\u0119 w sercu wielki ci\u0119\u017car, ale ty b\u0119dziesz mia\u0142a \u0142ask\u0119, \u017ce b\u0119dziesz silniejsza. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, za elektrownie atomowe na wschodzie, bo zaczyna si\u0119 niebezpiecze\u0144stwo dla moich dzieci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 i b\u0105d\u017acie zjednoczeni w imi\u0119 Jezusa Chrystusa. Moje dzieci, dotykam ziemi i chodz\u0119 w mojej ziemskiej pielgrzymce, aby usun\u0105\u0107 moje dzieci z bagna, a jednak wci\u0105\u017c widz\u0119, \u017ce odrzucaj\u0105 \u0142ask\u0119. Moje dziecko, nie l\u0119kaj si\u0119, ja zawsze b\u0119d\u0119 przy tobie i b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was wszystkich w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por ouvir meu chamado em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o e por dobrar os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meu filho, leva meu povo a Deus, n\u00e3o tenha medo, tamb\u00e9m carregava um grande fardo em meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o, mas voc\u00ea ter\u00e1 a gra\u00e7a de poder ser mais forte. Ore as crian\u00e7as, para as usinas nucleares no Oriente, pois o perigo come\u00e7a para meus filhos. Ore pela igreja e esteja unido em nome de Jesus Cristo. Meus filhos eu toco a terra e ando em minha peregrina\u00e7\u00e3o terrena para remover meus filhos da lama, mas ainda vejo que eles rejeitam a gra\u00e7a. Meu filho, n\u00e3o tema, eu sempre estarei ao seu lado e aben\u00e7oei todos voc\u00eas em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u542c\u5230\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u7948\u7977\u4e2d\u5f2f\u8170\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u5e26\u9886\u6211\u7684\u5b50\u6c11\u524d\u5f80\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5185\u5fc3\u4e5f\u627f\u62c5\u7740\u5de8\u5927\u7684\u8d1f\u62c5\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u60a8\u5c06\u6709\u80fd\u529b\u53d8\u5f97\u66f4\u575a\u5f3a\u7684\u6069\u5178\u3002\u7948\u7977\u513f\u7ae5\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4e1c\u65b9\u7684\u6838\u7535\u7ad9\u4e3a\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u5f00\u59cb\u5371\u9669\u3002\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ee5\u8036\u7a23\u57fa\u7763\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u56e2\u7ed3\u8d77\u6765\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u89e6\u6478\u5730\u7403\uff0c\u8d70\u8fdb\u6211\u7684\u5c18\u4e16\u671d\u5723\uff0c\u5c06\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4ece\u6ce5\u6cde\u4e2d\u79fb\u8d70\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\u4ecd\u7136\u770b\u5230\u4ed6\u4eec\u62d2\u7edd\u4e86\u6069\u5178\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u6211\u5c06\u6c38\u8fdc\u7ad9\u5728\u4f60\u8eab\u8fb9\uff0c\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u4eec\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":28,"month_string":"August","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: As prince of the heavenly legions, I bless you. My sword, given by God the Father, upholds the love of God to defend human creatures from all evil and to heal their body and soul. I am defender of God's people and I fight against darkness to bring light to mankind. I am pleased with your prayers and that you address prayers to me, but as the people of God, you must be fulfillers of the divine will in your daily work and actions, maintaining at all times or circumstances the balance, sobriety, equanimity and charity of the true child of God. I listen to various prayers during the day and some in the evening, but if they do not fulfil the Will of God, they are far from making me happy. I do not desire glamorous altars, but small altars in homes and great doers of the divine will in each one of you. I must mention to you that he who claims to be devoted to me must keep as his staff the love of God and of his neighbour as himself. Understand that all that is developing at this moment in the creation reaches the man of God in particular. If this creature of God has a hardened heart and a polluted mind, everything that comes into view in creation is detrimental to his spiritual work and actions. The designs of God are being fulfilled little by little and several revelations will be fulfilled with lightning speed. The human creature has been a contributor in altering the designs of God and this is the moment of fulfilment. The waters surge in great flows without control in the populations, the air blows with intensity causing damages, the fire arrives without being expected and together with the air they lead to burn everything in their path, the earth collapses in several places... Animals surprise the human creature with their behaviour... Birds die in the air contaminated by toxic substances that man himself places to be transported through the air leading the birds to fall lifeless in the cities. Be cautious and do not touch them. Marine animals come out of the sea or rivers in surprising numbers because the deep layers of the earth move causing marine animals to instinctively want to come out to save themselves. In the prairies, animals die in large numbers. People of God, what a power will use in war is being tested from on high. It is the commotion of creation. It is the commotion of the human creature that Satan takes advantage of to throw his darts of poison at those who deny the faith or mock the faith and at those who remain in a state of anger or spiritual foolishness. Those darts lead them to be inaccessible creatures, they lose charity, sensibility and their 'ego' grows without measure until they are lost; unless they submit to prayer and fasting so that the poison comes out of them and humility brings them closer to God. The onslaught of the devil against the human creature leads to prompt rebellions in the countries and the uprisings do not wait, although the repression is immediate. Communism has taken over the governments and the elite appoint them, leading the poor to be poorer, the middle class falls into poverty and the big capitalists see their status vanished if they refuse to implant the seal of evil. Do not lose faith, pray the holy rosary. So many wishes to approach great places of Marian apparitions without contemplating that they may be left somewhere along the way; but God in his infinite mercy has decreed that, in Marian shrines all over the world, his children will be blessed with the miracle and in some places far away from the main cities, the Holy Trinity will bless them as well. In all these sanctuaries water will gush forth to heal the sick in body and soul. People of God, do not despair, keep the faith firm and immovable. You are being tested. Calm your minds, help one another and you will not be disappointed. Do not fear, my legions fight with a weapon before which the devil is enraged: it is the weapon of love. People of God, my sword is given by God and signifies the Will of God and his power in the face of evil. I will defend you and fight for you by Divine Order. Without fear, increase the faith. I bless you. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 legion\u00f3w niebieskich b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. M\u00f3j miecz, dany przez Boga Ojca, podtrzymuje mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 Boga, aby broni\u0107 stworze\u0144 ludzkich przed wszelkim z\u0142em i uzdrawia\u0107 ich cia\u0142o i dusz\u0119. Jestem obro\u0144c\u0105 ludu Bo\u017cego i walcz\u0119 z ciemno\u015bci\u0105, aby przynie\u015b\u0107 \u015bwiat\u0142o ludzko\u015bci. Ciesz\u0119 si\u0119 z waszych modlitw i z tego, \u017ce kierujecie modlitwy do mnie, ale jako lud Bo\u017cy musicie by\u0107 wykonawcami Woli Bo\u017cej w waszych codziennych pracach i dzia\u0142aniach, zachowuj\u0105c w ka\u017cdym czasie i okoliczno\u015bciach r\u00f3wnowag\u0119, trze\u017awo\u015b\u0107, jednomy\u015blno\u015b\u0107 i mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 prawdziwego dziecka Bo\u017cego. S\u0142ucham r\u00f3\u017cnych modlitw w ci\u0105gu dnia i niekt\u00f3rych wieczorem, ale je\u015bli nie wype\u0142niaj\u0105 one Woli Bo\u017cej, s\u0105 dalekie od uszcz\u0119\u015bliwienia mnie. Nie pragn\u0119 wspania\u0142ych o\u0142tarzy, ale ma\u0142ych o\u0142tarzy w domach i wielkich wykonawc\u00f3w woli Bo\u017cej w ka\u017cdym z was. Musz\u0119 wam wspomnie\u0107, \u017ce ten, kto twierdzi, \u017ce jest mi oddany, musi zachowa\u0107 jako swoj\u0105 lask\u0119 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 Boga i bli\u017aniego jak siebie samego. Zrozumcie, \u017ce wszystko, co rozwija si\u0119 w tej chwili w stworzeniu, dosi\u0119ga szczeg\u00f3lnie cz\u0142owieka Bo\u017cego. Je\u015bli to stworzenie Bo\u017ce ma zatwardzia\u0142e serce i ska\u017cony umys\u0142, wszystko, co pojawia si\u0119 w stworzeniu, jest szkodliwe dla jego duchowej pracy i dzia\u0142a\u0144. Zamys\u0142y Bo\u017ce wype\u0142niaj\u0105 si\u0119 poma\u0142u, a kilka objawie\u0144 spe\u0142ni si\u0119 z szybko\u015bci\u0105 b\u0142yskawicy. Ludzkie stworzenie przyczyni\u0142o si\u0119 do zmiany plan\u00f3w Boga i to jest moment spe\u0142nienia. Wody wzbieraj\u0105 wielkimi strumieniami bez kontroli w populacjach, powietrze wieje z intensywno\u015bci\u0105 powoduj\u0105c szkody, ogie\u0144 przybywa bez oczekiwania i wraz z powietrzem prowadzi do spalenia wszystkiego na swojej drodze, ziemia zapada si\u0119 w kilku miejscach... Zwierz\u0119ta zaskakuj\u0105 ludzkie stworzenia swoim zachowaniem... Ptaki gin\u0105 w powietrzu ska\u017conym toksycznymi substancjami, kt\u00f3re cz\u0142owiek sam umieszcza w powietrzu, co prowadzi do tego, \u017ce ptaki padaj\u0105 bez \u017cycia w miastach. B\u0105d\u017a ostro\u017cny i nie dotykaj ich. Zwierz\u0119ta morskie wychodz\u0105 z morza lub rzek w zaskakuj\u0105cych ilo\u015bciach, poniewa\u017c g\u0142\u0119bokie warstwy ziemi poruszaj\u0105 si\u0119 powoduj\u0105c, \u017ce zwierz\u0119ta morskie instynktownie chc\u0105 wyj\u015b\u0107, aby si\u0119 uratowa\u0107. Na preriach zwierz\u0119ta gin\u0105 w du\u017cych ilo\u015bciach. Ludu Bo\u017cy, to co moc wykorzysta w wojnie jest sprawdzane z wysoka. To jest zamieszanie stworzenia. Jest to zamieszanie w ludzkim stworzeniu, kt\u00f3re szatan wykorzystuje, aby rzuca\u0107 swoje lotki z trucizn\u0105 na tych, kt\u00f3rzy zaprzeczaj\u0105 wierze lub wy\u015bmiewaj\u0105 si\u0119 z niej, a tak\u017ce na tych, kt\u00f3rzy pozostaj\u0105 w stanie gniewu lub duchowej g\u0142upoty. Te rzutki prowadz\u0105 ich do tego, \u017ce staj\u0105 si\u0119 istotami niedost\u0119pnymi, trac\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, wra\u017cliwo\u015b\u0107, a ich \"ego\" ro\u015bnie bez miary, a\u017c do zatracenia; chyba \u017ce poddadz\u0105 si\u0119 modlitwie i postowi, aby trucizna wysz\u0142a z nich, a pokora zbli\u017cy\u0142a ich do Boga. Napa\u015b\u0107 diab\u0142a na stworzenie ludzkie prowadzi do szybkich bunt\u00f3w w krajach, a powstania nie czekaj\u0105, cho\u0107 represje s\u0105 natychmiastowe. Komunizm przej\u0105\u0142 rz\u0105dy, a elity je powo\u0142uj\u0105, co prowadzi do tego, \u017ce biedni staj\u0105 si\u0119 biedniejsi, klasa \u015brednia popada w ub\u00f3stwo, a wielcy kapitali\u015bci widz\u0105, \u017ce ich status znika, je\u015bli odm\u00f3wi\u0105 wszczepienia piecz\u0119ci z\u0142a. Nie tra\u0107cie wiary, odmawiajcie r\u00f3\u017caniec \u015bwi\u0119ty. Tak wielu pragnie zbli\u017cy\u0107 si\u0119 do wielkich miejsc objawie\u0144 maryjnych, nie zastanawiaj\u0105c si\u0119 nad tym, \u017ce mog\u0105 zosta\u0107 opuszczeni gdzie\u015b po drodze; ale B\u00f3g w swoim niesko\u0144czonym mi\u0142osierdziu zadekretowa\u0142, \u017ce w sanktuariach maryjnych na ca\u0142ym \u015bwiecie jego dzieci zostan\u0105 pob\u0142ogos\u0142awione cudem, a w niekt\u00f3rych miejscach oddalonych od g\u0142\u00f3wnych miast, Tr\u00f3jca \u015awi\u0119ta pob\u0142ogos\u0142awi je r\u00f3wnie\u017c. We wszystkich tych sanktuariach wytry\u015bnie woda, kt\u00f3ra uzdrowi chorych na ciele i duszy. Ludu Bo\u017cy, nie rozpaczajcie, zachowajcie wiar\u0119 mocn\u0105 i niewzruszon\u0105. Jeste\u015bcie poddawani pr\u00f3bom. Uspok\u00f3jcie swoje umys\u0142y, pomagajcie sobie nawzajem, a nie zawiedziecie si\u0119. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, moje legiony walcz\u0105 broni\u0105, przed kt\u00f3r\u0105 diabe\u0142 jest w\u015bciek\u0142y: jest to bro\u0144 mi\u0142o\u015bci. Ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3j miecz jest dany przez Boga i oznacza wol\u0119 Boga i jego moc w obliczu z\u0142a. B\u0119d\u0119 was broni\u0142 i walczy\u0142 za was z Bo\u017cego rozkazu. Bez l\u0119ku zwi\u0119kszajcie wiar\u0119. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 Ci\u0119. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":8,"day":30,"month_string":"August","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My daughter, thank you for welcoming me into your heart. Mankind is descending into the abyss, My children have lost their reason, many confused priests will leave the Churches that are already emptying of believers. Oh! My child, everything is unfolding fast. Many should unite and fight, not with weapons, but with prayer, leading the flock to one Shepherd who is Jesus Christ. I ask the rulers: go around the world to bring peace, otherwise a great war will suck you in. By now, the time is being prepared for the Great Monarch, who is completing his preparation for his entrance, he will be clothed with the Holy Spirit and will bring peace in the time of antichrist and true Christian persecution. Thank you my children for your prayers, for they dry my tears. Many graces will descend today.  Pray for the Church and for Russia. The great serpent will advance, but I, the Immaculate Conception, will crush him. Now I bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Tochter, danke, dass du mich in deinem Herzen willkommen gehei\u00dfen hast. Die Menschheit steigt in den Abgrund ab, meine Kinder haben ihren Grund verloren, viele verwirrte Priester werden die Kirchen verlassen, die bereits Gl\u00e4ubige entleeren. Oh! Mein Kind, alles entfaltet sich schnell. Viele sollten sich vereinen und k\u00e4mpfen, nicht mit Waffen, sondern mit dem Gebet, was die Herde zu einem Hirten f\u00fchrt, der Jesus Christus ist. Ich bitte die Herrscher: Gehe um die Welt, um Frieden zu bringen, sonst wird ein gro\u00dfer Krieg dich einsaugen. Inzwischen wird die Zeit f\u00fcr den gro\u00dfen Monarchen vorbereitet, der seine Vorbereitung auf seinen Eingang abschlie\u00dft, er wird mit dem bekleidet sein mit dem Heiliger Geist und wird Frieden in die Zeit des antichristischen und wahren christlichen Verfolgung bringen. Vielen Dank an meine Kinder f\u00fcr Ihre Gebete, denn sie trocknen meine Tr\u00e4nen. Viele Gnaden werden heute absteigen. Bete f\u00fcr die Kirche und f\u00fcr Russland. Die gro\u00dfe Schlange wird voranschreiten, aber ich, die makellose Empf\u00e4ngnis, wird ihn zerquetschen. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen der heiligsten Dreifaltigkeit, Amen.","text_es":"Mi hija, gracias por darme la bienvenida en tu coraz\u00f3n. La humanidad est\u00e1 descendiendo al abismo, mis hijos han perdido la raz\u00f3n, muchos sacerdotes confundidos dejar\u00e1n las iglesias que ya se est\u00e1n vaciando de fieles. \u00a1Vaya! Mi hija, todo est\u00e1 teniendo lugar r\u00e1pidamente. Muchos deber\u00edan unirse y pelear, no con armas, sino con oraci\u00f3n, llevar el reba\u00f1o a un solo pastor que es Jesucristo. Le pregunto a los gobernantes: ve al mundo para traer paz, de lo contrario, una gran guerra la devolver\u00e1. En este momento, se est\u00e1n preparando los tiempos del Gran Monarca, que est\u00e1 completando su preparaci\u00f3n para su entrada, estar\u00e1 cubierto con el Esp\u00edritu Santo y traer\u00e1 paz en el tiempo del Anticristo y la verdadera persecuci\u00f3n cristiana. Gracias a mis hijos por sus oraciones, porque se secan las l\u00e1grimas. Hoy muchas gracias disminuir\u00e1n. Ore por la iglesia y por Rusia. La gran serpiente avanzar\u00e1, pero yo, la inmaculada concepci\u00f3n, la aplastar\u00e1. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Ma fille, merci de m'avoir accueilli dans votre c\u0153ur. L'humanit\u00e9 descend dans l'ab\u00eeme, mes enfants ont perdu leur raison, de nombreux pr\u00eatres confus quitteront les \u00e9glises qui vident d\u00e9j\u00e0 les croyants. Oh! Mon enfant, tout se d\u00e9roule rapidement. Beaucoup devraient s'unir et se battre, non pas avec des armes, mais avec la pri\u00e8re, menant le troupeau \u00e0 un berger qui est J\u00e9sus-Christ. Je demande aux dirigeants: faites le tour du monde pour apporter la paix, sinon une grande guerre vous aspire. \u00c0 ce jour, le moment est venu pour le grand monarque, qui termine sa pr\u00e9paration \u00e0 son entr\u00e9e, il sera v\u00eatu du Saint-Esprit et apportera la paix au temps de l'Ant\u00e9christ et de la vraie pers\u00e9cution chr\u00e9tienne. Merci mes enfants pour vos pri\u00e8res, car ils s\u00e8chent mes larmes. De nombreuses gr\u00e2ces descendreont aujourd'hui. Priez pour l'\u00e9glise et pour la Russie. Le grand serpent avancerai, mais moi, la conception immacul\u00e9e, je l'\u00e9craserai. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9, Amen.","text_it":"Figlia mia, grazie per avermi accolto nel tuo cuore. L\u2019umanit\u00e0 sta scendendo nell\u2019abisso, i miei figli hanno perso la ragione, molti sacerdoti confusi lasceranno le Chiese che si stanno gi\u00e0 svuotando di fedeli. Oh! figlia mia, tutto si sta svolgendo velocemente. Molti dovrebbero unirsi e combattere, non con le armi, ma con la preghiera, portando il gregge verso un solo Pastore che \u00e8 Ges\u00f9 Cristo. Chiedo ai governanti: andate per il mondo a portare la pace, altrimenti una grande guerra vi risucchier\u00e0. Ormai, si stanno preparando i tempi del Grande Monarca, che sta ultimando la sua preparazione per il suo ingresso, egli sar\u00e0 rivestito di Spirito Santo e porter\u00e0 la pace nel tempo dell\u2019anticristo e della vera persecuzione cristiana. Grazie figli miei per le vostre preghiere, perch\u00e9 asciugano le mie lacrime. Oggi scenderanno molte grazie.  Pregate per la Chiesa e per la Russia. Il grande serpente avanzer\u00e0, ma Io, l\u2019Immacolata Concezione, lo schiaccer\u00f2. Ora ti benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, amen.","text_pl":"Moja c\u00f3rko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce przyj\u0119\u0142a\u015b mnie do swojego serca. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 zst\u0119puje w otch\u0142a\u0144, Moje dzieci straci\u0142y rozum, wielu zdezorientowanych kap\u0142an\u00f3w odchodzi z Ko\u015bcio\u0142\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re ju\u017c pustoszej\u0105. Och! Moje dziecko, wszystko rozwija si\u0119 szybko. Wielu powinno si\u0119 zjednoczy\u0107 i walczy\u0107, nie broni\u0105, ale modlitw\u0105, prowadz\u0105c trzod\u0119 ku jednemu Pasterzowi, kt\u00f3rym jest Jezus Chrystus. Prosz\u0119 w\u0142adc\u00f3w: wyjd\u017acie na \u015bwiat, aby zaprowadzi\u0107 pok\u00f3j, inaczej poch\u0142onie was wielka wojna. Obecne czasy s\u0105 ju\u017c przygotowywane na przyj\u015bcie Wielkiego Monarchy; b\u0119dzie on przyobleczony Duchem \u015awi\u0119tym i przyniesie pok\u00f3j w czasach antychrysta i prze\u015bladowa\u0144 prawdziwych chrze\u015bcijan. Dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam moje dzieci za wasze modlitwy, bo one osuszaj\u0105 moje \u0142zy. Wiele \u0142ask zst\u0105pi dzisiaj. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 i za Rosj\u0119. Wielki w\u0105\u017c b\u0119dzie si\u0119 posuwa\u0142, ale Ja, Niepokalane Pocz\u0119cie, zmia\u017cd\u017c\u0119 go. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, Amen.","text_pt":"Minha filha, obrigado por me receber em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. A humanidade est\u00e1 descendo para o abismo, meus filhos perderam o motivo, muitos sacerdotes confusos deixar\u00e3o as igrejas que j\u00e1 est\u00e3o esvaziando os crentes. Oh! Meu filho, tudo est\u00e1 se desenrolando rapidamente. Muitos devem se unir e lutar, n\u00e3o com armas, mas com ora\u00e7\u00e3o, levando o rebanho a um pastor que \u00e9 Jesus Cristo. Pe\u00e7o aos governantes: percorre o mundo para trazer paz, caso contr\u00e1rio, uma grande guerra ir\u00e1 sugar voc\u00ea. A essa altura, est\u00e1 sendo preparado para o grande monarca, que est\u00e1 completando sua prepara\u00e7\u00e3o para sua entrada, ele estar\u00e1 vestido com o Esp\u00edrito Santo e trar\u00e1 paz no tempo do anticristo e da verdadeira persegui\u00e7\u00e3o crist\u00e3. Obrigado meus filhos por suas ora\u00e7\u00f5es, pois eles secam minhas l\u00e1grimas. Muitas gra\u00e7as v\u00e3o descer hoje. Ore pela igreja e pela R\u00fassia. A Grande Serpente avan\u00e7ar\u00e1, mas eu, a imaculada concep\u00e7\u00e3o, o esmagarei. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u6b22\u8fce\u6211\u8fdb\u5165\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u3002\u4eba\u7c7b\u6b63\u5728\u9677\u5165\u6df1\u6e0a\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u5931\u53bb\u4e86\u7406\u7531\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u56f0\u60d1\u7684\u7267\u5e08\u5c06\u79bb\u5f00\u5df2\u7ecf\u7a7a\u4e86\u4fe1\u5f92\u7684\u6559\u5802\u3002\u54e6\uff01\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u5728\u5feb\u901f\u53d1\u5c55\u3002\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u5e94\u8be5\u56e2\u7ed3\u548c\u6218\u6597\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7528\u6b66\u5668\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5c06\u7f8a\u7fa4\u5e26\u5230\u4e00\u4e2a\u662f\u8036\u7a23\u57fa\u7763\u7684\u7267\u7f8a\u4eba\u3002\u6211\u95ee\u7edf\u6cbb\u8005\uff1a\u73af\u6e38\u4e16\u754c\uff0c\u5e26\u6765\u548c\u5e73\uff0c\u5426\u5219\u4e00\u573a\u4f1f\u5927\u7684\u6218\u4e89\u4f1a\u5438\u5f15\u60a8\u3002\u5723\u7075\uff0c\u5c06\u5728\u654c\u57fa\u7763\u548c\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u57fa\u7763\u6559\u8feb\u5bb3\u65f6\u671f\u5e26\u6765\u548c\u5e73\u3002\u8c22\u8c22\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u7684\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u4eec\u5e72\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u773c\u6cea\u3002\u4eca\u5929\u8bb8\u591a\u6069\u5178\u5c06\u4e0b\u964d\u3002\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u548c\u4fc4\u7f57\u65af\u7948\u7977\u3002\u4f1f\u5927\u7684\u86c7\u4f1a\u524d\u8fdb\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u6211\u662f\u5b8c\u7f8e\u7684\u6982\u5ff5\uff0c\u4f1a\u7c89\u788e\u4ed6\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u6700\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":3,"month_string":"September","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. My little children, your faith moves me, for I know your difficulties, but when you pray and ask my Son Jesus, He brings providence down, and here you are on your knees praying with the Rosary in your hands. My children, this land will be purified by fire, but it will also be blessed by the water that will flow in Marian places for the healing of soul and body. My children, pray for Russia and pray that the nuclear power will not be touched. Pray for the Church that reigns in confusion. Today there is a person among you who wants to face the priesthood, you must say that Jesus needs holy priests. Jesus blesses these newlyweds. Today, many will be the graces that will descend upon you. Children, do not lose the way of the way, truth and life.  Now I bless you in the name of the Holy Trinity, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine kleinen Kinder, dein Glaube bewegt mich, denn ich kenne deine Schwierigkeiten, aber wenn du betst und meinen Sohn Jesus fragst, bringt er die Vorsehung nach unten, und hier bist du auf deinen Knien und bete mit dem Rosenkranz in deinen H\u00e4nden. Meine Kinder, dieses Land wird durch Feuer gereinigt, wird aber auch durch das Wasser gesegnet, das an marianischen Orten f\u00fcr die Heilung von Seele und K\u00f6rper flie\u00dft. Meine Kinder beten f\u00fcr Russland und beten, dass die Atomkraft nicht ber\u00fchrt wird. Bete f\u00fcr die Kirche, die verwirrt regiert. Heute gibt es eine Person unter Ihnen, die sich dem Priestertum stellen will, Sie m\u00fcssen sagen, dass Jesus heilige Priester braucht. Jesus segnet diese Jungverm\u00e4hlten. Heute werden viele die Gnaden sein, die auf Sie herabsteigen. Kinder, verlieren nicht den Weg des Weges, der Wahrheit und des Lebens. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen der Heiligen Dreifaltigkeit, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Ni\u00f1os, mis hijos, su fe me mueven, porque conozco sus dificultades, pero cuando ores y le preguntas a mi hijo Jes\u00fas, hace que la providencia descienda, y aqu\u00ed est\u00e1 de rodillas rezar con el rosario en sus manos. Mis hijos, esta tierra ser\u00e1 purificada con fuego, pero tambi\u00e9n ser\u00e1 bendecida por el agua que fluir\u00e1 en los lugares marianos para la curaci\u00f3n del alma y el cuerpo. Ni\u00f1os, rezan por Rusia y rezan para que la energ\u00eda nuclear no se toque. Ore por la iglesia que reine en confusi\u00f3n. Hoy hay una persona entre ustedes que quiere mirar el sacerdocio, debes decir que Jes\u00fas necesita santos sacerdotes. Jes\u00fas bendice a estos nuevos c\u00f3nyuges. Hoy, habr\u00e1 muchas gracias que te ir\u00e1n. Ni\u00f1os, no se pierdan el camino de la calle, la verdad y la vida. Ahora te bendiga en el nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes petits enfants, votre foi m'\u00e9value, car je connais vos difficult\u00e9s, mais quand vous priez et demandez \u00e0 mon fils J\u00e9sus, il fait tomber Providence, et vous \u00eates \u00e0 genoux en priant avec le chapelet dans vos mains. Mes enfants, cette terre sera purifi\u00e9e par le feu, mais elle sera \u00e9galement b\u00e9nie par l'eau qui coulera dans des endroits mariens pour la gu\u00e9rison de l'\u00e2me et du corps. Mes enfants, prient pour la Russie et prient pour que l'\u00e9nergie nucl\u00e9aire ne soit pas touch\u00e9e. Priez pour l'\u00e9glise qui r\u00e8gne dans la confusion. Aujourd'hui, il y a une personne parmi vous qui veut faire face \u00e0 la pr\u00eatrise, vous devez dire que J\u00e9sus a besoin de saints pr\u00eatres. J\u00e9sus b\u00e9nit ces jeunes mari\u00e9s. Aujourd'hui, beaucoup seront les gr\u00e2ces qui vous descendront sur vous. Enfants, ne perdez pas la voie de la voie, de la v\u00e9rit\u00e9 et de la vie. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom de la Sainte Trinit\u00e9, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, piccoli bambini miei, la vostra fede mi commuove, perch\u00e9 conosco le vostre difficolt\u00e0, ma quando pregate e chiedete a mio Figlio Ges\u00f9, Lui fa scendere la provvidenza, ed eccovi qui in ginocchio a pregare con il Rosario tra le mani. Figli miei, questa terra sar\u00e0 purificata con il fuoco, ma sar\u00e0 anche benedetta dall\u2019acqua che sgorgher\u00e0 nei luoghi Mariani per la guarigione dell\u2019anima e del corpo. Figli, pregate per la Russia e pregate affinch\u00e9 non venga toccato il nucleare. Pregate per la Chiesa che regna nella confusione. Oggi tra voi c\u2019\u00e8 una persona che vuole affacciarsi al sacerdozio, devi dire che Ges\u00f9 ha bisogno di Santi sacerdoti. Ges\u00f9 benedice questi nuovi sposi. Oggi, tante saranno le grazie che scenderanno su di voi. Figli, non perdete la strada della via, verit\u00e0 e vita.  Ora vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje ma\u0142e dzieci, wasza wiara porusza mnie, bo znam wasze trudno\u015bci, ale kiedy modlicie si\u0119 i prosicie mojego Syna Jezusa, On sprowadza opatrzno\u015b\u0107 i oto jeste\u015bcie na kolanach, modl\u0105c si\u0119 z R\u00f3\u017ca\u0144cem w r\u0119kach. Moje dzieci, ta ziemia b\u0119dzie oczyszczona przez ogie\u0144, ale b\u0119dzie te\u017c b\u0142ogos\u0142awiona przez wod\u0119, kt\u00f3ra pop\u0142ynie z miejsc maryjnych dla uzdrowienia duszy i cia\u0142a. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Rosj\u0119 i o to, by nie zosta\u0142a u\u017cyta si\u0142a atomowa. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, kt\u00f3ry przoduje w zam\u0119cie. Dzisiaj jest w\u015br\u00f3d was osoba, kt\u00f3ra chce wej\u015b\u0107 do kap\u0142a\u0144stwa, trzeba powiedzie\u0107, \u017ce Jezus potrzebuje \u015bwi\u0119tych kap\u0142an\u00f3w. Jezus b\u0142ogos\u0142awi tym nowym ma\u0142\u017conkom. Dzi\u015b wiele \u0142ask zst\u0105pi na Ciebie. Moje dzieci, nie zgubcie drogi do prawdy i \u017cycia. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos pequenos, sua f\u00e9 me move, pois conhe\u00e7o suas dificuldades, mas quando voc\u00ea ora e pergunta ao meu filho Jesus, ele derruba a Provid\u00eancia, e aqui est\u00e1 voc\u00ea de joelhos orando com o ros\u00e1rio em suas m\u00e3os. Meus filhos, esta terra ser\u00e1 purificada pelo fogo, mas tamb\u00e9m ser\u00e1 aben\u00e7oada pela \u00e1gua que fluir\u00e1 em lugares marianos para a cura da alma e do corpo. Meus filhos, oram pela R\u00fassia e orem para que a energia nuclear n\u00e3o seja tocada. Ore pela igreja que reina em confus\u00e3o. Hoje h\u00e1 uma pessoa entre voc\u00eas que quer enfrentar o sacerd\u00f3cio, voc\u00ea deve dizer que Jesus precisa de santos sacerdotes. Jesus aben\u00e7oa esses rec\u00e9m -casados. Hoje, muitos ser\u00e3o as gra\u00e7as que descer\u00e3o sobre voc\u00ea. Crian\u00e7as, n\u00e3o perdem o caminho do caminho, verdade e vida. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5c0f\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4f60\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u4f7f\u6211\u611f\u52a8\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u77e5\u9053\u4f60\u7684\u56f0\u96be\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u5f53\u4f60\u7948\u7977\u5e76\u95ee\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u65f6\uff0c\u4ed6\u628a\u666e\u7f57\u7ef4\u767b\u65af\u5012\u4e0b\u4e86\uff0c\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\uff0c\u4f60\u8dea\u5728\u819d\u76d6\u4e0a\uff0c\u7528\u5ff5\u73e0\u7948\u7977\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8fd9\u7247\u571f\u5730\u5c06\u88ab\u706b\u51c0\u5316\uff0c\u4f46\u4e5f\u5c06\u7531\u739b\u4e3d\u5b89\uff08Marian\uff09\u5728\u7075\u9b42\u548c\u8eab\u4f53\u6cbb\u6108\u7684\u5730\u65b9\u6d41\u6dcc\u7684\u6c34\u6765\u795d\u798f\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e3a\u4fc4\u7f57\u65af\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5e76\u7948\u7977\u4e0d\u4f1a\u611f\u52a8\u6838\u7535\u3002\u4e3a\u7edf\u6cbb\u6df7\u4e71\u7684\u6559\u4f1a\u7948\u7977\u3002\u4eca\u5929\uff0c\u4f60\u4eec\u5f53\u4e2d\u6709\u4e00\u4e2a\u60f3\u9762\u5bf9\u795e\u804c\u4eba\u5458\u7684\u4eba\uff0c\u60a8\u5fc5\u987b\u8bf4\u8036\u7a23\u9700\u8981\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u795e\u7236\u3002\u8036\u7a23\u795d\u798f\u8fd9\u4e9b\u65b0\u5a5a\u592b\u5987\u3002\u4eca\u5929\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u5c06\u6210\u4e3a\u60a8\u4e0b\u964d\u7684\u6069\u5178\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5931\u53bb\u9053\u8def\uff0c\u771f\u7406\u548c\u751f\u6d3b\u7684\u65b9\u5f0f\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u5723\u4e09\u4e00\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u4eec\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":4,"month_string":"September","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of our King, my faithfulness and my love for God led me to unite the angels to defend the Paternal Throne from the pride of Lucifer, who rose up against God together with other angels. It was a war in heaven against the devil and Lucifer had already lost his beauty by filling himself with pride and envy. Do not rest day or night because the devil does not rest. The struggle between good and evil is constant. At this moment we fight for the salvation of souls against the devil, who wants to take them to the lake of fire. The children of our Lord and King Jesus Christ cannot be passive, but combative, if necessary, against themselves, so that they do not fall into pride and sin. The pride of the devil caused him to be expelled from heaven together with his angels of wickedness and they were sent to earth. The devil has a motto: all for me, I live for me above all and everything. Therefore, I call you, people of God, to give everything for God, to live for God, loving god and your neighbour. Humanity is heading towards the abyss.... Humanity is heading towards confrontation.... Humanity is heading towards spiritual and physical starvation... humanity is heading towards the collapse of the economy... humanity is going towards the appropriation of the antichrist on those who receive him as owner of the earth and place his mark on themselves. Without believing what I mention to you, you laugh at the messages from heaven, yet prepare yourselves before you mourn. Confess your sins before darkness finds you in a state of sin. Great injustices will be carried out before your eyes and you will feel powerless, but Divine Justice is with the people of God and upon the people of God. Resist, you are not alone. People of God pray, do not tire of praying with your hearts. People of God pray and make reparation for the grave offenses of humanity against the Holy Trinity. People of God pray, the earth trembles with more strength: pray for Puerto Rico, Dominican Republic, Central America, Ecuador and Japan. People of God pray, the new plague arrives: the skin and respiratory system will be affected. The sun strongly impacts the earth with a solar storm, leaving the earth in darkness and humanity is silenced, and at the same time shaken. The human creature will light itself at nightfall with what it has prepared for this purpose. At night do not leave home, pray in family or alone, but pray. You are as in the time of Noah... You believe and prepare yourselves, even if you mock. You are already at that time! The earth is spinning, human time has accelerated and you, people of God, must stop and examine yourselves. I meet with my heavenly legions by Divine mandate to assist you in this time of transition. Have faith in the Holy Trinity, in our Queen and Mother and in our protection. You find yourselves before the Divine Help deserved by the obedient child, the child of faith and the humble child. The sacramentals must be blessed, it is necessary if they possess faith in them. My legions obey the Divine Will that desires good for his children. I bless them. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la, moja wierno\u015b\u0107 i mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do Boga sk\u0142oni\u0142y mnie do zjednoczenia anio\u0142\u00f3w w celu obrony Ojcowskiego Tronu przed pych\u0105 Lucyfera, kt\u00f3ry wraz z innymi anio\u0142ami powsta\u0142 przeciwko Bogu. By\u0142a to wojna w niebie przeciwko diab\u0142u, a Lucyfer ju\u017c straci\u0142 swoje pi\u0119kno, nape\u0142niaj\u0105c si\u0119 pych\u0105 i zazdro\u015bci\u0105. Nie odpoczywajcie we dnie i w nocy, bo diabe\u0142 nie odpoczywa. Walka mi\u0119dzy dobrem a z\u0142em jest nieustanna. W tej chwili walczymy o zbawienie dusz z diab\u0142em, kt\u00f3ry chce je zabra\u0107 do jeziora ognia. Dzieci naszego Pana i Kr\u00f3la Jezusa Chrystusa nie mog\u0105 by\u0107 bierne, ale bojowo nastawione, je\u015bli trzeba, to przeciwko sobie, aby nie popad\u0142y w pych\u0119 i grzech. Pycha diab\u0142a spowodowa\u0142a, \u017ce wraz ze swoimi anio\u0142ami niegodziwo\u015bci zosta\u0142 wyrzucony z nieba i zostali oni zes\u0142ani na ziemi\u0119. Diabe\u0142 ma motto: wszystko dla mnie, \u017cyj\u0119 dla siebie ponad wszystko i wszystkich. Dlatego wzywam was, ludu Bo\u017cy, aby\u015bcie wszystko oddali dla Boga, aby\u015bcie \u017cyli dla Boga, kochaj\u0105c Boga i bli\u017aniego. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 zmierza ku przepa\u015bci.... Ludzko\u015b\u0107 zmierza w kierunku konfrontacji.... Ludzko\u015b\u0107 zmierza w kierunku duchowego i fizycznego g\u0142odu... ludzko\u015b\u0107 zmierza w kierunku upadku gospodarki... ludzko\u015b\u0107 zmierza w kierunku zaw\u0142aszczenia antychrysta na tych, kt\u00f3rzy przyjm\u0105 go jako w\u0142a\u015bciciela ziemi i umieszcz\u0105 na sobie jego znak. Nie wierz\u0105c w to, o czym wam wspominam, \u015bmiejecie si\u0119 z wiadomo\u015bci z nieba, a jednak przygotujcie si\u0119, zanim b\u0119dziecie si\u0119 smuci\u0107. Wyznajcie swoje grzechy, zanim ciemno\u015b\u0107 znajdzie was w stanie grzechu. Wielkie niesprawiedliwo\u015bci b\u0119d\u0105 dokonywane na waszych oczach i b\u0119dziecie czu\u0107 si\u0119 bezsilni, lecz Boska Sprawiedliwo\u015b\u0107 jest z ludem Bo\u017cym i na ludzie Bo\u017cym. Opierajcie si\u0119, nie jeste\u015bcie sami. Ludu Bo\u017cy m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, nie m\u0119czcie si\u0119, modl\u0105c si\u0119 sercem. Ludu Bo\u017cy m\u00f3dl si\u0119 i czy\u0144 zado\u015b\u0107 za ci\u0119\u017ckie przewinienia ludzko\u015bci wobec Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej. Ludu Bo\u017cy m\u00f3dl si\u0119, ziemia dr\u017cy z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 si\u0142\u0105: m\u00f3dl si\u0119 za Puerto Rico, Dominikan\u0119, Ameryk\u0119 \u015arodkow\u0105, Ekwador i Japoni\u0119. Ludu Bo\u017cy m\u00f3dl si\u0119, nadchodzi nowa plaga: dotknie sk\u00f3r\u0119 i uk\u0142ad oddechowy. S\u0142o\u0144ce silnie uderza w ziemi\u0119 burz\u0105 s\u0142oneczn\u0105, pozostawiaj\u0105c ziemi\u0119 w ciemno\u015bci, a ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest uciszona, a jednocze\u015bnie wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119ta. Ludzkie stworzenie o\u015bwietli si\u0119 o zmroku tym, co przygotowa\u0142o w tym celu. W nocy nie wychod\u017acie z domu, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 w rodzinie lub samotnie, ale m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. Jeste\u015bcie jak w czasach Noego... Wierzycie i przygotowujecie si\u0119, nawet je\u015bli szydzicie. Jeste\u015bcie ju\u017c w tym czasie! Ziemia si\u0119 kr\u0119ci, czas ludzki przyspieszy\u0142 i wy, ludu Bo\u017cy, musicie si\u0119 zatrzyma\u0107 i zbada\u0107 siebie. Spotykam si\u0119 z moimi niebia\u0144skimi legionami przez Boskie upowa\u017cnienie, aby pom\u00f3c wam w tym czasie przej\u015bcia. Miejcie wiar\u0119 w Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 \u015awi\u0119t\u0105, w nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119 i w nasz\u0105 ochron\u0119. Znajdujecie si\u0119 przed Bosk\u0105 pomoc\u0105, na kt\u00f3r\u0105 zas\u0142uguje pos\u0142uszne dziecko, dziecko wiary i dziecko pokorne. Sakramentalia musz\u0105 by\u0107 pob\u0142ogos\u0142awione, jest to konieczne, je\u015bli posiadaj\u0105 wiar\u0119 w nie. Moje legiony s\u0105 pos\u0142uszne Woli Bo\u017cej, kt\u00f3ra pragnie dobra dla swoich dzieci. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 je. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":6,"month_string":"September","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for answering my call in your heart, where are my other children! Pray and fast, the world is the shell of so many sins starting with abortion, pride, haughtiness, no respect for one's body - temple of the Holy Spirit, unbridled lust, war, conflicts and materialism. The rulers are caught up in evil, the priests no longer have respect for my Son Jesus. You are caught up in the things of the world and do not care for your soul. I touch the earth to warn you, the Wrath of God will be great, particularly for Italy and Rome, the See of Peter. My children, I am here and I extend My arms waiting for the repentance and conversion of these children, to whom all would be forgiven if they would return to God. Beloved children, I now bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass du meinen Anruf in deinem Herzen beantwortet hast, wo sind meine anderen Kinder! Beten und schnell, die Welt ist die H\u00fclle so vieler S\u00fcnden, beginnt mit Abtreibung, Stolz, Hochmut, ohne Respekt vor dem eigenen K\u00f6rper - Tempel des Heiligen Geistes, ungez\u00fcgelte Lust, Krieg, Konflikte und Materialismus. Die Herrscher sind in das B\u00f6se gefangen, die Priester haben keinen Respekt vor meinem Sohn Jesus. Sie sind in die Dinge der Welt gefangen und k\u00fcmmern sich nicht um Ihre Seele. Ich ber\u00fchre die Erde, um dich zu warnen, der Zorn Gottes wird gro\u00dfartig sein, besonders f\u00fcr Italien und Rom, das See von Peter. Meine Kinder, ich bin hier und ich strecke meine Arme aus und warte auf die Umkehr und Bekehrung dieser Kinder, denen alle vergeben werden w\u00fcrden, wenn sie zu Gott zur\u00fcckkehren w\u00fcrden. Geliebte Kinder, ich segne dich jetzt im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n, \u00a1d\u00f3nde est\u00e1n mis otros hijos! Ore y r\u00e1pido, el mundo es el sobre de muchos pecados que comienzan por el aborto, el orgullo, el orgullo, sin respeto por el cuerpo, el Templo del Esp\u00edritu Santo, la libido desenfrenada, la guerra, los conflictos y el materialismo. Los gobernantes son tomados por el mal, los sacerdotes ya no tienen respeto por mi hijo Jes\u00fas. Te toman las cosas del mundo y no te importa tu alma. Toco la tierra para advertirte, la ira de Dios ser\u00e1 grande, particularmente para Italia y Roma, la sede de Pedro. Mis hijos, estoy aqu\u00ed y ensancho mis brazos esperando el arrepentimiento y la conversi\u00f3n de estos hijos, a quienes todo habr\u00eda sido perdonado si regresaran a Dios. Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur, o\u00f9 sont mes autres enfants! Priez et vite, le monde est la coquille de tant de p\u00e9ch\u00e9s en commen\u00e7ant par l'avortement, la fiert\u00e9, la hauteur, aucun respect pour son corps - le temple du Saint-Esprit, la luxure effr\u00e9n\u00e9e, la guerre, les conflits et le mat\u00e9rialisme. Les dirigeants sont pris dans le mal, les pr\u00eatres n'ont plus de respect pour mon fils J\u00e9sus. Vous \u00eates pris dans les choses du monde et ne vous souciez pas de votre \u00e2me. Je touche la terre pour vous avertir, la col\u00e8re de Dieu sera grande, en particulier pour l'Italie et Rome, le si\u00e8ge de Pierre. Mes enfants, je suis ici et je prolonge mes bras en attendant le repentir et la conversion de ces enfants, \u00e0 qui tous seraient pardonn\u00e9 s'ils retournaient \u00e0 Dieu. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, je vous b\u00e9nis maintenant au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore, dove sono gli altri miei figli! Pregate e digiunate, il mondo \u00e8 l\u2019involucro di tanti peccati iniziando dall\u2019aborto, l\u2019orgoglio, la superbia, nessun rispetto per il proprio corpo, tempio dello Spirito Santo, libidine sfrenata, guerra, conflitti e materialismo. I governanti sono presi dal male, i sacerdoti non hanno pi\u00f9 rispetto per mio Figlio Ges\u00f9. Siete presi dalle cose del mondo e non vi curate della vostra anima. Io tocco la terra per avvertirvi, l\u2019ira di Dio sar\u00e0 grande, particolarmente per l\u2019Italia e Roma, sede di Pietro. Figli miei, Io sono qui e allargo le mie braccia in attesa del pentimento e la conversione di questi figli, ai quali sarebbe perdonato tutto se tornassero a Dio. Figli adorati, ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam za odpowied\u017a na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach, gdzie s\u0105 moje inne dzieci! M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 i po\u015b\u0107cie, \u015bwiat jest otoczony skorup\u0105 wielu grzech\u00f3w pocz\u0105wszy od aborcji, pychy, braku szacunku dla w\u0142asnego cia\u0142a - \u015bwi\u0105tyni Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, niepohamowanej \u017c\u0105dzy, wojny, konflikt\u00f3w i materializmu. W\u0142adcy uwik\u0142ani s\u0105 w z\u0142o, kap\u0142ani nie maj\u0105 ju\u017c szacunku dla Mojego Syna Jezusa. Jeste\u015bcie poch\u0142oni\u0119ci sprawami tego \u015bwiata i nie dbacie o swoje dusze. Przychodz\u0119 na ziemi\u0119, aby was ostrzec, gniew Boga b\u0119dzie wielki, szczeg\u00f3lnie dla W\u0142och i Rzymu - Stolicy Piotrowej. Moje dzieci, jestem tu i wyci\u0105gam r\u0119ce oczekuj\u0105c skruchy i nawr\u00f3cenia tych dzieci, kt\u00f3rym wszystko by\u0142oby wybaczone, gdyby powr\u00f3ci\u0142y do Boga. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was teraz w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por atender minha chamada em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o, onde est\u00e3o meus outros filhos! Ore e r\u00e1pido, o mundo \u00e9 a concha de tantos pecados que come\u00e7am com aborto, orgulho, arrog\u00e2ncia, sem respeito pelo corpo de algu\u00e9m - Templo do Esp\u00edrito Santo, lux\u00faria desenfreada, guerra, conflitos e materialismo. Os governantes est\u00e3o envolvidos no mal, os sacerdotes n\u00e3o t\u00eam mais respeito pelo meu filho Jesus. Voc\u00ea est\u00e1 pego nas coisas do mundo e n\u00e3o se importa com sua alma. Eu toco a terra para avis\u00e1 -lo, a ira de Deus ser\u00e1 grande, principalmente para a It\u00e1lia e Roma, a S\u00e9 de Pedro. Meus filhos, estou aqui e estendo meus bra\u00e7os esperando o arrependimento e a convers\u00e3o dessas crian\u00e7as, a quem todos seriam perdoados se retornassem a Deus. Filhos Amados, agora o aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u63a5\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5176\u4ed6\u5b69\u5b50\u5728\u54ea\u91cc\uff01\u7948\u7977\u548c\u8fc5\u901f\uff0c\u4e16\u754c\u662f\u8bb8\u591a\u7f6a\u6076\u7684\u5916\u58f3\uff0c\u4ece\u5815\u80ce\uff0c\u9a84\u50b2\uff0c\u50b2\u6162\uff0c\u4e0d\u5c0a\u91cd\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u8eab\u4f53 - \u5723\u7075\u7684\u5723\u6bbf\uff0c\u65e0\u9650\u7684\u6b32\u671b\uff0c\u6218\u4e89\uff0c\u51b2\u7a81\u548c\u552f\u7269\u4e3b\u4e49\u3002\u7edf\u6cbb\u8005\u9677\u5165\u4e86\u90aa\u6076\u4e4b\u4e2d\uff0c\u796d\u53f8\u4e0d\u518d\u5c0a\u91cd\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u3002\u60a8\u88ab\u4e16\u754c\u7684\u4e8b\u7269\u6240\u56f0\u6270\uff0c\u4e0d\u5173\u5fc3\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u7075\u9b42\u3002\u6211\u89e6\u6478\u5730\u7403\u8b66\u544a\u4f60\uff0c\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u6124\u6012\u5c06\u662f\u4f1f\u5927\u7684\uff0c\u5c24\u5176\u662f\u5bf9\u4e8e\u610f\u5927\u5229\u548c\u7f57\u9a6c\uff0c\u5f7c\u5f97\u7684\u89c1\u9762\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\uff0c\u6211\u4f38\u51fa\u80f3\u818a\uff0c\u7b49\u5f85\u7740\u8fd9\u4e9b\u5b69\u5b50\u7684\u6094\u6539\u548cconversion\u4f9d\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u4ed6\u4eec\u56de\u5230\u4e0a\u5e1d\u8eab\u4e0a\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u90fd\u4f1a\u88ab\u539f\u8c05\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u73b0\u5728\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":9,"month_string":"September","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children: I keep you hidden in every beat of my heart. Receive my blessings together with my constant assistance for the needs of each one of you and what you face on your daily walk. You are the people whom I received at the foot of the Cross of Glory and Majesty. Some of those children have gone and are going away from this people whom my Son gave me: they live in debauchery and have joined the hordes of the devil. My Divine Son suffers because of this and I call them to conversion. Children: The elite are gaining in strength! The changes will not be long in coming; they are spreading throughout humanity and are not for the good of my children, nor for the good of their spiritual lives. Children: I call you to remain on alert! Stay within the true magisterium so that you would not stray from my Son. Do not stray from the commandments, and be children who observe god\u2019s law. My children: Remain on alert! Remain on alert in every respect, for there are several centres of armed conflict on earth, which will go from words to deeds. Humanity is living in danger due to modern armaments and arms unknown to humanity. Remain on alert! Look up: a heavenly body is approaching. Pray, my children, pray for China and Taiwan. Pray, my children, pray for Russia and Ukraine; pray, children - it is necessary. Pray, my children, pray for the United States: nature will make her suffer before men do. Pray, my children, pray for Argentina, communism has entered into this nation. My Son's people are not aware that with conversion and prayer great battles are won. The mediocre faith of some of my children prevents them from opening their hearts to my Son. At this moment I find people who are true refuges of consolation for my Son in the face of the sacrileges, offenses and acts of contempt committed against my Son. My children: Are you looking for refuges? Do you want to reach a physical refuge for the most crucial times? Firstly be refuges where my Son rests and finds contentment at this time and in times to come. Be love. Be doers of God's will. I love you and protect you. Do not fear, children, do not fear. I am with each one of you. I bless you. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci: Trzymam was w ukryciu w ka\u017cdym uderzeniu mojego serca. Przyjmijcie moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo wraz z moj\u0105 nieustann\u0105 pomoc\u0105 w potrzebach ka\u017cdego z was i w tym, co napotykacie na swojej codziennej drodze. Jeste\u015bcie ludem, kt\u00f3ry przyj\u0105\u0142em u st\u00f3p Krzy\u017ca Chwa\u0142y i Majestatu. Niekt\u00f3re z tych dzieci odesz\u0142y i odchodz\u0105 od tego ludu, kt\u00f3ry da\u0142 mi m\u00f3j Syn: \u017cyj\u0105 w rozpu\u015bcie i przy\u0142\u0105czy\u0142y si\u0119 do hord diab\u0142a. M\u00f3j Boski Syn cierpi z tego powodu i wzywam ich do nawr\u00f3cenia. Dzieci: Elity zyskuj\u0105 na sile! Zmiany nie nadejd\u0105 d\u0142ugo; rozprzestrzeniaj\u0105 si\u0119 po ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci i nie s\u0142u\u017c\u0105 dobru moich dzieci ani ich \u017cyciu duchowemu. Dzieci: Wzywam was do zachowania czujno\u015bci! Pozosta\u0144cie w obr\u0119bie prawdziwego magisterium, aby\u015bcie nie zb\u0142\u0105dzili od mojego Syna. Nie zbaczajcie z przykaza\u0144 i b\u0105d\u017acie dzie\u0107mi, kt\u00f3re przestrzegaj\u0105 prawa Bo\u017cego. Moje dzieci: Pozosta\u0144cie czujni! B\u0105d\u017acie czujni pod ka\u017cdym wzgl\u0119dem, bo na ziemi jest kilka o\u015brodk\u00f3w konfliktu zbrojnego, kt\u00f3ry przejdzie od s\u0142\u00f3w do czyn\u00f3w. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 \u017cyje w niebezpiecze\u0144stwie z powodu nowoczesnych zbroje\u0144 i broni nieznanych ludzko\u015bci. B\u0105d\u017acie czujni! Patrzcie w g\u00f3r\u0119: zbli\u017ca si\u0119 cia\u0142o niebieskie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Chiny i Tajwan. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Rosj\u0119 i Ukrain\u0119; m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci - to jest konieczne. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Stany Zjednoczone: natura sprawi, \u017ce b\u0119dzie cierpia\u0142a, zanim zrobi\u0105 to ludzie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Argentyn\u0119, komunizm wszed\u0142 do tego narodu. Lud mojego Syna nie jest \u015bwiadomy, \u017ce nawr\u00f3ceniem i modlitw\u0105 wygrywa si\u0119 wielkie bitwy. Mierna wiara niekt\u00f3rych moich dzieci uniemo\u017cliwia im otwarcie serca na mojego Syna. W tej chwili znajduj\u0119 ludzi, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0105 prawdziwymi ostojami pociechy dla mojego Syna w obliczu \u015bwi\u0119tokradztw, wykrocze\u0144 i akt\u00f3w pogardy pope\u0142nianych wobec mojego Syna. Moje dzieci: Czy szukacie ostoi? Czy chcecie osi\u0105gn\u0105\u0107 fizyczne schronienie na najbardziej kluczowe chwile? Najpierw b\u0105d\u017acie ostojami, w kt\u00f3rych m\u00f3j Syn odpoczywa i znajduje zadowolenie w tym czasie i w czasach przysz\u0142ych. B\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. B\u0105d\u017acie wykonawcami woli Bo\u017cej. Ja was kocham i chroni\u0119. Nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, dzieci, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119. Jestem z ka\u017cdym z was. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. ","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":12,"month_string":"September","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My daughter, thank you for accepting me in prayer. Now the time of battle has come, you have given birth to a godless humanity, you have allowed an idol to enter the Church instead of God and worshipped Him in His place. My children, be united in the true doctrine of the faith without losing heart, open your hearts to the Holy Spirit, be constant and be warriors. This, for you will cause marginalization and persecution, but do not be afraid, my Son will intervene. I am near you every day and will preserve you from the scourges. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Tochter, danke, dass du mich im Gebet angenommen hast. Jetzt ist die Zeit des Kampfes gekommen, Sie haben eine gottlose Menschheit zur Welt gebracht, Sie haben ein Idol erlaubt, die Kirche anstelle von Gott zu betreten und ihn an seiner Stelle anzubeten. Meine Kinder, werden in der wahren Lehre des Glaubens vereint, ohne das Herz zu verlieren, \u00f6ffnen Sie Ihren Herzen f\u00fcr den Heiligen Geist, seien Sie konstant und Krieger. Dies, denn Sie werden Marginalisierung und Verfolgung verursachen, aber ich habe keine Angst, mein Sohn wird eingreifen. Ich bin jeden Tag in Ihrer N\u00e4he und werde Sie vor den Gei\u00dfeln bewahren. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes Amen.","text_es":"Mi hija, gracias por darme la bienvenida en oraci\u00f3n. En este momento han llegado los tiempos de la batalla, has dado lugar a una humanidad sin Dios, permitiste la entrada de un \u00eddolo en el lugar de Dios en la iglesia y lo amaste en su lugar. Mis hijos, se unan en la verdadera doctrina de la fe sin perderse, abre sus corazones al Esp\u00edritu Santo, sean constantes y sean guerreros. Esto, para usted ser\u00e1 la causa de la marginaci\u00f3n y la persecuci\u00f3n, pero no tenga miedo, mi hijo intervenir\u00e1. Estoy cerca de ti todos los d\u00edas y te conservar\u00e9 de los Flagelli. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Ma fille, merci de m'avoir accept\u00e9 dans la pri\u00e8re. Maintenant que le temps de la bataille est venu, vous avez donn\u00e9 naissance \u00e0 une humanit\u00e9 impie, vous avez permis \u00e0 une idole d'entrer dans l'\u00c9glise au lieu de Dieu et de l'adorer \u00e0 sa place. Mes enfants, soyez unis dans la vraie doctrine de la foi sans perdre le c\u0153ur, ouvrez votre c\u0153ur au Saint-Esprit, soyez constant et soyez des guerriers. Ceci, car vous provoquera une marginalisation et une pers\u00e9cution, mais n'ayez pas peur, mon fils interviendra. Je suis pr\u00e8s de chez vous tous les jours et vous pr\u00e9serverai des fl\u00e9aux. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figlia mia, grazie per avermi accolta nella preghiera. Ormai sono giunti i tempi della battaglia, avete dato vita ad un\u2019umanit\u00e0 senza Dio, avete permesso l\u2019ingresso di un idolo al posto di Dio nella Chiesa e lo avete adorato al Suo posto. Figli miei, siate uniti nella vera dottrina della fede senza perdersi d\u2019animo, aprite i vostri cuori allo Spirito Santo, siate costanti e siate guerrieri. Questo, per voi sar\u00e0 causa di emarginazione e persecuzione, ma non abbiate paura, mio Figlio interverr\u00e0. Io vi sono vicina tutti i giorni e vi preserver\u00f2 dai flagelli. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moje dziecko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce przyj\u0119\u0142a\u015b mnie na modlitwie. Teraz nadszed\u0142 czas walki, zrodzili\u015bcie bezbo\u017cn\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107, dopu\u015bcili\u015bcie do Ko\u015bcio\u0142a bo\u017cka w miejsce Boga i oddali\u015bcie mu cze\u015b\u0107 w Jego miejsce. Moje dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie zjednoczeni w prawdziwej doktrynie wiary, nie trac\u0105c serca, otw\u00f3rzcie wasze serca na Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, b\u0105d\u017acie stali i wojowniczy. B\u0119dzie to dla was przyczyn\u0105 marginalizacji i prze\u015bladowa\u0144, ale nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, m\u00f3j Syn b\u0119dzie interweniowa\u0142. Jestem blisko was ka\u017cdego dnia i zachowam was od plag. A teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Minha filha, obrigado por me aceitar em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Agora que chegou o momento da batalha, voc\u00ea deu \u00e0 luz uma humanidade sem Deus, permitiu que um \u00eddolo entrasse na igreja em vez de Deus e o adorou em seu lugar. Meus filhos, unidos na verdadeira doutrina da f\u00e9 sem perder o cora\u00e7\u00e3o, abrem seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es para o Esp\u00edrito Santo, sejam constantes e sejam guerreiros. Isso, pois voc\u00ea causar\u00e1 marginaliza\u00e7\u00e3o e persegui\u00e7\u00e3o, mas n\u00e3o tem medo, meu filho intervir\u00e1. Estou perto de voc\u00ea todos os dias e vou preserv\u00e1 -lo dos flagelos. Agora deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u63a5\u53d7\u6211\u7684\u7948\u7977\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6218\u6597\u7684\u65f6\u95f4\u5df2\u7ecf\u5230\u6765\uff0c\u60a8\u5df2\u7ecf\u8bde\u751f\u4e86\u65e0\u795e\u7684\u4eba\u7c7b\uff0c\u60a8\u5141\u8bb8\u5076\u50cf\u8fdb\u5165\u6559\u4f1a\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u4e0a\u5e1d\uff0c\u5e76\u7528\u4ed6\u7684\u4ee3\u7406\u656c\u62dc\u4ed6\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5728\u4fe1\u4ef0\u7684\u771f\u5b9e\u6559\u4e49\u4e2d\u56e2\u7ed3\u8d77\u6765\u800c\u4e0d\u4f1a\u5931\u53bb\u5fc3\uff0c\u5411\u5723\u7075\u655e\u5f00\u5fc3hearts\uff0c\u4fdd\u6301\u6052\u5b9a\u5e76\u6210\u4e3a\u6218\u58eb\u3002\u8fd9\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u60a8\u4f1a\u9020\u6210\u8fb9\u7f18\u5316\u548c\u8feb\u5bb3\uff0c\u4f46\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u6211\u513f\u5b50\u4f1a\u5e72\u9884\u3002\u6211\u6bcf\u5929\u90fd\u5728\u60a8\u9644\u8fd1\uff0c\u5e76\u5c06\u60a8\u514d\u53d7\u7978\u5bb3\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7ed9\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":13,"month_string":"September","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My children and brothers, thank you for being here and for bending your knees under My cross. My children, I touch this blessed hill and this land so that graces may be many. My brothers, I look at you every day and how happy I am when I see many of you avoiding sin and when you have your eyes turned toward the light. Listen to what my and your Blessed Mother says, do not fear for the times of sorrow that await you because when you come here, you can rejoice in pure happiness, everything is ready. Now I bless you, in the name of the Father, in My name and the Holy Spirit. I will be with you throughout the prayer, raise your rosaries and approach the foot of the Cross and I will bless them. Your dear Jesus.","text_de":"Meine Kinder und Br\u00fcder, danke, dass Sie hier sind und sich die Knie unter meinem Kreuz beugen. Meine Kinder, ich ber\u00fchre diesen gesegneten H\u00fcgel und dieses Land, damit Gnaden viele sein k\u00f6nnen. Meine Br\u00fcder, ich sehe dich jeden Tag an und wie gl\u00fccklich ich bin, wenn ich sehe, dass viele von Ihnen die S\u00fcnde vermeiden und wenn Sie Ihre Augen zum Licht zugewandt haben. H\u00f6ren Sie, was meine und Ihre gesegnete Mutter sagt, f\u00fcr die Zeit der Trauer, die Sie erwarten, nicht f\u00fcrchten, denn wenn Sie hierher kommen, k\u00f6nnen Sie sich \u00fcber das reine Gl\u00fcck freuen, alles ist fertig. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters in meinem Namen und dem Heiligen Geist. Ich werde w\u00e4hrend des gesamten Gebets bei Ihnen sein, Ihre Rosenkr\u00e4nze erh\u00f6hen und sich dem Fu\u00df des Kreuzes n\u00e4hern, und ich werde sie segnen. Dein lieber Jesus.","text_es":"Mis hijos y hermanos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed y por haber doblado las rodillas debajo de mi cruz. Mis hijos, toco esta bendita colina y esta tierra, para que las gracias sean muchas. Mis hermanos, te miro todos los d\u00edas y lo feliz que estoy, cuando veo a muchos de ustedes que evitan el pecado y cuando miran hacia la luz. Escuche lo que dice mi y la santa madre, no teman por los tiempos de dolor que le esperan porque cuando vienes aqu\u00ed, puedes regocijarte en pura felicidad, todo est\u00e1 listo. Ahora te bendiga, en el nombre del Padre, en mi nombre y el Esp\u00edritu Santo. Estar\u00e9 contigo durante toda la oraci\u00f3n, levantar\u00e9 tus rosarios y me acertar\u00e9 al pie de la cruz y los bendecir\u00e9. Tu querido Jes\u00fas.","text_fr":"Mes enfants et mes fr\u00e8res, merci d'\u00eatre ici et d'avoir pli\u00e9 vos genoux sous ma croix. Mes enfants, je touche \u00e0 cette colline b\u00e9nie et \u00e0 cette terre pour que les gr\u00e2ces puissent \u00eatre nombreuses. Mes fr\u00e8res, je vous regarde tous les jours et \u00e0 quel point je suis heureux quand je vois beaucoup d'entre vous \u00e9viter le p\u00e9ch\u00e9 et quand vous avez les yeux tourn\u00e9s vers la lumi\u00e8re. \u00c9coutez ce que dit ma m\u00e8re et votre Sainte M\u00e8re, ne craignez pas les temps de chagrin qui vous attendent parce que lorsque vous venez ici, vous pouvez vous r\u00e9jouir d'un pur bonheur, tout est pr\u00eat. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis, au nom du P\u00e8re, en mon nom et au Saint-Esprit. Je serai avec vous tout au long de la pri\u00e8re, \u00e9l\u00e8verai vos chapelets et approcherai du pied de la croix et je les b\u00e9nirai. Votre cher J\u00e9sus.","text_it":"Figli e fratelli miei, grazie per essere qui e per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia sotto la mia croce. Figli miei, Io tocco questa collina benedetta e questa terra, affinch\u00e9 le grazie siano tante. Fratelli miei, vi guardo tutti i giorni e quanto sono felice, quando vedo molti di voi che evitano il peccato e quando avete lo sguardo rivolto verso la luce. Ascoltate ci\u00f2 che dice la mia e vostra Santissima Madre, non temete per i tempi di dolore che vi attendono perch\u00e9 quando verrete qui, potrete gioire della felicit\u00e0 pura, tutto \u00e8 pronto. Ora vi benedico, nel nome del Padre, nel Mio nome e dello Spirito Santo. Io sar\u00f2 con voi per tutta la preghiera, alzate i vostri rosari e avvicinatevi ai piedi della Croce ed Io li benedir\u00f2. Il vostro caro Ges\u00f9.","text_pl":"Moi synowie i bracia, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj i kl\u0119kacie pod moim krzy\u017cem. Moje dzieci, dotykam tego b\u0142ogos\u0142awionego wzg\u00f3rza i tej ziemi, aby \u0142aski by\u0142y liczne. Bracia moi, patrz\u0119 na was ka\u017cdego dnia i jak\u017ce si\u0119 ciesz\u0119, gdy widz\u0119, \u017ce wielu z was unika grzechu i gdy macie oczy zwr\u00f3cone ku \u015bwiat\u0142u. S\u0142uchajcie tego, co m\u00f3wi moja i wasza naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Matka, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119 o czasy smutku, kt\u00f3re was czekaj\u0105, bo kiedy przyjdziecie tutaj, b\u0119dziecie mogli cieszy\u0107 si\u0119 czystym szcz\u0119\u015bciem, wszystko jest gotowe. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, w imi\u0119 Ojca, w imi\u0119 Moje i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego. B\u0119d\u0119 z wami podczas ca\u0142ej modlitwy, podnie\u015bcie swoje r\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ce i podejd\u017acie do st\u00f3p Krzy\u017ca, a Ja wam pob\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119. Wasz kochany Jezus.","text_pt":"Meus filhos e irm\u00e3os, obrigado por estar aqui e por dobrar os joelhos sob minha cruz. Meus filhos, eu toco essa colina aben\u00e7oada e esta terra para que as gra\u00e7as possam ser muitas. Meus irm\u00e3os, olho para voc\u00ea todos os dias e como estou feliz quando vejo muitos de voc\u00eas evitando o pecado e quando voc\u00ea tem os olhos se virando para a luz. Ou\u00e7a o que minha m\u00e3e e sua m\u00e3e aben\u00e7oada diz, n\u00e3o tema pelos tempos de tristeza que o esperam porque, quando voc\u00ea vier aqui, voc\u00ea pode se alegrar com a pura felicidade, tudo est\u00e1 pronto. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo, em nome do Pai, em meu nome e no Esp\u00edrito Santo. Estarei com voc\u00ea durante toda a ora\u00e7\u00e3o, levantarei seus ros\u00e1rios e abordarei o p\u00e9 da cruz e eu os aben\u00e7oarei. Seu querido Jesus.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u548c\u5144\u5f1f\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u5e76\u5728\u6211\u7684\u5341\u5b57\u67b6\u4e0b\u5f2f\u8170\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u89e6\u6478\u4e86\u8fd9\u5ea7\u6709\u798f\u7684\u5c71\u4e18\u548c\u8fd9\u7247\u571f\u5730\uff0c\u4f7f\u6069\u5178\u53ef\u80fd\u5f88\u591a\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u6bcf\u5929\u90fd\u770b\u7740\u4f60\uff0c\u5f53\u6211\u770b\u5230\u4f60\u4eec\u4e2d\u7684\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u907f\u514d\u72af\u7f6a\u4ee5\u53ca\u60a8\u7684\u773c\u775b\u8f6c\u5411\u5149\u7ebf\u65f6\uff0c\u6211\u6709\u591a\u5feb\u4e50\u3002\u542c\u6211\u548c\u4f60\u7684\u5e78\u798f\u6bcd\u4eb2\u6240\u8bf4\u7684\u8bdd\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u62c5\u5fc3\u7b49\u5f85\u7740\u4f60\u7684\u60b2\u4f24\u65f6\u4ee3\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u5f53\u4f60\u6765\u5230\u8fd9\u91cc\u65f6\uff0c\u4f60\u53ef\u4ee5\u4e3a\u7eaf\u6d01\u7684\u5e78\u798f\u800c\u6b22\u6b23\u9f13\u821e\uff0c\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u51c6\u5907\u597d\u4e86\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u7684\u540d\u4e49\uff0c\u4ee5\u6211\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u548c\u5723\u7075\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002\u5728\u6574\u4e2a\u7948\u7977\u671f\u95f4\uff0c\u6211\u5c06\u4e0e\u60a8\u540c\u5728\uff0c\u4e3e\u8d77\u5ff5\u73e0\uff0c\u63a5\u8fd1\u5341\u5b57\u67b6\u7684\u811a\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u795d\u798f\u4ed6\u4eec\u3002\u4f60\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u8036\u7a23\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":15,"month_string":"September","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people: I love you; I bless you. You are the apple of my eye. I come in search of the conversion of my children.... I come before each one of you as a beggar of love and looking into your eyes, I desire to look into the eyes of the one who will deny me... Open the door of the human will to me so that I may help them to transform themselves! Children, who will open the door of the heart so that they may be worthy shelters of mine? A change of life is necessary for you to be able to be directed by my angels to the physical shelters that are found all over the earth, where you will have to live in total fraternity. Our Sacred Hearts are a refuge for my people where faith, hope, charity, firmness and love are multiplied so that my people continue in the midst of what is strong and surprising for humanity at the time of the Great Tribulation. My people, the nefarious advance of scientific intelligence used to destroy man himself by means of nuclear energy was and is the sentence of those powers. The gift of life given by my Father to man is the greatest gift and it is not for the disposal of the human creature. Humanity lives in war and in constant danger before the arrogance and unconsciousness of those who lead governments. They wish to stop the war, but my children continue to suffer as innocents. Those who serve the devil have greater interests and will not allow the cessation of the war, even if to do so they take the lives of their own people in order to raise the rest of the nations against the nation they point out. This is how they lead humanity: like sheep to the slaughter, they lead them to suffer and they open my side again with the spear of pride. My people, beloved my people, without stopping, listen to me: Prepare yourselves with all that is possible. Whoever is unable to prepare himself, I will see to it that he is provided with the means to survive. Get ready now! Without delay... Look at the sun as it rushes upon the earth bringing strong events upon the planet and upon my children. Some volcanoes, feared by my children, will begin to erupt. The earth will shake more strongly, the heat and cold will become extreme. Convert! Cease rivalries and strife in those who claim to stand by me. Be more mine than the devil's, you cannot serve two masters, be my children. Prayers please me if they are sincere, if they are proclaimed by repentant children desirous of growing spiritually in order to merge with the Divine Will. Do not worry about what happens to you, worry if trials do not come to you. Trials are a sign that you are walking towards me. Pray my children, pray, the crown in England is news with urgency, the people\u2019s desire independence. Pray my children, pray for Central America is shaking. Chile, France and Italy are shaken. Pray my children, pray, the great corporations that produce food for mankind are declining, the direction of food is diverted. Pray my children, pray, the elite grows stronger and the economy declines; they steer mankind towards their goals. They shall return to unleavened bread and feed themselves meagrely. Keep water collected. Be human creatures of firm faith and attentive. Live attentively so that you will not be deceived. Pray the holy rosary and receive me in my Body and Blood in the Eucharist properly prepared. Be experts in love. Prepare for the warning my children, be aware that you will be confronted with your actions and deeds. Repent! My people: In the face of discouragement, uncertainty and fear that you may possess, be creatures of faith in my love for my children. I will not give you stones for bread. Do not fear, my Mother protects you, do not fear. I remain with each one of you. I bless you and I send you my angels to go before you and open the way for you. I bless you, my children. May my peace inundate you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu: Kocham was; b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Jeste\u015bcie jab\u0142kiem mojego oka. Przychodz\u0119 w poszukiwaniu nawr\u00f3cenia moich dzieci.... Przychodz\u0119 przed ka\u017cdym z was jako \u017cebrak mi\u0142o\u015bci i patrz\u0105c w wasze oczy, pragn\u0119 spojrze\u0107 w oczy tego, kt\u00f3ry si\u0119 Mnie zaprze... Otw\u00f3rzcie Mi drzwi ludzkiej woli, abym m\u00f3g\u0142 im pom\u00f3c w przemianie! Dzieci, kto otworzy drzwi serca, aby mog\u0142y by\u0107 godnymi schronienia Moimi? Konieczna jest zmiana \u017cycia, aby\u015bcie mogli zosta\u0107 skierowani przez moich anio\u0142\u00f3w do fizycznych schronie\u0144, kt\u00f3re znajduj\u0105 si\u0119 na ca\u0142ej ziemi, gdzie b\u0119dziecie musieli \u017cy\u0107 w ca\u0142kowitym braterstwie. Nasze \u015awi\u0119te Serca s\u0105 schronieniem dla mojego ludu, gdzie pomna\u017ca si\u0119 wiara, nadzieja, mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, stanowczo\u015b\u0107 i mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, aby m\u00f3j lud trwa\u0142 po\u015br\u00f3d tego, co jest silne i zaskakuj\u0105ce dla ludzko\u015bci w czasie Wielkiego Ucisku. M\u00f3j ludu, nikczemny post\u0119p inteligencji naukowej s\u0142u\u017c\u0105cy zniszczeniu samego cz\u0142owieka za pomoc\u0105 energii j\u0105drowej by\u0142 i jest wyrokiem tych pot\u0119g. Dar \u017cycia dany cz\u0142owiekowi przez mojego Ojca jest najwi\u0119kszym darem i nie jest on przeznaczony do dyspozycji stworzenia ludzkiego. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 \u017cyje w wojnie i w ci\u0105g\u0142ym niebezpiecze\u0144stwie przed arogancj\u0105 i nie\u015bwiadomo\u015bci\u0105 tych, kt\u00f3rzy kieruj\u0105 rz\u0105dami. Oni chc\u0105 zatrzyma\u0107 wojn\u0119, ale Moje dzieci nadal cierpi\u0105 jako niewinni. Ci, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0142u\u017c\u0105 diab\u0142u, maj\u0105 wi\u0119ksze interesy i nie pozwol\u0105 na zaprzestanie wojny, nawet je\u015bli w tym celu odbieraj\u0105 \u017cycie w\u0142asnym ludziom, aby podnie\u015b\u0107 reszt\u0119 narod\u00f3w przeciwko narodowi, kt\u00f3ry wskazuj\u0105. Tak prowadz\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107: jak owce na rze\u017a, prowadz\u0105 j\u0105 do cierpienia i w\u0142\u00f3czni\u0105 pychy otwieraj\u0105 ponownie M\u00f3j bok. M\u00f3j ludu, umi\u0142owany m\u00f3j ludu, nie zatrzymuj\u0105c si\u0119, s\u0142uchajcie Mnie: Przygotujcie si\u0119 ze wszystkim, co jest mo\u017cliwe. Kto nie jest w stanie si\u0119 przygotowa\u0107, Ja zadbam o to, aby zapewniono mu \u015brodki do przetrwania. Przygotujcie si\u0119 natychmiast! Bezzw\u0142ocznie... Sp\u00f3jrzcie na s\u0142o\u0144ce, kt\u00f3re p\u0119dzi nad ziemi\u0105, przynosz\u0105c silne wydarzenia na planecie i na moich dzieciach. Niekt\u00f3re wulkany, kt\u00f3rych obawiaj\u0105 si\u0119 moje dzieci, zaczn\u0105 wybucha\u0107. Ziemia b\u0119dzie si\u0119 mocniej trz\u0105\u015b\u0107, ciep\u0142o i zimno stan\u0105 si\u0119 ekstremalne. Nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119! Zaprzesta\u0144cie rywalizacji i spor\u00f3w w tych, kt\u00f3rzy twierdz\u0105, \u017ce stoj\u0105 przy Mnie. B\u0105d\u017acie bardziej moi ni\u017c diabli, nie mo\u017cecie s\u0142u\u017cy\u0107 dw\u00f3m panom, b\u0105d\u017acie moimi dzie\u0107mi. Modlitwy ciesz\u0105 Mnie, je\u015bli s\u0105 szczere, je\u015bli s\u0105 g\u0142oszone przez skruszone dzieci pragn\u0105ce wzrasta\u0107 duchowo, aby po\u0142\u0105czy\u0107 si\u0119 z Wol\u0105 Bo\u017c\u0105. Nie martwcie si\u0119 o to, co si\u0119 z wami dzieje, nie martwcie si\u0119, je\u015bli pr\u00f3by nie przychodz\u0105 na was. Pr\u00f3by s\u0105 znakiem, \u017ce idziecie w moj\u0105 stron\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, korona w Anglii to wiadomo\u015bci z pilno\u015bci\u0105, lud pragnie niepodleg\u0142o\u015bci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 o Ameryk\u0119 \u015arodkow\u0105, jest wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119ta. Chile, Francja i W\u0142ochy s\u0105 wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119te. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci moje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, wielkie korporacje, kt\u00f3re produkuj\u0105 \u017cywno\u015b\u0107 dla ludzko\u015bci, podupadaj\u0105, kierunek \u017cywno\u015bci jest odwr\u00f3cony. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, elity rosn\u0105 w si\u0142\u0119, a gospodarka maleje; steruj\u0105 ludzko\u015bci\u0105 w kierunku swoich cel\u00f3w. Wr\u00f3c\u0105 do prza\u015bnego chleba i b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 skromnie \u017cywi\u0107. Zbierajcie wod\u0119. B\u0105d\u017acie ludzkimi istotami o mocnej wierze i uwa\u017cnymi. \u017byjcie uwa\u017cnie, aby\u015bcie nie zostali oszukani. Odmawiajcie r\u00f3\u017caniec \u015bwi\u0119ty i przyjmujcie Mnie w moim Ciele i Krwi w Eucharystii odpowiednio przygotowanej. B\u0105d\u017acie ekspertami w mi\u0142o\u015bci. Przygotujcie si\u0119 na ostrze\u017cenie moje dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie \u015bwiadomi, \u017ce zostaniecie skonfrontowani ze swoimi czynami i uczynkami. Nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119! M\u00f3j ludu: W obliczu zniech\u0119cenia, niepewno\u015bci i strachu, kt\u00f3ry mo\u017cecie posiada\u0107, b\u0105d\u017acie istotami wiary w moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do moich dzieci. Nie dam wam kamieni za chleb. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, moja Matka was chroni, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119. Pozostaj\u0119 z ka\u017cdym z was. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was i posy\u0142am wam moich anio\u0142\u00f3w, aby szli przed wami i otwierali wam drog\u0119. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, moje dzieci. Niech m\u00f3j pok\u00f3j was zalewa. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. ","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":15,"month_string":"September","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for honoring this day with prayer. Beloved children, how great is my love for you, but also my sorrow.  God had given you the earth, a paradise, and you have poisoned it, you eat gall believing it is sweet, you no longer have a sense of good and evil, you approach everything that kills you, yet my words some of you have put aside and you have not treasured them, you have lost your peace. Pray for Russia and for the politicians who will make you suffer. Now I leave you with the blessing of the Holy Trinity, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie diesen Tag mit dem Gebet geehrt haben. Geliebte Kinder, wie gro\u00dfartig ist meine Liebe zu dir, aber auch meine Trauer. Gott hatte dir die Erde gegeben, ein Paradies, und du hast es vergiftet, du isst Gall, weil du glaubt, es sei s\u00fc\u00df, du hast kein Gef\u00fchl von Gut und B\u00f6se, du n\u00e4herst Abgesehen von und Sie haben sie nicht gesch\u00e4tzt, Sie haben Ihren Frieden verloren. Bete f\u00fcr Russland und f\u00fcr die Politiker, die dich leiden lassen. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit dem Segen der Heiligen Dreifaltigkeit, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por honrar este d\u00eda con oraci\u00f3n. Amados a los ni\u00f1os, cu\u00e1n grande es mi amor para ti, pero tambi\u00e9n mi dolor. Dios te hab\u00eda dado la tierra, un para\u00edso y lo has envenenado, comes el atrapado creyendo que es dulce, ya no tienes el sentido del bien y el mal, te acercas a todo lo que te mata, sin embargo, mis palabras algunos de ustedes los ponen. Aparte y no los has atesorado, has perdido la paz. Ore por Rusia y por los pol\u00edticos que te har\u00e1n sufrir. Ahora te dejo con la bendici\u00f3n de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir honor\u00e9 cette journ\u00e9e de pri\u00e8re. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, \u00e0 quel point mon amour est g\u00e9nial pour vous, mais aussi mon chagrin. Dieu vous avait donn\u00e9 la terre, un paradis, et vous l'avez empoisonn\u00e9, vous mangez en croyant que c'est doux, vous n'avez plus un sens du bien et du mal, vous abordez tout ce qui vous tue, mais mes paroles d'entre vous ont mis Mis \u00e0 part et vous ne les avez pas ch\u00e9ris, vous avez perdu votre paix. Priez pour la Russie et pour les politiciens qui vous feront souffrir. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec la b\u00e9n\u00e9diction de la Sainte Trinit\u00e9, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver onorato questa giornata con la preghiera. Figli amati, quanto \u00e8 grande il mio amore per voi, ma anche il mio dolore.  Dio vi aveva dato la terra, un paradiso e voi l\u2019avete avvelenata, mangiate il fiele credendo sia dolce, non avete pi\u00f9 il senso del bene e del male, vi avvicinate a tutto ci\u00f2 che vi uccide, eppure le mie parole alcuni di voi le hanno messe da parte e non ne avete fatto tesoro, avete perso la pace. Pregate per la Russia e per i politici che vi faranno soffrire. Ora vi lascio con la benedizione della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, amen.","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam za uczczenie tego dnia modlitw\u0105. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, jak wielka jest moja mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 do was, ale i m\u00f3j smutek. B\u00f3g da\u0142 wam ziemi\u0119, raj, a wy j\u0105 zatruli\u015bcie, jecie \u017c\u00f3\u0142\u0107, uwa\u017caj\u0105c j\u0105 za s\u0142odk\u0105, nie macie ju\u017c poczucia dobra i z\u0142a, podchodzicie do wszystkiego, co was zabija, a jednocze\u015bnie moje s\u0142owa niekt\u00f3rzy z was odrzucili i nie cenili ich, stracili\u015bcie pok\u00f3j. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Rosj\u0119 i za polityk\u00f3w, kt\u00f3rzy sprawi\u0105, \u017ce b\u0119dziecie cierpie\u0107. Teraz zostawiam was z b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por honrar este dia com ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Filhos Amados, qu\u00e3o grande \u00e9 meu amor por voc\u00ea, mas tamb\u00e9m minha tristeza. Deus lhe deu a terra, um para\u00edso, e voc\u00ea o envenenou, voc\u00ea come Gall acreditando que \u00e9 doce, voc\u00ea n\u00e3o tem mais uma sensa\u00e7\u00e3o de bem e mal, voc\u00ea aborda tudo o que te mata, mas minhas palavras alguns de voc\u00eas colocaram Al\u00e9m e voc\u00ea n\u00e3o os valorizou, perdeu sua paz. Ore pela R\u00fassia e pelos pol\u00edticos que far\u00e3o voc\u00ea sofrer. Agora deixo voc\u00ea com a b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u4e3a\u8fd9\u4e00\u5929\u7684\u7948\u7977\u800c\u7eaa\u5ff5\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u6211\u5bf9\u4f60\u7684\u7231\u6709\u591a\u4f1f\u5927\uff0c\u4e5f\u662f\u6211\u7684\u60b2\u4f24\u3002\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7ed9\u4e86\u4f60\u5730\u7403\uff0c\u4e00\u4e2a\u5929\u5802\uff0c\u4f60\u628a\u5b83\u6bd2\u6b7b\u4e86\uff0c\u4f60\u5403\u4e86gall\u76f8\u4fe1\u5b83\u662f\u751c\u871c\u7684\uff0c\u4f60\u4e0d\u518d\u6709\u5584\u4e0e\u6076\u7684\u611f\u89c9\uff0c\u4f60\u63a5\u8fd1\u4e00\u5207\u6740\u6b7b\u4f60\u7684\u4e00\u5207\u9664\u4e86\u60a8\u8fd8\u6ca1\u6709\u73cd\u60dc\u4ed6\u4eec\uff0c\u60a8\u5df2\u7ecf\u5931\u53bb\u4e86\u548c\u5e73\u3002\u4e3a\u4fc4\u7f57\u65af\u548c\u5c06\u4f7f\u60a8\u53d7\u82e6\u7684\u653f\u5ba2\u7948\u7977\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u7559\u4e0b\u4e86\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u7684\u795d\u798f\uff0c\u963f\u4eec\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":17,"month_string":"September","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My beloved children, thank you for responding to my call of your heart. My children, terrible times await you but you must fight and continue to be warriors of light, do not fear, fear destroys faith, but love and trust will strengthen it. Beloved children, fight for God's sake and you will win in His love. Please children, do not give in to the wiles of the devil, these are times of trial. Pray for England, where her decline has begun. Now I leave you with my blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine geliebten Kinder, vielen Dank, dass Sie auf meinen Herzensruf geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, schreckliche Zeiten warten auf dich, aber du musst k\u00e4mpfen und weiterhin Lichtkrieger sein, keine Angst, Angst zerst\u00f6rt den Glauben, aber Liebe und Vertrauen werden ihn st\u00e4rken. Geliebte Kinder, k\u00e4mpfen um Gottes willen und Sie werden in seiner Liebe gewinnen. Bitte Kinder, geben Sie den Verletzungen des Teufels nicht nach, dies sind Gerichtszeiten. Bete f\u00fcr England, wo ihr Niedergang begonnen hat. Jetzt verlasse ich dich mit meinem Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder a mi llamada desde tu coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, los tiempos terribles te esperan, pero tienes que luchar y seguir siendo guerreros de la luz, no temen, el miedo destruye la fe, pero el amor y la confianza lo fortalecer\u00e1n. Queridos hijos, luchan por el amor de Dios y ganar\u00e1s en su amor. Por favor, ni\u00f1os, no se abandonen los trucos del diablo, estos son los tiempos de la prueba. Ore por Inglaterra, donde comenz\u00f3 su declive. Ahora te dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel de votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, terribles, vous attendent mais vous devez vous battre et continuer \u00e0 \u00eatre des guerriers de la lumi\u00e8re, ne craignez pas, la peur d\u00e9truit la foi, mais l'amour et la confiance le renforceront. Les enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, se battent pour l'amour de Dieu et vous gagnerez dans son amour. S'il vous pla\u00eet, les enfants, ne c\u00e8dent pas aux ruses du diable, ce sont des moments de proc\u00e8s. Priez pour l'Angleterre, o\u00f9 son d\u00e9clin a commenc\u00e9. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei prediletti, grazie per avere risposto alla mia chiamata del vostro cuore. Figli miei, tempi terribili vi attendono ma voi dovete lottare e continuare ad essere guerrieri di luce, non temete, la paura distrugge la fede, ma l\u2019amore e la fiducia la rinforzer\u00e0. Figli cari, combattete per amore di Dio e vincerete nel Suo amore. Vi prego figli, non abbandonatevi alle astuzie del demonio, questi sono tempi della prova. Pregate per l\u2019Inghilterra, dove \u00e8 iniziato il suo declino. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moje kochane dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiedzieli\u015bcie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, czekaj\u0105 was straszne czasy, ale musicie walczy\u0107 i nadal by\u0107 wojownikami \u015bwiat\u0142a, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, strach niszczy wiar\u0119, ale mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 i zaufanie j\u0105 wzmocni. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, walczcie o mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 Boga, a zwyci\u0119\u017cycie w Jego mi\u0142o\u015bci. B\u0142agam was, dzieci, nie poddawajcie si\u0119 podst\u0119pom diab\u0142a, to jest czas pr\u00f3by. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Angli\u0119, gdzie rozpocz\u0105\u0142 si\u0119 jej upadek. Zostawiam was teraz z moim b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos amados, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada de seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, tempos terr\u00edveis esperam voc\u00ea, mas voc\u00ea deve lutar e continuar sendo guerreiros da luz, n\u00e3o temem, medo destr\u00f3i a f\u00e9, mas o amor e a confian\u00e7a o fortalecer\u00e3o. Filhos Amados, lute pelo amor de Deus e voc\u00ea vencer\u00e1 em Seu amor. Por favor, as crian\u00e7as, n\u00e3o cedam aos arbustos do diabo, esses s\u00e3o momentos de julgamento. Ore pela Inglaterra, onde seu decl\u00ednio come\u00e7ou. Agora deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5bf9\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u7684\u547c\u5524\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u7cdf\u7cd5\u7684\u65f6\u523b\u5728\u7b49\u7740\u4f60\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u4f60\u5fc5\u987b\u6218\u6597\u5e76\u7ee7\u7eed\u6210\u4e3a\u5149\u660e\u7684\u6218\u58eb\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u5bb3\u6015\u6467\u6bc1\u4fe1\u4ef0\uff0c\u4f46\u7231\u4e0e\u4fe1\u4efb\u4f1a\u589e\u5f3a\u5b83\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e3a\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u7f18\u6545\u800c\u6218\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u8d62\u5f97\u4ed6\u7684\u7231\u3002\u8bf7\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5c48\u670d\u4e8e\u9b54\u9b3c\u7684\u5a01\u5c14\u65af\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u5ba1\u5224\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\u3002\u4e3a\u82f1\u683c\u5170\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5979\u7684\u8870\u843d\u5df2\u7ecf\u5f00\u59cb\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7ed9\u4f60\u7684\u795d\u798f\u7ed9\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":20,"month_string":"September","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, how I wish that faith, love and hope would prevail in all families and everything would be better, instead of letting in the lying devil who brings discord, doubt and strife. My children, look around you, nature is rebelling, volcanoes will ignite, the earth will shake so much. My children, in the Church founded by Peter, my Son is no longer recognized. I feel your sorrows and I ask you to leave them in this blessed place, and I will intervene. My children, I now leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, wie ich w\u00fcnsche, dass Glaube, Liebe und Hoffnung in allen Familien herrschen w\u00fcrden und alles besser w\u00e4re, anstatt den l\u00fcgnerischen Teufel hereinzulassen, der Zwietracht, Zweifel und Streit bringt. Meine Kinder, sehen sich um, die Natur ist Rebellieren, Vulkane werden zern, die Erde wird so viel zittern. Meine Kinder in der von Peter gegr\u00fcndeten Kirche, mein Sohn, wird nicht mehr anerkannt. Ich sp\u00fcre deine Sorgen und bitte dich, sie an diesem gesegneten Ort zu lassen, und ich werde eingreifen. Meine Kinder, ich verlasse Sie jetzt mit meinem m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, cu\u00e1nto me gustar\u00eda prevalecer la fe, el amor y la esperanza en todas las familias y todo saldr\u00eda mejor, en lugar de dejar que el diablo mentiroso entre que trae a Webe, dudas y luchas. Los ni\u00f1os, miran a su alrededor, la naturaleza se est\u00e1 rebelando, los volcanes se encender\u00e1n, la tierra temblar\u00e1 mucho. Mis hijos, en la iglesia fundada por Peter, mi hijo ya no se reconoce a s\u00ed mismo. Siento tus dolores y te pido que los dejes en este lugar bendecido, e intervenir\u00e9. Mis hijos, ahora los dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n materna en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, comment je souhaite que la foi, l'amour et l'espoir l'emportent dans toutes les familles et tout irait mieux, au lieu de laisser entrer le diable menteur qui apporte la discorde, le doute et les conflits. Mes enfants, regardez autour de vous, la nature se rebelle, les volcans s'enflammeront, la terre secouera tellement. Mes enfants, dans l'\u00e9glise fond\u00e9 par Peter, mon fils n'est plus reconnu. Je ressens vos peines et je vous demande de les laisser dans cet endroit b\u00e9ni, et j'interviendrai. Mes enfants, je vous laisse maintenant avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, quanto vorrei che in tutte le famiglie prevalesse la fede, l\u2019amore e la speranza e tutto andrebbe meglio, invece di far entrare il demonio menzognero che porta zizzania, dubbi e lotte. Figli, guardate intorno a voi, la natura si sta ribellando, i vulcani si accenderanno, la terra tremer\u00e0 tanto. Figli miei, nella Chiesa fondata da Pietro, mio Figlio non si riconosce pi\u00f9. Io sento i vostri dolori e vi chiedo di lasciarli in questo luogo Benedetto, ed Io interverr\u00f2. Figli miei, ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie Dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 Wam, \u017ce w swoich sercach odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie. Moje dzieci, jak\u017ce pragn\u0119, aby we wszystkich rodzinach zwyci\u0119\u017cy\u0142a wiara, mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 i nadzieja i wszystko by\u0142oby lepsze, zamiast wpuszcza\u0107 k\u0142amliwego diab\u0142a, kt\u00f3ry wprowadza niezgod\u0119, zw\u0105tpienie i spory. Moje dzieci, rozejrzyjcie si\u0119 wok\u00f3\u0142 siebie, natura si\u0119 buntuje, wulkany zap\u0142on\u0105, ziemia mocno si\u0119 zatrz\u0119sie. Moje dzieci, w Ko\u015bciele za\u0142o\u017conym przez Piotra m\u00f3j Syn nie jest ju\u017c uznawany. Czuj\u0119 tw\u00f3j b\u00f3l i prosz\u0119 ci\u0119 o pozostawienie go w tym b\u0142ogos\u0142awionym miejscu, a Ja b\u0119d\u0119 interweniowa\u0107. Moje dzieci, zostawiam was teraz z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, como desejo que a f\u00e9, o amor e a esperan\u00e7a prevalecessem em todas as fam\u00edlias e tudo seria melhor, em vez de deixar o diabo mentiroso que traz disc\u00f3rdia, d\u00favida e conflito. Meus filhos, olham ao seu redor, a natureza est\u00e1 se rebelando, os vulc\u00f5es v\u00e3o acender, a terra se agitar\u00e1 muito. Meus filhos, na igreja fundada por Pedro, meu filho n\u00e3o \u00e9 mais reconhecido. Sinto suas tristezas e pe\u00e7o que voc\u00ea as deixe neste lugar aben\u00e7oado, e eu intervirei. Meus filhos, agora deixo voc\u00ea com minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u5e0c\u671b\u6240\u6709\u5bb6\u5ead\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\uff0c\u7231\u4e0e\u5e0c\u671b\u5c06\u5360\u4e0a\u98ce\uff0c\u800c\u4e00\u5207\u90fd\u4f1a\u53d8\u5f97\u66f4\u597d\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u8ba9\u6492\u8c0e\u7684\u9b54\u9b3c\u5e26\u6765\u4e0d\u548c\u8c10\uff0c\u6000\u7591\u548c\u51b2\u7a81\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u73af\u987e\u56db\u5468\uff0c\u5927\u81ea\u7136\u6b63\u5728\u53db\u9006\uff0c\u706b\u5c71\u4f1a\u70b9\u71c3\uff0c\u5730\u7403\u4f1a\u6447\u6643\u592a\u591a\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u5728\u5f7c\u5f97\u521b\u7acb\u7684\u6559\u5802\u91cc\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u4e0d\u518d\u88ab\u8ba4\u53ef\u3002\u6211\u611f\u5230\u4f60\u7684\u60b2\u4f24\uff0c\u6211\u8bf7\u4f60\u628a\u4ed6\u4eec\u7559\u5728\u8fd9\u4e2a\u6709\u798f\u7684\u5730\u65b9\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u5e72\u9884\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u73b0\u5728\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u7ed9\u6211\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u795d\u798f\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":21,"month_string":"September","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart: Receive my blessing joined with my desire that all may come to the knowledge of truth. As children of God, you possess the capacity to ask the Divine Spirit for the gift of wisdom, so that you may understand what favours you in God's project and what harms you in god's plan in each one of you. The Divine Spirit prepares you so that you may decide to convert, maintaining the charity that leads you to love your neighbour. Keep very much in mind what my Divine Son said: 'but when you are delivered up, do not worry about how or what you will speak. What you have to speak will be communicated to you at that moment. For it is not you who will speak, but the Spirit of your Father who will speak in you.' My beloved children: The Christian\u2019s life must be Christocentric.... I am his Mother, but my Son is God: the centre of life. The true Christian bases his faith, he does not follow my Son by tradition, but because he knows him and loves him in spirit and truth. The Christian quenches his thirst in the knowledge of Divine Love for humanity, in the knowledge of the Law of God, in the knowledge of the sacraments and the works of mercy, he loves to delve into sacred scripture and knows that God is Love and Justice at the same time. The true Christian makes his life a constant practice of all that is duty, charity, obedience, respect, humility, tolerance; and whatever he must do to be in the manner of my Divine Son. Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart: Remain in spiritual alert so that you are not confused, be careful when speaking so that you don't sin. Each one knows himself and knows what he must change, how his work and actions are. Do it quickly! My Son knows everything and you must not delay. Be attentive children, the tension increases! Those who lead nations speak of nuclear energy as if they speak of protecting the gift of life. For some who are leaders or representatives of nations, talking about the use of nuclear energy is a matter of course. How those who cause pain to my Divine Son with this weapon from hell itself which acts against the gift of life will suffer! Keep the necessary serenity and faith without deserting. Without fear continue to know that my Son remains with his people, that St. Michael the Archangel defends you and that I protect you without rest. Pray my children, pray, the earth is shaking strongly leading to volcanoes becoming active and my children suffering. Pray my children, pray, in the depths of the earth, it has fractured by the movement of tectonic faults, accelerating the continuity of earthquakes. Pray my children, pray, the earth is in danger, the sun emanates strong solar winds affecting the means of communication. Children, stop and look at how at this moment the water is rushing over the earth, the sun is emanating its heat with greater force, the fire is spreading in various countries, the air is blowing stronger and the earth continues to sink in various places... These are signs of how much is going to happen. As Mother of humanity, I must constantly warn my children of how much pain it can cause them.... I keep looking at you, protecting you and interceding for you before my Divine Son to lessen some events of nature. Some of my children who inhabit the earth will move especially to South America in search of protection. In view of this, you must know that the lands of blessing must be purified beforehand. Be children of adoration before the blessed sacrament of the altar. My Divine Son hears the prayers offered with contrite hearts and returns them in blessings for all mankind. Pray, offer, prepare, be a blessing to your brothers, give the best you have in your heart. Beloved children: The cation suffers and the believers weep and wait for what precede this dire sign. Without losing the faith, go forward, pray, repair, offer and be fulfillers of the Divine will. Be fraternal. I protect you; my mantle covers you so that you will not be seen. I love you. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca: Przyjmijcie moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo po\u0142\u0105czone z moim pragnieniem, aby wszyscy doszli do poznania prawdy. Jako dzieci Bo\u017ce macie zdolno\u015b\u0107 proszenia Ducha Bo\u017cego o dar m\u0105dro\u015bci, aby\u015bcie mogli zrozumie\u0107, co wam sprzyja w projekcie Bo\u017cym, a co szkodzi w planie Bo\u017cym w ka\u017cdym z was. Duch Bo\u017cy przygotowuje was, aby\u015bcie mogli zdecydowa\u0107 si\u0119 na nawr\u00f3cenie, zachowuj\u0105c mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, kt\u00f3ra prowadzi was do mi\u0142o\u015bci bli\u017aniego. Zachowajcie bardzo mocno w pami\u0119ci to, co powiedzia\u0142 M\u00f3j Boski Syn: \"ale kiedy zostaniecie wydani, nie martwcie si\u0119 o to, jak lub co b\u0119dziecie m\u00f3wi\u0107. To, co macie m\u00f3wi\u0107, b\u0119dzie wam przekazane w tym momencie. Albowiem nie wy b\u0119dziecie m\u00f3wi\u0107, lecz Duch Ojca waszego, kt\u00f3ry b\u0119dzie m\u00f3wi\u0142 w was.\" Moje kochane dzieci: \u017bycie chrze\u015bcijanina musi by\u0107 chrystocentryczne.... Ja jestem jego Matk\u0105, ale m\u00f3j Syn jest Bogiem: centrum \u017cycia. Prawdziwy chrze\u015bcijanin opiera swoj\u0105 wiar\u0119, nie idzie za moim Synem przez tradycj\u0119, ale dlatego, \u017ce Go zna i kocha w duchu i prawdzie. Chrze\u015bcijanin gasi swoje pragnienie w poznaniu Boskiej Mi\u0142o\u015bci do ludzko\u015bci, w poznaniu Prawa Bo\u017cego, w poznaniu sakrament\u00f3w i dzie\u0142 mi\u0142osierdzia, uwielbia zag\u0142\u0119bia\u0107 si\u0119 w Pismo \u015awi\u0119te i wie, \u017ce B\u00f3g jest Mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 i Sprawiedliwo\u015bci\u0105 jednocze\u015bnie. Prawdziwy chrze\u015bcijanin czyni swoje \u017cycie nieustann\u0105 praktyk\u0105 tego wszystkiego, co jest obowi\u0105zkiem, mi\u0142osierdziem, pos\u0142usze\u0144stwem, szacunkiem, pokor\u0105, tolerancj\u0105; i tym, co musi czyni\u0107, aby by\u0107 na wz\u00f3r mojego Boskiego Syna. Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca: Pozosta\u0144cie w duchowej czujno\u015bci, aby\u015bcie nie byli zdezorientowani, b\u0105d\u017acie ostro\u017cni w m\u00f3wieniu, aby\u015bcie nie zgrzeszyli. Ka\u017cdy zna siebie i wie, co musi zmieni\u0107, jak wygl\u0105daj\u0105 jego prace i dzia\u0142ania. Zr\u00f3bcie to szybko! M\u00f3j Syn wie wszystko i nie wolno wam zwleka\u0107. B\u0105d\u017acie uwa\u017cne dzieci, napi\u0119cie wzrasta! Ci, kt\u00f3rzy przewodz\u0105 narodom, m\u00f3wi\u0105 o energii atomowej tak, jakby m\u00f3wili o ochronie daru \u017cycia. Dla niekt\u00f3rych, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0105 przyw\u00f3dcami lub przedstawicielami narod\u00f3w, m\u00f3wienie o wykorzystaniu energii j\u0105drowej jest czym\u015b oczywistym. Jak\u017ce b\u0119d\u0105 cierpie\u0107 ci, kt\u00f3rzy zadaj\u0105 b\u00f3l mojemu Boskiemu Synowi t\u0105 broni\u0105 z samego piek\u0142a, kt\u00f3ra dzia\u0142a przeciwko darowi \u017cycia! Zachowajcie konieczn\u0105 pogod\u0119 ducha i wiar\u0119 bez dezercji. Bez l\u0119ku wiedzcie nadal, \u017ce m\u00f3j Syn pozostaje ze swoim ludem, \u017ce \u015bw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142 broni was i \u017ce Ja was chroni\u0119 bez wytchnienia. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ziemia mocno si\u0119 trz\u0119sie, co prowadzi do uaktywnienia si\u0119 wulkan\u00f3w i cierpienia moich dzieci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, w g\u0142\u0119bi ziemi p\u0119k\u0142a ona przez ruch uskok\u00f3w tektonicznych, przyspieszaj\u0105c ci\u0105g\u0142o\u015b\u0107 trz\u0119sie\u0144 ziemi. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ziemia jest w niebezpiecze\u0144stwie, s\u0142o\u0144ce emanuje silne wiatry s\u0142oneczne wp\u0142ywaj\u0105ce na \u015brodki komunikacji. Dzieci, zatrzymajcie si\u0119 i popatrzcie, jak w tej chwili woda p\u0119dzi nad ziemi\u0105, s\u0142o\u0144ce emanuje swoje ciep\u0142o z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 si\u0142\u0105, ogie\u0144 rozprzestrzenia si\u0119 w r\u00f3\u017cnych krajach, powietrze wieje mocniej, a ziemia nadal zapada si\u0119 w r\u00f3\u017cnych miejscach... To s\u0105 znaki, jak wiele si\u0119 wydarzy. Jako Matka ludzko\u015bci musz\u0119 nieustannie ostrzega\u0107 moje dzieci przed tym, jak wiele b\u00f3lu mo\u017ce im zada\u0107.... Ci\u0105gle patrz\u0119 na was, chroni\u0119 was i wstawiam si\u0119 za wami przed Moim Boskim Synem, aby zmniejszy\u0107 niekt\u00f3re wydarzenia natury. Niekt\u00f3re z moich dzieci, kt\u00f3re zamieszkuj\u0105 ziemi\u0119, przenios\u0105 si\u0119 zw\u0142aszcza do Ameryki Po\u0142udniowej w poszukiwaniu ochrony. W zwi\u0105zku z tym musicie wiedzie\u0107, \u017ce ziemie b\u0142ogos\u0142awione musz\u0105 by\u0107 wcze\u015bniej oczyszczone. B\u0105d\u017acie dzie\u0107mi adoracji przed b\u0142ogos\u0142awionym sakramentem o\u0142tarza. M\u00f3j Boski Syn wys\u0142uchuje modlitw ofiarowanych ze skruszonymi sercami i zwraca je w b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwach dla ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ofiarujcie, przygotujcie, b\u0105d\u017acie b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem dla waszych braci, dajcie to, co macie najlepszego w sercu. Umi\u0142owane dzieci: Kation cierpi, a wierni p\u0142acz\u0105 i czekaj\u0105 na to, co poprzedza ten tragiczny znak. Nie trac\u0105c wiary, id\u017acie naprz\u00f3d, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, naprawiajcie, ofiarujcie i b\u0105d\u017acie wype\u0142niaczami woli Bo\u017cej. B\u0105d\u017acie braterscy. Chroni\u0119 was, m\u00f3j p\u0142aszcz was okrywa, aby\u015bcie nie byli widziani. Kocham was. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. ","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":23,"month_string":"September","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved people of God: I protect you by Divine order with my heavenly legions, which are all on earth. Every human being is the joy or the sorrow of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. This is the awareness to which every human being is called. Analyse your works and actions, ask yourselves whether you are the joy or the sorrow of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. This war is spiritual. It is not for nothing - it is for souls, because the devil continually tempts them so that they would fall and thus be a cause of pain for our King and Lord Jesus Christ. You know full well that, being part of humanity, you are in grave danger of being participants in the third world war, and you must be aware of this so that you would change, starting from the language you use, your expressions and gestures, to your personal relationship with the most Holy Trinity, with our Queen and Mother, with your companions on the way, your guardian angels and with your brothers and sisters. All of this tips the balance in favour of or against the good. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: This is the moment when war goes from words to deeds and humanity\u2019s suffering will begin with vehemence. The earth will shake forcefully; the earth\u2019s core is magnetized by the sun, which lashes it with its solar flares. What the earth contains within it will come out of the centre of the earth via volcanoes, and the great volcanoes will cause unexpected eruptions. Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, how many innocent people are preparing to die in war, compelled by those who lead them! How many human beings will go from having material possessions to being nomads, moving from country to country so as not to fall prey to war! How many will leave their countries so as not to be active participants in an army! It is the human being\u2019s folly, together with ambition for power, that leads man to act immediately. I hear in heaven: 'woe, woe, woe to him who raises his hand first to give the order that nuclear energy be used. It would be better for that man not to have been born.' You will see a celestial body burning in the sky and approaching earth. Resist, children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, resist. Continue to be attentive without falling into despair. The King of heaven and earth gives you his protection and that of his most holy Mother together with the angelic choirs. Onward without turning back! Hope and faith in the Divine Word do not allow you to falter. Without fear, without haste, continue with firm faith in the power of the most holy trinity. Be creatures of good. As the commander of the armies of heaven I bless those who take this call seriously. I promise you that one of my angels will remain next to you for the crucial moments. I bless you with my sword so that the human will would not lead you to fall into evil. I bless you, children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany ludu Bo\u017cy: Chroni\u0119 was z rozkazu Bo\u017cego moimi niebia\u0144skimi legionami, kt\u00f3re s\u0105 wszystkie na ziemi. Ka\u017cdy cz\u0142owiek jest rado\u015bci\u0105 lub smutkiem naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. To jest \u015bwiadomo\u015b\u0107, do kt\u00f3rej ka\u017cdy cz\u0142owiek jest powo\u0142any. Analizujcie swoje dzie\u0142a i czyny, pytajcie siebie, czy jeste\u015bcie rado\u015bci\u0105 czy smutkiem naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Ta wojna jest wojn\u0105 duchow\u0105. Nie jest o nic - jest o dusze, bo diabe\u0142 nieustannie je kusi, aby upad\u0142y i tym samym by\u0142y przyczyn\u0105 b\u00f3lu dla naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Wiecie dobrze, \u017ce b\u0119d\u0105c cz\u0119\u015bci\u0105 ludzko\u015bci, jeste\u015bcie w powa\u017cnym niebezpiecze\u0144stwie bycia uczestnikami trzeciej wojny \u015bwiatowej i musicie by\u0107 tego \u015bwiadomi, aby\u015bcie si\u0119 zmienili, pocz\u0105wszy od j\u0119zyka, kt\u00f3rego u\u017cywacie, waszych wypowiedzi i gest\u00f3w, a\u017c po wasz\u0105 osobist\u0105 relacj\u0119 z Tr\u00f3jc\u0105 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105, z nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0105, z waszymi towarzyszami drogi, waszymi anio\u0142ami str\u00f3\u017cami i z waszymi bra\u0107mi i siostrami. Wszystko to przechyla szal\u0119 na korzy\u015b\u0107 lub niekorzy\u015b\u0107 dobra. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Oto chwila, w kt\u00f3rej wojna przejdzie od s\u0142\u00f3w do czyn\u00f3w, a cierpienia ludzko\u015bci rozpoczn\u0105 si\u0119 z gwa\u0142towno\u015bci\u0105. Ziemia zatrz\u0119sie si\u0119 z si\u0142\u0105; j\u0105dro ziemi jest namagnesowane przez s\u0142o\u0144ce, kt\u00f3re uderza w nie swoimi rozb\u0142yskami s\u0142onecznymi. To, co zawiera w sobie ziemia, wydostanie si\u0119 z jej \u015brodka poprzez wulkany, a wielkie wulkany spowoduj\u0105 niespodziewane erupcje. Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, jak wielu niewinnych ludzi przygotowuje si\u0119 do \u015bmierci na wojnie, zmuszonych przez tych, kt\u00f3rzy ich prowadz\u0105! Jak wiele istot ludzkich przejdzie od posiadania d\u00f3br materialnych do bycia nomadami, przenosz\u0105c si\u0119 z kraju do kraju, aby nie pa\u015b\u0107 ofiar\u0105 wojny! Jak wielu opu\u015bci swoje kraje, aby nie by\u0107 aktywnymi uczestnikami armii! To ludzka g\u0142upota, wraz z ambicj\u0105 w\u0142adzy, prowadzi cz\u0142owieka do natychmiastowego dzia\u0142ania. S\u0142ysz\u0119 w niebie: \"Biada, biada, biada temu, kto pierwszy podniesie r\u0119k\u0119, aby wyda\u0107 rozkaz u\u017cycia energii j\u0105drowej. By\u0142oby lepiej, \u017ceby ten cz\u0142owiek si\u0119 nie urodzi\u0142\". Zobaczycie cia\u0142o niebieskie p\u0142on\u0105ce na niebie i zbli\u017caj\u0105ce si\u0119 do ziemi. Opierajcie si\u0119, dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, opierajcie si\u0119. Trwajcie w uwa\u017cno\u015bci, nie popadaj\u0105c w rozpacz. Kr\u00f3l nieba i ziemi daje wam swoj\u0105 ochron\u0119 i ochron\u0119 swojej naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Matki wraz z ch\u00f3rami anielskimi. Naprz\u00f3d bez odwrotu! Nadzieja i wiara w S\u0142owo Bo\u017ce nie pozwalaj\u0105 wam si\u0119 za\u0142ama\u0107. Bez l\u0119ku, bez po\u015bpiechu, kontynuujcie z mocn\u0105 wiar\u0105 w moc naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Tr\u00f3jcy. B\u0105d\u017acie istotami dobra. Jako dow\u00f3dca wojsk niebieskich b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 tych, kt\u00f3rzy powa\u017cnie traktuj\u0105 to wezwanie. Obiecuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeden z moich anio\u0142\u00f3w pozostanie obok was w decyduj\u0105cych momentach. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moim mieczem, aby ludzka wola nie doprowadzi\u0142a was do upadku w z\u0142o. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. ","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":24,"month_string":"September","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear blessed children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, do not be afraid, I know your hearts and I know that they are immersed in fear for everything that is surrounding you. Dear children, if your faith is strong, you will have peace in your hearts otherwise anxiety will take over. Pray for the priests, the stench of Satan's house reaches as far as the Church of Peter. The war advances without mercy, the waters will invade the cities and the volcanoes will make their force felt. My children, pray together, be united strongly, pray to Jesus to work in your hearts. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe gesegnete Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, haben keine Angst, ich kenne deine Herzen und ich wei\u00df, dass sie in Angst vor allem eintauchen, was dich umgibt. Liebe Kinder, wenn Ihr Glaube stark ist, werden Sie Frieden in Ihren Herzen haben, sonst wird die Angst \u00fcbernehmen. Bete f\u00fcr die Priester, der Gestank von Satans Haus reicht bis zur Kirche von Peter. Der Krieg f\u00e4hrt ohne Barmherzigkeit vor, das Wasser wird in die St\u00e4dte eindringen und die Vulkane werden ihre Kraft empfinden. Meine Kinder beten zusammen, seien Sie stark vereint und beten Sie zu Jesus, um in Ihren Herzen zu arbeiten. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Estimados ni\u00f1os de Benedetti, gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, no tengan miedo, conozco sus corazones y s\u00e9 que est\u00e1n inmersos en miedo por todo lo que te rodea. Queridos hijos, si su fe es fuerte, tendr\u00e1 paz en sus corazones de lo contrario, la ansiedad se har\u00e1 cargo. Ore por los sacerdotes, el hedor de la casa de Satan\u00e1s llega a la iglesia de Pietro. La guerra avanza sin piedad, las aguas invadir\u00e1n las ciudades y los volcanes har\u00e1n sentir su fuerza. Hijos, oren juntos, est\u00e9n fuertemente unidos, oren a Jes\u00fas para que opere en sus corazones. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants b\u00e9nis, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, n'ont pas peur, je connais votre c\u0153ur et je sais qu'ils sont plong\u00e9s dans la peur pour tout ce qui vous entoure. Chers enfants, si votre foi est forte, vous aurez la paix dans votre c\u0153ur sinon l'anxi\u00e9t\u00e9 prendra le relais. Priez pour les pr\u00eatres, la puanteur de la maison de Satan atteint jusqu'\u00e0 l'\u00e9glise de Pierre. La guerre avance sans piti\u00e9, les eaux envahiront les villes et les volcans feront sentir leur force. Mes enfants, priez ensemble, soyez fortement unis, priez J\u00e9sus pour travailler dans vos c\u0153urs. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli benedetti, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, non abbiate timore, conosco i vostri cuori e so che sono immersi nella paura per tutto ci\u00f2 che vi sta circondando. Figli cari, se la vostra fede sar\u00e0 forte, avrete la pace nei vostri cuori altrimenti l\u2019ansia prender\u00e0 il sopravvento. Pregate per i sacerdoti,  il fetore della casa di satana arriva fino alla Chiesa di Pietro. La guerra avanza senza piet\u00e0, le acque invaderanno le citt\u00e0 e i vulcani faranno sentire la loro forza. Figli, pregate insieme, siate uniti fortemente, pregate Ges\u00f9 affinch\u00e9 operi nei vostri cuori. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie b\u0142ogos\u0142awione dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce w swoich sercach odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie. Moje dzieci, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, znam wasze serca i wiem, \u017ce s\u0105 one zanurzone w l\u0119ku o wszystko, co was otacza. Moje drogie dzieci, je\u015bli wasza wiara jest silna, b\u0119dziecie mieli pok\u00f3j w waszych sercach, w przeciwnym razie niepok\u00f3j we\u017amie g\u00f3r\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za kap\u0142an\u00f3w, smr\u00f3d domu szatana si\u0119ga a\u017c do Ko\u015bcio\u0142a Piotra. Wojna post\u0119puje bez lito\u015bci, wody wtargn\u0105 do miast, a wulkany dadz\u0105 zna\u0107 o swojej sile. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 razem, b\u0105d\u017acie mocno zjednoczeni, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 do Jezusa, aby dzia\u0142a\u0142 w waszych sercach. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos aben\u00e7oados, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, n\u00e3o t\u00eam medo, eu conhe\u00e7o seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e sei que eles est\u00e3o imersos com medo por tudo o que est\u00e1 o cercando. Caros filhos, se sua f\u00e9 for forte, voc\u00ea ter\u00e1 paz em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es, de outra forma, a ansiedade assumir\u00e1 o controle. Ore pelos padres, o cheiro da casa de Satan\u00e1s chega at\u00e9 a Igreja de Pedro. A guerra avan\u00e7a sem miseric\u00f3rdia, as \u00e1guas invadir\u00e3o as cidades e os vulc\u00f5es far\u00e3o com que sua for\u00e7a se sentisse. Meus filhos, oram juntos, se unam fortemente, orem a Jesus para trabalhar em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u795d\u798f\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u6211\u77e5\u9053\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u6211\u77e5\u9053\u4ed6\u4eec\u6c89\u6d78\u5728\u5bb3\u6015\u5468\u56f4\u7684\u4e00\u5207\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u60a8\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u575a\u5f3a\uff0c\u60a8\u5c06\u5728\u5fc3\u4e2d\u4fdd\u6301\u548c\u5e73\uff0c\u5426\u5219\u7126\u8651\u5c06\u63a5\u7ba1\u3002\u4e3a\u796d\u53f8\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u6492\u65e6\u5bb6\u7684\u6076\u81ed\u5230\u8fbe\u5f7c\u5f97\u6559\u5802\u3002\u6218\u4e89\u65e0\u601c\u60af\u5730\u8fdb\u5c55\uff0c\u6c34\u57df\u5c06\u4fb5\u5165\u57ce\u5e02\uff0c\u706b\u5c71\u5c06\u4f7f\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u529b\u91cf\u611f\u53d7\u5230\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u529b\u91cf\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u4e00\u8d77\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u56e2\u7ed3\u4e00\u81f4\uff0c\u5411\u8036\u7a23\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5728\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u5de5\u4f5c\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":27,"month_string":"September","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My sweet children, thank you for answering My call in your hearts and thank you for bending your knees in prayer. My children, many are my tears for those who do not understand, do not believe, blaspheme and are not converted, I, as Mother want to save all my children. My Jesus is bestowing many graces, but often you are more attracted by the things of the world that invite perdition and you do not notice the good things that you have every day, unfortunately pride and haughtiness accompany you. My children, teach your children the recitation of the Holy Rosary. My children, I ask you to go to the streets of the world to proclaim the Gospel, tell everyone that Jesus will soon return and you must be prepared. Now, I bless you in the name of the Most Holy Trinity, amen.","text_de":"Meine s\u00fc\u00dfen Kinder, danke, dass Sie meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen beantwortet haben, und danke, dass Sie sich die Knie im Gebet gebeugt haben. Meine Kinder, viele sind meine Tr\u00e4nen f\u00fcr diejenigen, die nicht verstehen, nicht glauben, blasphemen und nicht konvertiert werden, ich m\u00f6chte, wie Mutter alle meine Kinder retten. Mein Jesus verleiht viele Gnaden, aber oft werden Sie mehr von den Dingen der Welt angezogen, die Verderblichkeit einladen, und Sie bemerken die guten Dinge, die Sie jeden Tag haben, nicht, leider stolz und Hochmut begleiten Sie. Meine Kinder lehren Ihren Kindern die Rezitation des heiligen Rosenkranzes. Meine Kinder, ich bitte Sie, auf die Stra\u00dfe der Welt zu gehen, um das Evangelium zu verk\u00fcnden. Sagen Sie allen, dass Jesus bald zur\u00fcckkehren und Sie m\u00fcssen vorbereitet sein. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen der heiligsten Dreifaltigkeit, Amen.","text_es":"Dulces hijos de mi, gracias por responder mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n y gracias por doblar las rodillas en oraci\u00f3n. Mis hijos, hay muchas l\u00e1grimas para aquellos que no entienden, no creen, blasfemas y no se convierten, como madre, quiero salvar a todos mis hijos. Mi Jes\u00fas est\u00e1 dando muchas gracias, pero a menudo m\u00e1s atra\u00eddos por las cosas del mundo que lo invitan a perdici\u00f3n y no notan las cosas hermosas que tiene todos los d\u00edas, desafortunadamente el orgullo y el orgullo lo acompa\u00f1an. Ni\u00f1os que ense\u00f1an a sus hijos la recitaci\u00f3n del Rosario Santo. Mis hijos, les pido que pases por las calles del mundo para anunciar el Evangelio, diles a todos que Jes\u00fas pronto regresar\u00e1 y que tendr\u00e1s que estar preparado. Ahora, te bendigo en el nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants doux, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur et merci d'avoir pli\u00e9 vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re. Mes enfants, beaucoup sont mes larmes pour ceux qui ne comprennent pas, ne croient pas, blasph\u00e9mer et ne sont pas convertis, moi, car la m\u00e8re veut sauver tous mes enfants. Mon J\u00e9sus accorde de nombreuses gr\u00e2ces, mais souvent vous \u00eates plus attir\u00e9 par les choses du monde qui invitent la perdition et vous ne remarquez pas les bonnes choses que vous avez chaque jour, malheureusement, l'orgueil et la verbcit\u00e9 vous accompagnent. Mes enfants enseignent \u00e0 vos enfants la r\u00e9citation du Saint Rosaire. Mes enfants, je vous demande d'aller dans les rues du monde pour proclamer l'\u00c9vangile, dire \u00e0 tout le monde que J\u00e9sus reviendra bient\u00f4t et que vous devez \u00eatre pr\u00eat. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9, Amen.","text_it":"Dolci bambini miei, grazie per aver risposto la mia chiamata nel vostro cuore e grazie per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia nella preghiera. Figli miei, tante sono le mie lacrime per coloro che non comprendono, non credono, bestemmiano e non si convertono, Io, come Madre\u200b \u200bvoglio salvare tutti i miei figli. Il mio Ges\u00f9 sta elargendo molte grazie, ma spesso si \u00e8 pi\u00f9 attratti dalle cose del mondo che invitano alla perdizione e non vi accorgete delle cose belle che si ha tutti i giorni, purtroppo l\u2019orgoglio e la superbia vi accompagna. Figli insegnate ai vostri bambini la recita del Santo Rosario. Figli miei, vi chiedo di andare per le strade del mondo ad annunciare il Vangelo, dite a tutti che Ges\u00f9 presto torner\u00e0 e dovrete essere preparati. Ora, vi benedico nel nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0, amen.","text_pl":"Moje s\u0142odkie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach i dzi\u0119kuj\u0119, \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie w modlitwie. Moje dzieci, wiele jest moich \u0142ez za tych, kt\u00f3rzy nie rozumiej\u0105, nie wierz\u0105, blu\u017ani\u0105 i nie nawracaj\u0105 si\u0119, Ja jako Matka chc\u0119 uratowa\u0107 wszystkie moje dzieci. M\u00f3j Jezus hojnie obdarza wieloma \u0142askami, ale cz\u0119sto bardziej poci\u0105gaj\u0105 was rzeczy tego \u015bwiata, kt\u00f3re prowadz\u0105 was do zguby, a nie zauwa\u017cacie pi\u0119knych rzeczy, kt\u00f3re macie na co dzie\u0144, niestety pycha i arogancja wam towarzysz\u0105. Moje dzieci, uczcie swoje dzieci odmawiania R\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ca \u015awi\u0119tego. Moje dzieci, prosz\u0119 was, aby\u015bcie wyszli na ulice \u015bwiata, aby og\u0142osi\u0107 Ewangeli\u0119, powiedzie\u0107 wszystkim, \u017ce Jezus wkr\u00f3tce powr\u00f3ci i trzeba by\u0107 przygotowanym. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos doces, obrigado por atender minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e obrigado por dobrar os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, muitos s\u00e3o minhas l\u00e1grimas para aqueles que n\u00e3o entendem, n\u00e3o acreditam, blasfema e n\u00e3o s\u00e3o convertidos, como a m\u00e3e quero salvar todos os meus filhos. Meu Jesus est\u00e1 concedendo muitas gra\u00e7as, mas muitas vezes voc\u00ea \u00e9 mais atra\u00eddo pelas coisas do mundo que convidam a perdi\u00e7\u00e3o e voc\u00ea n\u00e3o percebe as coisas boas que todos os dias, infelizmente, orgulho e arrog\u00e2ncia o acompanham. Meus filhos, ensinam a seus filhos a recita\u00e7\u00e3o do Santo Ros\u00e1rio. Meus filhos, pe\u00e7o que voc\u00ea v\u00e1 \u00e0s ruas do mundo para proclamar o evangelho, diga a todos que Jesus voltar\u00e1 em breve e voc\u00ea deve estar preparado. Agora, eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u53ef\u7231\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u5fc3\u4e2d\u63a5\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\uff0c\u5e76\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5c48\u670d\u4e8e\u7948\u7977\u3002\u5bf9\u4e8e\u90a3\u4e9b\u4e0d\u4e86\u89e3\uff0c\u4e0d\u76f8\u4fe1\uff0c\u4eb5\u6e0e\u548c\u4e0d\u8f6c\u6362\u7684\u4eba\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u7684\u773c\u6cea\u662f\u6211\u7684\u773c\u6cea\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6bcd\u4eb2\u60f3\u62ef\u6551\u6211\u6240\u6709\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u3002\u6211\u7684\u8036\u7a23\u8d4b\u4e88\u4e86\u8bb8\u591a\u6069\u5178\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u901a\u5e38\u60a8\u4f1a\u88ab\u9080\u8bf7\u706d\u7edd\u7684\u4e16\u754c\u6240\u5438\u5f15\uff0c\u800c\u4e14\u60a8\u6ca1\u6709\u6ce8\u610f\u5230\u6bcf\u5929\u62e5\u6709\u7684\u7f8e\u597d\u4e8b\u7269\uff0c\u4e0d\u5e78\u7684\u662f\uff0c\u9a84\u50b2\u548c\u50b2\u6162\u7684\u4f34\u968f\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6559\u60a8\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u7684\u6717\u8bf5\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u8981\u4f60\u53bb\u4e16\u754c\u8857\u5934\u5ba3\u626c\u798f\u97f3\uff0c\u544a\u8bc9\u6240\u6709\u4eba\u8036\u7a23\u5f88\u5feb\u5c31\u4f1a\u56de\u6765\uff0c\u4f60\u5fc5\u987b\u505a\u597d\u51c6\u5907\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u6700\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":9,"day":28,"month_string":"September","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: In adoration of the Holy Trinity, in honour and reparation for all human creatures, I come to you by Divine Order. I come to ask you for more dedication towards the most Holy Trinity so that prayers made 'in spirit and truth' acquire the necessary strength to touch souls, who at this moment need more than before to be touched by prayer made with the heart. I come to call you to consecrate yourselves to our Queen and Mother so that consecrated persons may be constant worshipers of the most holy sacrament of the altar. They need to be love towards their brothers: Respecting the life of others. Helping others with what they need, especially spiritually. Entering him on the path of eternal salvation based on the knowledge of the Holy Scripture so that they are fulfillers of the Law of God and what the law understands. Being fulfillers of the sacraments and of Divine Love, from where you receive the graces to continue. The human creature has not come to understand how in each action he performs, in each work he executes and with each thought, he is the generator of good or evil. The awareness that prayer must be 'prayed\u201d and at the same time put into practice is indispensable at this time. The human creature that puts brotherhood aside enters the danger of being a stumbling block for his fellow men. Be aware that they are kept in the moment to repent and turn to God, pleasing him. Thus, the chains that bind them will be broken and they will be new creatures, converted and convinced. Who does not have faith, cannot preach. Who does not have hope, does not preach hope. Who is not charity, does not preach with charity. Who is not love, does not preach with love. The people of the holy trinity must know that prayer ends with the praxis of what they pray for so that it bears fruit of eternal life. Empty faith is dead and the human creature without love is an empty creature. Those who wish to become part of the people of God must be willing to rise, if necessary, over himself to be in the Divine Way and leave behind the rags of human foolishness so that they live in the constant practice of love for God's will. They have neglected the spiritual state, they have minimized it and they do not want to renew themselves or be possessors of a generous spirit. Materialism has invaded them so much that they do not distinguish when they act out of interest or out of love. Humanity will be informed of the dreaded nuclear bomb and then silence...  They will be informed of the downturn in the economy and food shortages. And the people of God have been converted? Are they a converted people? Humanity will suffer and suffering will be heard by all creation until the Divine hand stops what the human creature has done and they will feel the weight of the Divine hand and the sin they have committed against God. The earth burns and will burn\u2026 The human creature does not cry out to God, but does evil to his fellow man, revolts in the streets and makes of himself an unknown creature due to his aggressiveness. Pray people of God, pray for Italy and France, they suffer for nature. Pray people of God, pray, Argentina cries and in her lament looks at our Queen and Mother of Lujan as she is and has been offended. Pray people of God, pray for Spain, the people rise up and nature scourges them. Pray people of God, pray for Mexico, it shakes, its people suffer and cry. Beloved people of the Holy Trinity: Will the envoy arrive and will he recognize you? He will see so much tyranny in the human heart and suffer like Christ. He will feel the hypocrisy in the human creature and will call them all to him. Convert! I bless you with my sword. I protect you. Saint Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: W adoracji Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, w czci i zado\u015b\u0107uczynieniu za wszystkie stworzenia ludzkie, przychodz\u0119 do was z rozkazu Bo\u017cego. Przychodz\u0119 prosi\u0107 was o wi\u0119ksze oddanie si\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, aby modlitwy zanoszone \"w duchu i prawdzie\" nabra\u0142y niezb\u0119dnej si\u0142y do dotkni\u0119cia dusz, kt\u00f3re w tej chwili bardziej ni\u017c dotychczas potrzebuj\u0105 by\u0107 dotkni\u0119te modlitw\u0105 zanoszon\u0105 sercem. Przychodz\u0119, aby wezwa\u0107 was do po\u015bwi\u0119cenia si\u0119 naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matce, aby osoby konsekrowane by\u0142y sta\u0142ymi czcicielami naj\u015bwi\u0119tszego sakramentu o\u0142tarza. Potrzebna jest im mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 wobec braci: Szanowa\u0107 \u017cycie innych. Pomaga\u0107 innym w tym, czego potrzebuj\u0105, zw\u0142aszcza duchowo. Wchodzi\u0107 mu na drog\u0119 wiecznego zbawienia na podstawie znajomo\u015b\u0107 Pisma \u015awi\u0119tego, aby byli wype\u0142niaczami Prawa Bo\u017cego i tego, co Prawo rozumie. By\u0107 wype\u0142niaczami sakrament\u00f3w i Bo\u017cej Mi\u0142o\u015bci, sk\u0105d otrzymuje si\u0119 \u0142aski do dalszego dzia\u0142ania. Stworzenie ludzkie nie dosz\u0142o do zrozumienia, jak w ka\u017cdym swoim dzia\u0142aniu, w ka\u017cdej pracy, kt\u00f3r\u0105 wykonuje i z ka\u017cd\u0105 my\u015bl\u0105 jest generatorem dobra lub z\u0142a. \u015awiadomo\u015b\u0107, \u017ce modlitwa musi by\u0107 \"odmawiana\" i jednocze\u015bnie wprowadzana w czyn jest w tym czasie niezb\u0119dna. Istota ludzka, kt\u00f3ra odsuwa na bok braterstwo, wchodzi w niebezpiecze\u0144stwo bycia przeszkod\u0105 dla swoich bli\u017anich. B\u0105d\u017acie \u015bwiadomi, \u017ce s\u0105 oni zatrzymani w chwili, w kt\u00f3rej mog\u0105 pokutowa\u0107 i zwr\u00f3ci\u0107 si\u0119 do Boga, podobaj\u0105c si\u0119 Mu. W ten spos\u00f3b \u0142a\u0144cuchy, kt\u00f3re je wi\u0105\u017c\u0105, zostan\u0105 zerwane i b\u0119d\u0105 to nowe stworzenia, nawr\u00f3cone i przekonane. Kto nie ma wiary, nie mo\u017ce g\u0142osi\u0107. Kto nie ma nadziei, nie g\u0142osi nadziei. Kto nie jest mi\u0142osierdziem, nie g\u0142osi z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Kto nie jest mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, nie g\u0142osi z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Lud Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej musi wiedzie\u0107, \u017ce modlitwa ko\u0144czy si\u0119 praktykowaniem tego, o co si\u0119 modli, aby przynosi\u0142o to owoce \u017cycia wiecznego. Pusta wiara jest martwa, a ludzkie stworzenie bez mi\u0142o\u015bci jest pustym stworzeniem. Ci, kt\u00f3rzy chc\u0105 sta\u0107 si\u0119 cz\u0119\u015bci\u0105 ludu Bo\u017cego, musz\u0105 by\u0107 gotowi wznie\u015b\u0107 si\u0119, je\u015bli to konieczne, ponad siebie, aby by\u0107 na Boskiej Drodze i pozostawi\u0107 za sob\u0105 szaty ludzkiej g\u0142upoty, aby \u017cy\u0107 w ci\u0105g\u0142ej praktyce mi\u0142o\u015bci do woli Bo\u017cej. Zaniedbali stan duchowy, zminimalizowali go i nie chc\u0105 si\u0119 odnowi\u0107 ani by\u0107 posiadaczami wielkodusznego ducha. Materializm tak bardzo ich opanowa\u0142, \u017ce nie rozr\u00f3\u017cniaj\u0105, kiedy dzia\u0142aj\u0105 z interesu, a kiedy z mi\u0142o\u015bci. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 zostanie poinformowana o straszliwej bombie atomowej, a potem cisza... Zostan\u0105 poinformowani o spowolnieniu gospodarki i braku \u017cywno\u015bci. A lud Bo\u017cy si\u0119 nawr\u00f3ci\u0142? Czy to jest nawr\u00f3cony lud? Ludzko\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dzie cierpie\u0107 i cierpienie b\u0119dzie s\u0142yszane przez ca\u0142e stworzenie, a\u017c Boska r\u0119ka powstrzyma to, co uczyni\u0142o ludzkie stworzenie i poczuj\u0105 oni ci\u0119\u017car Boskiej r\u0119ki i grzech, kt\u00f3ry pope\u0142nili przeciwko Bogu. Ziemia p\u0142onie i b\u0119dzie p\u0142on\u0105\u0107... Stworzenie ludzkie nie wo\u0142a do Boga, ale czyni z\u0142o bli\u017aniemu, buntuje si\u0119 na ulicach i czyni z siebie nieznane stworzenie z powodu swojej agresywno\u015bci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za W\u0142ochy i Francj\u0119, one cierpi\u0105 za natur\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, Argentyna p\u0142acze i w swoim lamencie patrzy na nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119 Lujan, jak jest i zosta\u0142a obra\u017cona. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Hiszpani\u0119, lud powstaje i natura go biczuje. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 ludu Bo\u017cy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Meksyk, on si\u0119 trz\u0119sie, jego lud cierpi i p\u0142acze. Umi\u0142owany lud Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej: Czy wys\u0142annik przyb\u0119dzie i czy was rozpozna? Zobaczy tyle tyranii w ludzkim sercu i b\u0119dzie cierpia\u0142 jak Chrystus. Poczuje ob\u0142ud\u0119 w ludzkim stworzeniu i wezwie ich wszystkich do siebie. Nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119! B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 ci\u0119 moim mieczem. Ja ci\u0119 chroni\u0119. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":3,"month_string":"October","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart, people of my most beloved Son: I love you; I hold you in my maternal heart so that in my heart you might adore the most Holy Trinity and give thanks for infinite Divine Mercy. People of my Son, this is the time for you to understand that your works and actions must be directed towards the good, setting aside spiritual mediocrity. At this time, human beings want to draw attention to their inner selves in order to stand out, without asking themselves or worrying whether excelling personally elevates them above their brothers and sisters, sometimes leaving them lying on the ground. As Mother I call you to conversion and not to personal interests, for the antichrist and his legions have knocked at the door of humanity and his wickedness has been accepted by the people of my Divine Son. You already feel crisis, you are already living in crisis; you have been through crises and emerged from them, but this crisis will not be overcome until my Divine Son intervenes. All creation has been changed by the hand of man, just as the human heart has changed. This is a time of the heightened influence of the evil one over a humanity that has been altered, that is dissatisfied, incomprehensible, estranged from God and unified in its thinking so as to blaspheme against the most Holy Trinity and against this Mother of humanity. My children, you are being unified in your thinking by means of the different electronic media used by the great powers and which you use in order to communicate. Pay attention, my children: World domination is upon humanity, exerting such a negative influence upon the minds of all, that you will come to work and behave very basely as human beings. People of my Son, entrust yourselves to my Divine Son; invite him to remain with you in all the works or actions of your daily lives; in this way you will remain protected by the most Holy Trinity, by the heavenly legions and by this Mother. The works and deeds of my Son's people must continually tend towards the good in order to hinder negative thoughts, because at this moment human beings are continually beset by negative thoughts that are being sent to them and which are not the fruit of human will. However, since humanity is opposed to my Son and is embracing what is worldly, you are easy prey for evil, which is continually tempting you. To free yourselves from temptation you must do good, think good, want good for yourselves and your brothers and sisters. Do not permit thoughts contrary to fraternity, contrary to love, to self-giving, to adoration towards the most Holy Trinity, to devotion towards all the heavenly choirs and to veneration towards this Mother. Remember, my children: You must subject yourselves to my Son and must continually ask him for the blood and water that flowed from his open side on the cross to be poured out upon you, in order that you would be bearers of good and so that the evil one with his wiles would not penetrate within you. Beloved people of my Son, walk rapidly towards him. Humanity is hanging by a thread and you must save your souls: save your souls! For you will be severely tested by those who wish to display the power of their weaponry over all humanity. Nonetheless, do not fear, my children: my Son will not give you stones for bread - my Son will bring down manna from heaven to sustain his children. Work and act within the good and you will receive the goodness and Divine Blessings necessary for you not to succumb when facing trials. I love you, my children, I cover you with my maternal mantle, I cover you with my love. Give me your hand, do not fear: I am my Son\u2019s disciple and I want you to be so as well. I bless you with my love, I bless you with my yes to God. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca, ludu mojego Syna najukocha\u0144szego: Kocham was; trzymam was w moim matczynym sercu, aby\u015bcie w moim sercu mogli adorowa\u0107 Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105 i dzi\u0119kowa\u0107 za niesko\u0144czone Mi\u0142osierdzie Bo\u017ce. Ludu mojego Syna, jest to czas, aby\u015bcie zrozumieli, \u017ce wasze prace i dzia\u0142ania musz\u0105 by\u0107 skierowane ku dobru, odk\u0142adaj\u0105c na bok duchow\u0105 przeci\u0119tno\u015b\u0107. W tym czasie istoty ludzkie chc\u0105 zwr\u00f3ci\u0107 uwag\u0119 na swoje wn\u0119trze, aby si\u0119 wyr\u00f3\u017cni\u0107, nie zadaj\u0105c sobie pytania ani nie martwi\u0105c si\u0119, czy wybitno\u015b\u0107 osobista wywy\u017csza ich ponad braci i siostry, pozostawiaj\u0105c ich czasem le\u017c\u0105cych na ziemi. Jako Matka wzywam was do nawr\u00f3cenia, a nie do osobistych interes\u00f3w, poniewa\u017c antychryst i jego legiony zapuka\u0142y do drzwi ludzko\u015bci, a jego niegodziwo\u015b\u0107 zosta\u0142a zaakceptowana przez lud mojego Boskiego Syna. Ju\u017c czujecie kryzys, ju\u017c \u017cyjecie w kryzysie; przechodzili\u015bcie kryzysy i wychodzili\u015bcie z nich, ale ten kryzys nie zostanie przezwyci\u0119\u017cony, dop\u00f3ki m\u00f3j Boski Syn nie zainterweniuje. Ca\u0142e stworzenie zosta\u0142o zmienione przez r\u0119k\u0119 cz\u0142owieka, tak jak zmieni\u0142o si\u0119 ludzkie serce. Jest to czas wzmo\u017conego wp\u0142ywu z\u0142ego na ludzko\u015b\u0107, kt\u00f3ra zosta\u0142a zmieniona, kt\u00f3ra jest niezadowolona, niezrozumia\u0142a, oderwana od Boga i zjednoczona w swoim my\u015bleniu, aby blu\u017ani\u0107 przeciwko Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej i przeciwko tej Matce ludzko\u015bci. Moje dzieci, jeste\u015bcie ujednolicani w swoim my\u015bleniu za pomoc\u0105 r\u00f3\u017cnych medi\u00f3w elektronicznych, kt\u00f3rymi pos\u0142uguj\u0105 si\u0119 wielkie mocarstwa i kt\u00f3rych u\u017cywacie do komunikacji. Zwr\u00f3\u0107cie uwag\u0119, moje dzieci: Dominacja \u015bwiatowa jest nad ludzko\u015bci\u0105, wywieraj\u0105c tak negatywny wp\u0142yw na umys\u0142y wszystkich, \u017ce przyjdzie wam pracowa\u0107 i zachowywa\u0107 si\u0119 bardzo zasadniczo jako istoty ludzkie. Ludu mojego Syna, powierzcie si\u0119 mojemu Boskiemu Synowi; zach\u0119cajcie Go, aby by\u0142 z wami we wszystkich pracach i dzia\u0142aniach waszego codziennego \u017cycia; w ten spos\u00f3b pozostaniecie chronieni przez Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105, przez legiony niebieskie i przez t\u0119 Matk\u0119. Dzie\u0142a i czyny ludu mojego Syna musz\u0105 nieustannie zmierza\u0107 ku dobru, aby powstrzyma\u0107 negatywne my\u015bli, poniewa\u017c w tej chwili istoty ludzkie s\u0105 nieustannie n\u0119kane przez negatywne my\u015bli, kt\u00f3re s\u0105 do nich wysy\u0142ane i kt\u00f3re nie s\u0105 owocem ludzkiej woli. Poniewa\u017c jednak ludzko\u015b\u0107 sprzeciwia si\u0119 mojemu Synowi i przyjmuje to, co \u015bwiatowe, jeste\u015bcie \u0142atwym \u0142upem dla z\u0142a, kt\u00f3re nieustannie was kusi. Aby uwolni\u0107 si\u0119 od pokus, musicie czyni\u0107 dobrze, my\u015ble\u0107 dobrze, pragn\u0105\u0107 dobra dla siebie i dla waszych braci. Nie dopuszczajcie my\u015bli przeciwnych braterstwu, przeciwnych mi\u0142o\u015bci, darowi z siebie, adoracji wobec Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, pobo\u017cno\u015bci wobec wszystkich ch\u00f3r\u00f3w niebieskich i czci wobec tej Matki. Pami\u0119tajcie, moje dzieci: Musicie podda\u0107 si\u0119 mojemu Synowi i nieustannie prosi\u0107 Go o wylanie na was krwi i wody, kt\u00f3re wyp\u0142yn\u0119\u0142y z Jego otwartego boku na krzy\u017cu, aby\u015bcie byli nosicielami dobra i aby z\u0142y ze swoimi podst\u0119pami nie przenikn\u0105\u0142 w was. Umi\u0142owani ludu mojego Syna, id\u017acie szybko w Jego kierunku. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 wisi na w\u0142osku i musicie ratowa\u0107 swoje dusze: ratujcie swoje dusze! Zostaniecie bowiem poddani ci\u0119\u017ckiej pr\u00f3bie przez tych, kt\u00f3rzy chc\u0105 pokaza\u0107 moc swojej broni nad ca\u0142\u0105 ludzko\u015bci\u0105. Niemniej jednak nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, moje dzieci: m\u00f3j Syn nie da wam kamieni za chleb - m\u00f3j Syn sprowadzi mann\u0119 z nieba, aby podtrzyma\u0107 swoje dzieci. Pracujcie i dzia\u0142ajcie w ramach dobra, a otrzymacie dobro i Boskie B\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwa niezb\u0119dne do tego, aby\u015bcie nie poddawali si\u0119 w obliczu pr\u00f3b. Kocham was, moje dzieci, okrywam was moim matczynym p\u0142aszczem, okrywam was moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Podajcie mi swoj\u0105 r\u0119k\u0119, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119: jestem uczennic\u0105 mojego Syna i chc\u0119, aby\u015bcie i wy ni\u0105 byli. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moim tak dla Boga. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. ","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":3,"month_string":"October","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My dear children, thank you for being here in prayer and for kneeling down. Blessed children, your humble prayer comforts Me and My Jesus. My children, do not fear for what is to come for I have already spread My Mantle here today and over all who have the true faith. My children, feed yourselves on the body and blood of My Son Jesus, He left it for you, not in remembrance, but in His true and living presence. Children, see to it that the modernism of the Church does not defile you; be faithful to the true Magisterium of the Faith. Jesus is watching you and sending you the Spirit of discernment about what is right, what is of God and what opens the doors to reach into the abyss of Satan. My children, I am with you and will never abandon you. Walk the path of holiness. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit. Then Our Lady added that many graces will descend on those who pray the chaplet to the Most Precious Blood of Jesus.","text_de":"Meine lieben Kinder, danke, dass du hier im Gebet bist und dich niedergekniet. Gesegte Kinder, dein bescheidenes Gebet tr\u00f6stet mich und meinen Jesus. Meine Kinder, f\u00fcrchte nicht, was kommen wird, ich habe meinen Mantel heute und \u00fcber alle, die den wahren Glauben haben, bereits hier verbreitet. Meine Kinder f\u00fcttern sich auf den K\u00f6rper und das Blut meines Sohnes Jesus, er hat es Ihnen hinterlassen, nicht in Erinnerung, sondern in seiner wahren und lebenden Gegenwart. Kinder, sehen Sie, dass die Moderne der Kirche Sie nicht verunreinigt; Sei dem wahren Lehramt des Glaubens treu. Jesus beobachtet dich und sendet dir den Geist der Unterscheidung dar\u00fcber, was richtig ist, was von Gott ist und was die T\u00fcren \u00f6ffnet, um in den Abgrund des Satans zu greifen. Meine Kinder, ich bin bei dir und werde dich niemals verlassen. Gehen Sie den Weg der Heiligkeit. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes. Dann f\u00fcgten unsere Lieben Frau hinzu, dass viele Gnaden auf diejenigen hinabsteigen, die den Chaplet zum kostbarsten Blut Jesu beten.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por haber doblado las rodillas. Los ni\u00f1os de Benedetti, su humilde oraci\u00f3n me consuela a m\u00ed y a mi Jes\u00fas. Mis hijos, no temen lo que vendr\u00e1 porque ya he difundido mi abrigo aqu\u00ed, hoy y de todos aquellos que tienen verdadera fe. Ni\u00f1os, comida del cuerpo y sangre de mi hijo Jes\u00fas, lo dej\u00f3 por ti, no en la memoria, sino en su presencia verdadera y viva. Ni\u00f1o, aseg\u00farese de que el modernismo de la iglesia no lo contamine, sea fiel al verdadero magisterio de la fe. Jes\u00fas te mira y te env\u00eda el esp\u00edritu de discernimiento sobre lo que es correcto, que es de Dios y lo que abre las puertas para llegar al abismo de Satan\u00e1s. Mis hijos, estoy contigo y nunca te abandonar\u00e9. Viaja por el camino de la santidad. Ahora te bendiga en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo. Luego, la Madonna agreg\u00f3 que muchas gracias pasar\u00e1n a quienes rezar\u00e1n a la corona a la preciosa sangre de Jes\u00fas.","text_fr":"Mes chers enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re et de s'agenouiller. Enfants b\u00e9nis, votre humble pri\u00e8re r\u00e9conforte moi et mon J\u00e9sus. Mes enfants, ne craignez pas ce qui est \u00e0 venir car j'ai d\u00e9j\u00e0 diffus\u00e9 mon manteau ici aujourd'hui et \u00e0 tous ceux qui ont la vraie foi. Mes enfants, vous nourrissez du corps et du sang de mon fils J\u00e9sus, il l'a laiss\u00e9 pour vous, non pas en souvenir, mais dans sa pr\u00e9sence vraie et vivante. Les enfants, veillent \u00e0 ce que le modernisme de l'\u00c9glise ne vous soul\u00e8ve pas; Soyez fid\u00e8le au vrai magist\u00e8re de la foi. J\u00e9sus vous regarde et vous envoie l'esprit de discernement sur ce qui est juste, ce qui est de Dieu et ce qui ouvre les portes \u00e0 atteindre dans l'ab\u00eeme de Satan. Mes enfants, je suis avec vous et je ne vous abandonnerai jamais. Suivre le chemin de la saintet\u00e9. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit. Ensuite, Notre-Dame a ajout\u00e9 que de nombreuses gr\u00e2ces descendent sur ceux qui prient le chaplet au sang le plus pr\u00e9cieux de J\u00e9sus.","text_it":"Cari figli miei, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia. Figli benedetti, la vostra umile preghiera conforta me e il mio Ges\u00f9. Figli miei, non temete per ci\u00f2 che arriver\u00e0 perch\u00e9 Io ho gi\u00e0 steso il Mio Manto qui, oggi e su tutti coloro che hanno la vera fede. Figli, cibatevi del corpo e del sangue di mio Figlio Ges\u00f9, Lui lo ha lasciato per voi, non nel ricordo, ma nella sua presenza vera e viva. Figli, fate in modo che il modernismo della Chiesa non vi contamini, siate fedeli al vero magistero della Fede. Ges\u00f9 vi guarda e vi manda lo Spirito di discernimento su ci\u00f2 che \u00e8 giusto, che \u00e8 di Dio e su ci\u00f2 che apre le porte per arrivare nell\u2019abisso di Satana. Figli miei, Io sono con voi e non vi abbandoner\u00f2 mai. Percorrete la via della santit\u00e0. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo. Poi la Madonna ha aggiunto che scenderanno tante grazie su coloro che pregheranno la coroncina al preziosissimo sangue di Ges\u00f9.","text_pl":"Moje drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj na modlitwie i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie. B\u0142ogos\u0142awione dzieci, wasza pokorna modlitwa pociesza mnie i mojego Jezusa. Moje dzieci, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119 o to, co ma nadej\u015b\u0107, poniewa\u017c Ja ju\u017c rozpostar\u0142am M\u00f3j P\u0142aszcz teraz, tutaj i nad wszystkimi, kt\u00f3rzy maj\u0105 prawdziw\u0105 wiar\u0119. Moje dzieci, karmcie si\u0119 Cia\u0142em i Krwi\u0105 mojego Syna Jezusa, On zostawi\u0142 je dla was nie na pami\u0105tk\u0119, ale dla swojej prawdziwej i \u017cywej obecno\u015bci. Moje dzieci, dopilnujcie, aby modernizm Ko\u015bcio\u0142a nie splugawi\u0142 was, b\u0105d\u017acie wierni prawdziwemu Magisterium Wiary. Jezus obserwuje ci\u0119 i posy\u0142a ci Ducha rozeznania tego, co jest w\u0142a\u015bciwe, co jest z Boga, a tego, co otwiera drzwi do otch\u0142ani szatana. Moje dzieci, jestem z wami i nigdy was nie opuszcz\u0119. Id\u017acie drog\u0105 \u015bwi\u0119to\u015bci. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego. Nast\u0119pnie Matka Bo\u017ca doda\u0142a, \u017ce na tych, kt\u00f3rzy odmawiaj\u0105 koronk\u0119 do Najdro\u017cszej Krwi Pana Jezusa, zst\u0105pi wiele \u0142ask.","text_pt":"Meus queridos filhos, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por se ajoelhar. Filhos aben\u00e7oados, sua humilde ora\u00e7\u00e3o conforta a mim e ao meu Jesus. Meus filhos, n\u00e3o temem o que est\u00e1 por vir, eu j\u00e1 espalhei meu manto aqui hoje e sobre todos os que t\u00eam a verdadeira f\u00e9. Meus filhos, alimentam -se com o corpo e o sangue do meu filho Jesus, ele deixou para voc\u00ea, n\u00e3o em lembran\u00e7a, mas em sua presen\u00e7a verdadeira e viva. Filhos, para que o modernismo da igreja n\u00e3o o perverse; Seja fiel ao verdadeiro magist\u00e9rio da f\u00e9. Jesus est\u00e1 observando voc\u00ea e enviando o esp\u00edrito de discernimento sobre o que \u00e9 certo, o que \u00e9 de Deus e o que abre as portas para alcan\u00e7ar o abismo de Satan\u00e1s. Meus filhos, estou com voc\u00ea e nunca vou te abandonar. Ande o caminho da santidade. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo. Ent\u00e3o Nossa Senhora acrescentou que muitas gra\u00e7as descerem sobre aqueles que oram o chapelar ao sangue mais precioso de Jesus.","text_zh":"\u6211\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\u548c\u8dea\u4e0b\u3002\u795d\u798f\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4f60\u8c26\u865a\u7684\u7948\u7977\u5b89\u6170\u6211\u548c\u6211\u7684\u8036\u7a23\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u62c5\u5fc3\u4f1a\u53d1\u751f\u4ec0\u4e48\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u4eca\u5929\u5df2\u7ecf\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u548c\u6240\u6709\u5177\u6709\u771f\u6b63\u4fe1\u4ef0\u7684\u4eba\u90fd\u6563\u5e03\u4e86\u6211\u7684\u5730\u5e54\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u517b\u6d3b\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u7684\u8eab\u4f53\u548c\u9c9c\u8840\uff0c\u4ed6\u628a\u5b83\u7559\u7ed9\u4f60\uff0c\u4e0d\u662f\u7eaa\u5ff5\u7684\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u5728\u4ed6\u771f\u5b9e\u800c\u6d3b\u7684\u5b58\u5728\u4e0b\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8bf7\u6ce8\u610f\uff0c\u6559\u4f1a\u7684\u73b0\u4ee3\u4e3b\u4e49\u4e0d\u4f1ade\u6bc1\u4f60\u3002\u5fe0\u4e8e\u4fe1\u4ef0\u7684\u771f\u6b63\u6742\u5fd7\u3002\u8036\u7a23\u5728\u770b\u7740\u4f60\uff0c\u5411\u4f60\u53d1\u9001\u4e86\u5173\u4e8e\u4ec0\u4e48\u662f\u6b63\u786e\u7684\uff0c\u4ec0\u4e48\u662f\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u7cbe\u795e\uff0c\u4ee5\u53ca\u6253\u5f00\u95e8\u7684\u4e1c\u897f\u8fdb\u5165\u6492\u65e6\u7684\u6df1\u6e0a\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u548c\u4f60\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\uff0c\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u4f1a\u629b\u5f03\u4f60\u3002\u8d70\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u9053\u8def\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002\u7136\u540e\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u592b\u4eba\u8865\u5145\u8bf4\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u6069\u8d50\u5c06\u964d\u843d\u5728\u90a3\u4e9b\u7948\u7977\u8036\u7a23\u6700\u5b9d\u8d35\u4e4b\u8840\u7684\u4eba\u8eab\u4e0a\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":7,"month_string":"October","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear blessed children, thank you for being here and for kneeling in prayer. My children, I am the Queen of the Rosary, of heaven and earth and I ask you to intensify the recitation of rosaries and pray together with the children, protect yourselves from the evil that grips the world. My children, pray for Korea, pray for the rulers who are making wrong decisions, pray for the holy priests massacred by attacks. My children, I ask you to Consecrate yourselves to my Immaculate Heart, for your protection. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe gesegnete Kinder, danke, dass Sie hier sind und im Gebet knien. Meine Kinder, ich bin die K\u00f6nigin des Rosenkranzes, des Himmels und der Erde und ich bitte Sie, die Rezitation von Rosenkr\u00e4nzen zu intensivieren und zusammen mit den Kindern zu beten, sich vor dem B\u00f6sen zu sch\u00fctzen, das die Welt greift. Meine Kinder, beten f\u00fcr Korea, beten f\u00fcr die Herrscher, die falsche Entscheidungen treffen, beten f\u00fcr die heiligen Priester, die durch Angriffe massakriert werden. Meine Kinder, ich bitte Sie, sich f\u00fcr Ihren Schutz an mein makelloses Herz zu weihen. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos ni\u00f1os benditos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed y por haber doblado las rodillas en oraci\u00f3n. Mis hijos, soy la reina del rosario, del cielo y la tierra y les pido que intensifique la recitaci\u00f3n de los rosarios y reza con los ni\u00f1os, prot\u00e9gase del mal que se ajusta al mundo. Los ni\u00f1os, rezan por Corea, rezan por los gobernantes que est\u00e1n tomando decisiones equivocadas, rezan por los santos sacerdotes masacrados por los ataques. Mis hijos, les pido que lo consagren para mi coraz\u00f3n inmaculado para su protecci\u00f3n. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants b\u00e9nis, merci d'\u00eatre ici et d'\u00eatre \u00e0 genoux dans la pri\u00e8re. Mes enfants, je suis la reine du chapelet, du ciel et de la terre et je vous demande d'intensifier la r\u00e9citation des chapelets et de prier avec les enfants, de vous prot\u00e9ger du mal qui saisit le monde. Mes enfants, priez pour la Cor\u00e9e, priez pour les dirigeants qui prennent de mauvaises d\u00e9cisions, priez pour les saints pr\u00eatres massacr\u00e9s par des attaques. Mes enfants, je vous demande de vous consacrer \u00e0 mon c\u0153ur immacul\u00e9, pour votre protection. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli Benedetti, grazie per essere qui e per aver piegato le ginocchia nella preghiera. Figli miei, Io sono la Regina del Rosario, del cielo e della terra e vi chiedo di intensificare la recita dei rosari e pregate insieme ai bambini, proteggetevi dal male che attanaglia il mondo. Figli, pregate per la Corea, pregate per i governanti che stanno prendendo decisioni sbagliate, pregate per i santi sacerdoti massacrati dagli attacchi. Figli miei, vi chiedo di Consacrarvi al mio Cuore Immacolato, per la vostra protezione. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie b\u0142ogos\u0142awione dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie do modlitwy. Moje dzieci, jestem Kr\u00f3low\u0105 R\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ca, nieba i ziemi, i prosz\u0119 was, aby\u015bcie zintensyfikowali odmawianie r\u00f3\u017ca\u0144c\u00f3w i modl\u0105c si\u0119 razem z dzie\u0107mi, chronili si\u0119 przed z\u0142em, kt\u00f3re ogarnia \u015bwiat. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Kore\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za rz\u0105dz\u0105cych, kt\u00f3rzy podejmuj\u0105 z\u0142e decyzje, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za \u015bwi\u0119tych kap\u0142an\u00f3w zmasakrowanych atakami. Moje dzieci, prosz\u0119 was, aby\u015bcie po\u015bwi\u0119cili si\u0119 mojemu Niepokalanemu Sercu, dla waszej ochrony. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos aben\u00e7oados, obrigado por estar aqui e por ajoelhar -se em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, sou a rainha do ros\u00e1rio, do c\u00e9u e da terra e pe\u00e7o que voc\u00ea intensifique a recita\u00e7\u00e3o de ros\u00e1rios e ore junto com as crian\u00e7as, protege -se do mal que segura o mundo. Meus filhos, oram pela Cor\u00e9ia, orem pelos governantes que est\u00e3o tomando decis\u00f5es erradas, orem pelos sagrados sacerdotes massacrados por ataques. Meus filhos, pe\u00e7o que voc\u00ea se consagre ao meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o imaculado, para sua prote\u00e7\u00e3o. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u795d\u798f\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u5e76\u8dea\u7740\u7948\u7977\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u662f\u5ff5\u73e0\u7684\u7687\u540e\uff0c\u5929\u5730\u7684\u5973\u738b\uff0c\u6211\u8bf7\u60a8\u52a0\u5f3a\u5ff5\u73e0\u7684\u6717\u8bf5\uff0c\u5e76\u4e0e\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u4e00\u8d77\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4fdd\u62a4\u81ea\u5df1\u514d\u53d7\u4e16\u754c\u906d\u53d7\u4e16\u754c\u7684\u90aa\u6076\u7684\u4fb5\u5bb3\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u4e3a\u97e9\u56fd\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4e3a\u505a\u51fa\u9519\u8bef\u51b3\u5b9a\u7684\u7edf\u6cbb\u8005\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4e3a\u88ab\u88ad\u51fb\u5c60\u6740\u7684\u5723\u6bcd\u7948\u7977\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u8981\u4f60\u5949\u732e\u81ea\u5df1\u7684\u5fc3\u810f\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fdd\u62a4\u81ea\u5df1\uff0c\u4ee5\u4fdd\u62a4\u81ea\u5df1\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":10,"month_string":"October","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My people, I love you... How much I love you! My people, you are loved by me. I come to examine you and to look at you in your actions.... Therefore, remain in conversion. So much rebellion of my people is the cause of the disasters on earth and yet some of my children do not want to look at what is happening? They are more foolish than foolishness itself! Until they find themselves drowning in lamentations, they will cry out to me. At this moment they do not wish to pray or visit me, they despise me, they live without needing me, humanity has thrown itself over the precipice and will reap the fruit of its foolishness, of its distance from my home. My people, blood is life, but the blood reflected in the moon is the announcement of the suffering of mankind. The blood moons have been seen as a spectacle and I must tell you that the past blood moons and the one you will see again presages the terrible suffering that humanity will face at this climactic moment. The red moon came dressed as a hunter, thus giving relevance to the very painful event of the use of nuclear energy. The hunter will act unceremoniously at the moment you least expect. My beloved people, from that blood moon called 'the hunter', the war takes another course. Pray, work and act desiring good for your brothers, however, you must first change yourselves so that you may give what you carry within. My people, the world economy is suffering a serious downturn. I call you to prayer so that inner peace may lead you to the clarity of what is happening. You will not attain inner peace without my presence in you. Hunters know where to hunt, that is why they draw their plans in advance. My children, my people: They will make use of nuclear energy and once these devices of the devil himself have been exploited, silence will overcome you, fear will seize you before the arrival of the announced events. Natural resources will be contaminated... The food will be contaminated... Winter will strike and my people, confronted with one another, worse than predatory animals, will make the life of my children a constant challenge. Attention my children! The threat of war is no longer a threat and my people will suffer. I call you to prepare and help those who cannot prepare. My House will provide for the one who possesses nothing. Pray my children, pray, pay attention for China will make an unexpected leap. Pray my children, pray for Taiwan. Pray my children, pray for the leaders of Russia. Pray my children, pray for the leaders of the United States. Pray my children, pray for the leaders of Ukraine. As mankind you are in grave danger and those who have not believed my words, which I have previously told you what would happen, I call you to believe at this time and to convert. I await you as a loving father. The human creature is dominated. This is my final call for you to prepare materially! Those who cannot prepare, I will provide for them. The demons lie in wait and St. Michael fights them. Be attentive, my children, be attentive! Be children worthy of me. Pray, cry out, come to me. My blessings with you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludu m\u00f3j, kocham ci\u0119... Jak bardzo was kocham! M\u00f3j ludu, jeste\u015b przeze mnie kochany. Przychodz\u0119, aby was zbada\u0107 i spojrze\u0107 na was w waszych dzia\u0142aniach.... Dlatego trwajcie w nawr\u00f3ceniu. Tak wiele buntu mojego ludu jest przyczyn\u0105 nieszcz\u0119\u015b\u0107 na ziemi, a jednak niekt\u00f3re z moich dzieci nie chc\u0105 patrze\u0107 na to, co si\u0119 dzieje? S\u0105 bardziej g\u0142upi ni\u017c sama g\u0142upota! Dop\u00f3ki nie stwierdz\u0105, \u017ce ton\u0105 w lamentach, b\u0119d\u0105 wo\u0142a\u0107 do Mnie. W tej chwili nie chc\u0105 si\u0119 modli\u0107 ani Mnie odwiedza\u0107, gardz\u0105 Mn\u0105, \u017cyj\u0105, nie potrzebuj\u0105c Mnie, ludzko\u015b\u0107 rzuci\u0142a si\u0119 nad przepa\u015bci\u0105 i b\u0119dzie zbiera\u0107 owoce swojej g\u0142upoty, swojego oddalenia od mojego domu. M\u00f3j ludu, krew jest \u017cyciem, ale krew odbita w ksi\u0119\u017cycu jest zapowiedzi\u0105 cierpienia ludzko\u015bci. Krwawe ksi\u0119\u017cyce by\u0142y postrzegane jako widowisko i musz\u0119 wam powiedzie\u0107, \u017ce przesz\u0142e krwawe ksi\u0119\u017cyce i ten, kt\u00f3ry zobaczycie ponownie, zapowiadaj\u0105 straszne cierpienie, z kt\u00f3rym ludzko\u015b\u0107 zmierzy si\u0119 w tym kulminacyjnym momencie. Czerwony ksi\u0119\u017cyc przyby\u0142 w stroju my\u015bliwego, nadaj\u0105c tym samym znaczenie bardzo bolesnemu wydarzeniu wykorzystania energii j\u0105drowej. My\u015bliwy zadzia\u0142a bezceremonialnie w momencie, kt\u00f3rego najmniej si\u0119 spodziewacie. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, od tego krwawego ksi\u0119\u017cyca zwanego \"my\u015bliwym\", wojna obiera inny kurs. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, pracujcie i dzia\u0142ajcie, pragn\u0105c dobra dla waszych braci, jednak najpierw musicie zmieni\u0107 siebie, aby\u015bcie mogli da\u0107 to, co nosicie w sobie. M\u00f3j ludu, gospodarka \u015bwiatowa prze\u017cywa powa\u017cny spadek. Wzywam was do modlitwy, aby wewn\u0119trzny pok\u00f3j doprowadzi\u0142 was do jasno\u015bci tego, co si\u0119 dzieje. Nie osi\u0105gniecie wewn\u0119trznego pokoju bez mojej obecno\u015bci w was. My\u015bliwi wiedz\u0105, gdzie maj\u0105 polowa\u0107, dlatego z wyprzedzeniem kre\u015bl\u0105 swoje plany. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3j lud: Wykorzystaj\u0105 energi\u0119 j\u0105drow\u0105 i gdy te urz\u0105dzenia samego diab\u0142a zostan\u0105 wyeksploatowane, cisza was ogarnie, strach zaw\u0142adnie wami przed nadej\u015bciem zapowiedzianych wydarze\u0144. Zasoby naturalne zostan\u0105 ska\u017cone... \u017bywno\u015b\u0107 zostanie ska\u017cona... Uderzy zima, a M\u00f3j lud, skonfrontowany ze sob\u0105, gorszy od drapie\u017cnych zwierz\u0105t, uczyni \u017cycie Moich dzieci nieustannym wyzwaniem. Uwaga moje dzieci! Nie ma ju\u017c gro\u017aby wojny i m\u00f3j lud b\u0119dzie cierpia\u0142. Wzywam was do przygotowania i pomocy tym, kt\u00f3rzy nie mog\u0105 si\u0119 przygotowa\u0107. M\u00f3j Dom zaopatrzy tego, kt\u00f3ry nic nie posiada. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, zwracajcie uwag\u0119 na to, \u017ce Chiny dokonaj\u0105 niespodziewanego skoku. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Tajwan. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za przyw\u00f3dc\u00f3w Rosji. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za przyw\u00f3dc\u00f3w Stan\u00f3w Zjednoczonych. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za przyw\u00f3dc\u00f3w Ukrainy. Jako ludzko\u015b\u0107 jeste\u015bcie w powa\u017cnym niebezpiecze\u0144stwie i ci, kt\u00f3rzy nie uwierzyli moim s\u0142owom, o kt\u00f3rych wcze\u015bniej m\u00f3wi\u0142em, co si\u0119 stanie, wzywam was, aby\u015bcie w tym czasie uwierzyli i nawr\u00f3cili si\u0119. Czekam na was jako kochaj\u0105cy ojciec. Ludzkie stworzenie jest zdominowane. To jest moje ostateczne wezwanie dla was, aby\u015bcie przygotowali si\u0119 materialnie! Tych, kt\u00f3rzy nie mog\u0105 si\u0119 przygotowa\u0107, Ja im zapewni\u0119. Demony czyhaj\u0105, a \u015bw. Micha\u0142 z nimi walczy. B\u0105d\u017acie uwa\u017cni, moje dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie uwa\u017cni! B\u0105d\u017acie dzie\u0107mi godnymi mnie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, wo\u0142ajcie, przychod\u017acie do mnie. Moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo z wami. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":11,"month_string":"October","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children. thank you for answering my call in your hearts and for kneeling in prayer. My children, how much my heart aches for humanity that is in the balance. My children, you who are the awakened ones, awaken the consciences of your brothers and pray for your souls. Humanity has changed love to hate, prayer to blasphemy, the gift that God left for you (the Eucharist) is now something without meaning. Children, this is the time of grace and many will be the miracles that will happen, pray for God to have mercy. The great powers are attacking each other because of the proximity of so many demons, who are leading them to the great war. Italy will go hungry, but you, my children, be united always in the name of the Lord and trust only in Him, for only in Him will be the victory. Make cenacles of prayer also in your families, consecrate yourselves to my Immaculate Heart and I will protect you. My children, you are attracted by false lights and great inventions, but when everything collapses, the disappointment will be enormous, open your hearts and pray. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder. Vielen Dank, dass Sie meinen Anruf in Ihren Herzen beantwortet und im Gebet knien. Meine Kinder, wie sehr mein Herz f\u00fcr die Menschheit schmerzt, die im Gleichgewicht ist. Meine Kinder, Sie, die die Erwachten sind, erweckten das Gewissen Ihrer Br\u00fcder und beten f\u00fcr Ihre Seelen. Die Menschheit hat die Liebe zu Hass ver\u00e4ndert, das Gebet in Blasphemie, das Geschenk, das Gott f\u00fcr Sie (die Eucharistie) hinterlassen hat, ist jetzt etwas ohne Bedeutung. Kinder, dies ist die Zeit der Gnade und viele werden die Wunder sein, die passieren werden, beten, dass Gott Barmherzigkeit hat. Die Gro\u00dfm\u00e4chte greifen sich aufgrund der N\u00e4he von so vielen D\u00e4monen an, die sie zum Ersten Weltkrieg f\u00fchren. Italien wird hungrig werden, aber Sie, meine Kinder, werden immer im Namen des Herrn vereint und vertrauen nur in ihm, denn nur in ihm wird der Sieg sein. Machen Sie auch in Ihren Familien Cenakles des Gebets, weihen Sie sich meinem makellosen Herzen und ich werde Sie besch\u00fctzen. Meine Kinder, Sie werden von falschen Lichtern und gro\u00dfen Erfindungen angezogen, aber wenn alles zusammenbricht, wird die Entt\u00e4uschung enorm sein, Ihre Herzen \u00f6ffnen und beten. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos. Gracias por responder mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n y por haber doblado las rodillas en oraci\u00f3n. Mis hijos, cu\u00e1nto sufre mi coraz\u00f3n por la humanidad que est\u00e1 en equilibrio. Ni\u00f1os, ustedes que son los despiertos, despiertan las conciencias de sus hermanos y rezan por sus almas. La humanidad ha cambiado el amor con el odio, la oraci\u00f3n con blasfemia, el regalo que ha dejado a Dios por ti (la Eucarist\u00eda), ahora es algo sin sentido. Ni\u00f1os, este es el momento de la gracia y muchos ser\u00e1n los milagros que suceder\u00e1n, rezan para que Dios tenga piedad. Las grandes potencias est\u00e1n atacando juntas debido a la proximidad de muchos demonios, que los est\u00e1n guiando a la Gran Guerra. Italia sufrir\u00e1 de hambre, pero ustedes, mis hijos, siempre se unir\u00e1n en nombre del Se\u00f1or y confiar\u00e1n solo en \u00e9l, porque solo en \u00e9l ser\u00e1 la victoria. Haz cenacles de oraci\u00f3n tambi\u00e9n en familias, consagrate a mi coraz\u00f3n inmaculado y te proteger\u00e9. Ni\u00f1os, se siente atra\u00eddo por las falsas luces y grandes inventos, pero cuando todo se derrumbe, la decepci\u00f3n ser\u00e1 enorme, abrir\u00e1 el coraz\u00f3n y reza. Ahora los bendiga, en el nombre del Padre, del Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants. Merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs et de s'agenouiller dans la pri\u00e8re. Mes enfants, combien mon c\u0153ur fait mal pour l'humanit\u00e9 qui est dans l'\u00e9quilibre. Mes enfants, vous qui \u00eates \u00e9veill\u00e9s, \u00e9veillez la conscience de vos fr\u00e8res et priez pour vos \u00e2mes. L'humanit\u00e9 a chang\u00e9 l'amour pour la haine, la pri\u00e8re en blasph\u00e8me, le don que Dieu a laiss\u00e9 pour vous (l'Eucharistie) est maintenant quelque chose sans sens. Enfants, c'est le moment de la gr\u00e2ce et beaucoup seront les miracles qui se produiront, prieront pour que Dieu ait piti\u00e9. Les grands pouvoirs s'attaquent mutuellement \u00e0 cause de la proximit\u00e9 de tant de d\u00e9mons, qui les m\u00e8nent \u00e0 la Grande Guerre. L'Italie aura faim, mais vous, mes enfants, serez toujours unis au nom du Seigneur et ne vous faites confiance qu'en lui, car seulement en lui sera la victoire. Faites \u00e9galement des cenacles de pri\u00e8re dans vos familles, consacrez-vous \u00e0 mon c\u0153ur immacul\u00e9 et je vous prot\u00e9gerai. Mes enfants, vous \u00eates attir\u00e9 par de fausses lumi\u00e8res et de grandes inventions, mais quand tout s'effondrera, la d\u00e9ception sera \u00e9norme, ouvrez vos c\u0153urs et priez. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei. grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore e per aver piegato le ginocchia nella preghiera. Figli miei, quanto soffre il mio cuore per l\u2019umanit\u00e0 che si trova in bilico. Figli, voi che siete i risvegliati, risvegliate le coscienze dei vostri fratelli e pregate per le vostre anime. L\u2019umanit\u00e0 ha cambiato l\u2019amore con l\u2019odio, la preghiera con la bestemmia, il dono che ha lasciato Dio per voi ( l\u2019Eucarestia), ormai \u00e8 qualcosa senza significato. Figli, questo \u00e8 il tempo di grazia e tanti saranno i miracoli che accadranno, pregate affinch\u00e9 Dio abbia misericordia. Le grandi potenze si stanno attaccando tra loro a causa della vicinanza di tanti demoni, che li stanno guidando alla grande guerra. L\u2019Italia patir\u00e0 la fame, ma voi, figli miei, siate uniti sempre nel nome del Signore e fidatevi solo di Lui, perch\u00e9 solo in Lui sar\u00e0 la vittoria. Fate cenacoli di preghiera anche nelle famiglie, consacratevi al mio Cuore Immacolato ed Io vi protegger\u00f2. Figli, siete attratti da false luci e da grandi invenzioni, ma quando tutto croller\u00e0, la delusione sar\u00e0 enorme, aprite il cuore e pregate. Ora vi benedico, nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo,amen.","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach i \u017ce ukl\u0119kn\u0119li\u015bcie do modlitwy. Moje dzieci, jak bardzo moje serce boli z powodu ludzko\u015bci, kt\u00f3ra jest w zawieszeniu. Moje dzieci, wy, kt\u00f3rzy jeste\u015bcie przebudzeni, obud\u017acie sumienia waszych braci i m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za wasze dusze. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 zamieni\u0142a mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 na nienawi\u015b\u0107, modlitw\u0119 na blu\u017anierstwo, dar, kt\u00f3ry B\u00f3g zostawi\u0142 dla ciebie (Eucharystia), jest teraz czym\u015b bez znaczenia. Moje dzieci, to jest czas \u0142aski i wiele cud\u00f3w si\u0119 wydarzy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, aby B\u00f3g si\u0119 zmi\u0142owa\u0142. Wielkie mocarstwa atakuj\u0105 si\u0119 wzajemnie z powodu blisko\u015bci tak wielu demon\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re prowadz\u0105 je do wielkiej wojny. W\u0142ochy b\u0119d\u0105 g\u0142odne, ale wy, moje dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie zawsze zjednoczeni w imi\u0119 Pana i ufajcie tylko Jemu, bo tylko w Nim b\u0119dzie zwyci\u0119stwo. Tw\u00f3rzcie kr\u0119gi modlitewne tak\u017ce w waszych rodzinach, po\u015bwi\u0119\u0107cie si\u0119 mojemu Niepokalanemu Sercu, a Ja b\u0119d\u0119 was chroni\u0107. Moje dzieci, przyci\u0105gaj\u0105 was fa\u0142szywe \u015bwiat\u0142a i wielkie wynalazki, ale kiedy wszystko si\u0119 zawali, rozczarowanie b\u0119dzie ogromne, otw\u00f3rzcie swoje serca i m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. A teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Minhas crian\u00e7as. Obrigado por atender meu chamado em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e por ajoelhar -se em ora\u00e7\u00e3o. Meus filhos, quanto meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o d\u00f3i pela humanidade que est\u00e1 em equil\u00edbrio. Meus filhos, voc\u00eas que s\u00e3o os despertados, despertam as consci\u00eancias de seus irm\u00e3os e oram por suas almas. A humanidade mudou o amor ao \u00f3dio, a ora\u00e7\u00e3o para a blasf\u00eamia, o presente que Deus deixou para voc\u00ea (a Eucaristia) agora \u00e9 algo sem significado. Filhos, este \u00e9 o tempo da gra\u00e7a e muitos ser\u00e3o os milagres que acontecer\u00e3o, orar\u00e3o para que Deus tenha miseric\u00f3rdia. Os grandes poderes est\u00e3o se atacando por causa da proximidade de tantos dem\u00f4nios, que os est\u00e3o levando \u00e0 Grande Guerra. A It\u00e1lia passar\u00e1 fome, mas voc\u00eas, meus filhos, estar\u00e3o sempre unidos em nome do Senhor e confiam apenas nele, pois apenas nele ser\u00e1 a vit\u00f3ria. Fa\u00e7a cen\u00e1culos de ora\u00e7\u00e3o tamb\u00e9m em suas fam\u00edlias, consagram -se ao meu cora\u00e7\u00e3o imaculado e eu o protegerei. Meus filhos, voc\u00ea \u00e9 atra\u00eddo por luzes falsas e \u00f3timas inven\u00e7\u00f5es, mas quando tudo desmorona, a decep\u00e7\u00e3o ser\u00e1 enorme, abrir\u00e1 seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es e orar\u00e1. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u3002\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u7b54\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\uff0c\u5e76\u8dea\u5728\u7948\u7977\u4e2d\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5fc3\u5bf9\u4eba\u7c7b\u7684\u75db\u82e6\u6709\u591a\u5927\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u60a8\u662f\u89c9\u9192\u7684\u4eba\uff0c\u5524\u9192\u4e86\u60a8\u5144\u5f1f\u7684\u826f\u5fc3\uff0c\u5e76\u4e3a\u60a8\u7684\u7075\u9b42\u7948\u7977\u3002\u4eba\u7c7b\u5df2\u7ecf\u6539\u53d8\u4e86\u7231\u7684\u4ec7\u6068\uff0c\u5411\u4eb5\u6e0e\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7559\u7ed9\u4f60\u7684\u793c\u7269\uff08\u5723\u4f53\u5723\u4e8b\uff09\u73b0\u5728\u6ca1\u6709\u610f\u4e49\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8fd9\u662f\u6069\u5178\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u5c06\u662f\u5c06\u4f1a\u53d1\u751f\u7684\u5947\u8ff9\uff0c\u7948\u6c42\u4e0a\u5e1d\u601c\u60af\u3002\u4f1f\u5927\u7684\u529b\u91cf\u662f\u56e0\u4e3a\u5982\u6b64\u4f17\u591a\u7684\u6076\u9b54\u7684\u63a5\u8fd1\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u5e26\u9886\u4ed6\u4eec\u9677\u5165\u4e86\u4f1f\u5927\u7684\u6218\u4e89\u3002\u610f\u5927\u5229\u4f1a\u997f\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u60a8\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u603b\u662f\u4ee5\u4e3b\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u56e2\u7ed3\u8d77\u6765\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u5bf9\u4ed6\u7684\u4fe1\u4efb\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u53ea\u6709\u4ed6\u624d\u662f\u80dc\u5229\u3002\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5bb6\u4eba\u4e2d\u4e5f\u8981\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5c06\u81ea\u5df1\u5949\u732e\u7ed9\u6211\u5b8c\u7f8e\u65e0\u7f3a\u7684\u5fc3\uff0c\u6211\u5c06\u4fdd\u62a4\u60a8\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u60a8\u88ab\u865a\u5047\u7684\u706f\u5149\u548c\u51fa\u8272\u7684\u53d1\u660e\u6240\u5438\u5f15\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u5f53\u4e00\u5207\u5d29\u6e83\u65f6\uff0c\u5931\u671b\u5c06\u662f\u5de8\u5927\u7684\uff0c\u655e\u5f00\u5fc3hearts\u5e76\u7948\u7977\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":16,"month_string":"October","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of my King and Lord Jesus Christ, as prince of the heavenly legions, I am sent to inform you that. The time has now come!... As decreed beforehand by the most Holy Trinity and mentioned to you. Beloved children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, the earth is shaking from the depths, amplifying the fault lines that create earthquakes. The earth has always shaken in one place or another, but you cannot deny that at this time the movements are more frequent and volcanic eruptions are intensifying because of the movements of the earth. Be warned about false doctrines: The law of God cannot be changed; the mystical body of our King and Lord Jesus Christ is aware that the law of God is one, and only in the cross and in unity can you grasp the dimensions of the Divine Will. Faithful people, it is necessary for you to go from a mediocre spiritual life to living spirituality in its fullness by faith. The people of God must have firm faith at this time when de-Christianisation is increasingly progressing. The human race\u2019s respect for the Divine has fallen very low, and this will generate the great persecution towards the people of God. For this reason, it is necessary for human beings to have faith and understanding, so that they would be steadfast in prayer; without prayer there is no fusion with the most Holy Trinity. Prayer is necessary, and as prince of the heavenly legions I assure you that every supplication raised with a contrite heart is accepted by the most Holy Trinity and by our Queen and Mother of the last times. Receive the Body and Blood of our King and Lord Jesus Christ and be faithful to the true magisterium of the Church of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Children of the most Holy Trinity: It is time for you to live the faith in fullness without fear, without anxiety, without stumbling as the war cry advances, and without forgetting that peace treaties are not peace, but preteens by the nations in order to prepare themselves more and to reach this point. Faith, people of God! Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: The Warning is near, just as war is near... Pray as god\u2019s people: pray the holy rosary - it is one of the prayers in which, together with our King and Lord Jesus Christ and with our Queen and Mother, you retrace the life, passion, death and resurrection of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Pray, pray. In the House of God praises are to be proclaimed to the most Holy Trinity and to our Queen and Mother of the End Times, and the holy rosary is to be proclaimed in the face of the threats that humanity is facing due to the proximity of a celestial body that is approaching the earth. Pray, children of the most Holy Trinity, pray about what is happening on earth at this time and pray for the powers that will go from making threats to the reality of arms. Pray, children of the most Holy Trinity, pray with your hearts that the intensity of the use of weapons unknown to you would decrease, if this is the Divine will. Pray: prayer is a balm for the soul. I bless and protect you. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 legion\u00f3w niebieskich jestem pos\u0142any, aby poinformowa\u0107 was, \u017ce. Nadszed\u0142 czas!!! Jak zadekretowa\u0142a wcze\u015bniej Tr\u00f3jca Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsza i wspomnia\u0142a wam. Umi\u0142owane dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, ziemia trz\u0119sie si\u0119 z g\u0142\u0119bi, wzmacniaj\u0105c linie uskokowe, kt\u00f3re tworz\u0105 trz\u0119sienia ziemi. Ziemia zawsze trz\u0119s\u0142a si\u0119 w tym czy innym miejscu, ale nie mo\u017cecie zaprzeczy\u0107, \u017ce w tym czasie ruchy s\u0105 cz\u0119stsze, a erupcje wulkan\u00f3w nasilaj\u0105 si\u0119 z powodu ruch\u00f3w ziemi. B\u0105d\u017acie ostrze\u017ceni przed fa\u0142szywymi doktrynami: Prawo Bo\u017ce nie mo\u017ce by\u0107 zmienione; mistyczne cia\u0142o naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa jest \u015bwiadome, \u017ce prawo Bo\u017ce jest jedno i tylko w krzy\u017cu i w jedno\u015bci mo\u017cna poj\u0105\u0107 wymiary Woli Bo\u017cej. Wierny ludu, konieczne jest, aby\u015b przeszed\u0142 od przeci\u0119tnego \u017cycia duchowego do \u017cycia duchowo\u015bci\u0105 w jej pe\u0142ni przez wiar\u0119. Lud Bo\u017cy musi mie\u0107 mocn\u0105 wiar\u0119 w tym czasie, gdy coraz bardziej post\u0119puje dechrystianizacja. Szacunek ludzko\u015bci do tego, co Boskie, spad\u0142 bardzo nisko i to zrodzi wielkie prze\u015bladowania wobec ludu Bo\u017cego. Z tego powodu konieczne jest, aby istoty ludzkie mia\u0142y wiar\u0119 i zrozumienie, aby by\u0142y niez\u0142omne w modlitwie; bez modlitwy nie ma po\u0142\u0105czenia z Tr\u00f3jc\u0105 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105. Modlitwa jest konieczna, a jako ksi\u0105\u017c\u0119 legion\u00f3w niebieskich zapewniam was, \u017ce ka\u017cde b\u0142aganie wznoszone skruszonym sercem jest przyjmowane przez Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105 i przez nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119 czas\u00f3w ostatecznych. Przyjmijcie Cia\u0142o i Krew naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa i b\u0105d\u017acie wierni prawdziwemu magisterium Ko\u015bcio\u0142a naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Dzieci Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej: Czas, aby\u015bcie \u017cyli wiar\u0105 w pe\u0142ni, bez l\u0119ku, bez niepokoju, bez potkni\u0119\u0107, gdy post\u0119puje wojenny krzyk, i bez zapominania, \u017ce traktaty pokojowe nie s\u0105 pokojem, lecz przedwst\u0119pnymi dzia\u0142aniami narod\u00f3w, aby bardziej si\u0119 przygotowa\u0107 i doj\u015b\u0107 do tego punktu. Wiara, ludu Bo\u017cy! Umi\u0142owany lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Ostrze\u017cenie jest bliskie, tak jak bliska jest wojna... M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 jako lud Bo\u017cy: odmawiajcie r\u00f3\u017caniec \u015bwi\u0119ty - jest to jedna z modlitw, w kt\u00f3rej wraz z naszym Kr\u00f3lem i Panem Jezusem Chrystusem oraz z nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0105, prze\u015bledzicie \u017cycie, m\u0119k\u0119, \u015bmier\u0107 i zmartwychwstanie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. W Domu Bo\u017cym maj\u0105 by\u0107 g\u0142oszone pochwa\u0142y ku czci Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej i ku czci naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki Czas\u00f3w Ostatecznych, a tak\u017ce ma by\u0107 g\u0142oszony r\u00f3\u017caniec \u015bwi\u0119ty w obliczu zagro\u017ce\u0144, jakie stoj\u0105 przed ludzko\u015bci\u0105 z powodu blisko\u015bci cia\u0142a niebieskiego, kt\u00f3re zbli\u017ca si\u0119 do ziemi. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 o to, co dzieje si\u0119 na ziemi w tym czasie i m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za moce, kt\u00f3re przejd\u0105 od gr\u00f3\u017ab do rzeczywisto\u015bci broni. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 sercem, aby zmniejszy\u0142a si\u0119 intensywno\u015b\u0107 u\u017cycia nieznanej wam broni, je\u015bli taka jest wola Bo\u017ca. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: modlitwa jest balsamem dla duszy. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was i chroni\u0119. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":16,"month_string":"October","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for being here in prayer and for answering my call in your hearts. My children, thank you for allowing me to be here with you, to bestow so many blessings. Pray in this blessed place together with this beloved son of mine who is in love with Jesus like a father's son (Our Lady was referring to Father Giulio Maria Scozzaro). Children, the roads will be winding to get to Jesus, but you will have the blessings and strength to sustain you. Please children, be faithful to the Word and the Gospel. I bless you now, in the Name of the Most Holy Trinity: Father and Son and Holy Spirit. Our Lady added that Father Giulio' latest book (What is the True Church of Christ?) will make the so-called children of God shake in their boots. She also said, there will be many Graces descending today. During Mass, after the Consecration, while the Eucharist was being held high, Gisella saw St. Pio of Pietrelcina at the altar, next to and to the left of Father Giulio Scozzaro who was celebrating Mass, and St. Pio said to Gisella: I am preparing this son of mine for Holiness.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass du hier im Gebet bist und meinen Anruf in deinen Herzen beantwortet hast. Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie mir erlaubt haben, hier bei Ihnen zu sein und so viele Segen zu schenken. Bete an diesem gesegneten Ort zusammen mit diesem geliebten Sohn von mir, der in Jesus verliebt ist wie der Sohn eines Vaters (unsere Frau bezog sich auf Pater Giulio Maria Scozzaro). Kinder, die Stra\u00dfen werden sich auf Jesus umgeben, aber Sie werden den Segen und die Kraft haben, um Sie zu erhalten. Bitte Kinder, seien Sie dem Wort und dem Evangelium treu. Ich segne dich jetzt im Namen der heiligsten Dreifaltigkeit: Vater und Sohn und Heiliger Geist. Unsere Lieben Frau f\u00fcgte hinzu, dass Pater Giulio 'neuestes Buch (was ist die wahre Kirche Christi?) Die sogenannten Kinder Gottes in ihren Stiefeln zittern lassen. Sie sagte auch, es werde heute viele Gnaden geben. W\u00e4hrend der Messe sah Gisella nach der Weihe, w\u00e4hrend die Eucharistie hoch gehalten wurde Bereite diesen Sohn von mir auf die Heiligkeit vor.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por haber respondido mi llamada en tu coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, gracias por permitirme quedarme aqu\u00ed con ustedes, para dar muchas bendiciones. Ore en este lugar Benedetto junto con este hijo favorito, enamorado de Jes\u00fas como el Hijo de un Padre (la Virgen se refiri\u00f3 al Padre Giulio Maria Scozzaro). Ni\u00f1os, los caminos ser\u00e1n sinuosos para llegar a Jes\u00fas, pero tendr\u00e1s las bendiciones y la fuerza necesarias para apoyarte. Por favor, ni\u00f1os, sean fieles a la Palabra y al Evangelio. Ahora te bendiga, en el nombre de la Sant\u00edsima Trinidad: Padre e Hijo y Esp\u00edritu Santo. La Madonna agreg\u00f3 que el \u00faltimo libro del Padre Giulio (\u00bfcu\u00e1l es la verdadera Iglesia de Cristo?) Har\u00e1 que las mu\u00f1ecas temblar\u00e1n a los So -Ledled Children of Dios. Tambi\u00e9n dijo: Habr\u00e1 muchas gracias que se reducir\u00e1n hoy. Durante la misa, despu\u00e9s de la consagraci\u00f3n, mientras que la Eucarist\u00eda se mantuvo en alto, Gisella vio a San Pio da Pietrelcina en el altar, el siguiente y la izquierda del padre Giulio Sczzaro, quien celebr\u00f3 misa y San Pio le dijo a Gisella: Estoy preparando esto mi hijo para Hantines .","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re et d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, merci de m'avoir permis d'\u00eatre ici avec vous, pour accorder tant de b\u00e9n\u00e9dictions. Priez dans cet endroit b\u00e9ni avec ce fils bien-aim\u00e9 qui est amoureux de J\u00e9sus comme le fils d'un p\u00e8re (Notre-Dame faisait r\u00e9f\u00e9rence au p\u00e8re Giulio Maria Scozzaro). Enfants, les routes seront enroul\u00e9es pour se rendre \u00e0 J\u00e9sus, mais vous aurez les b\u00e9n\u00e9dictions et la force pour vous soutenir. S'il vous pla\u00eet les enfants, soyez fid\u00e8le \u00e0 la Parole et \u00e0 l'\u00c9vangile. Je vous b\u00e9nis maintenant, au nom de la Tr\u00e8s Sainte Trinit\u00e9: P\u00e8re et Fils et Saint-Esprit. Notre-Dame a ajout\u00e9 que le dernier livre du p\u00e8re Giulio (quelle est la vraie \u00e9glise du Christ?) Foura les soi-disant enfants de Dieu secouer dans leurs bottes. Elle a \u00e9galement d\u00e9clar\u00e9 qu'il y aura de nombreuses gr\u00e2ces descendant aujourd'hui. Pendant la messe, apr\u00e8s la cons\u00e9cration, alors que l'Eucharistie \u00e9tait retenue haut, Gisella a vu Saint-Pio de Pietrelcina \u00e0 l'autel, \u00e0 c\u00f4t\u00e9 de et \u00e0 gauche du p\u00e8re Giulio Scozzaro qui c\u00e9l\u00e9brait la messe, et St. Pio a dit \u00e0 Gisella: I Je pr\u00e9pare ce fils \u00e0 moi pour la saintet\u00e9.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, grazie per avermi permesso di stare qui con voi, per elargire tante benedizioni.  Pregate in questo luogo Benedetto insieme a questo mio figlio prediletto, innamorato di Ges\u00f9 come il figlio di un padre (la Madonna si riferiva a Padre Giulio Maria Scozzaro). Figli, le strade saranno tortuose per arrivare a Ges\u00f9, ma avrete le benedizioni e la forza necessaria per sostenervi. Vi prego figli, siate fedeli alla Parola e al Vangelo. Ora vi benedico, nel Nome della Santissima Trinit\u00e0: Padre e Figlio e Spirito Santo. La Madonna ha aggiunto che l\u2019ultimo libro di Padre Giulio (Qual \u00e8 la vera Chiesa di Cristo?) far\u00e0 tremare i polsi ai cosiddetti figli di Dio. Ha anche detto: saranno tante le Grazie che scenderanno oggi. Durante la Messa, dopo la Consacrazione, mentre era tenuta elevata l\u2019Eucaristia, Gisella ha visto San Pio da Pietrelcina all\u2019altare, accanto e alla sinistra di Padre Giulio Scozzaro che celebrava la Messa e San Pio ha detto a Gisella: Sto preparando questo mio figlio alla Santit\u00e0.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj na modlitwie i \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce pozwalacie mi by\u0107 tutaj z wami, obdarza\u0107 was tak wieloma b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwami. M\u00f3dl si\u0119 w tym b\u0142ogos\u0142awionym miejscu razem z moim ukochanym synem, kt\u00f3ry jest zakochany w Jezusie jak syn ojca (Matka Bo\u017ca mia\u0142a na my\u015bli ojca Giulio Maria Scozzaro). Moje dzieci, drogi b\u0119d\u0105 kr\u0119te, aby dotrze\u0107 do Jezusa, ale b\u0119dziecie mieli b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwa i si\u0142\u0119, kt\u00f3ra was podtrzyma. Prosz\u0119, moje dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie wierne S\u0142owu i Ewangelii. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, w Imi\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej: Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego. Matka Bo\u017ca doda\u0142a, \u017ce najnowsza ksi\u0105\u017cka ojca Giulio (Czym jest Prawdziwy Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 Chrystusa?) sprawi, \u017ce tak zwane dzieci Bo\u017ce b\u0119d\u0105 dr\u017ce\u0107. Powiedzia\u0142a te\u017c: b\u0119dzie dzi\u015b wiele \u0141ask zst\u0119puj\u0105cych. Podczas Mszy \u015awi\u0119tej, po Konsekracji, gdy Eucharystia by\u0142a trzymana wysoko, Gisella zobaczy\u0142a \u015bw. Pio z Pietrelciny przy o\u0142tarzu, obok i na lewo od ksi\u0119dza Giulio Scozzaro, kt\u00f3ry odprawia\u0142 Msz\u0119 \u015awi\u0119t\u0105, a \u015bw. Pio powiedzia\u0142 do Giselli: Przygotowuj\u0119 tego mojego syna do \u015bwi\u0119to\u015bci.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por atender minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, obrigado por me permitir estar aqui com voc\u00ea, conceder tantas b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3os. Ore neste lugar aben\u00e7oado junto com este meu amado filho meu que est\u00e1 apaixonado por Jesus como o filho de um pai (Nossa Senhora estava se referindo ao padre Giulio Maria Scozzaro). Filhos, as estradas estar\u00e3o enroladas para chegar a Jesus, mas voc\u00ea ter\u00e1 as b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3os e a for\u00e7a para sustent\u00e1 -lo. Por favor, crian\u00e7as, sejam fi\u00e9is \u00e0 palavra e ao evangelho. Eu te aben\u00e7oo agora, em nome da Sant\u00edssima Trindade: Pai, Filho e Esp\u00edrito Santo. Nossa Senhora acrescentou que o \u00faltimo livro do padre Giulio (qual \u00e9 a verdadeira Igreja de Cristo?) Far\u00e1 os chamados filhos de Deus sacudirem em suas botas. Ela tamb\u00e9m disse que haver\u00e1 muitas gra\u00e7as descendentes hoje. Durante a missa, ap\u00f3s a consagra\u00e7\u00e3o, enquanto a Eucaristia estava sendo mantida, Gisella viu St. Pio de Pietrelcina no altar, ao lado e \u00e0 esquerda do padre Giulio Scozzaro, que estava comemorando a missa, e St. Pio disse a Gisella: Eu Estou preparando esse meu filho para a santidade.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\u5e76\u5728\u60a8\u7684\u5fc3\u4e2d\u63a5\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u60a8\u5141\u8bb8\u6211\u4e0e\u60a8\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\uff0c\u7ed9\u4e88\u5f88\u591a\u795d\u798f\u3002\u4e0e\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u4e00\u8d77\u5728\u8fd9\u4e2a\u6709\u798f\u7684\u5730\u65b9\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u4ed6\u50cf\u7236\u4eb2\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u4e00\u6837\u7231\u4e0a\u8036\u7a23\uff08\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u5973\u58eb\u6307\u7684\u662f\u6731\u5229\u5965\u00b7\u739b\u4e3d\u4e9a\u00b7\u65af\u79d1\u624e\u7f57\u795e\u7236\uff09\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u9053\u8def\u5c06\u7ed5\u7740\u8036\u7a23\u6765\u5230\u8036\u7a23\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u60a8\u5c06\u6709\u7ef4\u6301\u60a8\u7684\u795d\u798f\u548c\u529b\u91cf\u3002\u8bf7\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u5fe0\u4e8e\u5723\u8a00\u548c\u798f\u97f3\u3002\u6211\u73b0\u5728\u4ee5\u6700\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u4e09\u4f4d\u4e00\u4f53\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff1a\u7236\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u3002\u6211\u4eec\u7684\u592b\u4eba\u8865\u5145\u8bf4\uff0c\u6731\u5229\u5965\u795e\u7236\u7684\u6700\u65b0\u8457\u4f5c\uff08\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u57fa\u7763\u6559\u4f1a\u662f\u4ec0\u4e48\uff1f\uff09\u4f1a\u8ba9\u6240\u8c13\u7684\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u6447\u6643\u4ed6\u4eec\u7684\u9774\u5b50\u3002\u5979\u8fd8\u8bf4\uff0c\u4eca\u5929\u5c06\u6709\u5f88\u591a\u6069\u5178\u4e0b\u964d\u3002\u5728\u5f25\u6492\u671f\u95f4\uff0c\u5728\u5949\u732e\u4e4b\u540e\uff0c\u5f53\u5723\u4f53\u5723\u4e8b\u88ab\u9ad8\u9ad8\u5730\u4e3e\u884c\u65f6\uff0c\u5409\u585e\u62c9\u5728\u796d\u575b\u4e0a\u770b\u5230\u4e86\u5f7c\u5f97\u96f7\u5c14\u897f\u7eb3\u7684\u5723\u76ae\u5965\uff0c\u5728\u5e86\u795d\u5f25\u6492\u7684\u5409\u5229\u5965\u00b7\u65af\u79d1\u624e\u7f57\u795e\u7236\u65c1\u8fb9\uff0c\u5de6\u53f3\uff0c\u5723\u76ae\u5965\u5bf9\u5409\u8d5b\u62c9\u8bf4\uff1a\u6211\u4e00\u6211\u6b63\u5728\u4e3a\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u51c6\u5907\u5723\u6d01\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":18,"month_string":"October","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear daughter, thank you for welcoming me into your heart. You must tell the world to prepare itself spiritually from the devil's attacks; humanity will weep and gnash its teeth. I ask to make reparation for all offenses against my beloved Son. I speak through this beloved soul, I show you the signs of my presence and yet many children are deaf to my call. Humanity still does not understand that the offenses, blasphemies, sacrileges done even by my beloved children (Priests) will be their eternal condemnation. They live on material things without observing all the things of Heaven. My children, be humble, always bend your knees in prayer, live the Commandments and feed on the Body and Blood of the Redeemer. Now I bless you in the Name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Tochter, danke, dass du mich in deinem Herzen willkommen gehei\u00dfen hast. Sie m\u00fcssen der Welt sagen, sie soll sich geistig von den Angriffen des Teufels vorbereiten. Die Menschheit wird seine Z\u00e4hne weinen und knirschen. Ich bitte um die Wiedergutmachung f\u00fcr alle Straftaten gegen meinen geliebten Sohn. Ich spreche durch diese geliebte Seele, ich zeige dir die Zeichen meiner Anwesenheit und doch sind viele Kinder meinen Anruf taub. Die Menschheit versteht immer noch nicht, dass die Straftaten, Blasphemen und Sakrilegien auch von meinen geliebten Kindern (Priestern) ihre ewige Verurteilung sein werden. Sie leben von materiellen Dingen, ohne alle Dinge des Himmels zu beobachten. Meine Kinder, seien Sie dem\u00fctig, beugen Sie immer Ihre Knie im Gebet, leben Sie die Gebote und ern\u00e4hren sich vom K\u00f6rper und Blut des Erl\u00f6sers. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Querida hija, gracias por darme la bienvenida en tu coraz\u00f3n. Tienes que decirle al mundo que se prepare espiritualmente de los ataques del diablo, la humanidad llorar\u00e1 y replyar\u00e1 los dientes. Pido reparar todas las ofensas a mi querido hijo. Hablo a trav\u00e9s de esta alma favorita, te muestro los signos de mi presencia y, sin embargo, muchos ni\u00f1os son sordos a mi llamada. La humanidad todav\u00eda no entiende que las ofensas, las blasfemias, los sacrilizos tambi\u00e9n hechos por mis hijos favoritos (sacerdotes) ser\u00e1n su condena eterna. Viven cosas materiales sin observar todas las cosas en el cielo. Hijos, sean humildes, siempre dobla las rodillas en la oraci\u00f3n, viven los mandamientos y se alimentan del cuerpo y la sangre del redentor. Ahora te bendiga en el nombre del Padre y el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo. Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Ch\u00e8re fille, merci de m'avoir accueilli dans votre c\u0153ur. Vous devez dire au monde de se pr\u00e9parer spirituellement \u00e0 partir des attaques du diable; L'humanit\u00e9 pleurera et grincera ses dents. Je demande de r\u00e9parer toutes les infractions contre mon fils bien-aim\u00e9. Je parle \u00e0 travers cette \u00e2me bien-aim\u00e9e, je vous montre les signes de ma pr\u00e9sence et pourtant de nombreux enfants sont sourds \u00e0 mon appel. L'humanit\u00e9 ne comprend toujours pas que les infractions, les blasph\u00e8mes, les sacril\u00e8ges effectu\u00e9s m\u00eame par mes enfants bien-aim\u00e9s (pr\u00eatres) seront leur condamnation \u00e9ternelle. Ils vivent sur des choses mat\u00e9rielles sans observer toutes les choses du ciel. Mes enfants, soyez humble, pliez toujours vos genoux dans la pri\u00e8re, vivent les commandements et se nourrissent du corps et du sang du r\u00e9dempteur. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cara figlia, grazie per avermi accolta nel tuo cuore. Devi dire al mondo di prepararsi spiritualmente dagli attacchi del demonio, l\u2019umanit\u00e0 pianger\u00e0 e strider\u00e0 i denti. Chiedo di fare riparazione per tutte le offese al mio diletto Figlio. Parlo attraverso quest\u2019anima prediletta, vi mostro i segni della mia presenza eppure molti figli sono sordi alla mia chiamata. L\u2019umanit\u00e0 non capisce ancora che le offese, le blasfemie, i sacrilegi compiuti anche dai miei figli prediletti (Sacerdoti) sar\u00e0 la loro condanna eterna. Vivono delle cose materiali senza osservare tutte le cose del cielo. Figli, siate umili, piegate sempre le vostre ginocchia nella preghiera, vivete i Comandamenti e cibatevi del Corpo e del Sangue del Redentore. Ora vi benedico nel Nome del Padre e del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo. Amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dziecko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci za przyj\u0119cie mnie do swojego serca. Musisz powiedzie\u0107 \u015bwiatu, aby przygotowa\u0142 si\u0119 duchowo na ataki diab\u0142a; ludzko\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dzie p\u0142aka\u0107 i zgrzyta\u0107 z\u0119bami. Prosz\u0119 o zado\u015b\u0107uczynienie za wszystkie przewinienia wobec mojego ukochanego Syna. Przemawiam przez t\u0119 ukochan\u0105 dusz\u0119, ukazuj\u0119 wam znaki mojej obecno\u015bci, a jednak wiele dzieci jest g\u0142uchych na moje wezwanie. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 wci\u0105\u017c nie rozumie, \u017ce wykroczenia, blu\u017anierstwa, \u015bwi\u0119tokradztwa pope\u0142niane nawet przez Moje umi\u0142owane dzieci (kap\u0142an\u00f3w) b\u0119d\u0105 ich wiecznym pot\u0119pieniem. \u017byj\u0105 sprawami materialnymi, nie dostrzegaj\u0105c spraw niebieskich. Dzieci moje, b\u0105d\u017acie pokorne, zawsze kl\u0119kajcie do modlitwy, \u017cyjcie przykazaniami i karmcie si\u0119 Cia\u0142em i Krwi\u0105 Odkupiciela. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w Imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Querida filha, obrigado por me receber em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Voc\u00ea deve dizer ao mundo para se preparar espiritualmente dos ataques do diabo; A humanidade chorar\u00e1 e gna os dentes. Pe\u00e7o para fazer repara\u00e7\u00e3o por todas as ofensas contra meu amado filho. Falo atrav\u00e9s dessa amada alma, mostro os sinais da minha presen\u00e7a e, no entanto, muitas crian\u00e7as s\u00e3o surdas para o meu chamado. A humanidade ainda n\u00e3o entende que as ofensas, blasf\u00eamias, sacriles feitos at\u00e9 meus amados filhos (sacerdotes) ser\u00e3o sua condena\u00e7\u00e3o eterna. Eles vivem com coisas materiais sem observar todas as coisas do c\u00e9u. Meus filhos, sejam humildes, sempre dobram os joelhos em ora\u00e7\u00e3o, vivem os mandamentos e se alimentam do corpo e do sangue do Redentor. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\u6b22\u8fce\u6211\u8fdb\u5165\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u3002\u60a8\u5fc5\u987b\u544a\u8bc9\u4e16\u754c\u4ece\u9b54\u9b3c\u7684\u88ad\u51fb\u4e2d\u7cbe\u795e\u4e0a\u505a\u597d\u51c6\u5907\u3002\u4eba\u7c7b\u4f1a\u54ed\u6ce3\u548c\u54ac\u7259\u3002\u6211\u8981\u6c42\u5bf9\u6211\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u7684\u6240\u6709\u7f6a\u884c\u8fdb\u884c\u8d54\u507f\u3002\u6211\u901a\u8fc7\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u7075\u9b42\u8bb2\u8bdd\uff0c\u5411\u60a8\u5c55\u793a\u6211\u7684\u5b58\u5728\u7684\u8ff9\u8c61\uff0c\u4f46\u8bb8\u591a\u5b69\u5b50\u5bf9\u6211\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u5145\u8033\u4e0d\u95fb\u3002\u4eba\u7c7b\u4ecd\u7136\u4e0d\u660e\u767d\uff0c\u5373\u4f7f\u662f\u6211\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff08\u7267\u5e08\uff09\u6240\u505a\u7684\u72af\u7f6a\uff0c\u4eb5\u6e0e\uff0c\u796d\u7940\uff0c\u4e5f\u662f\u4ed6\u4eec\u6c38\u6052\u7684\u8c34\u8d23\u3002\u4ed6\u4eec\u751f\u6d3b\u5728\u7269\u8d28\u4e0a\uff0c\u800c\u6ca1\u6709\u89c2\u5bdf\u5929\u5802\u7684\u6240\u6709\u4e8b\u7269\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c26\u865a\uff0c\u603b\u662f\u5728\u7948\u7977\u4e2d\u5f2f\u8170\uff0c\u9075\u5b88\u8beb\u547d\uff0c\u5e76\u4ee5\u6551\u8d4e\u4e3b\u7684\u8eab\u4f53\u548c\u9c9c\u8840\u4e3a\u98df\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":23,"month_string":"October","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"People of my King and Lord Jesus Christ: You are beloved of the Holy Trinity, beloved of our Queen and Mother of the End Times. The practice of the fulfilment of the Law of God is the solid foundation on which every human creature strengthens its spirituality and therefore, its faith is firm and strong. Children of my King and Lord Jesus Christ: Current fashions are abominable. The woman and her nudity externalize the moment in which humanity finds itself. Men dress like women, with silk garments... Humanity is not aware of this era of the Holy Spirit, where with a worthy life, a Son of God would be able to reach a greater discernment in his work and act by the grace of the Holy Spirit. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: The Christian is lack of formation so that they may be truly faithful children of God and creatures of faith. I speak to you, not of forming great scholars, but of forming disciples of our King and Lord Jesus Christ with strengthened faith in the relationship of infinite Divine love for every human creature. At this moment, the presence of the Holy Trinity and of our Queen and Mother in the life of man is imperative. Is humanity already experiencing famine? It is growing from country to country until it encompasses the whole world. The hand of a creature of power will make mankind live the consequences of the use of the weapon that leads mankind to its greatest chaos. Death will ride the earth leaving in its wake the trail of suffering. Pray children of God, pray, the earth is in constant movement in the depths and it will rise to the surface. Pray, children of God, pray, humanity is going to war. It will be the worst nightmare that the human creature of this generation has ever lived. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: This moment of the Holy Spirit is where the greatest nightmares for humanity and the greatest blessings for humanity will take place. Who will attempt against Rome? Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, I bless you. I call you to repentance, to turn to the way of eternal truth. I call you not to fear, but to inner change guided by our Queen and Mother of the end times. Do not fear, be more steadfast in faith. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Jeste\u015bcie umi\u0142owani przez Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 \u015awi\u0119t\u0105, umi\u0142owani przez nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119 czas\u00f3w ostatecznych. Praktyka wype\u0142niania Prawa Bo\u017cego jest solidnym fundamentem, na kt\u00f3rym ka\u017cde ludzkie stworzenie umacnia swoj\u0105 duchowo\u015b\u0107 i dlatego jego wiara jest mocna i silna. Dzieci mojego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Obecne mody s\u0105 obrzydliwe. Kobieta i jej nago\u015b\u0107 uzewn\u0119trzniaj\u0105 moment, w kt\u00f3rym znajduje si\u0119 ludzko\u015b\u0107. M\u0119\u017cczy\u017ani ubieraj\u0105 si\u0119 jak kobiety, w jedwabne szaty... Ludzko\u015b\u0107 nie jest \u015bwiadoma tej epoki Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, gdzie godnym \u017cyciem Syn Bo\u017cy m\u00f3g\u0142by osi\u0105gn\u0105\u0107 wi\u0119ksze rozeznanie w swojej pracy i dzia\u0142a\u0107 dzi\u0119ki \u0142asce Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Chrze\u015bcijanom brakuje formacji, aby mogli by\u0107 prawdziwie wiernymi dzie\u0107mi Bo\u017cymi i stworzeniami wiary. M\u00f3wi\u0119 do was nie o formowaniu wielkich uczonych, ale o formowaniu uczni\u00f3w naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa z umocnion\u0105 wiar\u0105 w relacj\u0119 niesko\u0144czonej Bo\u017cej mi\u0142o\u015bci do ka\u017cdego ludzkiego stworzenia. W tej chwili obecno\u015b\u0107 Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej oraz naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki w \u017cyciu cz\u0142owieka jest konieczna. Czy ludzko\u015b\u0107 ju\u017c do\u015bwiadcza g\u0142odu? Narasta on z kraju do kraju, a\u017c obejmie ca\u0142y \u015bwiat. R\u0119ka istoty w\u0142adzy sprawi, \u017ce ludzko\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dzie \u017cy\u0142a konsekwencjami u\u017cycia broni, kt\u00f3ra prowadzi ludzko\u015b\u0107 do najwi\u0119kszego chaosu. \u015amier\u0107 przejedzie po ziemi, pozostawiaj\u0105c po sobie \u015blad cierpienia. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci Bo\u017ce, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ziemia jest w ci\u0105g\u0142ym ruchu w g\u0142\u0119bi i b\u0119dzie si\u0119 wynurza\u0107 na powierzchni\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci Bo\u017ce, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludzko\u015b\u0107 idzie na wojn\u0119. B\u0119dzie to najgorszy koszmar, jaki prze\u017cy\u0142a ludzka istota tego pokolenia. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: W tym momencie Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego b\u0119d\u0105 mia\u0142y miejsce najwi\u0119ksze koszmary dla ludzko\u015bci i najwi\u0119ksze b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwa dla ludzko\u015bci. Kto b\u0119dzie pr\u00f3bowa\u0142 przeciwko Rzymowi? Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Wzywam was do pokuty, do nawr\u00f3cenia si\u0119 na drog\u0119 wiecznej prawdy. Wzywam was nie do strachu, ale do wewn\u0119trznej przemiany kierowanej przez nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119 czas\u00f3w ostatecznych. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, b\u0105d\u017acie wytrwalsi w wierze. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":23,"month_string":"October","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, today, so many graces will descend and so many rays of light will enter your lives. I myself, during the Eucharist, will pass among you to bless you one by one,in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder werden heute so viele Gnaden absteigen und so viele Lichtstrahlen werden in Ihr Leben eintreten. Ich selbst, w\u00e4hrend der Eucharistie, werde unter Ihnen gehen, um Sie nacheinander im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes Amen zu segnen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, hoy, muchas gracias que disminuir\u00e1n y muchos rayos de luz entrar\u00e1n en sus vidas. Yo mismo, durante la Eucarist\u00eda, pasar\u00e9 entre ustedes para bendecirte uno a la vez, en nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, aujourd'hui, tant de gr\u00e2ces descendreont et tant de rayons de lumi\u00e8re entreront dans votre vie. Moi-m\u00eame, pendant l'Eucharistie, je passerai parmi vous pour vous b\u00e9nir un par un, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, oggi, tante saranno le grazie che scenderanno e tanti raggi luminosi entreranno nelle vostre vite. Io stessa, durante l\u2019Eucarestia, passer\u00f2 tra voi per benedirvi uno alla volta,nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, dzi\u015b zst\u0105pi wiele \u0142ask i wiele promieni \u015bwiat\u0142a wejdzie w wasze \u017cycie. Ja sama, podczas Eucharystii, przejd\u0119 mi\u0119dzy wami, aby was kolejno pob\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0107, w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Hoje, meus filhos, tantas gra\u00e7as descem e tantos raios de luz entrar\u00e3o em suas vidas. Eu mesmo, durante a Eucaristia, passarei entre voc\u00ea para aben\u00e7o\u00e1 -lo um por um, em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eca\u5929\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u4f1a\u4e0b\u964d\uff0c\u8fd9\u4e48\u591a\u7684\u6069\u5178\u5c06\u8fdb\u5165\u60a8\u7684\u751f\u547d\u3002\u6211\u672c\u4eba\uff0c\u5728\u5723\u4f53\u5723\u4e8b\u671f\u95f4\uff0c\u6211\u5c06\u4ee5\u7236\u4eb2\u548c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\uff0c\u963f\u4eec\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u6765\u4f20\u9012\u4f60\u4eec\u4e2d\u95f4\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":25,"month_string":"October","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for being here in prayer and for kneeling down.  My children, look around you at this sick world. Many think this time is the end, but much worse will come, you cannot imagine how cruel the devil can be. Many of you say you know my Son Jesus, with your mouth, but not with your heart. My daughter, chosen and beloved of God, you will soon receive from my Lily, the Mantle of Glory and the Sword of Righteousness, so that everything may be for the glory of God. Jesus is with you. Children, always be ready for the spiritual warfare that will be tiring, but my angels will fight for you. Children, I bless you and peace be with you, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass du hier im Gebet bist und dich niedergekniet. Meine Kinder, sehen sich in dieser kranken Welt um. Viele denken, dass diesmal das Ende ist, aber viel schlimmer wird kommen, Sie k\u00f6nnen sich nicht vorstellen, wie grausam der Teufel sein kann. Viele von Ihnen sagen, dass Sie meinen Sohn Jesus kennen, mit Ihrem Mund, aber nicht mit Ihrem Herzen. Meine Tochter, gew\u00e4hlt und geliebt von Gott, werden Sie bald von meiner Lilie, dem Mantel der Herrlichkeit und dem Schwert der Gerechtigkeit, empfangen, damit alles f\u00fcr die Herrlichkeit Gottes sein kann. Jesus ist bei dir. Kinder, sein immer bereit f\u00fcr den spirituellen Krieg, der anstrengend sein wird, aber meine Engel werden f\u00fcr Sie k\u00e4mpfen. Kinder, ich segne dich und Friede sei mit dir, Amen.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por haber doblado las rodillas. Mis hijos, miran a tu alrededor este mundo enfermo. Muchos piensan que esta vez es el final, pero mucho peor, no imaginen cu\u00e1n cruel puede ser el diablo. Muchos de ustedes dicen que conocen a mi hijo Jes\u00fas, con la boca, pero no con el coraz\u00f3n. Mi hija, la elecci\u00f3n y la favorita de Dios, pronto recibir\u00e1n de mi lirio, la capa de gloria y la espada de la justicia, para que todo sea para la gloria de Dios. Jes\u00fas est\u00e1 contigo. Ni\u00f1os, prep\u00e1rate para la guerra espiritual que ser\u00e1 agotador, pero mis \u00e1ngeles luchar\u00e1n por ti. Los ni\u00f1os te bendicen y la paz sea contigo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici dans la pri\u00e8re et de s'agenouiller. Mes enfants, regardez autour de vous ce monde malade. Beaucoup pensent que cette fois est la fin, mais bien pire, vous ne pouvez pas imaginer \u00e0 quel point le diable peut \u00eatre cruel. Beaucoup d'entre vous disent que vous connaissez mon fils J\u00e9sus, avec votre bouche, mais pas avec votre c\u0153ur. Ma fille, choisie et appr\u00e9ci\u00e9e de Dieu, vous recevrez bient\u00f4t de mon lis, du manteau de gloire et de l'\u00e9p\u00e9e de la justice, afin que tout soit pour la gloire de Dieu. J\u00e9sus est avec vous. Les enfants, soyez toujours pr\u00eats pour la guerre spirituelle qui sera fatigante, mais mes anges se battront pour vous. Enfants, je vous b\u00e9nis et que la paix soit avec vous, Amen.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver piegato le vostre ginocchia.  Figli miei, guardate intorno a voi questo mondo malato. Molti pensano che questo tempo sia la fine, ma molto peggio arriver\u00e0, non immaginate quanto il demonio possa essere crudele. Molti di voi dicono di conoscere mio Figlio Ges\u00f9, con la bocca, ma non con il cuore. Figlia mia, scelta e prediletta da Dio, riceverai presto dal mio Giglio, il manto della gloria e la spada della giustizia, affinch\u00e9 tutto sia per la gloria di Dio. Ges\u00f9 \u00e8 con te. Figli, siate sempre pronti per la guerra spirituale che sar\u00e0 faticosa, ma i miei angeli combatteranno per voi. Figli vi benedico e la pace sia con voi, amen.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj na modlitwie i \u017ce kl\u0119czycie. Moje dzieci, sp\u00f3jrzcie na ten chory \u015bwiat wok\u00f3\u0142 siebie. Wielu my\u015bli, \u017ce ten czas jest ko\u0144cem, ale przyjdzie jeszcze wiele z\u0142a, nie wyobra\u017cacie sobie, jak okrutny potrafi by\u0107 diabe\u0142. Wielu z was m\u00f3wi, \u017ce zna mojego Syna Jezusa, ale nie zna Go swoim sercem. Moja c\u00f3rko, wybrana i umi\u0142owana przez Boga, wkr\u00f3tce otrzymasz od mojej Lili\u0119, P\u0142aszcz Chwa\u0142y i Miecz Sprawiedliwo\u015bci, aby wszystko by\u0142o na chwa\u0142\u0119 Boga. Jezus jest z tob\u0105. Dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie zawsze gotowi na walk\u0119 duchow\u0105, kt\u00f3ra b\u0119dzie m\u0119cz\u0105ca, jednak moi anio\u0142owie b\u0119d\u0105 walczy\u0107 za was. Dzieci, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was i pok\u00f3j niech b\u0119dzie z wami, Amen.","text_pt":"Caros filhos, obrigado por estar aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por se ajoelhar. Meus filhos, olhe ao seu redor para este mundo doente. Muitos pensam que desta vez \u00e9 o fim, mas muito pior chegar\u00e1, voc\u00ea n\u00e3o pode imaginar o qu\u00e3o cruel o diabo pode ser. Muitos de voc\u00eas dizem que conhece meu filho Jesus, com sua boca, mas n\u00e3o com seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Minha filha, escolhida e amada por Deus, voc\u00ea em breve receber\u00e1 do meu l\u00edrio, o manto da gl\u00f3ria e a espada da justi\u00e7a, para que tudo possa ser para a gl\u00f3ria de Deus. Jesus est\u00e1 com voc\u00ea. Filhos, sempre estejam prontos para a guerra espiritual que ser\u00e1 cansativa, mas meus anjos lutar\u00e3o por voc\u00ea. Filhos, eu aben\u00e7oo voc\u00ea e a paz esteja com voc\u00ea, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u5728\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\u548c\u8dea\u4e0b\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u73af\u987e\u8fd9\u4e2a\u75c5\u4e16\u754c\u3002\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u8ba4\u4e3a\u8fd9\u6b21\u662f\u7ec8\u7ed3\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u66f4\u7cdf\u7684\u662f\uff0c\u60a8\u65e0\u6cd5\u60f3\u8c61\u9b54\u9b3c\u4f1a\u591a\u4e48\u6b8b\u9177\u3002\u4f60\u4eec\u4e2d\u7684\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u8bf4\uff0c\u4f60\u8ba4\u8bc6\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\uff0c\u5634\u5df4\uff0c\u4f46\u4e0d\u8981\u5fc3\u4e2d\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5973\u513f\u662f\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u9009\u62e9\u548c\u631a\u7231\uff0c\u60a8\u5f88\u5feb\u5c31\u4f1a\u4ece\u6211\u7684\u767e\u5408\uff0c\u8363\u8000\u7684\u62ab\u98ce\u548c\u516c\u4e49\u4e4b\u5251\u90a3\u91cc\u5f97\u5230\uff0c\u8fd9\u6837\u4e00\u5207\u53ef\u80fd\u90fd\u662f\u4e3a\u4e86\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u8363\u8000\u3002\u8036\u7a23\u4e0e\u4f60\u540c\u5728\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8bf7\u59cb\u7ec8\u4e3a\u4f1a\u611f\u5230\u75b2\u5026\u7684\u7cbe\u795e\u6218\u505a\u597d\u51c6\u5907\uff0c\u4f46\u6211\u7684\u5929\u4f7f\u4f1a\u4e3a\u60a8\u800c\u6218\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u548c\u5e73\u4e0e\u4f60\u540c\u5728\uff0c\u963f\u4eec\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":29,"month_string":"October","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people, people of my sacred heart: I bless you with faith\u2026 I bless you with hope\u2026 I bless you with charity\u2026 You are living in spiritual warfare: the war between good and evil, the war for souls, for your souls. You are part of humanity and of salvation history, therefore you must be aware of the intense times in which you are living and not allow the spiritual change that must prevail at this time to go unnoticed. It is important that you know the Old Testament so that what is happening at this moment would not be strange to you. Be aware of the miracle of love of my real presence in the Eucharistic Food and in my people, whom I protect. Some of my children possess great intellectual ability, yet they do not fight against their personal ego in order to transform themselves into creatures of faith, love, kindness, serenity, consolation, and charity for their fellow men - so necessary at this critical moment in which you find yourselves. The climate maintains its variations and its fierce action in every season, which will lead to the cruellest of winters. Pray children, pray for Russia, the United States, the Ukraine, and China. Pray children, pray for India: it will suffer due to nature. Pray children, pray: arms will make humanity stop. pray children, pray, volcanoes are increasing their activity. Pray children, pray, Latin America will suffer; I suffer for it. Defend the faith, pray with the heart. My people, my beloved people, you will be surprised by the sudden action of the use of nuclear energy, which will cause me to act with my justice. I will not allow the human race to destroy itself or creation. Wake up, do not sleep! Wake up, my children! My most holy Mother holds you in her Immaculate Heart. This Mothers who loves her children gives you her encouragement and her protection. My people: faith, faith, faith! I remain with you, delivering you from evil; you must allow me to do so. Ask for it with faith. Pray. My people must intercede for humanity. My love remains in each one of you. I protect you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, ludu mojego \u015bwi\u0119tego serca: b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was wiar\u0105... b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was nadziej\u0105... b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was mi\u0142osierdziem... \u017byjecie w duchowej walce: wojnie dobra ze z\u0142em, wojnie o dusze, o wasze dusze. Jeste\u015bcie cz\u0119\u015bci\u0105 ludzko\u015bci i historii zbawienia, dlatego musicie by\u0107 \u015bwiadomi intensywnych czas\u00f3w, w kt\u00f3rych \u017cyjecie i nie pozwoli\u0107, by duchowe zmiany, kt\u00f3re musz\u0105 w tym czasie zwyci\u0119\u017cy\u0107, przesz\u0142y niezauwa\u017cone. Wa\u017cne jest, aby\u015bcie znali Stary Testament, aby to, co dzieje si\u0119 w tej chwili, nie by\u0142o dla was obce. B\u0105d\u017acie \u015bwiadomi cudu mi\u0142o\u015bci mojej realnej obecno\u015bci w Pokarmie Eucharystycznym i w moim ludzie, kt\u00f3rego chroni\u0119. Niekt\u00f3re z moich dzieci maj\u0105 wielkie zdolno\u015bci intelektualne, ale nie walcz\u0105 ze swoim osobistym ego, aby przekszta\u0142ci\u0107 si\u0119 w istoty wiary, mi\u0142o\u015bci, \u017cyczliwo\u015bci, spokoju, pocieszenia i mi\u0142o\u015bci dla swoich bli\u017anich - tak potrzebnych w tym krytycznym momencie, w kt\u00f3rym si\u0119 znajdujecie. Klimat zachowuje swoje wahania i swoje ostre dzia\u0142anie w ka\u017cdej porze roku, co doprowadzi do najokrutniejszej zimy. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci, za Rosj\u0119, Stany Zjednoczone, Ukrain\u0119 i Chiny. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Indie: b\u0119d\u0105 cierpie\u0107 z powodu natury. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: bro\u0144 sprawi, \u017ce ludzko\u015b\u0107 si\u0119 zatrzyma. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, wulkany zwi\u0119kszaj\u0105 swoj\u0105 aktywno\u015b\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, Ameryka \u0141aci\u0144ska b\u0119dzie cierpie\u0107; ja cierpi\u0119 za ni\u0105. Bro\u0144cie wiary, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 sercem. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, b\u0119dziecie zaskoczeni nag\u0142ym dzia\u0142aniem wykorzystania energii j\u0105drowej, co spowoduje, \u017ce b\u0119d\u0119 dzia\u0142a\u0142 z Moj\u0105 sprawiedliwo\u015bci\u0105. Nie pozwol\u0119, aby rodzaj ludzki zniszczy\u0142 siebie i stworzenie. Obud\u017acie si\u0119, nie \u015bpijcie! Obud\u017acie si\u0119, moje dzieci! Moja naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Matka trzyma was w swoim Niepokalanym Sercu. Ta Matka, kt\u00f3ra kocha swoje dzieci, daje wam swoj\u0105 zach\u0119t\u0119 i swoj\u0105 ochron\u0119. M\u00f3j ludu: wiara, wiara, wiara! Ja pozostaj\u0119 z wami, wybawiaj\u0105c was od z\u0142a; musicie mi na to pozwoli\u0107. Pro\u015bcie o to z wiar\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. M\u00f3j lud musi wstawia\u0107 si\u0119 za ludzko\u015bci\u0105. Moja mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 pozostaje w ka\u017cdym z was. Ja was chroni\u0119. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":10,"day":29,"month_string":"October","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, you are now immersed in the greatest spiritual warfare of all time, the confused will be swept away like the wind, come closer to the true faith and the Eucharist, be humble and pray for God's justice to be mitigated, do penance. Children, Satan has raised his army, but my warriors of light will always win and be protected, for they have chosen to be under my Blessed Mantle. Beloved children, God is with you, behold the light and the cross and be faithful to my Son Jesus. Children I will follow you and instruct you step by step. Now I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen. ","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass Sie auf meinen Anruf in Ihrem Herzen geantwortet haben. Meine Kinder, Sie sind jetzt in den gr\u00f6\u00dften spirituellen Krieg aller Zeiten eingetaucht, die verwirrten werden wie der Wind weggefegt, n\u00e4her an den wahren Glauben und die Eucharistie kommen, dem\u00fctig sein und beten, dass Gottes Gerechtigkeit gemildert wird, Bu\u00dfe. Kinder, Satan, hat seine Armee auferweckt, aber meine Lichtkrieger werden immer gewinnen und gesch\u00fctzt werden, denn sie haben sich als unter meinem gesegneten Mantel entschieden. Geliebte Kinder, Gott ist bei dir, sieh das Licht und das Kreuz und sei meinem Sohn Jesus treu. Kinder Ich werde Ihnen folgen und Sie Schritt f\u00fcr Schritt anweisen. Jetzt segne ich dich im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Mis hijos, gracias por responder mi llamada en su coraz\u00f3n. Mis hijos, ahora est\u00e1n inmersos en la mayor guerra espiritual de todos los tiempos, los confundidos ser\u00e1n arrastrados como el viento, abordar\u00e1n la verdadera fe y la Eucarist\u00eda, ser humilde y rezar para que la justicia de Dios sea mitigada, haz la penitencia. . Hijos, Satan\u00e1s ha armado su ej\u00e9rcito, pero mis guerreros de la luz siempre ganar\u00e1n y estar\u00e1n protegidos, porque han elegido permanecer bajo mi manto bendecido. Ni\u00f1os de prediletti, Dios est\u00e1 contigo, mira la luz y la cruz y s\u00e9 fiel a mi hijo Jes\u00fas. Hijos Te seguir\u00e9 e instruir\u00e9 paso a paso. Ahora te bendigo en el nombre del Padre, el Hijo y el Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans votre c\u0153ur. Mes enfants, vous \u00eates maintenant immerg\u00e9 dans la plus grande guerre spirituelle de tous les temps, les confus seront balay\u00e9s comme le vent, se rapprochent de la vraie foi et de l'Eucharistie, soyez humble et priez pour que la justice de Dieu soit att\u00e9nu\u00e9e, p\u00e9nature. Enfants, Satan a \u00e9lev\u00e9 son arm\u00e9e, mais mes guerriers de la lumi\u00e8re gagneront toujours et seront prot\u00e9g\u00e9s, car ils ont choisi d'\u00eatre sous mon manteau b\u00e9ni. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, Dieu est avec vous, voici la lumi\u00e8re et la croix et \u00eatre fid\u00e8le \u00e0 mon Fils J\u00e9sus. Enfants, je vous suivrai et vous instruiterai \u00e9tape par \u00e9tape. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, ormai siete immersi nella pi\u00f9 grande guerra spirituale di tutti i tempi, i confusi saranno trascinati via come il vento, avvicinatevi alla vera fede e all\u2019Eucarestia, siate umili e pregate affinch\u00e9 la giustizia di Dio sia mitigata , fate penitenza. Figli , satana ha armato il suo esercito, ma i miei guerrieri di luce vinceranno sempre e saranno protetti, perch\u00e9 hanno scelto di stare sotto il mio Manto Benedetto. Figli prediletti, Dio \u00e8 con voi , guardate la luce e la croce e siate fedeli a mio Figlio Ges\u00f9. Figli vi seguir\u00f2 e vi istruir\u00f2 passo passo. Ora vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.  ","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, jeste\u015bcie teraz zanurzeni w najwi\u0119kszej wojnie duchowej wszech czas\u00f3w, zdezorientowani zostan\u0105 rozwiani jak wiatr, zbli\u017ccie si\u0119 do prawdziwej wiary i do Eucharystii, b\u0105d\u017acie pokorni i m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, aby sprawiedliwo\u015b\u0107 Bo\u017ca zosta\u0142a z\u0142agodzona, czy\u0144cie pokut\u0119. Moje dzieci, szatan uzbroi\u0142 swoj\u0105 armi\u0119, ale moi wojownicy \u015bwiat\u0142a zawsze b\u0119d\u0105 zwyci\u0119\u017ca\u0107 i b\u0119d\u0105 chronieni, poniewa\u017c wybrali bycie pod moim b\u0142ogos\u0142awionym p\u0142aszczem. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, B\u00f3g jest z wami, patrzcie na \u015bwiat\u0142o i krzy\u017c i b\u0105d\u017acie wierni mojemu Synowi Jezusowi. Moje dzieci, b\u0119d\u0119 za wami sz\u0142a i poucza\u0142a was z ka\u017cdym krokiem. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.  ","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por responder \u00e0 minha chamada em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, agora voc\u00ea est\u00e1 imerso na maior guerra espiritual de todos os tempos, os confusos ser\u00e3o varridos como o vento, aproximam -se da verdadeira f\u00e9 e da Eucaristia, sejam humildes e orem para que a justi\u00e7a de Deus seja atenuada, fa\u00e7a penit\u00eancia. Filhos, Satan\u00e1s levantou seu ex\u00e9rcito, mas meus guerreiros da luz sempre vencem e ser\u00e3o protegidos, pois optaram por estar sob meu manto aben\u00e7oado. Filhos Amados, Deus est\u00e1 com voc\u00ea, eis que a luz e a cruz e s\u00e3o fi\u00e9is ao meu Filho Jesus. Filhos, vou segui -lo e instru\u00ed -lo passo a passo. Agora eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai, do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u60a8\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u5fc3\u4e2d\u7684\u7535\u8bdd\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u60a8\u73b0\u5728\u6c89\u6d78\u5728\u6709\u53f2\u4ee5\u6765\u6700\u4f1f\u5927\u7684\u7cbe\u795e\u6218\u4e2d\uff0c\u6df7\u4e71\u5c06\u50cf\u98ce\u4e00\u6837\u88ab\u626b\u9664\uff0c\u66f4\u63a5\u8fd1\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u548c\u5723\u4f53\u5723\u4e8b\uff0c\u8c26\u865a\u5e76\u7948\u6c42\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u6b63\u4e49\u5f97\u5230\u7f13\u89e3\uff0c\u6094\u6539\u3002\u6492\u65e6\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\u5df2\u7ecf\u4e3e\u8d77\u4e86\u519b\u961f\uff0c\u4f46\u662f\u6211\u7684\u5149\u7ebf\u52c7\u58eb\u603b\u662f\u4f1a\u8d62\u5e76\u53d7\u5230\u4fdd\u62a4\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u4ed6\u4eec\u9009\u62e9\u5728\u6211\u7684\u795d\u798f\u5730\u5e54\u4e0b\u3002\u5fc3\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\uff0c\u4e0a\u5e1d\u4e0e\u4f60\u540c\u5728\uff0c\u770b\u7740\u5149\u548c\u5341\u5b57\u67b6\uff0c\u5fe0\u4e8e\u6211\u7684\u513f\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u8ddf\u968f\u60a8\uff0c\u5e76\u9010\u6b65\u6307\u5bfc\u60a8\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\uff0c\u513f\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":11,"day":3,"month_string":"November","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, as the envoy of the most Holy Trinity, I tell you that humanity, immersed in material things, is plunging deeper into that which is immediate and finite. Human beings have made a god of themselves, of their mortal bodies, of their ego, of their position in society, meaning that they can lose their souls if they do not immediately take the decision to change their lives completely by moving towards conversion. You are keeping your eyes on the two countries at war, this being the means by which you are being distracted, downplaying the importance of other countries in conflict. Keep in mind that there will be the death of a leader in the Balkans, which will immediately lead to war between nations. The children of our Queen and Mother are not analysing what is hidden behind what is happening at this time: the stage is set for the third world war. Poor humanity! The repeated scourging of the earth at the hands of nature is being hidden beneath scientific concepts, and what has been warned about by heaven is being called 'climate change\u201d. What is happening is leading humanity towards the fulfilment of what has been foretold. Great changes will accelerate the appearance of events for the purification of this generation. Another sign is appearing before you: the moon clothed in red, the colour of blood, which you know as the beaver moon. The beaver makes provisions for winter, but is threatened by those who pursue it in order to hunt it. The moon foreshadows humanity\u2019s progress toward its purification: It is a harbinger of the imminence of great earthquakes and volcanic eruptions... It is a harbinger of grief in societies that are protesting in most countries... It is a harbinger of serious armed uprisings intended to overthrow governments... It is a harbinger of the persecution of your brothers and sisters by a godless humanity. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ - a people filled with virtues scorned by man without God. This is a time of grief brought about by the intelligence of man, who has rejected the Holy Trinity and our Queen and Mother. His spiritual faculties are in decline, preventing humanity from harbouring faith and noble sentiments full of love, as commanded by our King and Lord Jesus Christ. This is the era of the Holy Spirit for those who stand firm in faith... It will be a time of wonders for those who want to convert: this is the moment to do so. No matter how intense the times may be, they are optimal for personal conversion. The manual for the way is love. The signpost marked so that you would not go astray is obedience. The meeting point is fraternal love. You have a Mother who loves you, and she shelters all her children in her Immaculate Heart so that they would not be led astray by evil. Attentive, obedient, fraternal and merciful: such are the people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ - a people of love, of charity and of firm and strong faith, so strong that the winds cannot bend them. Wait for the angel of peace, you will receive him by means of the firm faith with which you await him. Pray 'in season and out of season'. Pray with your works and actions, and love your fellow man even when your fellow man is your own torturer. Pray for those who do not love you. Pray with your heart. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, jako wys\u0142annik naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Tr\u00f3jcy m\u00f3wi\u0119 wam, \u017ce ludzko\u015b\u0107, zanurzona w rzeczach materialnych, pogr\u0105\u017ca si\u0119 coraz bardziej w tym, co dora\u017ane i sko\u0144czone. Istoty ludzkie uczyni\u0142y boga z siebie, ze swoich \u015bmiertelnych cia\u0142, ze swojego ego, ze swojej pozycji w spo\u0142ecze\u0144stwie, co oznacza, \u017ce mog\u0105 straci\u0107 swoje dusze, je\u015bli natychmiast nie podejm\u0105 decyzji o ca\u0142kowitej zmianie swojego \u017cycia, zmierzaj\u0105c ku nawr\u00f3ceniu. Trzymacie oczy na dw\u00f3ch krajach w stanie wojny, jest to \u015brodek, za pomoc\u0105 kt\u00f3rego jeste\u015bcie rozpraszani, bagatelizuj\u0105c znaczenie innych kraj\u00f3w w konflikcie. Pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce na Ba\u0142kanach nast\u0105pi \u015bmier\u0107 przyw\u00f3dcy, co natychmiast doprowadzi do wojny mi\u0119dzy narodami. Dzieci naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki nie analizuj\u0105 tego, co kryje si\u0119 za tym, co dzieje si\u0119 w tym czasie: scena jest ustawiona na trzeci\u0105 wojn\u0119 \u015bwiatow\u0105. Biedna ludzko\u015b\u0107! Powtarzaj\u0105ce si\u0119 biczowanie ziemi z r\u0105k natury jest ukrywane pod naukowymi koncepcjami, a to, przed czym ostrzega\u0142y niebiosa, nazywa si\u0119 \"zmianami klimatycznymi\". To, co si\u0119 dzieje, prowadzi ludzko\u015b\u0107 do spe\u0142nienia si\u0119 tego, co zosta\u0142o przepowiedziane. Wielkie zmiany przyspiesz\u0105 pojawienie si\u0119 wydarze\u0144 dla oczyszczenia tego pokolenia. Przed wami pojawia si\u0119 kolejny znak: ksi\u0119\u017cyc obleczony w czerwie\u0144, kolor krwi, kt\u00f3ry znacie jako ksi\u0119\u017cyc bobr\u00f3w. B\u00f3br robi zapasy na zim\u0119, ale jest zagro\u017cony przez tych, kt\u00f3rzy go \u015bcigaj\u0105, aby na niego polowa\u0107. Ksi\u0119\u017cyc ten zapowiada post\u0119py ludzko\u015bci w kierunku jej oczyszczenia: Jest zwiastunem blisko\u015bci wielkich trz\u0119sie\u0144 ziemi i wybuch\u00f3w wulkan\u00f3w... Jest zwiastunem \u017ca\u0142oby w spo\u0142ecze\u0144stwach, kt\u00f3re w wi\u0119kszo\u015bci kraj\u00f3w protestuj\u0105... Jest zwiastunem powa\u017cnych powsta\u0144 zbrojnych maj\u0105cych na celu obalenie rz\u0105d\u00f3w... Jest zwiastunem prze\u015bladowania waszych braci i si\u00f3str przez bezbo\u017cn\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa - ludu pe\u0142nego cn\u00f3t wzgardzonych przez cz\u0142owieka bez Boga. Jest to czas \u017ca\u0142oby wywo\u0142anej inteligencj\u0105 cz\u0142owieka, kt\u00f3ry odrzuci\u0142 Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 \u015awi\u0119t\u0105 oraz nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119. Jego w\u0142adze duchowe podupad\u0142y, uniemo\u017cliwiaj\u0105c ludzko\u015bci piel\u0119gnowanie wiary i szlachetnych uczu\u0107 pe\u0142nych mi\u0142o\u015bci, jak nakaza\u0142 nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus. Jest to era Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego dla tych, kt\u00f3rzy stoj\u0105 mocno w wierze... B\u0119dzie to czas cud\u00f3w dla tych, kt\u00f3rzy chc\u0105 si\u0119 nawr\u00f3ci\u0107: to jest moment, aby to uczyni\u0107. Niezale\u017cnie od tego, jak intensywne mog\u0105 by\u0107 te czasy, s\u0105 one optymalne dla osobistego nawr\u00f3cenia. Podr\u0119cznikiem drogi jest mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107. Drogowskazem oznaczonym, aby nie zb\u0142\u0105dzi\u0107, jest pos\u0142usze\u0144stwo. Punktem spotkania jest mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 braterska. Macie Matk\u0119, kt\u00f3ra was kocha, a wszystkie swoje dzieci chroni w swoim Niepokalanym Sercu, aby nie da\u0142y si\u0119 sprowadzi\u0107 na manowce z\u0142a. Uwa\u017cny, pos\u0142uszny, braterski i mi\u0142osierny: taki jest lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa - lud mi\u0142o\u015bci, mi\u0142osierdzia oraz mocnej i silnej wiary, tak mocnej, \u017ce wiatry nie mog\u0105 jej ugi\u0105\u0107. Czekajcie na anio\u0142a pokoju, otrzymacie go dzi\u0119ki mocnej wierze, z jak\u0105 na niego czekacie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 \"w por\u0119 i nie w por\u0119\". M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 swoimi dzie\u0142ami i czynami, kochajcie bli\u017aniego nawet wtedy, gdy wasz bli\u017ani jest waszym oprawc\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za tych, kt\u00f3rzy was nie kochaj\u0105. M\u00f3dl si\u0119 swoim sercem. \u015awi\u0119ty Michale Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. ","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":11,"day":3,"month_string":"November","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"My children, thank you for being here and for answering my call in your hearts. My children, my tears flow for those who do not heed my call. I weep for blasphemies and for priests who are not faithful to God. I weep for those who despite the signs of the times, are tied to the false lights of the world. My children, please convert, the times will be hard. Pray that your Father will be merciful. There will be famine in the world and there will be a shortage of food. Children, provide for yourselves and your brothers and sisters. The hearts of men are getting harder and harder and that is how Satan will lead into the abyss. Children, invoke Me in the time of suffering and I will be with you. Call upon my Son Jesus and He will change suffering into peace and sadness into joy. Be firm in faith, many do not know God and do not want to know Him, yet He is Father and does not want to lose you. Children, follow the path of Holiness, read the Gospel and the Word and there you will find everything you need. Love yourselves as God has loved you. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing, in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Meine Kinder, danke, dass ihr hier seid und auf meinen Ruf in euren Herzen antwortet. Meine Kinder, meine Tr\u00e4nen flie\u00dfen f\u00fcr diejenigen, die meinem Ruf nicht folgen. Ich weine um Gottesl\u00e4sterungen und um Priester, die Gott nicht treu sind. Ich weine um diejenigen, die trotz der Zeichen der Zeit an die falschen Lichter der Welt gebunden sind. Meine Kinder, bitte konvertiert, die Zeiten werden hart. Betet, dass euer Vater barmherzig ist. Es wird Hungersn\u00f6te auf der Welt geben und es wird an Nahrungsmitteln mangeln. Kinder, sorgt f\u00fcr euch und eure Br\u00fcder und Schwestern. Die Herzen der Menschen werden immer h\u00e4rter und so wird Satan in den Abgrund f\u00fchren. Kinder, ruft Mich in der Zeit des Leidens an und Ich werde bei euch sein. Ruft meinen Sohn Jesus an, und er wird Leiden in Frieden und Traurigkeit in Freude verwandeln. Sei fest im Glauben, viele kennen Gott nicht und wollen ihn nicht kennen, doch er ist Vater und will dich nicht verlieren. Kinder, folgt dem Weg der Heiligkeit, lest das Evangelium und das Wort Gottes und dort werdet ihr alles finden, was ihr braucht. Liebt euch, wie Gott euch geliebt hat. Nun \u00fcberlasse ich Ihnen meinen m\u00fctterlichen Segen, im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Hijos m\u00edos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed y por haber respondido a mi llamado en vuestro coraz\u00f3n. Hijitos, mis l\u00e1grimas caen por aquellos que no escuchan mi llamado. lloro por las blasfemias y por los sacerdotes que no son fieles a Dios, lloro por los que, a pesar de los signos de los tiempos, est\u00e1n atados a las falsas luces del mundo. Hijos, por favor convi\u00e9rtanse, los tiempos ser\u00e1n dif\u00edciles. Orad para que vuestro Padre sea misericordioso. Habr\u00e1 hambre en el mundo y escasez de alimentos. Hijitos, proveed para vosotros y para vuestros hermanos. El coraz\u00f3n de los hombres se endurece cada vez m\u00e1s y as\u00ed es como Satan\u00e1s los llevar\u00e1 al abismo. Hijos, invocadme en el momento del sufrimiento y estar\u00e9 con vosotros. Invocad a mi Hijo Jes\u00fas y \u00c9l cambiar\u00e1 el sufrimiento en paz y la tristeza en alegr\u00eda. Estad firmes en la fe, muchos no conocen a Dios y no quieren conocerlo, sin embargo, \u00c9l es Padre y no quiere perderos. Hijitos, sigan el camino de la Santidad, lean el Evangelio y la Palabra y all\u00ed encontrar\u00e1n todo lo que necesitan. Amaos unos a otros como Dios os am\u00f3. Ahora los dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n maternal, en el nombre del Padre, del Hijo y del Esp\u00edritu Santo, am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Mes enfants, merci d'\u00eatre l\u00e0 et d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, mes larmes coulent pour ceux qui ne r\u00e9pondent pas \u00e0 mon appel. Je pleure pour les blasph\u00e8mes et pour les pr\u00eatres qui ne sont pas fid\u00e8les \u00e0 Dieu. Je pleure pour ceux qui, malgr\u00e9 les signes des temps, sont li\u00e9s aux fausses lumi\u00e8res du monde. Mes enfants, convertissez-vous, les temps seront durs. Priez pour que votre P\u00e8re soit mis\u00e9ricordieux. Il y aura la famine dans le monde et il y aura une p\u00e9nurie de nourriture. Enfants, subvenez \u00e0 vos besoins et \u00e0 ceux de vos fr\u00e8res et s\u0153urs. Les c\u0153urs des hommes deviennent de plus en plus durs et c'est ainsi que Satan conduira dans l'ab\u00eeme. Enfants, invoquez-Moi au temps de la souffrance et Je serai avec vous. Invoquez mon Fils J\u00e9sus et Il changera la souffrance en paix et la tristesse en joie. Soyez ferme dans la foi, beaucoup ne connaissent pas Dieu et ne veulent pas Le conna\u00eetre, pourtant Il est P\u00e8re et ne veut pas vous perdre. Enfants, suivez le chemin de la Saintet\u00e9, lisez l'Evangile et la Parole et vous y trouverez tout ce dont vous avez besoin. Aimez-vous comme Dieu vous a aim\u00e9s. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Figli miei, grazie per essere qui e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli, le mie lacrime scendono per coloro che non ascoltano la mia chiamata. Piango per le bestemmie e per i sacerdoti che non sono fedeli a Dio. Piango per coloro che nonostante i segni dei tempi, sono legati alle false luci del mondo. Figli, vi prego convertitevi, i tempi saranno duri. Pregate affinch\u00e9 il Padre vostro sia misericordioso. Ci sar\u00e0 la carestia nel mondo e mancher\u00e0 il cibo. Figli, provvedete per voi e per i vostri fratelli. Il cuore degli uomini \u00e8 sempre pi\u00f9 duro ed \u00e8 cos\u00ec che Satana condurr\u00e0 negli abissi. Figli, invocatemi nel momento della sofferenza e Io sar\u00f2 con voi. Invocate mio Figlio Ges\u00f9 e Lui cambier\u00e0 la sofferenza nella pace e la tristezza nella gioia. Siate saldi nella fede, molti non conoscono Dio e non vogliono conoscerlo, eppure Lui \u00e8 Padre e non vuole perdervi. Figli, seguite la strada della Santit\u00e0, leggete il Vangelo e la Parola e l\u00ec troverete tutto ci\u00f2 che vi servir\u00e0. Amatevi come Dio vi ha amato. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna, nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Moje dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tutaj i \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, moje \u0142zy p\u0142yn\u0105 za tych, kt\u00f3rzy nie s\u0142uchaj\u0105 mojego wezwania. P\u0142acz\u0119 za blu\u017aniercami i za kap\u0142anami, kt\u00f3rzy nie s\u0105 wierni Bogu. P\u0142acz\u0119 za tymi, kt\u00f3rzy mimo znak\u00f3w czasu s\u0105 przywi\u0105zani do fa\u0142szywych lamp tego \u015bwiata. Moje dzieci, b\u0142agam was o nawr\u00f3cenie, czasy b\u0119d\u0105 ci\u0119\u017ckie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, aby Wasz Ojciec by\u0142 mi\u0142osierny. Na \u015bwiecie zapanuje g\u0142\u00f3d i zabraknie \u017cywno\u015bci. Moje dzieci, zapewnijcie byt sobie i swoim braciom. Serca ludzi staj\u0105 si\u0119 coraz twardsze i w ten spos\u00f3b szatan doprowadzi ich do przepa\u015bci. Dzieci, przywo\u0142ajcie Mnie w czasie waszego cierpienia, a Ja b\u0119d\u0119 z wami. Wzywajcie mojego Syna Jezusa, a On przemieni cierpienie w pok\u00f3j, a smutek w rado\u015b\u0107. B\u0105d\u017acie mocni w wierze, wielu nie zna Boga i nie chce Go pozna\u0107, a przecie\u017c On jest Ojcem i nie chce was straci\u0107. Moje dzieci, id\u017acie drog\u0105 \u015bwi\u0119to\u015bci, czytajcie Ewangeli\u0119, a tam znajdziecie wszystko, czego potrzebujecie. Kochajcie si\u0119 tak, jak B\u00f3g was umi\u0142owa\u0142. A teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem, w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Meus filhos, obrigado por estarem aqui e por atenderem ao meu chamado em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, minhas l\u00e1grimas correm por aqueles que n\u00e3o atendem ao meu chamado. Choro pelas blasf\u00eamias e pelos sacerdotes que n\u00e3o s\u00e3o fi\u00e9is a Deus. Choro por aqueles que, apesar dos sinais dos tempos, est\u00e3o presos \u00e0s falsas luzes do mundo. Meus filhos, por favor, convertam-se, os tempos ser\u00e3o dif\u00edceis. Ore para que seu Pai seja misericordioso. Haver\u00e1 fome no mundo e haver\u00e1 escassez de alimentos. Filhos, cuidem de voc\u00eas e de seus irm\u00e3os e irm\u00e3s. Os cora\u00e7\u00f5es dos homens est\u00e3o ficando cada vez mais duros e \u00e9 assim que Satan\u00e1s levar\u00e1 ao abismo. Filhos, invoquem-Me na hora do sofrimento e estarei com voc\u00eas. Invoque meu Filho Jesus e Ele transformar\u00e1 o sofrimento em paz e a tristeza em alegria. Seja firme na f\u00e9, muitos n\u00e3o conhecem a Deus e n\u00e3o querem conhec\u00ea-lo, mas Ele \u00e9 Pai e n\u00e3o quer te perder. Filhos, sigam o caminho da santidade, leiam o Evangelho e a Palavra e ali encontrar\u00e3o tudo o que precisam. Amai-vos como Deus vos amou. Agora deixo-vos com a minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna, em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u4f60\u4eec\u6765\u5230\u8fd9\u91cc\u5e76\u5728\u4f60\u4eec\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u7684\u53ec\u5524\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u7684\u773c\u6cea\u6d41\u7ed9\u90a3\u4e9b\u4e0d\u542c\u6211\u53ec\u5524\u7684\u4eba\u3002\u6211\u4e3a\u4eb5\u6e0e\u548c\u4e0d\u5fe0\u4e8e\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u7267\u5e08\u54ed\u6ce3\u3002\u6211\u4e3a\u90a3\u4e9b\u4e0d\u987e\u65f6\u4ee3\u7684\u75d5\u8ff9\uff0c\u4e0e\u4e16\u754c\u7684\u5047\u5149\u8054\u7cfb\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u7684\u4eba\u54ed\u6ce3\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8bf7\u8f6c\u6362\uff0c\u65f6\u4ee3\u4f1a\u5f88\u8270\u96be\u3002\u7948\u6c42\u4f60\u7684\u7236\u4eb2\u6148\u60b2\u4e3a\u6000\u3002\u4e16\u754c\u5c06\u53d1\u751f\u9965\u8352\uff0c\u98df\u7269\u5c06\u77ed\u7f3a\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u517b\u6d3b\u81ea\u5df1\u548c\u4f60\u7684\u5144\u5f1f\u59d0\u59b9\u3002\u4eba\u7684\u5fc3\u8d8a\u6765\u8d8a\u786c\uff0c\u6492\u65e6\u5c31\u662f\u8fd9\u6837\u628a\u5b83\u5e26\u5165\u6df1\u6e0a\u7684\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5728\u53d7\u82e6\u7684\u65f6\u5019\u547c\u5524\u6211\uff0c\u6211\u4f1a\u548c\u4f60\u4eec\u5728\u4e00\u8d77\u3002\u547c\u6c42\u6211\u7684\u5723\u5b50\u8036\u7a23\uff0c\u7942\u4f1a\u5316\u82e6\u4e3a\u5e73\u5b89\uff0c\u5316\u60b2\u4f24\u4e3a\u559c\u4e50\u3002\u575a\u5b9a\u4fe1\u5ff5\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u4e0d\u8ba4\u8bc6\u795e\uff0c\u4e0d\u60f3\u8ba4\u8bc6\u4ed6\uff0c\u4f46\u4ed6\u662f\u7236\u4eb2\uff0c\u4e0d\u60f3\u5931\u53bb\u4f60\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8ddf\u968f\u5723\u6d01\u7684\u9053\u8def\uff0c\u9605\u8bfb\u798f\u97f3\u548c\u8bdd\u8bed\uff0c\u5728\u90a3\u91cc\u4f60\u4f1a\u627e\u5230\u4f60\u9700\u8981\u7684\u4e00\u5207\u3002\u50cf\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7231\u4f60\u4e00\u6837\u7231\u81ea\u5df1\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u3001\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\uff0c\u5e26\u7740\u6211\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u795d\u798f\u79bb\u5f00\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":11,"day":5,"month_string":"November","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children, thank you for being here in prayer and for answering my call in your hearts. Beloved children, the plagues will be as many as the sins of the world, there will be earthquakes and floods and still you do not understand the warnings of heaven. My children, do not tire of stockpiling because I tell you, again, that famine will come suddenly. My children, the times of trial will be heavy but you pray and elevate your spirits. Pray for the Church. Beloved children, be confident because the new time is not far off, it will be a time of love, of peace where there will be no pain but only joy and finally you will work only for good. Now I leave you with my motherly blessing in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit. Amen.","text_de":"Geliebte Kinder, danke, dass ihr hier im Gebet seid und auf meinen Ruf in euren Herzen antwortet. Geliebte Kinder, die Plagen werden so viele sein wie die S\u00fcnden der Welt, es wird Erdbeben und \u00dcberschwemmungen geben und immer noch versteht ihr die Warnungen des Himmels nicht. Meine Kinder, werdet nicht m\u00fcde, Vorr\u00e4te anzuh\u00e4ufen, denn ich sage euch noch einmal, dass eine Hungersnot pl\u00f6tzlich kommen wird. Meine Kinder, die Zeiten der Pr\u00fcfung werden schwer sein, aber ihr betet und erhebt euren Geist. Betet f\u00fcr die Kirche. Geliebte Kinder, seid zuversichtlich, denn die neue Zeit ist nicht mehr fern, es wird eine Zeit der Liebe sein, des Friedens, wo es keinen Schmerz, sondern nur Freude geben wird und ihr schlie\u00dflich nur f\u00fcr das Gute arbeiten werdet. Nun \u00fcberlasse ich Ihnen meinen m\u00fctterlichen Segen im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes. Amen.","text_es":"Amados hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por responder a mi llamado en sus corazones. Amados hijos, las plagas ser\u00e1n tantas como los pecados del mundo, habr\u00e1 terremotos e inundaciones y a\u00fan no comprend\u00e9is los avisos del cielo. Hijos M\u00edos, no os cans\u00e9is de hacer acopio porque os digo, de nuevo, que el hambre vendr\u00e1 de repente. Hijos M\u00edos, los tiempos de prueba ser\u00e1n pesados \u200b\u200bpero orad y elevad vuestros esp\u00edritus. Oren por la Iglesia. Amados hijos, tened confianza porque el nuevo tiempo no est\u00e1 lejano, ser\u00e1 un tiempo de amor, de paz donde no habr\u00e1 dolor sino s\u00f3lo alegr\u00eda y finalmente trabajar\u00e9is s\u00f3lo para el bien. Ahora os dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n maternal en el nombre del Padre y del Hijo y del Esp\u00edritu Santo. Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, merci d'\u00eatre ici en pri\u00e8re et d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, les fl\u00e9aux seront aussi nombreux que les p\u00e9ch\u00e9s du monde, il y aura des tremblements de terre et des inondations et vous ne comprenez toujours pas les avertissements du ciel. Mes enfants, ne vous lassez pas de stocker car je vous le dis, encore une fois, que la famine va venir d'un coup. Mes enfants, les temps d'\u00e9preuve seront lourds mais vous priez et \u00e9levez votre esprit. Priez pour l'\u00c9glise. Enfants bien-aim\u00e9s, soyez confiants car le temps nouveau n'est pas loin, ce sera un temps d'amour, de paix o\u00f9 il n'y aura pas de douleur mais seulement de la joie et enfin vous ne travaillerez que pour le bien. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit. Amen.","text_it":"Amati figli, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli amati, le piaghe saranno tante quanto i peccati del mondo, ci saranno terremoti e alluvioni e ancora voi non capite i moniti del cielo. Figli miei, non stancatevi di fare scorte perch\u00e9 vi dico, ancora, che la carestia arriver\u00e0 all\u2019improvviso. Figli, i tempi della prova saranno pesanti ma voi pregate ed elevate il vostro spirito. Pregate per la Chiesa. Figli amati, siate fiduciosi perch\u00e9 il nuovo tempo non \u00e8 molto distante, sar\u00e0 un tempo di amore, di pace dove non ci sar\u00e0 dolore, ma solo gioia e finalmente opererete solo per il bene. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione materna nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo. Amen.","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tu na modlitwie i \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, plag b\u0119dzie tyle, ile grzech\u00f3w \u015bwiata, b\u0119d\u0105 trz\u0119sienia ziemi i powodzie, a mimo to nie rozumiecie ostrze\u017ce\u0144 nieba. Dzieci moje, nie m\u0119czcie si\u0119 gromadzeniem zapas\u00f3w, bo powtarzam wam, \u017ce g\u0142\u00f3d przyjdzie nagle. Moje dzieci, czasy pr\u00f3by b\u0119d\u0105 ci\u0119\u017ckie, ale wy m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 i podno\u015bcie na duchu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142. Ukochane dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie pewni, bo nowy czas jest ju\u017c niedaleko, b\u0119dzie to czas mi\u0142o\u015bci, pokoju, gdzie nie b\u0119dzie b\u00f3lu, ale tylko rado\u015b\u0107 i wreszcie b\u0119dziecie pracowa\u0107 tylko dla dobra. Zostawiam was teraz z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego. Amen.","text_pt":"Amados filhos, obrigado por estarem aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por responderem ao meu chamado em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Amados filhos, as pragas ser\u00e3o tantas quanto os pecados do mundo, haver\u00e1 terremotos e inunda\u00e7\u00f5es e ainda assim voc\u00eas n\u00e3o entendem as advert\u00eancias do c\u00e9u. Meus filhos, n\u00e3o se cansem de estocar porque lhes digo, novamente, que a fome vir\u00e1 de repente. Meus filhos, os tempos de prova\u00e7\u00e3o ser\u00e3o pesados, mas voc\u00eas orem e elevem seus esp\u00edritos. Ore pela Igreja. Amados filhos, estejam confiantes porque o novo tempo n\u00e3o est\u00e1 longe, ser\u00e1 um tempo de amor, de paz, onde n\u00e3o haver\u00e1 dor, mas apenas alegria e, finalmente, voc\u00ea trabalhar\u00e1 apenas para o bem. Agora deixo-vos com a minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo. Um homem.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u4f60\u4eec\u6765\u5230\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u4f60\u4eec\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u7684\u53ec\u5524\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u761f\u75ab\u5c06\u4e0e\u4e16\u754c\u7684\u7f6a\u6076\u4e00\u6837\u591a\uff0c\u4f1a\u6709\u5730\u9707\u548c\u6d2a\u6c34\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u4ecd\u7136\u4e0d\u4e86\u89e3\u4e0a\u5929\u7684\u8b66\u544a\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u538c\u5026\u56e4\u79ef\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u6211\u518d\u6b21\u544a\u8bc9\u4f60\u4eec\uff0c\u9965\u8352\u4f1a\u7a81\u7136\u6765\u4e34\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8bd5\u70bc\u7684\u65e5\u5b50\u4f1a\u5f88\u6c89\u91cd\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u4eec\u7948\u7977\u5e76\u632f\u594b\u7cbe\u795e\u3002\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u7948\u7977\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8981\u81ea\u4fe1\uff0c\u56e0\u4e3a\u65b0\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\u5df2\u7ecf\u4e0d\u8fdc\u4e86\uff0c\u90a3\u5c06\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u5145\u6ee1\u7231\u3001\u548c\u5e73\u7684\u65f6\u4ee3\uff0c\u6ca1\u6709\u75db\u82e6\uff0c\u53ea\u6709\u5feb\u4e50\uff0c\u6700\u540e\u4f60\u53ea\u4f1a\u4e3a\u5584\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u5723\u7236\u3001\u5723\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\uff0c\u5e26\u7740\u6bcd\u4eb2\u822c\u7684\u795d\u798f\u7559\u7ed9\u4f60\u3002\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":11,"day":6,"month_string":"November","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart, I bless you with my love. People of my son, I call you to be fraternal, to keep the faith, to give so as to receive, to look carefully at the signs and signals, in order that you would be people who meditate on everything that occurs. My Son suffers because of every action and work contrary to his will. The time has come when my children do not see, do not listen, and do not preach: they remain blind, deaf, and dumb in order to please those who are not in communion with the Divine Will. Humanity is being driven mad by the noise of what is worldly and harmful to body and spirit. You do not pray and have turned away from my son. You are a humanity without God. Humanity is in gravest danger and you do not see it; on the contrary, you constantly amuse yourselves without thinking of the offenses with which you are wounding my son. This generation is living in so much sin, greater than that of Sodom and Gomorrah. At this moment, the cup is almost empty. I am a Mother and a teacher: I am not the bearer of fear - on the contrary, I want you to prepare and convert. Humanity is living in total violence. You are empty inside, pleasing your basest instincts, and you are easy prey for evil. My Son loves you and this Mother and teacher loves you, therefore, I come to call you to spiritual change and to prepare yourselves to assuage hunger and cold. Keep prayer books in your homes, spiritual books that you need to have in print. You are walking in darkness, the same darkness that will reach earth and cover it completely; afterward, the Divine Light will come and will illuminate everything that exists. Love will be in those children who will repent, and they will be my son\u2019s, having a new life. People of my son, war continues to spread! The human race goes on aimlessly without seeing how the interests of one nation, in particular, are breathing fire so that the conflicts do not stop. Suffering is worsening for humanity. Famine will show man its face, and there will be lamentation. Countries will need the cover of darkness so as not to be seen at night and in order to protect their peoples. Without being afraid, children of my Immaculate Heart, continue ceaselessly increasing your faith, drawing closer to my Divine Son, praying to St. Michael the Archangel and his legions. Be creatures of inner peace, without arguments or envy and without arrogance, remembering that intelligence without God does not gain heaven, but wisdom, humility, meekness, obedience, love of neighbour and perseverance. . . People of my Son, pray, pray, pray; the earth has awakened in its bowels, and from within it, all that it contains will rise to the surface through volcanoes. People of my Son, pray, pray: France will weep, England will enter into chaos. Pray, children. People of my son, pray, pray: man\u2019s time is not god\u2019s time; hasten with your conversion. In the twinkling of an eye you, will find yourselves in chaos. You are loved by the most Holy Trinity. Be people who practice prayer, mercy, charity, fraternity, humility, and faith, without forgetting the law of God, works of mercy, the sacraments, and the word of sacred scripture. As your Mother I protect and bless you. I lovingly present your prayers and needs to the most Holy Trinity. Continue on your way without fear. Children of my Immaculate Heart: keep in mind that in the end, my Immaculate Heart will triumph. I love you, people of my son, I love you. I carry you within my womb and protect you. Do not fear, I am with you. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Ludu mojego Syna, wzywam was do braterstwa, do zachowania wiary, do dawania tak, aby otrzyma\u0107, do uwa\u017cnego patrzenia na znaki i sygna\u0142y, aby\u015bcie byli lud\u017ami, kt\u00f3rzy medytuj\u0105 nad wszystkim, co si\u0119 dzieje. M\u00f3j Syn cierpi z powodu ka\u017cdego dzia\u0142ania i pracy sprzecznej z Jego wol\u0105. Nadszed\u0142 czas, kiedy moje dzieci nie widz\u0105, nie s\u0142uchaj\u0105 i nie g\u0142osz\u0105: pozostaj\u0105 \u015blepe, g\u0142uche i nieme, aby zadowoli\u0107 tych, kt\u00f3rzy nie s\u0105 w jedno\u015bci z wol\u0105 Bo\u017c\u0105. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest doprowadzana do szale\u0144stwa przez ha\u0142as tego, co \u015bwiatowe i szkodliwe dla cia\u0142a i ducha. Nie modlicie si\u0119 i odwr\u00f3cili\u015bcie si\u0119 od Mojego Syna. Jeste\u015bcie ludzko\u015bci\u0105 bez Boga. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest w najwi\u0119kszym niebezpiecze\u0144stwie, a wy tego nie widzicie, przeciwnie, ci\u0105gle si\u0119 bawicie, nie my\u015bl\u0105c o przewinieniach, kt\u00f3rymi ranicie mojego Syna. To pokolenie \u017cyje w tak wielkim grzechu, wi\u0119kszym ni\u017c grzech Sodomy i Gomory. W tej chwili kielich jest prawie pusty. Jestem Matk\u0105 i Nauczycielk\u0105: nie jestem nosicielk\u0105 strachu - przeciwnie, chc\u0119, aby\u015bcie si\u0119 przygotowali i nawr\u00f3cili. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 \u017cyje w ca\u0142kowitej przemocy. Jeste\u015bcie puste w \u015brodku, zadowolone ze swoich najprostszych instynkt\u00f3w i jeste\u015bcie \u0142atwym \u0142upem dla z\u0142a. M\u00f3j Syn was kocha i ta Matka i nauczycielka was kocha, dlatego przychodz\u0119, aby wezwa\u0107 was do duchowej przemiany i przygotowa\u0107 si\u0119, aby zaspokoi\u0107 g\u0142\u00f3d i ch\u0142\u00f3d. Trzymajcie w swoich domach modlitewniki, ksi\u0105\u017cki duchowe, kt\u00f3re musicie mie\u0107 w druku. Chodzicie w ciemno\u015bci, tej samej ciemno\u015bci, kt\u00f3ra dotrze do ziemi i ca\u0142kowicie j\u0105 pokryje, po czym przyjdzie Boskie \u015awiat\u0142o i o\u015bwietli wszystko co istnieje. Mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dzie w tych dzieciach, kt\u00f3re si\u0119 nawr\u00f3c\u0105, i b\u0119d\u0105 to dzieci mojego Syna, maj\u0105ce nowe \u017cycie. Ludu mojego Syna, wojna wci\u0105\u017c si\u0119 rozprzestrzenia! Rodzaj ludzki idzie bez celu, nie widz\u0105c, jak interesy jednego narodu, w szczeg\u00f3lno\u015bci, ziej\u0105 ogniem, aby konflikty nie usta\u0142y. Cierpienie pogarsza si\u0119 dla ludzko\u015bci. G\u0142\u00f3d poka\u017ce cz\u0142owiekowi swoje oblicze i b\u0119dzie lament. Kraje b\u0119d\u0105 potrzebowa\u0142y os\u0142ony ciemno\u015bci, aby nie by\u0107 widzianym w nocy i aby chroni\u0107 swoje ludy. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca, nieustannie pog\u0142\u0119biajcie wasz\u0105 wiar\u0119, zbli\u017caj\u0105c si\u0119 do mojego Boskiego Syna, modl\u0105c si\u0119 do \u015bwi\u0119tego Micha\u0142a Archanio\u0142a i jego legion\u00f3w. B\u0105d\u017acie istotami wewn\u0119trznego pokoju, bez k\u0142\u00f3tni i zazdro\u015bci oraz bez arogancji, pami\u0119taj\u0105c, \u017ce inteligencja bez Boga nie zdobywa nieba, ale m\u0105dro\u015b\u0107, pokora, \u0142agodno\u015b\u0107, pos\u0142usze\u0144stwo, mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 bli\u017aniego i wytrwa\u0142o\u015b\u0107. . . Ludu mojego Syna, m\u00f3dl si\u0119, m\u00f3dl si\u0119, m\u00f3dl si\u0119; ziemia przebudzi\u0142a si\u0119 w swoich wn\u0119trzno\u015bciach, a z jej wn\u0119trza wszystko, co zawiera, wyp\u0142ynie na powierzchni\u0119 przez wulkany. Ludu mojego Syna, m\u00f3dl si\u0119, m\u00f3dl si\u0119: Francja b\u0119dzie p\u0142aka\u0107, Anglia wejdzie w chaos. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci. Ludu mojego Syna, m\u00f3dl si\u0119, m\u00f3dl si\u0119: czas cz\u0142owieka nie jest czasem Boga; pospiesz si\u0119 ze swoim nawr\u00f3ceniem. W mgnieniu oka znajdziecie si\u0119 w chaosie. Jeste\u015bcie kochani przez Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105. B\u0105d\u017acie lud\u017ami, kt\u00f3rzy praktykuj\u0105 modlitw\u0119, mi\u0142osierdzie, dobroczynno\u015b\u0107, braterstwo, pokor\u0119 i wiar\u0119, nie zapominaj\u0105c o prawie Bo\u017cym, dzie\u0142ach mi\u0142osierdzia, sakramentach i s\u0142owie Pisma \u015awi\u0119tego. Jako wasza Matka chroni\u0119 was i b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119. Z mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 przedstawiam wasze modlitwy i potrzeby Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej. Id\u017acie dalej swoj\u0105 drog\u0105 bez l\u0119ku. Dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca: pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce w ko\u0144cu moje Niepokalane Serce zatriumfuje. Kocham was, ludu mojego Syna, kocham was. Nosz\u0119 was w moim \u0142onie i chroni\u0119 was. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, Ja jestem z wami. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":11,"day":8,"month_string":"November","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear daughter, thank you, for welcoming me into your heart. Daughter, you must tell everyone to love and forgive. Do not be afraid for tomorrow if you are in Christ, I understand those who love and have faith and feel different from this world, which is caught up in frivolous things, lies and non-Christian conduct. Your prayers will mitigate the Wrath of God. Children, always have peace, love and hope in your hearts. I do not come to frighten you, but to ask you for conversion. I am a Mother who loves her children. My children, Archangel Michael, will be at your side, to deliver you from the evil that surrounds you. Jesus is coming and Heaven awaits you. Now, I bless you in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen.","text_de":"Liebe Tochter, danke, dass du mich in deinem Herzen willkommen gehei\u00dfen hast. Tochter, du musst allen sagen, dass sie lieben und vergeben sollen. F\u00fcrchte dich nicht vor morgen, wenn du in Christus bist, ich verstehe diejenigen, die lieben und glauben und sich anders f\u00fchlen als diese Welt, die in leichtsinnigen Dingen, L\u00fcgen und nichtchristlichem Verhalten gefangen ist. Ihre Gebete werden den Zorn Gottes mildern. Kinder, habt immer Frieden, Liebe und Hoffnung in euren Herzen. Ich komme nicht, um euch Angst zu machen, sondern um euch um Bekehrung zu bitten. Ich bin eine Mutter, die ihre Kinder liebt. Meine Kinder, Erzengel Michael, werden an deiner Seite sein, um dich von dem B\u00f6sen zu befreien, das dich umgibt. Jesus kommt und der Himmel erwartet Sie. Nun segne ich Sie im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen.","text_es":"Querida hija, gracias por acogerme en tu coraz\u00f3n. Hija, debes decirles a todos que amen y perdonen. No tem\u00e1is por el ma\u00f1ana si est\u00e1is en Cristo, entiendo a los que aman y tienen fe y se sienten diferentes de este mundo, que est\u00e1 enredado en frivolidades, mentiras y conductas no cristianas. Sus oraciones mitigar\u00e1n la Ira de Dios. Hijitos, tened siempre paz, amor y esperanza en vuestros corazones. No vengo a asustaros, sino a pediros la conversi\u00f3n. Soy una Madre que ama a sus hijos. Hijos m\u00edos, el Arc\u00e1ngel Miguel, estar\u00e1 a vuestro lado, para libraros del mal que os rodea. Jes\u00fas viene y el Cielo te espera. Ahora, los bendigo en el nombre del Padre y del Hijo y del Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n.","text_fr":"Ch\u00e8re fille, merci de m'avoir accueilli dans ton c\u0153ur. Ma fille, tu dois dire \u00e0 tout le monde d'aimer et de pardonner. N'ayez pas peur pour demain si vous \u00eates en Christ, je comprends ceux qui aiment et ont la foi et se sentent diff\u00e9rents de ce monde, qui est pris dans des choses frivoles, des mensonges et des conduites non chr\u00e9tiennes. Vos pri\u00e8res att\u00e9nueront la col\u00e8re de Dieu. Mes enfants, ayez toujours la paix, l'amour et l'espoir dans vos c\u0153urs. Je ne viens pas pour vous effrayer, mais pour vous demander la conversion. Je suis une maman qui aime ses enfants. Mes enfants, l'Archange Michel, seront \u00e0 vos c\u00f4t\u00e9s, pour vous d\u00e9livrer du mal qui vous entoure. J\u00e9sus vient et le Ciel vous attend. Maintenant, je vous b\u00e9nis au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen.","text_it":"Cara figlia, grazie, per avermi accolta nel tuo cuore. Figlia, devi dire a tutti di amare e perdonare. Non abbiate paura per il domani se siete in Cristo, capisco coloro che amano e che hanno fede e si sentono diversi da questo mondo, che \u00e8 preso dalle cose frivole, dalle bugie e da una condotta non Cristiana. Le vostre preghiere mitigheranno l\u2019Ira di Dio. Figli, abbiate sempre la pace, l\u2019amore e la speranza nel cuore. Io non vengo per spaventarvi, ma per chiedervi la conversione. Sono una Madre che ama i suoi figli. Figli miei, l\u2019Arcangelo Michele, sar\u00e0 al vostro fianco, per liberarvi dal male che vi circonda. Ges\u00f9 \u00e8 in arrivo e il paradiso vi attende. Ora, vi benedico nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo, amen.","text_pl":"Droga c\u00f3rko, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 ci, \u017ce przyj\u0119\u0142a\u015b mnie do swojego serca. C\u00f3rko, musisz powiedzie\u0107 wszystkim, \u017ceby kochali i przebaczali. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119 o jutro, je\u015bli jeste\u015bcie w Chrystusie, rozumiem tych, kt\u00f3rzy kochaj\u0105 i maj\u0105 wiar\u0119 i czuj\u0105 si\u0119 inni ni\u017c ten \u015bwiat, kt\u00f3ry jest uwik\u0142any w b\u0142ahe sprawy, k\u0142amstwa i niechrze\u015bcija\u0144skie post\u0119powanie. Twoje modlitwy z\u0142agodz\u0105 Gniew Bo\u017cy. Moje dzieci, miejcie zawsze w swoich sercach pok\u00f3j, mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 i nadziej\u0119. Nie przychodz\u0119, by was straszy\u0107, ale by prosi\u0107 o nawr\u00f3cenie. Jestem Matk\u0105, kt\u00f3ra kocha swoje dzieci. Moje dzieci, Archanio\u0142 Micha\u0142 b\u0119dzie u waszego boku, aby uwolni\u0107 was od z\u0142a, kt\u00f3re was otacza. Jezus nadchodzi i Niebo czeka na was. Teraz b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen.","text_pt":"Querida filha, obrigado por me acolher em seu cora\u00e7\u00e3o. Filha, voc\u00ea deve dizer a todos para amar e perdoar. N\u00e3o tenha medo do amanh\u00e3 se voc\u00ea est\u00e1 em Cristo, eu entendo aqueles que amam e t\u00eam f\u00e9 e se sentem diferentes deste mundo, que est\u00e1 preso em coisas f\u00fateis, mentiras e condutas n\u00e3o crist\u00e3s. Suas ora\u00e7\u00f5es mitigar\u00e3o a ira de Deus. Filhos, tenham sempre paz, amor e esperan\u00e7a em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. N\u00e3o venho para vos assustar, mas para vos pedir a convers\u00e3o. Sou uma M\u00e3e que ama seus filhos. Meus filhos, Arcanjo Miguel, estar\u00e3o ao seu lado, para livr\u00e1-los do mal que os cerca. Jesus est\u00e1 vindo e o C\u00e9u espera por voc\u00ea. Agora, eu te aben\u00e7oo em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, am\u00e9m.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u8c22\u8c22\u4f60\uff0c\u6b22\u8fce\u6211\u8fdb\u5165\u4f60\u7684\u5fc3\u91cc\u3002\u5973\u513f\uff0c\u4f60\u8981\u544a\u8bc9\u5927\u5bb6\u7231\u548c\u5bbd\u6055\u3002\u5982\u679c\u4f60\u5728\u57fa\u7763\u91cc\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\u660e\u5929\uff0c\u6211\u7406\u89e3\u90a3\u4e9b\u7231\u548c\u6709\u4fe1\u4ef0\u7684\u4eba\uff0c\u4ed6\u4eec\u4e0e\u8fd9\u4e2a\u88ab\u8f7b\u6d6e\u7684\u4e8b\u7269\u3001\u8c0e\u8a00\u548c\u975e\u57fa\u7763\u5f92\u884c\u4e3a\u7ea0\u7f20\u7684\u4e16\u754c\u611f\u5230\u4e0d\u540c\u3002\u4f60\u7684\u7948\u7977\u4f1a\u51cf\u8f7b\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u6124\u6012\u3002\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5fc3\u4e2d\u6c38\u8fdc\u6709\u548c\u5e73\u3001\u7231\u548c\u5e0c\u671b\u3002\u6211\u4e0d\u662f\u6765\u5413\u552c\u4f60\u7684\uff0c\u800c\u662f\u6765\u6c42\u4f60\u7688\u4f9d\u7684\u3002\u6211\u662f\u4e00\u4e2a\u7231\u5979\u5b69\u5b50\u7684\u6bcd\u4eb2\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u5927\u5929\u4f7f\u8fc8\u514b\u5c14\uff0c\u5c06\u5728\u4f60\u8eab\u8fb9\uff0c\u5c06\u4f60\u4ece\u56f4\u7ed5\u7740\u4f60\u7684\u90aa\u6076\u4e2d\u89e3\u6551\u51fa\u6765\u3002\u8036\u7a23\u6765\u4e86\uff0c\u5929\u5802\u5728\u7b49\u7740\u4f60\u3002\u73b0\u5728\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u7236\u3001\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\u795d\u798f\u4f60\uff0c\u963f\u95e8\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":11,"day":10,"month_string":"November","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved children of the most Holy Trinity, I come to you as a messenger of the most Holy Trinity. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, grow in faith. Live under the protection of the Divine Will. As the times intensify, the works and actions of those who walk in the shadow of the highest will give fruits of eternal life, and they will share them with their brothers and sisters. At this time, human beings are spending their lives in such deep spiritual emptiness that they project all their lack of fraternity toward their brothers and sisters. With every step that they take, they infect their brothers and sisters with the coldness with which the majority live their lives. The human ego is not to be rooted out but transformed and fused with the work and action of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, so that all human beings would live with deep love and share the blessing of being children of God. This generation, by turning away from the most Holy Trinity and seeking the Divine light down the wrong paths, has plunged into dangerous waters where they cannot swim, but only stay afloat, because they are putrid waters. I see so much of humanity running after the antichrist because of not knowing our King and Lord Jesus Christ, ignoring the fact that our King and Lord Jesus Christ worked miracles and did not boast about it, but on the contrary, went away quickly. What is different about the antichrist is that he will announce the supposed 'miracles\u201d that he will do. You know full well that they will not be miracles, but works of evil: he will make use of demons so as to appear to raise someone from the dead. It is therefore urgent that you know our King and Lord Jesus Christ directly from Holy Scripture. In this way, you will recognize him and not be deceived. Protect your mind, continue without soiling it and without bringing the harmful things of the world into it. Go to our Queen and Mother who guides you to her Divine Son in these times of so much turmoil. This people belonging to the most Holy Trinity are foolish. They know that there will not be peace: behind false peace agreements lies preparation for mutual annihilation with increased armaments. People of God, as you have decided to move further away from Divine Love, and in conjunction with the sign of the past blood moon, the following chastisement is announced to you: the abominable desolation of the church of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. The desolation of the soul has arrived at this time when they are removing the most Holy Trinity from places reserved for prayer and worship, when they are removing our Queen and Mother from them. This is a small warning before the great and final profanation. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, take this message with due seriousness! Increase your faith by being keepers of the law of God, of the sacraments and of the knowledge of him who sacrificed himself on the cross for the salvation of mankind. Meditate on this call. Do not take it lightly! In the love of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, I bless you, I illuminate your path, I protect and defend you. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, przychodz\u0119 do was jako pos\u0142aniec Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, wzrastaj w wierze. \u017byjcie pod ochron\u0105 Woli Bo\u017cej. W miar\u0119 jak czasy si\u0119 nasilaj\u0105, dzie\u0142a i czyny tych, kt\u00f3rzy chodz\u0105 w cieniu najwy\u017cszego, wydadz\u0105 owoce \u017cycia wiecznego, a oni podziel\u0105 si\u0119 nimi ze swoimi bra\u0107mi i siostrami. W obecnym czasie istoty ludzkie sp\u0119dzaj\u0105 swoje \u017cycie w tak g\u0142\u0119bokiej duchowej pustce, \u017ce rzutuj\u0105 ca\u0142y sw\u00f3j brak braterstwa na swoich braci i siostry. Z ka\u017cdym krokiem zara\u017caj\u0105 swoich braci i siostry ch\u0142odem, z kt\u00f3rym wi\u0119kszo\u015b\u0107 \u017cyje. Ludzkie ego nie ma by\u0107 wykorzenione, ale przekszta\u0142cone i zespolone z dzie\u0142em i dzia\u0142aniem naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, aby wszyscy ludzie \u017cyli g\u0142\u0119bok\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 i dzielili b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo bycia dzie\u0107mi Bo\u017cymi. To pokolenie, odwracaj\u0105c si\u0119 od Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej i szukaj\u0105c Boskiego \u015bwiat\u0142a na niew\u0142a\u015bciwych \u015bcie\u017ckach, pogr\u0105\u017cy\u0142o si\u0119 w niebezpiecznych wodach, w kt\u00f3rych nie potrafi p\u0142ywa\u0107, a jedynie utrzymuje si\u0119 na powierzchni, poniewa\u017c s\u0105 to wody gnilne. Widz\u0119, \u017ce tak wiele ludzko\u015bci biegnie za antychrystem z powodu nieznajomo\u015bci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, ignoruj\u0105c fakt, \u017ce nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus czyni\u0142 cuda i nie chwali\u0142 si\u0119 tym, a wr\u0119cz przeciwnie, szybko odszed\u0142. To co r\u00f3\u017cni antychrysta to fakt, \u017ce b\u0119dzie on og\u0142asza\u0142 rzekome \"cuda\", kt\u00f3re b\u0119dzie czyni\u0142. Wiecie dobrze, \u017ce nie b\u0119d\u0105 to cuda, ale dzie\u0142a z\u0142a: wykorzysta on demony, aby wydawa\u0142o si\u0119, \u017ce wskrzesza kogo\u015b z martwych. Dlatego pilne jest, aby\u015bcie znali naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa bezpo\u015brednio z Pisma \u015awi\u0119tego. W ten spos\u00f3b rozpoznacie go i nie dacie si\u0119 zwie\u015b\u0107. Chro\u0144 sw\u00f3j umys\u0142, trwaj bez brudzenia go i bez wprowadzania do niego szkodliwych rzeczy \u015bwiata. Id\u017acie do naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki, kt\u00f3ra prowadzi was do swego Boskiego Syna w tych czasach tak wielkiego zamieszania. Ten lud nale\u017c\u0105cy do Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Tr\u00f3jcy jest niem\u0105dry. Wiedz\u0105, \u017ce nie b\u0119dzie pokoju: za fa\u0142szywymi porozumieniami pokojowymi kryj\u0105 si\u0119 przygotowania do wzajemnej zag\u0142ady przy zwi\u0119kszonym uzbrojeniu. Ludu Bo\u017cy, poniewa\u017c postanowili\u015bcie jeszcze bardziej oddali\u0107 si\u0119 od Boskiej Mi\u0142o\u015bci i w po\u0142\u0105czeniu ze znakiem minionego krwawego ksi\u0119\u017cyca, zapowiadana jest wam nast\u0119puj\u0105ca kara: obrzydliwe spustoszenie ko\u015bcio\u0142a naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Spustoszenie duszy nadesz\u0142o w tym czasie, kiedy usuwaj\u0105 Naj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105 Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 z miejsc zarezerwowanych dla modlitwy i kultu, kiedy usuwaj\u0105 z nich nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119. Jest to ma\u0142e ostrze\u017cenie przed wielk\u0105 i ostateczn\u0105 profanacj\u0105. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, przyjmij to przes\u0142anie z nale\u017cyt\u0105 powag\u0105! Zwi\u0119kszajcie swoj\u0105 wiar\u0119, b\u0119d\u0105c str\u00f3\u017cami prawa Bo\u017cego, sakrament\u00f3w i wiedzy o tym, kt\u00f3ry po\u015bwi\u0119ci\u0142 si\u0119 na krzy\u017cu dla zbawienia ludzko\u015bci. Rozwa\u017cajcie to wezwanie. Nie traktujcie go lekko! W mi\u0142o\u015bci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was, o\u015bwietlam wasz\u0105 drog\u0119, chroni\u0119 i broni\u0119. \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":11,"day":14,"month_string":"November","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"Beloved children of the most Holy Trinity, I come to you as a messenger of the most Holy Trinity. My beloved people, I bless you with my love. My beloved children, my love covers all of humanity. All my children are covered by my love, and out of love, I allow each one of you to have access to my love or to reject it according to your free will. That is why some human beings accept my love, and others do not accept my love; nonetheless, I seek them everywhere so that they would convert to me. Humanity will go so far away from me that my church will seem not to recognize me, accepting acts and works that do not come from my will. Humanity wants a god that will allow it to work and act as it pleases, and that is not me. You must live in my will and be soldiers of my Divine love. My people, live in my infinite mercy by being creatures who fulfil my will and who love my most holy Mother. The scales of my justice stand before each individual: I am a Just Judge. My beloved people, this generation will witness a great devastation such as you have not experienced before; I, therefore, call you again and again to conversion. My children cannot continue to be the same: ones who judge their brothers and sisters, the same foolish people, the same ones who deliberately continue to be deaf, blind, and dumb, working and acting like the pharisees. Pray, my people, pray: communal prayer is necessary. Live in inner prayer according to my way of working and acting, keeping your mind on me and your relationship with me. Pray, my people, pray, pray: the great darkness will come, war will come from one moment to the next without your expecting it, like a flash of lightning, and there will be great darkness. Pray, my people, pray: great confusion is being poured out upon my mystical body; maintain your quest for holy living. Pray, my people, pray for Chile, Central America, and Mexico: they will be shaken. Pray, my people, pray for Japan, China, and the Middle East; pray for England and the United States: war is looming and disease will come again. My beloved people: Those who strive to change and to become better children of mine will not be disappointed; they will receive their reward. Dear children, I will not deceive you. 'I am your god\u201d, and I will remain with you. It is time to be silent and to devote yourselves to living according to my will. I bless you with my love, I bless you with my will. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, przychodz\u0119 do was jako pos\u0142aniec Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany lud, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105. Moje ukochane dzieci, moja mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 obejmuje ca\u0142\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107. Wszystkie moje dzieci s\u0105 obj\u0119te moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 i z mi\u0142o\u015bci pozwalam ka\u017cdemu z was mie\u0107 dost\u0119p do mojej mi\u0142o\u015bci lub j\u0105 odrzuci\u0107 wed\u0142ug waszej wolnej woli. Dlatego jedne istoty ludzkie przyjmuj\u0105 moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, a inne jej nie przyjmuj\u0105; mimo to szukam ich wsz\u0119dzie, aby si\u0119 do mnie nawr\u00f3cili. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 odejdzie ode Mnie tak daleko, \u017ce m\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 b\u0119dzie zdawa\u0142 si\u0119 Mnie nie uznawa\u0107, przyjmuj\u0105c czyny i dzie\u0142a, kt\u00f3re nie pochodz\u0105 z mojej woli. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 chce Boga, kt\u00f3ry pozwoli jej dzia\u0142a\u0107 i post\u0119powa\u0107 tak, jak jej si\u0119 podoba, a to nie jest Ja. Musicie \u017cy\u0107 w mojej woli i by\u0107 \u017co\u0142nierzami mojej Boskiej mi\u0142o\u015bci. M\u00f3j ludu, \u017cyj w moim niesko\u0144czonym mi\u0142osierdziu, b\u0119d\u0105c stworzeniami, kt\u00f3re wype\u0142niaj\u0105 moj\u0105 wol\u0119 i kt\u00f3re kochaj\u0105 moj\u0105 naj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105 Matk\u0119. Szala mojej sprawiedliwo\u015bci stoi przed ka\u017cdym cz\u0142owiekiem: Ja jestem S\u0119dzi\u0105 sprawiedliwym. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany lud, to pokolenie b\u0119dzie \u015bwiadkiem wielkiego spustoszenia, jakiego nie do\u015bwiadczyli\u015bcie wcze\u015bniej; dlatego wci\u0105\u017c na nowo wzywam was do nawr\u00f3cenia. Moje dzieci nie mog\u0105 by\u0107 nadal takie same: te, kt\u00f3re os\u0105dzaj\u0105 swoich braci i siostry, te same g\u0142upie ludy, te same, kt\u00f3re \u015bwiadomie nadal s\u0105 g\u0142uche, \u015blepe i nieme, pracuj\u0105c i dzia\u0142aj\u0105c jak faryzeusze. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3j ludu, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: konieczna jest modlitwa wsp\u00f3lnotowa. \u017byjcie w modlitwie wewn\u0119trznej wed\u0142ug mojego sposobu dzia\u0142ania i post\u0119powania, utrzymuj\u0105c sw\u00f3j umys\u0142 na Mnie i na waszej relacji ze Mn\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu m\u00f3j, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: nadejdzie wielka ciemno\u015b\u0107, wojna przyjdzie z chwili na chwil\u0119 bez waszego oczekiwania, jak b\u0142ysk pioruna, i nastanie wielka ciemno\u015b\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3j ludu, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: wielkie zamieszanie wylewa si\u0119 na Moje cia\u0142o mistyczne; podtrzymujcie wasze d\u0105\u017cenie do \u015bwi\u0119tego \u017cycia. M\u00f3dl si\u0119, ludu m\u00f3j, m\u00f3dl si\u0119 za Chile, Ameryk\u0119 \u015arodkow\u0105 i Meksyk: b\u0119d\u0105 wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119te. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3j ludu, za Japoni\u0119, Chiny i Bliski Wsch\u00f3d; m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Angli\u0119 i Stany Zjednoczone: zbli\u017ca si\u0119 wojna i powr\u00f3c\u0105 choroby. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu: Ci, kt\u00f3rzy staraj\u0105 si\u0119 zmieni\u0107 i sta\u0107 si\u0119 lepszymi dzie\u0107mi moimi, nie b\u0119d\u0105 zawiedzeni; otrzymaj\u0105 swoj\u0105 nagrod\u0119. Drogie dzieci, nie b\u0119d\u0119 was zwodzi\u0142. \"Ja jestem waszym Bogiem\" i pozostan\u0119 z wami. Nadszed\u0142 czas, aby zamilkn\u0105\u0107 i po\u015bwi\u0119ci\u0107 si\u0119 \u017cyciu zgodnie z moj\u0105 wol\u0105. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 wol\u0105. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":11,"day":18,"month_string":"November","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: I am sent by the most Holy Trinity at this time of confusion. Pilgrim people, may the Divine Love with which our King and Lord Jesus Christ and our Queen and Mother have addressed each one of you, encourage you so that you do not fall into confusion, into that temptation in which your brothers and sisters find themselves, not having the good sense to look at what is happening on earth, denying everything with great ignorance. Humanity must live with the constant need to aspire to stand beside our King and Lord Jesus Christ and our Queen and Mother. The creature will live in peace only if in its life it feels the need for our King and Lord Jesus Christ and our Queen and Mother. That is when its thinking will be fixed on our King and Lord Jesus Christ and our Queen and Mother. In this way human beings will know that they are on the right path, otherwise they will only live according to fleeting aspirations and false illusions, to which the evil oppressor of souls can lead them to succumb in an instant. Beloved of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, being incapable of loving life, you continue to despise it and continue not to value it. It is necessary for each person to have the certainty that you possess attributes with which god the father has endowed you in order to love God and to love your neighbour, and to be love, holy and pure, welcoming your neighbour and acknowledging that God is everything in your life. Believing that God exists, 'loving god above all things', does not make you less human, but freer. Therefore, he who loves his brother is truly a human being, a witness to Trinitarian Love. Humanity will acquire the certainty that without God it is nothing. It will live in inner emptiness because of despising the one it should love: our King and Lord Jesus Christ, who died on the cross and rose again to grant redemption to the human race. Therefore, not forgetting that heaven warns you out of love, you live with an obligation to adore the most Holy Trinity, being aware of the greatness that trinitarian love imprints within you. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: This people are like the waves of the sea: they come and go without attaining spiritual stability. They seek sensationalism and not the truth. War will continue in one place or another; winter comes with the burning fire of arms. The discontent of the peoples will lead them to revolt. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, the earth is opening up within it: earthquakes are intensifying and they will have greater force. Pray, people of the most Holy Trinity, pray for Central America, for Mexico and for the United States: the earth is shaking. Pray, people of the most Holy Trinity, pray for Panama, Chile, Ecuador, Colombia and Brazil: their land will be shaken. Pray, people of the most Holy Trinity, pray: there will be uncertainty where the eyes of humanity are turned at this moment. Pray, people of the most Holy Trinity, pray for France, Russia, Germany, Iraq, Ukraine and Libya: the spectre of war will be more visible. Pray, people of the most Holy Trinity, pray for Japan: it will be shaken and persecuted. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, maintain inner peace so that the fire of evil would not burn within you. Pray, put prayer into practice, persevere, confess your sins and receive the body and blood of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. I defend you; call upon me. In the unity of the faithful people, I bless you. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Jestem pos\u0142any przez naj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105 Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 w tym czasie zamieszania. Ludu pielgrzymuj\u0105cy, niech Boska Mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, z jak\u0105 nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus oraz nasza Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka zwr\u00f3cili si\u0119 do ka\u017cdego z was, doda wam otuchy, aby\u015bcie nie popadli w zam\u0119t, w t\u0119 pokus\u0119, w kt\u00f3rej znajduj\u0105 si\u0119 wasi bracia i siostry, nie maj\u0105cy zdrowego rozs\u0105dku, aby przyjrze\u0107 si\u0119 temu, co dzieje si\u0119 na ziemi, neguj\u0105c wszystko z wielk\u0105 ignorancj\u0105. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 musi \u017cy\u0107 z ci\u0105g\u0142\u0105 potrzeb\u0105 d\u0105\u017cenia do tego, aby stan\u0105\u0107 obok naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa oraz naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki. Stworzenie b\u0119dzie \u017cy\u0142o w pokoju tylko wtedy, gdy w swoim \u017cyciu b\u0119dzie odczuwa\u0142o potrzeb\u0119 naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa oraz naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki. Wtedy w\u0142a\u015bnie jego my\u015blenie b\u0119dzie utwierdzone na naszym Kr\u00f3lu i Panu Jezusie Chrystusie oraz naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matce. W ten spos\u00f3b istoty ludzkie b\u0119d\u0105 wiedzia\u0142y, \u017ce s\u0105 na w\u0142a\u015bciwej drodze, inaczej b\u0119d\u0105 \u017cy\u0142y tylko wed\u0142ug ulotnych d\u0105\u017ce\u0144 i fa\u0142szywych z\u0142udze\u0144, do kt\u00f3rych mo\u017ce je w jednej chwili doprowadzi\u0107 z\u0142y ciemi\u0119zca dusz. Umi\u0142owani naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, b\u0119d\u0105c niezdolnymi do kochania \u017cycia, nadal nim gardzicie i nadal go nie cenicie. Konieczne jest, aby ka\u017cdy cz\u0142owiek mia\u0142 pewno\u015b\u0107, \u017ce posiada cechy, kt\u00f3rymi obdarzy\u0142 go B\u00f3g Ojciec, aby kocha\u0107 Boga i kocha\u0107 bli\u017aniego, i by\u0107 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, \u015bwi\u0119t\u0105 i czyst\u0105, przyjmuj\u0105c bli\u017aniego i uznaj\u0105c, \u017ce B\u00f3g jest wszystkim w twoim \u017cyciu. Wiara w to, \u017ce B\u00f3g istnieje, \"kochanie Boga ponad wszystko\", nie czyni was mniej ludzkimi, ale bardziej wolnymi. Dlatego ten, kto kocha swojego brata, jest prawdziwie cz\u0142owiekiem, \u015bwiadkiem Mi\u0142o\u015bci Trynitarnej. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 zdob\u0119dzie pewno\u015b\u0107, \u017ce bez Boga jest niczym. B\u0119dzie \u017cy\u0142a w wewn\u0119trznej pustce z powodu gardzenia tym, kt\u00f3rego powinna kocha\u0107: naszym Kr\u00f3lem i Panem Jezusem Chrystusem, kt\u00f3ry umar\u0142 na krzy\u017cu i zmartwychwsta\u0142, aby da\u0107 odkupienie rodzajowi ludzkiemu. Dlatego, nie zapominaj\u0105c, \u017ce niebo ostrzega was z mi\u0142o\u015bci, \u017cyjecie z obowi\u0105zkiem adorowania Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, b\u0119d\u0105c \u015bwiadomymi wielko\u015bci, jak\u0105 odciska w was mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 trynitarna. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Ten lud jest jak fale morskie: przychodzi i odchodzi, nie osi\u0105gaj\u0105c duchowej stabilno\u015bci. Szukaj\u0105 sensacji, a nie prawdy. Wojna b\u0119dzie trwa\u0142a w tym czy innym miejscu; zima przychodzi z p\u0142on\u0105cym ogniem broni. Niezadowolenie lud\u00f3w doprowadzi je do buntu. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, ziemia otwiera si\u0119 w niej: trz\u0119sienia ziemi nasilaj\u0105 si\u0119 i b\u0119d\u0105 mia\u0142y wi\u0119ksz\u0105 si\u0142\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Tr\u00f3jcy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ameryk\u0119 \u015arodkow\u0105, za Meksyk i za Stany Zjednoczone: ziemia si\u0119 trz\u0119sie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, za Panam\u0119, Chile, Ekwador, Kolumbi\u0119 i Brazyli\u0119: ich ziemia b\u0119dzie wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119ta. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119: b\u0119dzie niepewno\u015b\u0107, gdzie w tej chwili zwr\u00f3cone s\u0105 oczy ludzko\u015bci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Tr\u00f3jcy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Francj\u0119, Rosj\u0119, Niemcy, Irak, Ukrain\u0119 i Libi\u0119: widmo wojny b\u0119dzie bardziej widoczne. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, ludu naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Tr\u00f3jcy, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Japoni\u0119: b\u0119dzie wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119ta i prze\u015bladowana. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, zachowaj wewn\u0119trzny pok\u00f3j, aby ogie\u0144 z\u0142a nie p\u0142on\u0105\u0142 w tobie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, wprowadzajcie modlitw\u0119 w czyn, wytrwale, wyznajcie swoje grzechy i przyjmijcie Cia\u0142o i Krew naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Ja was broni\u0119; wzywajcie mnie. W jedno\u015bci wiernego ludu b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":11,"day":22,"month_string":"November","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my Immaculate Heart, receive my motherly blessing. I walk with my children, I love them, I keep them united to my hands so that they may not be lost. At this time confusion is spreading like weeds in the field growing in haste without being seen. Ideologies with great falsehoods are separating my children from the mystical body of my Divine Son. One is the Divine word, do not follow those who wish to deceive you. Beloved children, the sun is in convulsion, agitated, emanating its force towards the earth and this, children, will result in a climate that will cause severe damage to the earth and to you. In the face of so much disbelief of my children towards the announcements of heaven, natural phenomena are accentuated and the earth continues to shake with great fury. In the face of so much disbelief of my children, the measures by which communities will suffer at human hands in every town and in every nation are accentuated. Children of my heart: Be on spiritual and physical alertness. Evil causes harm where my children insist on ignoring the law of God and the sacraments. You must consecrate yourselves to me so that you may maintain a defensive shield, as long as you remain obedient and good creatures in every aspect. Beloved children, you have forgotten that communism will dominate the world and spread over the earth. My children do not see that they are being led towards the precipice, dominated by those who do not desire the salvation of their souls. Communism gives power to small groups. These associations cause chaos and find themselves willing to fight for food and other necessities they lack. Demons are upon mankind. This is very dangerous: spiritual ignorance and ignorance of the Holy Scriptures. Prayer is indispensable, not praying keeps you away from the Holy Trinity and this Mother. Pray, pray, pray! My beloved, my Son's Church will be dressed in mourning and my children become more confused, due to spiritual ignorance. You will see a great sign in heaven before which some of my children will be terrified and the believers will know that, being at war, the warning will be near. Be responsible my children, be true children of my Divine Son. The happenings of mankind are difficult, the human creature must convert now! As if in the next moment it will be the Warning. Alert, children! Pray for the United States, nature turns against her. The friends of this nation abandon her in the midst of war. Pray children of my Divine Son, pray for France, the fire leads to burn great monuments of this nation. Pray children of my Divine son, pray, pray for Japan, pray for Afghanistan, pray for Australia, suffering comes to these nations. Pray children, pray, pray, the magnetism of the earth is less. Pray children before the disease that is approaching, pray before the new impediment to move, pray. Be faithful to my Divine Son. Be cautious in working and acting, the suffering of humanity is soon. Save the soul children! Be cautious and careful of your brothers, unite and be one heart of love, of prayer, of offering and of reparation. My heart is the Ark of Salvation. I protect you constantly, do not fear, I am with you. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Niepokalanego Serca, przyjmijcie moje matczyne b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo. Chodz\u0119 z moimi dzie\u0107mi, kocham je, trzymam je zjednoczone w moich r\u0119kach, aby si\u0119 nie zgubi\u0142y. W tym czasie zamieszanie rozprzestrzenia si\u0119 jak chwasty na polu, kt\u00f3re rosn\u0105 w po\u015bpiechu, nie b\u0119d\u0105c zauwa\u017cone. Ideologie z wielkim fa\u0142szem oddzielaj\u0105 moje dzieci od mistycznego cia\u0142a mojego Boskiego Syna. Jedno jest Boskie S\u0142owo, nie id\u017acie za tymi, kt\u00f3rzy chc\u0105 was zwie\u015b\u0107. Ukochane dzieci, s\u0142o\u0144ce jest w konwulsji, wzburzone, emanuje swoj\u0105 si\u0142\u0105 w kierunku ziemi i to, dzieci, spowoduje klimat, kt\u00f3ry spowoduje powa\u017cne szkody dla ziemi i dla was. Wobec tak wielkiej niewiary moich dzieci wobec zapowiedzi nieba, zjawiska naturalne s\u0105 zaakcentowane, a ziemia nadal trz\u0119sie si\u0119 z wielk\u0105 furi\u0105. Wobec tak wielkiej niewiary moich dzieci akcentowane s\u0105 \u015brodki, dzi\u0119ki kt\u00f3rym spo\u0142eczno\u015bci b\u0119d\u0105 cierpie\u0107 z r\u0105k ludzkich w ka\u017cdym mie\u015bcie i w ka\u017cdym narodzie. Dzieci mojego serca: B\u0105d\u017acie w duchowej i fizycznej czujno\u015bci. Z\u0142o wyrz\u0105dza szkody tam, gdzie moje dzieci uparcie ignoruj\u0105 prawo Bo\u017ce i sakramenty. Musicie po\u015bwi\u0119ci\u0107 si\u0119 Mi, aby zachowa\u0107 tarcz\u0119 obronn\u0105, o ile pozostaniecie pos\u0142usznymi i dobrymi istotami pod ka\u017cdym wzgl\u0119dem. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, zapomnieli\u015bcie, \u017ce komunizm zdominuje \u015bwiat i rozprzestrzeni si\u0119 po ziemi. Moje dzieci nie widz\u0105, \u017ce s\u0105 prowadzone ku przepa\u015bci, zdominowane przez tych, kt\u00f3rzy nie pragn\u0105 zbawienia ich dusz. Komunizm daje w\u0142adz\u0119 ma\u0142ym grupom. Te stowarzyszenia wywo\u0142uj\u0105 chaos i znajduj\u0105 ch\u0119tnych do walki o jedzenie i inne potrzeby, kt\u00f3rych im brakuje. Demony s\u0105 na ludzko\u015bci. To jest bardzo niebezpieczne: duchowa ignorancja i nieznajomo\u015b\u0107 Pisma \u015awi\u0119tego. Modlitwa jest niezb\u0119dna, nie modl\u0105c si\u0119 oddalacie si\u0119 od Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej i tej Matki. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119! Moi ukochani, Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 Mojego Syna b\u0119dzie ubrany w \u017ca\u0142ob\u0119, a Moje dzieci stan\u0105 si\u0119 bardziej zdezorientowane, z powodu duchowej ignorancji. Zobaczycie wielki znak w niebie, przed kt\u00f3rym niekt\u00f3re z moich dzieci b\u0119d\u0105 przera\u017cone, a wierni b\u0119d\u0105 wiedzie\u0107, \u017ce b\u0119d\u0105c w stanie wojny, ostrze\u017cenie b\u0119dzie bliskie. B\u0105d\u017acie odpowiedzialne moje dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie prawdziwymi dzie\u0107mi mojego Boskiego Syna. Wydarzenia ludzko\u015bci s\u0105 trudne, stworzenie ludzkie musi si\u0119 teraz nawr\u00f3ci\u0107! Jakby w nast\u0119pnej chwili mia\u0142o nast\u0105pi\u0107 Ostrze\u017cenie. Czujno\u015b\u0107, dzieci! M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Stany Zjednoczone, natura zwraca si\u0119 przeciwko niej. Przyjaciele tego narodu opuszczaj\u0105 j\u0105 po\u015br\u00f3d wojny. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci mojego Boskiego Syna, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Francj\u0119, ogie\u0144 prowadzi do spalenia wielkich pomnik\u00f3w tego narodu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci Mojego Boskiego Syna, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Japoni\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Afganistan, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Australi\u0119, cierpienie przychodzi do tych narod\u00f3w. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, magnetyzm ziemi jest mniejszy. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci przed chorob\u0105, kt\u00f3ra si\u0119 zbli\u017ca, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 przed now\u0105 przeszkod\u0105 w poruszaniu si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119. B\u0105d\u017acie wierni mojemu Boskiemu Synowi. B\u0105d\u017acie ostro\u017cni w pracy i dzia\u0142aniu, cierpienie ludzko\u015bci jest wkr\u00f3tce. Ratujcie dusze dzieci! B\u0105d\u017acie ostro\u017cni i uwa\u017cni na swoich braci, zjednoczcie si\u0119 i b\u0105d\u017acie jednym sercem mi\u0142o\u015bci, modlitwy, ofiary i zado\u015b\u0107uczynienia. Moje serce jest Ark\u0105 Zbawienia. Chroni\u0119 was nieustannie, nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, jestem z wami. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":11,"day":26,"month_string":"November","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: Be filled with the blessings of the Holy Trinity and of our Queen and Mother. I am sent by the Holy Trinity: As we begin the season of advent, I come to remind you of the duty to live peace in your hearts: The duty to live peace in the heart of each one of you. The duty to carry the Divine Light in each one of you and to be light for your brothers. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, the children of the King must prepare to live advent by repenting of sins committed while maintaining faith, hope and charity. The children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ light the first candle of this advent in every temple, in every home, in every heart, knowing that our King and Lord Jesus Christ is the light of the world and will keep that light burning forever and ever. Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, they continue to cling to the material, ignoring how soon the material will be a memory before the imposition of what they will call a new currency. The reaction of mankind will be weeping at the loss of dominion over the material. The human creature will be subdued. Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, when I look at paganism, I see in the midst of humanity how the human creature despises itself by allowing itself to continue to live in the shadows. This is the time for the human creature to send away debauchery and accept to be more and more of the Holy Trinity and of our Queen and Mother of the last times. Convert now! You must not wait. It is urgent that the children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ begin the path of conversion and strengthen the faith. This generation is dominated by earthly power. The evil one has set out to destroy the family and to lead the human creature to despise our Queen and Mother. This generation is in grave danger from the great volcanoes around the world that are awakening one after another. Pray children of God, pray for Japan, it suffers from nature and for its fellow men. Pray children of God, pray, suffering is coming to Brazil. Pray children of God, pray for San Francisco, it suffers because of nature. Pray children of God, pray for Chile, Sumatra, Australia, they are shaken by the force of nature. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, continue to till the spiritual soil, increasing faith, hope and charity. Be love and 'you will receive the rest in addition'. Humanity is purified, it is necessary that through purification Divine love reigns in every heart. I bless you with my sword on high. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: B\u0105d\u017acie nape\u0142nione b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej i naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki. Jestem pos\u0142any przez Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 \u015awi\u0119t\u0105: Rozpoczynaj\u0105c okres adwentu, przychodz\u0119, aby przypomnie\u0107 wam o obowi\u0105zku \u017cycia w pokoju w waszych sercach: Obowi\u0105zek \u017cycia w pokoju w sercu ka\u017cdego z was. Obowi\u0105zek niesienia Boskiego \u015awiat\u0142a w ka\u017cdym z was i bycia \u015bwiat\u0142em dla waszych braci. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, dzieci Kr\u00f3la musz\u0105 przygotowa\u0107 si\u0119 do \u017cycia adwentowego poprzez pokut\u0119 za pope\u0142nione grzechy przy zachowaniu wiary, nadziei i mi\u0142o\u015bci. Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa zapalaj\u0105 pierwsz\u0105 \u015bwiec\u0119 tego adwentu w ka\u017cdej \u015bwi\u0105tyni, w ka\u017cdym domu, w ka\u017cdym sercu, wiedz\u0105c, \u017ce nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus jest \u015bwiat\u0142em \u015bwiata i zachowa to \u015bwiat\u0142o p\u0142on\u0105ce na wieki wiek\u00f3w. Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, nadal trzymaj\u0105 si\u0119 materia\u0142u, ignoruj\u0105c jak wkr\u00f3tce materia\u0142 b\u0119dzie wspomnieniem przed narzuceniem tego, co nazw\u0105 now\u0105 walut\u0105. Reakcj\u0105 ludzko\u015bci b\u0119dzie p\u0142acz z powodu utraty panowania nad materi\u0105. Ludzkie stworzenie zostanie ujarzmione. Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, kiedy patrz\u0119 na poga\u0144stwo, widz\u0119 po\u015br\u00f3d ludzko\u015bci, jak ludzkie stworzenie gardzi sob\u0105, pozwalaj\u0105c sobie na dalsze \u017cycie w cieniu. Jest to czas, aby ludzkie stworzenie odes\u0142a\u0142o rozpust\u0119 i zgodzi\u0142o si\u0119 na to, aby by\u0107 coraz bardziej Tr\u00f3jc\u0105 \u015awi\u0119t\u0105 i nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0105 ostatnich czas\u00f3w. Nawr\u00f3\u0107cie si\u0119 teraz! Nie wolno wam czeka\u0107. Pilne jest, aby dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa rozpocz\u0119\u0142y drog\u0119 nawr\u00f3cenia i umocnienia wiary. To pokolenie jest zdominowane przez ziemsk\u0105 w\u0142adz\u0119. Z\u0142y wyruszy\u0142, aby zniszczy\u0107 rodzin\u0119 i doprowadzi\u0107 ludzkie stworzenie do wzgardzenia nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0105. To pokolenie jest w powa\u017cnym niebezpiecze\u0144stwie ze strony wielkich wulkan\u00f3w na ca\u0142ym \u015bwiecie, kt\u00f3re budz\u0105 si\u0119 jeden po drugim. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci Bo\u017ce, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Japoni\u0119, ona cierpi z powodu przyrody i za swoich bli\u017anich. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci Bo\u017ce, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, cierpienie przychodzi do Brazylii. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci Bo\u017ce, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za San Francisco, cierpi z powodu natury. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci Bo\u017ce, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Chile, Sumatr\u0119, Australi\u0119, one s\u0105 wstrz\u0105sane si\u0142\u0105 natury. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, nadal uprawiaj duchow\u0105 gleb\u0119, zwi\u0119kszaj\u0105c wiar\u0119, nadziej\u0119 i mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107. B\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, a \"reszt\u0119 otrzymacie w dodatku\". Ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest oczyszczona, trzeba, aby poprzez oczyszczenie Boska mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 kr\u00f3lowa\u0142a w ka\u017cdym sercu. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moim mieczem na wysoko\u015bciach. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":11,"day":30,"month_string":"November","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"Beloved children of my Sacred Heart: I come to you with my love, with my mercy. I invite you to look at your own faults, it is necessary that you look at yourselves so that you may be part of those who bear witness to my love. I am unity. My children are confused and divided and are easy prey to evil. They launch themselves to devastate one another? Who possesses greater words, greater faith, hope and charity? And yet they receive me in my body and blood, offending me by not being my children who use the gift of the word to create, but to destroy. These are the high moments when my people suffer because of nature, because of indecent fashions, because of the lack of morals among my people, everything is good because God is mercy! I am mercy and I look at the acts and actions of my people, offending me in the face of so much distancing and disobedience. My children, what is this? It is the product of the fact that my children are not Marian, they do not love my Mother, they are like those who call themselves orphans. This makes them creatures who are not guided by my Mother, intercessor of each one of you. I see how some of my children, by not eating with me, live in the constant novelty of the society that welcomes the worldly and sinful, leading them away from the right way of acting and acting. They forget easily, at the convenience of their erroneous criteria, being easy prey to evil, which at this time has decided to divide my church and lead them to perdition. My beloved people, there are so many countries that suffer the ravages of nature, so many who suffer hunger and thirst for justice... And my children, where are they? They are silenced so that they do not raise their voices! Pray my children, pray for my children who are imprisoned to be silenced and are abandoned. Pray my children, pray for Australia, it is shaking with force and fracturing its land, raising the waters of the sea towards the coasts of South America. Pray my children, pray, the convulsions, the uprisings, the lack of food with which you will begin the coming year, is a sign that you are being led to the time of famine and you will be at the gates of not being able to buy or sell. Pray my children, mankind is absorbed in passing interests, they forget everything, they do not listen or think, their happiness is in the results. Pray my children, pray, the passing of the moment continues and without thinking you will be in the hands of communism. Pray my children, pray, the waters of the ocean are entering the city admired by my children: the city of the great bridge in the United States will live the great tragedy. They know it and do not return to me, but the doom is greater every day. Pray my children, Brazil is plunged into chaos. These my people must banish the moments of merriment where they offend me with sins, especially sins of the flesh. Chaos arrives and my children suffer. Prayer with the heart is urgent, in this way you will attenuate the events and the riots. Pray my children, pray for Spain, it is shaking strongly. Pray my children, pray for Mexico, the earth is shaking, the disease is present. Pray my children, pray, the tiger rose and the lion joined him in silence, they will attack the eagle that has stood upright. Beloved children: your attention must remain focused on me, otherwise, the plagues of evil will rob you of peace, lovelessness will lead you to utter despicable words towards your brothers. It will fill your mouth with words of evil, it will elevate your ego so that you will hurt your brothers. Be dutiful to love and humility. The human creature without humility is easy prey for the devil. Be my very love in these moments when peace hangs on the thought of a human creature. Pray with your heart, be creatures of prayer and unity. Keep yourselves in me, being doers of my will. I bless you my children, 'you are the apple of my eye'. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszego Serca: Przychodz\u0119 do was z moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, z moim mi\u0142osierdziem. Zach\u0119cam was do przyjrzenia si\u0119 w\u0142asnym wadom, konieczne jest, aby\u015bcie spojrzeli na siebie, aby\u015bcie mogli by\u0107 cz\u0119\u015bci\u0105 tych, kt\u00f3rzy daj\u0105 \u015bwiadectwo mojej mi\u0142o\u015bci. Ja jestem jedno\u015bci\u0105. Moje dzieci s\u0105 zdezorientowane i podzielone, s\u0105 \u0142atwym \u0142upem dla z\u0142a. Wystrzeliwuj\u0105 si\u0119 wzajemnie, aby si\u0119 wyniszcza\u0107? Kto posiada wi\u0119ksze s\u0142owa, wi\u0119ksz\u0105 wiar\u0119, nadziej\u0119 i mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107? A jednak przyjmuj\u0105 Mnie w moim ciele i krwi, obra\u017caj\u0105c Mnie przez to, \u017ce nie s\u0105 moimi dzie\u0107mi, kt\u00f3re u\u017cywaj\u0105 daru s\u0142owa do tworzenia, ale do niszczenia. To s\u0105 te wysokie chwile, kiedy m\u00f3j lud cierpi z powodu natury, z powodu nieprzyzwoitych m\u00f3d, z powodu braku moralno\u015bci w\u015br\u00f3d mojego ludu, wszystko jest dobre, bo B\u00f3g jest mi\u0142osierdziem! Ja jestem mi\u0142osierdziem i patrz\u0119 na czyny i post\u0119powanie mojego ludu, obra\u017caj\u0105ce Mnie w obliczu tak wielkiego oddalenia i niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwa. Moje dzieci, co to jest? Jest to produkt tego, \u017ce moje dzieci nie s\u0105 maryjne, nie kochaj\u0105 mojej Matki, s\u0105 jak ci, kt\u00f3rzy nazywaj\u0105 siebie sierotami. To czyni z nich istoty, kt\u00f3re nie s\u0105 prowadzone przez moj\u0105 Matk\u0119, wstawienniczk\u0119 ka\u017cdego z was. Widz\u0119, jak niekt\u00f3re z moich dzieci, nie jedz\u0105c ze Mn\u0105, \u017cyj\u0105 w ci\u0105g\u0142ej nowo\u015bci spo\u0142ecze\u0144stwa, kt\u00f3re przyjmuje to, co \u015bwiatowe i grzeszne, odci\u0105gaj\u0105c je od w\u0142a\u015bciwego sposobu post\u0119powania i dzia\u0142ania. Zapominaj\u0105 \u0142atwo, na wygod\u0119 swoich b\u0142\u0119dnych kryteri\u00f3w, b\u0119d\u0105c \u0142atwym \u0142upem z\u0142a, kt\u00f3re w tym czasie postanowi\u0142o podzieli\u0107 m\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142 i doprowadzi\u0107 go do zguby. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany lud, jest tyle kraj\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re cierpi\u0105 spustoszenie natury, tyle kraj\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re cierpi\u0105 g\u0142\u00f3d i pragn\u0105 sprawiedliwo\u015bci... A moje dzieci, gdzie one s\u0105? S\u0105 uciszane, aby nie podnosi\u0142y g\u0142osu! M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za moje dzieci, kt\u00f3re s\u0105 uwi\u0119zione, aby by\u0142y uciszone i zosta\u0142y opuszczone. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Australi\u0119, ona trz\u0119sie si\u0119 z si\u0142\u0105 i \u0142amie swoj\u0105 ziemi\u0119, podnosz\u0105c wody morza w kierunku wybrze\u017cy Ameryki Po\u0142udniowej. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, konwulsje, powstania, brak \u017cywno\u015bci, z kt\u00f3rym rozpoczniecie nadchodz\u0105cy rok, to znak, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie prowadzeni do czasu g\u0142odu i staniecie u bram niemo\u017cno\u015bci kupna i sprzeda\u017cy. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest poch\u0142oni\u0119ta przemijaj\u0105cymi interesami, zapominaj\u0105 o wszystkim, nie s\u0142uchaj\u0105 i nie my\u015bl\u0105, ich szcz\u0119\u015bcie jest w wynikach. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, przemijanie trwa i bez zastanowienia znajdziecie si\u0119 w r\u0119kach komunizmu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, wody oceanu wkraczaj\u0105 do miasta podziwianego przez moje dzieci: miasta wielkiego mostu w Stanach Zjednoczonych prze\u017cyj\u0105 wielk\u0105 tragedi\u0119. Oni o tym wiedz\u0105 i nie wracaj\u0105 do mnie, ale zguba jest wi\u0119ksza ka\u017cdego dnia. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, Brazylia jest pogr\u0105\u017cona w chaosie. Ci Moi ludzie musz\u0105 wygna\u0107 chwile weso\u0142o\u015bci, w kt\u00f3rych obra\u017caj\u0105 Mnie grzechami, zw\u0142aszcza grzechami cia\u0142a. Nadchodzi chaos i cierpi\u0105 moje dzieci. Modlitwa sercem jest pilna, w ten spos\u00f3b z\u0142agodzicie wydarzenia i zamieszki. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Hiszpani\u0119, ona mocno si\u0119 trz\u0119sie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Meksyk, ziemia si\u0119 trz\u0119sie, choroba jest obecna. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, tygrys powsta\u0142 i lew do\u0142\u0105czy\u0142 do niego w milczeniu, zaatakuj\u0105 or\u0142a, kt\u00f3ry stan\u0105\u0142 w pozycji wyprostowanej. Umi\u0142owane dzieci: wasza uwaga musi pozosta\u0107 skupiona na Mnie, w przeciwnym razie plagi z\u0142a ograbi\u0105 was z pokoju, brak mi\u0142o\u015bci sk\u0142oni was do wypowiadania pod\u0142ych s\u0142\u00f3w wobec waszych braci. Nape\u0142ni wasze usta s\u0142owami z\u0142a, podniesie wasze ego tak, \u017ce b\u0119dziecie krzywdzi\u0107 waszych braci. B\u0105d\u017acie pos\u0142uszni mi\u0142o\u015bci i pokorze. Istota ludzka bez pokory jest \u0142atwym \u0142upem dla diab\u0142a. B\u0105d\u017acie Moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 w tych chwilach, kiedy pok\u00f3j zawis\u0142 na my\u015bl o ludzkim stworzeniu. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 sercem, b\u0105d\u017acie istotami modlitwy i jedno\u015bci. Trwajcie we Mnie, b\u0119d\u0105c wykonawcami mojej woli. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moje dzieci, \"jeste\u015bcie jab\u0142kiem mojego oka\". Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":12,"day":3,"month_string":"December","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Dear children, thank you for being here in prayer and for responding to my call in your hearts. My children, I still ask you for true conversion. Prayer with the heart will be taken to Heaven, so that God may hear your requests, your praises, your thanks. Precious children, many have given themselves over to the enticements of the evil one, but you be upright, righteous, charitable, humble and light a blessed candle when you pray to escape the darkness that grips you. Loving children, I love you with all the love of a Mother and I want you all saved. Dear children, pray for the Church, remember that God is merciful and He is good and despite what you see happening never lose your Faith and Hope. God wants your good and wants to fill you with graces. Do not reject His immense love. Unfaithful children, I say to you: open your eyes and watch God's Justice also fall on this earth. My faithful children, do not be afraid, be close to God with your hearts.  My children, pray for America, she will pay dearly for injustice and perverse laws. Now I leave you with my Motherly blessing, in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit, Amen. Our Lady reminds us again to read and meditate on the book of Revelation of St. John the Apostle.","text_de":"Liebe Kinder, danke, dass ihr hier im Gebet seid und auf meinen Ruf in euren Herzen antwortet. Meine Kinder, ich bitte euch immer noch um wahre Bekehrung. Das Gebet mit dem Herzen wird in den Himmel getragen, damit Gott Ihre Bitten, Ihr Lob, Ihren Dank erh\u00f6rt. Kostbare Kinder, viele haben sich den Verlockungen des B\u00f6sen hingegeben, aber ihr seid aufrecht, gerecht, wohlt\u00e4tig, dem\u00fctig und z\u00fcndet eine gesegnete Kerze an, wenn ihr betet, um der Dunkelheit zu entkommen, die euch erfasst. Liebe Kinder, ich liebe euch mit der ganzen Liebe einer Mutter und ich m\u00f6chte, dass ihr alle gerettet werdet. Liebe Kinder, betet f\u00fcr die Kirche, denkt daran, dass Gott barmherzig und gut ist, und verliert trotz allem, was geschieht, niemals euren Glauben und eure Hoffnung. Gott will dein Wohl und will dich mit Gnaden erf\u00fcllen. Weise Seine unermessliche Liebe nicht zur\u00fcck. Untreue Kinder, ich sage euch: \u00d6ffnet eure Augen und seht zu, wie Gottes Gerechtigkeit auch auf diese Erde f\u00e4llt. Meine treuen Kinder, f\u00fcrchtet euch nicht, seid Gott nahe mit euren Herzen. Meine Kinder, betet f\u00fcr Amerika, es wird f\u00fcr Ungerechtigkeit und perverse Gesetze teuer bezahlen. Nun \u00fcberlasse ich Ihnen meinen m\u00fctterlichen Segen, im Namen des Vaters und des Sohnes und des Heiligen Geistes, Amen. Unsere Liebe Frau erinnert uns erneut daran, das Buch der Offenbarung des heiligen Apostels Johannes zu lesen und dar\u00fcber nachzudenken.","text_es":"Queridos hijos, gracias por estar aqu\u00ed en oraci\u00f3n y por responder a mi llamado en sus corazones. Hijos m\u00edos, todav\u00eda os pido una verdadera conversi\u00f3n. La oraci\u00f3n con el coraz\u00f3n ser\u00e1 llevada al Cielo, para que Dios escuche vuestras peticiones, vuestras alabanzas, vuestros agradecimientos. Amados hijos, muchos se han entregado a las tentaciones del maligno, pero ustedes sean rectos, justos, caritativos, humildes y enciendan una vela bendita cuando oren para escapar de la oscuridad que los atenaza. Hijos amados, os amo con todo el amor de una Madre y os quiero a todos salvos. Queridos hijos, oren por la Iglesia, recuerden que Dios es misericordioso y es bueno ya pesar de lo que vean pasar nunca pierdan la Fe y la Esperanza. Dios quiere vuestro bien y quiere colmaros de gracias. No rechac\u00e9is Su inmenso amor. Hijos infieles, os digo: abrid los ojos y mirad c\u00f3mo la Justicia de Dios cae tambi\u00e9n sobre esta tierra. Mis hijos fieles, no teng\u00e1is miedo, estad cerca de Dios con vuestros corazones. Hijitos, oren por Am\u00e9rica, ella pagar\u00e1 muy cara la injusticia y las leyes perversas. Ahora los dejo con mi bendici\u00f3n maternal, en el nombre del Padre y del Hijo y del Esp\u00edritu Santo, Am\u00e9n. Nuestra Se\u00f1ora nos recuerda nuevamente que leamos y meditemos el libro del Apocalipsis de San Juan Ap\u00f3stol.","text_fr":"Chers enfants, merci d'\u00eatre ici en pri\u00e8re et d'avoir r\u00e9pondu \u00e0 mon appel dans vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, je vous demande encore une vraie conversion. La pri\u00e8re avec le c\u0153ur sera port\u00e9e au Ciel, afin que Dieu entende vos demandes, vos louanges, vos remerciements. Enfants pr\u00e9cieux, beaucoup se sont livr\u00e9s aux s\u00e9ductions du malin, mais soyez droits, justes, charitables, humbles et allumez une bougie b\u00e9nie lorsque vous priez pour \u00e9chapper aux t\u00e9n\u00e8bres qui vous \u00e9treignent. Enfants aimants, je vous aime de tout l'amour d'une M\u00e8re et je vous veux tous sauv\u00e9s. Chers enfants, priez pour l'\u00c9glise, souvenez-vous que Dieu est mis\u00e9ricordieux et qu'Il est bon et malgr\u00e9 ce que vous voyez arriver, ne perdez jamais votre Foi et votre Esp\u00e9rance. Dieu veut votre bien et veut vous combler de gr\u00e2ces. Ne rejetez pas son immense amour. Enfants infid\u00e8les, je vous dis : ouvrez les yeux et voyez aussi la Justice de Dieu tomber sur cette terre. Mes enfants fid\u00e8les, n'ayez pas peur, soyez proches de Dieu avec vos c\u0153urs. Mes enfants, priez pour l'Am\u00e9rique, elle paiera cher l'injustice et les lois perverses. Maintenant, je vous laisse avec ma b\u00e9n\u00e9diction maternelle, au nom du P\u00e8re et du Fils et du Saint-Esprit, Amen. Notre-Dame nous rappelle \u00e0 nouveau de lire et de m\u00e9diter sur le livre de l'Apocalypse de saint Jean l'Ap\u00f4tre.","text_it":"Cari figli, grazie per essere qui nella preghiera e per aver risposto alla mia chiamata nel vostro cuore. Figli miei, vi chiedo ancora la vera conversione. La preghiera con il cuore sar\u00e0 portata in Cielo, affinch\u00e9 Dio ascolti le vostre richieste, le vostre lodi, i vostri ringraziamenti. Figli preziosi, molti si sono dati alle lusinghe del maligno, ma voi siate retti, giusti, caritatevoli, umili e accendete una candela benedetta quando pregate per sfuggire alle tenebre che vi attanagliano. Figli amorevoli, Io vi amo con tutto l\u2019amore di una Madre e vi voglio salvi tutti. Cari figli, pregate per la Chiesa, ricordate che Dio \u00e8 misericordioso ed \u00e8 buono e nonostante ci\u00f2 che vedrete accadere non perdete mai la Fede e la Speranza. Dio vuole il vostro bene e vuole riempirvi di grazie. Non rifiutate il Suo immenso amore. Figli infedeli, dico a voi: aprite gi occhi e guardate anche la giustizia di Dio cadere su questa terra. Figli miei fedeli, non abbiate paura, siate vicino a Dio con il cuore.  Figli, pregate per l\u2019America, pagher\u00e0 a caro prezzo le ingiustizie e le leggi perverse. Ora vi lascio con la mia benedizione Materna, nel nome del Padre, del Figlio e dello Spirito Santo. Amen. La Madonna ricorda ancora di leggere e di meditare il libro dell\u2019Apocalisse di San Giovanni apostolo.","text_pl":"Drogie dzieci, dzi\u0119kuj\u0119 wam, \u017ce jeste\u015bcie tu na modlitwie i \u017ce odpowiadacie na moje wezwanie w waszych sercach. Moje dzieci, ponownie prosz\u0119 was o prawdziwe nawr\u00f3cenie. Modlitwa sercem b\u0119dzie zaniesiona do nieba, aby B\u00f3g us\u0142ysza\u0142 wasze pro\u015bby, wasze uwielbienia, wasze podzi\u0119kowania. Drogie dzieci, wielu odda\u0142o si\u0119 na pastw\u0119 Z\u0142ego, ale wy b\u0105d\u017acie prawi, sprawiedliwi, mi\u0142osierni, pokorni i zapalajcie b\u0142ogos\u0142awion\u0105 \u015bwiec\u0119, kiedy modlicie si\u0119, aby uciec z ciemno\u015bci, kt\u00f3ra was ogarnia. Kochane dzieci, kocham was z ca\u0142\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 Matki i pragn\u0119, aby\u015bcie wszyscy byli zbawieni. Drogie dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142, pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce B\u00f3g jest mi\u0142osierny i dobry i mimo tego, co zobaczycie, \u017ce si\u0119 dzieje, nigdy nie tra\u0107cie wiary i nadziei. B\u00f3g chce twojego dobra i chce ci\u0119 nape\u0142ni\u0107 \u0142askami. Nie odrzucajcie Jego ogromnej mi\u0142o\u015bci. Niewierne dzieci, m\u00f3wi\u0119 wam: otw\u00f3rzcie oczy i zobaczcie te\u017c, jak Sprawiedliwo\u015b\u0107 Bo\u017ca spada na t\u0119 ziemi\u0119. Moje wierne dzieci, nie b\u00f3jcie si\u0119, swoimi sercami b\u0105d\u017acie blisko Boga. Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ameryk\u0119, ona drogo zap\u0142aci za niesprawiedliwo\u015b\u0107 i przewrotne prawa. Teraz zostawiam was z moim matczynym b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem, w imi\u0119 Ojca i Syna i Ducha \u015awi\u0119tego, Amen. Matka Bo\u017ca ponownie przypomina nam, aby\u015bmy czytali i rozwa\u017cali ksi\u0119g\u0119 Apokalipsy \u015bw. Jana Aposto\u0142a.","text_pt":"Queridos filhos, obrigado por estarem aqui em ora\u00e7\u00e3o e por responderem ao Meu chamado em seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, ainda vos pe\u00e7o a verdadeira convers\u00e3o. A ora\u00e7\u00e3o com o cora\u00e7\u00e3o ser\u00e1 levada ao C\u00e9u, para que Deus ou\u00e7a seus pedidos, seus louvores, seus agradecimentos. Filhos preciosos, muitos se entregaram \u00e0s tenta\u00e7\u00f5es do maligno, mas sejam retos, justos, caridosos, humildes e acendam uma vela aben\u00e7oada quando orarem para escapar da escurid\u00e3o que os domina. Filhos amorosos, amo-vos com todo o amor de M\u00e3e e quero-vos todos salvos. Queridos filhos, rezem pela Igreja, lembrem-se que Deus \u00e9 misericordioso e Ele \u00e9 bom e apesar do que voc\u00eas veem acontecer, nunca percam sua F\u00e9 e Esperan\u00e7a. Deus quer o seu bem e quer ench\u00ea-lo de gra\u00e7as. N\u00e3o rejeite Seu imenso amor. Filhos infi\u00e9is, eu vos digo: abram os olhos e vejam a Justi\u00e7a de Deus cair tamb\u00e9m nesta terra. Meus filhos fi\u00e9is, n\u00e3o tenham medo, fiquem perto de Deus com seus cora\u00e7\u00f5es. Meus filhos, rezem pela Am\u00e9rica, ela pagar\u00e1 caro pela injusti\u00e7a e pelas leis perversas. Agora deixo-vos com a minha b\u00ean\u00e7\u00e3o materna, em nome do Pai e do Filho e do Esp\u00edrito Santo, Am\u00e9m. Nossa Senhora nos lembra novamente de ler e meditar no livro do Apocalipse de S\u00e3o Jo\u00e3o Ap\u00f3stolo.","text_zh":"\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u4f60\u4eec\u6765\u5230\u8fd9\u91cc\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u611f\u8c22\u4f60\u4eec\u5728\u5fc3\u4e2d\u56de\u5e94\u6211\u7684\u547c\u5524\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u4ecd\u7136\u8981\u6c42\u4f60\u4eec\u771f\u6b63\u7684\u7688\u4f9d\u3002\u7528\u5fc3\u7948\u7977\u4f1a\u88ab\u5e26\u5230\u5929\u5802\uff0c\u8fd9\u6837\u4e0a\u5e1d\u5c31\u4f1a\u542c\u5230\u4f60\u7684\u8bf7\u6c42\u3001\u4f60\u7684\u8d5e\u7f8e\u548c\u4f60\u7684\u611f\u8c22\u3002\u5b9d\u8d35\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u8bb8\u591a\u4eba\u5df2\u7ecf\u5c48\u670d\u4e8e\u90aa\u6076\u8005\u7684\u5f15\u8bf1\uff0c\u4f46\u4f60\u4eec\u8981\u6b63\u76f4\u3001\u6b63\u76f4\u3001\u4ec1\u6148\u3001\u8c26\u900a\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u7948\u7977\u9003\u79bb\u7b3c\u7f69\u7740\u4f60\u4eec\u7684\u9ed1\u6697\u65f6\u70b9\u71c3\u4e00\u652f\u6709\u798f\u7684\u8721\u70db\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u4ee5\u6bcd\u4eb2\u7684\u5168\u90e8\u7231\u6765\u7231\u4f60\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u5e0c\u671b\u4f60\u4eec\u90fd\u5f97\u6551\u3002\u4eb2\u7231\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e3a\u6559\u4f1a\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u8bb0\u4f4f\u4e0a\u5e1d\u662f\u4ec1\u6148\u7684\uff0c\u4ed6\u662f\u5584\u826f\u7684\uff0c\u5c3d\u7ba1\u4f60\u770b\u5230\u53d1\u751f\u4e86\u4ec0\u4e48\uff0c\u4f46\u6c38\u8fdc\u4e0d\u8981\u5931\u53bb\u4f60\u7684\u4fe1\u4ef0\u548c\u5e0c\u671b\u3002\u4e0a\u5e1d\u60f3\u8981\u4f60\u7684\u597d\u5904\uff0c\u60f3\u8981\u7528\u6069\u5178\u5145\u6ee1\u4f60\u3002\u4e0d\u8981\u62d2\u7edd\u7942\u65e0\u9650\u7684\u7231\u3002\u4e0d\u5fe0\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u6211\u5bf9\u4f60\u4eec\u8bf4\uff1a\u7741\u5f00\u4f60\u4eec\u7684\u773c\u775b\uff0c\u770b\u770b\u4e0a\u5e1d\u7684\u6b63\u4e49\u4e5f\u964d\u4e34\u5728\u8fd9\u4e2a\u5730\u7403\u4e0a\u3002\u6211\u5fe0\u5b9e\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e0d\u8981\u5bb3\u6015\uff0c\u8981\u5168\u5fc3\u4eb2\u8fd1\u4e0a\u5e1d\u3002\u6211\u7684\u5b69\u5b50\u4eec\uff0c\u4e3a\u7f8e\u56fd\u7948\u7977\uff0c\u5979\u5c06\u4e3a\u4e0d\u516c\u6b63\u548c\u4e0d\u6b63\u5f53\u7684\u6cd5\u5f8b\u4ed8\u51fa\u9ad8\u6602\u7684\u4ee3\u4ef7\u3002\u73b0\u5728\u6211\u4ee5\u5723\u7236\u3001\u5723\u5b50\u548c\u5723\u7075\u7684\u540d\u4e49\uff0c\u5c06\u6bcd\u4eb2\u822c\u7684\u795d\u798f\u7559\u7ed9\u4f60\u4eec\uff0c\u963f\u4eec\u3002\u5723\u6bcd\u518d\u6b21\u63d0\u9192\u6211\u4eec\u9605\u8bfb\u548c\u9ed8\u60f3\u4f7f\u5f92\u5723\u82e5\u671b\u7684\u542f\u793a\u5f55\u3002","source":"Trevignano Romano"},{"year":2022,"month":12,"day":5,"month_string":"December","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: As members of the mystical body of Christ, you are called to keep the faith and to be creatures of prayer, not only with words, but with testimony. Be creatures of faith and love, and at the same time be conscious that the haughty, the arrogant, the proud, the person who is unaware of what it means to be a child of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, is easy prey for the devil; he is constantly led by the evil one to be 'a stumbling block for his brothers'. Our King and Lord Jesus Christ grieves greatly over these foolish children who live half-heartedly, bringing evil upon themselves. Human foolishness, the fruit of the misuse of free will, leads human beings to plunge into suffering that they have brought upon themselves, and from which it will be difficult for them to emerge until they acknowledge that 'God is the Lord'. Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: When human beings give themselves over to human pleasures, they decay spiritually and punish themselves, entering into the darkness that worldliness makes them see as light in order to keep them in sin. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, this is not the time for a half-hearted spiritual life. Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, I call you to take sure steps. This is not a time to spend your lives senselessly; on the contrary, it is imperative for you to be authentic in your inner life. Blessings stand before you, people of God, but at the same time you attract evil by your unbridled works and behaviour. Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, you will suffer as humanity due to the continuous reaction of volcanoes that will provoke great eruptions and prevent you from continuing as is normal at the moment. Entire communities will be moved to safer places to prevent the gases from volcanic eruptions from causing irreparable damage. The earth will continue to shake everywhere, without stopping. Pray, children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, pray for Mexico: it will suffer due to nature and betrayal. Pray for Brazil: people will be exasperated, causing riots and the suffering of the innocent. Water will purify this nation. Pray for Japan: it will suffer greatly due to nature and by human hand. Pray for Indonesia: it will suffer greatly due to nature. Pray for Argentina, this nation will be tested. Intruders will spread dissent and create chaos, setting people against one another. Pray for this nation. Pray for Central America: it will suffer due to nature. You must pray with your heart. Pray for the United States, pray that its leaders would be cautious in their works and actions. Pray, because nature will continue to act forcefully in that nation. Pray with confidence and truth; pray for your brothers and sisters who are lukewarm in faith and do not bear witness to love, charity and fraternity. Receive the body and blood of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Pray the holy rosary as a sign of love for our Queen and Mother. Be faithful to God and love unity. Be faithful, each in your own state, for blessing and firmness in the faith are born of faithfulness. Wait with holy patience for the Angel of Peace, who will revive the hope that some of you have not lost, but which has been weakened by so many things that you have been facing. Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: Be charitable towards your fellow men. Charity is the bond that unites you. Human beings with hardened hearts are acting against charity in order to cause division, which the devil is currently fomenting against the mystical body of Christ. You must pray, you must fulfil prayer, you must put being children of our King and Lord into practice by working and acting in the manner of Christ. As children of so divine a redeemer, continue without fear, with confidence and the faith that in being doers of the Divine Will, you will have your reward. I protect you by divine command, I bless you with my sword. Faith, faith, faith. St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.  ","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Jako cz\u0142onkowie mistycznego Cia\u0142a Chrystusa jeste\u015bcie powo\u0142ani do zachowania wiary i do bycia stworzeniami modlitwy, nie tylko s\u0142owami, ale i \u015bwiadectwem. B\u0105d\u017acie stworzeniami wiary i mi\u0142o\u015bci, a jednocze\u015bnie b\u0105d\u017acie \u015bwiadomi, \u017ce cz\u0142owiek wynios\u0142y, arogancki, dumny, osoba, kt\u00f3ra nie jest \u015bwiadoma, co to znaczy by\u0107 dzieckiem naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, jest \u0142atwym \u0142upem dla diab\u0142a; jest stale prowadzona przez z\u0142ego, aby by\u0107 \"przeszkod\u0105 dla swoich braci\". Nasz Kr\u00f3l i Pan Jezus Chrystus bardzo boleje nad tymi g\u0142upimi dzie\u0107mi, kt\u00f3re \u017cyj\u0105 po\u0142owicznie, sprowadzaj\u0105c na siebie z\u0142o. G\u0142upota ludzka, owoc nadu\u017cycia wolnej woli, prowadzi cz\u0142owieka do pogr\u0105\u017cenia si\u0119 w cierpieniu, kt\u00f3re sam na siebie sprowadzi\u0142, a z kt\u00f3rego trudno mu b\u0119dzie wyj\u015b\u0107, dop\u00f3ki nie uzna, \u017ce \"B\u00f3g jest Panem\". Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Gdy cz\u0142owiek oddaje si\u0119 ludzkim przyjemno\u015bciom, rozk\u0142ada si\u0119 duchowo i sam siebie karze, wchodz\u0105c w ciemno\u015bci, kt\u00f3re \u015bwiatowo\u015b\u0107 ka\u017ce mu postrzega\u0107 jako \u015bwiat\u0142o, aby utrzyma\u0107 go w grzechu. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, to nie jest czas na po\u0142owiczne \u017cycie duchowe. Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, wzywam was do podj\u0119cia pewnych krok\u00f3w. Nie jest to czas na bezsensowne sp\u0119dzanie \u017cycia, wr\u0119cz przeciwnie, konieczne jest, aby\u015bcie byli autentyczni w swoim \u017cyciu wewn\u0119trznym. B\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwa stoj\u0105 przed wami, ludu Bo\u017cy, ale jednocze\u015bnie przyci\u0105gacie z\u0142o przez swoje nieokie\u0142znane dzie\u0142a i zachowania. Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, b\u0119dziecie cierpie\u0107 jako ludzko\u015b\u0107 z powodu ci\u0105g\u0142ej reakcji wulkan\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re wywo\u0142aj\u0105 wielkie erupcje i uniemo\u017cliwi\u0105 wam kontynuowanie tego, co jest obecnie normalne. Ca\u0142e spo\u0142eczno\u015bci b\u0119d\u0105 przenoszone w bezpieczniejsze miejsca, aby gazy z erupcji wulkan\u00f3w nie spowodowa\u0142y nieodwracalnych szk\u00f3d. Ziemia nadal b\u0119dzie si\u0119 trz\u0105\u015b\u0107 wsz\u0119dzie, bez przerwy. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Meksyk: b\u0119dzie cierpia\u0142 z powodu natury i zdrady. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Brazyli\u0119: ludzie b\u0119d\u0105 rozjuszeni, powoduj\u0105c zamieszki i cierpienie niewinnych. Woda oczy\u015bci ten nar\u00f3d. M\u00f3dl si\u0119 za Japoni\u0119: b\u0119dzie bardzo cierpie\u0107 z powodu natury i z r\u0119ki cz\u0142owieka. M\u00f3dl si\u0119 za Indonezj\u0119: b\u0119dzie bardzo cierpie\u0107 z powodu natury. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Argentyn\u0119: ten nar\u00f3d b\u0119dzie poddany pr\u00f3bie. Intruzi b\u0119d\u0105 szerzy\u0107 niezgod\u0119 i tworzy\u0107 chaos, nastawiaj\u0105c ludzi przeciwko sobie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za ten nar\u00f3d. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Ameryk\u0119 \u015arodkow\u0105: b\u0119dzie cierpie\u0107 z powodu natury. Musicie modli\u0107 si\u0119 sercem. M\u00f3dl si\u0119 za Stany Zjednoczone, m\u00f3dl si\u0119, aby ich przyw\u00f3dcy byli ostro\u017cni w swoich pracach i dzia\u0142aniach. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, poniewa\u017c natura b\u0119dzie nadal dzia\u0142a\u0107 z moc\u0105 w tym narodzie. M\u00f3dl si\u0119 z ufno\u015bci\u0105 i prawd\u0105; m\u00f3dl si\u0119 za swoich braci i siostry, kt\u00f3rzy s\u0105 letni w wierze i nie daj\u0105 \u015bwiadectwa mi\u0142o\u015bci, mi\u0142o\u015bci i braterstwa. Przyjmijcie Cia\u0142o i Krew naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Odmawiajcie r\u00f3\u017caniec \u015bwi\u0119ty jako znak mi\u0142o\u015bci do naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki. B\u0105d\u017acie wierni Bogu i mi\u0142ujcie jedno\u015b\u0107. B\u0105d\u017acie wierni, ka\u017cdy w swoim stanie, bo z wierno\u015bci rodzi si\u0119 b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo i sta\u0142o\u015b\u0107 w wierze. Czekajcie ze \u015bwi\u0119t\u0105 cierpliwo\u015bci\u0105 na Anio\u0142a Pokoju, kt\u00f3ry o\u017cywi nadziej\u0119, kt\u00f3rej niekt\u00f3rzy z was nie utracili, ale kt\u00f3ra zosta\u0142a os\u0142abiona przez tak wiele spraw, z kt\u00f3rymi si\u0119 borykacie. Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: B\u0105d\u017acie mi\u0142osierni wobec waszych bli\u017anich. Mi\u0142osierdzie jest wi\u0119zi\u0105, kt\u00f3ra was \u0142\u0105czy. Istoty ludzkie o zatwardzia\u0142ych sercach wyst\u0119puj\u0105 przeciwko mi\u0142osierdziu, aby wywo\u0142a\u0107 podzia\u0142, kt\u00f3ry diabe\u0142 obecnie podsyca przeciwko mistycznemu Cia\u0142u Chrystusa. Musicie si\u0119 modli\u0107, musicie wype\u0142nia\u0107 modlitw\u0119, musicie wciela\u0107 w \u017cycie bycie dzie\u0107mi naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana, pracuj\u0105c i dzia\u0142aj\u0105c na wz\u00f3r Chrystusa. Jako dzieci tak boskiego Odkupiciela, trwajcie bez strachu, z ufno\u015bci\u0105 i wiar\u0105, \u017ce b\u0119d\u0105c wykonawcami woli Bo\u017cej, otrzymacie swoj\u0105 nagrod\u0119. Chroni\u0119 was przez Boski rozkaz, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moim mieczem. Wiara, wiara, wiara. \u015aw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.  ","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":12,"day":9,"month_string":"December","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"Beloved children, receive my blessing united to my merciful Love. In the midst of the affliction in which you live and what is approaching, I call you to love my most holy Mother, who intercedes for each of my children. My blessed Mother loves you all and desires that all be saved. My people, without forgetting the warning, of which all human creatures will participate, you must review your life promptly and make reparation for the evil committed. My beloved, not only the human creature will suffer spiritually, but the earth will be purified by the blow of the heavenly body which the earth will receive and which you will see as a burst on high. That burst which will illuminate the earth and from which fire will fall from on high, will cause the waters of the seas to invade the earth. My beloved people, without getting into panic at this moment, how you must work and act is by detaching yourselves from the mundane. My people: They do not obey me; they refuse to be humble and to accept that they have a duty to change and not allow that misused human self to keep them in pride. They are my people, all humanity is my people, as all are my children. My people are not a special selection of children who pray more or who are better than the rest of their brothers. My people are all mankind. Thus, I love you, my people. Do not forget that the process of war is in ferment. War comes and my children suffer. At this moment there are several nations that are ready to be the first nation to attack another and from there the war will spread across the earth. When you least expect it, when you least think it, the scourge of war will happen and humanity will enter into chaos. War is the punishment that humanity itself will inflict on itself: punishment product of human selfishness... Product of the superiority that the majority of the rulers believe they possess over the peoples... Punishment resulting from the fact that they do not believe in me... Of the contempt to which I am continually subjected... Of the offenses against me, of the profanations and sacrileges that I continually receive... My Mother is treated with contempt, her most loving heart bleeds before so many offenses to which my people submit her. My most holy Immaculate Mother desires that my people, her children, be creatures of faith, humble creatures like her, creatures that unite and not disunite. This generation will receive the antichrist; they will follow him because of their ignorance of me, because of their disobedience to me and to what my Mother has revealed to them. They will accept the new doctrine that will be presented to them, forgetting that 'I am the Way, the Truth and the Life'. I have insisted on pride because this is what the human creature is saturated with and the antichrist is already taking from the proud, giving power in one place or another to those who out of pride feel that they are superior to their brothers. My children, confusion is entering my church and where there is confusion, I do not find myself, but the enemy of the soul has entered. You my children, know me so that you may recognize me. Be wary of those who invite you to act and act contrary to what I have taught you. Be on your guard, 'wolves in sheep's clothing' abound at this time. My people, beloved my people, continue to walk in the faith, not because of tradition, but because you know me and by knowing me you love me. Keep yourselves prepared for what is coming to earth, to humanity. Without thinking that the disease has been defeated, be cautious and prevent the organism by keeping the body's defences high. I am your God and I prepare you for what is coming to mankind. Pray my children, pray, the volcanoes continue to activate causing suffering to human creatures. Pray my children, pray for Greece, it will suffer for nature. Pray my children, pray, Nepal is shaken. Pray my children, pray for those who do not believe in my calls. Pray my children, pray for your brothers who do not love me. Pray my children, pray for the inattention with which my people live this moment which is of peace and not of so much noise or so much sin, because humanity will be surprised without expecting it. I protect you; I help you so that you may keep yourselves spiritually on the right path. Ask me for the help you need, be creatures of faith, love, forgiveness, charity and fraternity. My beloved ones: Receive my blessing and without fear be assured that I protect you. Therefore, you need a heart of flesh and not of stone. Keep faith in my word, in my promises and I will not abandon you. I bless your thoughts, your minds and your hearts so that you may act and act according to my example. My love is infinite, as my blessing is infinite. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci, przyjmijcie moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo zjednoczone z moj\u0105 Mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 Mi\u0142osiern\u0105. W\u015br\u00f3d utrapie\u0144, w kt\u00f3rych \u017cyjecie i kt\u00f3re si\u0119 zbli\u017caj\u0105, wzywam was do mi\u0142o\u015bci mojej naj\u015bwi\u0119tszej Matki, kt\u00f3ra wstawia si\u0119 za ka\u017cdym z moich dzieci. Moja b\u0142ogos\u0142awiona Matka kocha was wszystkich i pragnie, aby wszyscy zostali zbawieni. M\u00f3j ludu, nie zapominaj\u0105c o ostrze\u017ceniu, w kt\u00f3rym uczestniczy\u0107 b\u0119d\u0105 wszystkie ludzkie stworzenia, musicie szybko przejrze\u0107 swoje \u017cycie i zado\u015b\u0107uczyni\u0107 za pope\u0142nione z\u0142o. Moi ukochani, nie tylko ludzkie stworzenie b\u0119dzie cierpie\u0107 duchowo, ale ziemia zostanie oczyszczona przez uderzenie cia\u0142a niebieskiego, kt\u00f3re otrzyma ziemia i kt\u00f3re zobaczycie jako wybuch na wysoko\u015bci. Ten wybuch, kt\u00f3ry roz\u015bwietli ziemi\u0119 i z kt\u00f3rego spadnie ogie\u0144 z wysoko\u015bci, spowoduje wtargni\u0119cie w\u00f3d m\u00f3rz na ziemi\u0119. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, bez wpadania w panik\u0119 w tej chwili, to jak musicie pracowa\u0107 i dzia\u0142a\u0107 to poprzez oderwanie si\u0119 od tego co przyziemne. M\u00f3j lud: Nie s\u0105 Mi pos\u0142uszni; odmawiaj\u0105 pokory i przyj\u0119cia, \u017ce maj\u0105 obowi\u0105zek si\u0119 zmieni\u0107 i nie pozwoli\u0107, aby to nadu\u017cywane ludzkie ja utrzymywa\u0142o ich w pychy. Oni s\u0105 moim ludem, ca\u0142a ludzko\u015b\u0107 jest moim ludem, tak jak wszyscy s\u0105 moimi dzie\u0107mi. M\u00f3j lud nie jest specjaln\u0105 selekcj\u0105 dzieci, kt\u00f3re modl\u0105 si\u0119 wi\u0119cej lub kt\u00f3re s\u0105 lepsze od reszty swoich braci. Moim ludem jest ca\u0142a ludzko\u015b\u0107. Dlatego kocham was, m\u00f3j ludu. Nie zapominajcie, \u017ce proces wojny jest w fazie fermentu. Wojna przychodzi i moje dzieci cierpi\u0105. W tej chwili jest kilka narod\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re s\u0105 gotowe by\u0107 pierwszym narodem, kt\u00f3ry zaatakuje inny i stamt\u0105d wojna rozprzestrzeni si\u0119 po ca\u0142ej ziemi. Kiedy najmniej si\u0119 tego spodziewacie, kiedy najmniej o tym my\u015blicie, plaga wojny nast\u0105pi i ludzko\u015b\u0107 wejdzie w chaos. Wojna jest kar\u0105, kt\u00f3r\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107 sama sobie wymierzy: kar\u0105 b\u0119d\u0105c\u0105 produktem ludzkiego egoizmu... Produktem wy\u017cszo\u015bci, jak\u0105 wi\u0119kszo\u015b\u0107 w\u0142adc\u00f3w uwa\u017ca, \u017ce posiada nad ludami... Kara wynikaj\u0105ca z faktu, \u017ce nie wierz\u0105 we Mnie... Z pogardy, kt\u00f3rej jestem nieustannie poddawany... O obrazach wobec Mnie, o profanacjach i \u015bwi\u0119tokradztwach, kt\u00f3re nieustannie otrzymuj\u0119... Moja Matka jest traktowana z pogard\u0105, Jej najukocha\u0144sze Serce krwawi przed tyloma zniewagami, kt\u00f3rym poddaje J\u0105 m\u00f3j lud. Moja naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Niepokalana Matka pragnie, aby m\u00f3j lud, Jej dzieci, by\u0142 istotami wiary, pokornymi istotami jak Ona, istotami, kt\u00f3re jednocz\u0105, a nie rozdzielaj\u0105. To pokolenie przyjmie antychrysta; p\u00f3jd\u0105 za nim z powodu ich nieznajomo\u015bci Mnie, z powodu ich niepos\u0142usze\u0144stwa wobec Mnie i wobec tego, co objawi\u0142a im moja Matka. Przyjm\u0105 now\u0105 doktryn\u0119, kt\u00f3ra zostanie im przedstawiona, zapominaj\u0105c, \u017ce \"Ja jestem Drog\u0105, Prawd\u0105 i \u017byciem\". Nalega\u0142em na pych\u0119, poniewa\u017c tym jest przesycone ludzkie stworzenie i antychryst ju\u017c bierze od dumnych, daj\u0105c w\u0142adz\u0119 w tym czy innym miejscu tym, kt\u00f3rzy z pychy czuj\u0105, \u017ce s\u0105 lepsi od swoich braci. Moje dzieci, zamieszanie wchodzi do mojego Ko\u015bcio\u0142a, a tam gdzie jest zamieszanie, nie znajduj\u0119 siebie, ale wszed\u0142 wr\u00f3g duszy. Wy, moje dzieci, poznajcie mnie, aby\u015bcie mogli mnie rozpozna\u0107. B\u0105d\u017acie ostro\u017cni wobec tych, kt\u00f3rzy zach\u0119caj\u0105 was do dzia\u0142ania i post\u0119puj\u0105 niezgodnie z tym, czego was nauczy\u0142em. B\u0105d\u017acie czujni, \"wilki w owczej sk\u00f3rze\" obfituj\u0105 w tym czasie. M\u00f3j lud, umi\u0142owany m\u00f3j lud, nadal kroczcie w wierze, nie z powodu tradycji, ale dlatego, \u017ce mnie znacie, a znaj\u0105c mnie, kochacie mnie. Przygotowujcie si\u0119 na to, co nadchodzi na ziemi\u0119, na ludzko\u015b\u0107. Nie my\u015bl\u0105c, \u017ce choroba zosta\u0142a pokonana, b\u0105d\u017acie ostro\u017cni i zapobiegajcie jej, utrzymuj\u0105c wysoki poziom obrony organizmu. Ja jestem waszym Bogiem i przygotowuj\u0119 was na to, co nadchodzi na ludzko\u015b\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, wulkany nadal aktywuj\u0105 si\u0119 powoduj\u0105c cierpienie dla ludzkich stworze\u0144. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Grecj\u0119, ona b\u0119dzie cierpie\u0107 za natur\u0119. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, Nepal jest wstrz\u0105\u015bni\u0119ty. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za tych, kt\u00f3rzy nie wierz\u0105 w moje wezwania. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za waszych braci, kt\u00f3rzy mnie nie kochaj\u0105. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za nieuwag\u0119, z jak\u0105 m\u00f3j lud prze\u017cywa t\u0119 chwil\u0119, kt\u00f3ra jest chwil\u0105 pokoju, a nie tak wielkiego ha\u0142asu lub tak wielkiego grzechu, poniewa\u017c ludzko\u015b\u0107 zostanie zaskoczona, nie spodziewaj\u0105c si\u0119 tego. Chroni\u0119 was; pomagam wam, aby\u015bcie mogli utrzyma\u0107 si\u0119 duchowo na w\u0142a\u015bciwej drodze. Pro\u015bcie mnie o pomoc, kt\u00f3rej potrzebujecie, b\u0105d\u017acie istotami wiary, mi\u0142o\u015bci, przebaczenia, mi\u0142osierdzia i braterstwa. Moi umi\u0142owani: Przyjmijcie moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo i bez l\u0119ku b\u0105d\u017acie pewni, \u017ce was chroni\u0119. Dlatego potrzebujecie serca z cia\u0142a, a nie z kamienia. Zachowajcie wiar\u0119 w moje s\u0142owo, w moje obietnice, a ja was nie opuszcz\u0119. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 wasze my\u015bli, wasze umys\u0142y i wasze serca, aby\u015bcie mogli dzia\u0142a\u0107 i post\u0119powa\u0107 wed\u0142ug mojego przyk\u0142adu. Moja mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 jest niesko\u0144czona, tak jak niesko\u0144czone jest moje b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwo. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":12,"day":16,"month_string":"December","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: I am sent by the Holy Trinity to make known to you the word which is the Will of God. In the unity of a people walking in the footsteps of their King and Lord, continue to be knowledgeable about the good you should do and thus avoid evil. The awareness that 'God is a God of the living' must remain in the human creature, only in this way will humanity come to aspire to be more spiritual with full knowledge that without God they are nothing. Live in the tireless quest to stay closer to the Holy Trinity, to our Queen and Mother, to the Archangels and angels so that you may live desiring the divine and work and act within the good. Children of God, you find yourselves in the moment of expectation before the fulfilment of the prophecies announced with clear signs that foreshadow what is to come: Look at nature how it acts\u2026 The human creature has moved away from the temples and they do not adore our King and Lord Jesus Christ.... They receive the holy eucharist in mortal sin.... They despise and refuse to pray the holy rosary.... They mock the sacramentals.... The most Holy Trinity calls his priests to dress with dignity in their priestly vestments, since dressing as a consecrated creature has led to their being disrespected and mistaken for creatures not consecrated to the priestly ministry. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ must be constantly prepared for the coming food shortage and the strong change in the climate, especially in Europe. The earth's core is being affected by the magnetism of a celestial body approaching the earth. Europe will go through this time with extreme snowfall and cold not felt before. America will experience a change in its climate, temperatures will drop and they will feel cold, but not as extreme. It is the time of the warning for them to believe and mend their ways. Water appears where there is sand and where there is water, sand appears. Volcanoes roar in various countries all over the earth. The desert is invaded by water and where there is water, there will be desert. Pray, pray, pray children of our Lord and King Jesus Christ for the conversion of humanity, pray for the Asian continent. Pray, pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ for the shortage of food. Pray, pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, for the social uprisings and persecution in the countries. Pray, pray children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, from within the countries that have welcomed you, the fierce persecutors of the Christian faith will come out. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, keep our Queen and Mother attentive to the needs of each one through the prayer of the holy rosary, so that the pride that grows in the human creature may be weakened and overcome by humility. Pride is characteristic of the evil one, oppressor of souls, it mires the creature, it envelops him in evil and envy. Pride deforms the human creature in his actions and deeds, it blinds him and makes him unrecognizable. Act with humility, not with false humility, not with forced humility, but with the humility of the light that comes from our King and Lord Jesus Christ. Believe, believe, overcome sin, firmly repent by confessing and with a firm purpose of amendment, so that you will be new and renewed creatures by Divine Mercy. Be spiritually alert, be simple and humble creatures of heart. Knowledge should not be exhibited, but acted upon as a testimony of what dwells within each one of you. Prudence is a great companion for the gifts. The prudent do not expose themselves to be overthrown. These are serious times, very serious times where temptations, dissatisfaction, division and pleasures are being spread with haste by the spirits of evil. The human creature who repents, who recognizes God as his Lord and saviour and begins a new life, is guided by his guardian angel, a companion on the way so that he does not get lost. Go forward children of God, go forward united in the expectation of the fulfilment of all that has been prophesied. Keep the peace and be fraternal. You are accompanied by my legions, protected by our Queen and Mother and rescued by the blood of the Divine Lamb. Do not fear, grow in faith! St. Michael the Archangel. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Jestem pos\u0142any przez Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105, aby wam oznajmi\u0107 s\u0142owo, kt\u00f3re jest Wol\u0105 Bo\u017c\u0105. W jedno\u015bci ludu id\u0105cego \u015bladami swego Kr\u00f3la i Pana, trwajcie w \u015bwiadomo\u015bci dobra, kt\u00f3re powinni\u015bcie czyni\u0107, a przez to unika\u0107 z\u0142a. \u015awiadomo\u015b\u0107, \u017ce \"B\u00f3g jest Bogiem \u017cywych\" musi pozosta\u0107 w ludzkim stworzeniu, tylko w ten spos\u00f3b ludzko\u015b\u0107 b\u0119dzie d\u0105\u017cy\u0107 do bycia bardziej duchow\u0105 z pe\u0142n\u0105 \u015bwiadomo\u015bci\u0105, \u017ce bez Boga s\u0105 niczym. \u017byjcie w niestrudzonym d\u0105\u017ceniu do zbli\u017cenia si\u0119 do Tr\u00f3jcy \u015awi\u0119tej, do naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki, do Archanio\u0142\u00f3w i Anio\u0142\u00f3w, aby\u015bcie mogli \u017cy\u0107 pragn\u0105c tego, co boskie oraz pracowa\u0107 i dzia\u0142a\u0107 w ramach dobra. Dzieci Bo\u017ce, znajdujecie si\u0119 w chwili oczekiwania przed wype\u0142nieniem si\u0119 proroctw zapowiedzianych wyra\u017anymi znakami, kt\u00f3re zapowiadaj\u0105 to, co ma nadej\u015b\u0107: Popatrzcie na natur\u0119, jak ona dzia\u0142a... Stworzenie ludzkie oddali\u0142o si\u0119 od \u015bwi\u0105ty\u0144 i nie adoruj\u0105 naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa..... Przyjmuj\u0105 \u015bwi\u0119t\u0105 eucharysti\u0119 w grzechu \u015bmiertelnym.... Gardz\u0105 i odmawiaj\u0105 modlitw\u0119 r\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ca \u015bwi\u0119tego.... Wy\u015bmiewaj\u0105 sakramentalia.... Naj\u015bwi\u0119tsza Tr\u00f3jca wzywa swoich kap\u0142an\u00f3w do godnego ubierania si\u0119 w szaty kap\u0142a\u0144skie, poniewa\u017c ubieranie si\u0119 w nie doprowadzi\u0142o do tego, \u017ce nie s\u0105 oni szanowani i myleni z istotami nie po\u015bwi\u0119conymi do pos\u0142ugi kap\u0142a\u0144skiej. Lud naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa musi by\u0107 stale przygotowany na nadchodz\u0105cy niedob\u00f3r \u017cywno\u015bci i siln\u0105 zmian\u0119 klimatu, zw\u0142aszcza w Europie. Na j\u0105dro ziemi oddzia\u0142uje magnetyzm cia\u0142a niebieskiego zbli\u017caj\u0105cego si\u0119 do ziemi. Europa przejdzie przez ten czas z ekstremalnymi opadami \u015bniegu i zimnem nie odczuwanym wcze\u015bniej. Ameryka do\u015bwiadczy zmian w swoim klimacie, temperatury spadn\u0105 i b\u0119d\u0105 odczuwa\u0107 zimno, ale nie tak ekstremalne. Jest to czas ostrze\u017cenia dla nich, aby uwierzyli i naprawili swoje drogi. Woda pojawia si\u0119 tam, gdzie jest piasek, a gdzie jest woda, pojawia si\u0119 piasek. Wulkany rycz\u0105 w r\u00f3\u017cnych krajach na ca\u0142ej ziemi. Pustynia jest naje\u017cd\u017cana przez wod\u0119, a gdzie jest woda, tam b\u0119dzie pustynia. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Pana i Kr\u00f3la Jezusa Chrystusa o nawr\u00f3cenie ludzko\u015bci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 o kontynent azjatycki. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa o niedob\u00f3r \u017cywno\u015bci. Modlitwa, modlitwa dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa za powstania spo\u0142eczne i prze\u015bladowania w krajach. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, z wn\u0119trza kraj\u00f3w, kt\u00f3re was przyj\u0119\u0142y, wyjd\u0105 zagorzali prze\u015bladowcy wiary chrze\u015bcija\u0144skiej. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, zachowaj nasz\u0105 Kr\u00f3low\u0105 i Matk\u0119 uwa\u017cn\u0105 na potrzeby ka\u017cdego przez modlitw\u0119 r\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ca \u015bwi\u0119tego, aby pycha, kt\u00f3ra ro\u015bnie w ludzkim stworzeniu, zosta\u0142a os\u0142abiona i pokonana przez pokor\u0119. Pycha jest charakterystyczna dla z\u0142ego, ciemi\u0119\u017cyciela dusz, grz\u0119\u017anie w stworzeniu, otacza je z\u0142em i zawi\u015bci\u0105. Pycha deformuje istot\u0119 ludzk\u0105 w jej dzia\u0142aniach i czynach, za\u015blepia j\u0105 i czyni nierozpoznawaln\u0105. Dzia\u0142aj z pokor\u0105, nie z fa\u0142szyw\u0105 pokor\u0105, nie z wymuszon\u0105 pokor\u0105, ale z pokor\u0105 \u015bwiat\u0142a, kt\u00f3re pochodzi od naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Wierzcie, wierzcie, pokonujcie grzech, stanowczo \u017ca\u0142ujcie przez wyznanie i z mocnym celem poprawy, aby\u015bcie byli nowymi i odnowionymi stworzeniami przez Mi\u0142osierdzie Bo\u017ce. B\u0105d\u017acie czujni duchowo, b\u0105d\u017acie prostymi i pokornymi istotami serca. Wiedza nie powinna by\u0107 wystawiana na pokaz, ale stosowana jako \u015bwiadectwo tego, co mieszka w ka\u017cdym z was. Roztropno\u015b\u0107 jest wielk\u0105 towarzyszk\u0105 dar\u00f3w. Roztropni nie nara\u017caj\u0105 si\u0119 na obalenie. S\u0105 to powa\u017cne czasy, bardzo powa\u017cne czasy, w kt\u00f3rych pokusy, niezadowolenie, podzia\u0142y i przyjemno\u015bci s\u0105 rozprzestrzeniane z po\u015bpiechem przez duchy z\u0142a. Stworzenie ludzkie, kt\u00f3re si\u0119 nawraca, kt\u00f3re uznaje Boga za swojego Pana i Zbawiciela i rozpoczyna nowe \u017cycie, jest prowadzone przez swojego anio\u0142a str\u00f3\u017ca, towarzysza w drodze, aby si\u0119 nie zgubi\u0142o. Id\u017acie naprz\u00f3d dzieci Bo\u017ce, id\u017acie naprz\u00f3d zjednoczeni w oczekiwaniu na spe\u0142nienie si\u0119 wszystkiego, co zosta\u0142o przepowiedziane. Zachowajcie pok\u00f3j i b\u0105d\u017acie braterscy. Towarzysz\u0105 wam moje legiony, chroni was nasza Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka, ratuje was krew Boskiego Baranka. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119, wzrastajcie w wierze! \u015awi\u0119ty Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":12,"day":19,"month_string":"December","author":"Jesus Christ","text_en":"My beloved people, Children of my Sacred Heart, I bless you with my love, I bless you with faith, I bless you with fraternity, I bless you with my truth, so that you would be aware at all times that without charity, you will not overcome human selfishness, nor its fruit, which is hatred - and my children are saturated with hatred at this time. You must look within yourselves, even if it is difficult for you. My arrogant children do not listen to me; they look at their brothers and sisters without looking at themselves and these human creatures of mine must change so that they would learn to offer up their pain to me and learn to be humble. It is humility that you need at this time, for charity is not only about helping the needy, but loving and respecting one\u2019s neighbour with their faults and virtues. Humanity lacks everything that I have mentioned to you... Therefore, it is very important and indispensable that each one of you pray and offer me Eucharistic Communions in reparation for the errors with which my church is offending me. And bear in mind that receiving me in a state of grace, worthily prepared, as well as the prayer of the holy rosary, can succeed in lessening the intensity of some of the events to come, if it is my will. My people, some of my children are asking themselves, why is it that the most serious part of what heaven has announced in these prophecies is not happening? My children, if you would think, if you would reflect on what you want, you would retract and regret it. My people, great tragedy will come to some countries when they least expect it because of remaining distracted by the distorted Christmas of man today. The celebration of my birth has become a pagan festival, with representations of my birth that in some cases are shameful. They have wanted to force me into the pagan current of this time, even within my church. May those who mock my birth be anathema. My beloved people, the battle between good and evil continues with greater force. My beloved St. Michael the Archangel is defending you with all his heavenly armies, otherwise you would find yourselves at war. It is necessary for each one of my children, on a personal level, to be responsible to humanity by being light in the midst of so much darkness that surrounds you. South America, land of spiritual fruits and great resources, will be subjected to the uprisings that will recur in several south American countries. Children of my sacred heart: Do not take my word lightly: war is being prepared by those who believe they lead humanity, politicians, and nations. Pray, my children, pray for Brazil, prayer is urgent for this endangered nation. Prayer to my Divine Mercy offered for this land beloved by me and my Mother at three o'clock in the afternoon of each country, as well as the recitation of the holy rosary, with the offering of holy communion, is a blessing for my beloved land. Pray my children, pray for Argentina: this land that I love has disrespected me and has disrespected my Mother, whom some of my children love so much. I asked for Argentina to be consecrated to the Sacred Hearts and this request was taken lightly. My Mother who came as an intercessor was not obeyed. What my Mother wanted with all her heart to hold back, was greeted with disbelief. This is why the purification will be undergone that this people are bringing about. Pray, my children, pray for Peru: this nation is suffering from internal strife. Pray, my children, pray for Europe: the scourge of war is spreading. Cold will come, threatening my children. Pray for Italy and pray for Spain: they will suffer. Pray where war causes innocent people to perish. My people, social uprisings will spread throughout the earth, exacerbating famine, disease, persecution and injustice. The earth will shake continually with greater intensity. At times it will shake from within the earth; at other times the hand of man will intervene, and he will be punished for his wrongdoing. I come to the heart of each person as a beggar of love\u2026 I come in search of a place to warm my little defenceless body... I am the King of love in search of hearts of flesh to shelter me. My children, I do not want fearful people, but creatures of faith, with so much faith that they are aware that 'I am their God', and I will not abandon them. Keep your faith growing constantly. Fraternity is necessary at this time and respect is a barrier against evil. Be creatures of love, generous in patience and wanting the well-being of your neighbour. I love you, my children, I love you. My Sacred Heart burns with love for each one of you. I bless you. Your Jesus. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany ludu, Dzieci mojego Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszego Serca, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was wiar\u0105, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was braterstwem, b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was moj\u0105 prawd\u0105, aby\u015bcie zawsze byli \u015bwiadomi, \u017ce bez mi\u0142o\u015bci nie pokonacie ludzkiego egoizmu, ani jego owocu, kt\u00f3rym jest nienawi\u015b\u0107 - a moje dzieci s\u0105 w tym czasie przesycone nienawi\u015bci\u0105. Musicie patrze\u0107 w siebie, nawet je\u015bli jest to dla was trudne. Moje aroganckie dzieci nie s\u0142uchaj\u0105 mnie, patrz\u0105 na swoich braci i siostry, nie patrz\u0105c na siebie i te moje ludzkie stworzenia musz\u0105 si\u0119 zmieni\u0107, aby nauczy\u0142y si\u0119 ofiarowa\u0107 mi sw\u00f3j b\u00f3l i nauczy\u0107 si\u0119 pokory. To w\u0142a\u015bnie pokora jest wam potrzebna w tym czasie, bo dobroczynno\u015b\u0107 to nie tylko pomoc potrzebuj\u0105cym, ale mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 i szacunek dla bli\u017aniego z jego wadami i zaletami. Ludzko\u015bci brakuje wszystkiego, co wam wymieni\u0142em... Dlatego bardzo wa\u017cne i nieodzowne jest, aby ka\u017cdy z was modli\u0142 si\u0119 i ofiarowa\u0142 Mi Komuni\u0119 eucharystyczn\u0105 w zado\u015b\u0107uczynieniu za b\u0142\u0119dy, kt\u00f3rymi obra\u017ca Mnie m\u00f3j Ko\u015bci\u00f3\u0142. I pami\u0119tajcie, \u017ce przyjmowanie mnie w stanie \u0142aski, godnie przygotowanego, jak r\u00f3wnie\u017c modlitwa r\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ca \u015bwi\u0119tego, mo\u017ce zdo\u0142a\u0107 zmniejszy\u0107 intensywno\u015b\u0107 niekt\u00f3rych wydarze\u0144, kt\u00f3re maj\u0105 nadej\u015b\u0107, je\u015bli taka jest moja wola. M\u00f3j lud, niekt\u00f3re z moich dzieci zadaj\u0105 sobie pytanie: dlaczego nie dzieje si\u0119 najpowa\u017cniejsza cz\u0119\u015b\u0107 tego, co niebo zapowiedzia\u0142o w tych proroctwach? Moje dzieci, gdyby\u015bcie pomy\u015bleli, gdyby\u015bcie zastanowili si\u0119 nad tym, czego chcecie, wycofaliby\u015bcie si\u0119 i po\u017ca\u0142owali. M\u00f3j lud, wielka tragedia przyjdzie do niekt\u00f3rych kraj\u00f3w, kiedy najmniej si\u0119 tego spodziewaj\u0105, z powodu pozostawania w rozproszeniu przez zniekszta\u0142cone Bo\u017ce Narodzenie dzisiejszego cz\u0142owieka. Obchody moich narodzin sta\u0142y si\u0119 poga\u0144skim \u015bwi\u0119tem, z przedstawieniami moich narodzin, kt\u00f3re w niekt\u00f3rych przypadkach s\u0105 haniebne. Chcieli mnie wt\u0142oczy\u0107 w poga\u0144ski nurt tego czasu, nawet w moim ko\u015bciele. Niech ci, kt\u00f3rzy wy\u015bmiewaj\u0105 moje narodziny, zostan\u0105 ob\u0142o\u017ceni anatem\u0105. M\u00f3j umi\u0142owany lud, walka mi\u0119dzy dobrem a z\u0142em trwa z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 si\u0142\u0105. M\u00f3j ukochany \u015bw. Micha\u0142 Archanio\u0142 broni was wszystkimi swoimi niebia\u0144skimi armiami, inaczej znale\u017aliby\u015bcie si\u0119 w stanie wojny. Konieczne jest, aby ka\u017cde z moich dzieci, na poziomie osobistym, by\u0142o odpowiedzialne wobec ludzko\u015bci, b\u0119d\u0105c \u015bwiat\u0142em po\u015br\u00f3d tak wielu ciemno\u015bci, kt\u00f3re was otaczaj\u0105. Ameryka Po\u0142udniowa, ziemia duchowych owoc\u00f3w i wielkich zasob\u00f3w, b\u0119dzie poddana powstaniom, kt\u00f3re powt\u00f3rz\u0105 si\u0119 w kilku krajach Ameryki Po\u0142udniowej. Dzieci mojego \u015bwi\u0119tego serca: Nie traktujcie moich s\u0142\u00f3w lekko: wojna jest przygotowywana przez tych, kt\u00f3rzy uwa\u017caj\u0105, \u017ce przewodz\u0105 ludzko\u015bci, politykom i narodom. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Brazyli\u0119, modlitwa jest pilna dla tego zagro\u017conego narodu. Modlitwa do mojego Mi\u0142osierdzia Bo\u017cego ofiarowana za t\u0119 ziemi\u0119 umi\u0142owan\u0105 przeze mnie i moj\u0105 Matk\u0119 o godzinie trzeciej po po\u0142udniu w ka\u017cdym kraju, jak r\u00f3wnie\u017c odmawianie r\u00f3\u017ca\u0144ca \u015bwi\u0119tego, z ofiarowaniem komunii \u015bwi\u0119tej, jest b\u0142ogos\u0142awie\u0144stwem dla mojej ukochanej ziemi. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Argentyn\u0119: ta ziemia, kt\u00f3r\u0105 kocham, nie uszanowa\u0142a Mnie i nie uszanowa\u0142a mojej Matki, kt\u00f3r\u0105 niekt\u00f3re z moich dzieci tak bardzo kochaj\u0105. Prosi\u0142am o po\u015bwi\u0119cenie Argentyny Naj\u015bwi\u0119tszym Sercom i ta pro\u015bba zosta\u0142a potraktowana lekcewa\u017c\u0105co. Moja Matka, kt\u00f3ra przyby\u0142a jako or\u0119downiczka, nie by\u0142a pos\u0142uszna. To, co Moja Matka chcia\u0142a z ca\u0142ego serca powstrzyma\u0107, zosta\u0142o powitane z niedowierzaniem. Dlatego nast\u0105pi oczyszczenie, kt\u00f3re ten lud wprowadza. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Peru: ten nar\u00f3d cierpi z powodu wewn\u0119trznych spor\u00f3w. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Europ\u0119: plaga wojny si\u0119 rozprzestrzenia. Przyjdzie zimno, zagra\u017caj\u0105ce moim dzieciom. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za W\u0142ochy i m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Hiszpani\u0119: b\u0119d\u0105 cierpie\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 tam, gdzie wojna powoduje \u015bmier\u0107 niewinnych ludzi. M\u00f3j ludu, powstania spo\u0142eczne b\u0119d\u0105 si\u0119 szerzy\u0107 na ca\u0142ej ziemi, zaostrzaj\u0105c g\u0142\u00f3d, choroby, prze\u015bladowania i niesprawiedliwo\u015b\u0107. Ziemia b\u0119dzie si\u0119 trz\u0105\u015b\u0107 nieustannie z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 intensywno\u015bci\u0105. Niekiedy b\u0119dzie si\u0119 trz\u0105\u015b\u0107 z wn\u0119trza ziemi; innym razem interweniowa\u0107 b\u0119dzie r\u0119ka cz\u0142owieka, kt\u00f3ry zostanie ukarany za swoje z\u0142e post\u0119powanie. Przychodz\u0119 do serca ka\u017cdego cz\u0142owieka jako \u017cebrak mi\u0142o\u015bci... Przychodz\u0119 w poszukiwaniu miejsca, gdzie m\u00f3g\u0142bym ogrza\u0107 moje ma\u0142e bezbronne cia\u0142o... Jestem Kr\u00f3lem mi\u0142o\u015bci szukaj\u0105cym serc cielesnych, kt\u00f3re by mnie schroni\u0142y. Moje dzieci, nie chc\u0119 ludzi boja\u017aliwych, ale istot wierz\u0105cych, z tak wielk\u0105 wiar\u0105, \u017ce maj\u0105 \u015bwiadomo\u015b\u0107, i\u017c \"Ja jestem ich Bogiem\", a Ja ich nie opuszcz\u0119. Niech wasza wiara stale ro\u015bnie. Braterstwo jest w tym czasie konieczne, a szacunek jest barier\u0105 przed z\u0142em. B\u0105d\u017acie istotami mi\u0142o\u015bci, hojnymi w cierpliwo\u015bci i pragn\u0105cymi dobra bli\u017aniego. Kocham was, moje dzieci, kocham was. Moje Naj\u015bwi\u0119tsze Serce p\u0142onie mi\u0142o\u015bci\u0105 do ka\u017cdego z was. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 was. Wasz Jezus. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":12,"day":23,"month_string":"December","author":"Archangel Michael","text_en":"Beloved people of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: I am sent by the most Holy Trinity to reach the heart of all humanity who, as god\u2019s people, must save their souls. In commemorating the birth of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, every human being may place their whole physical and spiritual being before this divine child, so that with a person\u2019s fervent desire, they would be transformed by love, truth, goodness, charity, and all the gifts and virtues with which the infant Jesus adorns his children.  Children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ, humanity continues living in a chaos of unstoppable violence that spreads from one person to another, sometimes consenting to it without knowing why, but merely in order to imitate their brothers\u2019 behaviour. This is the intention of the powerful: to see to it that the human race would self-destruct in terms of morality, society, spirituality, food, and economics, so that, due to such a weight of inappropriate acts, human beings would renounce the most Holy Trinity, our Queen and Mother, and despise everything that reminds them of the divine, blaming God for everything that happens. As we commemorate the Nativity of the infant Jesus, evil is assaulting humanity more forcefully at this time than in the past, in view of the proximity of what our Queen and Mother has been warning you about for so long. It is human beings who have given free rein to their human will, going down various wrong paths that have led them to this moment. People of our King and Lord Jesus Christ: as we commemorate the Nativity, the affairs of men do not stop: conflicts continue, persecutions increase, and the unexpected will occur due to constant warfare on the part of evil, which humanity is allowing to undermine its life. Pray, pray for Mexico: it will suffer due to nature. Pray, pray, pray for Brazil without ceasing: your brothers and sisters need your prayers. Pray, pray for strength for the whole of humanity. Pray, pray for Europe: you urgently need to pray for Europe - it will suffer due to nature and man himself. You have a rocky road ahead of you. . . A single religion will impose itself on humanity, which easily surrenders to innovations. Human creatures forget that the cross of our King and Lord Jesus Christ is impregnated with the salvation of every human being, and that it is only on the path of truth and repentance that you can find salvation. You forget that our Queen and Mother drive away the devil: he fears her, and our Queen and Mother is attentive to her Son\u2019s people. You are on a path filled with every temptation, with the snares of evil, with the insinuations of evil, and evil knows that this is the time for it to take its spoils of souls. You must be strong and firm so as not to fall. Children of God, remain attentive and do not be careless, because from one moment to the next, there may be a conflict, planned in advance. Without exposing yourselves in the midst of the strife, each one of you should keep calm and stay where you are until you find a safe opportunity to leave, if you must do so. My legions are attentively awaiting your calls to come in haste, children of our King and Lord Jesus Christ. A great sign from on high is coming. Each one of you knows that Divine Protection is over humanity. Divine mercy is infinite: ask our King and Lord Jesus Christ for it to penetrate within you, and give him permission to make of each one of you a new creature, so that you would succeed in overcoming the many trials that humanity has brought upon itself. Adore the infant Jesus in the manger, in every home, in every place where he is correctly represented. My legions are caring for each one of you. I bless and protect you with my sword held high. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owany ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: Jestem pos\u0142any przez Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105, aby dotrze\u0107 do serca ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci, kt\u00f3ra jako lud Bo\u017cy musi ratowa\u0107 swoje dusze. Upami\u0119tniaj\u0105c narodziny naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, ka\u017cdy cz\u0142owiek niech z\u0142o\u017cy ca\u0142\u0105 swoj\u0105 fizyczn\u0105 i duchow\u0105 istot\u0119 przed tym Boskim Dzieci\u0119ciem, aby przy gor\u0105cym pragnieniu cz\u0142owieka, zosta\u0142 on przemieniony przez mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107, prawd\u0119, dobro\u0107, mi\u0142osierdzie i wszystkie dary i cnoty, kt\u00f3rymi Dzieci\u0105tko Jezus ozdabia swoje dzieci.  Dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, ludzko\u015b\u0107 nadal \u017cyje w chaosie niepowstrzymanej przemocy, kt\u00f3ra rozprzestrzenia si\u0119 z jednej osoby na drug\u0105, czasem godz\u0105c si\u0119 na ni\u0105 nie wiedz\u0105c dlaczego, a jedynie po to, by na\u015bladowa\u0107 zachowanie swoich braci. Taki jest zamiar pot\u0119\u017cnych: dopilnowa\u0107, aby rasa ludzka uleg\u0142a samozniszczeniu pod wzgl\u0119dem moralno\u015bci, spo\u0142ecze\u0144stwa, duchowo\u015bci, po\u017cywienia i ekonomii, aby z powodu takiego ci\u0119\u017caru niew\u0142a\u015bciwych czyn\u00f3w istoty ludzkie wyrzek\u0142y si\u0119 Tr\u00f3jcy Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tszej, naszej Kr\u00f3lowej i Matki, i gardzi\u0142y wszystkim, co przypomina im o bosko\u015bci, obwiniaj\u0105c Boga za wszystko, co si\u0119 dzieje. Gdy obchodzimy pami\u0105tk\u0119 Narodzenia Dzieci\u0105tka Jezus, z\u0142o napada na ludzko\u015b\u0107 w tym czasie mocniej ni\u017c w przesz\u0142o\u015bci, wobec blisko\u015bci tego, przed czym tak d\u0142ugo ostrzega\u0142a was nasza Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka. To istoty ludzkie da\u0142y woln\u0105 r\u0119k\u0119 swojej ludzkiej woli, id\u0105c r\u00f3\u017cnymi z\u0142ymi drogami, kt\u00f3re doprowadzi\u0142y je do tej chwili. Ludu naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa: gdy obchodzimy pami\u0105tk\u0119 Narodzenia Pa\u0144skiego, sprawy ludzi nie ustaj\u0105: konflikty trwaj\u0105, prze\u015bladowania nasilaj\u0105 si\u0119, a niespodziewane zdarzenia b\u0119d\u0105 mia\u0142y miejsce z powodu ci\u0105g\u0142ych dzia\u0142a\u0144 wojennych ze strony z\u0142a, kt\u00f3remu ludzko\u015b\u0107 pozwala podkopywa\u0107 swoje \u017cycie. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Meksyk: b\u0119dzie cierpia\u0142 z powodu natury. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Brazyli\u0119 bez przerwy: wasi bracia i siostry potrzebuj\u0105 waszych modlitw. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 o si\u0142\u0119 dla ca\u0142ej ludzko\u015bci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Europ\u0119: pilnie potrzebujecie modlitwy za Europ\u0119 - b\u0119dzie ona cierpie\u0107 z powodu natury i samego cz\u0142owieka. Macie przed sob\u0105 kamienist\u0105 drog\u0119. . . Jedna religia narzuci si\u0119 ludzko\u015bci, kt\u00f3ra \u0142atwo poddaje si\u0119 innowacjom. Ludzkie stworzenia zapominaj\u0105, \u017ce krzy\u017c naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa jest impregnowany na zbawienie ka\u017cdego cz\u0142owieka i \u017ce tylko na drodze prawdy i pokuty mo\u017cna znale\u017a\u0107 zbawienie. Zapominacie, \u017ce nasza Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka odp\u0119dza diab\u0142a: on si\u0119 Jej boi, a nasza Kr\u00f3lowa i Matka jest uwa\u017cna na lud swego Syna. Jeste\u015bcie na drodze pe\u0142nej wszelkich pokus, side\u0142 z\u0142a, insynuacji z\u0142a, a z\u0142o wie, \u017ce jest to czas dla niego, aby wzi\u0105\u0107 sw\u00f3j \u0142up z dusz. Musicie by\u0107 silni i stanowczy, aby nie upa\u015b\u0107. Dzieci Bo\u017ce, b\u0105d\u017acie uwa\u017cni i nie b\u0105d\u017acie nieostro\u017cni, bo z jednej chwili na drug\u0105 mo\u017ce nast\u0105pi\u0107 konflikt, zaplanowany z g\u00f3ry. Nie nara\u017caj\u0105c si\u0119 w samym \u015brodku sporu, ka\u017cdy z was powinien zachowa\u0107 spok\u00f3j i pozosta\u0107 tam, gdzie jest, dop\u00f3ki nie znajdziecie bezpiecznej mo\u017cliwo\u015bci odej\u015bcia, je\u015bli musicie to zrobi\u0107. Moje legiony z uwag\u0105 oczekuj\u0105 waszych wezwa\u0144 do przybycia w po\u015bpiechu, dzieci naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa. Nadchodzi wielki znak z wysoka. Ka\u017cdy z was wie, \u017ce Boska Ochrona jest nad ludzko\u015bci\u0105. Mi\u0142osierdzie Bo\u017ce jest niesko\u0144czone: pro\u015bcie naszego Kr\u00f3la i Pana Jezusa Chrystusa, aby przenikn\u0119\u0142o w was i dajcie Mu pozwolenie, aby z ka\u017cdego z was uczyni\u0142 nowe stworzenie, aby\u015bcie zdo\u0142ali pokona\u0107 wiele pr\u00f3b, kt\u00f3re ludzko\u015b\u0107 na siebie sprowadzi\u0142a. Adorujcie Dzieci\u0105tko Jezus w \u017c\u0142\u00f3bku, w ka\u017cdym domu, w ka\u017cdym miejscu, gdzie jest prawid\u0142owo przedstawiane. Moje legiony troszcz\u0105 si\u0119 o ka\u017cdego z was. B\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0119 i chroni\u0119 was z moim mieczem trzymanym wysoko. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"},{"year":2022,"month":12,"day":27,"month_string":"December","author":"Holy Mary","text_en":"Beloved children of my immaculate heart: I come to you to bless you and to bring you my motherly love. Faith is indispensable, my children, in order for you to remain in union with my Divine Son. Spiritually prepared, human beings will be able to stand in the midst of all that will come to fulfilment. I am speaking to you in terms of human time... Prepare yourselves, children, be more spiritual: it is urgent. Prepare yourselves, children, with what you have at your disposal. Do not wait to prepare, do it now. The time of darkness is coming, and yet by keeping the faith and being fraternal towards one another, my children will manage to help each other. Beloved children of my Divine Son, war will continue on earth with greater force, bringing famine, which will spread without stopping. My little children, in the constant calls to prepare yourselves, the Father\u2019s House has insisted that you should look at the signs and signals that have announced what will become humanity\u2019s sad reality. Show foresight: cold will come, replacing heat, and heat will replace cold. Stay alert: tensions between countries will become wars between countries. Humanity will remain in a constant state of anxiety. Darkness will come to various countries in the midst of war. Pray, my children, pray for all humanity. Pray, my children, pray for India, its people will suffer. Pray, my children, pray, do not wait; pay attention, children. Pray, my children, pray that your faith would grow as events progress. Pray, my children, pray, pray; earthquakes will continue on a larger scale. My children: As your Mother I advise you to strengthen your faith in the most Holy Trinity, so that you would keep silence, meditate and be people in whom the love of my son reigns, in order that you would not sin by harming your neighbour. Beloved children, being confronted with your own sins will be hard... Do not worsen it by sinning against your neighbour. My Divine Son suffers because of the weight of humanity\u2019s evil works and behaviour. Be fraternal, help one another, respect one another and pray that you would not fall into sin. Be creatures of peace and use your tongues to worship the most Holy Trinity. As creatures of goodness, adore my son 'in spirit and in truth'. Love your brothers and sisters as my son and I love them. Do not fear: 'am I not here who am your Mother?' I am protecting you. Mother Mary. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin. Hail Mary most pure, conceived without sin.","text_de":"","text_es":"","text_fr":"","text_it":"","text_pl":"Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego niepokalanego serca: Przychodz\u0119 do was, aby was b\u0142ogos\u0142awi\u0107 i przynie\u015b\u0107 wam moj\u0105 matczyn\u0105 mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107. Wiara jest niezb\u0119dna, moje dzieci, aby\u015bcie mogli pozosta\u0107 w jedno\u015bci z moim Boskim Synem. Przygotowane duchowo istoty ludzkie b\u0119d\u0105 mog\u0142y stan\u0105\u0107 po\u015br\u00f3d tego wszystkiego, co si\u0119 spe\u0142ni. M\u00f3wi\u0119 do was w kategoriach czasu ludzkiego... Przygotujcie si\u0119, dzieci, b\u0105d\u017acie bardziej duchowi: jest to pilne. Przygotujcie si\u0119, dzieci, z tym, co macie do dyspozycji. Nie czekajcie z przygotowaniem, zr\u00f3bcie to teraz. Nadchodzi czas ciemno\u015bci, a jednak zachowuj\u0105c wiar\u0119 i b\u0119d\u0105c braterskimi wobec siebie, moje dzieci zdo\u0142aj\u0105 sobie pom\u00f3c. Umi\u0142owane dzieci mojego Boskiego Syna, wojna b\u0119dzie trwa\u0142a na ziemi z wi\u0119ksz\u0105 si\u0142\u0105, przynosz\u0105c g\u0142\u00f3d, kt\u00f3ry b\u0119dzie si\u0119 rozprzestrzenia\u0142 bez przerwy. Moje ma\u0142e dzieci, w ci\u0105g\u0142ych wezwaniach do przygotowania si\u0119, Dom Ojca nalega\u0142, aby\u015bcie patrzyli na znaki i sygna\u0142y, kt\u00f3re zapowiada\u0142y to, co stanie si\u0119 smutn\u0105 rzeczywisto\u015bci\u0105 ludzko\u015bci. Wyka\u017ccie si\u0119 przezorno\u015bci\u0105: przyjdzie zimno, zast\u0119puj\u0105c ciep\u0142o, a ciep\u0142o zast\u0105pi zimno. B\u0105d\u017acie czujni: napi\u0119cia mi\u0119dzy pa\u0144stwami stan\u0105 si\u0119 wojnami mi\u0119dzy pa\u0144stwami. Ludzko\u015b\u0107 pozostanie w ci\u0105g\u0142ym stanie niepokoju. Ciemno\u015b\u0107 przyjdzie do r\u00f3\u017cnych kraj\u00f3w w trakcie wojny. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, Moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za ca\u0142\u0105 ludzko\u015b\u0107. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119 za Indie, ich lud b\u0119dzie cierpia\u0142. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, nie czekajcie; zwr\u00f3\u0107cie uwag\u0119, dzieci. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, aby wasza wiara ros\u0142a w miar\u0119 rozwoju wydarze\u0144. M\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, moje dzieci, m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119; trz\u0119sienia ziemi b\u0119d\u0105 kontynuowane na wi\u0119ksz\u0105 skal\u0119. Moje dzieci: Jako wasza Matka radz\u0119 wam umocni\u0107 wiar\u0119 w Tr\u00f3jc\u0119 Przenaj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105, aby\u015bcie zachowywali milczenie, medytowali i byli lud\u017ami, w kt\u00f3rych panuje mi\u0142o\u015b\u0107 mojego Syna, aby\u015bcie nie zgrzeszyli krzywdz\u0105c bli\u017aniego. Umi\u0142owane dzieci, konfrontacja z w\u0142asnymi grzechami b\u0119dzie trudna... Nie pogarszajcie tego, grzesz\u0105c przeciwko bli\u017aniemu. M\u00f3j Boski Syn cierpi z powodu ci\u0119\u017caru z\u0142ych dzie\u0142 i zachowa\u0144 ludzko\u015bci. B\u0105d\u017acie braterscy, pomagajcie sobie wzajemnie, szanujcie si\u0119 i m\u00f3dlcie si\u0119, aby\u015bcie nie popadli w grzech. B\u0105d\u017acie stworzeniami pokoju i u\u017cywajcie swoich j\u0119zyk\u00f3w, aby wielbi\u0107 Naj\u015bwi\u0119tsz\u0105 Tr\u00f3jc\u0119. Jako stworzenia dobra, adorujcie mojego Syna \"w duchu i w prawdzie\". Kochajcie swoich braci i siostry, tak jak m\u00f3j Syn i ja ich kochamy. Nie l\u0119kajcie si\u0119: \"czy\u017c nie jestem tu, kt\u00f3ra jestem wasz\u0105 Matk\u0105?\". Ja was chroni\u0119. Mama Maryja. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta. Zdrowa\u015b Maryjo najczystsza, bez grzechu pocz\u0119ta.","text_pt":"","text_zh":"","source":"Argentina"}]